NK107(tse)001:0: pan chen dri med bshes gnyen gyi dgongs nyams sgron
NK107(tse)001:1: ma snang byed 'bar ba'i gsang rgyud glegs bam dang
NK107(tse)001:2: po bzhugs so sgra thal 'gyur rtsa rgyud 'grel e
NK107(tse)001:3: ma ho 'dir rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:4: snying po las snying por gyur pa sgron ma 'bar
NK107(tse)001:5: ba rtsa ba'i rgyud 'di bdud rtsi 'o ma'i rgya
NK107(tse)001:6: mtsho lta bu'i nang nas mar gyi snying po lta
NK107(tse)001:7: bu rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po lung thams cad
NK107(tse)001:8: kyi gal mdo man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba
NK107(tse)001:9: rgyud 'bum phrag bcu bdun gyi yang zhun pan chen
NK107(tse)001:10: dri med bshes gnyen nam mtshan gzhan du b+hi ma
NK107(tse)001:11: la mi tra zhes snyan pa'i ba dan phyogs bcur
NK107(tse)001:12: khyab pa'i slob dpon chen po'i dgongs pa khyad par
NK107(tse)001:13: can 'di la don rnam pa lnga yis legs par
NK107(tse)001:14: bstan te rgyud kyi ngo bo nges tshig dbye ba
NK107(tse)001:15: bsdus don gtan la dbab pa dang lnga las 'di
NK107(tse)001:16: ni ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi gnad
NK107(tse)001:17: don 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs nyi
NK107(tse)001:18: ma'i snying po'i chos skor sgron ma 'bar ba'i gsang
NK107(tse)001:19: rgyud khyad par can bzhugs la sna tshogs sems yin
NK107(tse)001:20: du smra ba la sogs pa gsum mo de yang
NK107(tse)001:21: sna tshogs sems yin du smra ba'i rdzogs pa chen
NK107(tse)001:22: mo la gsum ste sems kyi snang tshul brten nas
NK107(tse)001:23: snang ba thams cad chos skur 'dod pa dang sems
NK107(tse)001:24: kyi 'khrul tshul la brten nas 'khrul pa la sna
NK107(tse)001:25: tshogs sems yin du smra ba la sogs pa gsum
NK107(tse)001:26: mo de yang sna tshogs sems yin du smra ba'i
NK107(tse)001:27: rdzogs pa chen mo la gsum ste sems kyi snang
NK107(tse)001:28: tshul la brten nas snang ba thams cad chos skur
NK107(tse)001:29: 'dod pa dang sems kyi 'khrul tshul la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:30: 'khrul pa ye shes su 'dod pa dang sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:31: rtogs tshul la brten nas 'gro ba drug rang grol
NK107(tse)001:32: du smra ba'i rdzogs pa che'o lhun grub rdzogs tshul
NK107(tse)001:33: du smra ba'i rdzogs pa chen po la yang gsum
NK107(tse)001:34: ste rang bzhin lhun grub rang bzhin med par smra
NK107(tse)001:35: ba dang nges med snang tshod mthun snang tsam du
NK107(tse)001:36: smra ba dang rol pa 'gag med ci byas thams
NK107(tse)001:37: cad sto med du smra ba'i rdzogs pa chen po'o
NK107(tse)001:38: snang tshul thams cad rang byung ye shes su smra
NK107(tse)001:39: ba'i rdzogs pa chen po la yang gsum ste gzhan
NK107(tse)001:40: sngos 'dul zad du smra ba dang dran pa khyungs
NK107(tse)001:41: 'gags thol byung chen por smra ba dang snang sems
NK107(tse)001:42: thug phrad kyi 'khor lo rdzogs par smra ba'i rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:43: pa chen po'o de dag ni rdzogs pa sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:44: rang bzhin dang rtsal la yon tan du blta ba'o
NK107(tse)001:45: 'khrul pa rang gdangs su smra ba'i rdzogs pa chen
NK107(tse)001:46: po la gsum ste rang byung gi ye shes las
NK107(tse)001:47: mi 'gyur bar smra ba dang mtha' bzhi rang grol
NK107(tse)001:48: du smra ba dang 'khor ba la thog mtha' med
NK107(tse)001:49: par smra ba'o byung tshul rang grol du smra ba
NK107(tse)001:50: la gsum ste snang stong rang sa nas grol bar
NK107(tse)001:51: 'dod pa dang 'khor ba dong nas sprugs par smra
NK107(tse)001:52: ba dang sgra bzhis 'jug khyab tu smra ba'i rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:53: pa chen po'o de dag ni lta spyod gtso bor
NK107(tse)001:54: ston pas 'khor 'das khar sbyor du blta ba'o yang
NK107(tse)001:55: gzhi mdung bsgyur du smra ba la yang gsum ste
NK107(tse)001:56: brtags pa lam khyer du smra ba dang 'khrul snang
NK107(tse)001:57: gzhi bzhag tu smra ba dang gnad 'dus byer snang
NK107(tse)001:58: du grol bar 'dod pa'o de dag ni snang sems
NK107(tse)001:59: stong par 'dod pa lus ngag gzhi rdzogs su blta
NK107(tse)001:60: ba'o lam drang thad du smra ba la gsum ste
NK107(tse)001:61: lus ngag gnad kyis grol bar 'dod pa dang bya
NK107(tse)001:62: bral gcig rdzogs su 'dod pa dang rang snang spang
NK107(tse)001:63: blang las 'das par 'dod pa'o de dag ni lus
NK107(tse)001:64: ngag yid kyi gnad gtso che bas rang rig mngon
NK107(tse)001:65: sum du 'dod pa'i lugs so 'bras bu ye grol
NK107(tse)001:66: du smra ba la gsum rdzogs pa mtha' dang rgyas
NK107(tse)001:67: par smra ba dang mtha' bral yongs rdzogs su smra
NK107(tse)001:68: ba dang gcig shes kun grol du smra ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:69: dag gi snang shes tha mi dad du 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:70: ste khams gsum dong sprugs su 'dod pa'i lugs so
NK107(tse)001:71: de ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i 'dod pa tha dad
NK107(tse)001:72: par byung ba ni sems gcig gi 'khor lo cig
NK107(tse)001:73: par ma shes pa las byung ba'o de yang sde
NK107(tse)001:74: gsum las man ngag gi sde klong dgu las chos
NK107(tse)001:75: nyid cer mthong du grol ba'i klong zhes bya'o bka'
NK107(tse)001:76: gsum las dngos su gsungs pa'i bka' 'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:77: chos thams cad bsdu na 'khor 'das gnyis su 'dus
NK107(tse)001:78: 'khor ba'i chos ni rnam par dag pa dang rang
NK107(tse)001:79: gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'o 'das pa'i chos ni lung
NK107(tse)001:80: gi chos dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi chos so
NK107(tse)001:81: lung ni bstan pa'i lung nga'i dang barjoda pa'i lung
NK107(tse)001:82: ngo bstan pa'i lung la gsum ste mdo sde dang
NK107(tse)001:83: 'dul ba mngon pa gsum mo barjoda pa'i lung ni
NK107(tse)001:84: so so'i gnyen po dang sbyar nas gsungs pa ste
NK107(tse)001:85: bye brag tu brgyad khrii bzhi stong rang bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:86: sems kyi rtog tshogs sna tshogs la dgongs te gsungs
NK107(tse)001:87: pa'o rtogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi chos la bka' rang
NK107(tse)001:88: gzhung du smra ba dang grub mtha' 'dod rgyal du
NK107(tse)001:89: smra ba'o grub mtha' 'dod rgyal ni bka' dang bka'
NK107(tse)001:90: la brten pa'i chos so de yang chos rnams thams
NK107(tse)001:91: cad bka' dang bstan chos gnyis su 'dus legs par
NK107(tse)001:92: gsungs dang de'i dgongs 'grel dang de'i dbang gis sh+aakya'i
NK107(tse)001:93: bstan pa 'di 'jig rten dag tu yun ring gnas
NK107(tse)001:94: brtan 'gyur zhes gsungs pas na bka' dang bstan chos
NK107(tse)001:95: kyi 'brel pa ni gser dmigs la rin po che'i
NK107(tse)001:96: rgyan sna tshogs kyis spras pa lta bu'o dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:97: ni rgyal po bsod nams dang ldan pa dang blon
NK107(tse)001:98: po rig pa dang ldan pa dus 'dzom pa lta
NK107(tse)001:99: bu'o de las ni khyad par du chos gser gyi
NK107(tse)001:100: snying po la nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed
NK107(tse)001:101: pa snying tig gsang ba bla na med pa rang
NK107(tse)001:102: gi rig pa mngon sum du ston par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:103: de las kyang sna tshogs ston par byed pa'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:104: thal 'gyur gyi rgyud zhes bya ba le'u drug gis
NK107(tse)001:105: bstan nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mngon gsum
NK107(tse)001:106: du gtan la 'bebs pa byed pa'o 'di la gang
NK107(tse)001:107: zag blo cig 'char ba rnams kyis gcig char du
NK107(tse)001:108: rtogs par bya ba'i phyir rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:109: dang rim gyis pa rnams kyis rim gyis rtogs par
NK107(tse)001:110: bya ba'i phyir rgyud kyi gzhung bstan pa'o de la
NK107(tse)001:111: rgyud kyi mtshan la gsum ste mtshan sgra 'gyur chen
NK107(tse)001:112: po'i man ngag gi gnad la brten nas snang grags
NK107(tse)001:113: kyi chos thams cad chos nyid kyi rang sgrar 'char
NK107(tse)001:114: bar bstan pa dang mtshan don 'gyur chos nyid mngon
NK107(tse)001:115: sum gyi man ngag la brten nas rang rig mngon
NK107(tse)001:116: sum du bstan pa dang brda' 'gyur tshig tsam la
NK107(tse)001:117: brten nas snang brtags thams cad nyams myong du 'char
NK107(tse)001:118: bar bstan pa'o de la sgra 'gyur gnad kyi man
NK107(tse)001:119: ngag la brten nas snang grags kyi chos thams cad
NK107(tse)001:120: chos nyid kyi rang sgrar 'char bar bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:121: sgra'i ngo bo dang nges tshig dang dbye ba gsum
NK107(tse)001:122: mo ngo bo ni barjoda pas barjoda bya'i don la
NK107(tse)001:123: phyin ci ma log pa rtogs par byed pa nyid
NK107(tse)001:124: yin la nges tshig ni don dang 'brel bas na
NK107(tse)001:125: sgra zhes bya la dbye na gnas pa'i sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:126: barjoda pa'i sgra'o gnas pa ni rang bzhin rtsa gnas
NK107(tse)001:127: na gnas pa dang chos nyid do rang bzhin rtsa
NK107(tse)001:128: na gnas pa ni 'od kyi gzugs kyis gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:129: sems kyi mtshan nyid ston par byed la yi ge'i
NK107(tse)001:130: gzugs kyis gnas pas barjoda bya'i gzhi mtshon par byed
NK107(tse)001:131: la kun bzang yab yum gyi sku'i gzugs kyis gnas
NK107(tse)001:132: pas sku gsum gyi mtshon gzhi mtshon par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:133: de ltar gsum ni gnas pas 'gyus la 'gyus pas
NK107(tse)001:134: stong pa zhes bya'o chos nyid ni 'gyu ba stong
NK107(tse)001:135: dag barjoda bya rang bzhin gnas dag go barjoda pa'i
NK107(tse)001:136: sgra la gnyis te 'byung rtags mtshon pa'i sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:137: tshig gi bdag nyid mtshon par byed pa gnyis so
NK107(tse)001:138: 'byung rtags mtshon pa ni 'byung ba bzhi'i rang sgra
NK107(tse)001:139: la brten nas bslabs pas sku gsum gyi sa bon
NK107(tse)001:140: 'jog par byed pa la 'jug pa dus kyi sgra
NK107(tse)001:141: don la rten nas rigs drug so so'i las dang
NK107(tse)001:142: las kyi bye brag ston par byed pa'o de gnyis
NK107(tse)001:143: la bslabs pas shes la shes pas rtogs pa'o tshig
NK107(tse)001:144: gi bdag nyid mtshon par byed pa ni sgra'i dbyings
NK107(tse)001:145: kyi chos dang chos nyid gtan la 'bebs la sgrub
NK107(tse)001:146: byed kyis rang dang gzhan gtan la 'bebs la gzhan
NK107(tse)001:147: sel gyis phyi rol bem rig gi gtan la 'bebs
NK107(tse)001:148: par byed la phan pa'i rkyen gyis blo dang shes
NK107(tse)001:149: pa'i btsal sbyong bar byed pa'o de la 'dir ni
NK107(tse)001:150: sgra don gnad kyi bye brag yi ge'i 'gyur byed
NK107(tse)001:151: bshad pa'o de la sems nyid gnas pa gzhi las
NK107(tse)001:152: shar ba tsam yin pas s+w+aa zhes bya'o lhun grub
NK107(tse)001:153: rdzogs tshul la snang tshul 'gag pa med pas na
NK107(tse)001:154: de nyid ma rig pas na pa'o de yang dus
NK107(tse)001:155: gsum mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa las rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:156: gyis brtags pas na da'o de las rtsal dang yon
NK107(tse)001:157: tan 'gag med du shar bas 'dre zhes bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:158: yang rang bzhin gyis brtags pas 'char byed sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:159: par 'char bar byed pas tra zhes bya'o gzhi las
NK107(tse)001:160: ma g.yos pas ma'o gzhi de yang ye nas stong
NK107(tse)001:161: pa ngos bzung du med pas t+aa zhes bya'o 'char
NK107(tse)001:162: sgo sna tshogs par 'char kyang snang la rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:163: med pas na rang zhes bya'o de yang sku gsum
NK107(tse)001:164: gyi dkyil 'khor la gnas pas na'o sku gsum rang
NK107(tse)001:165: la rdzogs pas ka sku gsum rang la 'char byed
NK107(tse)001:166: kyi 'od yod pas ri de yang dus thams cad
NK107(tse)001:167: du sgron ma bzhi'i ngo bo 'char byed lus la
NK107(tse)001:168: 'char bas na tan tra zhes bya la lus de
NK107(tse)001:169: yang zag pa rang zad pa'i phyir na zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:170: lus yin kyang gzhir grol ba'i gnad yod pa'i phyir
NK107(tse)001:171: na m+aa zhes bya'o mtshan don 'gyur chos nyid mngon
NK107(tse)001:172: sum la brten nas rang rang gi mngon sum du
NK107(tse)001:173: bstan pa ni mtshan gyi gnas lugs la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:174: chos nyid gshis kyi 'dug tshul gtan la dbab pa
NK107(tse)001:175: dang mtshon byed rgyud kyi don sdebs pa la brten
NK107(tse)001:176: nas skal pa can chos nyid mngon sum gyi lam
NK107(tse)001:177: gyi cha rkyen rdzogs par bstan pa'o de la mtshan
NK107(tse)001:178: gyi gnas lugs ni mtshan gyi yon tan dang mtshan
NK107(tse)001:179: rang gi ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul lo yon tan ni
NK107(tse)001:180: rin po che la sogs pa'o rang gi ngo bo'i
NK107(tse)001:181: bzhugs tshul ni sgra thal 'gyur roh de yang barjoda
NK107(tse)001:182: du med pa'i chos nyid kyi rol pa las yon
NK107(tse)001:183: tan gyi bye brag barjoda du med pas rang rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:184: su 'byung ba ni dper na yid bzhin gyi nor
NK107(tse)001:185: bu rin po che la dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung
NK107(tse)001:186: ba dang 'dra bar rdzogs chen gnad kyi man ngag
NK107(tse)001:187: mthong ba'i mi la chos nyid kyi yon tan sna
NK107(tse)001:188: tshogs 'phel ba'o de ltar chos nyid kyi yon tan
NK107(tse)001:189: 'byung bar byed pa la gsang ba'i rgyud 'di nas
NK107(tse)001:190: thams cad ston pa'o sgra zhes bya ba ni gong
NK107(tse)001:191: du bstan pa las de yang 'dir ni barjoda pa'i
NK107(tse)001:192: sgra don sum brgya dang drug 'og nas ston la
NK107(tse)001:193: de yang barjoda pa'i sgra don 'byung rtags kyis sgra'i
NK107(tse)001:194: rnam grangs stong phrag brgyad 'og nas ston no tshig
NK107(tse)001:195: gi bdag nyid mtshon par byed pa'i sgra'i rnam grangs
NK107(tse)001:196: drug cu tham pa 'og nas ston no de yang
NK107(tse)001:197: de dag gi dbye ba dang bsdu ba la sogs
NK107(tse)001:198: pa 'og nas rgyas par ston la 'dir mi spro'o
NK107(tse)001:199: de yang 'og nas yan lag gi skabs nas sgra'i
NK107(tse)001:200: babs so rnam par lnga tshangs dang khyab 'jug ka
NK107(tse)001:201: la ping ka la 'byung ba'i sgra dang ston pa'i
NK107(tse)001:202: gsung zhes pa la sogs pa'i skabs nas kyang rgyas
NK107(tse)001:203: par ston no de dag gi dgos pa yang mchog
NK107(tse)001:204: dang thun mong la sogs pa 'og nas ston no
NK107(tse)001:205: thal zhes pa ni 'og nas thal ba'i gnas ni
NK107(tse)001:206: rnam pa brgyad 'jig rten khams dang zhing khams dang
NK107(tse)001:207: dam bca' skyob dang skyon gnas dang 'phen pa'i sa
NK107(tse)001:208: dang sbyor ba dang grags dang song ba'i gnas de
NK107(tse)001:209: brgyad zhes pa la sogs pa 'og nas rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:210: ston no 'gyur zhes pa yang 'og nas 'gyur ni
NK107(tse)001:211: 'byung ba'i cho 'phrul gyis zhes pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:212: 'og nas ston noh chen po zhes bya ba ni
NK107(tse)001:213: rdzogs pa chen po spros gzhi dang bral ba la
NK107(tse)001:214: mtha' rtog pa med pas rgya chad dang phyogs lhung
NK107(tse)001:215: med pas de'i gong na gzhan med pa'o rgyud ni
NK107(tse)001:216: ngo bo dang nges tshig dang dbye ba dang dpe
NK107(tse)001:217: dang rgyu dang lngar shes par bya'o ngo bo ni
NK107(tse)001:218: thabs shes rab zung 'jug gi sgo nas rang rig
NK107(tse)001:219: pa'i rgyud mngon sum du ston par byed la nges
NK107(tse)001:220: tshig ni thang chad pa dang rgyun chags pa dang
NK107(tse)001:221: 'brel ba'i phyir na rgyud do dbye na tshig rgyud
NK107(tse)001:222: dang don rgyud do tshig rgyud la rgyud btags pa
NK107(tse)001:223: po dang rgyud mtshan nyid pa'o btags pa ni tshig
NK107(tse)001:224: tu bkod pa 'di dag ste bskyed pa'i rim pa
NK107(tse)001:225: gtso cher ston pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso
NK107(tse)001:226: cher ston pa dang gnyis so mtshan nyid pa ni
NK107(tse)001:227: rang bzhin gyi rgyud dang thabs kyi rgyud do tshig
NK107(tse)001:228: rgyud la rgyud brtags pa po dang rgyud mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:229: pa'o btags pa ni tshig tu bkod pa 'di dag
NK107(tse)001:230: ste rang bzhin ni rang rgyud dag pa po dang
NK107(tse)001:231: dri ma dang bcas pa gnyis gzhan rgyud dag pa
NK107(tse)001:232: dang dri ma dang bcas pa gnyis so don gyis
NK107(tse)001:233: bzhir 'gro ba'o de yang sems nyid la rnam rtog
NK107(tse)001:234: dang bcas pa dang rnam par rtog pa dag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:235: khyad par nas bzhag pa'o thabs kyi rgyud la mtshon
NK107(tse)001:236: bya thabs kyi rgyud shes pas bsdus pa dang mtshon
NK107(tse)001:237: byed thabs kyi rgyud shes byas bsdus pa rnams so
NK107(tse)001:238: don gyi rgyud ni gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK107(tse)001:239: rgyud do gzhi'i rgyud ni shes bya gnas pa'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:240: lugs sangs rgyas sgom des ma mdzad sems can sgrin
NK107(tse)001:241: pos ma bcos pa tshig dang yi ge gang gis
NK107(tse)001:242: kyang gtan la mi phebs la rdzogs pa chen po
NK107(tse)001:243: rang gi gnas lugs mtha' bral yongs su ma rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:244: pa gang yang med pa'o lam gyi rgyud ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:245: te gang zag gi dbang po'i bye brag tu byas
NK107(tse)001:246: nas lam mngon sum du byed pa dang rjes thob
NK107(tse)001:247: tu byed pa'o 'bras bu ni sku gsum lhun grub
NK107(tse)001:248: kyi rgyud dang chos nyid zad sar ka dag gi
NK107(tse)001:249: rgyud do dpe ni yon tan ston pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:250: che lta bu dang tshig don 'brel pa dbyer mi
NK107(tse)001:251: phyed pa thag pa lta bu dang rgyun du gnas
NK107(tse)001:252: pa til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa lta bu
NK107(tse)001:253: dang gsal byed gzhan la ma ltos pa mar me
NK107(tse)001:254: lta bu dang che chung dang yangs dog med pa
NK107(tse)001:255: nam mkha' lta bu'o rgyu ni chos dang gang zag
NK107(tse)001:256: dang de rtogs pa'i bdag nyid du byung ba'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:257: bya ba ni de lta bu'i tshig don dbyer mi
NK107(tse)001:258: phyed kyang tshig la rten nas don mngon sum rang
NK107(tse)001:259: thog tu 'bebs par byed pa'i gzhung tshig dang yi
NK107(tse)001:260: ger gcad pa cig bstan par bya bshad par bya
NK107(tse)001:261: zhes pa'i don no da ni rgyud kyi mtshan ngos
NK107(tse)001:262: bzung ba rgyud kyi don sdebs pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:263: skal ba can chos nyid mngon sum gyi lam gyis
NK107(tse)001:264: cha rkyen rdzogs par bstan pa ni rten gyi gang
NK107(tse)001:265: zag dad pa dang ldan pa gcig gis bla ma
NK107(tse)001:266: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa gcig la thog ma gzhi
NK107(tse)001:267: ma smin pa smin par byed pa la dbang bskur
NK107(tse)001:268: cig thob dgos de nas dbang de la brten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:269: nye rgyur dbang dang dam tshig dang sdom pa la
NK107(tse)001:270: gnas dgos de ltar rang gi rgyud smin par byas
NK107(tse)001:271: nas smin pa grol bar byed pa la bla ma'i
NK107(tse)001:272: man ngag zhu dgos gdams pa zhu ba'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:273: rang dad pa dang snying rje dang shes rab gsum
NK107(tse)001:274: 'dzom pa gal che de nas bla ma'i man ngag
NK107(tse)001:275: la sngon du 'gro ba lus ngag yid snod sbyang
NK107(tse)001:276: bar bya ba dang dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:277: ye shes kyi don rang gi rgyud la brten par
NK107(tse)001:278: bya ba gnyis so de la sngon du 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:279: la drug yod pa las lus ngag yid kyi bya
NK107(tse)001:280: ba rdzogs par bya ba dang lus ngag yid rnal
NK107(tse)001:281: du 'bebs pa gsum ste drug bya'o de yang khrid
NK107(tse)001:282: kyi lugs su byas te sngon du lus rdo rje'i
NK107(tse)001:283: skyil krung du 'dug pa zhag gsum du dur khrod
NK107(tse)001:284: du sbyangs de ltar sbyangs pas yan lag gi tshigs
NK107(tse)001:285: 'khrog pa dang lus kyi zhen pa log pa'i rtags
NK107(tse)001:286: ma byung na bskyar la bya'o de la dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:287: thun mong dang mchog gi dgos pa gnyis 'byung de
NK107(tse)001:288: nas ngag sbyang ba'i gnad h'u rings kyis rgyas gdab
NK107(tse)001:289: pa la zhag gnyis rtsal sbyang ba la zhag gnyis
NK107(tse)001:290: gnyen btsal zhing lam du bzhugs pa la zhag gnyis
NK107(tse)001:291: te drug tu ngag sbyangs pas barjoda pa brag cha
NK107(tse)001:292: ltar go ba dang rang gi ngag la zhen pa
NK107(tse)001:293: log pa dag 'byung ngo de ltar ma 'byung na
NK107(tse)001:294: bskyar la bya'o de ltar byas pa yang dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:295: gnyis yod do de nas sems sbyang ba ni sems
NK107(tse)001:296: kyi 'ong sa dang 'gro sa dang gnas sa la
NK107(tse)001:297: zhag gsum du brtag go de ltar brtags pas gzhi
NK107(tse)001:298: dang rtsa ba med rgyu mtshan brtsal du ma snyed
NK107(tse)001:299: pa'i sems nyid stong pa ngos bzung dang bral ba
NK107(tse)001:300: 'di dang rang sems la skye ba med pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:301: can du go ba dag 'byung ngo de ltar rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:302: nas lus dang ngag yid rnal du 'bebs pa'i thabs
NK107(tse)001:303: gsum rdzogs dran par bya'o sngon du 'gro ba de
NK107(tse)001:304: dag gi sngon du gang zag dam pa des tshogs
NK107(tse)001:305: bsags pa'i thabs sna tshogs pa byas la de nas
NK107(tse)001:306: rkyen gyis mi gnod pa'i dgon par grogs spangs la
NK107(tse)001:307: rang gcig pur gong ma'i don de dag nyams su
NK107(tse)001:308: blang bar bya'o de ltar rdzogs par byas la dngos
NK107(tse)001:309: gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyi don nyams
NK107(tse)001:310: su blang bar bya ste de la lus kyi gnad
NK107(tse)001:311: gzir bar bya ste chos kyi sku'i bzhugs stangs la
NK107(tse)001:312: nyi ma gcig tu sbyangs longs sku'i bzhugs stangs la
NK107(tse)001:313: nyi ma gcig / sprul sku'i bzhugs stangs la nyi ma gcig /
NK107(tse)001:314: de ltar nyi ma gsum du sbyangs la de nas
NK107(tse)001:315: gang mos pa de la dus thams cad du gnas
NK107(tse)001:316: par bya'o de nas ngag gi gnad gzir ba la
NK107(tse)001:317: nyi ma dang po dag bslab par bya ba la
NK107(tse)001:318: sbyangs te don med pa'i gtam yid la ci 'gyus
NK107(tse)001:319: pa thams cad barjoda par bya'o des ni rang gi
NK107(tse)001:320: ngag don med du 'gro ba'i dgos pa yod do
NK107(tse)001:321: de nas gnyis pa ngag gnas par bya ba ni
NK107(tse)001:322: smra ba la dgos pa ci dgos pa zhes dal
NK107(tse)001:323: ba med par rtag tu barjoda par bya'o des ni
NK107(tse)001:324: phyis mi smra bar 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do
NK107(tse)001:325: de nas ngag la bzla ba ni lce dang mchus
NK107(tse)001:326: ma bsgyur ba'i ngag mang po smra bar 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:327: des ni ngag gi rtsa ba phyin pa'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:328: yod do de ltar nyi ma gsum du sbyangs la
NK107(tse)001:329: su dang yang mi smra ba la zla ba gcig
NK107(tse)001:330: rang gi barjoda pa bkag pa la zla ba gcig
NK107(tse)001:331: tshig tsam dran pa tsam bkag pa la zla ba
NK107(tse)001:332: gcig de ltar rgyun du gnas pas chos thams cad
NK107(tse)001:333: barjoda du med pa'i don rgyud la skye bar nges
NK107(tse)001:334: so de nas sems kyi chos nyid gnad du chos
NK107(tse)001:335: nyid mngon gsum dang mi 'bral bar bya'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:336: gnad gsum la brten nas mngon sum rang thog tu
NK107(tse)001:337: dbab pa ni sgo'i gnad mig yin te chos sku'i
NK107(tse)001:338: gzigs stangs nyi ma gcig bya de ltar longs sku
NK107(tse)001:339: dang sprul sku la gnyis te nyi ma gsum du
NK107(tse)001:340: sbyangs la de nas dus thams cad du gnas par
NK107(tse)001:341: bya'o des ni mig gi nad sel ba'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:342: yod do de nas yul ni phyi yul nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:343: stong pa sprin dang bral ba chos nyid 'char bar
NK107(tse)001:344: byed pa'i yul yin no de la gzigs stangs gsum
NK107(tse)001:345: po gang mos kyis nyi ma gcig sbyangs bar bya'o
NK107(tse)001:346: de nas rlung rig gis gnad ni skabs su rlung
NK107(tse)001:347: ci nas kyang trag par bya ba dang res zhan
NK107(tse)001:348: res phu dang bcas pa dang res ha zhes phyir
NK107(tse)001:349: 'phang ba dang res hu zhes nang du bstams pa
NK107(tse)001:350: dang dkyil ba la sogs pa la nyi ma gcig
NK107(tse)001:351: sbyang ngo de nas rtag tu dal zhing phyir 'phang
NK107(tse)001:352: ba la dus thams cad du gnas par bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:353: ni chos nyid mngon sum gyi don te chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:354: ni de las logs pa'i chos yod pa ma yin
NK107(tse)001:355: la sngon ni dbang po gtan la phebs shing tshig
NK107(tse)001:356: la ma brten pa la gsum ni mig dang nam
NK107(tse)001:357: mkha' dang rig pa gsum du 'brel ba med pa'o
NK107(tse)001:358: de yan chad ni lag tu blang ba'i chos so
NK107(tse)001:359: 'di nas de'i yon tan te shes par bya'o dad
NK107(tse)001:360: pa dang ldan pa des nyin mtshan phyed par 'bral
NK107(tse)001:361: ba med par nyams su blangs pa las snang ba
NK107(tse)001:362: bzhi 'char te de la chos nyid mngon sum gyi
NK107(tse)001:363: snang ba zhes bya ba theg pa thun mong pa
NK107(tse)001:364: rnams kyis mi shes pa'i don no yid dpyod dang
NK107(tse)001:365: yin snyam la rag ma lus tshig dang yi ge
NK107(tse)001:366: la ma brten pa lta sgom spyod pas thog tu
NK107(tse)001:367: mi pheb la rgyud lung las ma byung ba'i chos
NK107(tse)001:368: nyid kyi snang ba ni sngon bas dbang po'i spyod
NK107(tse)001:369: yul du ma gyur bas de la yid dpyod tshig
NK107(tse)001:370: gis sgros gdags su med lta gsum sgo gsum dang
NK107(tse)001:371: rig pa yul gsum 'bral ba med pas sku gsum
NK107(tse)001:372: gzhan du gdeng mi 'cha' ba'o snang ba ni sprul
NK107(tse)001:373: pa sku'i snang ba ste 'di nyid gtan la phebs
NK107(tse)001:374: pa'o de nyid mthong nas goms pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:375: nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba 'char te nyams ni
NK107(tse)001:376: shes pa'i nyams bde ba dang gsal ba dang stong
NK107(tse)001:377: pa dang sna tshogs su 'char ste 'di ni snang
NK107(tse)001:378: ba'i nyams gtso che ste snang ba ni 'khrul pa'i
NK107(tse)001:379: snang ba rim gyis nub nas dag pa ye shes
NK107(tse)001:380: kyi snang ba 'char te 'od kha dog lnga ye
NK107(tse)001:381: shes lnga'i rtsal yon tan gyi 'byung ba'i rang gdangs
NK107(tse)001:382: 'char te 'od lnga thog ma rtsibs shar du 'char
NK107(tse)001:383: ba dang tshad ni me long tsam du snang la
NK107(tse)001:384: de nas gyen 'greng du snang ba ste tshad ni
NK107(tse)001:385: re lde'i rnam pa tsam du snang de yang ye
NK107(tse)001:386: shes lnga'i kha dog gi snang ba dang dbyibs kyi
NK107(tse)001:387: sna nga ba gru chad du snang ba dang mu
NK107(tse)001:388: khyud can dang gru chad dang yul gru dang mthong
NK107(tse)001:389: tshad dang stong gsum tsam du snang ba dang mchod
NK107(tse)001:390: rten brtsegs pa dang pad+ma dang pad+ma stong ldan dang
NK107(tse)001:391: mdung rtse dang lcags kyu dang ral gri lta bu
NK107(tse)001:392: dang d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa dang rin
NK107(tse)001:393: po che'i mig tshags dang mig mang ris dang gur
NK107(tse)001:394: khyim gyi snang ba ltar snang ba dag 'byung ngo
NK107(tse)001:395: de yang shes pa blo yin pas 'gyur la snang
NK107(tse)001:396: ba ni mi 'gyur pas so de nas rig pa
NK107(tse)001:397: tshad phebs kyi snang ba 'char ba ni rig pa
NK107(tse)001:398: ni lu gu rgyud mngon du gzir ba'i stobs te
NK107(tse)001:399: tshad ni sku rnams su smin pa ste phebs pa
NK107(tse)001:400: ni rang ngo shes pa la bya snang ba ni
NK107(tse)001:401: 'od dang 'od kyi 'ja' dang thig le dang thig
NK107(tse)001:402: le'i phyed sku dang sku dang ye shes kyi gzugs
NK107(tse)001:403: sku rnam rim gyis rdzogs pa rnams so de dag
NK107(tse)001:404: rdzogs nas chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba 'char teh
NK107(tse)001:405: chos nyid ni phyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid nyid
NK107(tse)001:406: ni mi thobs pa zad pa ni blo dang shes
NK107(tse)001:407: pa dang bdag dang gzhan dang yul dang 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:408: dang chos dang gang zag dang sku dang ye shes
NK107(tse)001:409: dang tha snyad tsam du yang med 'di'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:410: snang ba 'di yin min gang du yang ma grub
NK107(tse)001:411: pas sems can gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:412: la mtha' brten gyi man ngag ni mi 'gul ba
NK107(tse)001:413: gsum la gzhi bca' bas chos nyid nang phrad pa
NK107(tse)001:414: dang mngon gsum gyi tshad bzung bas yid ches nang
NK107(tse)001:415: du skye ba dang thob pa gsum gyis gzer btab
NK107(tse)001:416: pas mi ldog pa'i gzhi 'chos ba'o de yang mi
NK107(tse)001:417: 'gul ba gsum ni dad pa can nyams su len
NK107(tse)001:418: pa'i dus na lus mi 'gul ba bzhugs stangs gsum
NK107(tse)001:419: las mi 'da' bar bya'o des ni rtsa dal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:420: dgos pa yod de ltar rtsa dal ba'i rlung mi
NK107(tse)001:421: 'gyu la rlung ma 'gyus pas rnam par rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:422: tha dad pa la mi 'gyu ba'i dgos pa yod
NK107(tse)001:423: do 'di'i dus ni mig mi 'gul bar gzigs stangs
NK107(tse)001:424: gsum po gang rung las mi 'da' bar bya'o des
NK107(tse)001:425: ni rig pa nyid chos nyid ma la gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:426: dgos pa yod de chos nyid ma la gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:427: chos nyid rang thog tu phebs pa la de phebs
NK107(tse)001:428: pas yid dpyod tshig gi sgro 'dogs dang bral ba'i
NK107(tse)001:429: dgos pa yod do 'di'i dus na rlung mi 'gul
NK107(tse)001:430: bar dal ba brten pas dus thams cad du chos
NK107(tse)001:431: nyid dang mi 'bral ba'i dgos pa yod do sdod
NK107(tse)001:432: pa gsum gyis tshad bzung ba ni de ltar dus
NK107(tse)001:433: rgyun du gnas pas phyi snang ba sdod pa 'byung
NK107(tse)001:434: ste rig pa gang la gtad pa las mi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:435: zhing 'od gsal rlung gi g.yo ba dang bral ba
NK107(tse)001:436: dag 'byung ngo nang phung po sdad pa 'byung ste
NK107(tse)001:437: lus 'od gsal du 'gro bas bya ba dang bya
NK107(tse)001:438: ba ma yin pa las gang la yang 'jug snying
NK107(tse)001:439: mi 'dod pa la gsang ba rlung sems sdod pa
NK107(tse)001:440: ni lu gu brgyud 'gro 'ong dang bral ba dag
NK107(tse)001:441: 'byung ngo de yang 'di'i skabs su tshad rmi lam
NK107(tse)001:442: gyis gzung ba dang rtags lus ngag la 'char ba
NK107(tse)001:443: gnyis 'dod pa med kyang 'byung ste de ltar dus
NK107(tse)001:444: thams cad nyams su blangs pa las brtson 'grus rab
NK107(tse)001:445: 'di nyid la zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po
NK107(tse)001:446: mi snang bar b+hud tha la bag chags kyi rmi
NK107(tse)001:447: lam la rnam smin rgyun chad de rmi mi srid
NK107(tse)001:448: do 'bring chos nyid kyi bar ma do la rang
NK107(tse)001:449: gi chos nyid nyams su gyur nas b+hud thal ba
NK107(tse)001:450: la rmi lam rmi yang rmi lam la rmi lam
NK107(tse)001:451: du shes pa 'byung tha ma rang bzhin sprul sku'i
NK107(tse)001:452: zhing khams su dbugs phyung nas b+hud tha ba la
NK107(tse)001:453: bag chags ngan pa'i rmi lam rnams 'gags te dkar
NK107(tse)001:454: po'i phyogs kyi rmi lam rnams rmi ba dag 'byung
NK107(tse)001:455: ngo de'i phyir na khams gsum du mi brgyud pa'i
NK107(tse)001:456: lta ba zhes bya'o de yang skye ba gzhan gyis
NK107(tse)001:457: bar ma chod pas na gsang ba 'di'i gor zhugs
NK107(tse)001:458: so tsam gyis tshe gcig la sangs rgyas pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:459: bya'o de ltar rmi lam gyi rnam pa la 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:460: ma byung na sangs rgya ba la re ba med
NK107(tse)001:461: do 'di'i dus na rtags lus ngag yid gsum la
NK107(tse)001:462: 'char ba ni 'di dag ni snang ba bzhi mthong
NK107(tse)001:463: ba las 'byung ba ste chos nyid mngon sum gyi
NK107(tse)001:464: snang ba mthong ba'i dus na lus rus sbal mkhar
NK107(tse)001:465: gzhong du bcug pa lta bur 'gyur la ngag lkug
NK107(tse)001:466: pa lta bur 'gyur la sems mkha' 'gro snyi la
NK107(tse)001:467: zin pa lta bur 'gyur ro nyams gong 'phel gyis
NK107(tse)001:468: snang ba mthong ba'i dus na lus skyes bu nad
NK107(tse)001:469: kyis gdungs pa'i rnam pa lta bur 'gyur la ngag
NK107(tse)001:470: snyon pa'i rang tshig brdol ba lta bur 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:471: sems skyes bu tsi dug gis lan bdun thebs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:472: rnam pa lta bur 'gyur ro rig pa tshad phebs
NK107(tse)001:473: kyis snang ba mthong ba'i dus na lus glang po
NK107(tse)001:474: che 'dam du bying ba'i rnam pa ltar 'gyur lah
NK107(tse)001:475: ngag grul bum gyi phru gu brag bar nas thon
NK107(tse)001:476: pa ltar 'gyur la sems rims nad byang ba'i skyes
NK107(tse)001:477: bu ltar 'gyur ro chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba
NK107(tse)001:478: mthong ba'i dus na lus mkha' 'gro snyi nas bton
NK107(tse)001:479: pa'i rnam pa ltar 'gyur la ngag brag cha'i rnam
NK107(tse)001:480: pa ltar 'gyur ba dang sems skyes bu'i snying la
NK107(tse)001:481: mdas zin pa ltar 'gyur ba'o de ltar lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:482: yid kyi rtags bcu gnyis shar ba'i dus na lus
NK107(tse)001:483: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bya ba'i
NK107(tse)001:484: las la 'jug snying mi 'dod pa dang de ni
NK107(tse)001:485: lus kyi zhen pa rang sar log pa yin la
NK107(tse)001:486: ngag smra snying mi 'dod pa barjoda med kyi don
NK107(tse)001:487: khong du chud pa'i rtags yin sems khams gsum du
NK107(tse)001:488: mi ldog par yid ches pa chos nyid nyams kyi
NK107(tse)001:489: snang ba gdeng snyed pa'i rtags yang lus ngo tsha
NK107(tse)001:490: ba dang lus kyi bya ba'i bag las grol bas
NK107(tse)001:491: 'byung ba'i zag pa zad du nye ba'i dus rtags
NK107(tse)001:492: ngag 'brel ba med pa'i gtam 'byung bas 'khrul pa'i
NK107(tse)001:493: ngag zad du nye ba'i rtags sems sangs rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:494: ngo shes pas nyams su myong ba rang thog na
NK107(tse)001:495: gsal ba'i rtags so yang lus la 'khrul pa'i bya
NK107(tse)001:496: bas mi gnod pa'i rtags stobs yod kyang bya ba'i
NK107(tse)001:497: rnam pa gang la yang mi 'jug pa byar med
NK107(tse)001:498: kyi don rgyud la skyes pa'i rtags ngag gi nus
NK107(tse)001:499: pa thun mong ma yin pas sems gzhan la 'jug
NK107(tse)001:500: par nus pa ni gsang sngags thams cad kyi lam
NK107(tse)001:501: rgyud la shar ba'i rtags sems khams gsum du mi
NK107(tse)001:502: ldog par thag chod pa ni rig pa nyid rang
NK107(tse)001:503: tshad la phebs pa'i rtags so yang lus kyi gtad
NK107(tse)001:504: dang bral ba ni 'khrul pa zhig pa'i rtags yin
NK107(tse)001:505: ngag gtam gyi zungs zad pa ni chos nyid barjoda
NK107(tse)001:506: du med pa la dus thams cad du gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:507: rtags yin no de ltar na rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:508: chen po'i sgor zhugs so tsam khams gsum du 'jug
NK107(tse)001:509: mi srid pas na rab tu zab bo de ltar
NK107(tse)001:510: man ngag gi don sngon 'gro dang dngos gzhi gnyis
NK107(tse)001:511: ka'i don rgyud la skyes pas na khams gsum du
NK107(tse)001:512: mi ldog par yid ches pa'o de dag rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:513: don mtshan dang skyus gnyis ngo sprad na de yang
NK107(tse)001:514: sngon du rang dad pa dang ldan pa gal che
NK107(tse)001:515: dad pa med na zhing sa med par sa bon
NK107(tse)001:516: btab kyang 'bras bu mi smin pa dang 'dra bas
NK107(tse)001:517: na de yang 'di'i man ngag gi bkod pa dang
NK107(tse)001:518: po dbang bskur ba'i cho ga'i yan lag gi skabs
NK107(tse)001:519: na dad ldan skal ba chen po nyon ces pas
NK107(tse)001:520: so mtshan gyi skabs su che zhes pa la gzung
NK107(tse)001:521: ste de yang dad pa che bas 'jig rten 'di
NK107(tse)001:522: rgyab tu bor ba dang gtong phod che ba dang
NK107(tse)001:523: shes rab dang dad pa che ba dang mos gus
NK107(tse)001:524: dang 'jig rten gyi zang zing gis bla ma mnyes
NK107(tse)001:525: par byed pa dngah mos pa che bas dus thams
NK107(tse)001:526: cad du bla ma dang chos nyid kyi don la
NK107(tse)001:527: yid ches par byed pa'o gus pa che bas lus
NK107(tse)001:528: kyi bya ba ci dang ci byed pa bla ma'i
NK107(tse)001:529: bya ba las mi 'da' ba'o gdung ba che bas
NK107(tse)001:530: ngag gi bya ba ci dang ci byed ci smra
NK107(tse)001:531: ba thams cad chos kyi tshig dang bla ma la
NK107(tse)001:532: bstod pa'i tshig las mi 'da' ba'o de lta bu'i
NK107(tse)001:533: dad pa chen po dang ldan pa'i rigs kyi bu
NK107(tse)001:534: de la bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa med
NK107(tse)001:535: na lam log par 'gyur bas na de yang 'di
NK107(tse)001:536: nyid las rtsa ba yan lag bla ma dang so
NK107(tse)001:537: so'i mtshan nyid tshangs pa la zhes pa ste rin
NK107(tse)001:538: po che 'byung ba zhes pa ste bla ma brten
NK107(tse)001:539: pa las yon tan gyis 'phrel sgo dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:540: pa las 'byung bar byed pa ste dper na rin
NK107(tse)001:541: po che la 'dod pa'i don gang la gsol ba
NK107(tse)001:542: btab pa 'byung ba ltar bla ma la yang mchog
NK107(tse)001:543: thun mong gi dngos grub ji ltar 'dod pa gsol
NK107(tse)001:544: ba btab pa 'byung ba'o de yang gzhan gyi lung
NK107(tse)001:545: las kyang bla ma mkhas pa rnams la rtag tu
NK107(tse)001:546: bsten par bya ci phyir zhe na mkhas pa'i yon
NK107(tse)001:547: tan de las 'byung zhes pas so de ltar bla
NK107(tse)001:548: ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa de la bdag gis
NK107(tse)001:549: gzhi ma smin pa smin par bya ba'i don du
NK107(tse)001:550: lo gsum mam lnga'am bcu gcig gong nas dbang bskur
NK107(tse)001:551: bar zhu ba phul te de nas bla mas dbang
NK107(tse)001:552: bskur ba'i rim pa ni bkod pa dang po nas
NK107(tse)001:553: dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bshad phyi dang nang dang
NK107(tse)001:554: gsang ba dang gang la yongs su rdzogs pa yis
NK107(tse)001:555: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de yang mtshan
NK107(tse)001:556: gyi skabs su dbang bskur ba las byin brlabs 'byung
NK107(tse)001:557: ba ni 'byung bar byed pa zhes pa ste de
NK107(tse)001:558: yang gang zag dad pa dang ldan pa la yid
NK107(tse)001:559: ches 'byung la mos gus dang ldan pa la byin
NK107(tse)001:560: brlabs 'byung la gtong phod dang ldan pa la zang
NK107(tse)001:561: zing 'byung la shes rab dang ldan pa la rtogs
NK107(tse)001:562: pa 'byung la nyams len dang ldan pa la nyams
NK107(tse)001:563: myong 'byung bar byed pa'o de yang gang las 'byung
NK107(tse)001:564: zhe na sngon du dbang bskur thob pa las 'byung
NK107(tse)001:565: ba'o de ltar spros bcas dang spros med dang shin
NK107(tse)001:566: tu spros pa med pa dang rab tu spros pa
NK107(tse)001:567: med pa'i dbang rang gi rgyud la brten pa'i nyer
NK107(tse)001:568: rgyur dam tshig brten pa ni yang 'di nyid las
NK107(tse)001:569: mdor bsdus sku dang gsung dang thugs rang gi lus
NK107(tse)001:570: ngag yid la sbyar zhes pa la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:571: te de yang mtshan gyi skabs su rin ces pa
NK107(tse)001:572: ste de yang dper na rang gang 'dod pa'i nor
NK107(tse)001:573: la rin ma bcas par mi thob la gang 'dod
NK107(tse)001:574: pa'i rin bcas nas thob pa ltar dbang thob pa'i
NK107(tse)001:575: rten du yon phul ba yang de nyid las rgyal
NK107(tse)001:576: srid dang zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de
NK107(tse)001:577: yang dam tshig dang ldan pa'i mi la dngos grub
NK107(tse)001:578: 'byung bar nges so de ltar ma smin pa smin
NK107(tse)001:579: par byas nas smin pa grol bar byed pa la
NK107(tse)001:580: bla ma'i man ngag zhu ste gdam ngag la sngon
NK107(tse)001:581: 'gro dang dngos gzhi gnyis te sngon 'gro la lugs
NK107(tse)001:582: gsum yod de rang don gtso che ba 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:583: rus shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa rig pa'i sna 'khrid
NK107(tse)001:584: par byed pa dang gzhan don gtso che bar byed
NK107(tse)001:585: pa sgra bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyis sku gsum gyis sna
NK107(tse)001:586: 'khrid par byed pa dang rang gzhan gnyis med du
NK107(tse)001:587: bstan pa lus ngag yid kyi 'byung byed sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:588: sna 'khrid par byed pa gsum ka rgyud 'di'i bkod
NK107(tse)001:589: pa dang po las shin tu zhib par bstan no
NK107(tse)001:590: de yang mtshan skabs nas sgra zhes pa ste ru
NK107(tse)001:591: shan 'byed pa'i skabs su lus kyis sgra bya ba
NK107(tse)001:592: dang byed pa la brten nas 'khor ba dang ru
NK107(tse)001:593: shan phyed pas 'di'i dus su ci dang ci byas
NK107(tse)001:594: pa tsam gyis ma 'ongs pa'i dus na de dag
NK107(tse)001:595: 'brel pa chod de 'khor ba dang ru shan phyed
NK107(tse)001:596: pa'o ngag gi sgra barjoda pa sna tshogs la brten
NK107(tse)001:597: nas 'khor ba'i ngag dang ru shan phyed pas 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:598: dus su ci dang ci smras pa tsam gyis ma
NK107(tse)001:599: 'ongs pa'i dus na de dag gi 'brel ba chod
NK107(tse)001:600: de 'khor ba'i ngag dang ru shan phyed pa'o sems
NK107(tse)001:601: kyi sgra dran tshad bsam sna tshogs la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:602: 'khor ba'i sems dang ru shan phyed pas 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:603: na ci dang ci bsam pas ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:604: na de dag gis 'brel pa chod de 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:605: sems dang 'brel pa chod de ru shan phyed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:606: yang sgra bzhi la bslab pa'i sngon 'gro'i dbang du
NK107(tse)001:607: byas na sa'i sgra la bslabs pas sa 'og dang
NK107(tse)001:608: sa bla'i 'jig rten shes shing de dag tu rgyu
NK107(tse)001:609: bar nus pa dang chu'i sgra la bslabs pas rgya
NK107(tse)001:610: mtsho chen po dang chu phran rnams kyi mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:611: shes shing de dag la dbang bsgyur nus pa dang
NK107(tse)001:612: me'i sgra la bslabs pas rang gzhan gyi drod kyi
NK107(tse)001:613: mtshan nyid shes shing phyi rol gyi 'byung ba me
NK107(tse)001:614: la dbang bsgyur nus pa'o yang rlung gi sgra la
NK107(tse)001:615: bslabs pas phyi nang gi rlung gi mtshan nyid shes
NK107(tse)001:616: shing phyi'i 'byung ba rlung la dbang bsgyur nus pa'o
NK107(tse)001:617: de lta bu la dus rtag tu bslab pas bem
NK107(tse)001:618: po dang rig bcas kyi sgra dang skad dang brda'i
NK107(tse)001:619: tshogs la 'jol nyog tu spyod par nus pas so
NK107(tse)001:620: yang lus ngag yid kyi sngon du 'gro ba'i dbang
NK107(tse)001:621: du byas na lus kyi sgra rdo rje skyil krung
NK107(tse)001:622: du 'dug pas lus kyi zhen pa rang log pa
NK107(tse)001:623: dang ngag gi sgra yi ge h'u gis sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:624: la gnas pas barjoda pa tsam sngags tshig tu 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:625: ba dang sems kyi sgra byung sa gnas sa 'gro
NK107(tse)001:626: sa gsum la brtags pas dran bsam thams cad ting
NK107(tse)001:627: nge 'dzin du 'gyur ba'o de ltar yang 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:628: kyi bkod pa dang po las rdo rje skyil krung
NK107(tse)001:629: dang bcas te zhes pa la sogs pas zhib tu
NK107(tse)001:630: gsungs so de nas rnal du 'bebs pa'i cho ga
NK107(tse)001:631: yang 'di'i gzhung nas zhib tu gsungs so mtshan gyi
NK107(tse)001:632: skabs su byed pa zhes pa ste lus ngag yid
NK107(tse)001:633: sor 'jug pa zhes pa ste de yang lus sor
NK107(tse)001:634: chud pas rdos bcas rang 'gags ngag sor chud pas
NK107(tse)001:635: barjoda pa rang 'gags pas sems sor chud pas dran
NK107(tse)001:636: pas lam rgyun chad pa'o de nas dngos gzhi'i don
NK107(tse)001:637: rgyud la brten pa ni dang po lus kyi gnad
NK107(tse)001:638: gzir ba ni de yang 'di'i bkod pa dang po
NK107(tse)001:639: las de yang lus ni sku gsum du 'dus ces
NK107(tse)001:640: pa la sogs pa zhib tu bstan la ngag gi
NK107(tse)001:641: gnad du yang ngag ni bslab dang gnas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:642: zhes pa dang sems ni dbyings la gtad pas 'grub
NK107(tse)001:643: zhes pas so de ya mtshan gyi skabs su chen
NK107(tse)001:644: po zhes bya ste lus seng ge chen po dang
NK107(tse)001:645: glang po chen po dang drang srong chen po gsum
NK107(tse)001:646: las ma 'das chos sku longs sku sprul sku chen
NK107(tse)001:647: po gsum gzhi gcig las ma g.yos pa zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:648: de nas gnad rnam pa gsum la brten nas mngon
NK107(tse)001:649: gsum rang thog tu dbab pa ni yang de nyid
NK107(tse)001:650: las gnad gsum man ngag 'bral mi bya zhes pas
NK107(tse)001:651: bstan te mtshan gyi skabs su rgyud ces bya ste
NK107(tse)001:652: sgo'i gnad gzigs stangs gsum du bstan pa ni chos
NK107(tse)001:653: sku nas longs sku'i rgyud du byung la longs sku
NK107(tse)001:654: nas sprul sku'i rgyud yin no lus kyi gnad mig
NK107(tse)001:655: dang nam mkha' dang rig pa dang gsum rgyun chags
NK107(tse)001:656: pas na rgyud ces bya'o rlung rig gi gnad ni
NK107(tse)001:657: rlung dal ba la brten pa rang rgyud 'jam pa
NK107(tse)001:658: 'gyur ba dang lu gu rgyud dbyings kyi nang du
NK107(tse)001:659: zin pas rlung sems kyi rgyun chad pa zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:660: de ltar byas pa la snang ba bzhi 'char pa
NK107(tse)001:661: yang yang de nyid las de las snang ba bzhir
NK107(tse)001:662: 'gyur te zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de
NK107(tse)001:663: yang mtshan gyi skabs su 'gyur zhes pa ste tha
NK107(tse)001:664: mal pa'i snang ba rigs pa mngon sum gyis snang
NK107(tse)001:665: bar 'gyur pas chos nyid la 'grus med pa dang
NK107(tse)001:666: 'khrul pa rags pa'i snang ba nyams gong 'phel chos
NK107(tse)001:667: nyid 'od gsal du 'gyur bas 'khrul pa ni stongs
NK107(tse)001:668: pa dang 'byung ba bazhi'am lnga sku lnga ye shes
NK107(tse)001:669: lnga rig pa tshad phebs kyi snang bar 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:670: nyams su blang bya'i gzhi stongs pa dang nyams kyi
NK107(tse)001:671: snang ba rnams rang zad nas chos nyid zad par
NK107(tse)001:672: 'gyur ba ni 'di nyid la zad pa dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:673: pa'i phung po mi snang bar b+hu da thal ba'o
NK107(tse)001:674: de nas mtha' rten gyi man ngag ni de nyid
NK107(tse)001:675: las mi 'gul ba gsum la gzhi bcas pas ces
NK107(tse)001:676: pa la sogs pa zhib tu bshad do de yang
NK107(tse)001:677: mtshan gyi skabs su tha mal pa zhes pa ste
NK107(tse)001:678: de ltar man ngag nyams su blang ba thal ba
NK107(tse)001:679: las mi 'gul ba gsum gzhir thal ba las thabs
NK107(tse)001:680: la dbang thob sdod pa gsum gyis tshad bzung bas
NK107(tse)001:681: thal bas rtags tshad la dbang thob pa dang thob
NK107(tse)001:682: pa gsum gyis gzer du thal ba las bzlog pa
NK107(tse)001:683: med pa'i ngang du bsgral ba'o da ni mtshan brda'
NK107(tse)001:684: 'gyur tshig tsam la brten nas nang rtags thams cad
NK107(tse)001:685: chos nyid kyi nyams su myong bar 'char bar brtan
NK107(tse)001:686: pa ni de la rin po che 'byung bar byed
NK107(tse)001:687: pa sgra thal 'gyur chen po'i rgyud ces bya ba
NK107(tse)001:688: ni don 'gyur ba med pa las tshig gi sgro
NK107(tse)001:689: 'dog sna tshogs su 'phros pa las brtags pa yang
NK107(tse)001:690: brda' tsam chos nyid kyang brda' tsam du rang shar
NK107(tse)001:691: la snang ba'i dus na yang brda' tsam du rang
NK107(tse)001:692: shar la 'byung ba'i dus na yang brda' tsam du
NK107(tse)001:693: rang byung la gnas pa'i dus na yang brda' tsam
NK107(tse)001:694: du rang gnas te grol ba yang brda' tsam du
NK107(tse)001:695: rang grol ba las byed spyod thams cad rol pa
NK107(tse)001:696: snang rtags thams cad rgyan dang kha dog /
NK107(tse)001:697: 'khor 'das thams cad brda' tsam du rang shar ba'i
NK107(tse)001:698: ngang las rang bzhin gyi brda' 'di ltar snang grags
NK107(tse)001:699: kyis bsdus pa thams cad chos nyid kyi brdar byung
NK107(tse)001:700: bas gang ltar shar gang ltar 'dug kyang chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:701: las 'gro sa med pas na gang yang ma spangs
NK107(tse)001:702: rang sar bzhag pa chos nyid las 'gro sa med
NK107(tse)001:703: pas na gang yang ma spangs rang gzhag chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:704: de las ma 'das pa spyod pa de nyid ma
NK107(tse)001:705: bcos lta ba de la ma yengs bsgom pa de
NK107(tse)001:706: ltar thams cad chos nyid kyi yon tan du shar
NK107(tse)001:707: ba la rin po che zhes bya ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:708: rin chen gang las byung na 'di ltar snang brtags
NK107(tse)001:709: thams cad rang bzhin gyis brdar shes pa las byung
NK107(tse)001:710: ba'o de yang gcig la brtags pas du ma ma
NK107(tse)001:711: grub du ma brtag pas gcig ma grub gnyis ka
NK107(tse)001:712: la brtags pas rang bzhin med pa'o de yang gang
NK107(tse)001:713: las byung na brtags pa thams cad ming ming thams
NK107(tse)001:714: cad brdar shes pa las byung ba'o 'byung bar byed
NK107(tse)001:715: pa zhes bya ba ni barjoda pa'i brda' tshig dang
NK107(tse)001:716: yi ge la brten nas rang bzhin gyis ngag las
NK107(tse)001:717: chos nyid barjoda du med pa'i brda' 'byung bar byed
NK107(tse)001:718: la de yang ji lta bus brten nas skye na
NK107(tse)001:719: barjoda pa thams cad tshig tshig thams cad brtags pa
NK107(tse)001:720: brtags pa thams cad ming ming thams cad rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:721: med pa rang bzhin med pa'i mtha' stong ba'o sgra
NK107(tse)001:722: zhes bya ba ni byas shing brtan ba'i brda' ste
NK107(tse)001:723: de yang byas pa thams cad 'jigs la 'jig pa'i
NK107(tse)001:724: mtha' mi rtag la mi rtag pa'i stong zhing bdag
NK107(tse)001:725: med pa'o de ltar chos nyid kyi mtha' yang stong
NK107(tse)001:726: zhing bdag med pa'o thal 'gyur zhes bya ba ni
NK107(tse)001:727: gnas pa'i brda' ste snang ba gnas pas dbyings su
NK107(tse)001:728: shes la lus la gnas pas gnas lugs su shes
NK107(tse)001:729: pas te de yang gzugs brtags pas stong la brtags
NK107(tse)001:730: pa la yang rang bzhin med la rang bzhin med
NK107(tse)001:731: pa'i mtha' stong pa ngos bzung dang bral ba ste
NK107(tse)001:732: de ltar na barjoda pas stong la gnas pas dag
NK107(tse)001:733: pa zhes bya'o chen po yi zhes bya ba ni
NK107(tse)001:734: rdzogs pa chen po gnas bzhi dang bral ba la
NK107(tse)001:735: gzhi yin pas gnas pa'i brdar byung la 'bras bu
NK107(tse)001:736: yin pas rang bzhin gyi brdar byung ba'o rgyud ni
NK107(tse)001:737: yan lag gi 'du byed kyi brda' la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:738: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag par gtan la phebs
NK107(tse)001:739: bsgrub brgyud kyi brda' la brten nas tshig don dbyer
NK107(tse)001:740: med du rtog pa dang mi snang ba'i brda' la
NK107(tse)001:741: brten nas byung tshor thams cad chos nyid du rtogs
NK107(tse)001:742: pa dang byin gyis brlabs pa'i brda' la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:743: dbang po rnams rang yan lus ngag rnams kyi na
NK107(tse)001:744: 'dar rtogs pa'o zhes bya ba ni de ltar brda'
NK107(tse)001:745: la brten nas dad pa can khams gsum du mi
NK107(tse)001:746: ldog pa'i gzhung tshig dang yi ger bcas pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:747: bstan par zhes pa'i don to de ltar mtshan bstan
NK107(tse)001:748: pa da ni gzhung don 'brel ba bstan pa ste
NK107(tse)001:749: 'di la gsum la rgyud 'byung ba'i phyir phyag btsal
NK107(tse)001:750: ba mdor bstan pa dang rgyud kyi dgos don rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:751: par bya ba'i phyir gleng gzhi gnyis zung 'brel du
NK107(tse)001:752: bstan pa dang le'u lus dang yan lag rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:753: bshad pa'o de la phyag btsal ba ni rgyu ma
NK107(tse)001:754: smin pa smin par bya ba'i don du phyag btsal
NK107(tse)001:755: ba dang sku'i rnam pa gsum gyis 'bras bu rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:756: pa'i don du phyag btsal ba'o de la rgyu ma
NK107(tse)001:757: smin pa smin pa'i don du phyag btsal ba ni
NK107(tse)001:758: de yang sngon 'byung du lha'i bu dga' byed dbang
NK107(tse)001:759: phyug gis rgyud kyi ston pa'i sku'i yon tan la
NK107(tse)001:760: dmigs nas mos pa rnam par dag pas lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:761: sdig pa ma lus pa dag pa bcom la rjes
NK107(tse)001:762: 'jug gi dus na bdag cag la sogs pas kyang
NK107(tse)001:763: mos pa rnam par dag pas so yang ston pa'i
NK107(tse)001:764: gsung gis yon tan la dmigs nas mos pa dag
NK107(tse)001:765: pas ngag gi sdig pa ma lus pa bcom pas
NK107(tse)001:766: na bcom zhes bya'o de bzhin du thugs la yang
NK107(tse)001:767: ngo de ltar bcom pas sngon 'byung rjes 'jug gnyis
NK107(tse)001:768: kas lus kyi dag pa dang ngag dang yid rnam
NK107(tse)001:769: par dag pa dang ldan pas na ldan pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:770: bya'o de ldan pas lus bya ba las 'das ngag
NK107(tse)001:771: barjoda pa las 'das yid rtog pa las 'das pas
NK107(tse)001:772: na 'das zhes bya'o de yang phyi rol ba'i ston
NK107(tse)001:773: pas byas shing byung ba lta bu ma yin te
NK107(tse)001:774: rang gi mos pa dang ldan gus pa las byung
NK107(tse)001:775: ba'o mos gus de yang gang las byung zhe na
NK107(tse)001:776: dad pa chen po dus gsum du skyo ngal med
NK107(tse)001:777: pa dang snying rje chen po dus gsum du thang
NK107(tse)001:778: lhod med pa las byung ba'o de ltar byung ba
NK107(tse)001:779: las thun mong du lus ngag yid kyi rtags rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:780: la mchog tu sku gsum gyi 'bras bu rang la
NK107(tse)001:781: rdzogs pa'o de yang sngon 'byung gi dus bsdus pa
NK107(tse)001:782: po dag gis rjes 'jug tu mos pa skyes pa
NK107(tse)001:783: dag gis ston pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin
NK107(tse)001:784: las mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i byin rlabs
NK107(tse)001:785: las byung ba'o de yang sngon 'byung du bsdus pa
NK107(tse)001:786: po bdag gis mos pa dag pas bdag gi dpal
NK107(tse)001:787: du 'gyur la de nyid la brten nas sems can
NK107(tse)001:788: la dmigs pas na gzhan gyi dpal du gyur pa'o
NK107(tse)001:789: kun tu ni bdag gcig pur ma zad de sems
NK107(tse)001:790: can kun gyis kyang mos pa dag par byas na
NK107(tse)001:791: de ltar 'byung bar nges pa'o de yang thog ma
NK107(tse)001:792: dang bar dang mtha' mar dge bas na don bzang
NK107(tse)001:793: po zhes bya'o de lta bu'i rgyud kyi ston pa
NK107(tse)001:794: la phyag 'tshal lo zhes barjoda pas lus ngag yid
NK107(tse)001:795: kyi dge ba thun mong ma yin pa rdzogs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:796: sku gsum gyi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i don du phyag
NK107(tse)001:797: btsal ba ni gzhi g.yos pa med pa'i bcom ldan
NK107(tse)001:798: 'das rang byung mchog gis ston pa dpal kun tu
NK107(tse)001:799: bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo zhes barjoda pa tsam
NK107(tse)001:800: gyis chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu bzang
NK107(tse)001:801: po'i sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan dbyer mi phyed
NK107(tse)001:802: par 'gyur la de yang lam 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:803: rang byung chen po'i yi ge drug gis rang sgra
NK107(tse)001:804: la brten nas longs sku'i ston pa dpal kun rig
NK107(tse)001:805: rnam par snang mdzad dang dbyer mi phyed par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:806: la 'bras bu re dogs med pa'i mchog gi ston
NK107(tse)001:807: pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad gsung tshig dang yi
NK107(tse)001:808: ge thugs mnyam bzhag dang rjes thob la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:809: sprul pa sku'i ston pa dpal drug pa rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:810: 'chang dang dbyer mi phyed par 'gyur bas na phyag
NK107(tse)001:811: 'tshal lo zhes byas pas sngon 'byung dang rjes 'jug
NK107(tse)001:812: gnyis ka'i lus ngag yid gsum du grol bas na
NK107(tse)001:813: 'bras bu zhes tha snyad du bya'o da ni rgyud
NK107(tse)001:814: kyi dgongs pa'i don rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir na
NK107(tse)001:815: gleng gzhi gnyis zung 'brel du bstan pa ni de
NK107(tse)001:816: las 'dir theg pa thun mong pa rnams las khyad
NK107(tse)001:817: par du 'phags par bstan pa'i phyir thun mong ma
NK107(tse)001:818: yin pa'i gleng gzhi rang gzhung du bstan no 'di
NK107(tse)001:819: skad bdag gis bstan pa'i dus gcig na zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:820: ste ston pa dang gnas dang 'khor dang chos dang
NK107(tse)001:821: dus rnams 'dzom pas thun mong ma yin par bstan
NK107(tse)001:822: pa ste de yang 'di zhes bya ste gnas phun
NK107(tse)001:823: sum tshogs pa gcig gzhan ma yin pa 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:824: 'dus pa so so'i lus te gnas yin pas rigs
NK107(tse)001:825: pa'i bzhugs sa phun sum tshogs pa yin pas 'di
NK107(tse)001:826: la brten nas cir yang bsgyur du btub pas so
NK107(tse)001:827: de ltar yin par cis shes na 'khor dang 'das
NK107(tse)001:828: pa'i thog mar ni ces pa la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:829: no 'di'i 'go gleng gzhi'i dris lan gyis rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:830: bshad pa'i skabs nas kyang gnas ni rnam pa gsum
NK107(tse)001:831: yin te zhes pa la sogs pas rgyas par bstan
NK107(tse)001:832: no bdag ces pa ni ston pa phun sum tshogs
NK107(tse)001:833: pa rang byung rig pa'i ye shes su byung ba
NK107(tse)001:834: ste de yang ston pa yin pas de nyid barjoda
NK107(tse)001:835: bya thams cad kyi gzhi mar byung la phun sum
NK107(tse)001:836: tshogs pa yin pas 'khor 'das thams cad de nyid
NK107(tse)001:837: kyi ngang las byung zhing de nyid du 'dus shing
NK107(tse)001:838: tshogs pas na'o de ltar yin par cis shes na
NK107(tse)001:839: rang byung rig pa bcos pa med ces pa la
NK107(tse)001:840: sogs pas shes so de yang gis zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:841: ste de yang gzhan ma smos par sdud par byed
NK107(tse)001:842: pa'i tshig ste 'khor phun sum tshogs pa lus la
NK107(tse)001:843: bde ba bskyed pa'i rgyu dang sku dang ye shes
NK107(tse)001:844: 'od dang kha dog la sogs pa ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:845: 'khor yin pas rig pa yon tan gyi rtsal snang
NK107(tse)001:846: char byung la phun sum tshogs pa yin pas de
NK107(tse)001:847: nyid la bstan pa'o dgos 'dod rdzogs par 'byung ba'o
NK107(tse)001:848: de yang cis shes na bde chen lus la 'dus
NK107(tse)001:849: pa'i thabs kyi 'khor zhes pas so de ltar gnas
NK107(tse)001:850: dang ston pa dang 'khor dang gsum tshogs pa la
NK107(tse)001:851: bshad par bya ba'i chos dgos te de yang bstan
NK107(tse)001:852: pa'i zhes pa ste bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:853: med na mi 'grol bas rtsa dang rlung la brten
NK107(tse)001:854: pa'i bde ba ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:855: steh de nyid bstan pa yin pas thabs khyad par
NK107(tse)001:856: can la brten nas thabs khyad par can btsan thabs
NK107(tse)001:857: su sangs rgya ba dang phun sum tshogs pa yin
NK107(tse)001:858: pas sna gcig la brten nas sangs rgyas kyi yon
NK107(tse)001:859: tan phun sum tshogs pa'o de ltar cis shes na
NK107(tse)001:860: rtsa rlung thabs kyi bde chen chos zhes pas shes
NK107(tse)001:861: so de yang ston pa nyid kyis 'khor gyi nang
NK107(tse)001:862: du tshul lam thabs ji ltar gsungs na rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:863: rnam par dag pa'i barjoda du med pa'i sgra skad
NK107(tse)001:864: sna tshogs pa'i rang byung rang shar du grags pas
NK107(tse)001:865: na skad ces bya'o 'o na de dag nam 'dzom
NK107(tse)001:866: na dus zhes bya ste dus gsum mnyam pa nyid
NK107(tse)001:867: gcig dang tha mi dad pa'i dus te dus yin
NK107(tse)001:868: pas 'dzom pa la 'gyur ba med la phun sum
NK107(tse)001:869: tshogs pa yin pas de nyid kyi ngang la thams
NK107(tse)001:870: cad dbyer mi phyed par bzhugs so de ltar yin
NK107(tse)001:871: par cis shes na 'das dang ma 'ongs da ltar
NK107(tse)001:872: med ces pas so 'o na de dag gnas logs
NK107(tse)001:873: cig na ston pa logs cig la sogs pa ma
NK107(tse)001:874: yin teh thams cad rig pa rdo rje lu gu
NK107(tse)001:875: rgyud kyi sku dang dbyer med pa sna gcig ces
NK107(tse)001:876: bya ste gnas kyang rang byung rig pa'i ye shes
NK107(tse)001:877: ston pa dang 'khor dang dus kyang rang byung rig
NK107(tse)001:878: pa'i ye shes sam rig pa rdo rje lu gu
NK107(tse)001:879: rgyud kyi sku las gzhan pa ni ma yin no
NK107(tse)001:880: de ltar byed ces na thams cad rang byung ye
NK107(tse)001:881: shes zhes pas shes so mdor na de thams cad
NK107(tse)001:882: rnal 'byor pa'i lus la 'tshogs pas na phun sum
NK107(tse)001:883: tshogs pa zhes bya'o dus cig na zhes kyang bya'o
NK107(tse)001:884: de ltar lus la gnas par cis shes na na
NK107(tse)001:885: zhes bya ba lus mtshon par byed pa ste lus
NK107(tse)001:886: la gnas zhes pa'i tha tshig go de lta bu'i
NK107(tse)001:887: gnas kyi rin ci zhe na 'khor dang zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:888: gang la 'khor na gzhi rig pa chos kyi sku
NK107(tse)001:889: la 'khor gang du 'khor na 'khrul pa las dang
NK107(tse)001:890: bag chags tha dad par 'khor de ltar de'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:891: nyid shes pas 'bras bu khams gsum las grol ba'o
NK107(tse)001:892: de yang gang la brten pas gol zhe na sgra
NK107(tse)001:893: bzhi rang tshad la phebs pas grol bar nges so
NK107(tse)001:894: 'das pa'i zhes pa ni gzhi barjoda bya las 'das
NK107(tse)001:895: pas gtan la dbab bya dang 'bebs byed gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:896: ma grub lam brtsol bsgrub las 'das pas sbyang bya
NK107(tse)001:897: dang sbyong byed gnyis su ma grub 'bras bu blo
NK107(tse)001:898: las 'das pas thob bya dang thob byed gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:899: ma grub pa'o de yang gang las byung zhe na
NK107(tse)001:900: 'byung ba bzhi'i 'dod yon lam du bslongs pa las
NK107(tse)001:901: 'byung ba'o thog mar ni zhes pas ste sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:902: sgom des ma mdzad sems can sgrin de ma bcos
NK107(tse)001:903: pa'i gnas lugs ngo bo cir yang ma grub pa
NK107(tse)001:904: rang bzhin gang du yang ma 'gags par gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:905: thugs rjes kun tu khyab cing gang gis yang snang
NK107(tse)001:906: tshul mi shes pa nyid de 'khor ba'i thog mar
NK107(tse)001:907: byung bas 'khrul pa'i gzhi yin 'das pa'i thog mar
NK107(tse)001:908: byung bar dag pa ye shes su zang thal gnyis
NK107(tse)001:909: dang gnyis ka ma yin pa'i thog mar byung bas
NK107(tse)001:910: rtsal dang rol pa sna tshogs su snang ba nyid
NK107(tse)001:911: do de yang gang gis kyang brtags pa'am byas pa
NK107(tse)001:912: med par rang byung du sus kyang byas pa med
NK107(tse)001:913: pa'i ye shes su bzhugs pa las sems can rnams
NK107(tse)001:914: kyi nye bar len pa'i rgyu 'byung ba dang chu
NK107(tse)001:915: dang me dang rlung 'dus pa'i gzugs dang tshor ba
NK107(tse)001:916: dang 'du shes dang 'du byed dang rnam par shes
NK107(tse)001:917: pa 'dus pa'i phung po lngar shar te 'gro ba'i
NK107(tse)001:918: lus su smin par byas pa ni phyi'i sa las
NK107(tse)001:919: nang du shar smin pas lus kyi gzhi byas phyi
NK107(tse)001:920: chu las nang khrag tu smin pas lus kyi bsdus
NK107(tse)001:921: pa byas phyi'i me las nang du drod du smin
NK107(tse)001:922: pas lus smin cing gsal bar byas phyi'i rlung las
NK107(tse)001:923: nang du dbugs su smin pas lus kyi 'degs byas
NK107(tse)001:924: pas lus su grub pa ni gnas te rin po
NK107(tse)001:925: che rnam pa bzhi las grub pa'i gzhal med khang
NK107(tse)001:926: gru bzhi dom tshad bzhi dang yar gyi sgo bzhi
NK107(tse)001:927: lus kyi bye brag gi rta babs dang bcas pa
NK107(tse)001:928: ni ston pa'i gnas thun mong ma yin pa shin
NK107(tse)001:929: tu ngo mtshar ba'o de yang lus kyi dkyil 'khor
NK107(tse)001:930: de lta bu'i dbus su tsi ta rin po che'i
NK107(tse)001:931: nang du pha ma'i rgyu rkyen la brten pa bdag
NK107(tse)001:932: gis rlung sems gnyis pha ma'i rgyu rkyen gnyis bzhi
NK107(tse)001:933: 'dus pa las rin po che sna bzhi'i lus 'khor
NK107(tse)001:934: lo bzhi dang bcas pa btsa' ba'i byed pa can
NK107(tse)001:935: du grub pa'o de ltar phyi 'byung ba bzhi dang
NK107(tse)001:936: nang rin po che bzhi dang gsang ba rgyu rkyen
NK107(tse)001:937: rlung sems bzhi 'dus shing don dam kun rdzob las
NK107(tse)001:938: bskyed pa'i gzhal med khang na rig pa'i ye shes
NK107(tse)001:939: bzhugs pas gnas zhes bya ste gnas phun sum tshogs
NK107(tse)001:940: pas zhes bya'o de lta bu'i gnas su ston pa'i
NK107(tse)001:941: mtshan nyid ces zhe na thog mar byung yang rang
NK107(tse)001:942: byung du byung ba'i rig pa nyid sus kyang bcos
NK107(tse)001:943: pa med pa'i ston par bzhugs pa de de ci'i
NK107(tse)001:944: phyir ston pa yin na gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:945: rtog pa tha dad pa'i 'khrul pa yongs su dag
NK107(tse)001:946: pa de nyid la 'phral rkyen gang gis mi gnod
NK107(tse)001:947: pa bcas bcos las ma grol bar ston pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:948: bya'o de lta ba'i ston pa la yang 'khor 'byung
NK107(tse)001:949: ba bzhi rnam par dag pa'i bde ba las 'byung
NK107(tse)001:950: ba'i ye shes chen po lnga dang sku lnga dang
NK107(tse)001:951: ye shes lnga dang shes rab lnga dang me dang
NK107(tse)001:952: mnyam du gnas pa la sogs te rlung lnga 'dus
NK107(tse)001:953: pa'i gsang sngags kyi thabs kyi 'khor rnams dang gang
NK107(tse)001:954: du yang mi phyed par 'khrul pa sna tshogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:955: dmigs pa med pa la snyoms par bzhugs so de'i
NK107(tse)001:956: tshe chos ci zhe na rtsa la brten pa'i mi
NK107(tse)001:957: rtog pa'i ye shes kyi bde ba rba rlabs bzung
NK107(tse)001:958: ba dang skyil ba dang mnan pa dang gtems pa
NK107(tse)001:959: las 'byung ba dang de bzhin sri ma ka dang
NK107(tse)001:960: 'khyim ma bzung ba dang dkyil ba dang mnan pa
NK107(tse)001:961: dang gtems pa las 'byung ba rnams dang de ltar
NK107(tse)001:962: rlung la bslab pa'i rim pa sna tshogs pa gsang
NK107(tse)001:963: sngags kyi thabs kyis bde ba chen po bskyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:964: chos ni bstan pa ste rang la brten nas skye
NK107(tse)001:965: bas na thun mong ma yin pa'o de yang 'gro
NK107(tse)001:966: ba so so gang la mos pa'i nyams dang mthun
NK107(tse)001:967: par chos bshad pas na bstan pa'o de ltar bzhis
NK107(tse)001:968: 'das pa la ma yin de bzhin du ma 'ongs
NK107(tse)001:969: pa'ng ma yin da ltar med par 'di nyid la
NK107(tse)001:970: tshang pas gang du yang ma phyed gang yang mi
NK107(tse)001:971: 'byed pa yongs su med pas dus zhes bya ste
NK107(tse)001:972: de rnams kyang rang byung ye shes gcig gis 'khor
NK107(tse)001:973: las ma 'das pas na thams cad rang byung ye
NK107(tse)001:974: shes so zhes pa'o da ni thun mong gi gleng
NK107(tse)001:975: gzhi theg pa gzhan dang go bstun du bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:976: ni ston pas bsdus pa po la 'di ma yin
NK107(tse)001:977: pa zhing khams gzhan du yang 'khor gzhan la 'di
NK107(tse)001:978: skad bdag gis bstan zhes gsungs pa'i don khong du
NK107(tse)001:979: chud nas sdud pa po lha'i bu dga' byed dbang
NK107(tse)001:980: phyug kho rang gi 'khor gyi nang du tshig 'di
NK107(tse)001:981: skad barjoda de 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:982: gcig na zhes barjoda pas 'khor rnams la go rgyu
NK107(tse)001:983: ma byung la la las ji lta bu zhig thos
NK107(tse)001:984: snyam pa tsam skyes pa dang la las ni khyod
NK107(tse)001:985: kyis thos dang thos na gnas ni gang du thos
NK107(tse)001:986: snyam pa dang ston pa ji skad bya ba las
NK107(tse)001:987: thos snyam pa dang grogs gang dang lhan cig tu
NK107(tse)001:988: thos snyam pa dang chos ni ji skad bya ba
NK107(tse)001:989: zhig thos snyam pa dang dus ni gang tsam na
NK107(tse)001:990: thos snyam pa'i rtog pa skyes so bsdus pa po
NK107(tse)001:991: de nyid kyang b+hud tha'i rnam 'phrul yin pas 'khor
NK107(tse)001:992: gyi rtog pa rnams thugs su chud nas 'di zhes
NK107(tse)001:993: bya ba gnas phun sum tshogs pa chos kyi sku'i
NK107(tse)001:994: gnas chos kyi dbyings yin la longs sku'i gnas rnam
NK107(tse)001:995: dag stug po bkod par thos la sprul pa sku'i
NK107(tse)001:996: gnas dga' ldan rtsegs pa zhes bya bar thos pa
NK107(tse)001:997: byas so de rang la ci la zer snyam na
NK107(tse)001:998: dga' ldan ldan pa bsod nams brtsegs zhes pa la
NK107(tse)001:999: sogs pas shes par gyis shig /
NK107(tse)001:1000: gnas dang de yin na ston pa ni gang las
NK107(tse)001:1001: thos pa byas snyam na skad ces bya ste lha
NK107(tse)001:1002: tshangs pa'i skad kyis nye ring med par gsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1003: gsung dang mnyam pa'i khye'u snang ba dam pa bsam
NK107(tse)001:1004: gyis mi khyab pa la thos so de yang ma
NK107(tse)001:1005: go na rkyen zhes smin pa'i gzugs kyi sku la
NK107(tse)001:1006: sogs par shes par gyis shig /
NK107(tse)001:1007: de'anga rgyud pa'am gzhan gyis bar ma chod par bdag
NK107(tse)001:1008: rang gi rna ba'i dbang po phyin ci ma log
NK107(tse)001:1009: pas thos pa byas so grogs ni gang zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:1010: ste lha'i bu nyi ma rab tu snang byed dang
NK107(tse)001:1011: zla ba dri ma med pa dang sangs rgyas stong
NK107(tse)001:1012: rtsa gnyis la sogs pa rnams dang thos pa byas
NK107(tse)001:1013: te de ma go na gdul bya bardzusa nas skyes
NK107(tse)001:1014: pa rnams dang bya ba log pa shes par gyis
NK107(tse)001:1015: shig chos ni gcig zhes bya ste don gyis sgra
NK107(tse)001:1016: thal 'gyur chen po gsang ba'i brgyud 'di thos so
NK107(tse)001:1017: de ma go na drug cu rtsa gcig bzhi'i 'od
NK107(tse)001:1018: dkar ni zhes pa la sogs pas shes par gyis
NK107(tse)001:1019: shig de ltar gzhi'i dus na gcig na bzhugs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1020: dus na des thos pa byas pa yin te des
NK107(tse)001:1021: ma go na 'og nas dus kyi skabs nas ston
NK107(tse)001:1022: no de la 'dir ni gnas kyi don rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:1023: bshad na bskal pa dang po tshe lo dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:1024: med pa thub pa'i dus na sems can rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:1025: lus len pa'i 'go 'dzugs pa'i tshe lus kyi ming
NK107(tse)001:1026: gi sngon du nyon mongs pa sngon rgyu med cing
NK107(tse)001:1027: bag la nyal tsam las med pas dga' ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1028: bde ba 'ba' zhig la spyod pas na 'dod chags
NK107(tse)001:1029: dang zhe sdang dang gti mug sngon du rgyu med
NK107(tse)001:1030: pa ste rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan dang ldan pa'o
NK107(tse)001:1031: de nas rang bzhin gyis rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK107(tse)001:1032: dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa las
NK107(tse)001:1033: gnas 'di lta bur skyes pa yin te de ltar
NK107(tse)001:1034: sngon rgyu med kyang bag la nyal gyi bag chags
NK107(tse)001:1035: rnams brtsegs pa las 'gro ba drug gi gzugs 'char
NK107(tse)001:1036: gzhi ma 'gags pa las thog ma gzugs med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1037: lha rnams kyi lus su byung la de rnams nas
NK107(tse)001:1038: gzugs khams kyi lha rnams kyi lus las 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1039: lha dang mi rnams kyi thog ma'i lus ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:1040: ba sa dang chu dang me rlung gi 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:1041: chen po bzhi mi snang bar dag pa chen po
NK107(tse)001:1042: lus zhes bya ba dkar dmar 'ja' tshon lnga'i 'od
NK107(tse)001:1043: kyi khyim du snang bas 'gro na yang phan tshun
NK107(tse)001:1044: du nam mkha' la 'gro la 'dug na yang nam
NK107(tse)001:1045: mkha' la 'khod do 'di'i dus na 'gro ba'i lus
NK107(tse)001:1046: rnams kyang sha dang khrag gis bkod pa'i 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:1047: 'dus pa'i gzugs su med pa'i lus ni 'od gsal
NK107(tse)001:1048: chen po'i lus zang thal 'gro 'ong dang bcas par
NK107(tse)001:1049: gnas pa'o 'di'i dus na rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK107(tse)001:1050: dag pa chen po'i lus zhes bya ba rgyan dang
NK107(tse)001:1051: kha dog gis rab tu mdzes shing zas dang gos
NK107(tse)001:1052: kyang ting nge 'dzin la ma brten pas na rab
NK107(tse)001:1053: tu rgyas pa'i mdangs yod pa'i lus de lta bur
NK107(tse)001:1054: gdul bya bardzusa nas skyes pa'i 'gro ba rnams la
NK107(tse)001:1055: gzigs na nyes skyoon gang gis kyang ma gos pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1056: pad ma'i 'dab ma dang yu ba dang ze'u 'bru
NK107(tse)001:1057: rnams rab tu rgyas pa lta bas chog mi shes
NK107(tse)001:1058: shing rab tu mdzes shing gzugs dang kha dog shin
NK107(tse)001:1059: tu rdzogs pa'i mdangs 'dab ma kha stong dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:1060: pa'i sbub ma'i gnas nas thon te ston pa sangs
NK107(tse)001:1061: rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:1062: yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa'i gzugs 'od kyi mdangs
NK107(tse)001:1063: yod par gyur te de yang rgyu'i rkyen yod pas
NK107(tse)001:1064: lus kyi gzhi byas dmigs pa'i rkyen las yul dang
NK107(tse)001:1065: snang char byung de ma thag pa'i rkyen gyis lus
NK107(tse)001:1066: sems 'brel byas bdag po'i rkyen bzhis sprul pa'i sku'i
NK107(tse)001:1067: gzugs su smin pa'i phyir na gzugs kyi sku rab
NK107(tse)001:1068: tu mdzes shing mtshan dang dpe byad kyis spras pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1069: 'od kyis rab tu bskor ba bardzusa nas skyes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1070: lus bslangs te sems can gyi don du byon pa'o
NK107(tse)001:1071: de yang gong gi gnas pad ma la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:1072: ston pa ni sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan gyi
NK107(tse)001:1073: mkhyen pa'i cha nas bzhag la de ltar yon tan
NK107(tse)001:1074: rdzogs pa'i stobs kyis nyon mongs pa 'khrul pa'i rnam
NK107(tse)001:1075: par rtog pa tha dad pa sangs pas skye ba
NK107(tse)001:1076: dang 'chi ba'i mtha' gnyis la mi rtog ste sku
NK107(tse)001:1077: dang ye shes su ngang gis rgyas pas mdzad pa
NK107(tse)001:1078: ma lus pa la thogs pa med par mdzad do
NK107(tse)001:1079: de nyid bdud bzhi ngam ngam shugs kyis bcom pas
NK107(tse)001:1080: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa sna tshogs dang ldan pas
NK107(tse)001:1081: na khams gsum 'khor ba'i blos bdag tu rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:1082: las 'das pas na rang bzhin shugs kyis 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:1083: gang la yang dbyer med pa'i thugs rje shugs las
NK107(tse)001:1084: 'byung ba'o de yang sa brgyad pa'i dus na byang
NK107(tse)001:1085: chub sems dpa' rnams la don 'gags pa med par
NK107(tse)001:1086: 'char ba la dgongs nas dgung lo brgyad pa rab
NK107(tse)001:1087: tu mdzes pa'i gzugs su sprul pa ni gdul bya
NK107(tse)001:1088: la 'gro ba 'dul byed kyi spyan gyis gzigs pa
NK107(tse)001:1089: dang skye gnas pad ma la snang bar 'dul byed
NK107(tse)001:1090: kyi spyan gyis gzigs pa dang lha'i bu rnams la
NK107(tse)001:1091: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis gzigs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1092: stangs dang gsum las ston pa'i skur byung ba ste
NK107(tse)001:1093: bardzusa nas skyes pa'i 'gro ba rnams 'dul ba'i skur
NK107(tse)001:1094: byon no de ltar 'jig rten du ston pa byon
NK107(tse)001:1095: pa'i tshe sku'i rnam pa thams cad las snang ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1096: 'od ni brgya stong bye ba khrag khrig drug cu
NK107(tse)001:1097: drug cus 'jig rten thams cad du snang bar byas
NK107(tse)001:1098: pa'o de yang 'jig rten 'di ma gtogs pas gzhan
NK107(tse)001:1099: yang 'jig rten gyi khams bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK107(tse)001:1100: snang bar mdzad pas 'dir 'di dag las kyang sprul
NK107(tse)001:1101: pa'i skur dpag tu med pa 'phros pas mdzad pa
NK107(tse)001:1102: rnams kyi dang por byung ngo spyir na mdo rgyud
NK107(tse)001:1103: rnams 'byung bar byed pas te gleng gzhi zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:1104: ba ni thams cad kyi dang po la phun sum
NK107(tse)001:1105: tshogs pa lnga po rnams kyi sa bon ni ston
NK107(tse)001:1106: pas 'dzin pas na gdul bya'i rnam par rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:1107: zad par byed pa la dgongs pa'o ston pa de
NK107(tse)001:1108: lta bu la 'khor rgyas par bshad pa ni de'i
NK107(tse)001:1109: tshe gdul bya'i sems can ni ma dag pa'i gdul
NK107(tse)001:1110: bya ma yin par rang bzhin gyis dag pas bardzusa
NK107(tse)001:1111: nas skyes pa rnams la chos ston pa'i skur byung
NK107(tse)001:1112: ba ste gdul bya'i 'gro ba de dag kyang kha
NK107(tse)001:1113: dog shin tu dkar zhing 'od kyi gzi mdangs kyis
NK107(tse)001:1114: brgyan pa sha khrag rang ka ma'i gzugs dang bral
NK107(tse)001:1115: bas 'od kyi lus su yod pa de yang shel
NK107(tse)001:1116: gyi gong bu bzhin du zang thal du yod pa
NK107(tse)001:1117: ni nyon mongs pa sngon du rgyu'i dri ma med
NK107(tse)001:1118: pa'i dus na nyon mongs pa rags pa rnams 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:1119: dus na rang dag pa ste nyon mongs pa bag
NK107(tse)001:1120: la nyal ba ma yin pa phyi rol gyi yul
NK107(tse)001:1121: lus la mngon par rgyu ba rnams dang bral nas
NK107(tse)001:1122: rang so la gnas pa'o de yang gang las byung
NK107(tse)001:1123: zhe na mig gis rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i dbang
NK107(tse)001:1124: po dang rna ba dang sna dang lce dang lus
NK107(tse)001:1125: kyi rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i dbang po lnga ni
NK107(tse)001:1126: rang gsal ba tsam las rang rgyud du 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:1127: med do 'di'i dus na pho mo'i dbang po'i sgo
NK107(tse)001:1128: yang ma dod pas pho mo'i mtshan ma rnams ni
NK107(tse)001:1129: 'od kyi sbubs su nub nas mi snang la sbubs
NK107(tse)001:1130: phyi nang du rgyu ba la brten pa'i 'gro 'ong
NK107(tse)001:1131: kyang rang bzhin gyis zad pas tshe lo yang dpag
NK107(tse)001:1132: tu med pa thub bo de'i stobs kyis 'gro na
NK107(tse)001:1133: yang bar snang la 'gro la gnas na yang bar
NK107(tse)001:1134: snang dag la 'od dang bcas nas gnas so phan
NK107(tse)001:1135: tshun du 'gro na yang bar snang la 'gro la
NK107(tse)001:1136: 'khod na yang bar snang ba 'khod pa dang de
NK107(tse)001:1137: bzhin du langs par byed pa'i dus na yang bar
NK107(tse)001:1138: snang dag la langs pa las ma gtogs pa med
NK107(tse)001:1139: do de bzhin du 'gro ba dang 'greng ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1140: nyal ba dang bskyod cing rgyugs pa'i rnam pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:1141: la yang bar snang nyid las gzhan pa'i 'gro 'dug
NK107(tse)001:1142: ci yang min no 'di'i dus na nyi ma dang
NK107(tse)001:1143: zla ba'i snang ba med par rang las 'od byung
NK107(tse)001:1144: ba'i snang ba las 'byung ba'i rang gdangs gsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1145: gnad kyis nyi zla la sogs pa'i gnad kyis 'od
NK107(tse)001:1146: mi snang ngo rang bzhin gyi bsod nams kyis gos
NK107(tse)001:1147: med kyang lus kyi sha rnams 'jam pa'i ngang tshul
NK107(tse)001:1148: can du yod do 'di'i dus na lus khru tshad
NK107(tse)001:1149: sum cu rtsa gnyis pa rab tu mdzes shing ldem
NK107(tse)001:1150: bag dang ldan pa las 'od kyi mdangs yod pa'o
NK107(tse)001:1151: shes pa bag yangs su yod pa la rnam par
NK107(tse)001:1152: shes pa gud du bcad pa med par bsam gtan
NK107(tse)001:1153: dang po'i lha'i sems gnas pa bzhin du yid kyi
NK107(tse)001:1154: rnam par shes pa mngon par 'du bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1155: byed pa dang bral nas gzugs med pa'i lha rnams
NK107(tse)001:1156: kyi dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba'i las kyi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:1157: byed ltar phung po dang khams dang dbang po rnams
NK107(tse)001:1158: gud du gcad pa'i las kyi bye brag mi snang
NK107(tse)001:1159: ngo de lta bu'i gdul bya'i sems can lha'i bu
NK107(tse)001:1160: nyi ma rab tu snang byed dang zla ba dri
NK107(tse)001:1161: ma med pa la sogs pa rnams dang de'i tshe
NK107(tse)001:1162: khyad par gyi 'khor ni bskal pa bzang po 'di
NK107(tse)001:1163: nyid las khyad par du b+hud tha ba 'di tsam
NK107(tse)001:1164: zhig 'byung ba'i ltas su snying po bcud du 'dril
NK107(tse)001:1165: ba'i pad+ma 'dab ma stong dang ldan pa las sangs
NK107(tse)001:1166: rgyas stong rtsa gcig khyad par las kyi sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1167: kyi gzugs dang rtsa gnyis kyi gzugs rnams ni snang
NK107(tse)001:1168: ba rang bzhin med pa 'ja' tshon nam sgyu ma'i
NK107(tse)001:1169: lus ji bzhin du sangs rgyas de dag rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:1170: gzugs su snang ngo de'i tshe khyad par du ston
NK107(tse)001:1171: pa'i gzugs las ris can du dkar ba dang dmar
NK107(tse)001:1172: ba dang ser ba dang ljang ba dang mthing kha'i
NK107(tse)001:1173: 'od zer dpag tu med pa spros pas sems can
NK107(tse)001:1174: rnams la snang bar byas so de lta bu'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:1175: la bstan pa khyad par can sdud pa po nga
NK107(tse)001:1176: ni lha'i bu dga' byed dbang phyug ces bya ba
NK107(tse)001:1177: 'od snang rdzogs pa'i lus blangs te ston pa sangs
NK107(tse)001:1178: rgyas bcom ldan 'das dang zhal mjal gsung thos pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1179: dus na ston pa'i gsung gi byin rlabs las 'od
NK107(tse)001:1180: zer gyi khyim sna tshogs su 'phros pa las sdud
NK107(tse)001:1181: pa po bdag kyang rang bzhin gyis ni bde ba
NK107(tse)001:1182: rnyed nas b+hud tha'i dgongs pa dang dbyer mi phyed
NK107(tse)001:1183: par 'gyur ro de yang gang las byung na de'i
NK107(tse)001:1184: tshe sangs rgyas rnams kyi mdzad pa'i byin gyis barlaba
NK107(tse)001:1185: las rang bzhin gyis nam mkha' la 'od kyi skar
NK107(tse)001:1186: ma 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i 'od skar ma
NK107(tse)001:1187: bskram pa lta bu snang bar byas so de ni
NK107(tse)001:1188: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ba'i chos
NK107(tse)001:1189: kyi rnam grangs la sho lo ka 'bum phrag drug
NK107(tse)001:1190: cu rtsa bzhi 'byung ba'i snga ltas so de yang
NK107(tse)001:1191: bar snang stong pa nyid la 'od lnga'i skar ma
NK107(tse)001:1192: 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi dang de'i 'od kyi
NK107(tse)001:1193: thigs pa bcu bdun gzugs su bkod par snang ste
NK107(tse)001:1194: de yang rang bzhin gyis snang ba las ma rtogs
NK107(tse)001:1195: pa sus kyang byas pa med par snang bar byas
NK107(tse)001:1196: so spyir 'od kyi tshogs dpag tu med pa las
NK107(tse)001:1197: skar ma rnams khyad par du snang la de las
NK107(tse)001:1198: kyang khyad par du 'od kyi thigs pa yang zhun
NK107(tse)001:1199: bcu bdun du snang bar byas pa ni rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:1200: rdzogs pa chen po rnams las khyad par du gyur
NK107(tse)001:1201: pa'i gsang chen nges pa'i rgyud bcu bdun 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1202: snga ltas so de yang chos gser gyi snying po
NK107(tse)001:1203: nyi ma rab tu snang ba 'di la sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1204: kyi bstan pa dam par rdzogs pa nyid yin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1205: phyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i bstan pa'i btsas
NK107(tse)001:1206: sus kyang byas pa med par rin po che rgya
NK107(tse)001:1207: rtsa gcig gi rgyu las rang byung ba'i sku dang
NK107(tse)001:1208: de ni sprul pa'i sku dngos yin la gsung gi
NK107(tse)001:1209: bstan pa dngos rin po che stong phrag brgyad cu
NK107(tse)001:1210: rtsa lnga'i rgyu las byung la sangs rgyas thams cad
NK107(tse)001:1211: kyis gsung gis sa bon ldang bar byed pa longs
NK107(tse)001:1212: sku dngos dang de ni rang byung gi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:1213: shwa lo ka brgya phrag gnyis dang phyed dang brgyad
NK107(tse)001:1214: yod do thugs kyi bstan pa dngos rin po che
NK107(tse)001:1215: dgu brgya dang dgu bcu rtsa lnga las rang byung
NK107(tse)001:1216: pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis thugs kyi sa bon
NK107(tse)001:1217: ldang bar byed pa chos sku dngos yin te rang
NK107(tse)001:1218: bzhin chos nyid kyi rdo rje zhes bya'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:1219: bstan pa'i gzugs brnyan dang bstan pa dngos gnyis las
NK107(tse)001:1220: de ltar bstan pa dngos yin pas na don gyi
NK107(tse)001:1221: bem po'i sprul pa'i sku zhes bya ste de gsum
NK107(tse)001:1222: gang yang rung ba'i gcig gang zag gcig la babs
NK107(tse)001:1223: pa ni 'bad pa med par 'chi 'phos ma thag
NK107(tse)001:1224: tu sangs rgyas pa la the tshom med do de
NK107(tse)001:1225: ltar na thugs kyi rdo rje de ni skyes bu
NK107(tse)001:1226: gang la babs pa'i chag gang gi tshad dang gsung
NK107(tse)001:1227: gi btsas zhes bya ste zho rtsa bas dang 'dra
NK107(tse)001:1228: bas na bstan pa thams cad 'chags shing 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1229: rten 'dis byed de gzhung tshad ni brgya phrag gnyis
NK107(tse)001:1230: dang phyed dang brgyad yod cing skad rigs mi mthun
NK107(tse)001:1231: pa'i 'gro ba skal ba can gang gis bltas kyang
NK107(tse)001:1232: rang rang gi yi ge dang mthun par snang ba'o
NK107(tse)001:1233: sku'i gzugs de ni bstan pa gang la dbang ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1234: skyes bu'i lus bongs dang mnyam pa'o de dag gsum
NK107(tse)001:1235: kyang dus 'di tsam na 'byung zhes bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1236: sangs rgyas sus kyang byas pa ma yin par rang
NK107(tse)001:1237: byung du ye thog ma nas 'di ni rang snang
NK107(tse)001:1238: bar bzhugs pa nyid las gdul bya so so'i las
NK107(tse)001:1239: dang skal pa yod pa la mthun par snang ba
NK107(tse)001:1240: ste de yang bstan pa tsam dang lhan cig tu
