NK107(tse)001:1241: gnas pa ma yin te chos gser gyi snying po
NK107(tse)001:1242: nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed pa nyid la
NK107(tse)001:1243: snang ba las ma gtogs pa bstan pa kun dang
NK107(tse)001:1244: lhan cig gnas pa ma yin no des na gsang
NK107(tse)001:1245: chen nges pa'i rgyud bcu bdun po 'dir rang gi
NK107(tse)001:1246: snying dang 'dra ba yin pa'i phyir rab tu gsang
NK107(tse)001:1247: ngo de'i phyin na bstan pa dngos gsum po 'di
NK107(tse)001:1248: rnams ni dngos grub mchog rnams kyi yang mthar thug
NK107(tse)001:1249: yin no de ci'i phyir zhe na 'di gsum su
NK107(tse)001:1250: la babs pa'i gang zag de ni 'bad cing brtsol
NK107(tse)001:1251: ba ma yin par gang du skal ba dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:1252: pa de nyid gang su dang phrad pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:1253: grol bar nges so des na rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:1254: chen po bya btsal dang bral ba zhes bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:1255: yang gzhan btsol 'bad pa las byung ba ma yin
NK107(tse)001:1256: te sngon thog ma nas sangs rgyas barjoda du med
NK107(tse)001:1257: pa'i ye thog ma nas phyag mdzad pa'i byin brlabs
NK107(tse)001:1258: las byung ste de lta bu'i bstan pa dngos su
NK107(tse)001:1259: la brgyud na chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun
NK107(tse)001:1260: tu bzang po la nges par brgyud de ma 'ongs
NK107(tse)001:1261: pa'i dus na yang las can rnams la snang bar
NK107(tse)001:1262: byed pa'i don du sprul pa'i sku cig ma byung
NK107(tse)001:1263: na ma byung byung na 'di dag gsum la brten
NK107(tse)001:1264: nas sa bon ldang bar byed pa'o de dag bstan
NK107(tse)001:1265: pa dngos ste de dag gsum ni gnas gang na
NK107(tse)001:1266: bzhugs na rdo rje de nyid ni nub phyogs u
NK107(tse)001:1267: rgyan gyi yul rgya mtsho lan tsh+wa'i ro dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:1268: pa'i gling bya ba na da lta klu'i rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:1269: gtsug gi nor bu rab tu snang bar byed pa
NK107(tse)001:1270: zhes bya bsah 'khor stong phrag du ma dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:1271: pas phyag tshags mdzad nas soh de yang b+hud rda'i
NK107(tse)001:1272: thugs kyi bstan pa byung ba'i dus na 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:1273: dang lhan cig tu gnas soh de su la babs
NK107(tse)001:1274: pa nyid kyang 'bad med du b+hud tha ba'o gsung
NK107(tse)001:1275: de rdo rje gsum gyi steng gi nam mkha' nas
NK107(tse)001:1276: dpag tshad lnga'i steng na nam mkha' 'gro ma rin
NK107(tse)001:1277: po che dpal 'phreng ma zhes bya bah 'khor 'bum
NK107(tse)001:1278: phrag stong rtsa gnyis dang bcas pas bzung nas phyag
NK107(tse)001:1279: rgya dam pa mdzad do de yang gsung gis 'dul
NK107(tse)001:1280: ba'i bstan pa'i dus na 'di dang lhan cig tu
NK107(tse)001:1281: gnas pas de su la babs pa de yang 'bad
NK107(tse)001:1282: med du grol bar nges so sku'i sku ni 'dzam
NK107(tse)001:1283: bu'i gling kun tu 'khor gnas shing 'di dang 'di
NK107(tse)001:1284: na yod kyi nges pa med do de yang skus
NK107(tse)001:1285: 'dul ba'i bstan pa'i dus na 'di dang lhan cig
NK107(tse)001:1286: tu gnas so su la 'bas pa de yang snga
NK107(tse)001:1287: ma dang 'dra'o de nas sprul pa'i sku gcig gis
NK107(tse)001:1288: bstan pa mi gnas pa'i tshe na 'di gsum gang
NK107(tse)001:1289: zag gcig la 'tshogs te de yang 'di nyid du
NK107(tse)001:1290: grol te de las lo nyer lnga na nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:1291: la 'phar nas 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan du 'phar
NK107(tse)001:1292: te bstan pa gzhan gyi btsas byed par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:1293: sangs rgyas kyi 'das pa rjes su bzung zhing bcangs
NK107(tse)001:1294: pa de yang 'bad pa cher bya mi dgos par
NK107(tse)001:1295: grol ba dag yin no des ni dngos kyi bstan
NK107(tse)001:1296: pa ji ltar 'byung ba bstan nas da ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:1297: pa gzugs brnyan gyi bstan pa ji ltar 'byung zhing
NK107(tse)001:1298: zab mo snying po'i don ji ltar yin pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:1299: pa ni de ltar sangs rgyas dngos kyi bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1300: byin gyis brlabs las gzugs brnyan gyi bstan pa'i cho
NK107(tse)001:1301: 'phrul 'di lta bu bstan pa tsam dang yang mi
NK107(tse)001:1302: 'dra bar gser gyi snying po nyi ma rab tu
NK107(tse)001:1303: snang byed 'di tshul lam thabs ji lta bu zhe
NK107(tse)001:1304: na gzugs su bkod pa sus kyang tshig tu barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1305: pa med par 'di'i dus na sa chu me rlung
NK107(tse)001:1306: med pa'i nam mkha' la gang gis kyang mi 'byed
NK107(tse)001:1307: par mdun gyi bar snang las 'di dang bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:1308: dngos kyi byin brlabs las tshig rnams kun gyi thog
NK107(tse)001:1309: mar yang dag pa'i chos nyid kyi rang sgrar byung
NK107(tse)001:1310: ba ni dgu gnyis ni bco brgyad de ri rab
NK107(tse)001:1311: kyi khang bu'i brtsegs pa'i bar gyi nam mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:1312: zer bas te mas bsgrangs pa'i khang bu dang po
NK107(tse)001:1313: gnod sbyin gyi khang bu'i steng na sna tshogs dung
NK107(tse)001:1314: phyur gyi nam mkha' dpag tshad stong ngo de'i steng
NK107(tse)001:1315: na lto 'phye'i khang bu'i steng na legs bkod 'phrul
NK107(tse)001:1316: gyi nam mkha' dpag tshad nyis stong gsum pa mi'am
NK107(tse)001:1317: ci'i khang bu'i steng na yid 'ong rdul bral gyi
NK107(tse)001:1318: nam mkha' bzhi stong bzhi pa kun dge'i khang bu'i
NK107(tse)001:1319: steng na yongs su mnyam ldan gyi nam mkha' dpag
NK107(tse)001:1320: tshad stong phrag brgyad yod lnga pa sa bsrung gi
NK107(tse)001:1321: khang pa'i steng na bsgyur byed gar mkhan gyi nam
NK107(tse)001:1322: mkha' dpag tshad stong phrag bcu drug yod do drug
NK107(tse)001:1323: pa rnam ldan gyi khang bu'i steng na pad ma
NK107(tse)001:1324: yongs dag'i nam mkha' dpag tshad stong phrag sum cu
NK107(tse)001:1325: rtsa gnyis yod bdun pa gza' brgyad kyi khang bu'i
NK107(tse)001:1326: steng na sprin spungs pa rnam par 'thor ba'i nam
NK107(tse)001:1327: mkha' dpag tshad stong phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi yod
NK107(tse)001:1328: do brgyad pa lha min grags ldan gyis khang bu'i
NK107(tse)001:1329: steng na rtsub 'gyur gyi nam mkha' dpag tshad 'bum
NK107(tse)001:1330: phrag gcig dang stong phrag nyer brgyad yod dgu pa
NK107(tse)001:1331: yul 'khor srung gi khang pa'i steng na rang ga
NK107(tse)001:1332: dag pa'i nam mkha' dpag tshad 'bum phrag gnyis dang
NK107(tse)001:1333: stong phrag lnga dang gnyis yod bcu pa 'phags skyes
NK107(tse)001:1334: po'i khang bu'i steng na yid kyi g.yo bral gyi
NK107(tse)001:1335: nam mkha' dpag tshad 'bum phrag bzhi dang stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:1336: bzhi yod bcu gcig pa spyan mi bzang gi khang
NK107(tse)001:1337: pa'i steng na ngad pa dang ldan pa zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:1338: ba'i nam mkha' dpag tshad 'bum phrag brgyad khri phrag
NK107(tse)001:1339: gnyis stong phrag brgyad yod bcu gnyis pa rnam thos
NK107(tse)001:1340: sras kyi khang bu'i steng na yangs pa can gyi
NK107(tse)001:1341: nam mkha' bye ba gcig dang 'bum phrag gnyis dang
NK107(tse)001:1342: khri phrag lnga dang stong phrag gnyis yod bcu gsum
NK107(tse)001:1343: pa sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i khang bu'i steng na
NK107(tse)001:1344: gdul ba 'gyur bar byed pa'i nam mkha' dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:1345: bye ba gnyis dang 'bum phrag gsum dang stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:1346: bzhi yod bcu bzhi pa dga' ldan gyi khang bu'i
NK107(tse)001:1347: steng na 'jug pa sangs pa'i nam mkha' dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:1348: bye ba bzhi dang 'bum phrag drug dang stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:1349: brgyad yod do bco lnga pa 'phrul dag'i khung bu'i
NK107(tse)001:1350: steng nah bzod ldan gyi nam mkha' bye ba phrag
NK107(tse)001:1351: dgu dang 'bum phrag gnyis dang khri phrag gcig dang
NK107(tse)001:1352: stong phrag gnyis yod do bcu drug pa gzhan 'phrul
NK107(tse)001:1353: dbang byed kyi khang bu'i steng na srog gi snying
NK107(tse)001:1354: po'i zhes pa'i nam mkha' dpag tshad gcig dang sa
NK107(tse)001:1355: ya gcig dang bye ba brgyad dang 'bum phrag bzhi
NK107(tse)001:1356: dang khri phrag gnyis dang stong phrag bzhi yod do
NK107(tse)001:1357: bcu bdun pa rab mtsho snang ma'i khang bu'i steng
NK107(tse)001:1358: na spos kyi dri ltos pa'i nam mkha' sa ya
NK107(tse)001:1359: gsum dang bye ba gnyis 'bum phrag brgyad dang khri
NK107(tse)001:1360: phrag bzhi yod de'i steng bco brgyad pa na 'dod
NK107(tse)001:1361: pa na gzugs rnam par 'byed pa'i rol mo rtse
NK107(tse)001:1362: zhes bya ba'i khang bu'i steng na bkod pa yongs
NK107(tse)001:1363: su grol ba zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:1364: sa ya drug dang bye ba lnga dang 'bum phrag
NK107(tse)001:1365: gnyis dang khri phrag brgyad dang stong phrag gnyis yod
NK107(tse)001:1366: do bzhi'i yang stengs nas zhes bya ba ni shar
NK107(tse)001:1367: phyogs na dga' ba'i rol mo'i tshal dang lho na
NK107(tse)001:1368: rtse ba'i rol mo'i zhing dang nub na bde ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1369: dang byang na rab tu yid 'phros pa zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:1370: ba'i zhing dang bzhi'i yang stengs na bkod pa mi
NK107(tse)001:1371: g.yo ba mtho dman snyam pa'i khang pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:1372: che'i char ka rab tu 'od 'bar ba zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:1373: ba na lha tshangs pa chen po 'khor lha'i bu
NK107(tse)001:1374: sems rab tu mi g.yo ba khrag khrig dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:1375: med pa dang lha'i bu mo 'dod pa dang bral
NK107(tse)001:1376: zhing bzod pa thob pa nya nyer gyi grangs dang
NK107(tse)001:1377: mnyam pa dang sna tshogs rang bzhin gyi gzugs mi
NK107(tse)001:1378: phyed pa grangs med pa'i tshogs dpag tu med pas
NK107(tse)001:1379: yongs su bskor zhingh mdun du bltas pa'i dbus na
NK107(tse)001:1380: tshangs pa chen po'i rgyal po zhal grangs med pa
NK107(tse)001:1381: nas sgra dbyangs kyi tshig 'byung ngo phyag dang zhabs
NK107(tse)001:1382: ri rab kyi rdul dang mnyam pas sprul pa barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1383: du med pa'i 'gyed pa gcig gnas te gong ma'i
NK107(tse)001:1384: de rnams la khang bu'i dbyibs dang kha dog dang
NK107(tse)001:1385: tshad dang yon tan dang 'khor 'di tsam la longs
NK107(tse)001:1386: spyod pa dang tshe tshad la sogs pa yod de
NK107(tse)001:1387: 'dir ma spros so de lta bu'i gnas tshangs pa
NK107(tse)001:1388: chen po'i gnas der yang dag par rdzogs pa'i b+hud
NK107(tse)001:1389: tha yis tshangs pa'i bu pho gdong lnga pa zur
NK107(tse)001:1390: phud brgyad kyis rnam par spras pa ba spu nyag
NK107(tse)001:1391: ma re las sprul pa'i lha'i bu dang bu mo
NK107(tse)001:1392: dgu khri dang dgu stong 'gyed pa zhal nas tshangs
NK107(tse)001:1393: dbyangs sna tshogs par bsgrogs pa dag sprul nas sde
NK107(tse)001:1394: snod thams cad kyi rtsa ba sgra thal 'gyur chen
NK107(tse)001:1395: po'i rgyud 'di lha tshangs pa chen po'i dbyangs 'phrul
NK107(tse)001:1396: byed 'bum phrag brgyad las nges 'byed du grangs su
NK107(tse)001:1397: nges barjoda pa'i sgra drag pa las gzugs brnyan mngon
NK107(tse)001:1398: par snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dpag tu med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1399: ngang las gsungs pas tshangs pa'i 'khor dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:1400: pa'i kha nas kyang tshig 'di dag rang byung du
NK107(tse)001:1401: byung bas tshangs pa'i 'jig rten rnams dus gcig la
NK107(tse)001:1402: b+hud tha ste 'khor ba nyid mi snang bar byas
NK107(tse)001:1403: so de nas yang khang bu brtsegs pa'i bar gyi
NK107(tse)001:1404: nam mkha' la chos nyid kyi rang sgrar 'di dag
NK107(tse)001:1405: tshig rang byung du byung bas gong nas khang bu
NK107(tse)001:1406: brtsegs pa'i nang na 'dug pa'i gzugs can rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:1407: kyang sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu gcig char du thob
NK107(tse)001:1408: ste 'khor ba dong sprugs so de nas ri rab
NK107(tse)001:1409: kyi khong seng du lha khyab 'jug chen po zhes
NK107(tse)001:1410: bya ba 'khor dpag tu med pas yongs su bskor
NK107(tse)001:1411: ba las babs te sangs rgyas kyi gsung gis 'di
NK107(tse)001:1412: ni byin gyis brlabs kyis rang sgrar ston pas gsungs
NK107(tse)001:1413: pas khyab 'jug chen po 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab
NK107(tse)001:1414: pa dang bcas pas kyang 'di nyid tshig tu barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1415: pas de dag 'khor dang bcas pa la sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1416: kyi 'bras bu gcig char du thob nas de nyid
NK107(tse)001:1417: stongs par byas so de nas 'jig rten mi 'byed
NK107(tse)001:1418: ces bya ba'i nam mkha' phyogs dang bral ba de
NK107(tse)001:1419: la ka la ping ka'i zhes bya ba'i khang pa
NK107(tse)001:1420: gzhal du med pa'i 'bum phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:1421: yod par babs te sgra dbyangs rab tu mdun cing
NK107(tse)001:1422: dad pa rab tu spro ba zhes bya ba'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:1423: las drangs te bstan pas ka la ping ka'i rgyal
NK107(tse)001:1424: po 'khor dang bcas pa yang sangs rgyas kyi 'bras
NK107(tse)001:1425: bu cig char du thob nas de nyid stongs par
NK107(tse)001:1426: byas so de yang gang las byung na sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1427: dngos kyi bstan pa kun gyi bcud rin po che
NK107(tse)001:1428: 'byung bar byed pa sgras thal 'gyur gyi rgyud 'dir
NK107(tse)001:1429: 'dus pa'i gnad ni rgyud kyi rgyal po yin pas
NK107(tse)001:1430: 'khor ba dong sprugs chen zhes bya la 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:1431: ni sde snod thams cad kyi rtsa bar 'dug pas
NK107(tse)001:1432: dpal 'khor ba 'byin pa'i rgyud ces kyang bya la
NK107(tse)001:1433: tshig rnams kun gyi gzhi yin pas stong pa kun
NK107(tse)001:1434: 'byung bar byed pa'i rgyud ces bya'o dam chos kun
NK107(tse)001:1435: gyi thog mar yad dag pa tshul cig tsam du
NK107(tse)001:1436: ji ltar byung zhe na gong ma rnams ni barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1437: du med pa'i rang sgra zhes bya'o da ni gsum
NK107(tse)001:1438: pa barjoda pa'i tshig tsam du gtan la phab nas
NK107(tse)001:1439: rdzus nas skyes pa'i 'gro ba rnams la gsungs pa
NK107(tse)001:1440: ni de yang 'dul byed sku las 'phros pa'i gsung
NK107(tse)001:1441: brgya phrag gcig gsal byed gsung las 'phros pa'i gsung
NK107(tse)001:1442: brgya phrag gcig gnas byed thugs las 'phros pa'i gsung
NK107(tse)001:1443: tshig brgya phrag gcig sde sum rgya dang 'phrin las
NK107(tse)001:1444: 'dul stangs kyi tshig sum cu yon tan rdzogs tshul
NK107(tse)001:1445: gyi tshig sum cu ste drug cu'i sgra la drangs
NK107(tse)001:1446: te ston pas gsungs pas lha'i bu nyi ma rab
NK107(tse)001:1447: tu snang byed la sogs pa'i bardzusa nas skyes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1448: 'gro ba bye ba khrag khrig rnams kyi khong nas
NK107(tse)001:1449: kyang rang bzhin du byung bas de dag gis kyang
NK107(tse)001:1450: barjoda pa tshig tsam gyi don khong du chud nas
NK107(tse)001:1451: de nyid rang du sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob
NK107(tse)001:1452: bo de nas yang sgo nga las skyes pa'i 'gro
NK107(tse)001:1453: ba rnams kyi gnas su babs te 'byung ba sa
NK107(tse)001:1454: sgra'i chos nyid dang chu'i dang me'i dang rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:1455: sgra'i chos nyid phyi rol du btags pa yis sems
NK107(tse)001:1456: can so so'i sgra thabs dang shes rab kyi rtsal
NK107(tse)001:1457: phyir shar ba las sems can so so'i lus la
NK107(tse)001:1458: sgra'i byed pa'i rgyu 'byung ba tsha ba grang ba
NK107(tse)001:1459: gnyis las byed rgyu nang 'gyur ba las sems can
NK107(tse)001:1460: so so'i lus la sgra stong phrag brgyad la dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:1461: stong phrag brgyad du bsgyur bas chos nyid kyi nyon
NK107(tse)001:1462: mongs pa mi 'dra ba stong phrag brgyad nyid zhag
NK107(tse)001:1463: phrug cig la 'byung bar nges te de'i dus mkhas
NK107(tse)001:1464: pas bzung bas dus thams cad du chos nyid dang
NK107(tse)001:1465: 'bral ba med par 'gyur ro de yang phyi rol
NK107(tse)001:1466: 'byung rtags kyi sgra la stong phrag bzhi yod do
NK107(tse)001:1467: sa'i sgra la 'byongs na skad cig la chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:1468: kyi rang sgra mi 'dra ba stong phrag gcig shes
NK107(tse)001:1469: la de yang gnas pa'i chos nyid kyi sgra'o de
NK107(tse)001:1470: bzhin du chu la 'jug pa'i chos nyid kyi sgra
NK107(tse)001:1471: me la 'joms pa'i chos nyid kyi sgra rlung las
NK107(tse)001:1472: 'byongs pas 'byed pa'i chos nyid kyi sgra stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:1473: gcig skad cig la shes so de rnams shes pa
NK107(tse)001:1474: las dgos pa ci yod na 'khrul pa'i 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:1475: rgyun 'chad pa'i dgos pa yod do nang bslab bya
NK107(tse)001:1476: las byung ba'i chos nyid kyi sgra la stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:1477: bzhi yod pa las rtsa ba'i chos nyid la goms
NK107(tse)001:1478: pas stong phrag gcig skad cig la shes te de
NK107(tse)001:1479: ni gsal ba'i chos nyid kyi sgra thig le bde
NK107(tse)001:1480: ba'i chos nyid rlung gis stong pa'i mi rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:1481: rang shugs kyi chos nyid la goms pas zung 'jug
NK107(tse)001:1482: gi chos nyid kyi sgra don stong phrag gcig shes
NK107(tse)001:1483: so de rnams shes pas dbyings dang rig pa'i 'gyus
NK107(tse)001:1484: chad zin par nges de dag ston pa'i byin gyis
NK107(tse)001:1485: brlabs par snang sgong skyes kyi dus kyi sems can
NK107(tse)001:1486: lha'i bu mchog dga' tsug phud la sogs pa sgong
NK107(tse)001:1487: skyes kyi 'gro ba dag gis kyang dbyangs tshig tu
NK107(tse)001:1488: barjoda pa tsam gyis kyang b+hud ta'i 'bras bu thob
NK107(tse)001:1489: nas sgo nga las skyes pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:1490: skye gnas lan gcig rgyun chad do de'i phyir na
NK107(tse)001:1491: khams gsum yongs su bsgrol ba'i rgyud bla na med
NK107(tse)001:1492: pa zhes bya'o theg pa spyi'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK107(tse)001:1493: dpag tu med pa gsungs kyang 'bras bu gcig char
NK107(tse)001:1494: du grol ba 'di rab tu zab pas na khyad
NK107(tse)001:1495: par byed pa ni sgra'i rgyu'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs
NK107(tse)001:1496: pa las yang drod gsher las skyes pa'i 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:1497: rnams la sgra dang tshig rnams kyi chos nyid las
NK107(tse)001:1498: 'byung ba'i gzhi zhes bya ba'i tshig byas pa med
NK107(tse)001:1499: par 'phros te sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi yan lag
NK107(tse)001:1500: skus 'dul ba la nyi shu ste lhang nge ba
NK107(tse)001:1501: dang lhan ne ba dang lham me ba dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1502: tu grang ba dang mi g.yo ba dang mdun dang
NK107(tse)001:1503: rgyab med pa dang kun tu thal le ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1504: steng 'og tu med pa dang 'dzum pa dang gzhad
NK107(tse)001:1505: pa dang rab tu gzhad pa dang rab tu cher
NK107(tse)001:1506: gzhad pa dang 'ging ba dang 'ging chen dang bsgyings
NK107(tse)001:1507: pa dang bskyil ba dang rab tu 'khyil ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1508: gsal ba dang 'jam pa dang 'phro ba'i gzugs rnams
NK107(tse)001:1509: kyis 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du snang bar
NK107(tse)001:1510: byas so de dag ni sku'i bstan pa la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:1511: pa'o yang gsung gis 'dul ba'i yan lag nyi shu
NK107(tse)001:1512: ni khrag khrog dang 'tshag 'tshog dang chem chem dang
NK107(tse)001:1513: mar mer dang yam yom dang 'ar 'ur dang thag
NK107(tse)001:1514: thug dang rtag rtog dang gya gyu dang sang seng
NK107(tse)001:1515: de nyi shu ni 'gro ba rnams la snang bar
NK107(tse)001:1516: byas pa ni gsung gi bstan pa la dgongs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:1517: thugs kyis 'dul ba'i gsung ni g.yo ba dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1518: tu g.yo ba dang 'gul ba dang rab tu 'gul
NK107(tse)001:1519: ba dang 'phrig pa dang rab tu 'phrig pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1520: 'dar ba dang rab tu 'dar ba dang yir ba
NK107(tse)001:1521: dang rab tu yir ba dang mnyam pa dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1522: tu mnyam pa dang ring ba dang rab tu ring
NK107(tse)001:1523: ba dang khyab pa dang rab tu khyab pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1524: gnas pa dang rab tu gnas pa dang sang nge
NK107(tse)001:1525: ba dang sal le ba ste nyi shus 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:1526: gyi khams thams cad du snang bar byas so de
NK107(tse)001:1527: ltar drug cur ston pa yang phyi nang gi snang
NK107(tse)001:1528: ba 'dus pa'i 'khor drod las skyes pa rnams la
NK107(tse)001:1529: gsungs so de nyid gsungs pa tsam gyis 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:1530: de dag gis sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob nas
NK107(tse)001:1531: lan cig rgyun chad do de'i phyir na dpal 'gro
NK107(tse)001:1532: ba rnam dag zad par byed pa'i rgyud ces kyang
NK107(tse)001:1533: bya'o 'o na mngal nas skyes pa'i 'gro ba ma
NK107(tse)001:1534: 'ongs pa de yang dgos pa rang ci yod ce
NK107(tse)001:1535: na sangs rgyas kyi chos gcig ma gsungs na ma
NK107(tse)001:1536: gsungs gsungs pa'i tshul ni dgongs pa rnam pa gsum
NK107(tse)001:1537: yin te 'gro ba rnams nyon mongs pa rags su
NK107(tse)001:1538: song ba las gnyen po la dgongs pa ste bka'
NK107(tse)001:1539: stsal pa ni gdul bya gang zag gcig gis rgyud
NK107(tse)001:1540: la gdul gzhi nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK107(tse)001:1541: gnas te de yang 'dod chags las gyur pa'i rtog
NK107(tse)001:1542: pa mi 'dra ba nyi khri dang chig stongah de
NK107(tse)001:1543: bzhin du gti mug las dang zhe sdang las dang
NK107(tse)001:1544: dug gsum cha mnyam zhing 'dres pa las gyur pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1545: rtog pa mi 'dra ba nyi khri dang chig stong
NK107(tse)001:1546: 'gyus pa'i gnyen por 'dul ba las gyur pa'i chos
NK107(tse)001:1547: kyi rnam grangs mi 'dra ba nyi khri dang chig
NK107(tse)001:1548: stong dang de bzhin du mdo sde dang mngon pa
NK107(tse)001:1549: dang sde snod rin po che gsum cha mnyam pa
NK107(tse)001:1550: las gyur pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs bzhi khri dang
NK107(tse)001:1551: chig stong du gsungs pa ni tsha ba'i nad la
NK107(tse)001:1552: ga bur ltar gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:1553: de las yang bsdus te nges par gtan la phab
NK107(tse)001:1554: pa ni dbang po'i don du dgongs te bka' stsal
NK107(tse)001:1555: pa ste spyir 'gro ba tha dad kyang dbang po
NK107(tse)001:1556: che long la dgongs pa ni 'jig rten gyi blo
NK107(tse)001:1557: can dang 'das pa'i blo can gnyis las mi 'da'
NK107(tse)001:1558: de la dgongs pas 'jig rten gyi theg pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1559: 'das pa'i theg pa'o de la zhib rtsegs su dgongs
NK107(tse)001:1560: pa ni 'jig rten pa la 'jig rten sor bzhag
NK107(tse)001:1561: gi theg pa lha dang mir lung du ma bstan
NK107(tse)001:1562: pa la phyin ci log gi theg pa mu stegs
NK107(tse)001:1563: rtag chad gnyis so de dag kyang theg par cis
NK107(tse)001:1564: grol zhe na lha dang mi la brten nas gnyis
NK107(tse)001:1565: kar du 'gro zhing dong bas na theg pa'o mu
NK107(tse)001:1566: stegs pas kyang kho rang gi ma ltos pas kho
NK107(tse)001:1567: rang rang gi sar 'gro zhing dong pas na theg
NK107(tse)001:1568: pa'o 'jig rten las 'das pa la gnyis te rgyu
NK107(tse)001:1569: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu gsang sngags
NK107(tse)001:1570: kyi theg pa'o de yang dbang po che long du
NK107(tse)001:1571: gang zag rgyud la yid ches byed pa dang 'bras
NK107(tse)001:1572: bu la yid ches byed pa'i blo rim pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:1573: la dgongs pa'o rgyu la gsum ste nyan thos dang
NK107(tse)001:1574: rang rgyal dang byang chub sems dapa'i theg pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1575: gsum ni dbang po tha ma gsum gyi dbang du
NK107(tse)001:1576: byas pa'o 'di dag gi bye brag dang lha'i khyad
NK107(tse)001:1577: par la sogs pa ni 'dir mi spro'o sngags la
NK107(tse)001:1578: gnyis te phyi pa thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa
NK107(tse)001:1579: dang nang pa thabs kyi theg pa'i gzhung ni gang
NK107(tse)001:1580: zag rtogs pa che chung gnyis kyi dbang du byas
NK107(tse)001:1581: pa'o de yang phyi pa la kri ya u pa
NK107(tse)001:1582: ya yo ga'i theg pa dang gsum ni dbang po
NK107(tse)001:1583: 'bring po gsum la dgongs pa'o nang pa ma h+aa
NK107(tse)001:1584: a nu a ti yo ga'i theg pa gsum ni
NK107(tse)001:1585: dbang po rab gsum la dgongs pa'o de dag ni
NK107(tse)001:1586: dbang po'i don du gsungs pa ste skas kyi rim
NK107(tse)001:1587: pa lta bur gsungs pa'o de las kyang rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:1588: chen po a ti yo ga la sde ni gsum
NK107(tse)001:1589: klong ni dgu sh+loo ka ni 'bum phrag drug cu
NK107(tse)001:1590: rtsa bzhi bam po ni nyi khri dang chig stong
NK107(tse)001:1591: le'u ni stong phrag sum cu rtsa lnga barjoda bya'i
NK107(tse)001:1592: nam makha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rnam grangs ni rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1593: par gzhan du bstan no de dag las kyang bsdu
NK107(tse)001:1594: na bsdus dang zhes pa bsdu ba la dgongs te
NK107(tse)001:1595: bka' stsal ba ni chos thams cad kyang sde snod
NK107(tse)001:1596: rin po che gsum du 'dus de gsum yang bka'
NK107(tse)001:1597: dang bstan chos gnyis su 'dus de gnyis kyang rig
NK107(tse)001:1598: par 'dus pas na bsdu ba zhes bya ste rig
NK107(tse)001:1599: pa nyid kyang rdo rjee lu gu rgyud chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:1600: mngon sum dang 'bral ba med par gnas so de
NK107(tse)001:1601: ru 'dus pa'i gnad kyi gang zag brtson 'grus kyi
NK107(tse)001:1602: khyad kyis rab zag bcas mi snang bar 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:1603: la b+hud tha ba dang 'bring chos nyid kyi bar
NK107(tse)001:1604: do la b+hud tha ba dang tha ma yang mngal
NK107(tse)001:1605: du mi rgyu bar rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams
NK107(tse)001:1606: su bardzusa te skyes nas de nas dbugs phyung nas
NK107(tse)001:1607: sangs rgya'o de'i phyir na gsang chen nges pa'i bka'
NK107(tse)001:1608: 'di'i sgor zhugs pa tsam gyis khams gsum du mi
NK107(tse)001:1609: 'jug pa'o de ltar skye ba bzhis bsdus pa'i sems
NK107(tse)001:1610: can la tshig rnams bsdus te snang bar byas pas
NK107(tse)001:1611: ni lan cig 'gro ba rnams kyi skye gnas rgyun
NK107(tse)001:1612: chad do de gsum ma yin pa'i barjoda bya'i tshig
NK107(tse)001:1613: ni dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas 'das pa
NK107(tse)001:1614: dang ma byon pa dang da ltar byon pas gsungs
NK107(tse)001:1615: pa med do da ni bzhi pa gong ma'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:1616: tshig rnams kyi bsdu ba dang dbye bas nges par
NK107(tse)001:1617: rtogs par bstan pa ni barjoda pa'i gzhi sgra yin
NK107(tse)001:1618: pas sgra'i gnas gzhan gyi bye brag shes na sde
NK107(tse)001:1619: snod kyi chos la thogs pa med par shes so
NK107(tse)001:1620: barjoda pa'i sgra tshig yin pas tshig gi mtha' chod
NK107(tse)001:1621: na rang sems nyid dang dbyer mi phyed do barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1622: pa'i 'jug pa ming yin par ming gi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:1623: rnams shes na 'das pa dang 'das pa ma yin
NK107(tse)001:1624: pa'i srog la dbang thob ba'o de ltar gsum du
NK107(tse)001:1625: nges par bsdus pa las gong ma'i sgra'i gnas gzhan
NK107(tse)001:1626: rnams las nges par bsdus pa ni de la tshangs
NK107(tse)001:1627: pa chen po'i sgra'i rnam par rol pa dbyangs kyi
NK107(tse)001:1628: 'jug pa las dang bcas pa ni tshangs pa'i zhes
NK107(tse)001:1629: pa 'jig rten gyi lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1630: bye brag dpag tu med pa'i dbang po dang bsam
NK107(tse)001:1631: pa la sogs pa mkhyen pas 'gro ba rnams 'dul
NK107(tse)001:1632: ba la dgongs nas ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK107(tse)001:1633: 'das nyid kyang de nyid du sprul nas 'gro ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1634: rgyud tshangs pa'i gnas nas phyin ci ma log par
NK107(tse)001:1635: bstan pa ni gsungs dbyangs gcig la ma go ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1636: bye brag ni lus kyi brtsal sprugs pa'i dbyangs brgya
NK107(tse)001:1637: tham pas mos pa'i lus kyi gdung bas spu zing
NK107(tse)001:1638: du 'gyur ba dang ngag gi dang ba 'dren pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1639: dbyangs brgyas mos pa'i ngag dang zhing 'jam par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:1640: la sems kyi gdung ba brgya yis mos pa'i kun
NK107(tse)001:1641: slong du 'gyur ba dang dbang po nyams gsal byed
NK107(tse)001:1642: kyi dbyangs brgyas mos pa'i dbang po lnga phyin ci
NK107(tse)001:1643: ma log par 'gyur ba dang shes pa rang 'thad
NK107(tse)001:1644: par byed pa'i dbyangs brgyas mos pa'i shes pa bag
NK107(tse)001:1645: yangs su 'gyur ba dang snang ba lus kyi dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:1646: brgyas mos pa'i snang rkyen chos nyid kyi ngang du
NK107(tse)001:1647: grol bar 'gyur ba dang rig pa gnad la bor
NK107(tse)001:1648: ba'i dbyangs brgyas / mos pa'i rig pa rang thog
NK107(tse)001:1649: na gsal bar 'gyur ba dang rlung ar gtad pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1650: dbyangs brgyas mos pa'i 'gyu ba rnams rang sar dag
NK107(tse)001:1651: par 'gyur ro tshogs drug rang yan gyi dbyangs brgyas
NK107(tse)001:1652: mos pa'i lus sems kyi na brtar tshud pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1653: mjug pa gsol 'debs kyi dbyangs brgyas mos pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:1654: ngag yid zhen pa dang bral bar gyur to de
NK107(tse)001:1655: ltar stong dang de bzhin gshegs pa dang rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:1656: dang rin po che dang pad+ma dang las kyi rigs
NK107(tse)001:1657: kyi dbyangs lngas ni 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa lnga
NK107(tse)001:1658: rnam par dag pa la dgongs pa'o de dag las
NK107(tse)001:1659: bsdu na byin barlaba 'jug par byed pa'i dbyangs chos
NK107(tse)001:1660: nyid nges pa'i don gcod par byed pa ni so
NK107(tse)001:1661: dang mchu la ma brten pa brgyas nyams 'jug par
NK107(tse)001:1662: byed pa'oh lces ma bsgyur ba brgyas nyams brten par
NK107(tse)001:1663: byed la 'a dang ye la brten pa'i dbyangs brgyas
NK107(tse)001:1664: nyams spel bar byed pa'o de lta brgya ni tshangs
NK107(tse)001:1665: pa'i dbyangs ces las kyi len lugs zhes bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:1666: nas rab tu stengs pa pad+ma lta bu dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1667: tu sing ba rta sing lta bu dang rab tu
NK107(tse)001:1668: lcong ba grul bum lta bu dang gsum ni lus
NK107(tse)001:1669: ngag yid kyi bying rgod brdar sha gcod par byed
NK107(tse)001:1670: pa'o de las kyang bsdu na ring byed sum cur
NK107(tse)001:1671: nges par bsdu ba ni l+aa ring po nas drangs
NK107(tse)001:1672: pa'i 'gyur mi 'dra ba lnga y+ae ring po nas
NK107(tse)001:1673: drangs pa'i lnga +ae ring po la lnga sh+ae ring
NK107(tse)001:1674: la lnga n+ai ring po la lnga k+aa nas drangs
NK107(tse)001:1675: pa'i 'gyur mi 'dra ba lnga ste sum cu ni
NK107(tse)001:1676: 'di dag rab tu dben pa'i sa phyogs su phyin
NK107(tse)001:1677: nas rang la rang gis bskul nas nang du ye
NK107(tse)001:1678: shes thol byung du skye ba dang phyi snang ba
NK107(tse)001:1679: ban bun du 'gyur bar nges so de las kyang
NK107(tse)001:1680: bsdu na gsal byed ni ka li dang sbyar zhing
NK107(tse)001:1681: tshig rab tu gsal ba ngag 'phra zhing 'jam pa
NK107(tse)001:1682: la bzhi a li la bzhi a b+hi zhig la
NK107(tse)001:1683: bzhi h'u b+ha zhig dang sbyar zhing tshig rab tu
NK107(tse)001:1684: gsal ba la bzhi ste bcu drug ni dam tshig
NK107(tse)001:1685: skong bar byed pa'o de yang sngon 'byung dang rjes
NK107(tse)001:1686: 'jug gi bre brag gis nges par 'bras bu thob
NK107(tse)001:1687: boh de nas de bzhin nam mkha' nas ka chos
NK107(tse)001:1688: nyid la rtogs pa seng nyams len ka'i brtson 'grus
NK107(tse)001:1689: sgra dus thams cad du chos nyid las mi 'da'
NK107(tse)001:1690: ba de rnams yang dag pa rnal 'byor pa la
NK107(tse)001:1691: rdzogs pas chos nyid rang sgra dang dbyer mi phyed
NK107(tse)001:1692: par 'gyur ro de yang 'dren pa ni skad dang
NK107(tse)001:1693: rlung 'jug pa ni tshig dang shes pa dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1694: tu 'dres pa bsnyen pa ni chung zhing gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:1695: dang phra zhing ring ba dang 'jam zhing gdang ba
NK107(tse)001:1696: dag go gsal byed ni tshig dang skad du 'byor
NK107(tse)001:1697: pa'o sgra ni ha dang he dang he rnams so
NK107(tse)001:1698: don ni dbyings dang rig par ldan pas bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:1699: yang dang po si si nas drangs pas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:1700: gtad sa 'jug gnyis pa ha ha nas drangs pas
NK107(tse)001:1701: nyams btsan thabs su skye gsum pa hi hi nas
NK107(tse)001:1702: drangs pas bde ba rang lugs su 'char bzhi pa
NK107(tse)001:1703: he he nas drangs pas dga' bde mchog gi sa
NK107(tse)001:1704: la rol lnga pa ho ho nas drangs pas gzhi
NK107(tse)001:1705: rang lugs su mthong drug pa h+aum h+aum nas drangs
NK107(tse)001:1706: pas rtogs pa rgyud la 'char bdun pa i +ai
NK107(tse)001:1707: nas drangs pa'i rig pa'i lam mthong brgyad pa la
NK107(tse)001:1708: l+ai nas drangs pas rig pa gzhi las 'phos dgu
NK107(tse)001:1709: pa la de nas drangs pas lha'i bsam bya rnyed
NK107(tse)001:1710: bcu pa la nas drangs pa'i phyi nyams nang du
NK107(tse)001:1711: gsal bcu gcig pa ram nas drangs pa'i 'gyu ba
NK107(tse)001:1712: rgyun 'chad bcu gnyis pa zla 'od nas drangs pas
NK107(tse)001:1713: chos nyid kyi mthong ba dag pa rgyud la skyes
NK107(tse)001:1714: so de yang bsdu na barjoda pa tshig gi gzhi
NK107(tse)001:1715: ma yin pa ni sgra dang dam bca' dang gtan
NK107(tse)001:1716: tshigs dang chos can dang bsgrub bya la ma rmongs
NK107(tse)001:1717: par bsdus pa'o de yang ston pa'i gsung las nges
NK107(tse)001:1718: par bsdus na 'di dag ni dbyangs las gzhan du
NK107(tse)001:1719: 'gyur ba'i sgra'i bye brag gis chos nyid kyi don
NK107(tse)001:1720: gtan la 'bebs pa'o de yang sems can gyis rnam
NK107(tse)001:1721: par rtog pa sangs par byed pa'i yan lag tu
NK107(tse)001:1722: phyi rol 'byung ba'i sgra la lnga nang rig bcas
NK107(tse)001:1723: kyi sgra la lnga gsang ba chos nyid kyi rang
NK107(tse)001:1724: sgra la lnga thabs kyis bskul ba dang shes rab
NK107(tse)001:1725: kyis bskul ba gnyis te sum cu rtsa gnyis so
NK107(tse)001:1726: 'byung ba sa la sa'i sgra sdig pa dang sa'i
NK107(tse)001:1727: chu'i bsing ba dang sa'i me'i bsil ba dang sa'i
NK107(tse)001:1728: rlung gi rdul phran dang phyi'i sgra khyab par byed
NK107(tse)001:1729: cing bskyed pa'o de bzhin du chu la yang lnga
NK107(tse)001:1730: ste chu'i sa bshang pa dang chu'i chu sh+ao ba
NK107(tse)001:1731: dang chu'i me sir ba dang chu'i rlung bslab pa
NK107(tse)001:1732: dang spyi myur ba'o me'i me 'tsheg pa dang me'i
NK107(tse)001:1733: sa 'phrig pa dang chu sbar ba dang rlung 'dreg
NK107(tse)001:1734: pa dang spyi 'gyur ba'o rlung ni lding ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1735: de'i sa 'ur ba dang chu sh+ao ba dang me
NK107(tse)001:1736: ldig ba dang spyi 'tshub pa'o nang rig bcas ni
NK107(tse)001:1737: rigs drug so so'i la lha dang mi gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:1738: byas pa'o gsang ba chos nyid ni rlung rten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1739: rang sgra chos kyi rang sgra 'ur ba na de
NK107(tse)001:1740: la 'phyongs pas rlung tshad zin la rtsa ba brten
NK107(tse)001:1741: pas 'tshig cing rgal ba ste de la 'byongs pas
NK107(tse)001:1742: 'chi ba'i ltos zad thig le la brten pa 'phra
NK107(tse)001:1743: zhing bde ba ste de la 'byongs pas 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1744: rtsa ba chod lus bcud sa la brten pa 'phra
NK107(tse)001:1745: zhing 'gum pa ste de la 'byongs pas zas gos
NK107(tse)001:1746: dang bral dbang bo'i gnad la brten pa gsal zhing
NK107(tse)001:1747: byer ba ste de 'byongs pas mngon par shes pa
NK107(tse)001:1748: drug 'char ro thabs kyis bskul ba ni lag gi
NK107(tse)001:1749: 'du byed dang lus kyi gnad gzir ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:1750: dag las so so'i sgra byung bas bde ba rang
NK107(tse)001:1751: lugs su byung shes rab ni shes pa dang shes
NK107(tse)001:1752: bya la brten nas stong pa dang stong pa chen
NK107(tse)001:1753: po'i nyams 'byung ngo de rnams las spros pas so
NK107(tse)001:1754: so'i byed pa'i yan lag sgra'i dbyings la gnas srung
NK107(tse)001:1755: dang ring byed la sogs la sogs pa bcu gzhan
NK107(tse)001:1756: sel la ka ri dang su ri la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:1757: bcu sgrub byed la bskyob pa dang 'phen byed la
NK107(tse)001:1758: sogs pa bcu phan pa'i rkyen can la mkha' gsal
NK107(tse)001:1759: dang po 'jug pa la sogs pa bcu ste bzhi
NK107(tse)001:1760: bcu de yang sgra'i gnas lus gzhan snang ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1761: gnyis su ma 'dus pa med do de yang khyad
NK107(tse)001:1762: par du bsdus nas rtog spyod sems kyi sgra'i rigs
NK107(tse)001:1763: 'gyur ba dang 'phen pa gzugs kyi sgra'i rigs bkod
NK107(tse)001:1764: pa'i rigs dang gnyis ni de yang 'gyur ba'i drangs
NK107(tse)001:1765: dang tshad zin na dus tshod dang rgyu rkyen la
NK107(tse)001:1766: mkhas la bkod pa'i mtshan nyid gtan la phebs na
NK107(tse)001:1767: bka' dang bstan chos rnams la ma bslab par mkhas
NK107(tse)001:1768: pa'o de dag ni sgra dang tshig ni gzhi mar
NK107(tse)001:1769: byung ba'o da ni lnga pa gtan pa'i sgra dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:1770: de dag gis dgongs pa bstan te de yang sgra
NK107(tse)001:1771: dbyangs de'i dgongs pa ci yin zhe na skad mi
NK107(tse)001:1772: mthun pa so so'i bye brag gi 'phrul gyis yang
NK107(tse)001:1773: sems can rnams kyi rig pa'i sgra'i bstan chos la
NK107(tse)001:1774: bslab na spyir rnam grangs mang po yod kyang bya
NK107(tse)001:1775: ba'i rim pa 'di ltar bslab bo bdag sa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:1776: yin na 'a nas sbyangs pas tshangs pa'i sgra'i phul
NK107(tse)001:1777: bdun la mkhas par 'gyur bdag chu'i lus yin na
NK107(tse)001:1778: 'u nas bslabs pas khyab 'jug gi sgra'i phul bdun
NK107(tse)001:1779: la mkhas par 'gyur me'i lus yin na 'e nas
NK107(tse)001:1780: bslabs pas ka la ping ka'i sgra'i phul bdun la
NK107(tse)001:1781: mkhas par 'gyur rlung gi lus yin na 'u nas
NK107(tse)001:1782: bslabs pas mkha' lding gi sgra'i phul bdun la mkhas
NK107(tse)001:1783: par 'gyur ro de dag ni rtsa ba'i sgra bcu
NK107(tse)001:1784: bzhi 'or gnyis su bsgrangs pa la nyer brgyad yod
NK107(tse)001:1785: de de dag re re la 'byongs pas bye brag
NK107(tse)001:1786: gi sgra don mang po la mkhas par 'byongs par
NK107(tse)001:1787: 'gyur ba ni bye brag 'og nas ston la bslab
NK107(tse)001:1788: thabs ni ri mo zhes pa 'khor lo cha bzhi
NK107(tse)001:1789: la le tshe nyer brgyad du byas pa las dbus
NK107(tse)001:1790: na cha chung ru bzhi bsil la 'a dang 'u
NK107(tse)001:1791: dang 'e dang 'u rnams bkod de 'a la brda'
NK107(tse)001:1792: dang k+sha dang spru dang lkan &&& dang b+hasha&a&a&a dang
NK107(tse)001:1793: m+mama&a&a&a dang de nas drug po de dag re re
NK107(tse)001:1794: la sbyangs pa'i tshig bshad phyed dang brgyad brgyad khyab
NK107(tse)001:1795: 'jug gi stong stong ka la ping ka'i phyed dang
NK107(tse)001:1796: gnyis stong mkha' lding gi 'bum phrag re la dbang
NK107(tse)001:1797: ngo yang 'u la sbru dang shamru&a&a&a dang salaru&a&a&a dang
NK107(tse)001:1798: neemya&a&a&a dang khegli&a&a&a dang skamru&a&a&a rnams la bslabs na yang
NK107(tse)001:1799: re res yang gong dang 'dra'o yang 'e la ig+ma&a&a&a
NK107(tse)001:1800: dang rgak+aa&a&a&a dang h+r+aina&a&a&a dang sbya dang ranyaye&a&a&a dang h+yi
NK107(tse)001:1801: zhes bya ba la re re la byas pas kyang
NK107(tse)001:1802: gong bzhin no yang 'u'o&a&a&ala b+hayu&a&a&ahdang hram dang yama&a&a&a dang
NK107(tse)001:1803: k+shum dang t+yi&a&a&adang rlung la bslabs pas kyang gong ltar
NK107(tse)001:1804: 'grub bo 'di dag rnams la mkhas par byas pa
NK107(tse)001:1805: yis chos kyi rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas rnams
NK107(tse)001:1806: la ma bslabs pas mkhas par 'gyur te spra sar
NK107(tse)001:1807: pa bsgrub pa'i gnad la yang 'di las lhag pa
NK107(tse)001:1808: med doh de nas tshig gi 'dres rnams la blo
NK107(tse)001:1809: sbyangs pas rang gi lus dang 'dra ba'i sprul pa
NK107(tse)001:1810: grangs med pa 'byin par byed pa dang 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:1811: na phyi rol du rtags su bkod pa'i sgra'i don
NK107(tse)001:1812: rnams de nyid la brten nas shes pa'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:1813: yod do da ni drug pa cho 'phrul las gzugs
NK107(tse)001:1814: brnyan gyi bstan pa dngos ji ltar byung ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:1815: pa ni gong du bstan pa de ltar b+hud tha'i
NK107(tse)001:1816: gsung gi cho 'phrul du gzugs brnyan gyi bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:1817: 'di la 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde grangs
NK107(tse)001:1818: mang po las khyad par du mar gyi nying khu
NK107(tse)001:1819: lta bu bka' rdzogs pa chen po de las kyang
NK107(tse)001:1820: khyad par du bsdus pa gsang chen nges pa'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:1821: bcu bdun de dag las kyang mchog tu zab pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1822: sgra thal 'gyur dam chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba
NK107(tse)001:1823: lta bu skyes bu'i snying dang 'dra ba 'di rgyud
NK107(tse)001:1824: rnams kun sangs rgyas kyis ma gsungs pa'i thog mar
NK107(tse)001:1825: yang dag pa'i rgyud 'di chos so cog gi rtsa
NK107(tse)001:1826: pa'i sgra mtshon re zhes bya ba las thig thal
NK107(tse)001:1827: 'gyur du byung ba las gdul bya skye ba bzhis
NK107(tse)001:1828: bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis las dang bag chags
NK107(tse)001:1829: sbyong bar byed pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po sgra thal
NK107(tse)001:1830: 'gyur las sde snod kyi chos rnams sems can gang
NK107(tse)001:1831: la gang mos su rgyud la sogs pa'i chos thams
NK107(tse)001:1832: cad nges par 'byung ba'i bstan pa thams cad dus
NK107(tse)001:1833: 'phros so de'i phyir na 'di nyid bstan pa thams
NK107(tse)001:1834: cad kyi dam pa chos thams cad 'di nyid la
NK107(tse)001:1835: 'du zhing thams cad du mched par byas pas b+hud
NK107(tse)001:1836: rda'i bstan pa mi yul du yun ring du gnas
NK107(tse)001:1837: par byed pa'i gnad do sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu
NK107(tse)001:1838: 'grub nges pas rgyud 'di nas 'byung ba bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:1839: byas na the tshom med do de'i phyir na sangs
NK107(tse)001:1840: rgyas kyi gsungs yang dag pa 'dis 'khor ba'i chos
NK107(tse)001:1841: nub par byed pa'o de lta bu la sogs te
NK107(tse)001:1842: rgyud 'di la yon tan ni bcangs pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:1843: skye ba 'og ma la b+hud tha ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:1844: bzhin du bris pa dang klog pa dang mnyan pa
NK107(tse)001:1845: dang bshad pa la yang de bzhin no mngon gsum
NK107(tse)001:1846: lam du byas na khams gsum du 'khor mi srid
NK107(tse)001:1847: do de ltar ma yin pa'i rgyud 'di'i mtshan la
NK107(tse)001:1848: bsam pa tsam gyis kyang 'das pa'i 'bras bu thob
NK107(tse)001:1849: par nges so de'i phyir na bstan pa la dbang
NK107(tse)001:1850: ba'i sprul pa'i sku cig gis bstan pa gang byung
NK107(tse)001:1851: ba'i thog mar rgyud 'di ni byung ba'o des na
NK107(tse)001:1852: rgyud byung pas ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'phel
NK107(tse)001:1853: ba'o da ni bdun pa dus phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1854: tshig don rgyas par bshad de sems can gyi lus
NK107(tse)001:1855: 'byung ba la snga ba bardzusa skyes te de lus
NK107(tse)001:1856: kun gyi thog mar byung ba ste sprul sku dang
NK107(tse)001:1857: chos mthun pas na bardzusa nas skyes pa'i thog mar
NK107(tse)001:1858: ni lha'i bu rnam pa gnyis las 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:1859: mched pa'i tshe ston pa 'jig rten du byon pa
NK107(tse)001:1860: ste 'jig rten ni mi 'byed ces bya la 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:1861: dus na 'gro ba bardzusa nas skyes pa de dag
NK107(tse)001:1862: kyang tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:1863: su ston pa byon pas res shig bardzusa skyes kyis
NK107(tse)001:1864: 'gro ba rnams rgyun chad do ston pa sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:1865: bcom ldan 'das kyi byin brlabs las bardzusa nas skyes
NK107(tse)001:1866: pa'i 'gro ba lha'i bu nyi ma rab tu snang
NK107(tse)001:1867: byed la sogs pa rnams dang mi 'byed pa rang
NK107(tse)001:1868: bzhin rnam par dag pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK107(tse)001:1869: 'dzin la dbyer mi phyed par gyur pas de'i tshe
NK107(tse)001:1870: 'khor de dag gis kyang chos thams cad ngo bo
NK107(tse)001:1871: dbyer med par gyur to ston pas gsungs pa'i barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1872: cing gsungs pa'i sgra las byung ba'i tshig rnams kyang
NK107(tse)001:1873: bde bar rig ste ston pa yon tan dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:1874: pa 'di gang las byung snyam pa las dang po
NK107(tse)001:1875: chos kyi sku rgyu ma rig pa med pas de
NK107(tse)001:1876: nyid las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku brdal ba kun
NK107(tse)001:1877: la khyab par byung la de las sprul pa'i sku
NK107(tse)001:1878: spros gzhi thams cad dang bral ba la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:1879: la chos ma nyan pa ste 'di'i dus na sku
NK107(tse)001:1880: gsum dang 'khor rnams kyang chos nyid 'gyur ba med
NK107(tse)001:1881: pa'i ngang las dbyer mi phyed par snyoms par zhugs
NK107(tse)001:1882: te rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don mtha' bral
NK107(tse)001:1883: yongs rdzogs kyi dkyil 'khor gcig tu thabs cig tu
NK107(tse)001:1884: 'khod do de ltar gtso 'khor thams cad chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:1885: kyi ngang du cig las dbyer med do zhes de
NK107(tse)001:1886: dag gis ni thun mong gi gleng gzhi la don
NK107(tse)001:1887: bdun gyis bstan nas da ni rgyud kyi gzhung le'u'i
NK107(tse)001:1888: lus dang yan lag bstan te de yang rgyud chen
NK107(tse)001:1889: po gsang ba bla na med pa 'di la yang
NK107(tse)001:1890: le'u drug gis bkod pa yongs su rgyas par bstan
NK107(tse)001:1891: te de la 'dir ni dang po sna tshogs bkod
NK107(tse)001:1892: pa man ngag gi don bstan pa la gnyis te
NK107(tse)001:1893: rgyud kyi lus rnam par bzhag pa'i don gyis khog
NK107(tse)001:1894: dbub pa dang yan lag rnam par bzhag pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:1895: gyis 'bras bu nye bar bstan pa'o de la lus
NK107(tse)001:1896: rnam par bzhag pa la gnyis te zhus pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:1897: gyis man ngag gi tshig don gsal bar bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:1898: dang lan gyi don gyis chos kyi rnam grangs gang
NK107(tse)001:1899: yin pa la 'jug ngo shes par bstan pa'o zhus
NK107(tse)001:1900: pa ni gleng gzhi bstan pa de nas 'khor de
NK107(tse)001:1901: dag gi nang nas ston pa nyid gcig dang tha
NK107(tse)001:1902: mi dad pa'i ngang las rang bzhin snang ba'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:1903: rnams kyi nang nas lha'i bu dga' byed dbang phyug
NK107(tse)001:1904: gis ni ston pa la 'di skad ces gsol to
NK107(tse)001:1905: e ma gong gi sgra tshig rnams la ngo mtshar
NK107(tse)001:1906: nas kye kye rang bzhin gyi don rdzogs par mdzod
NK107(tse)001:1907: cig par gsol ba btab pa'o bcom pa ni ston
NK107(tse)001:1908: pa khyod kyis sngon 'byung du sngon du 'gro ba'i
NK107(tse)001:1909: man ngag la btsal rdzogs pa ste sgra bzhi la
NK107(tse)001:1910: 'byongs pas phyi nang gi bya ba 'byung ba bzhi
NK107(tse)001:1911: rang rgyud du 'dzin pa bcom la 'khor 'das ru
NK107(tse)001:1912: shan 'byed pa la 'byongs pas khams gsum la dmigs
NK107(tse)001:1913: pa'i yul bcom la sems kyi sna 'khrid pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:1914: ngag yid gsum gyi sngon 'gro la 'byongs pas sems
NK107(tse)001:1915: kyi rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa bcom pas
NK107(tse)001:1916: na bcom mo de ltar bcom pas sku gsung thugs
NK107(tse)001:1917: yongs su rdzogs par sku gsum dang ldan la lus
NK107(tse)001:1918: ngag yid ched du byed pa rnams las 'das so
NK107(tse)001:1919: zhing khams 'di ltar snang ba dam pa 'od kyi
NK107(tse)001:1920: tshogs dpag tu med pas spras pa nyid las ston
NK107(tse)001:1921: pa nyid kyi sku las 'od zer gyis tshogs bsam
NK107(tse)001:1922: gyis mi khyab pa 'dus pa'i zhes so bos nas
NK107(tse)001:1923: gong ma'i sgra las tshig gis rang bzhin 'di lta
NK107(tse)001:1924: ste bsdus pa po bdag zhu ba bgyid do ces
NK107(tse)001:1925: zhus so sgra'i skabs su 'byung ba bzhi'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:1926: drag po de ji lta bu lags ma 'ongs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1927: dus na 'byung ba bzhi'i gnad yig la sogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1928: thad ka'i man ngag rnams 'byung bar 'gyur ba la
NK107(tse)001:1929: dgongs te dris pa'oh yan lag gi don la sogs
NK107(tse)001:1930: pa kun gzhung gis shes so da ni zhus pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1931: don bdun cu tham pa zhus pa de bdag ma
NK107(tse)001:1932: yin pa gzhan gyi don du yang gsol ba gdab
NK107(tse)001:1933: pa ni lha'i bu bdag la rim pa gsal bar
NK107(tse)001:1934: dbye bas sems can gzhan ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi
NK107(tse)001:1935: gang zag las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams su
NK107(tse)001:1936: byung la rgyud 'di la dad cing lus kyis rab
NK107(tse)001:1937: tu 'dun pa kun rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:1938: don la yid ches nas 'di nyid bstan cing barjoda
NK107(tse)001:1939: pa tsam gyis lus ngag yid kyi bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1940: bral zhing bla na med pa'i bde ba chen po
NK107(tse)001:1941: rnyed nas 'khor ba'i tha ma las dang sdug basngala
NK107(tse)001:1942: zad nas nih bdag gis ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi
NK107(tse)001:1943: gang zag la bstan pa tsam gyis mya ngan las
NK107(tse)001:1944: 'das pa'i lam sna zin par 'gyur te de ltar
NK107(tse)001:1945: sems can rnams la phan pa'i phyir bdag gis ci
NK107(tse)001:1946: dang ci zhus pa ston pas gong 'og ma nor
NK107(tse)001:1947: bar rim pa gsal bar phye la gsungs shigah ces
NK107(tse)001:1948: zhus pa la gnyis su byas nas bstan no da
NK107(tse)001:1949: ni lan gyi don bstan pa la spyi'i rnam par
NK107(tse)001:1950: bzhag pa'i nang don bdun cu rtsa bzhis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1951: dang por 'byung ba'i dgos pa bstan pa la nang
NK107(tse)001:1952: don yan lag gi bye brag brgyad kyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:1953: dang poh ston pa'i gsung gi che ba'i byin rlabs
NK107(tse)001:1954: ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa ni de nas khyad
NK107(tse)001:1955: par sems la ni zhes pa la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:1956: te de nas ni zhus pa'i 'og tu khyad par
NK107(tse)001:1957: ni rtog pa las 'das pa'i rang sems las ni
NK107(tse)001:1958: bstan pa gzhan du sgra'am tshig gam ming 'di zhes
NK107(tse)001:1959: bya bar b+hud rda nyid dang ston pa gzhan gyis
NK107(tse)001:1960: kyang ma bsgrags kyang ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK107(tse)001:1961: 'das kyis rang bzhin gyi byin rlabs kyis sus kyang
NK107(tse)001:1962: bcos pa med pa'i rnam rig pa mkha' dbyings la
NK107(tse)001:1963: khyab 'jug la sogs pas bris shing sus kyang bkod
NK107(tse)001:1964: pa ma yin par gsang ba b+hud rda'i gsung gi
NK107(tse)001:1965: 'jug pa yan lag ni yangs pa dang ring ba
NK107(tse)001:1966: dang 'jug pa dang snyan pa dang rab tu snyan
NK107(tse)001:1967: pa dang khyab pa dang 'byin pa dang rab tu
NK107(tse)001:1968: 'byin pa dang mdangs dang dbyangs cig gis go ba
NK107(tse)001:1969: dang bcu ni spyan yongs su dag pa las ljags
NK107(tse)001:1970: kyi dbang po las 'phros so yang drag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1971: rab tu grags pa dang spu zings su gyur pa
NK107(tse)001:1972: dang ring byed dang ring byed chen po dang brdas
NK107(tse)001:1973: bskul ba dang brdas 'jug pa dang brda' las rnam
NK107(tse)001:1974: par rol pa dang myos pa dang myos chen du
NK107(tse)001:1975: 'gyur ba bcu ni snyan gyi sgra tshig rnam par
NK107(tse)001:1976: dag pa las ljags kyi dbang po las rab tu
NK107(tse)001:1977: spros so yang mnyam pa dang mi mnyam pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1978: mnyam pa chen po dang snang ba dang mched ba
NK107(tse)001:1979: dang nye bar mched pa dang gcod pa dang rab
NK107(tse)001:1980: tu gcod pa dang 'du ba dang 'dzin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:1981: bcu ni shangs kyi dbang po rab tu dag pa
NK107(tse)001:1982: las ljags kyi dbang po las 'phros so yang bzhad
NK107(tse)001:1983: pa dang bzhad pa chen po dang rab tu bzhad
NK107(tse)001:1984: pa dang cher bzhad pa dang gad mo dang gad
NK107(tse)001:1985: mo chen po dang ye shes kyi gad mo dang
NK107(tse)001:1986: mchog gi gad mo dang 'khor ba'i mtha' yongs su
NK107(tse)001:1987: spong ba'i tshig dang de dag rnams stongs par byed
NK107(tse)001:1988: pa dang bcu ni ljags kyi barjoda pa rnam par
NK107(tse)001:1989: dag pa las byung ba steh rang bzhin gyis stong
NK107(tse)001:1990: pa ni nam mkha' las 'phros pa'oh yang 'ur 'ur
NK107(tse)001:1991: dang chem chem dang g.yos pa dang rab tu g.yos
NK107(tse)001:1992: pa dang 'gul ba dang kun tu 'gul ba dang
NK107(tse)001:1993: rab tu 'gul ba dang sbir sbir dang sbung sbung
NK107(tse)001:1994: dang bskyod pa chen po dang bcu ni sku'i bzhugs
NK107(tse)001:1995: tshul rnam par dag pa las byung ba steh de
NK107(tse)001:1996: yang mgul gyi bum pa las rnam par 'phros te
NK107(tse)001:1997: gdul bya la snang bar byas so yang gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:1998: dang rab tu gnas pa dang gzi mdangs gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:1999: dang sprin spungs pa mthor ba zhes bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:2000: 'dus pa dang 'dus pa chen po dang nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:2001: rab tu snang ba dang 'od kyi skar ma'i tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2002: kyi dpung rab tu 'thor ba dang mi 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:2003: dang zab pa dang shin tu zab pa dang bcu
NK107(tse)001:2004: ni thugs rnam par dag pa'i byin brlabs las rab
NK107(tse)001:2005: tu byung steh ljags kyi pad mo las rnam par
NK107(tse)001:2006: 'phros so de ltar drug cu'i dbyangs dang ldan pas
NK107(tse)001:2007: b+hud rda'i zhing khams rnams dang sems can rnams la
NK107(tse)001:2008: snang bar byas pa ni ye shes dag pa'i nam
NK107(tse)001:2009: mkha' la gdul bya las dag pa'i lha'i bu dga'
NK107(tse)001:2010: byed dbang phyug la sogs pa'i sus kyang ma bris
NK107(tse)001:2011: pa'i 'od zer brgya phrag du mas spras pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2012: ri mo'i tshul tsam du mthong bsah de nyid rab
NK107(tse)001:2013: tu rtogs pa skyes pa ni 'od kyi mdangs dang
NK107(tse)001:2014: ldan par dbang po'i dwangs ma mig la nges par
NK107(tse)001:2015: snang ste de las mig gi dbang po'i mngon sum
NK107(tse)001:2016: du snang bas chos nyid kyi thabs la mkhas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2017: de ltar snang ba mthong ba tsam las nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:2018: nas sgrar yang gong gi lha tshangs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:2019: 'od zer stong dang ldan pa'i sgra lasah yang dag
NK107(tse)001:2020: par rab tu gsal ba 'di skad du byung ngo
NK107(tse)001:2021: e skye ba med pa'i lam hring 'jug cing gsal
NK107(tse)001:2022: bar byed pa'i lha'i bu dga' byed dbang phyug /
NK107(tse)001:2023: khyod nyon zhes gdams pa dang bcas te byung nas
NK107(tse)001:2024: 'byung bzhi'i sgra don la sogs pa rnams la slob
NK107(tse)001:2025: par 'dod pas lus dang ni lus kyi gnad gzir
NK107(tse)001:2026: ba gtsoh de ma gzir na lus la gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2027: ye shes mngon du snang mi srid pas theg pa
NK107(tse)001:2028: spyi dang khyad par mi rnyed do de nas ngag
NK107(tse)001:2029: gi gnad du smra ba gcad pa gal che ngag
NK107(tse)001:2030: ma bcad na barjoda du med pa'i don rgyud la
NK107(tse)001:2031: skye mi srid doh yid so so gang la slob
NK107(tse)001:2032: pa'i gnad la gtad pa rab tu gtso bas na
NK107(tse)001:2033: de la ma gtad na so so'i don gyi chos
NK107(tse)001:2034: nyid mthong mi srid doh gang la ci slob kyang
NK107(tse)001:2035: lus ngag yid gsum gnad che ba yin no zhes
NK107(tse)001:2036: sngon 'byung du ba sdud pa po la gdams la
NK107(tse)001:2037: rjes 'jug tu bla mas slob ma la gdams pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2038: 'di dag gang slob kyang log pa'i tha mal pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2039: spyod pa dang sems kyi bsam pa rnams spangs teh
NK107(tse)001:2040: 'jig rten 'di'i blo med pas nges par 'grub boh
NK107(tse)001:2041: 'di dag gang la slob kyang dbang po mig la
NK107(tse)001:2042: sogs pa la tsan+dana la sogs pa'i dri zhim po
NK107(tse)001:2043: rnams kyis khrus dag par byas nasah sems kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:2044: par rtog pa ngan pa'i dri ma spangs pa'i sems
NK107(tse)001:2045: thams cad mkhyen pa la dmigs pa mi 'gyur la
NK107(tse)001:2046: dag pa nyid kyisah nyon zhes sdud pa po la
NK107(tse)001:2047: gsungs lah rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas slob
NK107(tse)001:2048: ma la gdams pa'oh ces ston pa nyid las gzhung
NK107(tse)001:2049: 'di las gdams pa chen po'i don bstan nasah da
NK107(tse)001:2050: ni gnyis pa chos nyid kyi rnam grangs 'di'i che
NK107(tse)001:2051: lugs ji ltar yin pa bstan pa nih e ma
NK107(tse)001:2052: ngo mtshar rmad byung ba'ih zhes pa la sogs pas
NK107(tse)001:2053: bstan te e ma zhes bstan pa gzhan la 'di
NK107(tse)001:2054: lta bu'i don med pa la dgongs pa yin lah
NK107(tse)001:2055: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i zhes pa ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:2056: nyid thabs kyi sna kha mi 'dra ba la bslab
NK107(tse)001:2057: pa'i bye brag mang por ston pa la yin la
NK107(tse)001:2058: zhing khams gzhan dang gzhan du b+hud rda gzhan rnams
NK107(tse)001:2059: kyis ma gsungs pa'i don gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhan
NK107(tse)001:2060: rnams las khyad par 'phags pa 'di la mos pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2061: gang zag skal pa yod pa rnams 'dod pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2062: gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i khams gsum gyis gnas su
NK107(tse)001:2063: 'di dang phrad pa'i gang zag de mi ldog pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2064: phyir na 'di ni dngos grub dam pa yin pas
NK107(tse)001:2065: 'gro ba rigs dang mi ldan pa rnams la rab
NK107(tse)001:2066: tu gsang bas rdzogs pa chen po nges pa'i bka'
NK107(tse)001:2067: 'di 'grub nges so de'i phyir na bstan pa thams
NK107(tse)001:2068: cad kyi snying po 'di yin pas 'di las bstan
NK107(tse)001:2069: pa thams cad 'phel ba'i don du theg pa thams
NK107(tse)001:2070: cad kyi yang rab rtse mo ste chos thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2071: kyi me long ste 'di nas thams cad gsal don
NK107(tse)001:2072: thams cad kyi 'jug bsdud pa yin pas da dad
NK107(tse)001:2073: pa can sangs rgya ba'i thus ka 'dis byed doh
NK107(tse)001:2074: sangs rgyas kyi bka' thams cad kyi 'grel pa yin
NK107(tse)001:2075: pas 'di nas khog 'grel loh man ngag thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2076: snying po yin pas 'di nas mngon sum snying tig
NK107(tse)001:2077: gi gnad ston no 'di'i don kun la yod kyang
NK107(tse)001:2078: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba chen po'i don yin noh
NK107(tse)001:2079: chos thams cad kyi snying gi tig ka lta bu
NK107(tse)001:2080: yin pas yid dpyod tshig gi spros pa bcad pa'oh
NK107(tse)001:2081: lung thams cad kyi mig yin pas 'di gsum de
NK107(tse)001:2082: nas gsal bar ston noh gsang sngags thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:2083: lde mig yin pas 'di nyid kyis chos thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2084: kyi sgo 'byed par byed pa'o lta ba thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2085: kyi zhe phugs yin pas 'di nyid las 'gro sa
NK107(tse)001:2086: gzhan med do spyod pa thams cad kyi sbyangs sa
NK107(tse)001:2087: yin pas 'di nyid nas bya ba'i gnad khyad par
NK107(tse)001:2088: du ston pa'o bsgom pa thams cad kyi gnad yin
NK107(tse)001:2089: pas 'di nyid bstan pa tsam gyis sems rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:2090: gyis gnas pa 'byung ngo 'gro ba drug gi mngal
NK107(tse)001:2091: gyi grong khyer thams cad kyi rgyun gcod par byed
NK107(tse)001:2092: pas 'di nyid kyi sgor zhugs so tsam gyis khams
NK107(tse)001:2093: gsum du mi ldog pa'o ngan song thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:2094: phyags ma lta bu yin pas khams gsum du mi
NK107(tse)001:2095: brgyud par ngo shes pa'o de lta bu'i so so'i
NK107(tse)001:2096: skye bo dang nyan thos la sogs pa rnams la
NK107(tse)001:2097: gsang ba'i tshig don la brten nas mchog gi sid+d+hi
NK107(tse)001:2098: thob par byed pa'i rgyud bshad kyis bsdud pa po
NK107(tse)001:2099: rdo rje yang 'dzin pa'i rigs dang 'khor gzhan dag
NK107(tse)001:2100: rnams kyang nyon cig zhes gnyis pa chos kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:2101: grangs 'di'i che lugs ji ltar yin pa bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:2102: da ni nang don gsum pa 'di la yid ches
NK107(tse)001:2103: kyis shig pa gdams pa dang bcas pa la bstan
NK107(tse)001:2104: pa ni nga yis spros pa'i tshig rnams la zhes
NK107(tse)001:2105: pa la sogs pas bstan teh nga ni ston pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2106: byin brlabs spros pa ni sgra tshig rnams la ni
NK107(tse)001:2107: rgyud kyi gzhung yi ge ris su bris pa yid
NK107(tse)001:2108: ches skyes la 'khrul pa'am 'chal ba rdul gyi cha
NK107(tse)001:2109: tsam yang med pas gzhung 'di nas bstan pa'i chos
NK107(tse)001:2110: kyi rnam grangs rnams la nges pa kho nar ji
NK107(tse)001:2111: skad gsungs pa bzhin 'grub cing don ji ltar 'dod
NK107(tse)001:2112: pa bzhin 'byung bas na yid ches shing the tshom
NK107(tse)001:2113: med par ji skad gsungs pa'i 'bras bu 'byin par
NK107(tse)001:2114: nges so des na rgyud 'di sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK107(tse)001:2115: pa'i snying po yin par bstan pas na yid ches
NK107(tse)001:2116: par bya'o zhes gsum pa rgyud 'di la yid ches
NK107(tse)001:2117: par gyis shig pa gdams pa dang bcas pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:2118: nas da ni nang don bzhi pa 'byung ba chu'i
NK107(tse)001:2119: dgos pa byung tshul dang bcas pa bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2120: kye kye dga' bar byed pas zung ces pa la
NK107(tse)001:2121: sogs pas bstan te kye kye ni rang bzhin gyi
NK107(tse)001:2122: don gyis shig pa bsdud pa po la bos nas
NK107(tse)001:2123: dga' bar byed pa lha'i bu khyod kyis zung zhig
NK107(tse)001:2124: ces gdams pa steh le'u 'di'i mgo ru dod du
NK107(tse)001:2125: dris pa'i dri ba bdun cu dris pa la de'i
NK107(tse)001:2126: tshig rnams gsal bar phye na 'byung ba'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:2127: 'di yang khyab 'jug zur phud lnga pa'i sgra las
NK107(tse)001:2128: 'phros te gang gis kyang gzhi ma bsgyur bas ni
NK107(tse)001:2129: skad drag pa las rang 'byung du byung ste de
NK107(tse)001:2130: las yi ge'i rnam 'phrul 'di lta bu dag tu
NK107(tse)001:2131: byung ste de yang rang bzhin rnam par dag pa
NK107(tse)001:2132: sus kyang bcos pa med pa'i nam mkha' la yi
NK107(tse)001:2133: ger ma bkod pa tshig 'di rnams byas pa med
NK107(tse)001:2134: par rang byung bar dris pa dang lan gyis tshul
NK107(tse)001:2135: du gdul bya rnams la snang bar byung ngoh de
NK107(tse)001:2136: yang glo bur du byung ba ni ma yin te
NK107(tse)001:2137: gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs la babs kyis grub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2138: phyir na tshig thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhi ma 'di
NK107(tse)001:2139: ltar sems can rnams las snang bar byung ngoh 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2140: ba ni sa dang chu dang me dang rlung gis
NK107(tse)001:2141: dgos pa 'di lta ste 'byung ba chus ni phyi
NK107(tse)001:2142: rol dang lus kyi dwangs ma kun bsdud pas na
NK107(tse)001:2143: de nyid la goms pas tshe dpal grub cing lo
NK107(tse)001:2144: bcu drug lon pa'i lus kyi rnam par dang 'dra
NK107(tse)001:2145: bar 'gyur ro phyi'i dngul dang nang gi dri chen
NK107(tse)001:2146: dang chu'i snyigs ma rnams ni 'byed pa'i las byed
NK107(tse)001:2147: pas 'di nyid rtag tu sbyor ba dang ldan pas
NK107(tse)001:2148: byas na bcud kyis len par 'gyur la de yang
NK107(tse)001:2149: chu'i lus gsum so so'i lus la de dang mthun
NK107(tse)001:2150: par byed pa na de yang dgos pas dwangs ma
NK107(tse)001:2151: las 'byung ba'i 'gyur log pa las tsha ba'i 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2152: bar 'gyur ba dang snyigs ma'i gnas 'gyur ba las
NK107(tse)001:2153: grang bar ngo shes pa ni rlung bsgom pa'i skabs
NK107(tse)001:2154: bstan no zhes bzhi pa 'byung ba chu'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:2155: byung tshul dang bcas pa bstan nas da ni lnga
NK107(tse)001:2156: pa 'byung ba sa'i dgos pa bstan pa ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2157: ba sas ni rnal 'byor pa'i lus kyi gzhi ma
NK107(tse)001:2158: 'dzin pa dang nang lus su grub pa'i lus su
NK107(tse)001:2159: chags pa'i las rnams byed pa steh de'i lus bskyed
NK107(tse)001:2160: pa'i tshe de nyid smin pas lus kyi rtsa gsum
NK107(tse)001:2161: la sogs pa bskyed nas rtsa la brten pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:2162: 'byongs nas khyad par gyi chos nyid skye ba'o de'i
NK107(tse)001:2163: rtsa'i rigs bzhi shes pa la de'i dgos pas kun
NK107(tse)001:2164: rdzob byang chub kyi sems kyi thig le bzung ba
NK107(tse)001:2165: dang bskyil ba dang rlung dang bsre ba dang rtsa'i
NK107(tse)001:2166: dmigs btab nas lus kyi 'byung ba 'phel ba shes
NK107(tse)001:2167: so zhes lnga pa sa'i 'byung ba'i dgos pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:2168: nas da ni drug pa 'byung ba me'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:2169: ston pa ston teh mes ni lus kyi 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2170: rnams spel ba dang dbang po dang yan lag smin
NK107(tse)001:2171: cing shes pas gsal ba'i las rnams byed pa ste
NK107(tse)001:2172: de las ye shes kyi rlung 'bar zhing mched pas
NK107(tse)001:2173: mig la sogs te de dbang po rnams kyi bkrag
NK107(tse)001:2174: dang gzi mdangs bskyed par byed do de nyid nang
NK107(tse)001:2175: du me dang mnyam par sbyar bas dgos pa lus
NK107(tse)001:2176: kyi rkang mthil nas drod kyi rnam pa rta rnga'i
NK107(tse)001:2177: cha'i rnam pa rnams skyes pas gos kyi rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:2178: du shis par byed do zhes drug pa me'i dgos
NK107(tse)001:2179: pa bstan nas da ni bdun pa rlung gi dgos
NK107(tse)001:2180: pa bstan pa ni de yang rlung gis lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2181: nyer len stongs pa dang stong pa nyid kyi 'bras
NK107(tse)001:2182: bu la spyod pa dang ye shes kyi sgron ma
NK107(tse)001:2183: rnams 'degs pa dang lus bskyod cing yan lag g.yob
NK107(tse)001:2184: pa'i las rnams byed pa ni 'di la 'byongs pas
NK107(tse)001:2185: rkang mgyogs chen po 'grub la 'di la gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2186: tshe lus kyi sha rnams 'gul zhing rtsa rnams 'phreg
NK107(tse)001:2187: pas rnal 'byor ba'i lus nyid ye shes su 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:2188: par byed doh de'i dgos pa rang sems kyi gnas
NK107(tse)001:2189: pa shes te rlung tshad zin pa dag 'byung ngoh
NK107(tse)001:2190: zhes bdun pa rlung gi dgos pa bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:2191: ni brgyad pa 'byung ba bzhi las kyi 'gyur shes
NK107(tse)001:2192: brtsi ba bstan te 'byung ba ni chu la lam
NK107(tse)001:2193: du byas na de nyid dbang bsgyur zhing tshe la
NK107(tse)001:2194: dbang ba 'grub sa la byas pas mtshon gyis mi
NK107(tse)001:2195: tshugs pa dang gong ma'o mes shes pa gsal zhing
NK107(tse)001:2196: mngon shes dang gong ma'o rlung la lam du byas
NK107(tse)001:2197: pas de nyid la dbang bsgyur nus shing nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:2198: rab tu dag par byed do de ltar bzhi bdag
NK107(tse)001:2199: gi dbang du 'dus pa las b+hud rda'i dkyil 'khor
NK107(tse)001:2200: stong la che ba'i snang ba ston nus par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:2201: ro de yang 'byung ba bzhis thog ma yang lus
NK107(tse)001:2202: la sogs pa grub pa'i rgyu byas te lus 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2203: ba las grub pas na 'byung ba lam du byas
NK107(tse)001:2204: na 'bras bu myur ba'i gnad do bar du lus
NK107(tse)001:2205: gnas shing 'dzin pa 'byung ba sas byas pas 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2206: ba bso ba'i cho ga byas na lus la nad
NK107(tse)001:2207: med cing bar chad mi 'byung tha ma yang lus
NK107(tse)001:2208: 'jig pa'i las kun 'byung bas byed pas 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2209: sbo zhing spol ba'i las byas na tshe ring zhing
NK107(tse)001:2210: dus tshod shes par 'gyur ro de'i phyir na 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2211: ba chen pos byed pas na gang ltar byas kyang
NK107(tse)001:2212: 'grub pa la the tshom med do de'i phyir na
NK107(tse)001:2213: 'byung ba'i gnad shes na dngos su las sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2214: byed pa'i bdag por snang la ma dag pas sdug
NK107(tse)001:2215: basngala sna tshogs par 'gyur ro des na 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2216: bzhi'i dgos pas rang gzhan gyis don 'grub la 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2217: ba'i bya ba rdzogs pa'i don la mkhas na gzhan
NK107(tse)001:2218: 'jig pa'i cho ga yang nges par 'grub bo zhes
NK107(tse)001:2219: brgyad pa 'byung ba bzhi'i las kyi 'gyur shes rtsi
NK107(tse)001:2220: ba bstan te de dag kun gyis dri ba dang
NK107(tse)001:2221: po 'byung ba'i dgos pa bstan pa la yan lag
NK107(tse)001:2222: gi don brgyad du byas nas bstan no da ni
NK107(tse)001:2223: dris lan gnyis pa yan lag gi lan rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:2224: bstan pa la nang don gsum gyis bstan pa'i yan
NK107(tse)001:2225: lag gi dang po rgyud kyi mtshan gzhung nges pa
NK107(tse)001:2226: 'jug pa blo'i 'jug pa dang bcas pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:2227: ni yan lag don ni 'di lta bu zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:2228: la sogs pas bstan te rgyud kyi tshig don gsal
NK107(tse)001:2229: bar phye na yan lag gi mtshan dang gzhung du
NK107(tse)001:2230: sbyar ba don ni de la brten nas gang zag
NK107(tse)001:2231: gi rgyud 'grol bar byed pa'oh 'di lta bu zhes
NK107(tse)001:2232: pa ni bstan par bya zhes pa'i don no sprul
NK107(tse)001:2233: pa'i sangs rgyas gzhan rnams kyis 'di lta bu'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:2234: mi mkhyen pa'i ston pa rdo rje 'chang gis 'dir
NK107(tse)001:2235: tshig tu barjoda pa gsal ba'i rim par phye nas
NK107(tse)001:2236: bstan pa ni rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang rgyud
NK107(tse)001:2237: kyi gzhung bstan pa dag gis yang dang yang du
NK107(tse)001:2238: bstan pa ni gang zag gi blo rim gyis pa
NK107(tse)001:2239: dang blo gcig 'char ba rnams kyis mtshan bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:2240: tsam gyis go la blo rim gyis pa rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:2241: rgyud gzhung bstan pas rtogs par bstan pa la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:2242: pa'oh de ltar mtshan dang gzhung gnyis po blo rim
NK107(tse)001:2243: gyis rtogs par bya ba'i phyir rnam pa bshad par
NK107(tse)001:2244: bya'o zhes dang po rgyud kyi mtshan gzhung nges pa
NK107(tse)001:2245: blo'i 'jug pa dang bcas pa bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:2246: yan lag gi don gnyis pa rgyud kyi gzhung don
NK107(tse)001:2247: rnam par phye ba bstan pa ni gzhung la ni
NK107(tse)001:2248: tshig rnam par spras pa rnam pa gnyis su ni
NK107(tse)001:2249: lus rnam par bzhag ba dang yan lag gis 'bru
NK107(tse)001:2250: gnyer bar brtag go de yang lus nyid rnam par
NK107(tse)001:2251: bzhag pas rgyud kyi khog dbub pa ni lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2252: don mtshan gleng gzhi dris pa dang bcas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2253: yan lag gi don gyis 'bru gnyer ba ni zhus
NK107(tse)001:2254: pa'i lan la rgyas par dbye ba dag yin no
NK107(tse)001:2255: de yang lus rnam par bzhag pa ni khyad par
NK107(tse)001:2256: gyi gleng gzhi dang thun mong gi gleng gzhi rnam
NK107(tse)001:2257: pa gnyis yin pa la theg pa gzhan las khyad
NK107(tse)001:2258: par 'phags pa'i don du thun mong min pa'i gleng
NK107(tse)001:2259: gzhi rnal 'byor pa rang gi lus la sbyar te
NK107(tse)001:2260: bshad pa ni gong du bstan no theg pa gzhan
NK107(tse)001:2261: rnams dang lung tsam zhig sgo bstun pa'i phyir thun
NK107(tse)001:2262: mong dag gi gleng gzhi yis 'di skad bdag gis
NK107(tse)001:2263: thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes bsdud pa po lha'i
NK107(tse)001:2264: bu dga' byed dbang phyug gis kho rang gi 'khor
NK107(tse)001:2265: rnams la yid ches par bya ba'i phyir bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:2266: ste gdul bya gang zag gcig la 'dul gzhi phung
NK107(tse)001:2267: po lnga yod pas de'i 'dul byed du phun sum
NK107(tse)001:2268: tshogs pa lnga byung bas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:2269: yun ring bar gnas par byed do zhes gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:2270: rgyud gzhung gi don rnam par phye ba bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:2271: da ni gsum pa rgyud kyi don yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:2272: tshig don rnam par bsdus te bstan pa ni yan
NK107(tse)001:2273: lag ni tshig gi 'bru gnyer rnams la gzhung gi
NK107(tse)001:2274: le'u drug bstan nas khams gsum gyi sems can rnams
NK107(tse)001:2275: b+hud tha bar byed pa'i cha rkyen rgyas par ston
NK107(tse)001:2276: par byed pa'o de yang le'u dang po sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2277: bkod pa'i man ngag gi rtsa ba'i tshig gi don
NK107(tse)001:2278: ni lus la bkod pa brgyad cu rtsa gcig yan
NK107(tse)001:2279: lag la nyis brgya dang brgyad cu rtsa bzhi le'u
NK107(tse)001:2280: gnyis pa gnad thams cad 'dus pas bkod pa la
NK107(tse)001:2281: lus la sum cu rtsa gnyis yan lag la brgya
NK107(tse)001:2282: phrag gnyis dang bcu le'u gsum pa ye shes kyi
NK107(tse)001:2283: bkod pa'i lus la nyi shu rtsa dgu la yan
NK107(tse)001:2284: lag la bye brag tu phye ba nyis brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:2285: drug go bzhi pa chos nyid bkod pa'i le'u la
NK107(tse)001:2286: lus rnam par bzhag pa la lus la nyer dgu
NK107(tse)001:2287: yan lag 'bru gnyer ba la lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK107(tse)001:2288: kyis bstan noh lnga pa lta sgom bkod pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:2289: pa'i le'u la lus rnam par bzhag pa sum cu
NK107(tse)001:2290: rtsa gnyis yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la drug
NK107(tse)001:2291: cu rtsa gsum bstan no drug pa sku rnam par
NK107(tse)001:2292: bkod pa'i le'u la lus rnam par bzhag pa la
NK107(tse)001:2293: bcu drug yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la sum
NK107(tse)001:2294: cu rtsa gnyis so de dag ni le'u'i grangs drug
NK107(tse)001:2295: gis gzhung 'di nyid las sa gcod kyi dmigs tsam
NK107(tse)001:2296: zhig 'og nas bstan pa'i don 'dir bshad pa'o des
NK107(tse)001:2297: 'di la tshig don ji ltar gnas pa'i tshig dang
NK107(tse)001:2298: don ni dper na skyes bu zhig gis lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2299: khog pa kha phye bas don snying la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:2300: nang na ci yod pa gsal ba ltar de yang
NK107(tse)001:2301: don snying la sogs pa dang snod rgyu long la
NK107(tse)001:2302: sogs pa dbang po la snang bar ston pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2303: 'dra bar rgyud kyi tshig gi don la rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:2304: gnyis te bsdus pas dris pa dang ston pas lan
NK107(tse)001:2305: du gsungs pa'o lan gnyis la rnam pa gnyis te
NK107(tse)001:2306: dri bas mdor bstan pa dang lan gyis rgyas par
NK107(tse)001:2307: bshad pa'o de yang gang gi phyir bstan ce na
NK107(tse)001:2308: gdul bya'i yul gang zag skal ba can 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:2309: la mos pa rnams kyi don du tshig sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2310: su spros pa dag yin no zhes lus dang yan
NK107(tse)001:2311: lag gi don rnam par phye ste bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:2312: gsum du byas nas bstan no da ni dris lan
NK107(tse)001:2313: gsum pa'i lan sangs rgyas rnams kyis dgongs pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:2314: rnam par bzhag pa bstan pa la yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:2315: don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po rig pa rang
NK107(tse)001:2316: snang gi blo can rnams rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:2317: tsam gyis go bar bstan pa ni e ma rgyud
NK107(tse)001:2318: dag nges 'byung la zhes pa la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:2319: te e ma ni ngo mtshar ba la dgongs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2320: rgyud ni mtshan gyi skabs su bstan la dag pa
NK107(tse)001:2321: ni 'di las sde snod thams cad 'byung zhing rtsa
NK107(tse)001:2322: ba yin pa la dgongs pa'o nges par 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2323: ni drang don lta bu ma yin pa la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:2324: la b+hud rda'i thugs kyi dgongs pa rnam pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:2325: yin te blo'i rim pa gnyis la dgongs pa ste
NK107(tse)001:2326: de la 'dir ni rig pa rang snang gi blo
NK107(tse)001:2327: can rnams la rgyud kyi mtshan don rnams las phye
NK107(tse)001:2328: ste bstan pa ni sgra 'gyur du bstan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2329: brda' 'gyur du bstan pa dang don 'gyur du bstan
NK107(tse)001:2330: pa gsum gyis bstan te de ltar gsum mtshan du
NK107(tse)001:2331: bstan pa tsam la brten nas chos nyid mngon sum
NK107(tse)001:2332: la lam du byas te 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa
NK107(tse)001:2333: nyid do de ltar gyur pas 'dod pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:2334: pa'i khams gsum du 'khor ba'i lam rgyun gcad nas
NK107(tse)001:2335: phyis 'khor ba'i lus gzhan la phyir 'phos pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:2336: la ldog pa med pa'i phyir na chos nyid zad
NK107(tse)001:2337: pa'i mtshan nyid shes pa'o zhes yan lag gis don
NK107(tse)001:2338: dang po rig pa rang snang gi blo can rnams
NK107(tse)001:2339: la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa tsam gyis go bar
NK107(tse)001:2340: bstan nas da ni gnyis pa dmigs pa yul can
NK107(tse)001:2341: gyi blo can rnams la brgyud kyi gzhung don rnam
NK107(tse)001:2342: par phye ste bstan par go bar bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2343: de la dmigs pa ni mtshan ma dang tshig la
NK107(tse)001:2344: rjes su 'dzin pa rnams so yul gyi ni rten
NK107(tse)001:2345: dmigs pa'am tshig la brten nas skye bar byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2346: blo'i dbang po'i bye brag tu 'gyur ba rnams so
NK107(tse)001:2347: rgyud 'di'i gzhung gi tshig rnams rnam par phye ste
NK107(tse)001:2348: sems can rnams la gang la gang mos su gzhung
NK107(tse)001:2349: 'di nas bstan pa'i nges pa'i don gyis gzhan rnams
NK107(tse)001:2350: gnad re re dag la gnad tshugs nas de nyid
NK107(tse)001:2351: dang dus thams cad du 'bral ba med par de'i
NK107(tse)001:2352: don yongs su rtogs na khams gsum 'khor ba dag
NK107(tse)001:2353: la gang zag 'di gnas pa med do de ci'i
NK107(tse)001:2354: phyir zhe na rgyud 'di nas gnad mi 'dra ba
NK107(tse)001:2355: rab tu zab par ston pas soh gal te spros
NK107(tse)001:2356: pa nyid la dga' ba'i mi yin na gzhung 'di
NK107(tse)001:2357: nas bstan pa'i man ngag sna tshogs thabs la bslabs
NK107(tse)001:2358: par gyur na mi des kyang de dag so so'i
NK107(tse)001:2359: bsgrub pa snyems te 'di'i nang nas gsungs pa'i bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:2360: pa'i rim pa rnams la bsgrub pas kyang nges par
NK107(tse)001:2361: 'thob bo de dag gi dgongs pa'i gnad don gyi
NK107(tse)001:2362: man ngag ni 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin du so
NK107(tse)001:2363: so'i skabs nas 'byung ba bzhin du shes par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:2364: zhes dri ba gsum pa b+hud rda'i dgongs pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:2365: rnam par bzhag pa la gnyis su byas nas bstan
NK107(tse)001:2366: no da ni dris lan bzhi pa rgyud kyi mtshan
NK107(tse)001:2367: gyi rnam grangs kyi lus rnam par bzhag pa la
NK107(tse)001:2368: gnyis te sgra'i gnas gzhan la bslab pa dang bslabs
NK107(tse)001:2369: pa'i sgra'i dgos pa bstan pa'o sgra'i gnas gzhan la
NK107(tse)001:2370: bslab pa la yan lag gi don drug gis bstan
NK107(tse)001:2371: pa'i dang po bka'i babs so la brten nas khungs
NK107(tse)001:2372: gsal bar bstan pa ni rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di
NK107(tse)001:2373: nyid kyi zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te rgyud
NK107(tse)001:2374: kyi thal 'gyur zhes bya bas te rgyal po ni
NK107(tse)001:2375: rgyud gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i don no
NK107(tse)001:2376: 'di nyid kyi ni thabs kyi don sna mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:2377: ba mang po ston pas so nges pa ni mi
NK107(tse)001:2378: 'grub mi srid pa'i don no mtshan gyi ni sdud
NK107(tse)001:2379: pa pos lhag ma rnams bzhag nas sgra zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:2380: ba de la ma bde nas dris pa'o rnam grangs
NK107(tse)001:2381: la zhes bya ba ni 'og nas thal dang 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:2382: dang sgra la sogs pa ston kyang 'di nyid du
NK107(tse)001:2383: sgra zhes bya ba la brten nas bka' rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:2384: chen po'i don gyi man ngag ni 'di'i nang nas
NK107(tse)001:2385: tshig tsam du nges par brtags nas phye ste tshig
NK107(tse)001:2386: gi 'bru rnams chos nyid kyi don dang mthun par
NK107(tse)001:2387: yang dag par rig pa'i don gyi ngo bo gang
NK107(tse)001:2388: la 'di ltar bskyal lo de yang sgra'i barjoda pa
NK107(tse)001:2389: 'di lta bu gsang sngags kyi rgyud rnams gzhan du
NK107(tse)001:2390: nges ma bshad pa'i chos 'di lta bu e ma
NK107(tse)001:2391: ngo mtshar che ba nyid yid pas nga yis 'di
NK107(tse)001:2392: lta bu'i chos nyid la lam du byas pas sangs
NK107(tse)001:2393: rgyas pa yin te rab tu gsang ba'i don 'di
NK107(tse)001:2394: sdud pa po khyod la spro yis phyin ci ma
NK107(tse)001:2395: log par nga la nyon zhes sngon 'byung du sdud
NK107(tse)001:2396: pa po la gdams pa rjes 'jug gi dus su
NK107(tse)001:2397: bla mas slob ma la gdams pa'o de yang sgra
NK107(tse)001:2398: zhes pa'i babs so ni tshangs pa dang khyab 'jug
NK107(tse)001:2399: dang sing g+ham la dang 'byung ba dang ston pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2400: gsung dang rnam pa lnga ni tshangs pa dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:2401: pa la gnas rnam pa lnga khyab 'jug dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:2402: pa la bcu gsum sing g+ha dang zhes pa la
NK107(tse)001:2403: sum brgya dang drug cu 'byung ba'i sgra dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:2404: pa la gnas brgyad ston pa'i gsung zhes pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2405: dbyangs cig gis 'gro ba rnams go bar byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2406: de ltar sgra'i babs so lnga yis 'byung ba'i chos
NK107(tse)001:2407: rnams la bza' ba dang bsgo ba dang 'gro ba'i
NK107(tse)001:2408: tshe b+har 'gyur ba dang nam mkha' la 'phur ba
NK107(tse)001:2409: dang sa la zang thal du rgyu bar nus pa
NK107(tse)001:2410: dang chu la mi 'bying ba dang mes mi tshig
NK107(tse)001:2411: pa dang rlung gis 'thor ba la sogs pa'i 'jigs
NK107(tse)001:2412: pa med pa dang ci dga' rol ba sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2413: pa chen pos spyod do zhes dang po sgra'i babs
NK107(tse)001:2414: so la brten nas khungs gsal bar bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:2415: ni gnyis pa lha tshangs pa chen po'i khang bu
NK107(tse)001:2416: brtsegs pa'i gnas sgra'i gnas la bslab pas thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2417: chos nyid du 'char bar bstan pa ni tshangs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2418: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa 'byung bar byed pa'i rten
NK107(tse)001:2419: gyi khyad par tshangs pa chen po yon tan dang
NK107(tse)001:2420: ldan pa la bya'o sgra'i gnas ni gzugs kyis gnas
NK107(tse)001:2421: pas gti mug zad par byed pa'o tshor ba'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:2422: pas nga rgyal zad par byed pa dang 'du shes
NK107(tse)001:2423: kyi gnas pas 'dod chags zad par byed pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2424: 'du byed kyi gnas pas phrag dog zad par byed
NK107(tse)001:2425: pa dang rnam par shes pa'i gnas pas zhe sdang
NK107(tse)001:2426: zad par byed pa dang lnga po la bslab par
NK107(tse)001:2427: bya ba'i rim pa ni gnad ni rnal 'byor pa
NK107(tse)001:2428: dad pa dang ldan pa zhig gis 'di'i gnad rnams
NK107(tse)001:2429: bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la longs par
NK107(tse)001:2430: byas la zla grogs spangs la rkyen gyis mi gnod
NK107(tse)001:2431: pa'i ri khrod dgon par 'gro ba'i tshe tshogs bsags
NK107(tse)001:2432: pa'i cho ga byas te rang gi rdzas dang longs
NK107(tse)001:2433: spyod 'di nyid 'grub pa'i tshod dang sbyar ba las
NK107(tse)001:2434: mi bzung bar rang gi bla ma la bzhed pa
NK107(tse)001:2435: med kyang 'bul bar bya'o gal te bla ma mi
NK107(tse)001:2436: snang na rdo rje'i spun sring rab tu bzang ba
NK107(tse)001:2437: dam tshig gi sel med pa la 'bul bar bya'o
NK107(tse)001:2438: de yang yul gyis bskal pa la sogs pa med
NK107(tse)001:2439: na sngags kyi grub pa thob nges pa'i gang zag
NK107(tse)001:2440: la tshogs bsags so de yang med na rab tu
NK107(tse)001:2441: byung ba'i dge slong tshul khrims bsrung nges pa la
NK107(tse)001:2442: tshogs bsags so de ltar tshogs bsags pa'i thabs kyi
NK107(tse)001:2443: yan lag rnams rdzogs par byas la mi mi rgyu
NK107(tse)001:2444: ba'i dur khrod la sogs pa'i gnas su rang gcig
NK107(tse)001:2445: pur grogs spangs la tshangs pa'i sgra'i gnas sbyang bar
NK107(tse)001:2446: bya ba ni de yang gnas dang po gzugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:2447: mtha' rdul yin pas sngon du lus la sku mnye
NK107(tse)001:2448: byas la rnal 'byor pa'i ngag rab tu dal bas
NK107(tse)001:2449: rdul rdul rdul rdul rdul zhes par med par barjoda
NK107(tse)001:2450: pas skabs su dun med par 'jug snyam pa skye
NK107(tse)001:2451: de nas dus 'ga' na 'di la dgos pa ci
NK107(tse)001:2452: 'dug snyam pa skye de nas res dgod snying 'dod
NK107(tse)001:2453: pa dang res ngu snying 'dod pa dang khu cho
NK107(tse)001:2454: chen po 'don snying 'dod pa dag 'byung ste de
NK107(tse)001:2455: dag gang byung ba mi spang bar bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:2456: zla ba drug tu byas pas chu'i sgra skabs su
