NK107(tse)001:2457: thos te 'di'i dus na shes nyams rab tu gseng
NK107(tse)001:2458: zhing gsal ba 'byung de nas zla ba gcig nas
NK107(tse)001:2459: 'khor lo lta bu'i nyams su myong ba dang pad
NK107(tse)001:2460: ma lta bu dang rdo rje lta bu dang mchod
NK107(tse)001:2461: rten brtsegs pa lta bu dang de nas rin po
NK107(tse)001:2462: che'i khang pa brtsegs pa lta bu mthong zhing 'di
NK107(tse)001:2463: tsam na shes pa bde lugs su spyod pa la
NK107(tse)001:2464: gnas shing rab tu gsal ba'i nyams dang ldan pa
NK107(tse)001:2465: dag 'byung ngo de dag nyid kyang gong ma nas
NK107(tse)001:2466: zla ba re re la 'byung ba yin no de
NK107(tse)001:2467: nas gong gi sgra'i gnas gzhan so so la bslabs
NK107(tse)001:2468: pas so so'i skabs kyi nyams su myong ba dag
NK107(tse)001:2469: la spyod par nges pa dag 'byung ngo yang sa'i
NK107(tse)001:2470: lus yod pa'i rnal 'byor pas tshor ba'i gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:2471: nga rgyal zad par byed pa la bslab par bya
NK107(tse)001:2472: ste de yang tshor ba'i mtha' sdug basngala dang bde
NK107(tse)001:2473: ba dang btang snyoms gsum las mi 'da' ste de
NK107(tse)001:2474: yang sa zug pa'i mis tshogs bsags pa dang dbang
NK107(tse)001:2475: bskur ba dang dben pa'i gnas rten pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:2476: pa snga ma ltar byas la yang rlung cig gi
NK107(tse)001:2477: 'khor lo'i khongs su brda' brda' brda' brda' brda' brda'
NK107(tse)001:2478: zhes pa bar ma chad par zla ba phyed bar
NK107(tse)001:2479: ma chad par bya'o de nas lus ngag yid kyi
NK107(tse)001:2480: bde ba rang lugs su 'char ba 'byung de nas
NK107(tse)001:2481: zla ba gcig na sa'i sgra don gyis nges par
NK107(tse)001:2482: snang ba 'ga' 'byung de nas zla ba phyed na
NK107(tse)001:2483: rang bzhin gyis byas pa med par ngag tu rang
NK107(tse)001:2484: brdol te sa'i sgra e srum zhes pa dag thol
NK107(tse)001:2485: byung du 'byung zhing 'di'i dus na rang gi lus
NK107(tse)001:2486: kyi rdul phra rab zin pa dag 'byung de nas
NK107(tse)001:2487: zla ba phyed na lus ri brag rnams la zang
NK107(tse)001:2488: thal du rgyu bar nus shing sa 'og gi 'jig
NK107(tse)001:2489: rten gsal bar mthong ba dag 'byung ngo de nas
NK107(tse)001:2490: zla ba gcig na sa'i sgra nye bar spyod pa
NK107(tse)001:2491: zhes bya ste sa la brten pa'i sgra don gyi
NK107(tse)001:2492: snang ba 'char zhing de'i yan lag gis sgra'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:2493: snyems pas so so'i tshig bshad la dbang ba dag
NK107(tse)001:2494: tu 'gyur ro yang sa byer ba'i mis brdu brdu
NK107(tse)001:2495: brdu brdu brdu brdu brdu zhes rlung gcig gi khongs
NK107(tse)001:2496: su legs par barjoda na sdug basngala las grol bar
NK107(tse)001:2497: nyams kyi snang ba rab tu dag pa nyid 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2498: ba ni zla ba gcig barjoda pa'i bting la lus
NK107(tse)001:2499: la rdul chen po dun med par 'byung ba dang
NK107(tse)001:2500: de nas yang bar ma chad par zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:2501: dang gnyis su barjoda pas lus kyi skyi rim ba
NK107(tse)001:2502: bdun du byi zhing shes pa yang bde ba mi
NK107(tse)001:2503: rtog pa 'byung de nas zla ba gcig na tshangs
NK107(tse)001:2504: pa 'dun na 'don gyi skad e sa ri zhes
NK107(tse)001:2505: bya ba rang brdol du ngag las 'byung zhing lus
NK107(tse)001:2506: rab tu skyi bung byed cing skra dang ba bu
NK107(tse)001:2507: rnams 'byin par 'gyur ba ni sa'i chos nyid dmer
NK107(tse)001:2508: ti zhes bya ba rang dal la spyod pa la
NK107(tse)001:2509: nye ba yin no de nas zla ba phyed na
NK107(tse)001:2510: shes ba gsal la ma yengs pa'i nyams 'byung ngo
NK107(tse)001:2511: de nas yang sa'i sgra la nye bar spyod pa
NK107(tse)001:2512: dag 'byung ngo yang sa snyoms pa'i lus kyis rlung
NK107(tse)001:2513: gcig gis khongs su snya snya snya snya snya snya
NK107(tse)001:2514: snya zhes pa la zla ba gcig dum gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:2515: sbyangs pas lus rab tu gtse zhing tsha bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:2516: yang de nyid las bar ma chad par barjoda pa
NK107(tse)001:2517: las de dag rimas kyis yal nas zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:2518: dang gnyis na lus rab tu bsnyen cing lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2519: lhu tshigs rnams las gnyan du rung ba dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:2520: med pa dag 'byung ngo de yang lus kyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2521: ba khyad par gyi rang sgra yin te brten pa
NK107(tse)001:2522: dang brten pa'i tshul gyis rang bzhin rnam par dag
NK107(tse)001:2523: pa'o de nas zla ba gnyis na sa'i sgra la
NK107(tse)001:2524: nye bar spyod pa dag 'byung ngo yang 'du shes
NK107(tse)001:2525: kyi gnas pas 'dod chags zad par byed pa la
NK107(tse)001:2526: bslab pa ni de yang 'du ba'i mtha' gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:2527: mi gnas shing 'bar la shes pa'i mtha' 'gyur ba'o
NK107(tse)001:2528: yang rnal 'byor pa sngon du 'gro ba snga ma
NK107(tse)001:2529: ltar rdzogs pa'i me zug pa gcig gis ngag rab
NK107(tse)001:2530: tu gsal ba dang ldan pa'i dbyangs gcig gis rlung
NK107(tse)001:2532: 'ung zhes dal ba med par zhag nyer gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:2533: nyin mtshan du gnyid spangs nas barjoda pas ngag tu
NK107(tse)001:2534: skad rigs mi mthun pa'i skad rnams rang 'byung du
NK107(tse)001:2535: ngag la 'byung ba dang lus rab tu 'dar ba
NK107(tse)001:2536: dang sems phya sangs khyer pa dag 'byung de nas
NK107(tse)001:2537: zla ba gcig tu bar ma chad par byas pa
NK107(tse)001:2538: las yang lus gzhan gyis bltas na me'i phung por
NK107(tse)001:2539: 'gyur ba mthong bas na gang la reg pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:2540: 'tshig nus snyam pa dang ngag la mtshan ma med
NK107(tse)001:2541: pa dang spros pa med pa'i tshig rnams rang brdol
NK107(tse)001:2542: du 'byung ba dang sems la bde ba gsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:2543: nyams 'char ro de nas zla ba gcig na 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2544: ba me'i sgra la nye bar spyod do yang me
NK107(tse)001:2545: byer bas ngag bsal zhing snyoms pas rlung gi 'khor
NK107(tse)001:2546: lo la r+ae r+ae r+ae r+ae r+ae r+ae r+ae zhes
NK107(tse)001:2547: dal ba med par barjoda pas zla ba gcig na
NK107(tse)001:2548: ngag la gtam rgyud ngo mtshar can mang por smra
NK107(tse)001:2549: ba dag 'byung de nas zla ba gcig na ngag
NK107(tse)001:2550: gi zhen pa rang log pa dag 'byung de nas
NK107(tse)001:2551: zhag dgu na lus ngag yid bde ba zhing gsal
NK107(tse)001:2552: ba la yang zhing snyoms pa'i bde ba dag 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2553: ngo de nas zla ba phyed na 'byung ba me'i
NK107(tse)001:2554: sgra la nye bar spyod pa dag 'byung ngo yang
NK107(tse)001:2555: me snyoms pas rlung gcig gi khongs su y+ae y+ae
NK107(tse)001:2556: y+ae y+ae y+ae y+ae y+ae zhes zla ba gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:2557: barjoda pa las lus ngag bde stong gsal ba'i shed
NK107(tse)001:2558: skye ba dang ngag la khyad par gyi nus pa
NK107(tse)001:2559: snyed pa dag 'byung ngo de nas zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:2560: na tshangs pa kun 'khor gyi sgra ha ris zhes
NK107(tse)001:2561: bya ba la spyad pas lus kyi srog chags rnams
NK107(tse)001:2562: tshig cing med par 'gyur ro de nas zhag bcu
NK107(tse)001:2563: na me'i sgra la nye bar spyod do yang 'du
NK107(tse)001:2564: byed kyi gnas pa la phrag dog zad par byed
NK107(tse)001:2565: pa ni de yang 'du 'tshogs pa las 'du byed
NK107(tse)001:2566: rnam par 'phrul pa yin pas na rlung zug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2567: mis sngon 'gro la sogs pa gong ltar byas la
NK107(tse)001:2568: rab tu dben par song ste yang rlung gcig gis
NK107(tse)001:2569: khongs su ngag rab tu 'phra bas 'u 'u 'e
NK107(tse)001:2570: 'e 'u 'u y+ae y+ae barjoda pas zla ba gcig
NK107(tse)001:2571: na lus sgyid lugs pa dag 'byung de nas zla
NK107(tse)001:2572: ba phyed na lus zang thal du yod pa snyam
NK107(tse)001:2573: pa 'byu de nas phyed na sems rtog pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2574: bral ba'i nyams 'byung ngo de nas zhag dgu na
NK107(tse)001:2575: rlung gi sgra la nye bar spyod do yang rlung
NK107(tse)001:2576: byer bas ngag gcig gi 'khor lo la ngag rab
NK107(tse)001:2577: tu lding bas smra smra smra smra smra smra smra
NK107(tse)001:2578: zhes zla ba gcig tu barjoda pa las tshangs lha
NK107(tse)001:2579: nye phan gyi lha rnams kyi sgra sa hri zhes
NK107(tse)001:2580: pa la nye bar spyod pa 'byung de nas zla
NK107(tse)001:2581: ba phyed na sgra phra mo dag khong du chud
NK107(tse)001:2582: pa nyid 'byung la de nas zla ba phyed na
NK107(tse)001:2583: lus ngag la ngo mtshar ba'i mtshan ma dag 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2584: ngo de nas phyed na rlung gi sgra la nye
NK107(tse)001:2585: bar spyod do yang rnam par shes pa'i gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:2586: zhe sdang zad par byed pa'i bslab pa'i thabs ni
NK107(tse)001:2587: 'di ni nam mkha' ma ning stongs pas na lus
NK107(tse)001:2588: bzhi kas spyi thun mong du bslab pa'i thabs te
NK107(tse)001:2590: 'am zhes bya ba la rang gi lo grangs tsam
NK107(tse)001:2591: gyis zhag sbyangs sa yin 'ar 'ar 'ar 'ar zhes
NK107(tse)001:2592: bya ba la yang lo grangs tsam sbyangs me yin
NK107(tse)001:2593: na de da d+aed+aa ded d+aed+aa ded d+aed+aa ded d+aed+aa
NK107(tse)001:2594: zhes bya ba la snga ma dang 'dra'o rlung yin
NK107(tse)001:2595: na se s+ae se s+ae se s+ae se s+ae zhes
NK107(tse)001:2596: pa la lo grangs tsam cig sbyangs pa las lus
NK107(tse)001:2597: kyi 'phen pa log pa dang zhag de dag re
NK107(tse)001:2598: re la shes pa'i 'jug pa mi 'dra ba re
NK107(tse)001:2599: re skye ba dang so so'i lus la 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2600: 'phel ba la sogs pa'i rtags 'byung bar nges so
NK107(tse)001:2601: 'di dag ni so so'i bye brag 'brel ba rnam
NK107(tse)001:2602: par rtags pa'o de ltar lnga po la bslabs pas
NK107(tse)001:2603: spyir phung po lnga'i rab tu 'byed pa 'gag pa
NK107(tse)001:2604: dang nang du nyon mongs pa lnga'i byed pa rang
NK107(tse)001:2605: 'gags pas so so'i 'byung ba'i sgra la nye bar
NK107(tse)001:2606: spyod cing gnas pa dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro de
NK107(tse)001:2607: ltar tshangs pa'i sgra gnas lnga la gzugs kyi gnas
NK107(tse)001:2608: pa la nyis brgya yod de de yang byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2609: 'gyur gyis nye bar brtags na de dag re re
NK107(tse)001:2610: dag la rang gi lo'i grangs brgya brgya dang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:2611: gnyis bslab na barjoda bya tshig la mkhas par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:2612: ba dang smra byed grangs la mkhas par 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:2613: dang gnas pa shes byed la mkhas par 'gyur pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2614: de yang gnas ni gong du lnga bstan pas phung
NK107(tse)001:2615: po lnga'i rang rgyud du 'dzin pa rnam par dag
NK107(tse)001:2616: pas nyon mongs pa lnga'i 'gyu ba rgyun chad pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2617: gzhan zhes bya ba'i byed pa re re ste zhes
NK107(tse)001:2618: pa ni tshangs pa chen po'i tshig gi 'phrul rnams
NK107(tse)001:2619: te rgyu zhes brda' dang bsdur gnas pa b+ha dang
NK107(tse)001:2620: se zhes ring thung du byed 'phrul dang ra ri
NK107(tse)001:2621: a kring sang kar ki ta dang smer ti zhes
NK107(tse)001:2622: bya bas de la brten pa'i rjes su 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:2623: dang ldog pas a +aa i +ai la sogs te
NK107(tse)001:2624: a li dbyangs kyi yi ge rnams la gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:2625: bye brag pa las rnam par dag pa'i las kyi
NK107(tse)001:2626: rnam par spyod pa ste 'dis ni tshangs pa'i tshigs
NK107(tse)001:2627: su gcad pa phyed dang lnga la dbang ba dag
NK107(tse)001:2628: 'byung ngo 'phrul byed kyi tshigs su gcad pa phyed
NK107(tse)001:2629: dang gnyis te de tsam gyi tshigs sdebs rnams la
NK107(tse)001:2630: mkhas par 'gyur ro yang gong ma'i 'gro ldog las
NK107(tse)001:2631: ka kha ga g+ha nga la sogs te ka li
NK107(tse)001:2632: gsal byed kyi yi ge rnams la gnas pas de'i
NK107(tse)001:2633: bye brag gi 'phrul bas tshangs pa'i tshigs su bcad
NK107(tse)001:2634: pa gsum la dbang ba ni snga ma'i 'dres kyis
NK107(tse)001:2635: shes par bya'o de ltar yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK107(tse)001:2636: brgyad kyi steng du 'di ni bod kyi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:2637: thams cad kyi 'gyur gyi yi ge li gnyis dang
NK107(tse)001:2638: rgyu mtshan gyi 'gyur gyi yi ge ri gnyis bod
NK107(tse)001:2639: kyi rnal 'byor pas sdebs shes pas yi ge lnga
NK107(tse)001:2640: bcu po de 'gyur gyis rnam par bcad cing 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:2641: ba las tshangs pa'i gnas re re la brgya phrag
NK107(tse)001:2642: gnyis gnyis su 'gyur ro de ltar pam gnas re
NK107(tse)001:2643: re la yi ge lnga po bzhi bzhis nges par
NK107(tse)001:2644: 'dren pa dang barjoda pa dang 'jug pa'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:2645: las bka' dang bstan chos rnams kyi las kyi rtog
NK107(tse)001:2646: pa nges sbyor ba la mkhas par nges so de
NK107(tse)001:2647: ltar stong dang gzugs la sogs pa'i gnas lnga las
NK107(tse)001:2648: gzhan stong dang de'i yan lag rnams la nye bar
NK107(tse)001:2649: spyod pa yin pas na de yang barjoda pa'i tshe
NK107(tse)001:2650: rdo rje'i lce dang kha dong kha dang ral gri
NK107(tse)001:2651: dang 'khor lo'i lces barjoda la 'dren pa chu dang
NK107(tse)001:2652: sa dang me dang rlung nas 'dren la 'jug pa
NK107(tse)001:2653: zug pa dang byer ba dang snyoms pa dang 'khrug
NK107(tse)001:2654: pa dag yin no 'phrul byed ni 'grin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2655: rkan dang so dang mchu'i bsgyur byed las shes par
NK107(tse)001:2656: bya'o tshigs su bcad pa ni yi ge'i 'go dang
NK107(tse)001:2657: 'jug gi ming ni rnam grangs la brten nas shes
NK107(tse)001:2658: par bya'o 'di ltar 'di nyid shes pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:2659: ni sprul pa'i sku sangs rgyas las dang nyon mongs
NK107(tse)001:2660: pa bcom pas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2661: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen par ldan pas na mi
NK107(tse)001:2662: shes log shes las 'das pa'i yon tan dang tshangs
NK107(tse)001:2663: pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas pas kyang reg par sbyor
NK107(tse)001:2664: ro zhes yan lag gnyis pa lha tshangs pa'i khang
NK107(tse)001:2665: bu rnam par brtsegs pa sgra'i gnas pa la bslabs
NK107(tse)001:2666: pas thams cad chos nyid du 'char bar bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:2667: da ni yan lag gi don gsum pa khyab 'jug
NK107(tse)001:2668: gi sbra'i gnas gzhan la bslabs pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:2669: don rtogs ye shes su 'char bar bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2670: khyab pa la lnga ste 'byung ba la khyab pas
NK107(tse)001:2671: 'byung rtags mtshon pa la brten nas snang ba chos
NK107(tse)001:2672: nyid la sbyar ba dang lus la khyab pa la
NK107(tse)001:2673: brten nas lus na tsha dang sdug basngala las grol
NK107(tse)001:2674: bar bstan pa dang barjoda pa khyab pa la brten
NK107(tse)001:2675: nas sgra tshig thams cad rang bzhin barjoda du med
NK107(tse)001:2676: pa'i bzlas par 'gyur ba dang ngag la khyab pa
NK107(tse)001:2677: la brten nas a li dang ka li'i 'phreng bas
NK107(tse)001:2678: tshig dang don sbyor gyi man ngag la mkhas par
NK107(tse)001:2679: 'gyur ba'o yid la khyab pa la brten nas ting
NK107(tse)001:2680: nge 'dzin 'bum phrag gcig stan gcig gi steng du
NK107(tse)001:2681: skye bar 'gyur ba'o 'jug pa ni bzhi ste chu'i
NK107(tse)001:2682: dus gsum gyi 'jug pa la brten nas 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:2683: kyi chos thams cad bsdud pa dang sa'i 'jug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2684: dus gsum la brten nas sems dang sems kyi snang
NK107(tse)001:2685: ba brtan par byed pa dang me'i 'jug pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:2686: gsum la brten nas phyi dang nang gi snang ba
NK107(tse)001:2687: rnams smin par byed pa dang rlung gis dus gsum
NK107(tse)001:2688: gyi 'jug pa la brten nas 'khor 'das lus sems
NK107(tse)001:2689: kyi byed pa rnams 'byed cing bskyod par byed ba'o
NK107(tse)001:2690: khyab 'jug gi gnas ni bcu drug ste gnyis dang
NK107(tse)001:2691: ni khyab pa'i gnas pas phyi nang sgra'i gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:2692: rnam 'phrul la bslab pa ni 'jug pa'i gnas stongs
NK107(tse)001:2693: pa dang nye bar mched pa la bslab pa ste
NK107(tse)001:2694: de yang dang po a la'i tshig la rim dang
NK107(tse)001:2695: gcig char du sbyang ngo de yang brtson 'grus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2696: bye brag gis zla ba bdun dang bco lnga dang
NK107(tse)001:2697: lo gsum gyi bar la nges par sbyangs shing bslab
NK107(tse)001:2698: pas rnam par shes pa'i bya ba sna tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:2699: la legs par spyod pa ni khyab par byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2700: sgra don la sbyangs pa'o 'jug pa ni ka li'i
NK107(tse)001:2701: rnam pa rim gyis pa dang gcig char ba la
NK107(tse)001:2702: sbyangs pas yang gong dang 'dra ba'o de ltar byas
NK107(tse)001:2703: pa la khyab 'jug gi barjoda pa dag pa las
NK107(tse)001:2704: rang gi lus ngag gi tshad zin pa dang rnam
NK107(tse)001:2705: par dag pas khams rnam pa gsum gyis ngo bo
NK107(tse)001:2706: nyid mthong ba dag tu 'gyur ro lnga dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:2707: pa ni mig gis mthong ba dag pa la bslab
NK107(tse)001:2708: pa dang rna ba dang sna dang lce dang lus
NK107(tse)001:2709: kyi mthong ba rnam par dag pa la bslab pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2710: mig gi kha dog dang dbyibs kyi bye brag rnams
NK107(tse)001:2711: sna tshogs pa la rim gyis pa dang thams cad
NK107(tse)001:2712: sna tshogs pa la bslab pa brtson 'grus kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:2713: pa yis zla ba gsum dang drug dang bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:2714: su sbyangs pas phyi snang ba 'gyur bas rdul phra
NK107(tse)001:2715: rab kyi grangs tshad zin pa dang nang phung po
NK107(tse)001:2716: 'gyur bas bya ba'i rnam pa gang la yang mi
NK107(tse)001:2717: 'jug pa nyid do de nas rim gyis lkog tu
NK107(tse)001:2718: gyur pa'i gzugs kyi rnam pa rnams mig gi dbang
NK107(tse)001:2719: pos legs par mthong ba ni dpag tshad brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:2720: stong dang khri'i bye brag tu gsal ba ni mig
NK107(tse)001:2721: gi 'jig rten pa'i rten gyis rgyu nye bar stongs
NK107(tse)001:2722: pa tsam la brten nas mthong ba'o de nas rna
NK107(tse)001:2723: ba la bslab pa ni de dag ni rlung gis
NK107(tse)001:2724: sbyangs te pi wang dang gling bu dang rnga dang
NK107(tse)001:2725: dra ba rgyud mngas dang bum ldir gyi rnga dang
NK107(tse)001:2726: ha ra dang ha ra chen po la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:2727: gang mos pa la sbyang pa ste 'di dag gi
NK107(tse)001:2728: dus na rlung rab phu dal ba rten pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2729: rlung dang sgra rab tu bsre ba dang shes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2730: dbang po rna bar gtad pa gnad yin no de
NK107(tse)001:2731: ltar zla ba gcig dang gnyis dang bzhi byas na
NK107(tse)001:2732: phyir 'byung ba'i thos pa tsam gyis lus ngag la
NK107(tse)001:2733: rtags 'ga' 'byung nang rig bcas kyi lkog gyur gyi
NK107(tse)001:2734: sgra thos pas snyam pa'i nyams la brten nas zag
NK107(tse)001:2735: pa dang bcas pa'i rna ba'i mngon bar shes pa
NK107(tse)001:2736: dum bur 'char ba'o de nas sna'i mthong ba rnam
NK107(tse)001:2737: par dag pa la bslab pa ni spos sbyar ma
NK107(tse)001:2738: la sogs te dri sna tshogs pa la bslabs pas
NK107(tse)001:2739: sna'i mthong ba rnam par dag pa 'byung ba ni
NK107(tse)001:2740: 'di'i dus na rlung nang du bag tsam bzung ba
NK107(tse)001:2741: dang shes pa sna la gzung ba dang lus glang
NK107(tse)001:2742: po che'i nyal stabs kyis rnam pa ltar bya ba
NK107(tse)001:2743: yin no de ltar zla ba gnyis dang bzhi dang
NK107(tse)001:2744: drug tu bslabs pas gang la reg cing dri bsnams
NK107(tse)001:2745: pa la brten nas de'i chos nyid bsam pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2746: dbang po'i rnam pa rnams shes par 'gyur ro de
NK107(tse)001:2747: nas yang lce'i mthong ba rnam par dag pa la
NK107(tse)001:2748: bslab pa ni bu ram dang 'dza' ti rlon pa
NK107(tse)001:2749: dang ba lang ke rlon pa dang ka la hi'i
NK107(tse)001:2750: lo ma dang san 'ji li'i 'bras bu dang tsang
NK107(tse)001:2751: ka'i skang bcag pa'i snying po rnams legs par sbyar
NK107(tse)001:2752: te rdza gzhan du longs ma spyad pa'i so ma'i
NK107(tse)001:2753: nang du rgun chang gi khu ba dang legs par
NK107(tse)001:2754: cha snyams sbal la bcad du btub pa dang mi'i
NK107(tse)001:2755: rkang mar dang rta rkyang gi tshil bus legs par
NK107(tse)001:2756: dril la rdza'i kha na yar rlung mi 'chor bar
NK107(tse)001:2757: legs par gcad la zhag rnal 'byor pa'i lo grangs
NK107(tse)001:2758: tsam zhig bzhag pas sir sgra dang tsir sgra 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2759: de nas grul bum gyi skad phra mos sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2760: pa 'byung ngo de nas zhag 'ga' na yal ba
NK107(tse)001:2761: dag tu 'gyur te 'di'i dus na chang sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2762: pas bsil nas zhag gsum du bzhag la de nas
NK107(tse)001:2763: dad ldan stan bde bar bcas la gan rkyal du
NK107(tse)001:2764: nyal la bla ma'am rdo rje mched dam tshig dang
NK107(tse)001:2765: ldan pa zhig gis sran ma'i rdog ma tsam zhig
NK107(tse)001:2766: lce'i steng du bzhag go de ltar nyi ma re
NK107(tse)001:2767: la lo grangs tsam re bzhag mtshan mo bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:2768: su bzhag de ltar zla ba gsum du bya'o 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:2769: dus su 'bras sam rab tu 'jam pa'i kha zas
NK107(tse)001:2770: rten shes pa lce'i steng du a dkar po bsam
NK107(tse)001:2771: ste de la gtad de 'di'i dus su ci barjooda
NK107(tse)001:2772: pa tsam chos nyid kyi rang sgrar 'gyur te sems
NK107(tse)001:2773: can gzhan la phan pa dang bde ba'i don nges
NK107(tse)001:2774: par 'grub bo de nas gzhan gyi barjoda pa tsam
NK107(tse)001:2775: la brten nas ngag barjoda pa'i dbang pos bsam pa
NK107(tse)001:2776: rnams shes par 'gyur ro 'byung ba spo ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:2777: rnams kyang nges par 'grub bo 'di ni 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2778: so so'i lus kyi lo dang zla ba dang zhag
NK107(tse)001:2779: dang nyi ma dang dus nges pa la 'jug pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2780: yang lus kyi mthong ba rnam par dag pa la
NK107(tse)001:2781: bslab pa ni rtag tu lus la seng ldeng gi
NK107(tse)001:2782: chus khrus bya zhing til mar gyis basku'o lag pa
NK107(tse)001:2783: dang rkang pa'i tshigs rnams su mar sna tshogs pas
NK107(tse)001:2784: byug mthil bzhi la 'byung ba gnad kyi rten 'brel
NK107(tse)001:2785: zhes bya ste sa'i bcud sa zhag gis lag pa
NK107(tse)001:2786: g.yas me'i tsan dan gyi thal bas g.yon chu'i tsan
NK107(tse)001:2787: dan dkar po'i thig les rkang pa g.yon rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:2788: sems can sna tshogs pa'i kha rlangs kyis rkang mthil
NK107(tse)001:2789: g.yas su gdug go de nas stan bde ba'i steng
NK107(tse)001:2790: du seng ge'i nyal lugs su nyal te skyes pa
NK107(tse)001:2791: yin na mchan khung g.yas su dar men gyi ldo
NK107(tse)001:2792: bzhug stong dar gyis mi dam tsam du bcing smad
NK107(tse)001:2793: du ga bur gyi thig le thams cad du bya'o
NK107(tse)001:2794: 'di ltar zla ba lnga byas na lus mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:2795: ba gnyis dang bzhi dang brgyad dang bcu drug dang
NK107(tse)001:2796: sum cu rtsa gnyis dang drug cu rtsa bzhi la
NK107(tse)001:2797: sogs par sprul zhing gzhan gyis lus la reg pa
NK107(tse)001:2798: tsam gyis so so las kyi sdug basngala dang tshe
NK107(tse)001:2799: tshad la sogs pa shes par 'gyur ro de ltar
NK107(tse)001:2800: slob pa'i dus thams cad du nyan thos dang so
NK107(tse)001:2801: so skye bo la sogs pas mi mthong bar bya
NK107(tse)001:2802: ba ni dam tshig go drug ces pa ni lha
NK107(tse)001:2803: dang lha min dang mi dang byol song dang yi
NK107(tse)001:2804: dwags dang dmyal ba'i 'jug pa yan lag dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:2805: pa la bslab par bya'o de yang de 'di dag
NK107(tse)001:2806: gi dus su dus rnam pa bzhis brtsis te 'byung
NK107(tse)001:2807: ba dang 'jug pa dang gnas pa dang ldog pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2808: dus bazhi'o de yang lha'i 'jug pa dpyid zla ra
NK107(tse)001:2809: ba 'byung ba dbyar gnas pa ston ldog pa dgun
NK107(tse)001:2810: no lha min gyis de'i 'dres kyis 'bring po bzhi
NK107(tse)001:2811: mi'i tha chung bazhi'o lhag ma gsum po ni zhag
NK107(tse)001:2812: gi byer zug dus bcu gnyis dang sbyar ro de
NK107(tse)001:2813: yang chu dang sa'i zug pa gnyis dang byer ba
NK107(tse)001:2814: gnyis byol song gi 'jug pa dang 'byung ba dang
NK107(tse)001:2815: gnas pa dang ldog pa'o de gnyis kyi snyoms pa
NK107(tse)001:2816: gnyis dang me dang rlung gi zug pa gnyis yi
NK107(tse)001:2817: dwags so de gnyis kyi byer ba gnyis dang snyoms
NK107(tse)001:2818: pa gnyis de bzhi la dmyal ba'i 'jug pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2819: 'byung ba dang ldog pa'o de la lha'i 'jug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2820: dus na chu'i rten cing 'brel ba sna tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:2821: byas pas lha'i skad sna tshogs pa shes te de'i
NK107(tse)001:2822: grangs dang barjoda lugs ni 'og nas ston te de
NK107(tse)001:2823: bzhin du 'byung ba sa'i gnas pa me'i ldog pa
NK107(tse)001:2824: rlung gi rten 'brel byas pas lha'i skad sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2825: pa shes pa ni de ltar zla ba bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:2826: rdzogs par byas pa las 'byung bar nges so de
NK107(tse)001:2827: bzhin du lha min dang mi la yang 'adre'o byol
NK107(tse)001:2828: song dang gsum po ni dus de dag las ma
NK107(tse)001:2829: nor ba'i rtsis kyis zin par byas la sa dang
NK107(tse)001:2830: chu dang me dang rlung gi spo ba dang spel
NK107(tse)001:2831: ba'i las sna tshogs pa byas pas nges par 'grub
NK107(tse)001:2832: pa ni yang lo gcig tu zla ba gsum gsum
NK107(tse)001:2833: du byas pas yang 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra don shes
NK107(tse)001:2834: pas lha'i gnas dang phrad pas mig gi mngon shes
NK107(tse)001:2835: 'grub la lha min gyis rna ba'i mngon shes 'grub
NK107(tse)001:2836: la mis sna byol song gis lce'i yi dwags kyis
NK107(tse)001:2837: lus kyi dmyal bas yid kyi 'gyu ba dang 'gyu
NK107(tse)001:2838: ba ma yin pa'i mngon par shes pa rnams 'grub
NK107(tse)001:2839: bo gsum gyis zhes pa ni barjoda pa'i sems rkyen
NK107(tse)001:2840: sems las byung rang bzhin sems kyi mthong ba rnam
NK107(tse)001:2841: par dag pa'o de yang barjoda pa'i gzhi ni gcig
NK107(tse)001:2842: gcig gcig zhes pa la zla ba gnyis bar ma
NK107(tse)001:2843: chad par zla ba gnyis sbyangs pas /
NK107(tse)001:2844: thig le nyag gcig du ma dang cha shas dang
NK107(tse)001:2845: bral ba'i nyams don rgyud la skye'o des sems stong
NK107(tse)001:2846: ba ngos bzung dang bral ba'i sgra don rgyud la
NK107(tse)001:2847: skye'o de nas sems kyi rkyen la sbyangs pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2848: brgya phrag 'bum zhes pa la zla ba gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:2849: sbyangs pas sems las byung ba de dag gi tshad
NK107(tse)001:2850: zin par 'gyur ro de nas rang bzhin du barjooda
NK107(tse)001:2851: pa grangs bye brag sna tshogs pa la zla ba
NK107(tse)001:2852: gnyis su sbyangs pas sems kyi rnam par mi rtog
NK107(tse)001:2853: pa'i ye shes kyi tshad zin par 'gyur ro gzhan
NK107(tse)001:2854: las zhes pa de dag nyid la brgya brgya ste
NK107(tse)001:2855: zhes pa ste de yang gcig gcig pa la nyi
NK107(tse)001:2856: ma bcu de bzhin gnyis gnyis zhes barjoda pa nyi
NK107(tse)001:2857: ma bcu de bzhin gsum gsum dang bzhi bzhi dang
NK107(tse)001:2858: lnga lnga dang drug drug dang bdun bdun dang brgyad
NK107(tse)001:2859: brgyad dang dgu dgu dang bcu bcu zhes pa'i bar
NK107(tse)001:2860: la byas pas nyi ma brgya dang de re re
NK107(tse)001:2861: la byas pas na'o de nas bcu drug po'i rim
NK107(tse)001:2862: pa dang bdun te brgya brgya la nyi ma gcig
NK107(tse)001:2863: de bzhin stong stong dang khri khri dang 'bum 'bum
NK107(tse)001:2864: dang bye ba bye ba zhes bya ba dang sa
NK107(tse)001:2865: ya sa ya zhes bya ba dang grangs med grangs
NK107(tse)001:2866: med zhes pa dang dung phyur dung phyur zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:2867: dang phyal phyol phyal phyol zhes pa dang yal yol
NK107(tse)001:2868: yal yol zhes pa dang nyar nyer nyar nyer zhes
NK107(tse)001:2869: pa dang ther 'bum ther 'bum zhes pa dang sang
NK107(tse)001:2870: seng sang seng zhes pa dang 'bar 'bur 'bar 'bur
NK107(tse)001:2871: zhes pa dang rang ring rang ring zhes pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2872: barjoda med barjoda med zhes pa la sogs pa la
NK107(tse)001:2873: zhag re re ste bcu drug tu byas pas khyab
NK107(tse)001:2874: 'jug las kyi mtha' nye bar ston pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:2875: dag tu 'gyur te 'bras bu tshigs su bcad pa
NK107(tse)001:2876: gang la mos pa tsam gyis nges par shes pa
NK107(tse)001:2877: dag tu 'gyur ro de nas chos thams cad barjoda
NK107(tse)001:2878: du med pa'i don khong du chud par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:2879: de ltar yang sangs rgyas phal po che'i mdo las
NK107(tse)001:2880: grangs kyi mtha' chos thams cad barjoda du med pa
NK107(tse)001:2881: la bskyal nas yod do de ltar bslabs pa las
NK107(tse)001:2882: zur zhes sgra 'jug pa'i rgyal mtshan phud phyed zhes
NK107(tse)001:2883: sgra bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan la brten nas tshig dang
NK107(tse)001:2884: tshig ma yin pa'i sgro 'dogs gcod par byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2885: las kyi rgyu skye bar byed pa ni slob ma
NK107(tse)001:2886: mtshan nyid drug dang ldan pa ste bla ma gus
NK107(tse)001:2887: shing dam tshig ldan dad dang gtong bar nus pa
NK107(tse)001:2888: dang khro dang dregs pa rnam par spangs zhes pas
NK107(tse)001:2889: drug tshang pa dang de'i steng du byang sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:2890: sdom pa rnams dang ldan pa dang des kyang mi
NK107(tse)001:2891: phan te rdzogs pa chen po 'di nyid bsgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:2892: dang nyan pa dang bshad pa dang 'dzin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:2893: klog pa dang 'chang ba dang tshul bzhin du yid
NK107(tse)001:2894: la byed pas mngon sum gyis don rgyud la brten
NK107(tse)001:2895: pa gcig la gong ma'i don thogs pa med par
NK107(tse)001:2896: rgyud la skye'o de yang ji ltar skye zhes na
NK107(tse)001:2897: nges par 'khor 'das 'byed par byed pa'i sgra tshig
NK107(tse)001:2898: 'khrul gyi rnam pa las gong du bstan pa'i grangs
NK107(tse)001:2899: kyi zhes bya ste de la brten nas 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:2900: gnyis med du la zla ba'i gnad de de'i barjoda
NK107(tse)001:2901: bya gcig la sogs pa rlung dang bsre ba shes
NK107(tse)001:2902: na rgyun du shes bya ste zag pa med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:2903: mngon par shes pa lnga 'grub ste de ltar grub
NK107(tse)001:2904: pa'i gnad kyis bka' dang bstan chos thams cad la
NK107(tse)001:2905: mkhas par 'gyur ro zhes yan lag gi don gsum
NK107(tse)001:2906: pa khyab 'jug gi gnas gzhan la bslab pa la
NK107(tse)001:2907: brten nas don rtogs ye shes su 'char bar bstan
NK107(tse)001:2908: nas da ni yan lag gi don bzhi pa ping
NK107(tse)001:2909: ka la'i sgra'i gnas gzhan la brten nas 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:2910: pa dang 'das pa rnams 'du bar bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:2911: ping zhes 'jug pa las kyi 'byung bzhi gnad la
NK107(tse)001:2912: bor ba ni thabs khyad par yin la 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2913: las kyi 'phrul 'khor gyis 'byung ba bzhi bcud la
NK107(tse)001:2914: bor ba ni sgra'i gnas ma grub na spogs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:2915: gnas pa las kyi sde bas bka' la 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:2916: bzhi dkrugs pa'i gnad kyis lus kyi 'byung bzhi mnyam
NK107(tse)001:2917: par bya'o ldog pa las kyi 'gyur la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:2918: 'byung ba go bzlog pa'i byed pa ni sgra thams
NK107(tse)001:2919: cad la mkhas par bya ba ste 'di dag ni
NK107(tse)001:2920: 'og nas ston no ga la'i zhes bya ba ni
NK107(tse)001:2921: drang srong chen po mngon par shes pa mnga' bas
NK107(tse)001:2922: gzugs 'dab bzang chen por sprul nas nam mkha' nas
NK107(tse)001:2923: sgra ka hring bya ba las dbyangs sum brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:2924: drug cu 'byung ba ni sngon 'byung du sku'i spros
NK107(tse)001:2925: pa rnam pa sna tshogs pa las mos pa khyad
NK107(tse)001:2926: par du skye ba'i rgyu brgya dang nyi shu yod
NK107(tse)001:2927: pas de'i bya ba ma log pa las gdul bya
NK107(tse)001:2928: ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyis rnal 'byor pa'i lus la
NK107(tse)001:2929: sgra dbyangs kyi bye brag brgya dang nyi shur byung
NK107(tse)001:2930: ba ni 'di dag la bslab par bya ba'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:2931: brgya dang nyi shur yod pa ni rnal 'byor pa
NK107(tse)001:2932: dad pa dang ldan pa zhig gis sngon du tshogs
NK107(tse)001:2933: bsags pa'i bya ba ci rigs par byas la de
NK107(tse)001:2934: nas grogs spangs te dgon pa la sogs pa dur
NK107(tse)001:2935: khrod dam rab tu dben par song ste rang gcig
NK107(tse)001:2936: pu mi mi rgyu ba'i sar song la lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2937: bye brag dbyangs blang pa ni 'di'i dus na lus
NK107(tse)001:2938: ji ltar bde bar bcos la lus kyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:2939: bzhi la dmigs pa gsal bar gtad la de yang
NK107(tse)001:2940: bskyed byed dang po'i tsakra kha dog dkar po dran
NK107(tse)001:2941: pa 'dus pa ser po ro rnams 'dus pa dmar
NK107(tse)001:2942: po rtse mo rnam par bkod pa lnga ljang khu
NK107(tse)001:2943: ni so so la dmigs pa gtod pa'i tshe na
NK107(tse)001:2944: gsal bar bya ste lag pa g.yas 'gal me bskor
NK107(tse)001:2945: ba ltar bya ste ngag tu sa r+aa sa r+aa
NK107(tse)001:2946: zhes pa la nyi ma gcig tu sbyangs pas lus
NK107(tse)001:2947: kyi rtsa rnams 'khrog pa'i dgos pa yod do 'di
NK107(tse)001:2948: rnams kyi dus su sems ni bskyed byed la gtad
NK107(tse)001:2949: do de nas sor mo lnga rim gyis brkyang bskum
NK107(tse)001:2950: dang gnyis 'dus kyi sgra 'byin pa la nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:2951: lnga ste drug de dag gi dus na sde tshan
NK107(tse)001:2952: dang po'i yi ge rim gyis so de nas yang
NK107(tse)001:2953: lag pa g.yon pa gong ltar byas la ngag tu
NK107(tse)001:2954: a hring zhes dbyangs dang ldan pa la sems snga
NK107(tse)001:2955: ma dang 'dra'o sor mo snga ma ltar byas la
NK107(tse)001:2956: sde tshan gnyis pa'i yi ge rim gyis so de
NK107(tse)001:2957: nas 'go g.yas su yid tsam bsgril zhing ngag tu
NK107(tse)001:2958: a rab tu thung bar barjoda pa dang yang g.yon
NK107(tse)001:2959: du bsgril zhing ngag tu sing ha zhes barjoda la
NK107(tse)001:2960: de nas dbus su la ngag tu kung zhes ring
NK107(tse)001:2961: bar barjoda do de ltar bco lnga po 'dis ni
NK107(tse)001:2962: 'dod pa'i don nye bar spel zhing sangs rgyas kyi
NK107(tse)001:2963: bden pa 'dzin par 'gyur ro de nas yang rang
NK107(tse)001:2964: gi snying khar thal mo g.yas pa bkab ste lag
NK107(tse)001:2965: pa'i sor mo rim gyis brdeg cing ngag tu sde
NK107(tse)001:2966: tshan gsum pa'i yi ge rnams rim gyis barjoda par
NK107(tse)001:2967: bya zhing sems dran pa 'dul pa la gtad pa
NK107(tse)001:2968: la nyi ma lnga bya'o de nas g.yon pa'i sor
NK107(tse)001:2969: mos bya zhing sde tshan bzhi pa'o de nas mig
NK107(tse)001:2970: g.yas su blta ba la dang g.yon dang dbus dang
NK107(tse)001:2971: steng dang 'og dang dal gyis lta zhing sde tshan
NK107(tse)001:2972: lnga pa'i yi ge rnams rim gyis rab tu gdung
NK107(tse)001:2973: ba'i dbyangs kyis barjoda par bya'o de ltar zla ba
NK107(tse)001:2974: phyed du byas pas khyad par gyi sems kyi bya
NK107(tse)001:2975: rdzogs pa dag yin no de nas yang lus glo
NK107(tse)001:2976: g.yas phabs te nyal ba la zhag lnga ngag rab
NK107(tse)001:2977: tu lcong ba'i dbyangs kyis ya zhes barjoda do sems
NK107(tse)001:2978: ni ro rnams kyi 'khor lo la gtad do g.yon
NK107(tse)001:2979: phab pa la yang lnga'i dus na yang zhes rab
NK107(tse)001:2980: tu 'phra bar barjoda do de bzhin du gan rkyal
NK107(tse)001:2981: du dang ngag ra kha sbub pa la rag sha
NK107(tse)001:2982: de nas stong sgo ig skad 'don pa la lnga
NK107(tse)001:2983: ste nyer lnga ro'i 'khor lo la sems gtad pa
NK107(tse)001:2984: ni lus kyi sdig pa ma lus pa dag par
NK107(tse)001:2985: 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do de ni lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:2986: bya ba la brten nas chos nyid kyi rang sgra
NK107(tse)001:2987: la brten nas nyams su myong ba skye ba yin
NK107(tse)001:2988: no sug bzhi sa la btsugs te byol song gi
NK107(tse)001:2989: skad sna tshogs pa barjoda pa la nyi ma bcu
NK107(tse)001:2990: sems rtse mo la gtad do langs pa la bcu
NK107(tse)001:2991: ngag tu h'u 'gugs pa'i tshul du barjoda lag pa
NK107(tse)001:2992: gnyis 'gal me bskor ba'i tshul du bya zhing ngag
NK107(tse)001:2993: tig zhes 'dren pa'i tshul du barjoda la bcu langs
NK107(tse)001:2994: te rkang pa gyad kyi dor stabs lta bu la
NK107(tse)001:2995: bcu ngag tu ha zhes sdigs pa'i tshul gyis so
NK107(tse)001:2996: pho ba g.yas bcud cing ngag tu phata barjoda pa
NK107(tse)001:2997: la bcu g.yon du bcud zhing ngag tu ram barjoda
NK107(tse)001:2998: pa la bcu de nas lus kyi bya ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:2999: sna tshogs pa bya ba ni rgyug pa dang 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3000: ba dang 'dug pa dang g.yas brkyang pa dang g.yon
NK107(tse)001:3001: brkyang pa dang thal mo snying khar sbyar ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3002: thal mo'i sgra rab tu mi drag tsam brdab pa
NK107(tse)001:3003: dang gzug bzhi gyen la blang ba dang gzhu 'gengs
NK107(tse)001:3004: ba ltar bya ba dang rdo 'degs pa ltar bya
NK107(tse)001:3005: ba dang phyag bsgyur ba dang lus kyi bya ba
NK107(tse)001:3006: sna tshogs pa bya zhing ngag tu yid la ji
NK107(tse)001:3007: ltar dran pa'i tshig rnams barjoda par bya'o de rnams
NK107(tse)001:3008: la sogs lnga ste brgya dang nyi shu byas pas
NK107(tse)001:3009: rang bzhin du lus kyi sdig pa ma lus pa
NK107(tse)001:3010: dag pa dang mchog tu lus khams gsum las grol
NK107(tse)001:3011: ba dang thun mong du lus kyi zhen pa bzlog
NK107(tse)001:3012: par 'gyur ro 'di dag byed pa'i tshe na lus
NK107(tse)001:3013: ngag gi zhen pa rang log pa dag kyang 'byung
NK107(tse)001:3014: bar nges so rang bzhin du lus kyi ba spu
NK107(tse)001:3015: gyen la langs pa dang gdong nas mchi ma 'dzag
NK107(tse)001:3016: pa dang skad sna tshogs pa 'don snying 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:3017: dag 'byung ngo de ni lus rang bzhin gyis rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:3018: pa chen po la sbyor ba'i gnad do de dag
NK107(tse)001:3019: gi dus thams cad du gzhan gyis ma mthong ba
NK107(tse)001:3020: dang ma thos pa dang rang bar ma chad pa
NK107(tse)001:3021: gal che'o de bzhin ngag dang zhes pa ni dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:3022: kyi sde tshan nges par 'byed pa dag ste rab
NK107(tse)001:3023: tu bsing ba dang spung ba dang gzir ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3024: lcong ba dang gdung ba dang ring ba dang thung
NK107(tse)001:3025: ba dang 'phra ba dang gsal ba dang mi phyed
NK107(tse)001:3026: pa dang 'dar ba dang rengs pa dang khugs pa
NK107(tse)001:3027: dang lteng pa dang mer ba dang then pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3028: 'theng pa dang 'khor ba dang mi 'gul ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3029: breng nge ba dang dung nge ba dang sha ta
NK107(tse)001:3030: ba dang ka ta pa dang cang ka te dang
NK107(tse)001:3031: ke la ka dang mi ri li dang gzhad pa
NK107(tse)001:3032: dang 'dzum pa dang rab tu bzhad pa dang 'bar
NK107(tse)001:3033: ba'i 'od dang sum cu dbyangs kyii gzhi ste de
NK107(tse)001:3034: re re la 'dren bzhi bzhir shes par bya'o la
NK107(tse)001:3035: lo nas ring zhing 'jam par drang ngo lo de
NK107(tse)001:3036: zhes gsal zhing dag par drang ngo lo de she
NK107(tse)001:3037: zhes ring zhing nges par drang ngo she la lo
NK107(tse)001:3038: zhes yangs shing gsing par drang ngo shes ma lo
NK107(tse)001:3039: de zhes dal zhing khugs par drang ngo la li
NK107(tse)001:3040: ma lo de zhes thung zhing phyed par drang ngo
NK107(tse)001:3041: yang lo de zhes ring zhing khugs par dang ngo
NK107(tse)001:3042: a le ma lo de zhes thung zhing gsal bar
NK107(tse)001:3043: drang ka'i zhes lding zhing then par drang ngo ka'i
NK107(tse)001:3044: lo de zhes 'khor zhing bsing bar drang ngo la
NK107(tse)001:3045: la dang la la dang zhes lding zhing thebs par
NK107(tse)001:3046: drang ngo zhes thung zhing then par drang ngo am
NK107(tse)001:3047: zhes 'dar zhing des par drang ngo h+aum zhes ring
NK107(tse)001:3048: zhing 'phra bar drang ngo +aahh+aum zhes gnan zhing 'gugs
NK107(tse)001:3049: par ro ram zhes gsal zhing 'bar ba ro kring
NK107(tse)001:3050: zhes 'khor zhing lding ba'o hri zhes 'bar zhing des
NK107(tse)001:3051: pa'o 'ba' zhes gsal dang ldan par bya'o ha zhes
NK107(tse)001:3052: drag cing gsal bar ro ra r+aa zhes khugs cing
NK107(tse)001:3053: lding par ro a +aa zhes gsal zhing phyed par
NK107(tse)001:3054: ro si s+ai zhes 'dar zhing mi phyed par ro
NK107(tse)001:3055: li l+ai zhes sing la 'phru ba'o i +au zhes
NK107(tse)001:3056: 'dzum zhing dengs pa'o hi hi zhes dag cing sing
NK107(tse)001:3057: pa'o i +au zhes 'jam la rengs pa'o ko la
NK107(tse)001:3058: e zhes thung zhing gdung pa'o mu la o zhes
NK107(tse)001:3059: ring la dag pa'o kha kha ri zhes gzir zhing
NK107(tse)001:3060: che ba'o ra r+aa ri r+ai zhes 'bar zhing mched
NK107(tse)001:3061: pa'o sa r+aa sa r+ai zhes dag cing gdung par
NK107(tse)001:3062: bya'o hi hi b+he la zhes drag cing rdzogs par
NK107(tse)001:3063: bya'o lo hi g+ha zhes rab tu brtse bas so
NK107(tse)001:3064: na na zhes ldang zhing ldeng pas te de ltar
NK107(tse)001:3065: sum cus gong ma rnams dang rim gyis sbyar ba
NK107(tse)001:3066: la de ltar dbyangs re re la 'dren bzhi bzhir
NK107(tse)001:3067: byas te nyi ma bzhi bzhir byas pas 'dren brgya
NK107(tse)001:3068: dang nyi shu la rab tu ma yengs par bya
NK107(tse)001:3069: zhing sems dga' zhing gsal ba la gtad par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:3070: 'di'i dus na sgra che ba yang ma yin ha
NK107(tse)001:3071: cang chung ba yang ma yin la rab tu gsal
NK107(tse)001:3072: ba'i brdas mtshon na byin brlabs mngon sum du 'char
NK107(tse)001:3073: bar byed pa'o de ltar zla ba bzhi rdzogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3074: 'og tu sangs rgyas kyi gsung dbyangs cig gis dkyil
NK107(tse)001:3075: 'khor du go ba dag 'byung ngo de ltar byung
NK107(tse)001:3076: ba'i dus na bka' dang bstan chos rnams don dang
NK107(tse)001:3077: yi ge'i go nas shes par 'gyur ro sems la
NK107(tse)001:3078: yang zhes pa ni rlung phyir 'phen pa la nyi
NK107(tse)001:3079: ma nyi shu nang du thub pa la nyi shu
NK107(tse)001:3080: phyir 'phen nang du rngub pa phyed ma la nyi
NK107(tse)001:3081: shu g.yas nas rgyu ba la nyi shu g.yon nas
NK107(tse)001:3082: rgyu ba la nyi shu dbus nas rgyu ba la
NK107(tse)001:3083: nyi shu ste zla ba bzhir sbyang ngo 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:3084: na lus shin tu dal brten cing drang srong lta
NK107(tse)001:3085: bu'i 'dug stangs su 'dug pa gnad yin no sems
NK107(tse)001:3086: ni lus kyi bye brag gis chu dkyil dang sa
NK107(tse)001:3087: dang me dang rlung gi dkyil 'khor du gtad pa
NK107(tse)001:3088: gnad yin no 'di dag gi dus na khong nas
NK107(tse)001:3089: 'byung ba'i yi ge dang mgrin pa dang rkan dang
NK107(tse)001:3090: lce dang so dang mchu'i gnas nas 'byung ba'i yi
NK107(tse)001:3091: ge rnams la rim gyis rtsal sbyangs pas de dag
NK107(tse)001:3092: gi sgra don rnams kyang rim gyis shes par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:3093: ro de yang thog ma'i gsal byed kyi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:3094: la brten nas tshigs su gcad pa nyin re la
NK107(tse)001:3095: brgya phrag lnga dang de nas stong dang de nas
NK107(tse)001:3096: sum stong dang nyin re la 'bum phrag re re
NK107(tse)001:3097: dang bye ba dang sa ya la dbang thob par
NK107(tse)001:3098: 'gyur ro de dag rnams kyang don dang yi ge
NK107(tse)001:3099: la brten nas bde blag tu khong du chud par
NK107(tse)001:3100: 'gyur ro de'i phyir na yi ge khong dang mgrin
NK107(tse)001:3101: pa la sogs pa'i gang yin pa'i gong ma nas
NK107(tse)001:3102: tsam pa ste b+hud rda'i nges par barjoda pa'i gsung
NK107(tse)001:3103: shes shing barjoda pa tsam gyis kyang thun mong du
NK107(tse)001:3104: lus ngag gi bar chad nye bar zhi ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3105: 'khor 'du zhing bsod nams dang ldan pa dang 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3106: ba byams shing gdul bya rnams 'dul bar 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:3107: ni 'jig rten pa'i lha tshangs pa dang brgya byin
NK107(tse)001:3108: dang khyab 'jug dang 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs
NK107(tse)001:3109: med pa dang spyod pa rnams kyis kyang bsrung ba
NK107(tse)001:3110: dang skyob pa dang sbed pa dang bskyang ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3111: bde legs su 'grub par byed do de bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:3112: 'das pa'i lha la b+hud rda dang byang chub sems
NK107(tse)001:3113: dpa' dang rigs dang rigs kyi yum la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:3114: dpag tu med pa rnams kyis kyang gzugs ston pa
NK107(tse)001:3115: dang gsung bsgrag pa dang thugs kyi dgongs pa ji
NK107(tse)001:3116: ltar yin pa rnams ston pa dang rnal 'byor pa
NK107(tse)001:3117: de'i lus dang ngag dang yid la bde lugs su
NK107(tse)001:3118: byin gyis rlobs pa dag yin no de bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:3119: 'jig rten gyi mkha' 'gro ma ma mo bdun dang
NK107(tse)001:3120: sring mo dang zab mo dang rgad byed mo dang
NK107(tse)001:3121: dmar mo dang rab tu khros ma chen mo dang
NK107(tse)001:3122: 'bar ma dang kun tu 'bar ma la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:3123: rnams kyis kyang rnal 'byor pa de'i 'khor du 'dus
NK107(tse)001:3124: shing bde ba 'byin pa dang legs par gter ba
NK107(tse)001:3125: dang 'khor 'du zhing longs spyod rnams rdzogs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3126: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang myang ba dang lhag
NK107(tse)001:3127: pa dang bya ba gang yang ma rmongs pa dag
NK107(tse)001:3128: tu 'gyur ro de bzhin du 'das pa'i mkha' 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3129: ma bde gshegs rigs dang rdo rje dang rin po
NK107(tse)001:3130: che dang pad ma dang las kyi rigs la sogs
NK107(tse)001:3131: pa rnams rnal 'byor pa 'di nyid la 'du ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3132: phyir sngon du de dag gi sgra bsgrag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3133: a li mi li ha ha zhes pa dang e
NK107(tse)001:3134: dring e dring zhes pa dang se e zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:3135: la sogs pa dpag tu med pa drag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3136: yang rab 'um 'khro ba'i tshig zung zung zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:3137: dang rgyob rgyob zhes pa dang ma btamng shig ma
NK107(tse)001:3138: btamng shig zhes pa dang sod sod zhes pa'i sgra'i
NK107(tse)001:3139: bye brag rnams mkha' 'gro ma'i sgra yin par shes
NK107(tse)001:3140: na rnal 'byor pa de la dngos grub chen po
NK107(tse)001:3141: 'byung ste de ltar mkha' 'gro ma de rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:3142: skad gsal ba dang gdang pa dang rab tu yid
NK107(tse)001:3143: 'phrog par shes pa dang rnal 'byor pa des mig
NK107(tse)001:3144: dang rna ba dang sna dang lce dang lus dang
NK107(tse)001:3145: yid kyis te mig gi lkog tu 'gyur ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3146: shin tu lkog tu gyur pa rnams kyis gzugs mthong
NK107(tse)001:3147: ba dang de bzhin du rna ba sgra ste gzhan
NK107(tse)001:3148: yang ngo yid kyi mngon shes dang drug la nges
NK107(tse)001:3149: par spyad nas bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi bka'i
NK107(tse)001:3150: don nyid shes nas khong du chud pa'i rtags su
NK107(tse)001:3151: nyi ma re la tshig tshigs su gcad pa'i grangs
NK107(tse)001:3152: brgya dang stong dang khri dang 'bum rnams 'dzin par
NK107(tse)001:3153: 'gyur ba nyid kyis yang so so'i don dang yi
NK107(tse)001:3154: ge'i sgo nas gnas dang nges par sbyor shes par
NK107(tse)001:3155: 'gyur ro de ltar sbyor shes nas yang sprul pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3156: bya chu bsgyur zhes pa'i sgra la yang snyan par
NK107(tse)001:3157: barjoda pa'i b+hud rda'i gsung ni bsam gyis mi khyab
NK107(tse)001:3158: par 'phros pa'i don shes pas rnal 'byor pa de
NK107(tse)001:3159: sgra don la mkhas pa'i cho ga rdzogs pa'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:3160: yan lag gi don bzhi la ping g+ha la'i sgra'i
NK107(tse)001:3161: gnas gzhan la brten nas 'jig rten pa dang 'das
NK107(tse)001:3162: pa'i 'gro ba rnams 'du bar 'gyur ba bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:3163: da ni yan lag gi don lnga pa 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:3164: bzhi'i sgra'i gnas gzhan la brten nas sprul pa sku'i
NK107(tse)001:3165: sa bon nye bar bzhag pa bstan pa ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:3166: ba zhes pa ni gang 'byung bar byed na bem
NK107(tse)001:3167: po la brten nas rig bcas kyi mtshan nyid 'byung
NK107(tse)001:3168: bar byed la phyi rol gyi 'byung ba bzhi la
NK107(tse)001:3169: brten nas nang lus kyi 'byung ba bzhi 'byung bar
NK107(tse)001:3170: byed pas na 'byung ba zhes bya la nang lus
NK107(tse)001:3171: kyi 'byung ba bzhi la brten nas rig pa'i ye
NK107(tse)001:3172: shes mngon sum du 'byung bar byed pas na 'byung
NK107(tse)001:3173: ba zhes bya la rig pa mngon gsum la brten
NK107(tse)001:3174: nas sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thogs pa med par
NK107(tse)001:3175: 'byung bas na 'byung ba zhes bya'o de ltar 'byung
NK107(tse)001:3176: ba de rnams kyi sgra don ni dpal dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:3177: pa mdzes pa dang stobs sam nus pa la bya
NK107(tse)001:3178: ste mdzes pas ni chos nyid mngon sum du mthong
NK107(tse)001:3179: bar byed pa ni 'byung ba'i sgra la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:3180: mthong bas na nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3181: snang bas mdzes shing dpal ba'o de lta bu la
NK107(tse)001:3182: brten nas 'khor ba las pha rol du sgrol bar
NK107(tse)001:3183: byed pa la dpa' bo zhes bya'o de'i nus pas
NK107(tse)001:3184: las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad 'jom par byed
NK107(tse)001:3185: pa'o dpa' bar byed pa'i zhes pa ni sku rnam
NK107(tse)001:3186: pa gsum dang de las kyang khyad par du sprul
NK107(tse)001:3187: pa sku'i nus pa dngos su 'byin par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3188: de dag kyang gang la brten nas 'byung zhe na
NK107(tse)001:3189: chu dang sa dang me dang rlung dang bzhi dag
NK107(tse)001:3190: las de ltar 'byung ba bzhi po re re las
NK107(tse)001:3191: gnyis gnyis te ni 'byung ba tsha ba dang grang
NK107(tse)001:3192: ba'o gcig ni ma ning stongs pas na zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:3193: ste ma ning gis 'byung ba nam mkha' yin pas
NK107(tse)001:3194: btsir ma btub pa'o de pho dang mo'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:3195: las zhes pa ni chu pho las grang ba chu
NK107(tse)001:3196: mo las tsha ba de bzhin du sa yang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3197: me la gnyis rlung pho mo gnyis las rlung tsha
NK107(tse)001:3198: ba dang grang ba'i 'byung ba'i byed rgyu can du
NK107(tse)001:3199: byung bas ni 'gro ba'i skabs su yang mo tsha
NK107(tse)001:3200: ba shas che bas 'dod chags kyi nye rgyu can
NK107(tse)001:3201: yin la pho grang ba shas che bas zhe sdang
NK107(tse)001:3202: gi nye rgyu can yin la ma ning tsha grang
NK107(tse)001:3203: gang du yang ma phyed pas gti mug gi nye
NK107(tse)001:3204: rgyu can yin pa'o de ltar 'byung ba'i tsha grang
NK107(tse)001:3205: gi dbye ba las tsha ba'i 'byung ba mo la
NK107(tse)001:3206: stong phrag dag ni gnyis su 'gro ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:3207: chu'i chu la brgya dang nyer lnga 'o de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:3208: du chu'i sa dang chu'i me dang chu'i rlung la
NK107(tse)001:3209: brgya dang nyer lnga'o ste stong phrag gnyis so de
NK107(tse)001:3210: nas pho mo'i bye brag gnyis kyi 'dres kyis yang
NK107(tse)001:3211: stong phrag gnyis gnyis te stong phrag bzhi'i sgra don
NK107(tse)001:3212: ni de nyid la bslab par bya ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:3213: nyid kyi sgra'i rnam grangs shes pas grol ba'o gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3214: so de la bslab par bya ba ni dad pa
NK107(tse)001:3215: dang ldan pa'i skal ldan gyis tshogs bsags pa'i yan
NK107(tse)001:3216: lag rnam pa sna tshogs pa byas la rkyen gyis
NK107(tse)001:3217: mi gnod pa'i gnad khyad par can du rang gi
NK107(tse)001:3218: 'byung ba dang mthun par song la 'byung bzhi'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:3219: don la bslab pa ni 'og nas ston no de
NK107(tse)001:3220: ltar nyams su blangs pas 'byung ba so so'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:3221: stong phrag bzhi po de barjoda cing de nyid kyi
NK107(tse)001:3222: don la brtags pa yis gong ma'i de rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:3223: sgra don rnams kyi bye brag rnal 'byor pa yis
NK107(tse)001:3224: barjoda pa shes na 'byung ba bzhi'i rang sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:3225: 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i rang skad dang de dag ni
NK107(tse)001:3226: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK107(tse)001:3227: dpa' kun gyi skad la yang dag par thos pa
NK107(tse)001:3228: tsam gyis 'chi 'pho dang skye ba dang las dang
NK107(tse)001:3229: bsam pa rnams la bde lugs su ni rna ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3230: dbang po phyin ci ma log pas nyan par spro
NK107(tse)001:3231: ba ni dbang po dang las dang las kyi matha'i
NK107(tse)001:3232: rnam pa rnams la thogs pa med par gang zag
NK107(tse)001:3233: su dad pa de nyid kyis su yis sems nges
NK107(tse)001:3234: par 'byongs par byas pa ni 'byung 'jug gnas dang
NK107(tse)001:3235: ldog pa'i khyad par la brten nas rigs lha'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:3236: dang lha min dang mi dang byol song dang yi
NK107(tse)001:3237: dwags dang dmyal ba dang drug gi skad brda' la
NK107(tse)001:3238: yang dag par nges par sbyor shes pas mdor na
NK107(tse)001:3239: mngon par shes pa drug 'grub pa ni sprul pa
NK107(tse)001:3240: sku'i sa bon nges par 'jog pa ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:3241: lha'i mig gi mthong ba rnam par dag pas nyan
NK107(tse)001:3242: thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyis 'khor dang sku'i bye
NK107(tse)001:3243: brag rnams mthong ba dang rna ba'i dbang po rnam
NK107(tse)001:3244: par dag pas nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang
NK107(tse)001:3245: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bka'i bgro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:3246: thos pa dang sna'i tshor bas de dag gi dri
NK107(tse)001:3247: ma tshor ba dang lces ro myong ba ste bdud
NK107(tse)001:3248: rtsi ma ling ka 'thung ba lta bu'i ro myong
NK107(tse)001:3249: bar 'gyur ro lus kyis reg pa dang bde ba
NK107(tse)001:3250: lugs su spyod yid kyis de dag gi chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:3251: la bde lugs su spyod pa'o yang lha'i mig gi
NK107(tse)001:3252: mthong ba rnam par dag pas mkha' 'gro ma sna
NK107(tse)001:3253: tshogs pa'i gzugs mthong ba dang rna bas sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:3254: snas dri dang lce yis ro myong ba dang lus
NK107(tse)001:3255: kyis reg par nus pa dang yid kyis chos la
NK107(tse)001:3256: bde lugs su spyod pa'o yang mi'i mig gis rigs
NK107(tse)001:3257: la sogs pas gong dang 'dra'o byol song gis sprul
NK107(tse)001:3258: pa'o yi dwags kyis sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK107(tse)001:3259: dpag tu med pa'o dmyal ba'i mig gi mthong ba
NK107(tse)001:3260: rnam par dag pas sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3261: zhing khams rnams dang de dag gis sku'i tshad rnams
NK107(tse)001:3262: mthong ba dang rna bas zhing khams dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:3263: pa na bka' 'gro ba mdzad pa'i gsung rnams thos
NK107(tse)001:3264: pa dang snas de dag rnams kyi dri rab tu
NK107(tse)001:3265: bde bar 'jug pa zhes bya ba tshor ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3266: lces de dag gi ji ltar gsungs pa'i chos rnams
NK107(tse)001:3267: barjoda shes pa dang lus kyis reg par nus pa
NK107(tse)001:3268: dang yid kyis bde lugs su spyod pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:3269: dmyal ba ni las kyi bsags pa tshan che bas
NK107(tse)001:3270: de nyid rnam par dag pa las mthong ba khyad
NK107(tse)001:3271: che ba'o de nyid du nges pa dang bcas te
NK107(tse)001:3272: mngon par snang ba'o zhes yan lag gis don lnga
NK107(tse)001:3273: pa 'byung ba bzhi' sgra'i gnas gzhan la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:3274: sprul pa sku'i sa bon nye bar bzhag pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:3275: nas da ni yan lag gis don drug pa ston
NK107(tse)001:3276: pa'i gsung gi 'jug pa la brten nas byin barlaba
NK107(tse)001:3277: nges pa'i tshad bstan pa ni 'das dang zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:3278: sngar sangs rgyas pa rnams kyang 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:3279: don la sbyangs pas sangs rgyas la ma 'ongs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3280: sangs rgyas rnams kyang 'byung bzhi'i sgra don la bslabs
NK107(tse)001:3281: pas sangs rgyas par 'byung la da ltar gyis sangs
NK107(tse)001:3282: rgyas rnams kyang 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra don la bslabs
NK107(tse)001:3283: te de yang ston pa'i yon tan khyad par can
NK107(tse)001:3284: mnga' bas te gsung gi sgra tshig cir yang ston
NK107(tse)001:3285: pas na ston pa yin la 'byung ba phra rags
NK107(tse)001:3286: su 'dzin pa'i rtog pa spangs te sku gsum gcig
NK107(tse)001:3287: tu rgyas pa'o de ltar sgra'i gnas gzhan la ngag
NK107(tse)001:3288: sbyangs pas 'byung bar rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i rtog
NK107(tse)001:3289: pa bcom la des 'byung ba'i sgra don la 'byongs
NK107(tse)001:3290: pa'i yon tan dang ldan la khams gsum 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3291: las dang bag chags las 'das pa'o dbyangs ni snyan
NK107(tse)001:3292: cing gzhan 'jug par byed pa yin la de yang
NK107(tse)001:3293: tshig tu barjoda pa la brten nas so so'i blo
NK107(tse)001:3294: sna sna tshogs par go ba dag 'byung ste de
NK107(tse)001:3295: ltar tshig gcig gi dkyil 'khor la sgra tshig ming
NK107(tse)001:3296: dang bral ba zhes bya ba'i ngang du thams cad
NK107(tse)001:3297: 'dus so de yang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:3298: skal ba can gyi snang ba la sgra chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:3299: du shar ba'i gnas la brten nas de ltar rigs
NK107(tse)001:3300: drug gi mig la sogs pa'i dbang po drug ni
NK107(tse)001:3301: rnam par dag pas de'i chos nyid la rjes su
NK107(tse)001:3302: sbyor ba las khyad par gyis yon tan drug cu
NK107(tse)001:3303: 'byung ba ni mig gi rna ba rnam par dag
NK107(tse)001:3304: pa dang de bzhin du sna dang lce dang lus
NK107(tse)001:3305: dang yid dang mig gi rnam par dag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3306: drug ste de la mig gi dbang po'i rten rnam
NK107(tse)001:3307: pa drug de nyid la yul la sogs pa'i brten
NK107(tse)001:3308: pa drug / rten gyi khyad par bslab thabs drug
NK107(tse)001:3309: dbang po rang gi ngo bo drug ste drug cu'o
NK107(tse)001:3310: de yang mig gi rna ba'i rnam par dag pas
NK107(tse)001:3311: lkog tu gyur pa rnams mthong ba dang de'i snas
NK107(tse)001:3312: gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa gcig dang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3313: dang gsum dang bzhi la sogs pa mthong ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3314: de'i shes rab kyi spyan gyis chos dang chos ma
NK107(tse)001:3315: yin pa rnams 'byed pa dang lus kyi ye shes
NK107(tse)001:3316: kyi spyan gyis stong pa nyid thams cad mthong ba
NK107(tse)001:3317: dang yid kyis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan
NK107(tse)001:3318: gyis 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa dus
NK107(tse)001:3319: gcig la mkhyen pa dang mig gi mig rnam par
NK107(tse)001:3320: dag pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis shes bya
NK107(tse)001:3321: dang shes byas bsdus pa'i chos rnams ji lta ba
NK107(tse)001:3322: bzhin du mkhyen pa'o de bzhin du rna ba la
NK107(tse)001:3323: sogs pa rnams la bcu bcu brtsis pas chos kyi
NK107(tse)001:3324: rnam grangs yon tan gyis rnam par bzhag pa sum
NK107(tse)001:3325: brgyas nges pa ston pa nih chos sku dang longs
NK107(tse)001:3326: sku dang sprul pa'i sku gsum las khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:3327: sprul pa'i sku las 'phro nges par 'jog par byed
NK107(tse)001:3328: pa ste de'i las 'phros pa yis ni de'i yang
NK107(tse)001:3329: zer tsam gyis rnal 'byor pa sgra la goms pa
NK107(tse)001:3330: rnams kyis rnam par rtog pa'i chu rgyun 'gag go
NK107(tse)001:3331: de 'gags pas sgra gnas pa dang gzhi'i don khong
NK107(tse)001:3332: du chud 'byed pas tshig don rnams gsal bar byed
NK107(tse)001:3333: pas na sgra 'jug pas rang gzhan gyi don yul
NK107(tse)001:3334: mthong ba tsam gyis brten nas shes so de ltar
NK107(tse)001:3335: de dag la brtan pa thob cing gang la yul
NK107(tse)001:3336: mthong bas shes shing 'jug pa dang de dag la
NK107(tse)001:3337: brten nas rtogs pa skye ste de nyid la dus
NK107(tse)001:3338: thams cad du nges par 'jug pa'o zhes dris lan
NK107(tse)001:3339: bzhi pa la yan lag gi don drug tu byas
NK107(tse)001:3340: nas bstan no da ni dris lan bzhi pa'i yan
NK107(tse)001:3341: lag gi don gnyis pa gnas gzhan la bslabs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3342: dgos pa bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3343: kyis bstan pa'i dang po mchog gi dgos pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:3344: pa ni de ltar sgra'i dgos pa ni zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:3345: la sogs pas bstan te gong du bstan pa de
NK107(tse)001:3346: ltar sgra'i dgos pa ni rnam pa chig gnyis gzhung
NK107(tse)001:3347: na gsal de la gang zag las can dad pa
NK107(tse)001:3348: so so'i nges par 'byed pas na 'phrul gyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:3349: pa la brten nas thob pa ste de yang gang
NK107(tse)001:3350: gi sgra don dang 'og gi 'byung ba'i sgra la
NK107(tse)001:3351: bslabs pas dngos grub mchog la lus sprul skur 'grub
NK107(tse)001:3352: ngag longs skur 'grub yid chos skur 'grub 'gyu ba
NK107(tse)001:3353: rdo rje 'chang gi sku 'grub lah 'dzin pas ngo
NK107(tse)001:3354: bo nyid kyi sku dang lnga mngon par 'grub pa
NK107(tse)001:3355: ni sku lnga zung 'jug rdo rje 'chang gi rtags
NK107(tse)001:3356: 'byung ste sku re re la rtags gnyis gnyis go
NK107(tse)001:3357: rim gyis sbyar te sna tshogs sprul pa dang yangs
NK107(tse)001:3358: shing gsal ba dang barjoda pas shes pa dang smras
NK107(tse)001:3359: pas rdo rje 'dzin pa la nges pa'i yon tan
NK107(tse)001:3360: rdzogs pa dang spangs pa dang rab tu mi 'byed
NK107(tse)001:3361: pas gsal ba dang 'phra ba dang gang yang 'byin
NK107(tse)001:3362: pa dang zang thal ba dang thogs pa med pa
NK107(tse)001:3363: dang de ltar sku lnga 'grub pa'i rtags bcu yis
NK107(tse)001:3364: zung 'jug rdo rje 'chang gis lus dang mnyam pa
NK107(tse)001:3365: ni mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad
NK107(tse)001:3366: bzang po brgyad cu dang 'od zer dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:3367: pa rnams kyis rab tu brgyan pa rnams kyis rab
NK107(tse)001:3368: tu brgyan pa'i rnams 'thob bo de la sogs te
NK107(tse)001:3369: 'di la yon tan gyi tshogs barjoda kyis mi long
NK107(tse)001:3370: ba ni chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid shes
NK107(tse)001:3371: pa dang chos kyi dbyings stong zhing bdag med pa
NK107(tse)001:3372: nyid la spyod pa dang de bzhin du rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:3373: rdzogs pa chen po gzhi dngos po gshis kyi 'dug
NK107(tse)001:3374: tshul rgya gar yang ma chad la phyogs gang du
NK107(tse)001:3375: yang ma lhung pa nyid kyi don khong du chud
NK107(tse)001:3376: pas mtha' bral yongs rdzogs nyid la longs spyod pa
NK107(tse)001:3377: dang lam dang zhes pa ni spyir gsang sngags kyi
NK107(tse)001:3378: lam gnyis las rjes thob dang dngos gsum pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3379: las 'di ni dngos gsum pa dbang po dang 'brel
NK107(tse)001:3380: bar skye bas na yid dpyod tshig gis sgro gdags
NK107(tse)001:3381: su med pa'o de ltar kyang sems sde las mngon
NK107(tse)001:3382: gsum pa dang rgyab nas 'byung zhes pa'o 'bras bu
NK107(tse)001:3383: la cig char du longs spyod par nus pa ste
NK107(tse)001:3384: de yang chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba nyid la
NK107(tse)001:3385: longs spyod pa'o de yang lus kyi bde ba la
NK107(tse)001:3386: brten nas ngag gi bde ba de la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:3387: ngag gi bde bas sgra tshig thams cad don dang
NK107(tse)001:3388: sbyor shes pa dang de la brten nas sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:3389: bde ba sna tshogs gnyis su med pa'i nyams 'char
NK107(tse)001:3390: ro zhes 'byung ba la sogs pa'i sgra don la
NK107(tse)001:3391: bslabs pas mchog gi dgos pa bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:3392: yan lag gi don gnyis pa thun mong gi dgos
NK107(tse)001:3393: pa bstan pa ni thun mong gyur pa'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:3394: ni zhes pa 'jig rten pa la dgos pa ste
NK107(tse)001:3395: tshad ma zhes bya ba gzhal bya mngon sum pa
NK107(tse)001:3396: dang lkog tu 'gyur ba la sogs pa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:3397: gtan la phebs pa dang tshangs pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:3398: sgra'i gnas lnga la rang bzhin gyis logs pas bem
NK107(tse)001:3399: po dang rig bcas kyi rnam pa rnams la dbang
NK107(tse)001:3400: bsgyur ba dang rig pa ni phyi chos can gtan
NK107(tse)001:3401: la 'bebs par byed pa dang bya ba byed pa
NK107(tse)001:3402: dang ltos pa nyid la nang chos nyid gtan la
NK107(tse)001:3403: 'bebs pa chos thams cad mi rigs rigs par bshad
NK107(tse)001:3404: pa dang chos nyid kyi rigs pa rnams sgra la
NK107(tse)001:3405: dbyangs pa tsam gyis shes pa'o bstan chos ni la
NK107(tse)001:3406: bzla ba'i bstan chos 'gron du chags pa lta bu
NK107(tse)001:3407: dang shan 'byed pa'i bstan chos skyes bu tshe zad
NK107(tse)001:3408: pa bur chang gtong ba lta bu dang brtsod pa
NK107(tse)001:3409: lhur len pa'i bstan chos kam ting ba'i 'phrul lta
NK107(tse)001:3410: bu dang bsgrub pa lhur len pa'i bstan chos ma
NK107(tse)001:3411: bu chud pa nas lus bskyed pa lta bu dang
NK107(tse)001:3412: dgongs pa ltar len pa'i bstan chos skyes bu rang
NK107(tse)001:3413: 'dod kyi don la yid ches pa lta bu rnams
NK107(tse)001:3414: la yang bde lugs su spyod do de bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:3415: 'jig rten gyi bzo'i rnam pa rin po che stong
NK107(tse)001:3416: phrag brgya bcu rtsa lnga la sbyor ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:3417: bzhin du 'bum phrag dang bye ba la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:3418: dang gzugs kyi rnam par 'phrul pa dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:3419: pa dang sgra dang dri dang ro dang reg gi
NK107(tse)001:3420: bye brag dang nam mkha' lding gi rtog pa'i bye
NK107(tse)001:3421: brag pa'i khyad par gyi sbyor ba la sogs te
NK107(tse)001:3422: sgra la bslab pa tsam gyis thogs pa med par
NK107(tse)001:3423: shes pa dang sgyu rtsal ni mtshan ma ngan sngags
NK107(tse)001:3424: kyi sbyor ba sna tshogs pa dang ral gri dang
NK107(tse)001:3425: gtun shing dang mda' bo che dang 'khor lo dang
NK107(tse)001:3426: 'khor lo chen po dang gnam lcags kyi sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:3427: bsgyur ba la sogs sna tshogs pa rnams shes pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3428: 'phang dang ni gong ma'i sbyor ba de rnams sbyor
NK107(tse)001:3429: shes pa dang skor shes pa dang 'phen shes pa
NK107(tse)001:3430: dang gsor shes pa dang lcags kyi rtam la bdun
NK107(tse)001:3431: dang bcu bzhi dang nyi shu dang sum cu dang
NK107(tse)001:3432: brgya la thogs pa med par 'gyur ba'o de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:3433: du lcags kyi khang bu brtsegs pa rnams rtse nas
NK107(tse)001:3434: gzhom nus pa dang ri brag rnams dal gyis gzhom
NK107(tse)001:3435: nus pa dang mdung rtse lta bu'i gsum pa'i rtse
NK107(tse)001:3436: mo la rgya mtsho chen po rnams 'dus shing rlob
NK107(tse)001:3437: nus pa dag 'byung ngo gzhan yang gang gis kyang
NK107(tse)001:3438: ma spyad pa'i las rgyal po'i khang bzang dang btsun
NK107(tse)001:3439: mo rnams kyis khang bu brtsegs pa dang gnod sbyin
NK107(tse)001:3440: gyi khyim dang klu rnams kyi grong khyer 'joms pa
NK107(tse)001:3441: dang 'khor lo chen po'i char gyi grong khyer thams
NK107(tse)001:3442: cad bshig pa la sogs pa 'grub bo de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:3443: du 'byung ba chu la mi 'bying ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:3444: nyid zas dang skom dang rtsi sbyor du gyur pa
NK107(tse)001:3445: dang de bzhin du sa la 'dzul ba la sogs
NK107(tse)001:3446: pa dang mes mi 'tshig pa dang rlung gis mi
NK107(tse)001:3447: 'khyer ba la sogs pa nam mkha' la 'phur ba
NK107(tse)001:3448: la sogs pa lnga la spyod par nus pa'o gzhan
NK107(tse)001:3449: yang sgra la bslabs pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i lus la
NK107(tse)001:3450: 'khor lo dang mda' bo che la sogs pa'i mtshon
NK107(tse)001:3451: rnam pa sna tshogs pa rnams kyis mi tshugs la
NK107(tse)001:3452: sbyar dug dang rtsi dug dang rdzi dug dang mthong
NK107(tse)001:3453: dug la sogs pa reg dug dang btsan dug dang
NK107(tse)001:3454: sha dug dang rlangs dug dang thun mong dang khyad
NK107(tse)001:3455: par gyi sbyor ba sna tshogs pa'i dug rnams las
NK107(tse)001:3456: thar zhing rgyal bar 'gyur ba dang bem po sa
NK107(tse)001:3457: chu me rlung la sogs pas bsdus pa dang 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3458: ba rigs drug gi lus kyis bsdus pa'i rigs bcas
NK107(tse)001:3459: kyi sgra rnams dang de bzhin du nyan thos dang
NK107(tse)001:3460: rang rgyal dang byang chub sems dpa' dang mkha' 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3461: ma'i brda' dang de bzhin du tshig la brten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3462: tha snyad rnams la'ng mkhas par 'gyur ro mdor na
NK107(tse)001:3463: 'jig rten na ji ltar dgos pa rnams 'grub la
NK107(tse)001:3464: 'jig rten pa'i bstan bcos dang 'das pa'i bstan chos
NK107(tse)001:3465: rnams dang de daga don dang yi ge'i sgo nas
NK107(tse)001:3466: brtsom shes pa dang sangs rgyas kyi bka'i mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:3467: kyi byin gyis brlabs kyi dang rjes su gnang ba
NK107(tse)001:3468: dngos rnams la don dang yi ge'i sgo nas shes
NK107(tse)001:3469: par 'gyur ro gzhan yang sman spyad kyi bye brag
NK107(tse)001:3470: dpag tu med pa dang sems can spyir brtsis dang
NK107(tse)001:3471: gang zag sgo brtsis kyi sbyor ba'i bye brag mi
NK107(tse)001:3472: 'dra ba dpag tu med pa rnams phyed par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:3473: ro de bzhin du 'jig rten pa dang rjes su
NK107(tse)001:3474: mthun pa'i tshigs su bcad pa dang thang yig phul
NK107(tse)001:3475: du phyin pa rnams shes pas lha dang mi rnams
NK107(tse)001:3476: dga' ba dang 'jig rten gyi sbyor ba 'khor dang
NK107(tse)001:3477: longs spyod dang dga' zhing snyan pa dang dge zhing
NK107(tse)001:3478: legs pa dang bde zhing skyid pa dang ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:3479: 'dod pa lhun gyis grub par 'gyur la gal te
NK107(tse)001:3480: 'jig rten 'di na sgra la slob pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:3481: bar chad na yang ma 'ongs pa'i dus na de
NK107(tse)001:3482: ltar 'grub pa ni 'bad pa med par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:3483: zhes dris lan bzhi pa'i yan lag gi don gsum
NK107(tse)001:3484: pa sgra don la bslab pa'i dgos pa la gnyis
NK107(tse)001:3485: su byas nas bstan no da ni dris lan lnga
NK107(tse)001:3486: pa'i lus rnam par bzhag pa rgyu mtshan nges pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3487: mtshan nyid gtan la dbab par bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:3488: lag gi don nye bar mtshon pa khyad par gyi
NK107(tse)001:3489: don la gnyis te thal ba'i las dang bye brag
NK107(tse)001:3490: la brten nas 'byung ba'i mtshan nye bar mtshon pa
NK107(tse)001:3491: dang thal 'gyur gyi sgra don nges par bstan pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3492: de la thal ba'i gnas dang bye brag la gsum
NK107(tse)001:3493: ste thal zhes pa'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs mdor bstan
NK107(tse)001:3494: pa ni de ltar sgra don dgos pa 'grub ces
NK107(tse)001:3495: pa la sogs pa'i tshig brgyad 'og nas ston no
NK107(tse)001:3496: yan lag gi don gnyis pa phyi rol gyi 'jig
NK107(tse)001:3497: rten gyi 'phel 'grib la brten nas nang du chos
NK107(tse)001:3498: nyid kyi skye tshul gtan la dbab pa ni de
NK107(tse)001:3499: yang 'jig pa snod kyi khyad par bstan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3500: rten pa bcud kyi khyad par bstan pa dang khams
NK107(tse)001:3501: zhes 'tshogs pa 'dus shing 'byed pa'i khyad par bstan
NK107(tse)001:3502: pa'o de yang chags pa dang zhes pa ni rang
NK107(tse)001:3503: bzhin du nam mkha' stong pa sus kyang byas pa
NK107(tse)001:3504: med pa'i ngo bo stong pa ci'i rnam par yang
NK107(tse)001:3505: ma grub pa mtshan ma rdzas kyi bye brag du
NK107(tse)001:3506: ma yin 'du byed rtog pa tsam du yang med
NK107(tse)001:3507: la sgra dang bsgrub byed tsam du yang ma grub
NK107(tse)001:3508: la rdul dang de nyid kyi cha tsam du yang
NK107(tse)001:3509: grub pa med pa las sangs rgyas rnams kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:3510: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi brtsal phyogs
NK107(tse)001:3511: med du shar ba las sems can rtogs pa 'jug
NK107(tse)001:3512: pa'i las kyi khyad par las sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen
NK107(tse)001:3513: pa ma 'gags pa nyid chos nyid kha 'khyal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3514: thugs rjes 'gyu ba phra 'gyur zhes bya'o de las
NK107(tse)001:3515: sangs rgyas nyid sems can du 'khrul pa'i cha las
NK107(tse)001:3516: langs te nam mkha' stong pa la chos nyid rang
NK107(tse)001:3517: sgrar 'byung 'byung zhes grags dang sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK107(tse)001:3518: rje yul med pa stong pa zang thal du bzhugs
NK107(tse)001:3519: pa de'i ngang las 'byung zhes bya ba'i sgra de
NK107(tse)001:3520: gdul bya'i yul du gyur pa las 'gyu byed 'jug
NK107(tse)001:3521: pa las kyi rlung zhes pa b+hud rda'i thugs rje
NK107(tse)001:3522: kha 'khyal ba las 'byung zhes bya ba'i tshig la
NK107(tse)001:3523: 'od byung ste kha dog ljang bu phra rab rdul
NK107(tse)001:3524: gyi cha brgya stong gi cha tsam las bye brag
NK107(tse)001:3525: tu gyur pa cha med pa zhes bya ba'i rnam
NK107(tse)001:3526: pa tsam zhig sngo langs kyis byung ba las b+hud
NK107(tse)001:3527: rda'i thugs rje'i yul du gyur te de las dbyibs
NK107(tse)001:3528: rab tu 'phra ba lcags kyu'i rnam pa lta bur
NK107(tse)001:3529: 'gyur de las 'byung ba'i sbyor ba'i yi ge ya
NK107(tse)001:3530: ma zhes bya ba 'gyu ba rlung gis cha las
NK107(tse)001:3531: 'byung ba shar ba ni b+hud rda'i thams cad mkhyen
NK107(tse)001:3532: pa'i ye shes phyin ci log tu song ba las
NK107(tse)001:3533: byung ste de las chos nyid kyi rang sgra rlung
NK107(tse)001:3534: zhes bya ba lan gsum du byung ba las sangs
NK107(tse)001:3535: rgyas gang gis thos pa rnams 'khrul te rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:3536: dal sprin rab tu srab chags pa'i rnam pa 'dra
NK107(tse)001:3537: ba chags te rgya che zhing rab tu snyoms par
NK107(tse)001:3538: chags so de rnam par gzigs pas sangs rgyas kyis
NK107(tse)001:3539: 'khrul par ngo ma shes te spyan la sogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3540: sbyor ba mdzad pas 'phra 'gyur gyis rlung zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:3541: ba thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal de
NK107(tse)001:3542: dag bshig nas med par byas so de yang sdud
NK107(tse)001:3543: byed chu'i rlung gis bsdus yang las dang las kyi
NK107(tse)001:3544: bye brag gis cha'i rtog pa las chags byed sa'i
NK107(tse)001:3545: rlung bar snang la skar mda' chags pa'i rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:3546: lta bu las yang chags so de las smin byed
NK107(tse)001:3547: rlung gis rlung de dag smin par byas te rdo
NK107(tse)001:3548: rje rgya gram rgya khyon dpag tu med pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:3549: chags so de las 'byed byed rlung gi rlung gis
NK107(tse)001:3550: g.yas su lan gsum bskor bas 'byung ba po'i 'dod
NK107(tse)001:3551: pa'i las byas g.yon du lan gcig bskor bas mo'i
NK107(tse)001:3552: 'dod pa'i las byas de ltar byas pas 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:3553: rlung zhes bya ba de la rgya khyon dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:3554: med pa grangs kyi tshad dam che chung gi tshad
NK107(tse)001:3555: bzung bar mi nus pa dag chags so yang ye
NK107(tse)001:3556: shes lnga'i rtsal phyir 'khyal ba las rlung gi steng
NK107(tse)001:3557: du nam mkha' dag zhing gsal ba las bdud rtsi
NK107(tse)001:3558: las kyi char babs te de yang rlung gi dkyil
NK107(tse)001:3559: 'khor chur rab tu sra zhing skyes bu chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:3560: mtshan mchog dang ldan pas rdo rje 'phangs pas kyang
NK107(tse)001:3561: phed pa ma yin la de lta bu'i steng du
NK107(tse)001:3562: chu dar sngon po las chu'i zil pa chags pa
NK107(tse)001:3563: lta bur chags pa las thugs rje 'dzin pa'i khyad
NK107(tse)001:3564: par las chos nyid rang sgra chu chu zhes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3565: sgra 'byung ba las kha dog sngo la mtsher ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3566: gdangs yod pa dkar seng gi dngul gyi rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:3567: 'dra ba gcig lang gis 'byung de las 'od gsal
NK107(tse)001:3568: ba'i 'od 'phros pas zil pa'i rnam pa las chags
NK107(tse)001:3569: byed chu'i zhes bya ba rlung gi gar khyab pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3570: bar snang la 'o ma'i spris ma'i rnam pa dang
NK107(tse)001:3571: 'dra ba chags so de las bskyod byed chu'i sas
NK107(tse)001:3572: brtan par byas smin byed chu'i mes khams su smin
NK107(tse)001:3573: par byas de las 'od 'phros pas bskyod byed rlung
NK107(tse)001:3574: gi rlung gi dal bas phral ste nam mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:3575: steg ste rang la snga mas ji tsam yod pa
NK107(tse)001:3576: tsam zhig bar snang la rlung las bteg pa ni
NK107(tse)001:3577: chu'i rlung gi las so de las rab tu sra
NK107(tse)001:3578: zhing brtan la rlung las dpag tshad phyogs kun nas
NK107(tse)001:3579: lnga lngas chung bar chags pa ni rten dang brten
NK107(tse)001:3580: pa'i khyad par du yod do 'di ni srid pa
NK107(tse)001:3581: las kyi las ma rim zhes bya ste rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:3582: steng du chu'i 'og tu sems can dmyal ba'i 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3583: ba chags pa ni rlung g.yos pas de las sgra
NK107(tse)001:3584: chen po zung zung zhes pa dang rgyob rgyob zhes
NK107(tse)001:3585: pa 'byung la rlung gi sgra nang 'thabs pa las
NK107(tse)001:3586: me byung bas snang ba mer 'bar la de la
NK107(tse)001:3587: sems can dmyal ba rnams kyis tsha ba'i 'du shes
NK107(tse)001:3588: su mthong bas tsha ba'i dmyal ba zhes bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:3589: la rnam grangs su phye ba ni theg pa chung
NK107(tse)001:3590: ba dbang po dman pa rnams la dgongs pa'oh bdag
NK107(tse)001:3591: gis gzhan na bshad pa yang yod de 'di ni
NK107(tse)001:3592: gzhan dang lung tsam sgo bstun gyis tshul du byas
NK107(tse)001:3593: pa'o de yang lung gis yid ches bar byed na
NK107(tse)001:3594: bdud rtsi rol pa khang bu rnam par brtsegs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3595: rgyud las 'di ji bzhin du bshad nas yod do
NK107(tse)001:3596: de yang me chu'i dal gros pa las rab tu
NK107(tse)001:3597: grang ba'i reg pa dang ldan pa'i chu'i rgyun nam
NK107(tse)001:3598: mkha' nas babs me rnams shi ste grang pa 'ga'
NK107(tse)001:3599: zhig la spyod do des na grang ba'i dmyal ba
NK107(tse)001:3600: zhes bya'o de nas yang me 'bar ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:3601: nas chu 'bab pa'i snang ba 'ga' zhig la 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3602: mor spyod de de gnyis kyang gud na yod pa
NK107(tse)001:3603: lta bu ni ma yin no des na tsha reg
NK107(tse)001:3604: dang grang reg dus gcig la myong bas na sems
NK107(tse)001:3605: can dmyal ba zhes bya'o 'gro ba drug po 'di
NK107(tse)001:3606: rnams las rim gyis chags pa ni srid pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:3607: ma dag pa las byung ba'o 'di yang ma rig
NK107(tse)001:3608: pa 'khrul pa rang gis rang ma rig pa las
NK107(tse)001:3609: byung ba'o 'di ni 'du byed sna tshogs pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:3610: kyis 'khrul 'khor du phyin pa'o de las sa sa
NK107(tse)001:3611: zhes pa'i sgra rang byung ba las kha dog ser
NK107(tse)001:3612: ba'i mdangs phyung de'i rang bzhin gyis lus kyi khyad
NK107(tse)001:3613: par 'byung ba bzhi'i rnam 'phrul du gyur te bsdud
NK107(tse)001:3614: zhes pa ni chus bsdus pas sa'i spris mar gyur
NK107(tse)001:3615: de lasa chags byed sa'i sas 'o ma las spris
NK107(tse)001:3616: ma'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar sa'i rang bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:3617: gyur pa las so de nas smin byed sa'i mes
NK107(tse)001:3618: rab tu sra ba'i sa'i dal du chags pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:3619: nas bskyed byed sa'i rlung gis nam mkha' la brdeg
NK107(tse)001:3620: go de la rlung la 'degs shing 'dzin pa'i stobs
NK107(tse)001:3621: yod pas nam mkha' la 'phags te 'og ma bas
NK107(tse)001:3622: dpag tshad gnyis gnyis kyis phyogs kun nas chung pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3623: de'i chu'i steng sa'i 'og tu yi dwags kyi 'jig
NK107(tse)001:3624: rten chags te grong khyer dang lus mi 'dra ba
NK107(tse)001:3625: dpag tu med pa chags pa ni dmyal ba'i sdug
NK107(tse)001:3626: basngala la brten nas yi dwags chags te 'og mar
NK107(tse)001:3627: 'khrul pa'i sdug basngala nyams su myong ba las 'dir
NK107(tse)001:3628: 'og ma la ltos pa las sdug basngala chung ba'o
NK107(tse)001:3629: de yang nam mkha' gser du mthong bas 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:3630: yid la btags shing dngos su spyad du med pas
NK107(tse)001:3631: na yid btags la 'og chu'i dal te g.yos pas
NK107(tse)001:3632: zas dang skom du mthong ste 'dod pa'i phyir phyi
NK107(tse)001:3633: bzhin du phyin yang ma snyegs pas na phyi nang
NK107(tse)001:3634: gi sgrib pa can du grags so 'di la mang
NK107(tse)001:3635: nyung dang grangs tshad ni barjoda kyis mi langs ngo
NK107(tse)001:3636: de ltar gser gyi 'khor lo'i steng du ri rab
NK107(tse)001:3637: ri'i rgyal po rin po che dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:3638: las byas pa'i 'khor lo kha dog sna tshogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3639: 'khor lo brtsibs barjoda kyis mi langs par chags pa
NK107(tse)001:3640: ni 'byung ba bzhi gcig tu smin pa'i stobs las
NK107(tse)001:3641: byung ba'o de yang 'byung ba bzhi so so'i rlung
NK107(tse)001:3642: gi stobs kyis nam mkha' la rang gi rgya khyon
NK107(tse)001:3643: dang mnyam par btegs pa'i 'og tu byol song gi
NK107(tse)001:3644: 'gro ba rnams chags te rigs mi 'dra ba barjoda
NK107(tse)001:3645: kyis mi lang ba gzugs dang kha dog dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:3646: med par gnas te de yang gling bar gyii mun
NK107(tse)001:3647: pa ni ma yin la de nyid na nyi zla'i
NK107(tse)001:3648: snang ba med pas gcig sha gcig gis za ba
NK107(tse)001:3649: la sogs pa dpag tu med do de dag gis
NK107(tse)001:3650: ni phyi rim bzhi'i steng du 'gro ba mi'i skye
NK107(tse)001:3651: 'gro rnams chags pa ni gling bzhi bzhi tshan du
NK107(tse)001:3652: bkod pa dpag tu med par 'gro ba mi rigs
NK107(tse)001:3653: mi 'dra ba stong phrag brgya rtsa gcig tu chags
NK107(tse)001:3654: so ri rab kyi khong seng bang rim bzhi yod
NK107(tse)001:3655: pa'i bang rim gsum pa'i steng na lha min gyi
NK107(tse)001:3656: 'gro ba rnams su chags pa ni rigs mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:3657: ba dgu brgya dang dgu bcu rtsa lngar chags so
NK107(tse)001:3658: de nas 'dod pa la sogs pa'i lha'i rigs rnams
NK107(tse)001:3659: chags pa ni 'og ma 'og ma'i sdug basngala nyams
NK107(tse)001:3660: su myong ba shes pa las byung ba yin la
NK107(tse)001:3661: yas rim bar lhung bar gyur pa yin la 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:3662: pa'i chos nyid shes pa la chos nyid spyod pa
NK107(tse)001:3663: dang du ma longs te g.yeng pas lus yas rims
NK107(tse)001:3664: su ltung ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni khams gsum
NK107(tse)001:3665: du 'khor ba zhes bya'o de yang las dang dbang
NK107(tse)001:3666: po'i khyad par la brten nas 'bras bu mngon par
NK107(tse)001:3667: rdzogs par rdzogs sangs rgya ba yod do gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:3668: nyid dang zhes pa ni bskal pa chen po 'bum
NK107(tse)001:3669: phrag drug cu rtsa gnyis kyi yun du gnas la
NK107(tse)001:3670: sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis la lo stong lnga brgya
NK107(tse)001:3671: phrag bco lnga bco lnga'i yan gyis de srid du
NK107(tse)001:3672: gnas so 'jig pa'i dus zhes pa ni de dag
NK107(tse)001:3673: 'das pa'i 'og tu sngon du gzugs med pa'i lha
NK107(tse)001:3674: rnams mngon par shes pa yod pas de dag rnams
NK107(tse)001:3675: 'jigs pa mthong steh gzugs khams kyi lha la sogs
NK107(tse)001:3676: pa rim gyis babs nasah sngon gyi las kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:3677: par smin pa 'di lta bu kye ma kye ma
NK107(tse)001:3678: zhes 'dzer cing phyogs kun du 'o dod 'bod pa
NK107(tse)001:3679: dang sgra chen po 'byin no de nas gzugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:3680: lha rnams rab tu 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i sems
NK107(tse)001:3681: kyis sngon gyi las bzang po bsags pa rnams rjes
NK107(tse)001:3682: su dran nas byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas
NK107(tse)001:3683: dkon mchog gsum rjes su dran nas skyabs su dong
NK107(tse)001:3684: pa la sogs pa'i rjes su dran pa skyes te
