NK107(tse)001:3685: yar la bros pas la la ni 'jig la la
NK107(tse)001:3686: la ni 'jig pa'i bskal pa gnyis dang gsum gyi
NK107(tse)001:3687: bar la gnas pa yang yod la sngon gyi bsags
NK107(tse)001:3688: pa'i 'bras bu rnams mchog tu dran pa dag ni
NK107(tse)001:3689: mi 'jig pa yang yod de yang nam mkha' stong
NK107(tse)001:3690: pa rang bzhin gyis khyab pa las g.yo ba rlung
NK107(tse)001:3691: gi sgra 'ur zhing rgyun ring par gyur pa las
NK107(tse)001:3692: 'jig rten thams cad ldeg cing rab tu 'tsheg cing
NK107(tse)001:3693: 'khrog pa dang 'dar zhing yed par gyur ba las
NK107(tse)001:3694: dmyal ba'i sred pa yang yo ga g.yo ba dang
NK107(tse)001:3695: 'dar ba dang 'phrig pa dang rab tu skrag par
NK107(tse)001:3696: gyur pa la sogs pas sems can dmyal ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:3697: ni e ma bdag cag ni sdug basngala 'di zad
NK107(tse)001:3698: par gyur na ci ma rung zhes barjoda cing gal
NK107(tse)001:3699: te srid pa 'di dag 'jig par 'gyur ram zhes
NK107(tse)001:3700: smra zhing sems can dmyal ba'i sdug basngala zad na
NK107(tse)001:3701: ci ma rung snyam pa las yang las kyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:3702: par smin pa'i stobs kyis bskal pa'i me chen po
NK107(tse)001:3703: 'bar nas phyogs kun du bskal pa'i me chen po
NK107(tse)001:3704: rab tu skyi bung ba dag 'bros pa las chu'i
NK107(tse)001:3705: dal las rim gyis skams nas gser gyi sa gzhi
NK107(tse)001:3706: la thug gi bar song yi dwags ni la la
NK107(tse)001:3707: 'jig la la la las kyi rnam par smin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3708: dbang gis de nyid du gnas par 'gyur la nam
NK107(tse)001:3709: mkha' la so so'i lus gnas pas yid 'gyur ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3710: sdug basngala ba rnams la spyod do de nas 'og
NK107(tse)001:3711: gi phyogs nas rnam pa'i rlung g.yos de'i rtse mo
NK107(tse)001:3712: la bskal pa'i me 'bar bas sa gzhi res mes
NK107(tse)001:3713: bsregs shing res rlung gi gtor la de ltar me
NK107(tse)001:3714: rlung gi las 'byung ba pho mo so so'i las
NK107(tse)001:3715: byas pas ni sa gzhi yang med par byas de
NK107(tse)001:3716: nas byol song dang mi dang lha min dang skye
NK107(tse)001:3717: gnas thams cad dang lha'i srid pa yang phal cher
NK107(tse)001:3718: stong par byas so de ltar zhig nas gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:3719: ni khyad par gyi las so stong pa nyid ni
NK107(tse)001:3720: ji ltar gnas pa dang chags pa dang 'jig pa
NK107(tse)001:3721: dang stong pa yun snyam mo de ltar byung ba
NK107(tse)001:3722: de yang rgyu ni 'byung ba las kyi rgyu bzhi
NK107(tse)001:3723: las byung ba ni 'byung ba so so'i sgra bzhi
NK107(tse)001:3724: las byung ste chu'i sgra bshang pa dang sa'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:3725: ldig pa dang me'i sgra 'tshigs pa dang rlung sgra
NK107(tse)001:3726: 'bir ba la sogs pa bzhi'i rgyu byas la de
NK107(tse)001:3727: ltar yin pa'i gnad kyis 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la
NK107(tse)001:3728: bslabs pas 'khrul snang zad par 'gyur ba ni gnad
NK107(tse)001:3729: yang dag pa'o 'di ltar snod bcud kyi rgyu ni
NK107(tse)001:3730: las dang las kyi rnam par smin pas byas so
NK107(tse)001:3731: grub tshul dang ni spyi mthun gyi las kyis grub
NK107(tse)001:3732: pa ni ma yin no rang byung du byung bas
NK107(tse)001:3733: na 'byung ba zhes bya ste de yang gzhi la
NK107(tse)001:3734: babs kyis grub pas na grub pa zhes bya'o grangs
NK107(tse)001:3735: tshad do zhes pa ni 'di yang khyad par gling
NK107(tse)001:3736: dpag tu med pa las so so'i ri rab dang
NK107(tse)001:3737: bcas pa dang de yang grangs tshad nges par byed
NK107(tse)001:3738: pas na gling re re la bzhi bzhis bskor nas
NK107(tse)001:3739: yod do zhes yan lag gi don gnyis pa phyi
NK107(tse)001:3740: rol gyi 'byung ba'i 'brel 'phel 'grib la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:3741: nang chos nyid kyi skye tshul la bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:3742: ni yan lag gi don gsum pa thal ba'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:3743: dang zhing khams bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:3744: bcu gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po thal ba'i dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:3745: zhes pa'i zhing khams gtan la dbab pa ni zhing
NK107(tse)001:3746: zhes pa bskyed cing 'dun pa la bya khams zhes
NK107(tse)001:3747: pa 'jug cing gnas pa la bya rnam pa bcu
NK107(tse)001:3748: gnyis pa zhes pa ni grangs bkod pa ste 'di
NK107(tse)001:3749: dag ni rdo rje gdan spyir bzhag pa'o 'jig pa
NK107(tse)001:3750: sems can gyi dus brten pa 'dod cing 'dun pas
NK107(tse)001:3751: khyad par byas pa'i sa zhes bya'o de'i 'og na
NK107(tse)001:3752: ni zhes pa dpag tshad lnga brgya na thal ni
NK107(tse)001:3753: gser la sogs pa rin po che'i bye ma sna
NK107(tse)001:3754: tshogs pas brdal ba'o dbyangs zhes pa ni sgra'i bye
NK107(tse)001:3755: brag snyan pa dpag tu med pa yod pa la
NK107(tse)001:3756: bya'o zhing khams 'di na rin po che sna dgu
NK107(tse)001:3757: brgya dang dgu bcu rtsa lngas rnam par mdzes pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3758: ra bas kun nas bskor ba ni rgya che ba
NK107(tse)001:3759: la dgongs pa yin te de yang rgya dang khyon
NK107(tse)001:3760: du snyam pa 'di tsam zhig yod zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:3761: dpag par dka' ba ni 'di dang 'di tsam yod
NK107(tse)001:3762: kyi tshad sus kyang mi zin pa'o rab tu mdzes
NK107(tse)001:3763: pa ni yid du 'ong ba la phyi nas bltas
NK107(tse)001:3764: pas nang gsal nang nas bltas pas phyi gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:3765: 'od dang kha dog dang rin po che sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:3766: pa'i rgyan gyis spras pa'o de yang rgyu rin po
NK107(tse)001:3767: che mar gad ta dang mthon mthing la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:3768: stong phrag dgu brgya dang dgu bcu rtsa lnga'i rgyu
NK107(tse)001:3769: las rang byung bah rkyen 'od lnga'i snang bas rab
NK107(tse)001:3770: tu mdzes par byas pa de yang rang bzhin sprul
NK107(tse)001:3771: pa sku'i yon tan gyi cha shas kyi zhing zhes
NK107(tse)001:3772: bya'o ston pa'i zhes pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa
NK107(tse)001:3773: rin po che rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:3774: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan phun sum tshogs pa mnga'
NK107(tse)001:3775: ba sku mdun dang rgyab med pa zhal phyogs bcu
NK107(tse)001:3776: kun du thal le ba mdzes pa'i rgyan rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:3777: sna tshogs pas rab tu spras pa rin po che'i
NK107(tse)001:3778: chun 'phyang gis rab tu brgyan pa bzhugs so de'i
NK107(tse)001:3779: bstan pa ni dam pa'i chos 'dul ba brgya phrag
NK107(tse)001:3780: phyed dang bcu gsum ston par byed la de'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3781: ni dgra bcom pa phyed dang nyis stong yod do
NK107(tse)001:3782: de'i steng na zhes pa ni dpag tshad lnga stong
NK107(tse)001:3783: yod pa'i gzhal med khang yod de nas dgra bcom
NK107(tse)001:3784: pa'i 'khor dpag tu med pa yod la de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:3785: du 'og ste zhes pa na yang ngo phyogs bzhi
NK107(tse)001:3786: dang mtshams bzhi sde brgyad na yang yod do de
NK107(tse)001:3787: yang rin po che rab tu chung zhing mdzes pa
NK107(tse)001:3788: la shes pa'i nyams dga' ba ni las kyi khyad
NK107(tse)001:3789: par gyis dga' ba las rin po che'i sil ma
NK107(tse)001:3790: rnams kyis bkod pa legs par spras pa ni rin
NK107(tse)001:3791: po che'i chun 'phyangs yod pa'o zhes thal ba'i dbyangs
NK107(tse)001:3792: zhes bya ba'i zhing khams bstan pa ste nying lag
NK107(tse)001:3793: gi don dang po bstan nas da ni nying lag
NK107(tse)001:3794: gi don gnyis pa thal ba'i 'dzin zhes bya ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3795: zhing khams bstan pa ni de nas ni thal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3796: dbyangs kyi 'og na dga' bas 'byed pa dang bde
NK107(tse)001:3797: bas 'byed pa dang rol pas 'byed pa dang shin
NK107(tse)001:3798: tu bde dgas 'byed pa dang nyi ma snang byed
NK107(tse)001:3799: dang de'i 'og na zla bas rnam par rol pa
NK107(tse)001:3800: zhes bya ba ni rin po che dgu'i rgyu'i seng+ge
NK107(tse)001:3801: dang zel ba sbu gu dang mdzes ldan snying po
NK107(tse)001:3802: dang rnam par rol pa dang sprin spras chen po
NK107(tse)001:3803: dang 'bar ba'i 'khor lo can las grub pa rgya
NK107(tse)001:3804: khyon dmigs su mi tshud pa grong khyer gyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:3805: par 'phrul pa nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang lding
NK107(tse)001:3806: ba dang 'phar ba dang rnam par bkod pa legs
NK107(tse)001:3807: pa'i 'og nas sprin chen po spungs pa'i steng na
NK107(tse)001:3808: thal ba ni brdal ba'i don no 'dzin zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:3809: ba ni 'og gi sprin chen po'i tshogs 'dzin pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3810: de'i dbyibs na gser gyi 'khor lo drug pa chags
NK107(tse)001:3811: pa dang 'dra ba'i rnam pah dbyibs rtsibs stong yod
NK107(tse)001:3812: pa phyi nang med par zang thal ba las 'gro
NK107(tse)001:3813: ba rnams rgyu bar nus pa ston pa ni yang
NK107(tse)001:3814: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'khor rnam par bkod
NK107(tse)001:3815: pa zhes bya ba la 'khor byang chub sems dpa'
NK107(tse)001:3816: bye ba khrag khrig gis bskor te mdun du brdar
NK107(tse)001:3817: nas longs su bkod pa ni re re la'ng 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3818: lnga brgya lnga brgya yod do bstan pa ni bden
NK107(tse)001:3819: pa gnyis kyi chos la 'jol nyog tu spyod cing
NK107(tse)001:3820: chos kyi dbyings stong nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3821: ngang las thams cad thabs gcig go rin po che
NK107(tse)001:3822: 'bum phrag lnga brgya yis spras te phyogs dang rgya
NK107(tse)001:3823: khyon dpag tu med pa rnams kyis legs par rin
NK107(tse)001:3824: po che mthon mthing gis gzhi bkod pa ni zhing
NK107(tse)001:3825: khams gnyis pa thal ba 'dzin zhes bya ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:3826: nas da ni zhing khams gsum pa thal ba skyob
NK107(tse)001:3827: ces bya ba bstan pa nih 'di nas 'jig pa
NK107(tse)001:3828: bsam gtan pa gzhan du 'pho ba la dgongs la
NK107(tse)001:3829: brten pa sprul pa sku'i zhing khyad par du gyur
NK107(tse)001:3830: pa thal ba 'dzin zhes bya ba'i g.yas na grags
NK107(tse)001:3831: ldan zhes bya ba'i b+hu rda'i zhing chung pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:3832: na ston pa byang chub sems dpa' blo gros bstan
NK107(tse)001:3833: zhes bya ba dang 'khor mkha' 'gro ma 'bum phrag
NK107(tse)001:3834: dang bcas pa na bstan pa mdo sde rnam par
NK107(tse)001:3835: rol pa zhes bya ba dus gsum du sgra mi
NK107(tse)001:3836: 'chad par bsgrogs so de'i g.yas nas dpag tshad stong
NK107(tse)001:3837: phrag na g.yo ldan zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas zhing
NK107(tse)001:3838: rin po che in+da ni la las grub pa dpag
NK107(tse)001:3839: tshad lnga stong gi khyon yod pa kun kyang rin
NK107(tse)001:3840: po che'i phung po rab tu 'dar ba zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:3841: bas spras pa ston pa bdud rnam par 'joms pa
NK107(tse)001:3842: la 'khor gnod sbyin bye ba gcig bstan pa mdo
NK107(tse)001:3843: sde rnam par bsgrogs pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so
NK107(tse)001:3844: de nas g.yas su dpag tshad lnga brgya na pad
NK107(tse)001:3845: ma dag pa zhes bya ba rab tu dmar ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3846: mdangs yod pa ston pa rdzogs ldan la 'khor drang
NK107(tse)001:3847: srong stong phrag lnga bstan pa mdo sde rtse las
NK107(tse)001:3848: 'jug pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so de nas dpag
NK107(tse)001:3849: tshad nyis brgya na thal ba rin po cher gser
NK107(tse)001:3850: gyi bye mas brdal ba brgya khyon dmigs su mi
NK107(tse)001:3851: tshud pa'o skyob zhes bya ba ni sdug basngala thams
NK107(tse)001:3852: cad las nges par sgrol bar byed pa'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:3853: khyad par du rin po che ma rgad dag gis
NK107(tse)001:3854: rab tu spungs pa'i steng na 'od dmar po'i mdangs
NK107(tse)001:3855: kyis rnam par 'phros pa khyad par du kha dog
NK107(tse)001:3856: dkar ba dang ser ba dang dmar ba dang ljang
NK107(tse)001:3857: khu dang mthing khas nges par gsal ba ni ye
NK107(tse)001:3858: shes lnga'i mdangs kyis rnam par 'khrug pa zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:3859: ston pa ni sangs rgyas rin chen gtsug tor can
NK107(tse)001:3860: zhes bya ba la 'khor tshe dang ldan pa dgu
NK107(tse)001:3861: khri dgu stong gis bskor ba de dag re re
NK107(tse)001:3862: la yang dgra bcom pa lnga brgya lnga brgyas yongs
NK107(tse)001:3863: su bskor ba bstan pa dam pa'i chos 'dul ba
NK107(tse)001:3864: nye rag gcod pa zhes bya ba sgrogs shing de'i
NK107(tse)001:3865: bden pas 'khor de dag kyang so so'i las dang
NK107(tse)001:3866: mtshan mar bcas te rang rang gi lus ngag yid
NK107(tse)001:3867: kyi spyod pa las mi 'da' ba'o zhes gsum pa
NK107(tse)001:3868: thal ba skyob pa'i zhing bstan nas da ni bzhi
NK107(tse)001:3869: pa thal ba brdal ba'i zhing bstan pa ni de
NK107(tse)001:3870: nas ni thal ba skyob pa nas 'jig pa rlung
NK107(tse)001:3871: spyod pa chu 'di nas ni nam mkha' dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:3872: dgu'i steng na yid 'jug pa'i zhing khams na ston
NK107(tse)001:3873: pa zla 'od dri ma med pa 'khor srin po
NK107(tse)001:3874: 'bum phrag lnga bstan pa dam pa'i chos rims 'byed
NK107(tse)001:3875: gsal ba'i nyi ma de'i dpag tshad lnga'i steng na
NK107(tse)001:3876: zhing khams yangs pa'i 'od ston pa ri dbang gi
NK107(tse)001:3877: rgyal po 'khor tshangs pa'i bu mo lnga stong gis
NK107(tse)001:3878: yongs su bskor ba bstan pa smra ba gcod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3879: 'khor lo zhes bya ba sgrogs so de nas dpag
NK107(tse)001:3880: tshad phyed dang gnyis kyi steng na zhing khams rin
NK107(tse)001:3881: po che mang po yod pa ston pa mi 'khrug
NK107(tse)001:3882: pa 'khor brgya byin gyi rgyal po dgu khri dang
NK107(tse)001:3883: dgu stong bstan pa dam pa'i chos lung du bstan
NK107(tse)001:3884: pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so de nas bcu'i steng
NK107(tse)001:3885: na zhing khams 'dun pa byed pa ston pa gser
NK107(tse)001:3886: mdog mdzes pa 'khor klu'i bu brgya phrag brgyad bstan
NK107(tse)001:3887: pa dbang po'i chos klu shing gsal ba'i sgron ma'o
NK107(tse)001:3888: de nas brgyad kyi steng na zhing khams 'bru rnam
NK107(tse)001:3889: par bkod pa ston pa 'od rab tu 'gyed pa
NK107(tse)001:3890: 'khor khyab 'jug gi rgyal po lnga stong dang bstan
NK107(tse)001:3891: pa dam pa'i chos rnam par dag pa bsgrogs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:3892: de nas gsum gyi steng na zhing khams nor bu
NK107(tse)001:3893: gsal ba ston pa dran pa'i dpal 'khor mi'am ci'i
NK107(tse)001:3894: bu mo stong phrag bdun bstan pa dam pa'i chos
NK107(tse)001:3895: gdung ba sel ba bsgrogs pa'o de ltar drug gis
NK107(tse)001:3896: steng na de nas dpag tshad lnga brgya'i steng na
NK107(tse)001:3897: thal ba rin po che spras mthing zhes pas rnam
NK107(tse)001:3898: par brdal ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams brgya khyon
NK107(tse)001:3899: grangs med pa bcu yod pa dbyibs pad ma 'dab
NK107(tse)001:3900: ma rgyas pa'i dbyibs 'dra ba 'dab ma bye ba
NK107(tse)001:3901: phrag khrig gis yongs su bskor ba 'dab ma de
NK107(tse)001:3902: dag re re'i steng na nyi zla'i khang bu brtsegs
NK107(tse)001:3903: pa re re la bsil drod snyoms pa'i nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:3904: bcu bcu legs par 'char ba shin tu brdal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3905: khod snyoms pa'i ni g.yo ba'i rlung gis byas pa
NK107(tse)001:3906: khang bu re re las lha mo bye ba 'char
NK107(tse)001:3907: bar byed pa'i gzhi re re yod pa kha dog
NK107(tse)001:3908: sna tshogs pa'i 'od rab tu 'bar ba la kha
NK107(tse)001:3909: dog ni khyad par du dkar ba la dmar ba'i
NK107(tse)001:3910: mdangs yod pa'i snang bas kun du 'khrug pa'o 'di
NK107(tse)001:3911: na gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams la 'byung bzhi'i rags
NK107(tse)001:3912: pa'i gzugs brnyan snang ba med pa ni 'di ni
NK107(tse)001:3913: skye ba gcig la b+hud tha ba sha stag go
NK107(tse)001:3914: ston pa 'khor ba 'jig pa la nyan thos 'bum
NK107(tse)001:3915: khrag drug cu rtsa lngas yongs su bskor ba'o bstan
NK107(tse)001:3916: pa ni dam pa'i chos 'du mched rgyas pa yongs
NK107(tse)001:3917: su rtogs pa zhes bya ba 'khor rnams la bsgrogs
NK107(tse)001:3918: so zhing khams 'di bskal pa rdzogs ldan chen po
NK107(tse)001:3919: zhes bya ba ste thal pa zhes bya ba yin
NK107(tse)001:3920: pas 'di la 'jig pa med do zhes zhing khams
NK107(tse)001:3921: bzhi pa thal ba brdal pa zhes bya ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:3922: nas da ni zhing khams lnga pa thal ba'i be
NK107(tse)001:3923: con zhes bya ba bstan pa ni 'di nas ni
NK107(tse)001:3924: thal ba brdal ba'i 'jig pas brten pa rlung 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:3925: steng du yang nam mkha' bar snang dpag tshad brgya
NK107(tse)001:3926: brgya yod de zhing khams 'di kun kyang dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:3927: lnga stong la go zhing snyam pa yod de yang
NK107(tse)001:3928: ming bstan pa ni zhing khams rol bas 'byed pa
NK107(tse)001:3929: ston pa sgrol byed rgyal po 'khor lha'i bu brgya
NK107(tse)001:3930: phrag dgu bstan pa gsal ba'i sgron ma zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:3931: ba bsgrogs so de'i steng na brtse ba'i rol pa
NK107(tse)001:3932: ston pa rdo rje kun 'dus 'khor nam mkha' lding
NK107(tse)001:3933: lnga brgya bstan pa stong la rab mchog go yang
NK107(tse)001:3934: zhing khams bkod pa dag pa ston pa rab snang
NK107(tse)001:3935: bde byed 'khor sred med kyi bu pho stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:3936: dgu bstan pa dam pa'i chos dpung rnam par bkod
NK107(tse)001:3937: pa zhes bya ba ston no yang zhing khams rin
NK107(tse)001:3938: po che rtogs ldan ston pa 'khor ba 'jig 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3939: lha'i bu mo lnga stong lnga brgya bstan pa brtse
NK107(tse)001:3940: ba bkod pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so de'i steng
NK107(tse)001:3941: na zhing khams sde 'pham par byed pa ston pa
NK107(tse)001:3942: rab tu dang pa 'khor khyab 'jug sred ldan gyi
NK107(tse)001:3943: bu pho stong phrag lnga stong ngo bstan pa mngon
NK107(tse)001:3944: par byed pa'o yang de'i steng zhing khams shin tu
NK107(tse)001:3945: yangs pa na ston pa 'khor lo'i stobs kyis rol
NK107(tse)001:3946: pa 'khor 'bras bu na spyod pa'i lha'i bu 'bum
NK107(tse)001:3947: phrag lnga bstan pa gnam lcags mi g.yo ba'o yang
NK107(tse)001:3948: de'i steng na zhing khams rgyu bar dga' ba ston
NK107(tse)001:3949: pa gzi brjid kyi rgyal po 'khor tshangs pa'i chung
NK107(tse)001:3950: ma lnga stong bstan pa dur khrod khang bu brtsegs
NK107(tse)001:3951: pa'o yang de'i steng na zhing khams sprin gyis legs
NK107(tse)001:3952: par brgyan pa ston pa mtha' yas grol ba 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3953: lto 'phye drug stong lnga brgya bstan pa gser gyi
NK107(tse)001:3954: me tog mdzes pa'o de'i steng na zhing khams 'dul
NK107(tse)001:3955: zhing dag pa ston pa pad ma dam pa 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3956: lha min gyi bu dang bu mo lnga stong bstan
NK107(tse)001:3957: pa sangs rgyas kyi bden pa 'byin pa rnam par
NK107(tse)001:3958: bsgrogs so de'i steng na zhing khams rab tu dag
NK107(tse)001:3959: gsal ston pa mi mnyam pa 'khor rags pa'i gzugs
NK107(tse)001:3960: can bdun stong bstan pa rab gsal g.yos yang zhing
NK107(tse)001:3961: 'gyu ba dag pa ston pa rab tu bkod pa
NK107(tse)001:3962: 'khor sems can phal pa khri bstan pa 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:3963: stong gis brgyan pa zhing khams 'bru bkod pa ston
NK107(tse)001:3964: pa dge skyob 'khor bran mo lnga stong bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:3965: rags pa 'dul ba yang zhing mdzes pa'i snying po
NK107(tse)001:3966: ston pa 'khor ba las rab tu thal ba 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3967: dmigs can bu mo stong phrag drug bstan la mchod
NK107(tse)001:3968: par byed pa yang zhing dga' ba'i zhing ston pa
NK107(tse)001:3969: rin po che spung gis mdzes pa 'khor grags ldan
NK107(tse)001:3970: gyi bu stong phrag dgu bstan pa skad cig la
NK107(tse)001:3971: dga' bar byed pa'o yang zhing myur ba'i nor bu
NK107(tse)001:3972: ston pa ro langs bgegs pa 'khor bya khyung gi
NK107(tse)001:3973: rigs stong phrag drug bstan pa lus ngag gi bcings
NK107(tse)001:3974: pa las grol ba yang zhing kun tu yang pa
NK107(tse)001:3975: ston pa 'khor rgyun nyi ma 'khor 'dab bzangs rigs
NK107(tse)001:3976: kyi bu mo stong bstan pa 'du byed pa yang
NK107(tse)001:3977: zhing 'jigs pa med pa 'khor las 'jug bu nyi
NK107(tse)001:3978: khri bstan pa bskyed pas 'jug pa'o yang zhing snying
NK107(tse)001:3979: pos brtsegs pa ston pa sdug basngala gcod pa 'khor
NK107(tse)001:3980: rab gsal gyi 'gro ba nyis stong ston pa sdug
NK107(tse)001:3981: basngala 'joms pa yang zhing mngon pa'i dpung 'khor gtsug
NK107(tse)001:3982: phud can gyi las can khri bstan pa snying pos
NK107(tse)001:3983: mdzes pa zhing 'khor lo can ston pa 'od zer
NK107(tse)001:3984: kun nas 'byung ba 'khor 'dod pa'i lha lnga stong
NK107(tse)001:3985: bstan pa myong bas brtse ba'o de'i steng na zhing
NK107(tse)001:3986: pad ma brtsegs pa ston pa gzhon nu rol pa
NK107(tse)001:3987: 'khor mi 'byed kyi bdag po lnga stong bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:3988: 'gyu bas 'byed pa zhes bya'o de ltar bcu dgu
NK107(tse)001:3989: 'das pa'i yar stengs na thal ba'i zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:3990: rin po che rigs mi 'dra ba stong phrag brgyad
NK107(tse)001:3991: cu rtsa dgu sil mas brdal ba be con ni
NK107(tse)001:3992: phyogs kun nas gser dang dngul dang bee d+aur+ya dang
NK107(tse)001:3993: mthon mthing la sogs pa'i be con gyis brtsegs pas
NK107(tse)001:3994: kun nas bskor ba'i zhes bya ba ni ming ngo
NK107(tse)001:3995: de yang rab tu zhes pa shin tu mnyam pa'i
NK107(tse)001:3996: tshad ljongs bde zhes pa dbus nas bltas na mtha'
NK107(tse)001:3997: dma' ba snyam pa mtha' nas bltas na dbus dma'
NK107(tse)001:3998: ba snyam pa dpag tshad 'bum phrag dgu pa ye
NK107(tse)001:3999: shes chen po'i byin brlabs las rab tu nyams dga'
NK107(tse)001:4000: ba rin po che rigs mi 'dra ba'i sil ma'i
NK107(tse)001:4001: phung po sna tshogs pa las nges par spras te
NK107(tse)001:4002: ni rab tu snyoms pas brdal bas rwa bar skabs
NK107(tse)001:4003: su spungs pa'i tshul du byung ba ni rab tu
NK107(tse)001:4004: khod snyoms pa'i rtags te de'i steng du rkang pa
NK107(tse)001:4005: bzhag pa tsam gyis kyang nem pa snyam byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4006: ston pa'i ni me tog gi sprin gyis rnam par
NK107(tse)001:4007: spungs pa la 'khor byang chub sems dpa' bye ba
NK107(tse)001:4008: phyed dang brgyad kyis yongs su bskor te mdun gyis
NK107(tse)001:4009: brdar ba'o bstan pa ni dam pa'i chos smugs pa
NK107(tse)001:4010: sel ba zhes bya ba'i 'khor lo bskor ro de
NK107(tse)001:4011: yang rdzogs pa chen po gnyis ldan pa zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4012: ba 'di'i 'gro ba 'di dag kyang skye ba gcig
NK107(tse)001:4013: gis thogs pa sha stag ste de dag gi phyi
NK107(tse)001:4014: rim na thod pa skam po'i 'phreng bas bskor ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4015: zhes zhing khams lnga pa thal ba'i be con zhes
NK107(tse)001:4016: bya ba bstan nas da ni drug pa thal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4017: rgyun zhes bya ba'i zhing khams bstan pa ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:4018: nas 'jig pa me brten pa rlung byang shar gyi
NK107(tse)001:4019: mtshams nas dpag tshad lnga 'das pa na thal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4020: zhes bya ba rin po che lnga yis yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4021: brdal ba'o rgyun zhes bya ba ni ye shes kyi
NK107(tse)001:4022: rlung gis rnam par dag pa'i snang ba la rgyun
NK107(tse)001:4023: du spyod pa'o mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis rab
NK107(tse)001:4024: tu mchod par byed pa brten pa rgyu ba dang
NK107(tse)001:4025: mi rgyu ba'i 'gro ba rnams brten par byed pa
NK107(tse)001:4026: dbyibs bang rim gyis rnam par brtsegs pa 'dra ba
NK107(tse)001:4027: bang rim gser gyi me tog gis rab tu mdzes
NK107(tse)001:4028: par byas pa dpag tshad drug khri'i brgya dang khyon
NK107(tse)001:4029: yod pa bkod pa ni me tog gi 'phreng bas
NK107(tse)001:4030: bskor ba 'dra ba'i rin po che lnga yis yongs
NK107(tse)001:4031: su spras pa rab tu dang ba 'dren pa'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:4032: dang kyi bung zhes byed pa dang 'khor ba'i dpung
NK107(tse)001:4033: 'joms pa zhes bya ba dang brgyal ba slong ba
NK107(tse)001:4034: zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byin pa'o rab tu bsing ba
NK107(tse)001:4035: dang dag pa dang gdung ba dang bde ba dang
NK107(tse)001:4036: yid gzhungs pa zhes bya ba'i dbyangs sna tshogs 'byung
NK107(tse)001:4037: ba'i gzhi yod pas dga' bde la spyod cing nyon
NK107(tse)001:4038: mongs pa sngon du rgyu bag la nyal ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:4039: lta bu'i zhing khams na ston pa glang po che
NK107(tse)001:4040: kun du mtha' yas par zhes bya ba 'khor gnod
NK107(tse)001:4041: sbyin stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa lngas yongs su bskor
NK107(tse)001:4042: cing mdun du 'dar nas rab tu 'dun cing dad
NK107(tse)001:4043: do bstan pa ni dus 'byung bar nges par byed
NK107(tse)001:4044: pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so zhes zhing khams drug
NK107(tse)001:4045: pa thal ba'i rgyun zhes bya ba bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:4046: ni bdun pa rab tu thal bas khyab zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4047: ba bstan pa ni zhing khams de'i steng nas 'di
NK107(tse)001:4048: dag rnams la dpag tshad brgya brgya'i nam mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:4049: zhing khams dpag tshad khri phrag bdun bdun yod pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4050: de dag gi ming ni yangs pa dang 'byed pa
NK107(tse)001:4051: dang gsal ba dang mi g.yo ba dang mnyam pa
NK107(tse)001:4052: dang mi snyam pa dang mnyam pa dang mi mnyam
NK107(tse)001:4053: pa zhes bya ba dang mdzes pa dang rab mdzes
NK107(tse)001:4054: dang 'jigs bral dang dga' ba'i dbyangs dang bkod pa
NK107(tse)001:4055: dag pa dang bkod pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4056: snying pos brgyan pa dang ros gang ba dang rims
NK107(tse)001:4057: ldan dang rims ldan chen po dang yang byed dang
NK107(tse)001:4058: dbyangs kyis mdzes pa dang dris rab tu gdangs pa
NK107(tse)001:4059: dang sgra 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i gzhi dang reg
NK107(tse)001:4060: ldan nyi ma zhes bya'o ston pa ni blo gros
NK107(tse)001:4061: stong ldan dang nyi mas sbyin dang zla ba'i sbyin
NK107(tse)001:4062: dang skar ma'i rgyangs po dang 'od kyis spras pa
NK107(tse)001:4063: dang gser gdugs kyis bstibs pa dang chags pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4064: bral ba dang sdang ba gcod pa dang mgon pos
NK107(tse)001:4065: rol ba dang cod pan gyi rgyal po dang nor
NK107(tse)001:4066: bu'i phreng ba dang dpag med 'od dang gsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4067: snying po dang khams las rgyal ba dang sgras 'byin
NK107(tse)001:4068: pa dang seng ges bsgyings pa dang zla bas spras
NK107(tse)001:4069: pa dang dge bas rdzogs pa dang sdig bral skyob
NK107(tse)001:4070: pa dang nges 'joms stong ldan dang theg pas 'jog
NK107(tse)001:4071: pa chen po'o 'khor ni skye dgu'i bdag po dang
NK107(tse)001:4072: ljon pa'i rgyal po dang seng ge'i rgyal po dang
NK107(tse)001:4073: grags 'byin gyi rgyal po dang grul bum gyi dang
NK107(tse)001:4074: grib gnon dang 'jug srid dang dra ba can dang
NK107(tse)001:4075: ri'i mdangs dang dpa' ba'i yid can gyi bu dang
NK107(tse)001:4076: dga' byed dbang phyug gi bu dang smin drug gi
NK107(tse)001:4077: bu dang lag na be con gyi bu dang lag
NK107(tse)001:4078: na 'khor lo can gyi bu dang srin mo dang
NK107(tse)001:4079: khyab 'jug mo dang tshangs pa mo dang gser dmigs
NK107(tse)001:4080: can gyis yongs su spras pa dang 'phreng thogs kyi
NK107(tse)001:4081: bu dang ka lan ta'i bu mo dang rigs can
NK107(tse)001:4082: gyi bu ste de dag stong phrag nyi shu lnga'am
NK107(tse)001:4083: nyi shus yongs su bskor ba'o bstan pa ni dam
NK107(tse)001:4084: pa'i chos rtse mo dpungs pa dang rin po che
NK107(tse)001:4085: bskod pa dang lha'i nyi ma dang klu dbang gi
NK107(tse)001:4086: zla ba dang 'gro drug gcod pa dang ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4087: sgron ma nges pa dang skyes pa rab kyis 'jug
NK107(tse)001:4088: pa dang ched du barjoda pa rnam par dag pa
NK107(tse)001:4089: dang spugs 'byin par byed pa dang gzengs bstod par
NK107(tse)001:4090: byed pa dang pad ma dkar po dang rtogs pa
NK107(tse)001:4091: nges barjoda dang snyan pas 'jugs pa dang 'bar ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4092: me lce dang yang dag snying po dang snang ba
NK107(tse)001:4093: thabs sbyor dang sa la'i rgyal po dang bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4094: las rgyas pa dang bsrung ba'i 'khor lo dang sra
NK107(tse)001:4095: ba 'jom pa dang dam pa'i chos 'phen par byed
NK107(tse)001:4096: pa la sogs pas bsgrogs so de'i steng nas dpag
NK107(tse)001:4097: tshad lnga brgya'i steng na rab tu ni dri ma
NK107(tse)001:4098: med cing sdug basngala dang bral ba'o thal ba zhes
NK107(tse)001:4099: pa ni rin po che nor bu rag ldan gyis
NK107(tse)001:4100: yongs su brdal ba'o khyab ces bya ba ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:4101: la dpag tshad bdun khri bdun stong srid dang dpangs
NK107(tse)001:4102: mnyam pa la steng 'og thams cad du ye shes
NK107(tse)001:4103: kyi sprin bkod pas khyab pa'o dmigs pas dag pa
NK107(tse)001:4104: ni de dag khang bzang rnams kyang phyi nas bltas
NK107(tse)001:4105: pas nang gsal ba nang nas bltas pas phyi gsal
NK107(tse)001:4106: ba phyi nang med par zang thal ba'o rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:4107: du ni zhes pa ni yod pa dang med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4108: bye brag las rnam par 'phrul pa'o phyi rin po
NK107(tse)001:4109: che shel dang nang rin po che mthon mthing la
NK107(tse)001:4110: dri ma med pas zang thal du snang ba'o ston
NK107(tse)001:4111: pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das dpa' bas 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:4112: gtsug gi nor chen zhes bya ba la 'khor lha'i
NK107(tse)001:4113: bu bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gis yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4114: bskor cing mdun du bltas so de dag re re
NK107(tse)001:4115: la 'khor grags 'byin ma'i bu mo lnga stong gis
NK107(tse)001:4116: bskor ba'o bstan pa chos kyi bdud rtsis myos pa
NK107(tse)001:4117: zhes bya ba sgrogs so de yang 'byung ba'i ros
NK107(tse)001:4118: myos pa legs par myos pa zhes bya ba ston
NK107(tse)001:4119: to de dag so so'i byed pa'i rgyu dad pa
NK107(tse)001:4120: dang shes rab rkyen bstan pa'i chos bsten pa khyab
NK107(tse)001:4121: pa sems dang ye shes 'jug pa mnyam bzhag dang
NK107(tse)001:4122: rjes thob la gnas pa'o zhes zhing khams bdun pa
NK107(tse)001:4123: rab tu thal ba zhes bya ba bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:4124: ni zhing khams brgyad pa thal ba'i sgra zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4125: ba bstan pa ni zhing khams 'di nas 'jig pa
NK107(tse)001:4126: las rten pa bag chags so lho shar du bcal
NK107(tse)001:4127: ba'i g.yon gyi phyogs nas thad kar gzhal ba'i bar
NK107(tse)001:4128: bar na dpag tshad lnga bcu yod pa'i phar 'das
NK107(tse)001:4129: pa na zhing dpag tshad lnga brgya lnga brgya yod
NK107(tse)001:4130: pa de'i ming ni 'khros pa bzhi dang dpung bkod
NK107(tse)001:4131: pa dang sa'i snying po dang nam makha'i 'od dang
NK107(tse)001:4132: rgyun du dga' ba dang las mtha' gcod pa'i dpung
NK107(tse)001:4133: ngo ston pa ni rdo rje 'joms pa dang rdo
NK107(tse)001:4134: rje chen po rnam par sgyings pa dang nyi ma'i
NK107(tse)001:4135: 'od zer stong gi spyi phud dang nam makha'i 'od
NK107(tse)001:4136: dang bdud rtsi'i 'od kyis mun pa sel ba dang
NK107(tse)001:4137: gnyis 'jug rdzogs pa'i phyag go 'khor ni dga' byed
NK107(tse)001:4138: kyi bu dang 'jug srid mo dang ma mo dang
NK107(tse)001:4139: rengs byed ma dang bsil byed ma rgyal bas phyin
NK107(tse)001:4140: pa'i 'khor stong phrag lnga lngas yongs su bskor ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4141: bstan pa ni chu'i dpung 'joms pa dang sa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:4142: me'i dang rlung gi dang nam makha'i dang 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4143: las 'joms pa zhes bya ba rnams so bsgrogs so
NK107(tse)001:4144: de ltar 'jug pa lus la brten pa sems khams
NK107(tse)001:4145: ni tshogs pa drug 'das pa na thal ba ni
NK107(tse)001:4146: gsera gyi me tog sila mas rab tu brdal ba
NK107(tse)001:4147: sgra ni ring ba dang thung ba dang gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:4148: dang drag pa dang rgyun ring ba dang mi phyed
NK107(tse)001:4149: pa la sogs pa rnams 'byung ba dang zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4150: ba ni ming ngo skyob byed ni bdud dang mu
NK107(tse)001:4151: stegs rnams las so 'phan ni 'od la kha dog
NK107(tse)001:4152: lnga yis phye ba'o cis rab tu bsrungs ba ni
NK107(tse)001:4153: rin po che lnga las grub pa'i dar gyi lda
NK107(tse)001:4154: ldis phyogs kun nas bslubs pa ni la phyogs bzhi
NK107(tse)001:4155: rab tu mdzes pa'i rgyal mtshan kha dog sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:4156: pa bsgreng ba ste de yang shar phyogs na dngul
NK107(tse)001:4157: la rin po che sna tshogs pas spras pa'i rgyal
NK107(tse)001:4158: mtshan dang lho na beed+aur+ya dang nub na byi ru
NK107(tse)001:4159: dang byang phyogs na in+da ni la las grub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4160: rin po che sna tshogs pas spras pa'i rgyal mtshan
NK107(tse)001:4161: rnams bsgreng ngo mtshams bzhi na rin po che dmar
NK107(tse)001:4162: chen la sogs pa'i gdugs la dril bu g.yer kha'i
NK107(tse)001:4163: dra bas rnam par spras pa la sogs pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4164: dar kha dog gsal ba'i phye ma phur ma dang
NK107(tse)001:4165: rnga yab sna tshogs pa rnams bsgreng pa'o nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:4166: las dus dus su me tog sil ma'i char 'bab
NK107(tse)001:4167: pa gyur cing de nyid babs pa tsam las dri
NK107(tse)001:4168: zhim pa sna tshogs pa 'bab pa'o de'i ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4169: 'khor lo stong dang ldan pa zhes ba la 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4170: byang chub sems dpa' 'bum phrag gnyis kyis bskor ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4171: de dag re re la lha'i bu rang du ba
NK107(tse)001:4172: tsang ba lnga brgya lnga brgyas yongs su bskor pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4173: de lta bu nyid la bstan pa ni bde ba
NK107(tse)001:4174: rol pa 'byung ba zhes bya ba sgrogs so 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4175: de dag gi mtshan nyid mdzes byed gzugs rab tu
NK107(tse)001:4176: ldem bag dang ldan pa la sgra snyan tha dad
NK107(tse)001:4177: pa dang ye shes dang las las grub pa'i tshogs
NK107(tse)001:4178: kyis yongs su bskor ba'o zhes zhing khams brgyad pa
NK107(tse)001:4179: thal ba'i sgra zhes bya ba bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:4180: zhing khams dgu pa thal ba'i rlung zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4181: bstan pa ni 'di nas 'jig pa 'dus byas brten
NK107(tse)001:4182: pa rang rig pa lho nub nas brtsub 'gyur gyi
NK107(tse)001:4183: nam mkha' zhes bya ba'i dus snyam pa la nam
NK107(tse)001:4184: mkha' nas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo 'bab pa yod do
NK107(tse)001:4185: de'i g.yas na brtse ba'i 'jig rten zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4186: na 'jig rten gyi sgra dbyings kyi 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:4187: gnas so de nas 'og na sgra ldan gyi nam
NK107(tse)001:4188: mkha' zhes bya ba dpag tshad lnga yod de 'di
NK107(tse)001:4189: la skabs su sgra mi snyan pa dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:4190: pa nam mkha' nas 'ong ngo de'i 'og na zhing
NK107(tse)001:4191: dngos byed chen po ston pa rin po che mang
NK107(tse)001:4192: yod 'khor rgyu ldan gyi 'gro ba lnga stong bstan
NK107(tse)001:4193: pa nyi zla zung 'jug go sgra mi snyan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4194: nam mkha' dpag tshad lnga las rab tu sgra mi
NK107(tse)001:4195: snyan pa sgrogs pa dag gi 'og na zhing ka
NK107(tse)001:4196: ru si ta zhes dpag tshad bdun stong ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4197: bcud 'dus chen po 'khor lnga ldan gyi khye'u dgu
NK107(tse)001:4198: brgya dang dgu stong gis bskor bstan pa bdud kyis
NK107(tse)001:4199: gnon pa'o de'i 'og na yid 'dod kyi nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:4200: dpag tshad lnga stong yod pa las nam mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:4201: gser gyi bye ma'i char dus dus su bab pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4202: de'i 'og na zhing dpungs pa'i 'khor lo dpag tshad
NK107(tse)001:4203: khri yod pa ston pa gser ldan 'od bsrungs 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4204: zag pa med pa lnga stong lnga brgya bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:4205: rgya mtsho'i gting zab par ston pa'o yang de'i 'og
NK107(tse)001:4206: na dri ldan gyi nam mkha' dpag tshad drug las
NK107(tse)001:4207: skabs su dri sna tshogs pa 'byung ba'o /
NK107(tse)001:4208: de'i 'og na zhing khams 'khor lo rnam par 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:4209: pa ston pa mkhyen pa rdzogs pa 'khor 'dab bzangs
NK107(tse)001:4210: kyi rigs lnga stong bstan pa dub pa gseng ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4211: de'i 'og na rab tu bslan pa'i nam mkha' dpag
NK107(tse)001:4212: tshad lnga brgya de las rab tu tsha ba'i chu'i
NK107(tse)001:4213: char dus dus su 'babs pa'o de'i 'og zhing gser
NK107(tse)001:4214: gyi dong rtse brtsegs pa dpag tshad khri yod pa
NK107(tse)001:4215: na ston pa seng ge 'jug pa la 'khor ltos
NK107(tse)001:4216: bsgyur gyi 'gro ba stong phrag dgus bskor ba las
NK107(tse)001:4217: bstan pa las rab brgyas pa'o de'i 'og na rang
NK107(tse)001:4218: ldan gyis nam mkha' dpag tshad sum cu la spu
NK107(tse)001:4219: gri'i char 'bab pa'i 'og na zhing bde bas 'byin
NK107(tse)001:4220: pa dpag tshad dgu brgya pa na ston pa legs
NK107(tse)001:4221: par skyob pa yis 'khor chu 'dzin gyi rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:4222: sum stong la bstan pa 'o ma'i sprin zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4223: ba bsgrogs so de ltar drug 'das pa'i 'og na
NK107(tse)001:4224: yid 'ong gi nam mkha' dpag tshad bcu pa las
NK107(tse)001:4225: gzugs la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon tan yid du
NK107(tse)001:4226: 'ong ba'i b+ham zhig 'byung ngo de'i 'og nas tha
NK107(tse)001:4227: mal pa'i bar snang las 'gro zhing lding ba nyid
NK107(tse)001:4228: la rlung zhes pa 'gro ba dang bskyod pa'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:4229: las snyan cing spro ba dag 'byung la g.yo zhing
NK107(tse)001:4230: sa'i las kyi byed pa bskyod pas bar snang gi
NK107(tse)001:4231: khams la zhing khams 'di phan tshun du 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:4232: dang de bzhin du g.yo zhing du lding ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:4233: nyid bskyod pa las ni sangs rgyas dang chos dang
NK107(tse)001:4234: dge 'dun gyi sgra rnams 'byung ngo dpag tshad stong
NK107(tse)001:4235: phrag bcu bzhi yod do ston pa ni mar me
NK107(tse)001:4236: 'dzin chen po la 'khor dgra bcom pa sum khri
NK107(tse)001:4237: dang lnga stong gis bskor ba la de dag re
NK107(tse)001:4238: re la'ng klu'i bu mo lnga brgyas bskor ba la
NK107(tse)001:4239: bstan pa tshad bstan gyi rlung gis rab tu g.yo
NK107(tse)001:4240: ba lnga ldan chen po zhes bya ba bsgrogs so
NK107(tse)001:4241: 'di'i dus na khyad par gyi 'jug pa rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:4242: gsum yin no zhes zhing khams dgu pa thal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4243: rlung zhes bya ba bstan nas da ni zhing khams
NK107(tse)001:4244: bcu pa rin po che'i rlung thal ba zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4245: bstan pa ni de'i steng na 'byung ba'i dris myos
NK107(tse)001:4246: pa zhes bya ba'i nam mkha' dpag tshad drug brgya
NK107(tse)001:4247: drug brgya yod pa'i so so'i steng na 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:4248: gyi khams bcu gsum yod pa ni dran pa'i gling
NK107(tse)001:4249: dpag tshad brgyad cu gser ldan gyi gling nyis brgya
NK107(tse)001:4250: sgra 'byin gyi gling bdun stong rengs pa'i gling lnga
NK107(tse)001:4251: stong khams ldan gyi gling stong phrag gnyis spu gri'i
NK107(tse)001:4252: 'khor lo'i gling khri ba lding spyod kyi gling nyi
NK107(tse)001:4253: khri ba 'gon byed kyi gling dgu stong pa sgra
NK107(tse)001:4254: dang sgra byed pa dang pu sha dang ki la
NK107(tse)001:4255: sa dang bzhi ni dgu stong pa'o bkod pa brtsegs
NK107(tse)001:4256: pa'i gling khri phrag lnga yod pa ste 'di dag
NK107(tse)001:4257: ni zhing ma yin te 'jig rten mi phal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4258: skye gnas so de ltar bcu gsum brtsegs pa na
NK107(tse)001:4259: de'i steng gser gyi gdung bsgrogs pa zhes pa'i nam
NK107(tse)001:4260: mkha' dpag tshad drug yod pa'i steng na rin po
NK107(tse)001:4261: che ni dpag tu med pa spungs pa'o thal ba
NK107(tse)001:4262: zhes bya ba ni gzhal med khang stong dgu brgya
NK107(tse)001:4263: dgu bcu rtsa lnga yod pa las de dag re
NK107(tse)001:4264: re la rab tu mdzes shing bkra shis pa'i nyi
NK107(tse)001:4265: ma 'bum 'bum gyis brgyan pa'o de yang nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:4266: la bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa stong stong
NK107(tse)001:4267: lha rnams kyis barjoda par byed do de yang zhing
NK107(tse)001:4268: khams dpag tu med pa dgu khri dgu stong yod
NK107(tse)001:4269: pa'i nang na gzhal med khang re re la nyi
NK107(tse)001:4270: ma 'bum 'bum yod pa rlung gis bskyod pa las
NK107(tse)001:4271: ni lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin dang tshangs pa
NK107(tse)001:4272: dang sing g+ha la'i sgra 'byung ngo de nyid thos
NK107(tse)001:4273: pa la brten nas ngag gis bde ba nyams su
NK107(tse)001:4274: myong bar 'gyur ro rnams kyis spras pa ni 'od
NK107(tse)001:4275: dpag tu med pa 'phro ba'o gzugs phun sum tshogs
NK107(tse)001:4276: pa la sogs te 'dod pa'i yon tan rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:4277: brgyan pa'o 'phrul gyi yi ge ni rtsa la gnas
NK107(tse)001:4278: pa'i a li dang ka li ri mo ni ka
NK107(tse)001:4279: li'i 'phreng bas lus la bskor a lis mgo la
NK107(tse)001:4280: bskor mdzes pa kha dog sna tshogs pas bris pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4281: de la dgos pa ni 'byung po'i nad las grol
NK107(tse)001:4282: ba dang gdon dang 'byung po las grol ba dang
NK107(tse)001:4283: mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams las grol ba ni ma
NK107(tse)001:4284: 'ongs pa'i dus kyi yon tan la dmigs pa'o ston
NK107(tse)001:4285: pa ni sangs rgyas ring bsrel gyis rnam par brgyan
NK107(tse)001:4286: pa'o de la 'khor mgrin bcu'i bdag po dgu khri
NK107(tse)001:4287: dang dgu stong gis bskor ba'o de re re la
NK107(tse)001:4288: tshangs pa'i bu mo lnga brgya lnga brgyas yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4289: bskor ba'o bstan pa ni chos thams cad kyi gzugs
NK107(tse)001:4290: brnyan rab tu rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid ces bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4291: bsgrogs so de yang de dag gi bar bar na
NK107(tse)001:4292: dar gyis lda ldi rab tu spras pa zhing khams
NK107(tse)001:4293: de nas nam mkha' las pad ma rab tu mdzes
NK107(tse)001:4294: pa stong phrag du ma'i cha 'bab cing rin po
NK107(tse)001:4295: che rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i gzugs kyis rab tu
NK107(tse)001:4296: mdzes par byas pa'o zhes 'jig rten bcu pa rin
NK107(tse)001:4297: po che'i thal ba zhes bya ba bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:4298: ni zhing khams bcu gcig pa 'dul ba'i thal ba
NK107(tse)001:4299: zhes bya ba bstan pa ni 'di nas nub byang
NK107(tse)001:4300: mtshams kyi steng na g.yo ba dgu ldan zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4301: ba'i nam makha'i steng na 'jig pa gzugs la rten
NK107(tse)001:4302: pa nam mkha' 'o khams ni 'khrugs shing 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:4303: zhing bskyod pa dam pa dpag tshad bdun stong ston
NK107(tse)001:4304: pa ye shes bkod pa bstan pa snyigs ma 'jig
NK107(tse)001:4305: pa 'khor sred med kyi bu mo dgu brgya lnga
NK107(tse)001:4306: bcu'o de'i steng na lhag mthong gi nam mkha' dpag
NK107(tse)001:4307: tshad khri de'i steng na 'jig rten sred bral zhes
NK107(tse)001:4308: bya ba dpag tshad lnga stong bdun brgya ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4309: legs pa'i rdo rje 'khor dga' ldan bu khri phrag
NK107(tse)001:4310: gcig dang bstan pa dam pa bkod pa'o yang nam
NK107(tse)001:4311: mkha' 'dzin bral zhes bya ba lnga brgya'i steng na
NK107(tse)001:4312: zhing srid pa zhi ba zhes bya ba lnga stong
NK107(tse)001:4313: la ston pa snying po gzugs mdzes zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4314: 'khor skyor bral gyi bu mo stong bstan pa chos
NK107(tse)001:4315: kyis bkod pa'o yang nam mkha' skye ba gdang ba
NK107(tse)001:4316: khri phrag dgu'i steng na zhing 'khor lo legs spyod
NK107(tse)001:4317: dpag tshad khri gnyis ston pa gdung sel chen po
NK107(tse)001:4318: 'khor gzhon nu'i bu mo lnga stong bstan pa khyad
NK107(tse)001:4319: par 'dus pa zhes bya ba'o yang yid rol gyi
NK107(tse)001:4320: nam mkha' 'bum phrag gnyis kyi steng na zhing bde
NK107(tse)001:4321: byed rol pa khri phrag gnyis ston pa sde 'joms
NK107(tse)001:4322: pa chen po la 'khor 'gro ba mi'i 'du ba
NK107(tse)001:4323: lnga stong bstan pa gnas 'jug stongs pa'o 'du ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4324: 'byung ba'i khyad par las thal ba zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4325: ni 'od ma'i mdangs kyis kun nas 'khrugs pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:4326: la dpag tshad stong phrag bco brgyad yod pa gzugs
NK107(tse)001:4327: gang yin pa la mchod pa gzugs la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:4328: lnga rdzogs pas gzhal med khang re re la lha
NK107(tse)001:4329: mo g.yog mo lnga bcu dang bcas pa dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:4330: med pas yongs su mchod par byed pa'o nang 'od
NK107(tse)001:4331: kyis khengs shing rlung gis bskyod pa la tsan dan
NK107(tse)001:4332: gyi dri 'byung bar byed pa'o ston pa ni lo
NK107(tse)001:4333: bcu drug lon cing rab tu mdzes pa dkar ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4334: mdangs yod pa la zhabs rnams la 'khor lo ldan
NK107(tse)001:4335: pa la rin po che rnams kyis rab tu mdzes
NK107(tse)001:4336: par byas pa'o de ltar khyad par gyi yon tan
NK107(tse)001:4337: gzugs bzang la dbang po rnams shin tu dag pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4338: de lta bu'i ston pa la 'khor nyan thos dgu
NK107(tse)001:4339: khri dang dgu stong gis bskor ba de dag re
NK107(tse)001:4340: re la tshe dang ldan pa stong phrag re res
NK107(tse)001:4341: bskor ba'o bstan pa ni rin po che cha snyam
NK107(tse)001:4342: pa zhes bya ba bsgrogs so 'khor ni de dag
NK107(tse)001:4343: kyang rab tu gzhon pa dbang po 'dul zhing khrims
NK107(tse)001:4344: dang ldan pa dge slong dang dge slong ma'i gzugs
NK107(tse)001:4345: 'dzin pa rnams kyis bskor ba'o zhes zhing khams bcu
NK107(tse)001:4346: gcig pa 'du ba'i thal ba zhes bya ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:4347: nas da ni zhing khams bcu gnyis pa dung ldan
NK107(tse)001:4348: gyi thal ba zhes bya ba bstan pa ni de'i
NK107(tse)001:4349: 'og na g.yos 'gyur gyi nam mkha' dpag tshad dgu
NK107(tse)001:4350: khri bzhi stong yod pa la rlung rab tu 'bar
NK107(tse)001:4351: ba gnag cing 'tshub pa'i sgra sgrogs cing phyogs kun
NK107(tse)001:4352: nas 'bud par byed pa'i 'og na rab tu mtshon
NK107(tse)001:4353: chas rnam par spras pa'i 'jig rten zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4354: dpag tshad bdun stong pa na ston pa dga' ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4355: dbyangs la 'khor grags 'byin ma lnga stong gis bskor
NK107(tse)001:4356: zhing bstan pa bdud rtsi 'dus pa'o de'i 'og na
NK107(tse)001:4357: me rlung gi dpag tshad lnga stong pa las skabs
NK107(tse)001:4358: su me rlung gi sgra drag cing 'khrug par byed
NK107(tse)001:4359: pa las de'i 'og na zhing dong rtse rnam par
NK107(tse)001:4360: brtsegs pa dpag tshad sum stong pa na ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4361: blo'i stobs ldan 'jigs skyob 'khor 'dun pa dag pa
NK107(tse)001:4362: brgya phrag lngas bskor ba bstan pa me lce'i 'od
NK107(tse)001:4363: 'byin pa'o de'i 'og na kha dog 'khrug pa'i nam
NK107(tse)001:4364: mkha' dpag tshad khri khrag gnyis de'i 'og na zhing
NK107(tse)001:4365: ba ti pa la lnga stong ston pa 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:4366: rab tu sbyin pa 'khor tshangs rigs kyi lha lnga
NK107(tse)001:4367: brgya bstan pa sgron ma nges pa'o de'i 'og na
NK107(tse)001:4368: nam mkha' gser gyi char pa 'bab pa'i 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:4369: can lnga stong zhing rtogs pa sgra 'byin pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:4370: bya ba dpag tshad sum stong ston pa yon tan
NK107(tse)001:4371: mtha' yas pa bstan pa ral gyi'i dpung gis brtse
NK107(tse)001:4372: ba'o de'i 'og na sde'i sgra 'byin pa'i nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:4373: drug khri bzhi stong na zhing 'bar ba'i 'od 'phros
NK107(tse)001:4374: rnam par spras pa dpag tshad bdun khri ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4375: mya ngan med pa 'khor dpa' ba'i 'gro ba dpag
NK107(tse)001:4376: tshad stong phrag lngas bskor ba bstan pa rgyud brten
NK107(tse)001:4377: rab tu bkod pa'o de'i 'og na mtha' mi g.yo
NK107(tse)001:4378: ba mi gsal ba'i nam mkha' gnyis khri de'i 'og
NK107(tse)001:4379: na rnam brgyad g.yo ldan lnga stong na ston pa
NK107(tse)001:4380: dbu'i gtsug tor gyis 'khor ba 'jig pa la 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4381: 'dod pa na spyod pa'i lha'i bu lnga brgya bstan
NK107(tse)001:4382: pa 'byung ba'i bcud zhes bya ba'o de'i 'og na
NK107(tse)001:4383: ser gsal gyi nam mkha' la dpag tshad drug khri
NK107(tse)001:4384: nyis brgya de'i 'og na zhing legs spras 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:4385: zhes bya ba dpag tshad lnga stong brgyad brgya ston
NK107(tse)001:4386: pa las kyis rab 'joms 'khor skye dgu'i gtso bo
NK107(tse)001:4387: stong phrag lnga bstan pa gdung ba rab 'byed do
NK107(tse)001:4388: yang nam mkha' dmar nag 'khros pa khri phrag brgyad
NK107(tse)001:4389: zhing gsal ba'i nyi ma lnga stong ston pa ting
NK107(tse)001:4390: 'dzin byed pa 'khor sa'i lha mo dgu brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:4391: dgu bcu bstan pa pad ma'i gdung rnam par bkod
NK107(tse)001:4392: pa'o de nas kyi 'og na dmar mthing gis spras
NK107(tse)001:4393: pa'i nam mkha' dpag tshad dgu khri dang dgu stong
NK107(tse)001:4394: gi 'og na dgu pa dung ltar dkar ba'i zhing
NK107(tse)001:4395: sa gzhi rab tu 'jam pa thal ba'i ni sa
NK107(tse)001:4396: rnams brdal zhing rab tu 'gyur ba lha zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4397: ba ni khyad par gyi yon tan dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:4398: pa yod pa'o de na rab tu ngad cing bde
NK107(tse)001:4399: ba skye ba'i dri dang gsung pa'i dri yis ston
NK107(tse)001:4400: pa dang 'khor du bcas pa rab tu myos te
NK107(tse)001:4401: bde ba la reg pa'o kha dog nyer lngas 'khyug
NK107(tse)001:4402: cing rab tu 'bar ba'i 'od rnams kyis khengs te
NK107(tse)001:4403: de dag kyang rab tu mer mer po yis kun
NK107(tse)001:4404: tu sprin gyi phung po ltar 'khrigs pa dag yod
NK107(tse)001:4405: do ston pa nyid ni gzi brjid kyis rnam par
NK107(tse)001:4406: brgyan pa zhing khams dpag tshad 'bum phrag cig yod
NK107(tse)001:4407: pa na 'khor ni skye ba gnyis kyis thogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4408: byang chub sems dpa' sha stag dgu khris yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4409: bskor ba de dag re re la mchod pa'i lha
NK107(tse)001:4410: mo lnga lngas rab tu mchod pa'o bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4411: skyes pa rab kyi sde zhes bya ba ston no
NK107(tse)001:4412: ston pa de'i 'khor longs spyod dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:4413: rdzogs so zhes zhing khams bcu gnyis pa dung ldan
NK107(tse)001:4414: zhes bya ba bstan nas da ni zhing khams bcu
NK107(tse)001:4415: gsum pa skar ma'i thal ba zhes bya bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:4416: ni 'di nas ni dbus na gnas pa ste 'jig
NK107(tse)001:4417: rten las kyi rlung gis phan tshun du bskyod pas
NK107(tse)001:4418: 'jig rten gyi khams brgya dang stong dang brgya stong
NK107(tse)001:4419: bye ba khrag khrig grangs med pa 'khrug mar gnas
NK107(tse)001:4420: pa ste skar mad'i tshogs kyis nam mkha' yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4421: gang bar rab tu 'khrug pa ltar gnas pa'i dbus
NK107(tse)001:4422: skar ma'i rlung gis phan tshun du bskyod pa ste
NK107(tse)001:4423: dpag tshad khri dang lnga stong yod pa la rin
NK107(tse)001:4424: po che ze ba smu gu rnams kyis spras pa
NK107(tse)001:4425: thal ba zhes bya ba ni dur khrod kyi khang
NK107(tse)001:4426: bu brtsegs pa rnam pa sna tshogs pas bskor ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4427: 'khor lo ni phan tshun du bltas na lnga brgyar
NK107(tse)001:4428: brtsegs pa yan man du lnga stong du brtsegs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4429: rnam pa ni de dag re re la yang lnga
NK107(tse)001:4430: lnga dang dgu dgu yis yongs su brtsegs pa'o 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4431: lo de dag re re la yang lha'i grong khyer
NK107(tse)001:4432: lnga brgya lnga brgya yod pa rin po che char
NK107(tse)001:4433: ka dang nor bu sna tshogs pa'i chun 'phyangs rnams
NK107(tse)001:4434: kyis brgyan pa de dag kun gyi nang nas rab
NK107(tse)001:4435: tu 'jig shing skyi bung ba'i 'brug chen po sgra
NK107(tse)001:4436: drag pa dang glog dmar po rab tu sha g.ya'
NK107(tse)001:4437: ba 'khrug par byed pa dang gnod sbyin gyi rigs
NK107(tse)001:4438: stong phrag tu ma rab tu 'jig pa'i lce rnams
NK107(tse)001:4439: 'byin cing sgra yis sgrogs pa dang h'u zhes rab
NK107(tse)001:4440: tu grags pa'i sgra sna tshogs su 'byin pa na
NK107(tse)001:4441: ston pa ni dpal he ru kahrnama par 'khros pa
NK107(tse)001:4442: zhes bya bas 'khor rnams la gzugs rnam par 'phrul
NK107(tse)001:4443: ba ni dbu sum cu rtsa gnyis la phyag drug
NK107(tse)001:4444: cu rtsa bzhi pa zhabs lngar bsgrad pa rnam par
NK107(tse)001:4445: 'phrul zhing rab tu bsgyings pa'o 'khor rab tu 'khro
NK107(tse)001:4446: ba'i tshogs dbu gsum la phyag drug pa yod pa
NK107(tse)001:4447: dgu khris bskor te de dag re re la ma
NK107(tse)001:4448: mo'i rigs dang mkha' 'gro ma'i rigs brgya brgyas yongs
NK107(tse)001:4449: su bskor ba'o bstan pa ni lung chen po bco
NK107(tse)001:4450: brgyad la gzer chen po drug drug gis yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4451: bskor ba'o bstan pa khyad par can de nyid la
NK107(tse)001:4452: 'od byung bas dpag tu med pa'i 'od kyis 'phreng
NK107(tse)001:4453: ba yongs su bskor ba las klu'i gdung zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:4454: ba'i bstan pa'i las khyad par can rnams 'byung ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4455: de ltar khyad par gyi zhing rnam par dag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4456: yon tan las phyogs thams cad me ri'i rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:4457: dur khrod kyi rang bzhin du 'phro ba las mtshams
NK107(tse)001:4458: pa kun nas rab tu gsal ba'i nyi ma mang
NK107(tse)001:4459: po 'byung bar byed pa ste gzhi khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:4460: byed pa'o zhes zhing bcu gnyis te thal ba'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:4461: dang zhing khams bstan pa la nying lag bcu gsum
NK107(tse)001:4462: du byas nas bstan no da ni zhus don lnga
NK107(tse)001:4463: pa'i yan lag gi don gnyis pa thal 'gyur gyi
NK107(tse)001:4464: sgra don nges par bstan pa la drug gis bstan
NK107(tse)001:4465: pa'i dang po dam bca' dang gtan tshigs nges pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4466: mtshan nyid bstan pa ni rang dang gzhan gyis dam
NK107(tse)001:4467: baca'i tshig ces pa la sogs pas bstan te rang
NK107(tse)001:4468: gi 'dod pa rdzogs pa chen po mtha' bral yongs
NK107(tse)001:4469: rdzogs zhes bya bar 'dod pa pha rol po gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4470: gyi dam baca'i tshig ji skad zer ba longs par
NK107(tse)001:4471: bya ste rang gi 'dod pa'i tshig gis nges par
NK107(tse)001:4472: gsal te rang skyon nges par brtags pas de sel
NK107(tse)001:4473: ba'i tshig la mkhas par bya ste rang gi dang
NK107(tse)001:4474: gzhan gyi 'dod pa go bar bya ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:4475: dam bca' mtha' bral yongs rdzogs te mtha' dang bral
NK107(tse)001:4476: bas gang du yang ma grub la yongs su rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:4477: pas spangs blang gang du yang ma phye ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:4478: ltar yin par cis shes na lung dang rigs pas
NK107(tse)001:4479: man ngag gis shes te lung ni mtha' dang bral
NK107(tse)001:4480: ba yongs su rdzogs zhes pa dang mtha' bral 'di
NK107(tse)001:4481: la 'gag pa ci zhes pa dang gzhan gyi lung
NK107(tse)001:4482: las kyang kun bral nyag gcig ci ma spangs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:4483: zhes mdo las lung gsungs pa dang sems sde las
NK107(tse)001:4484: kyang yongs su rdzogs pa bsngo dang bral zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:4485: dang yod mtha' rdzogs la med mtha' rdzogs zhes gsungs
NK107(tse)001:4486: pa la sogs pa lung drangs na dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:4487: do rig pa ni rtag chad kyi mtha' yod med
NK107(tse)001:4488: dang gnyis ka dang gnyis ka ma yin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4489: bral bas rang gshis su yod pa dang gzhan gyi
NK107(tse)001:4490: 'dod pa bral bas tshig tsam du yang grub pa
NK107(tse)001:4491: med do de yang mtha' dang bral bas 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:4492: med la yongs su rdzogs pas phyogs su ma lhung
NK107(tse)001:4493: ba'o de yang ltos med gang shar gyi rigs pas
NK107(tse)001:4494: 'grub ste ltos med pas gang du yang yeng med
NK107(tse)001:4495: de gang yang mi 'gog la gang yang chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:4496: du shar bas bsgrub rgyu ci yang med pas mtha'
NK107(tse)001:4497: bral yongs rdzogs su rigs so man ngag ni kun
NK107(tse)001:4498: la dgags bsgrub med pa b+ha zhig tu bshad pa
NK107(tse)001:4499: mang ngo de ltar lung rigs pa man ngag gis
NK107(tse)001:4500: skyon bsal bas rang 'dod la yid ches la dam
NK107(tse)001:4501: bca' bzhi bsgrub pa ni gcig shes kun grol ba
NK107(tse)001:4502: ste chos nyid gcig pur thams cad shes pas bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:4503: pa'o de ltar rang gi bsgrub mtha' la dngos 'gal
NK107(tse)001:4504: dang rgyud 'gal dang rang gi tshig gis bsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4505: 'gal ba spang ngo de ltar 'gal ba'i skyon gsum
NK107(tse)001:4506: spangs te rang bzhin gyi don the tshom bsal ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4507: de yang rdzogs pa chen po'i don de cig shes
NK107(tse)001:4508: kun grol gyi gtan tshigs kyis bsgrubs pas gcig gang
NK107(tse)001:4509: du shes na chos nyid du shes pas so kun
NK107(tse)001:4510: snang grags kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad du grol
NK107(tse)001:4511: lo ci'i phyir grol na chos nyid du shes pas
NK107(tse)001:4512: so shes par cis shes na dngos po'i 'dug tshul
NK107(tse)001:4513: spang blang med pas so de'i phyir na shes bya
NK107(tse)001:4514: rang gnas kyi gtan tshigs thams cad la gzhig pa
NK107(tse)001:4515: dang rang gi dam bca' khas blang bar bya'o gnas
NK107(tse)001:4516: pa'i mkhar bzung ba ni rdzong brtsegs ma gsum ste
NK107(tse)001:4517: yang yin gyis 'gal ba snyam pa'i mtha' bsal mgo
NK107(tse)001:4518: snyam gyi yod med kyi mtha' bsal ltos med kyis
NK107(tse)001:4519: yin min gyi mtha' bsal lo de ltar gtan tshigs
NK107(tse)001:4520: kyis zur la 'bros pa ni rigs pas gnad bsal
NK107(tse)001:4521: ba'o phyogs bzhi ni gtan tshigs bzhi dang dam bca'
NK107(tse)001:4522: bzhi dang rigs pa bazhi'o dbus su ni rdzong gsum
NK107(tse)001:4523: la bzhi po rnams kyis 'khor lo bri ba ni
NK107(tse)001:4524: rang 'dod dang gzhan 'dod kyi 'gyur brtsi ba'o phyogs
NK107(tse)001:4525: nyal ni mu stegs rtag chad nas sems tsam man
NK107(tse)001:4526: chad dngos por smra ba yin pas b+hud thal ba
NK107(tse)001:4527: la gang gis kyang phan gnod ma grub pa'o dbu
NK107(tse)001:4528: ma nas sngags phyi nang gnyis stong par smra ba
NK107(tse)001:4529: ste 'di kun gyis kyang b+hud thal ba la phan
NK107(tse)001:4530: gnod du ma grub pa'o gtan tshigs gang gi phyir
NK107(tse)001:4531: na dngos po rang rgyud du zhen pas khams gsum
NK107(tse)001:4532: 'khor ba'i phyir dang stong pa'i mtha' bkag pas gzugs
NK107(tse)001:4533: med pa'i khams su 'ching bar byed pa las ma
NK107(tse)001:4534: gtogs pa med pa'i phyir ro de yang bsgrub bya'i
NK107(tse)001:4535: don la mngon par zhen pas khams gsum du 'ching
NK107(tse)001:4536: ba'o de yang dngos por smra ba'i chos nyid rang
NK107(tse)001:4537: gsal rgyu mtshan bral ba'i mtshan nyid ma rtogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4538: phyir gzhan la thal ba'i phyir sems tsam las rang
NK107(tse)001:4539: gi rig pa'i myong pa las don dam du 'dod
NK107(tse)001:4540: pa'i phyir dang mu stegs kyis rtag chad kyi rang
NK107(tse)001:4541: bzhin la don dam du 'dod pa'i phyir dang nyan
NK107(tse)001:4542: thos dang rang rgyal gyi chos dang gang zag la
NK107(tse)001:4543: don dam du 'dod pa'i phyir ro pha rol du
NK107(tse)001:4544: phyin pa dang sngags phyi nang gi stong pa nges
NK107(tse)001:4545: par 'jug pa dang bcas pa'i phyir ro de yang
NK107(tse)001:4546: ci'i phyir ma grub na sems tsam las gzhan phyi
NK107(tse)001:4547: rol gyi don ni med la rang rig pa myong
NK107(tse)001:4548: ba tsam du bden no zer na dam bca' mi
NK107(tse)001:4549: 'grub ste rang rig myong ba de skyes nas myong
NK107(tse)001:4550: ngam ma skyes par myong skyes na rtag pa la
NK107(tse)001:4551: skyes sam mi rtag pa la skyes sam gong ma
NK107(tse)001:4552: ltar na rang rig rtag pa la gong ma blo
NK107(tse)001:4553: bur ba gnyis 'gal lo mi rtag pa la skyes
NK107(tse)001:4554: na dgos med de rgyu rang rig rtag pa la
NK107(tse)001:4555: myong ba mi rtag pa skyes pa la dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:4556: med pa'i phyir gal te rang rig pa'i myong ba
NK107(tse)001:4557: de rang las skyes na yang thug med du 'gro
NK107(tse)001:4558: la gzhan las skyes na yang me las chu skye
NK107(tse)001:4559: bar thal ba'i skyon spang bar mi nus so de
NK107(tse)001:4560: bzhin du dbu ma'i kun rdzob don dam gyi dbye
NK107(tse)001:4561: ba mi 'thad pa dang kun rdzob nang gi dbye
NK107(tse)001:4562: ba log pa dang yang dag pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:4563: yang sgra nyams pas mi 'thad par so so'i skabs
NK107(tse)001:4564: su brtag go de bzhin du don dam la rnam
NK107(tse)001:4565: grangs dang rnam grangs ma yin pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:4566: yang mi 'thad do de yang dbu ma rang rgyud
NK107(tse)001:4567: pa'i snang ba chos can dam bca' bsgrub bya ma
NK107(tse)001:4568: grub ste snang ba chos can du bzhag pas chos
NK107(tse)001:4569: nyid mi skye ba dang gnyis pa gtan tshigs kyis
NK107(tse)001:4570: kyang mi 'grub ste gcig tu shes bya la grub
NK107(tse)001:4571: pa med pas du ma yang mi grub la gcig
NK107(tse)001:4572: spangs pa'i du ma mi 'grub pas so gsum pa
NK107(tse)001:4573: dpe barjoda kyang mi 'grub bo de ltar na phyi
NK107(tse)001:4574: rol pa dang dngos por smra ba gnyis la khyad
NK107(tse)001:4575: par med pas na rdzogs chen mtha' bral yongs su
NK107(tse)001:4576: rdzogs pa la 'di dag mi srid do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4577: na rang dang gzhan gnyis ka la dam bca' dang
NK107(tse)001:4578: bsgrub bya dang gtan tshigs gsum dag gis tshig gi
NK107(tse)001:4579: 'phen pas bskor ro rang gi bsgrub bya'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:4580: 'di nyid la mkhas pas chos nyid kyi rdzong la
NK107(tse)001:4581: bros shing snang btags thams cad la yang sbyar ro
NK107(tse)001:4582: des na rang dang gzhan gyi don dang pha rol
NK107(tse)001:4583: nyams par byed pa'i barjoda bya'o zhes nying lag gi
NK107(tse)001:4584: don dang po dam bca' dang gtan tshigs nges pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4585: mtshan nyid bstan nas da ni gnyis pa skyon yon
NK107(tse)001:4586: gyis bye brag gis rang gi don dang gzhan gyi
NK107(tse)001:4587: grub pa'i matha'i rnam pa bstan pa ni skyon ni
NK107(tse)001:4588: zhes pa ni rang dang ni dam bca' dang gtan
NK107(tse)001:4589: tshigs dang bsgrub bya'i skyon rnams la brtag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4590: de nas de sel ba'i barjoda bya bsam par bya
NK107(tse)001:4591: ba ni gzhan dngos po dang stong pa gnyis las
NK107(tse)001:4592: kyang dam bca' bsgrub bya gtan tshigs kyi skyon rnams
NK107(tse)001:4593: shes par byas la sun 'byin pa dang rang 'dod
NK107(tse)001:4594: bsgrub pa dang de la rang gi bsgrub bya la
NK107(tse)001:4595: rang skyon rang gis shes par byas la skyon bsal
NK107(tse)001:4596: ba'i barjoda bya bsam par bya'o rang gis 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4597: dam bca' mtha' bral yongs rdzogs yin la gtan tshigs
NK107(tse)001:4598: gcig shes kun grol bsgrub bya ltos med gang shar
NK107(tse)001:4599: ro de yang rdzong ni rol ba rang shar dang
NK107(tse)001:4600: gnas su rang dag pa la bros so de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4601: grub mtha' so so'i skyon rnams ngos bzung ste gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4602: 'dod dgag pa dang rang gi yon tan rnams ni
NK107(tse)001:4603: rdzogs par bya'o grub pa'i mtha' gzhan gyi yon tan
NK107(tse)001:4604: shes par byas la gzhan yon tan du 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4605: skyon rnams barjoda bya la mkhas pas brtag go de
NK107(tse)001:4606: yang sgra 'jug pa'i rgyu mtshan dang bshad pa'i rgyu
NK107(tse)001:4607: mtshan la brten nas don barjoda tshig tsam las de'i
NK107(tse)001:4608: skyon yon la brtags la de nyid la tshad las
NK107(tse)001:4609: bsogs pa shes par bya'o de yang dam bca' dang
NK107(tse)001:4610: 'brel ba dang de bzhin gtan tshigs dang bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4611: 'brel med pa'i mtshan nyid kyis shes par byas lah
NK107(tse)001:4612: gzhan 'dod nyams par bya ba'o de yang khyab byed
NK107(tse)001:4613: chen po'i skyon dang khyab chung pa'i skyon rnams gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4614: la thal 'gyur bartsi'o zhes nying lag gi don gnyis
NK107(tse)001:4615: pa skyon yon gyi bye brag gis rang dang gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4616: gyi grub pa'i mtha' bstan nas da ni nying lag
NK107(tse)001:4617: gis don gsum pa 'bigs par byed pa'i gtan tshigs
NK107(tse)001:4618: kyi 'khor lo bstan pa ni 'phen pa ni lus
NK107(tse)001:4619: kyi rlung la brten nas tshigs rnams phyi nang du
NK107(tse)001:4620: 'phos pa'i las byas pas rang dang pha rol gyi
NK107(tse)001:4621: gtan tshigs kyi 'khor lo rnams barjoda bya'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:4622: du shes par bya'o 'di'i dus na pha rol gyi
NK107(tse)001:4623: 'dod pa'i tshig dang de nyid zur tsam la brten
NK107(tse)001:4624: nas skyon dang yon tan dang skyon gyis bye brag
NK107(tse)001:4625: gzhog shes pa'i dgos pa yod pa dang de yang
NK107(tse)001:4626: zur bzhi las bsgrub bya dang gtan tshigs kyi 'khor
NK107(tse)001:4627: lo yis ni 'og dang zhes pa bsgrub byed kyi
NK107(tse)001:4628: 'khor lo ste rang gi 'dod pa ste 'bigs par
NK107(tse)001:4629: byed pa ste gzhan gyis 'dod pa nyams par byed
NK107(tse)001:4630: pa'o logs dang ni rdzong ste shes bya lnga bskor
NK107(tse)001:4631: gyis rdzong gis khams gsum dong sprugs su sbyar ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4632: zur la 'bigs par byed pa ni 'di nas kyang
NK107(tse)001:4633: dbu ma'i rten 'brel chos can snang ba rten 'brel
NK107(tse)001:4634: nyams par byed la chos nyid ni don dam rang
NK107(tse)001:4635: bzhin med zhes bya ba yang shes bya la ma
NK107(tse)001:4636: grub la tshul dag gis ni gsum la gtan tshigs
NK107(tse)001:4637: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba yang ma grub
NK107(tse)001:4638: la dper na gzugs brnyan bzhin zhes ba'i dpe barjoda
NK107(tse)001:4639: kyang ma grub pa'o gnyis gnyis ni dam bca' dang
NK107(tse)001:4640: bsgrub bya dang gtan tshigs dang dpe barjoda rnams la
NK107(tse)001:4641: skyon yon gnyis gnyis te brgyad du 'gyur ro 'jug
NK107(tse)001:4642: pas ni tshig gi rtogs pa bcug pas pha rol
NK107(tse)001:4643: rnams la 'bigs par byed do de ltar lus la
NK107(tse)001:4644: rlung brten pa rlung la tshig brten pas kyang pha
NK107(tse)001:4645: rol grub pa'i mtha' la 'bigs par byed do de
NK107(tse)001:4646: ltar lus kyi rlung gis kyang ni las dang nyon
NK107(tse)001:4647: mongs pa rnams kyang ring par 'phen par byed do
NK107(tse)001:4648: de ltar rlung de'i las ma dag pa las ye
NK107(tse)001:4649: shes 'phen par byed pa'o zhes gsum pa 'bigs par
NK107(tse)001:4650: byed pa'i gtan tshigs kyi 'khor lo bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:4651: ni nying don bzhi pa shes bya bzhi bskor gyi
NK107(tse)001:4652: sbyor ba la snang btags thams cad chos nying du
NK107(tse)001:4653: bsre ba bstan pa ni sbyor ba'i ni 'di ltar
NK107(tse)001:4654: snang bas bsdus pa'i 'di chos can thams cad chos
NK107(tse)001:4655: nyid yin te snang ba thams cad ye nas grol
NK107(tse)001:4656: ba'i phyir zhes pa dang yang ni gcig shes pas
NK107(tse)001:4657: kun grol ba'i phyir dper na mdud pa gcig bkrol
NK107(tse)001:4658: bas do thag brgya 'chad pa bzhin no yang na
NK107(tse)001:4659: 'khor ba'i 'khrul pa 'di chos can yang dag par
NK107(tse)001:4660: na mya ngan 'das pa yin te thams cad ming
NK107(tse)001:4661: yin pa'i phyir ro dper na ming bsgyur gyi skyes
NK107(tse)001:4662: bu bzhin no zhes pa la sogs pa'i sbyor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4663: dmigs kyis rang gi 'dod pa bskyang ngo de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4664: na chos can dang gcig dam bca' dang gnyis gtan
NK107(tse)001:4665: tshigs dang gsum dang dpe yis barjoda pa mtshon te
NK107(tse)001:4666: bzhi la sbyor ba bskor gcig tu bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4667: snang ba dang mi snang ba thams cad bsgre ste
NK107(tse)001:4668: chos can dang 'brel so bsgrub la yul la brten
NK107(tse)001:4669: nas shes na tshig thams cad la mkhas par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:4670: ro de la dgos pa ci yod na phyi rol
NK107(tse)001:4671: pa'i brgol ba bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod do de
NK107(tse)001:4672: ltar na rang gi chos can la skyon 'dug gam
NK107(tse)001:4673: mi 'dug brtags la skyon med du dam bca' ba'o
NK107(tse)001:4674: gtan tshigs dag gis ni dam bca' dang bsgrub bya
NK107(tse)001:4675: dang 'brel ba'i don brtsi ste gal te ma 'brel
NK107(tse)001:4676: na skyon chen por 'gro bas 'brel pa brtsi ba
NK107(tse)001:4677: gal che'o de yang dpe barjoda kyis ni 'di ltar
NK107(tse)001:4678: snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad 'brel bar byas 'di
NK107(tse)001:4679: ltar snang ngo cog thams cad chos nyid du grol
NK107(tse)001:4680: ba'i gnad do de ltar sbyor ba bzhi bskor gyis
NK107(tse)001:4681: rnal 'byor pa yis grub mtha' blo la brten pa
NK107(tse)001:4682: yis rang dang gzhan gyis shes pa'i rtsal gyil chos
NK107(tse)001:4683: can dang chos nyid thams cad la bsgre bar bya'o
NK107(tse)001:4684: zhes nying don bazha pa shes bya bzhi bskor gyis
NK107(tse)001:4685: snang brtags thams cad chos nyid du bsre ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:4686: nas da ni nying don lnga pa phyi rol gyi
NK107(tse)001:4687: grub mtha' nyams pas khyad par bstan pa ni gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4688: 'dod 'chol par brtags pas rang yang ldog pa'i skyon
NK107(tse)001:4689: dang rang gi khyab pa dang 'brel ba nyams par
NK107(tse)001:4690: 'gyur ba dang gzhan gyi 'gal 'brel brtsis pas gzhan
NK107(tse)001:4691: gyi 'gal ba 'du ba'i skyon grags pa dag gis
NK107(tse)001:4692: rang dang gzhan gyi thal 'gyur ste 'brel ba khyab
NK107(tse)001:4693: ches pas nyams pa dang bsgrub bya ltos chungs pas
NK107(tse)001:4694: nyams pa dang gtan tshigs la ldog pa rtogs pas
NK107(tse)001:4695: nyams pa dag go de yang bsgrub byar bya ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4696: 'brel ma 'brel khyab che chung ldog pa dang de'i
NK107(tse)001:4697: 'brel pa las dang mtshan nyid la spyad pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:4698: bya ste barjoda pa'i tshig rang bzhin gyi la rtog
NK107(tse)001:4699: pa tha dad du bcug pa de nyid la de
NK107(tse)001:4700: dag gi rjes su 'gro ldog shes pa'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4701: rgol ba dang phyir rgol ba'i rgyu dang rkyen gang
NK107(tse)001:4702: las bskyed pa dang de'i tha ma'i smin so brtsi
NK107(tse)001:4703: ba dang mdor na sna tshogs pa'i rtog pa bzhug
NK107(tse)001:4704: go gzhan skyon dang rang skyon la 'gro bar 'dod
NK107(tse)001:4705: pa dang song ba'i bye brag shes te bsal ba
NK107(tse)001:4706: dang skyon spang ba dang bye brag gi 'brel so
NK107(tse)001:4707: tha dad du brtsi ba shes par bya'o zhes nying
NK107(tse)001:4708: lag gi don lnga pa phyi rol gyi grub matha'i
NK107(tse)001:4709: nyams pa'i khyad par bstan nas da ni nang don
NK107(tse)001:4710: drug pa tshig gi byed pa'i rgyu bshad pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4711: song ba zhes bya ba phyi rol gyi yul rang
NK107(tse)001:4712: gi 'dod pa dang gzhan gyi 'dod pa rnams dang
NK107(tse)001:4713: bar gyi phung po gsum la bsal bas tshig gi
NK107(tse)001:4714: lam dang sgra'i gnas dang tshig gi 'brel so la
NK107(tse)001:4715: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid shes grub matha'i 'dod pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:4716: khong du chud pas de'i dran pa dang dngos po
NK107(tse)001:4717: dang dngos po med pa rnams la 'jal shes par
NK107(tse)001:4718: 'gyur ro de yang tshig gi 'brel gyis bya ba
NK107(tse)001:4719: bral ba dang da ltar byung ba dang phyis byed
NK107(tse)001:4720: pa dang rang la ldog pa dang bcas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4721: de bzhin du gzhan dang tshig gi lam rnams dang
NK107(tse)001:4722: phyir lan du ldog pa med pa dang 'brel phyis
NK107(tse)001:4723: bartsi'o de yang rang gi grub pa rnams dang phyis
NK107(tse)001:4724: bsgrub pa rnams su phyed pa ni brtag pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:4725: ltar tshig don 'brel bar byed rgyu rnams brtag ste
NK107(tse)001:4726: de dag gi rang bzhin 'brel shes par bya'o zhus
NK107(tse)001:4727: don lnga pa yan lag gi don gnyis pa thal
NK107(tse)001:4728: 'gyur gyi sgra don nges par bstan pa la nying
NK107(tse)001:4729: don drug tu byas nas bstan no da ni zhus
NK107(tse)001:4730: don drug pa rgyud kyis mtshan nges pa'i mtha' bsdud
NK107(tse)001:4731: 'gyur ba'i mtshan nyid bstan pa la yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:4732: don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po dang po 'byung
NK107(tse)001:4733: ba rang ngo'i 'brel gyis lus kyi 'gyur byed par
NK107(tse)001:4734: bstan pa ni rgyu mtshan nges pa'i mtha' bsdud ni
NK107(tse)001:4735: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de yang rgyud
NK107(tse)001:4736: kyi mtshan la brten nas gang zag gcig b+hud tha
NK107(tse)001:4737: ba'i thabs bstan pa ni rgyud ni brtags pa tshig
NK107(tse)001:4738: gis rgyud rtags su bkod pa rnams la don gyi
NK107(tse)001:4739: rgyud rang rgyud rnam par dag pa rnams la rang
NK107(tse)001:4740: shes rig gi rgyal po dang kun tu bzang po
NK107(tse)001:4741: ma bcos pa'i chos nyid do de la myang ngan
NK107(tse)001:4742: las 'das pa'i mtshan nyid rnams rdzogs pas na rgyud
NK107(tse)001:4743: mtshan nyid pa zhes bya ste de lta bu la
NK107(tse)001:4744: btags pa'i tshig rgyud kyi mtshan gyi nges pa'i snying
NK107(tse)001:4745: po mtha' 'gyur ba zhes bstan pas de'i bsdud ni
NK107(tse)001:4746: mtshan skabs su 'gyur zhes bya ba ni phyi'i 'byung
NK107(tse)001:4747: ba'i cho 'phrul nam zhes bya ste dbyar dgun ston
NK107(tse)001:4748: dpyid bzhi la bya ste de yang 'gro ba gcig
NK107(tse)001:4749: gi tshe stong dang smad dang bar stod dang bar
NK107(tse)001:4750: smad dang bzhi la sbyar bas dus kyi 'pho ba
NK107(tse)001:4751: zhes pa dang zla zhes bya ba ni nang gi
NK107(tse)001:4752: dus zla ba bcu gnyis las khyad par du dus
NK107(tse)001:4753: bzhi nges par phye ste dgun zla gsum chu'i dus
NK107(tse)001:4754: yin dpyid sa dbyar me ston zla gsum rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:4755: dus yin pas so de yang dus kyi 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:4756: ni dgu rdo ltar gnas pa'i dus te phung po
NK107(tse)001:4757: dang khams la sogs pa thams cad sra ba'i mdangs
NK107(tse)001:4758: yod pas nyams len kyang de dang sbyar ro dpyid
NK107(tse)001:4759: sa bon ltar gnas pa'i dus te snga ma las
NK107(tse)001:4760: 'gyur te phung po dang khams la sogs pa thams
NK107(tse)001:4761: cad de nyid du 'dus shing gnas pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:4762: pa'o dbyar pad ma ltar gnas pa ste phung po
NK107(tse)001:4763: dang khams la sogs pa rnams gsal ba la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:4764: pa'o ston ni 'bru ltar gnas pa ste phung po
NK107(tse)001:4765: dang khams la sogs pa thams cad rgyas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4766: 'byung ba rgyas pa dang byang chub kyi sems rgyas
NK107(tse)001:4767: pa ste 'di'i dus na nyams su las dang po
NK107(tse)001:4768: pas blangs na nyams thun mong ma yin pa skye
NK107(tse)001:4769: ba'o de ltar phyi'i dus bzhi ni nang phung po'i
NK107(tse)001:4770: snod kyis bcud la skyabs pa dang bcud kyis snod
NK107(tse)001:4771: la skyabs pa'i dbang gis rnal 'byor pa'i nyams su
NK107(tse)001:4772: myong ba dang shes pa yang 'gyur te shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4773: na bun ltar gnas pa'i dus dang rlangs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4774: smugs pa ltar gnas pa'i dus dang 'ja' tshon sgyu
NK107(tse)001:4775: ma'i rnam pa ltar gnas pa'i dus la de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4776: 'gyur ba'i dus tshod rnal 'byor pas nyams myo nga
NK107(tse)001:4777: la mkhas pas dus nges par bzung ba ni dge
NK107(tse)001:4778: sbyor 'phel che ba'i lugs dang nyams khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:4779: skye ba'i dus nges par rtogs pa la legs par
NK107(tse)001:4780: spyod pa'o de yang 'byung ba'i dus nges ni ston
NK107(tse)001:4781: rlung gi dus na khyad par du rlung gi rnal
NK107(tse)001:4782: 'byor pas dge ba'i las dang dus dang sbyar bas
NK107(tse)001:4783: 'grub la dbyar me'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis me'i
NK107(tse)001:4784: dus la 'grub la dpyid sa'i dus na sa'i rnal
NK107(tse)001:4785: 'byor pa rnams kyis 'grub ba'o dgun chu'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:4786: chu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis 'grub pa'o de'i 'dres
NK107(tse)001:4787: kyis ni 'byung ba'i 'gyur byed kyis phyi rol gyi
NK107(tse)001:4788: 'byung ba rnams 'gyur bas na dus 'byed pa nges
NK107(tse)001:4789: pa'i rnam pas 'byung bar nges la phyi'i las kyis
NK107(tse)001:4790: 'byung ba'i lus kyi 'gyur bas 'gro ba'i rtog pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4791: gnas 'gyur ba ni rlung las me'i 'byung bas 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:4792: bas tsha zhing 'phen pa'i las su 'gro la rlung
NK107(tse)001:4793: las chu'i 'byung bar 'gyur ba las bsdud pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:4794: su 'gro la chu las sa'i las su 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:4795: las ba sdud cing 'dzin pa'i las su 'agro'o de
NK107(tse)001:4796: ltar 'byung ba bzhi las chu pho mo gnyis de
NK107(tse)001:4797: brgyad du 'khor bar byed do de yang lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:4798: bzhi sa'i lus kyis zug par byed pa dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:4799: gis byer bar byed pa dang chu yis snyoms par
NK107(tse)001:4800: byed pa dang mes 'khrugs pa'i 'gyur byed ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:4801: yin te de yang tsha ba dang grang ba gnyis
NK107(tse)001:4802: las rlung las rlung gi khams su 'byung ba 'khrugs
NK107(tse)001:4803: pa las tsha ba dang grang ba gnyis 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:4804: dang sa las bad kan du 'gyur bas yang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:4805: me las mkhris pa chu las 'dus pa'i chu dang
NK107(tse)001:4806: bzhi ni gsum snyam pa las gcig tu 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:4807: bzhi yin la 'dus pa'i rang ngo dang lnga ni
NK107(tse)001:4808: 'byung ba 'gyur zhing 'byung ba'i byed pa'i lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:4809: gzhi sa chu me rlung bzhi las kun gyi lus
NK107(tse)001:4810: su smin par byas la don dam pa'i 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:4811: bzhi las sgron ma bzhi smin pa'o de yang 'byung
NK107(tse)001:4812: ba bzhi po rang la yang sa'i sa dang chu
NK107(tse)001:4813: dang me dang rlung dang bzhi yin de dag bzhi
NK107(tse)001:4814: la yang so so'i stongs pa'i gnas te 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:4815: re re la brgyad yod pa yin no zhes 'byung
NK107(tse)001:4816: ba dang po las kyi 'brel gyis lus kyi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:4817: byed bstan nas da ni yan lag gi don gnyis
NK107(tse)001:4818: pa 'gyur byed 'byung ba las kyi mtha' brtsi ba
NK107(tse)001:4819: bstan pa ni de ltar phyi nang gi 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:4820: la sogs pa 'gyur bar byed pa ste nang gi
NK107(tse)001:4821: shes pa sna tshogs su 'gyur bar byed pa'i rtsal
NK107(tse)001:4822: las byung ba ste yang nang du shes pa dga'
NK107(tse)001:4823: ba dang mi dga' ba sna tshogs su 'phro bar
NK107(tse)001:4824: byed pa yang 'byung ba'i snod lus kyi len so'i
NK107(tse)001:4825: 'byung ba'i gnad las byung ba ste 'byung ba so
NK107(tse)001:4826: so'i byed pa phyin ci log las byung ba ste
NK107(tse)001:4827: yang phyi'i rlung lus la zug pa'i dus na nang
NK107(tse)001:4828: gi rlung rtsa nang du 'khyil ba las ni shes
NK107(tse)001:4829: pa 'khyil ba dang ye shes kyi rtsal nang gsal
NK107(tse)001:4830: du 'byung ba ste 'di'i dus na rtsa rba rlabs
NK107(tse)001:4831: btun pa gnad yin no yang phyi'i me nang du
NK107(tse)001:4832: byer ba las nang nas shes pa mched pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4833: ye shes kyi rtsal sbyang ba gnad do yang phyi'i
NK107(tse)001:4834: sa zug pa las nang gis sa lus la snyoms
NK107(tse)001:4835: pa las ni shes pa snying la 'dus pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4836: rlung spyi bor gnon pa gnad yin no de ni
NK107(tse)001:4837: phyi'i 'byung ba 'gyur ba'i rtags te 'di rnams la
NK107(tse)001:4838: lus nges par sbyang ba gnad yin no rtsa'i yi
NK107(tse)001:4839: ge rab tu 'dren pa'i tshul gyis barjoda pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4840: gal te sems gnas pa byung na rlung gi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:4841: byed la de yang nang gi lus kyi smin so
NK107(tse)001:4842: ni phyi rlung las nang rlung du smin pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4843: rlung gi chu las smin pa shes pa mtha' yas
NK107(tse)001:4844: de'i sas shes pa rtse gcig de'i me sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:4845: par 'phro rlung gi rlung las smin pa bye brag
NK107(tse)001:4846: la 'jug par byed do sa sa zhes pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4847: sa'i sa las smin pa shes pa bsgyur bar dka'
NK107(tse)001:4848: 'o de'i chu lci zhing sos dal de'i me rgod
NK107(tse)001:4849: cing zlog par daka'o de'i rlung rab tu yang la
NK107(tse)001:4850: dbang po mi gsal me me zhes pa me'i me
NK107(tse)001:4851: / blo sna mang zhing rab tu ragasah de'i chu
NK107(tse)001:4852: 'gyur spras spros mang de'i blo rtse mang la khyab
NK107(tse)001:4853: chung de'i rlung yang zhing 'gyur ldog che yang chu'i
NK107(tse)001:4854: chu dang ring zhing 'khro mi shes de'i sa rab
NK107(tse)001:4855: tu gsal la des de'i me bsam mno mang zhing
NK107(tse)001:4856: 'grub pa dka' de'i rlung brtson zhing rab tu sdug
NK107(tse)001:4857: basngala che'o de ltar 'byung ba gcig gis byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4858: las bzhi byas pas 'byung bzhi la bzhi bzhi ste
NK107(tse)001:4859: bcu drug la de yang sas ni khyab par byed
NK107(tse)001:4860: pa'i ni lus kyi gzhi 'dzin la de yang gzhi
NK107(tse)001:4861: la kha dog bzhir 'gyur ro chus ni nang lus
NK107(tse)001:4862: la 'jug pa dang bsdud pa'i las byed mes ni
NK107(tse)001:4863: gnas par byed cing shes pa'i rtsal sbyong ba'o rlung
NK107(tse)001:4864: gis lus dang dbang po rnams bsrung bar byed cing
NK107(tse)001:4865: tha ma yang 'jig pa'i las byed do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:4866: 'byung ba chu pho las 'khrugs cing yid kyi las
NK107(tse)001:4867: byed mos 'jig cing 'khrul pa'i las byed do yang
NK107(tse)001:4868: phos 'khor zhing snang bar ston mos mched cing 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:4869: pa'i las byed me phos zhen cing chags par byed
NK107(tse)001:4870: mos 'dod cing 'dun par byed rlung phos 'phro zhing
NK107(tse)001:4871: zhe sdang gi las byed mos 'byed cing ser sna'i
NK107(tse)001:4872: las byed do de ltar zung bzhi sdebs pa las
NK107(tse)001:4873: ya brgyad do de ltar du 'byung ba'i rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:4874: tha dad pa las smin kyang sems nyid du sdom
NK107(tse)001:4875: pas gcig tu nges par brtag go de yang dpa'
NK107(tse)001:4876: zhes mdzes pa la smos pa dang las tha dad
NK107(tse)001:4877: du byed pas na de ltar sems gcig gi byed
NK107(tse)001:4878: pa'i brgyud las phyi 'byung ba dang nang phung po'i
NK107(tse)001:4879: 'gyu byed dpag tu med par byung ba ni sems
NK107(tse)001:4880: nyid kyi mtshan nyid stong pa ngos bzung med par
NK107(tse)001:4881: gtan la ma phebs pa las byung ba nyid do
NK107(tse)001:4882: zhes zhus don drug pa rgyu mtshan nges pa'i mtha'
NK107(tse)001:4883: bsdud bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:4884: byas nas bstan no da ni zhus don bdun pa
NK107(tse)001:4885: lus rnam par bzhag pa la rgyud kyi le'u barjoda
NK107(tse)001:4886: bya'i rim pa bstan pa la nang don gnyis kyis
NK107(tse)001:4887: bstan pa'i dang po le'u yi mtshan nges par bstan
NK107(tse)001:4888: pa ni le barjoda nyid kyang gsal phye na zhes
NK107(tse)001:4889: pa gzhung na gsal lo gnyis pa le'u yi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:4890: tshad nges par bstan pa ni de yang tshad bstan
NK107(tse)001:4891: zhes bya ba ni lus dang yan lag gi tshad
NK107(tse)001:4892: la sogs pa gong du bstan la le'u'i 'gyur dag
NK107(tse)001:4893: shes shing zhes pa ni gong du drug tu bstan
NK107(tse)001:4894: la de ltar drug la brten nas dpal rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:4895: 'chang gi dgongs pa 'di lta bu la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:4896: 'byung ba'i gter la longs spyod pas na rang gi
NK107(tse)001:4897: lus ngag gi bde ba'i thabs kyis rigs pa'i sku
NK107(tse)001:4898: nyid kyang lung bstan pa thob pas rdo rje 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:4899: pa ni sems kyi gnas so de yang 'gro ba'i
