NK107(tse)001:4900: lus grub pa dang chags pa dang gnas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4901: 'jig pa bzhi ka bdag skyob pa ni rlung gis
NK107(tse)001:4902: byed pas na lha zhes bya'o rlung gi las lhag
NK107(tse)001:4903: ma ni spyi'i 'byung ba 'jig pa dang chags pa
NK107(tse)001:4904: dang gnas pa dang stong pa'i las kyang de tsam
NK107(tse)001:4905: mo zhes bdun pa le barjoda kyi rim pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:4906: pa la yan lag gi don gnyis su byas nas
NK107(tse)001:4907: bstan no da ni zhus don brgyad pa lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:4908: don rgyud kyi gzhung tshad rdzogs pa'i don bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:4909: la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:4910: po rdzogs pa'i tshig don gsal bar bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4911: rdzogs pa zhes pa ni bzhag pa las zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:4912: gzhung gsal lo da ni gnyis pa rdzogs so zhes
NK107(tse)001:4913: pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni ring byed ces pa
NK107(tse)001:4914: ni sgra'i mtshan nyid bstan pa ste bem po dang
NK107(tse)001:4915: rig bcas kyi sgra la bslabs pas rdzogs pa chen
NK107(tse)001:4916: po'i rang bzhin gcig char du grol ba'i rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:4917: las 'gro ba lha dang mi dang lha min dang
NK107(tse)001:4918: byol song dang yi dwags dang dmyal ba dang drug
NK107(tse)001:4919: gi skad ni lha'i e tri brten nas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4920: dang lha min ho teng la brten nas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4921: dang mi'i 'a le ma se brten nas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4922: dang byol song 'u 'ung brten nas shes pa dang
NK107(tse)001:4923: yi dwags kyi ra rir la brten nas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4924: dang dmyal ba'i ka kring la brten nas shes pa
NK107(tse)001:4925: rnams dang de'i rnam 'phrul las lha'i sgra phas lta
NK107(tse)001:4926: zhes pa la 'jug pa dang lha min yab phyad
NK107(tse)001:4927: mi'i 'ung gnas dang byol song gi ring thung dang
NK107(tse)001:4928: yi dwags kyi kang seng dang dmyal ba'i khyab 'jug
NK107(tse)001:4929: khur gyi brda'i 'jug pa thams cad la snang ngo
NK107(tse)001:4930: de ltar shes pa la dgos pa ci yod na
NK107(tse)001:4931: rigs drug gi gnas so so'i nus pas bsgyur bas
NK107(tse)001:4932: b+hud tha ba dang byang chub sems dpa' la sogs
NK107(tse)001:4933: pa gang mos su 'pho bar nus nges so de'i
NK107(tse)001:4934: phyir na rang bzhin rdzogs pa'i thabs la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:4935: rdzogs pa chen po la sbyor bar byed pas na
NK107(tse)001:4936: rdzogs so zhes bya'o de yang stong pas rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:4937: dngos po'i mtha' gcad nas brtag pa mthar 'dzin gyi
NK107(tse)001:4938: las log la snang snang ba'i 'byed pa rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:4939: ni stong par rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i mtha' gcad
NK107(tse)001:4940: nas chad pa mthar 'dzin pa las log go de
NK107(tse)001:4941: ltar na rgyud kyi gzhung gi tshig don gsal bar
NK107(tse)001:4942: phye nas gzhung 'di'i tshig don rnam pa lhag ma
NK107(tse)001:4943: med par yongs su rdzogs pas rdzogs soh+ya&a&a&a zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:4944: de ltar yang rgyud kyi 'brel don rdzogs pa ni
NK107(tse)001:4945: gzhi nyid la sogs pa'i tshig drug gzhung na gsal
NK107(tse)001:4946: lo zhes pa brgyad pa rgyud kyi gzhung tshad rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:4947: pa'i don la yan lag gi don gnyis su byas
NK107(tse)001:4948: nas bstan no da ni zhus don dgu pa rgyud
NK107(tse)001:4949: kyi gleng gzhi nges pa'i tshig don bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:4950: yan lag gi don bdun gyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK107(tse)001:4951: gdul byed kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni gleng gzhi
NK107(tse)001:4952: dag la yang dag tshig ces pa la sogs pas
NK107(tse)001:4953: bstan te de yang gleng pa tshig yin pa glengs
NK107(tse)001:4954: pas zhes bya'o de yang don gyi ngo bo de
NK107(tse)001:4955: nyid gang du glengs na thog ma'i dus su rang
NK107(tse)001:4956: gang gis glengs na ston pa drug pa rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:4957: 'chang gis glengs gang glengs na sgra thal 'gyur zhes
NK107(tse)001:4958: bya ba rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di glengs so tshul
NK107(tse)001:4959: lam thabs ji ltar glengs na lha tshangs pa'i skad
NK107(tse)001:4960: kyis glengs so gang la glengs na b+hud rda stong
NK107(tse)001:4961: rtsa gnyis la sogs pa'i 'khor dang lha'i bu dpag
NK107(tse)001:4962: tu med pa rnams la glengs so dus nam glengs
NK107(tse)001:4963: na tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:4964: na glengs so de ltar glengs pa la dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:4965: ci yod na gang zag brtson 'grus rab 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:4966: la b+hud tha ba'i dgos pa yod 'bring chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:4967: kyi bar do la b+hud tha ba'i dgos pa yod
NK107(tse)001:4968: tha ma rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing khams su dbugs
NK107(tse)001:4969: 'byin pa'i dgos pa yod do gzhi ni rig pa
NK107(tse)001:4970: nyid yin te rig pa nyid med na gnas la
NK107(tse)001:4971: sogs pas kyang dgos pa med pas na de yang
NK107(tse)001:4972: rig pa'i snang ba dang ngo bo gnyis so ngo
NK107(tse)001:4973: bo de rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku 'dus
NK107(tse)001:4974: ma byas pas dus thams cad pa rkyen gyis mi
NK107(tse)001:4975: shigs pas ngo bo zang thal ba tshig dang yid
NK107(tse)001:4976: spyod du ma gyur pas lu gu rgyud sngon du
NK107(tse)001:4977: snang la sgros btags su med pas barjoda bya gang
NK107(tse)001:4978: gis kyang thog tu mi phebs pa'o rig pa'i snang
NK107(tse)001:4979: ba ni gnyis te dngos snang cir yang ma grub
NK107(tse)001:4980: la 'dra snang tha dad du gyur pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:4981: dngos snang sku yin pas sku gsum lam snang du
NK107(tse)001:4982: gsal ba dang 'dra snang 'od yin pas snang ba'i
NK107(tse)001:4983: nyams sna tshogs su gsal ba'o de ltar ngo bo
NK107(tse)001:4984: la brten nas chos nyid gtan la phebs pas na
NK107(tse)001:4985: rang rig gzhan 'byung gi brtsol ba chod pa'o snang
NK107(tse)001:4986: ba la brten nas 'od snang tha dad pa gtan
NK107(tse)001:4987: la phab pas 'khrul snang ye shes su shar bas
NK107(tse)001:4988: bar ma do'i chos nyid mngon sum du gyur pa
NK107(tse)001:4989: las phyis kyi re dogs kyi mtha' chod de 'bras
NK107(tse)001:4990: bu dus 'di nyid du gtan la phebs pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:4991: ltar na de gnyis la brten nas yang dag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:4992: tshig rnams 'byung bar byed pa'o de yang gang zag
NK107(tse)001:4993: gi rigs mi 'dra ba so sor yod kyang gdul
NK107(tse)001:4994: bya gzhi gzugs kyi phung po rdul dang rdul phran
NK107(tse)001:4995: las grub pa dang tshor ba bde sdug btang snyoms
NK107(tse)001:4996: las grub pa dang 'du shes kyi phung po rnam
NK107(tse)001:4997: par rgyu ba dang mi rgyu ba las grub pa
NK107(tse)001:4998: dang 'du byed kyi phung po sems dang sems byung
NK107(tse)001:4999: las grub pa dang rnam shes kyi phung po 'jug
NK107(tse)001:5000: pa'i yan lag du ma dang bcas pa las byung
NK107(tse)001:5001: ba'i rnam pa lnga yod pa la dgongs nas phung
NK107(tse)001:5002: po lnga po de'i 'du byed du gleng gzhi ste
NK107(tse)001:5003: gnas dang ston pa dang 'khor dang bstan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5004: dus dang lngar byung bas na gleng pa tshig yin
NK107(tse)001:5005: la de'i dus na barjoda pa gsung yin no zhes
NK107(tse)001:5006: yan lag gi don dang po gdul bya dang 'dul
NK107(tse)001:5007: byed kyi mtshan nyid bstan nas da ni yan lag
NK107(tse)001:5008: gi don gnyis pa gnad kyi nges tshig rnam par
NK107(tse)001:5009: phye ste bstan pa ni de yang gzhi ni gnas
NK107(tse)001:5010: dang ston pa dang 'khor dang bstan pa dang dus
NK107(tse)001:5011: dang rnam pa lnga yin te de la gnas ni
NK107(tse)001:5012: chos kyi sku'i gnas chos kyi dbyings dang longs sku'i
NK107(tse)001:5013: gnas rnam dag stug po bkod pa dang sprul sku'i
NK107(tse)001:5014: gnas tha dad ma nges pa dang 'gro ba'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5015: la bzhag pa'o de ltar rnam pa gsum gsum du
NK107(tse)001:5016: 'dod pa ni las dang mthun pa'i bye brag las
NK107(tse)001:5017: byung ba'o de yang phun zhes bya ba ye shes
NK107(tse)001:5018: lnga dang rin po che lnga 'dus pa la gnas
NK107(tse)001:5019: zhes bya'o gsum ni gong ma'i gnas kyi ming gi
NK107(tse)001:5020: rnam grangs ste chos thams cad kyi 'char gzhi ma
NK107(tse)001:5021: 'gags pa'o 'tshogs pas gzhal med khang gi yon tan
NK107(tse)001:5022: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal ba nang nas bltas
NK107(tse)001:5023: na phyi gsal ba 'dod pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5024: dang rlung gi stobs kyis yang ba dang bskyod pa
NK107(tse)001:5025: la sogs rdzogs pa'o zhes nang don gnyis pa gnas
NK107(tse)001:5026: kyi nges tshig bstan nas da ni gsum pa ston
NK107(tse)001:5027: pa phun sum 'tshogs pa'i nges tshig bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5028: ston pa nyid kyang ni chos kyi sku'i ston pa
NK107(tse)001:5029: kun tu bzang po nyid 'khor bar lhung ma myong
NK107(tse)001:5030: ba dang longs sku'i ston pa kun rig rnam par
NK107(tse)001:5031: snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho 'khor 'das kyi mtshams nas
NK107(tse)001:5032: bltas kyang 'khor ba nyid du 'dzin pa med pa
NK107(tse)001:5033: la sprul pa'i sku khye'u snang ba dam pa bsam
NK107(tse)001:5034: gyis mi khyab pa nyid 'khor ba na gnas kyang
NK107(tse)001:5035: 'khor ba'i chos las grol ba dang gsum yin te
NK107(tse)001:5036: phun zhes bya ba chos kyi sku mtshan med stong
NK107(tse)001:5037: par rdzogs pa dang longs sku ris med zang thal
NK107(tse)001:5038: du rdzogs pa dang sprul pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe
NK107(tse)001:5039: byad du rdzogs pa'o gsum ni sku gsum gyi 'char
NK107(tse)001:5040: byed ma 'gags pa'o de ltar sku gsum so so'i
NK107(tse)001:5041: yon tan 'tshogs pas 'khor rnams bsdud pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:5042: ston pa'i sku'i yon tan la dmigs nas gzugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:5043: khams su 'khor 'dus la gsung gi yon tan la
NK107(tse)001:5044: dmigs nas 'dod pa'i khams kyi 'gro ba rnams 'khor
NK107(tse)001:5045: du 'dus la thugs kyi yon tan la dmigs nas
NK107(tse)001:5046: gzugs med pa'i 'gro ba rnams 'du ba'o zhes ston
NK107(tse)001:5047: pa phun sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:5048: ni bzhi pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig
NK107(tse)001:5049: rnam par phye ste bstan pa ni 'khor yang ni
NK107(tse)001:5050: chos kyi sku'i 'khor b+hud d+ha dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:5051: longs sku'i 'khor rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs pa sprul
NK107(tse)001:5052: sku'i 'khor 'jig rten dang 'das pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:5053: dpag tu med pa dang rnam pa gsum yin no
NK107(tse)001:5054: phun zhes bya ba gzugs su bkod pa'i rigs dpag
NK107(tse)001:5055: tu med pa 'dus pa'o de ltar gong ma'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:5056: gyi rigs gsum gyis drangs te rigs mi 'dra ba
NK107(tse)001:5057: sna tshogs 'dus pa ni skal pa dang ldan pa
NK107(tse)001:5058: 'ga' zhig go de ltar 'tshogs pa rnams kyang ston
NK107(tse)001:5059: pa la rab tu dad cing 'dun pa skyes pa
NK107(tse)001:5060: b+ha zhig las gzhan ni med do zhes pa'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:5061: gyi nges tshig bstan nas da ni lnga pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5062: pa phun sum 'tshogs pa'i nges tshig rnam par phye
NK107(tse)001:5063: ba bstan pa ni bstan pa nyid kyang ni sku'i
NK107(tse)001:5064: bstan pa b+hud d+ha thams kyi sku rin po che
NK107(tse)001:5065: rigs mi 'dra ba stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi
NK107(tse)001:5066: las rang byung ba dang gsung gi bstan pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5067: pa thams cad kyi btsas rang 'byung gi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:5068: rin po che brgya rtsa gcig las rang byung ba
NK107(tse)001:5069: thugs kyi bstan pa rang bzhin chos nyid kyi rdo
NK107(tse)001:5070: rje rin po che sna dgu brgya dang dgu bcu
NK107(tse)001:5071: rtsa dgu las rab tu byung ba dang gsum yin
NK107(tse)001:5072: te de las kyang gsung rin po che las khyad
NK107(tse)001:5073: par du bsdus pa sgra thal 'gyur chen po'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:5074: ces bya ba chos rnams kun gyi rtsa bar bstan
NK107(tse)001:5075: pa 'di nyid do de yang phun zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:5076: bstan pa thams cad kyi yang snying 'dus pa sgra
NK107(tse)001:5077: thal 'gyur 'di dam chos kun gyi bcud bsdus nas
NK107(tse)001:5078: skal ldan rnams la snang bar byas ba 'adi'o gsum
NK107(tse)001:5079: ni dam pa'i chos mngon pa'i sde snod rin po
NK107(tse)001:5080: che dang dam pa'i chos mdo sde dang 'dul ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5081: sde snod rin po che'o de yang sde mang zhing
NK107(tse)001:5082: chags pa yin la snod ni 'dus shing shong bar
NK107(tse)001:5083: byed pa yin no de dag las khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:5084: bsdus pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po de las
NK107(tse)001:5085: kyang gsang ba'i sgra'i rgyud 'di nyid do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:5086: sde snod rin po che gsum gyi bcud gsang ba
NK107(tse)001:5087: sgra rgyud la 'tshogs pas gang zag skal pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5088: ldan pa rnams grol bar byed pa'o zhes lnga pa
NK107(tse)001:5089: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig rnam par
NK107(tse)001:5090: phye ba bstan nas da ni drug pa dus phun
NK107(tse)001:5091: sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig rnam par phye ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:5092: pa ni de yang dus kyang sum la zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:5093: ni 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar
NK107(tse)001:5094: gsum rgyud kyi ston pa 'khor dang bcas pa la
NK107(tse)001:5095: 'dus la de ltar gsum la gnas dang ston pa
NK107(tse)001:5096: dang 'khor dang bstan pa dang bzhi 'dus pas na
NK107(tse)001:5097: 'dus pa zhes bya'o phun zhes theg pa 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:5098: pa dang 'das pa'i theg pa las 'das par bsdu
NK107(tse)001:5099: de la bzhi yod pa las gsang ba bla na
NK107(tse)001:5100: med pa lus dang dbang po yan lag rdzogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5101: skyes bu dang 'dra ba nyid du rab tu zab
NK107(tse)001:5102: par bsdus pa'o de yang rgyud bcu bdun yod pa
NK107(tse)001:5103: las gsang ba sgra rgyud 'di rab tu zab par
NK107(tse)001:5104: bsdus pa'o de rnams kun rdzogs de thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:5105: gnad ston par byed pa sgra thal 'gyur gyi rgyud
NK107(tse)001:5106: do gsum ni 'das pa rig pa'i rang ngo la
NK107(tse)001:5107: gsal ba dang da lta mkhyen pa rang rdzogs su
NK107(tse)001:5108: gsal la phyis ni thugs rnam par dag pa'i ye
NK107(tse)001:5109: shes su gsal ba'o de ltar thams cad 'tshogs pas
NK107(tse)001:5110: bstan pa chen po che ni nges par rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5111: chen po rtsod gzhi dang bral ba'o zhes drug pa
NK107(tse)001:5112: dus phun sum tshogs pa'i nges tshig rnam par dbye
NK107(tse)001:5113: ba bstan nas da ni bdun pa gleng gzhi gnyis
NK107(tse)001:5114: kyi khyad par thun mong dang thun mong ma yin
NK107(tse)001:5115: pa'i khyad par bstan pa ni thun mong min pas
NK107(tse)001:5116: khyad par te zhes pa la sogs pa tshigs su
NK107(tse)001:5117: bcad pa gnyis gzhung gsal lo zhes rgyud kyi zhus
NK107(tse)001:5118: don dgu pa gleng gzhi zhes pa'i tshig bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5119: la yan lag bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:5120: bdun du byas nas bstan no da ni zhus don
NK107(tse)001:5121: bcu pa rgyud kyi lus rnam par bzhag pa b+hud
NK107(tse)001:5122: d+ha'i bstan pa 'phel 'grib nye bar mtshon pa dus
NK107(tse)001:5123: nges pa'i gnad bstan pa lah yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:5124: drug gis bstan pa'i dang po bstan pa'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:5125: gyi dus kyi ming gi rnam grangs kyi bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5126: ni 'di ltar bstan pa na sprul pa sku'i bstan
NK107(tse)001:5127: pa 'di nyid la lhag ma'i tshig gnyis gzhung gsal
NK107(tse)001:5128: de yang tshe lo dpag tu med pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:5129: b+hud d+ha thams cad kyi snying po rdzogs ldan gyi
NK107(tse)001:5130: bstan pa rin po che byung bas 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:5131: rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan la gnas pas byung la
NK107(tse)001:5132: tshe lo bye ba la rdzogs ldan zhes pa'i bstan
NK107(tse)001:5133: pa byung bas 'gro ba rnams rang bzhin gyi bde
NK107(tse)001:5134: ba rnyed do 'bum pa la rdzogs ldan dag ni
NK107(tse)001:5135: chen po zhes bya ba byung bas 'gro ba rab
NK107(tse)001:5136: tu dga' ba dang ldan pa'o de nas tshe lo
NK107(tse)001:5137: brgyad khri pa la de bzhin du gnyis ldan dang
NK107(tse)001:5138: gsum ldan pa zhes bya ba la 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:5139: rab tu rengs pa la spyod do de nas tshe
NK107(tse)001:5140: lo bzhi khri pa la bstan pa sum ldan chen
NK107(tse)001:5141: po bya ba la 'gro ba rnams rab tu bde
NK107(tse)001:5142: ba la spyod pas de yang rabs bdun pa'i bstan
NK107(tse)001:5143: pa rin po che rgyas pa bya ba'i phyir de
NK107(tse)001:5144: dag re re la brgya phrag bdun pa gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:5145: yin no zhes dang po bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib nges
NK107(tse)001:5146: par mtshon pa'i dus nges par bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:5147: yan lag gi don gnyis pa bstan pa 'grib pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5148: bye brag gi bstan pa rin po che ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:5149: 'dzin cing las rab kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5150: gong gi bdun po de dag re re'i bar dag
NK107(tse)001:5151: tu mun pa ni dam pa'i chos mi gnas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:5152: bskal pa ni nye bar mtshon pa ste chos med
NK107(tse)001:5153: pa ni yun ring du mngon pa nas bskal pa
NK107(tse)001:5154: zhes smos pa yin la rang bzhin du lo drug
NK107(tse)001:5155: cu drug cu 'byung ste 'di'i dus su sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:5156: dang chos dang dge 'dun zhes bya ba'i sgra tsam
NK107(tse)001:5157: yang med pa dag 'byung ngo de'i 'go zug pa
NK107(tse)001:5158: dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung gis bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5159: rin po che btsas ni zhing gzhan du 'byung ste
NK107(tse)001:5160: de yang 'di nas byang gi phyogs na g.yo ba
NK107(tse)001:5161: dang ldan pa b+hud tha'i zhing khams yod de der
NK107(tse)001:5162: bstan pa'i sgron me gsung gi sprul pa ste der
NK107(tse)001:5163: gnas te de'i tshe de'i dus na bskal pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5164: ldan pa dpal ldan skyong zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:5165: dge slong dag gi gzugs 'dzin pa zhig gis gsung
NK107(tse)001:5166: gi bstan pa 'di 'dzin par 'gyur te de nyid
NK107(tse)001:5167: dang yang chos gser gyi snying po nyi ma rab
NK107(tse)001:5168: tu snang bar byed pa 'di dang lhan cig tu
NK107(tse)001:5169: gnas pa ni khyad par du rgyud gsang ba rin
NK107(tse)001:5170: po che 'di dang spyod pa yin no de nas
NK107(tse)001:5171: de'i tshe ston pa de'i yon bdag ni rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:5172: dzi na mi tra zhes bya bas byed par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5173: ro de gnyis 'dus pa las b+hud d+ha'i bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5174: me sgron ltar rab tu gsal ba'i gzhi ma byed
NK107(tse)001:5175: par 'gyur ro snying po dang ldan pa zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:5176: bar 'gyur te de nyid lo ni stong dang sum
NK107(tse)001:5177: brgya'i bar la gnas pa yin no de nas yang
NK107(tse)001:5178: sdig spyod pa'i rgyal po zhig byung ste de nyid
NK107(tse)001:5179: nub nas de nas mun pa'i bskal pa ni lo
NK107(tse)001:5180: ni drug cu'i bar la gnas pa'o zhes gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:5181: 'phel ba dang 'grib pa'i bstan pa rin po che
NK107(tse)001:5182: byang du ji ltar 'dzin pa bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:5183: gsum pa lho phyogs su bstan pa rin po che'i
NK107(tse)001:5184: 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa ni de
NK107(tse)001:5185: nas yang de'i 'og tu lho phyogs 'tshal ba skyob
NK107(tse)001:5186: zhes bya ba'i zhing khams su 'gyur te de yang
NK107(tse)001:5187: gling ni yangs shing rab tu rin po che rnams
NK107(tse)001:5188: kyiis mdzes pa ni bstan pa'i btsas rang byung gi
NK107(tse)001:5189: srog shing dang 'dra ba der babs te yang bstan
NK107(tse)001:5190: pa'i me ro ldang bar byed do dga' ba'i dpal
NK107(tse)001:5191: zhes bya ba'i ston pa byang chub sems dapa'i cha
NK107(tse)001:5192: byad gsang ba lcang lo can gyi rigs dag ni
NK107(tse)001:5193: lag na rdo rje'i gzugs 'dzin pa'i dbang gis dam
NK107(tse)001:5194: pa'i chos gser gyi snying po nyi ma rab tu
NK107(tse)001:5195: snang bar byed pa 'di b+hud rda'i bstan pa dam
NK107(tse)001:5196: pa 'di ni 'dzin par 'gyur te ston pa de'i
NK107(tse)001:5197: yon bdag ni khyim bdag gi rigs dge ba'i dngos
NK107(tse)001:5198: grub zhes bya bas byed par 'gyur ro de'i dus
NK107(tse)001:5199: na bstan pa dam pa 'di nyid lo brgya'i bar
NK107(tse)001:5200: la gnas par byed do de nas yang nub nas
NK107(tse)001:5201: yang chos med pa mun pa'i bskal par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:5202: lo ni brgya dang nyi shur chos med par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5203: ro zhes nang don gsum pa lho phyogs su bstan
NK107(tse)001:5204: pa rin po che'i 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:5205: bstan nas da ni bzhi pa de nas shar phyogs
NK107(tse)001:5206: kyi 'jig rten gyi khams su bstan pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:5207: che ji ltar babs shing nub pa'i dus bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5208: ni de nas 'dzam bu gling gi shar phyogs na
NK107(tse)001:5209: bde ba'i rlung zhes bya ba 'jig rten gyi khams
NK107(tse)001:5210: na lag na rdo rje'i ri'i gnas ri'i rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:5211: rdo 'byung ba'i ri'i rtse mo la gsung gi bstan
NK107(tse)001:5212: pa dam pa 'di babs nas 'di'i dus na su
NK107(tse)001:5213: tra sde zhes bya ba'i chos skyong ba'i rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:5214: nyid kyis bstan pa 'di 'dzin te de'i yon bdag
NK107(tse)001:5215: bram ze dza ya a ka ra zhes bya bas
NK107(tse)001:5216: byed par 'gyur ro 'di'i dus na bstan pa 'di
NK107(tse)001:5217: lo stong dang bzhi brgyar gnas par byed do de
NK107(tse)001:5218: nas yang de nyid nub nas de'i 'og tu mun
NK107(tse)001:5219: pa'i bskal pa ni lo ni stong phrag lngar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5220: ro zhes bzhi pa shar du bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib
NK107(tse)001:5221: ji ltar 'byung ba bstan nas da ni yan lag
NK107(tse)001:5222: gi don lnga pa nub phyogs su bstan pa'i 'phel
NK107(tse)001:5223: 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa ni de nas
NK107(tse)001:5224: de'i 'og tu 'dzam bu gling gi nub phyogs na
NK107(tse)001:5225: rab tu rtse ba'i gling zhes bya bar b+ha ti
NK107(tse)001:5226: sa li zhes bya ba'i skal ldan 'gro ba'i rigs
NK107(tse)001:5227: bzang po'i rigs la yang bstan pa kun gyis yang
NK107(tse)001:5228: bcud kyi snying po ni sku'i dang gsung gi dang
NK107(tse)001:5229: thugs kyi gsum 'gro ba de la babs nas de'i
NK107(tse)001:5230: tshe dge slong bde ba'i yid skyob ces bya ba
NK107(tse)001:5231: zhig gis b+hud d+ha'i bstan pa dam pa 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:5232: yin te de'i tshe yon bdag ni dpa' bo 'jig
NK107(tse)001:5233: pa zhes bya ba rdol ba'i rigs shig gis lo
NK107(tse)001:5234: stong gi bar la dam pa'i chos 'di nyid gser
NK107(tse)001:5235: gyi snying po nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed
NK107(tse)001:5236: pa 'di nyid gnas shing 'phel bar byed do de
NK107(tse)001:5237: 'das pa'i 'og tu mun pa'i skal pa nyid lo
NK107(tse)001:5238: ni stong phrag lngar gnas so zhes lnga pa nub
NK107(tse)001:5239: phyogs su bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:5240: bstan nas da ni drug pa yang 'dzam bu'i gling
NK107(tse)001:5241: du 'phel 'grib tu 'gyur te sprul pa'i sku gcig
NK107(tse)001:5242: gi bstan pa 'jig cing 'jig rten 'pho ba bstan
NK107(tse)001:5243: pa ni de ltar 'das pa'i 'og tu de nas
NK107(tse)001:5244: yang ni 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir bstan pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:5245: che'i btsas ni sku gsung thugs kyi bstan pa dngos
NK107(tse)001:5246: babs te de yang gang du babs zhe na b+hud
NK107(tse)001:5247: d+ha 'byung ba'i gnas rdo rje'i gdan zhes bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5248: rin po che 'byung ba'i gnas su dam pa'i chos
NK107(tse)001:5249: 'di nyid ni blo gros bzang po zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:5250: la babs te 'di'i 'dzin par 'gyur ro de'i tshe
NK107(tse)001:5251: yon bdag ni mkha' 'gro ma bsil byed gtsang ma
NK107(tse)001:5252: zhes bya bas byas nas dam pa'i chos 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:5253: la 'phel nas 'od 'bar ba'i rang bzhin du 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5254: nas gang zag b+hud tha ba yang dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:5255: pa 'byung ngo de nyid lo ni lnga brgya lnga
NK107(tse)001:5256: bcu'i bar la gnas so de 'das pa'i 'og tu
NK107(tse)001:5257: 'jig rten 'di sa dang chu dang me dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:5258: gi sdebs 'khrugs nas bskal pa 'di nyid zhig ste
NK107(tse)001:5259: 'di mi gnas stong pa chen por 'gyur ro de
NK107(tse)001:5260: yang bskal pa zhes pa dang por gnas pa las
NK107(tse)001:5261: 'di'i tshe na yang tha ma 'jig pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:5262: 'byung ngo zhe zhus don bcu tham pa b+hud d+ha'i
NK107(tse)001:5263: bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib nye bar mtshon pa dus nges
NK107(tse)001:5264: pa'i gnad bstan pa la drug tu byas nas bstan
NK107(tse)001:5265: no da ni zhus don bcu gcig pa rgyud kyis
NK107(tse)001:5266: lus rnam par bzhag pa 'dzam bu'i gling du bstan
NK107(tse)001:5267: pa'i 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:5268: yan lag gi don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK107(tse)001:5269: bstan pa 'jig pa'i nyer rgyu gang zag gi mtshan
NK107(tse)001:5270: nyid dang po bstan pa ni bstan pa 'jig pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5271: nye rgyu ni zhes pa gzhung gsal lo gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:5272: bstan pa 'jig pa'i nye rgyu gnyis pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5273: yang yang ni 'dzam gling byang gi ngos la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5274: pa yang gzhung gsal lo gsum pa 'jig pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5275: 'phel ba'i nye rgyu yang de 'das 'dzam gling byang
NK107(tse)001:5276: shar du zhes pa yang gzhung gsal lo yang bzhi
NK107(tse)001:5277: pa 'phel 'grib kyi nye rgyu bstan pa yang de
NK107(tse)001:5278: 'das 'og tu 'dzam gling dbus zhes pa yang gzhung
NK107(tse)001:5279: gsal lnga pa 'phel 'grib kyi nye rgyu'i gang zag
NK107(tse)001:5280: bstan pa yang de nas yang ni 'dzam gling dbus
NK107(tse)001:5281: zhes pa la sogs pa yang gzhung gsal lo drug
NK107(tse)001:5282: pa yang de 'og 'dzam bu gling gi lho la
NK107(tse)001:5283: sogs pa yang gzhung gsal lo bdun pa yang de
NK107(tse)001:5284: 'das 'og tu 'dzam gling mtshams zhes pa yang gzhung
NK107(tse)001:5285: gsal lo da ni brgyad pa bstan pa'i grangs nges
NK107(tse)001:5286: pa la bstan nas 'dzam bu gling du 'phel 'grib
NK107(tse)001:5287: kyi rim pa 'jug bsdu ba dang bcas pa yang
NK107(tse)001:5288: de ltar rim pa bdun gyis ni zhes pa yang
NK107(tse)001:5289: gzhung gsal lo de dag gis ni 'dzam bu'i gling
NK107(tse)001:5290: du bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba dris
NK107(tse)001:5291: lan bcu gcig pa la yan lag gi don brgyad
NK107(tse)001:5292: kyis bstan no da ni zhus don bcu gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:5293: rgyud kyis lus rnam par bzhag pa sprul pa sku'i
NK107(tse)001:5294: bstan pa nges pa so so'i 'dul bar byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5295: dus bstan pa la yan lag gi don gsum gyis
NK107(tse)001:5296: bstan pa'i dang po ud pa la me tog mdzes
NK107(tse)001:5297: pa'i bstan pa ni de ltar dar 'grib rdzogs nas
NK107(tse)001:5298: ni zhes pa la sogs pa rnams gzhung gsal lo
NK107(tse)001:5299: 'di dag kun gzhung gis shes so gnyis pa 'khor
NK107(tse)001:5300: ba 'jig pa'i bstan pa bstan pa ni de 'og
NK107(tse)001:5301: gtsug phud dbyangs ldan pa'i zhes pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5302: yang gzhung gsal lo gsum pa 'jig rten 'og ma
NK107(tse)001:5303: la ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa ni de nas
NK107(tse)001:5304: 'jig rten 'og ma la zhes pa gzhung gsal lo
NK107(tse)001:5305: des zhus don bcu gnyis pa la gsum du byas
NK107(tse)001:5306: nas bstan no da ni rgyud kyi zhus don bcu
NK107(tse)001:5307: gsum pa b+hud d+ha'i bstan pa dngos dang gzugs brnyan
NK107(tse)001:5308: gyi bstan pa la brten nas bskal pa can gyi
NK107(tse)001:5309: 'gro ba bstan pa rin po che 'di ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:5310: babs par 'gyur ba'i mtshan nyid bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:5311: lag gi don lngas bstan pa'i dang po bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5312: gnyis kyi 'jug pa yan lag dang bcas pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5313: pa ni rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ni zhes
NK107(tse)001:5314: pa gzhung gsal lo gnyis pa bstan pa dngos de
NK107(tse)001:5315: ji ltar gzung ba phan yon dang bcas pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5316: pa ni nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed ces
NK107(tse)001:5317: pa gzhung gsal lo gsum pa bstan pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:5318: che gnyis po 'di dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dgongs
NK107(tse)001:5319: pas brgyud pa la brten nas gti mug can 'jug
NK107(tse)001:5320: cing dmigs gtad med pa'i bsgom pa bstan pa yang
NK107(tse)001:5321: bka' gsang nges pa'i bcu bdun dang zhes pa gzhung
NK107(tse)001:5322: gsal lo bzhi pa rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud pa la
NK107(tse)001:5323: brten nas gdul bya 'dod chags can 'jug cing blang
NK107(tse)001:5324: dor med pa'i spyod pa bstan pa ni nga ni
NK107(tse)001:5325: mya ngan 'das 'og tu zhes pa yang gzhung gsal
NK107(tse)001:5326: lo lnga pa gang zag snyan khungs brgyud pa'i skal
NK107(tse)001:5327: ldan ji ltar 'byung ba la brten nas gdul bya
NK107(tse)001:5328: zhe sdang can 'jug cing gza' gtad med pa'i lta
NK107(tse)001:5329: ba'i don 'byung bar bstan pa yang de'i rjes la
NK107(tse)001:5330: rgyal po'i rigs zhes pa la sogs yang gzhung gsal
NK107(tse)001:5331: lo zhes zhus don bcu gsum pa bstan pa dngos
NK107(tse)001:5332: dang gzugs brnyan gyi bstan pa ji ltar babs par
NK107(tse)001:5333: 'gyur ba'i mtshan nyid rim pa bdun pa la sngar
NK107(tse)001:5334: byas nas bstan no da ni zhus don bcu bzhi
NK107(tse)001:5335: pa bstan pa rin po che las b+hud d+ha'i zhing
NK107(tse)001:5336: khams ji ltar 'phel bar 'gyur ba bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:5337: yan lag gi don lngar byas nas bstan pa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:5338: po bstan pa dngos kyi sa bon la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:5339: b+h+aud d+ha'i zhing khams 'phel bar bstan pa ni bstan
NK107(tse)001:5340: pa snying tig gsang ba 'di zhes pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5341: pa gzhung gsal lo gnyis pa 'di nyid la brten
NK107(tse)001:5342: nas ston pa dang 'khor gyi khyad par zhing khams
NK107(tse)001:5343: su dam pa'i chos 'dul ba'i bstan pa ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:5344: 'byung ba bstan pa ni yang ni bstan pa'i me
NK107(tse)001:5345: ro ldang zhes pa la sogs pa yang gzhung gsal
NK107(tse)001:5346: lo gsum pa 'di nyid la brten nas dam pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5347: chos mdo sde'i bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5348: ba bstan pa yang de yang dgra bcom 'bum phrag
NK107(tse)001:5349: gnyis zhes pa yang gzhung gsal lo bzhi pa dam
NK107(tse)001:5350: pa'i chos mngon ba'i bstan pa ji ltar 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:5351: bstan pa yang de nas ston pa sku 'khrungs nas
NK107(tse)001:5352: zhes pa la sogs pa yang gzhung gsal lo lnga
NK107(tse)001:5353: pa bstan pa'i tha ma la sems can gyis lus
NK107(tse)001:5354: kyi rnam pa spel ba'i bye brag bstan pa yang
NK107(tse)001:5355: de nas las kyi bye brag las zhes pa la
NK107(tse)001:5356: sogs pa gzhung gsal lo des zhus don bcu bzhi
NK107(tse)001:5357: pa la sngar byas nas bstan no da ni rgyud
NK107(tse)001:5358: kyi zhus don bac+wo lnga pa lus la yan lag
NK107(tse)001:5359: dang sa gcod kyi dmigs pa bstan pa la drug
NK107(tse)001:5360: ste rgyud bzhi'i lus dang sna tshogs bkod pa man
NK107(tse)001:5361: ngag gi lus dang yan lag bstan pa ni rgyud
NK107(tse)001:5362: kyi lus dang yan lag ni zhes pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5363: pa gzhung gsal lo gnyis pa gnad 'dus bkod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5364: lus dang yan lag bstan pa ni gnyis pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5365: ni zhes pa gzhung gsal lo gsum pa ye shes
NK107(tse)001:5366: bkod pa'i lus dang yan lag gi don bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5367: ni gsum pa'i lus ni zhes pa gzhung gsal lo
NK107(tse)001:5368: bzhi pa chos nyid bkod pa'i le'u'i lus dang yan
NK107(tse)001:5369: lag bstan pa ni bzhi pa'i lus dang ces pa
NK107(tse)001:5370: gzhung gsal lo lnga pa lta sgom bkod pa'i le'u'i
NK107(tse)001:5371: lus dang yan lag bstan pa ni lnga pa'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5372: dang yan lag ni zhes pa gzhung gsal lo drug
NK107(tse)001:5373: pa sku rnam par bkod pa'i lus dang yan lag
NK107(tse)001:5374: bstan pa ni drug pa'i zhes pa gzhung gsal lo
NK107(tse)001:5375: yan lag gis rgyas par bshad pa ni gzhung gis
NK107(tse)001:5376: shes so da ni rgyud kyi le'u dang po'i zhus
NK107(tse)001:5377: don bcu drug pa 'byung ba rnams kyi 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:5378: bstan pa la yan lag gi don gsum gyi bstan
NK107(tse)001:5379: pa'i dang po phyi'i 'byung ba la brten nas sems
NK107(tse)001:5380: can las kyi bye brag gi rnam pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5381: ni de las 'byung ba ni phyi'i sa dang chu
NK107(tse)001:5382: dang me dang rlung gis 'dod pa 'di lta ste
NK107(tse)001:5383: zhes pa'o sems can gyi spyi mthun las kyi bye
NK107(tse)001:5384: brag las sems can rnams kyi las kyi brten so
NK107(tse)001:5385: ni phyi'i 'byung ba nam mkha' la rlung gi dal
NK107(tse)001:5386: brten de la chu'i dal brten pa dang de la
NK107(tse)001:5387: sa'i dal brten pas de yang sems can las kyi
NK107(tse)001:5388: bye brag gis sa las kun gso ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:5389: la brten nas dbang po rnams gsal bar byas so
NK107(tse)001:5390: de yang sems can nyon mongs pas 'khor ba dang
NK107(tse)001:5391: de'i tshe skye ba rdzogs par 'dod do zhes dang
NK107(tse)001:5392: po phyi'i 'byung ba la brten nas sems can las
NK107(tse)001:5393: kyi bye brag rnams bstan nas da ni gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:5394: nang gi 'byung ba la brten nas sems can gyi
NK107(tse)001:5395: lus kyi bskyed pa bstan pa ni nang gi lus
NK107(tse)001:5396: bskyed pa'i gzhi la 'byung ba ni sha dang khrag
NK107(tse)001:5397: dang drod dang dbugs so las kyi rim pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5398: skye ba dang rga ba dang na ba dang 'chi
NK107(tse)001:5399: ba'o de yang 'byung ba sas ni lus kyi byas
NK107(tse)001:5400: pas sha rnams bskyed cing smin pa'o de yang dang
NK107(tse)001:5401: po barlangasa pa dang de nas thig le dang de
NK107(tse)001:5402: las kha dog bskyed pas lus kyi smin so sha'i
NK107(tse)001:5403: smin so 'dod pa ni gzugs kyi phung po bskyed
NK107(tse)001:5404: pa'i gzhi byas pa'o de yang 'byung ba chus ni
NK107(tse)001:5405: dang po 'phra ba dang 'phra 'gyur dang rab tu
NK107(tse)001:5406: 'phra 'gyur dang barlana las lus kyi 'byung ba kun
NK107(tse)001:5407: bsdus nas ni dngas mas bskyed pas khrag tu smin
NK107(tse)001:5408: par 'dod pa ni tshor ba'i phung po bskyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5409: gzhi byas pa'o de yang mes ni lus kun smin
NK107(tse)001:5410: par byas te de yang dang po mched pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5411: rab tu mched pa dang nye bar mched pa las
NK107(tse)001:5412: kha dog bskyed pas drod du smin par 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:5413: ni 'du shes kyi phung po bskyed pa'i gzhi byas
NK107(tse)001:5414: so de yang 'byung ba rlung gis 'gro ba'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5415: kun 'degs pa la de la 'byed pa dang rab
NK107(tse)001:5416: tu 'byed pa dang nye bar 'byed pa las 'phen
NK107(tse)001:5417: sdud bskyod pas sbugs su smin par byed pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5418: 'du byed kyi phung po bskyed pa'i gzhi byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:5419: zhes gnyis pa nang gi 'byung ba la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:5420: 'gro ba'i lus bskyed pa bstan nas da ni gsum
NK107(tse)001:5421: pa 'byung ba'i sgra don la bslab pa'i mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:5422: nye bar bstan pa ni de'i 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:5423: ni sa'i sgra dang chu'i sgra dang me'i sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:5424: rlung gi sgra la bslab pa'o don ni bem po
NK107(tse)001:5425: dang rig bcas kyis skad shes pa'o bye brag gis
NK107(tse)001:5426: ni gzugs la sogs pa la bslab pa'i thabs so
NK107(tse)001:5427: spyi'i rnam par nges pa bstan pa ni 'dir mdo
NK107(tse)001:5428: tsam du bstan la bye brag tu 'og nas ston
NK107(tse)001:5429: no 'byung ba sa dang chu dang me dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:5430: gis gzugs la bslabs pas rnal 'byor pa'i lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:5431: stobs zad par 'gyur ba ni 'byung ba gnad yig
NK107(tse)001:5432: tu bslab pa'i thabs rnams shes par bya'o sgra yis
NK107(tse)001:5433: sgra bzhi mtshams sbyor du shes par bya'o lhag ma
NK107(tse)001:5434: ni gzhung gsal lo zhus don bcu drug pa 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5435: ba'i 'dod pa la gsum du byas nas bstan no
NK107(tse)001:5436: da ni zhus don bcu bdun pa sems can gyi
NK107(tse)001:5437: dus kyi rim pa bstan la yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:5438: gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po dus kyi rim pa
NK107(tse)001:5439: mdor bstan pa ni sems can dus ni rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:5440: brgyad ces pa la sogs pas bstan te de yang
NK107(tse)001:5441: sems can 'chi ba'i dus byed pa ni 'du ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5442: nad gzhi'i ngang du lus kyi 'byung ba 'khrugs nas
NK107(tse)001:5443: tshe'i dus byed pa dang rlung gi 'phel 'grib la
NK107(tse)001:5444: brten nas byed pa dang tshe stod smad kyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5445: ba'i las kyi 'gyur las byed pa dang shes pa
NK107(tse)001:5446: ga cig tu mi gnas par byed pa dang nyon
NK107(tse)001:5447: mongs pa drag po skyed pa la brten nas byed
NK107(tse)001:5448: pa dang byang sems ye shes kyi 'gyu ba'i tshad
NK107(tse)001:5449: nor nas byed pa dang 'byung ba byer zug snyoms
NK107(tse)001:5450: pa'i dus 'gyur ba'i las byed dus byed pa dang
NK107(tse)001:5451: brgyad do zhes dang po dus kyi rim pa mdor
NK107(tse)001:5452: nas da ni gnyis pa dus kyi 'byung ba 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5453: ba las phyis rlung sems 'pho ba'i rtags bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5454: ni dbyar me'i dus la rnal 'byor pa'i shes pa
NK107(tse)001:5455: yang re lde spyamng la btags pa ltar gnas te
NK107(tse)001:5456: gos dang zas kyi rnal 'byor gyi rim pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5457: pa ni 'di'i dus su me'i lus yin na me
NK107(tse)001:5458: gso ba'i cho ga bya chu yin na spel ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5459: cho ga bya sa yin na gnas pa'i cho ga
NK107(tse)001:5460: bya rlung yin na snyoms pa'i cho ga bya'o zas
NK107(tse)001:5461: dang gos la sogs pa nyal ba'i 'khor lo dang
NK107(tse)001:5462: sbyar ro dgun chu'i dus la chu'i lus yin na
NK107(tse)001:5463: gnas pa bya sas bzlog pa bya mes dkrug pa
NK107(tse)001:5464: bya rlung gis gso zhing spel ba bya'o ston rlung
NK107(tse)001:5465: gi dus la rlung gis spar ba bya'o chus bsdud
NK107(tse)001:5466: pa dang mes gseng ba bya sas dgug pa bya'o
NK107(tse)001:5467: dpyid sa yin te sa lus yin na 'phel ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5468: las bya chus gso ba'i cho ga bya sas gseng
NK107(tse)001:5469: mes spar rlung gis bsil ba'i cho ga bya'o lhag
NK107(tse)001:5470: ma 'phrin las bzhi la sogs pa'i dge ba'i bya
NK107(tse)001:5471: lug la sogs pa ni nyal 'khor ltar bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:5472: yang spyi'i dus bzhi la ston zla gsum rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:5473: khams la rlung bcos pa'i kha zas la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5474: brten no dbyar gsum mkhris pa'i khams de nyid la
NK107(tse)001:5475: shis pa'i sbyor ba bya'o dgun bad kan chu'i khams
NK107(tse)001:5476: la de nyid la shis pa'i sbyor ba bya'o dpyid
NK107(tse)001:5477: gsum 'dus pa sa'i khams la sum sbyor la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5478: pa bya'o de ltar dus bzhi la 'byung ba snyoms
NK107(tse)001:5479: pa'i sbyor ba mkhas pas bya'o gal te de dag
NK107(tse)001:5480: gis las 'gyur bas 'byung ba bzhi so so'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:5481: nas 'phos pa yis lus kyi 'byung ba byer zug
NK107(tse)001:5482: gi las 'gyur ba ste so so'i lo dang zla
NK107(tse)001:5483: ba dang zhag dang nyi ma dang rang rang gis
NK107(tse)001:5484: dus nges pa la nad kyis btab nas de nas
NK107(tse)001:5485: lus kyi 'byung ba rdzogs pa'i dus zhag bcu gsum
NK107(tse)001:5486: du 'gro ba'i rang bzhin gyis dus na sems can
NK107(tse)001:5487: de'i rlung 'phos pas sems can gyis lus kyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5488: ba rang bag la nyal ba sems 'phos pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:5489: la bab pas de nyid chos nyid bar ma do
NK107(tse)001:5490: la 'jug pa'o de ltar 'byung ba so so'i las
NK107(tse)001:5491: 'gyur ba de'i dus na rlung gi yang nas yang
NK107(tse)001:5492: du brtsegs ma'am thung par byung la 'di ni chu'i
NK107(tse)001:5493: las la'o sa'i lus la yang na dal zhing bar
NK107(tse)001:5494: ma chad pa dag 'ong ngo me la yang na
NK107(tse)001:5495: tsha zhing 'phra bar 'gyur ro rlung la 'phar zhing
NK107(tse)001:5496: rgal bar 'gyur ba'i dus na 'di lta bu 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5497: ba'i me de tshe thung bar byed do 'di dag
NK107(tse)001:5498: gi dus na mi de'i shes pa 'khrog cing 'bar
NK107(tse)001:5499: ba'i las rlung gi mi la chu la myos pa'am
NK107(tse)001:5500: me la skabs su gseng chu la 'phyo bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5501: ro 'di'i dus na las ma dag pa rnams las
NK107(tse)001:5502: nyon mongs pa lnga 'dus pa yin 'phen pa'i rlung
NK107(tse)001:5503: gi las ma dag pa las ngan song gsum gyis
NK107(tse)001:5504: gnas su 'phen par byeed do de yang las ma
NK107(tse)001:5505: dag pa'i 'gro ba chu la rang gi byang chub
NK107(tse)001:5506: sems ni 'jil ba dang las kyi rlung byed pa
NK107(tse)001:5507: log pa'i rtags su ngan song du 'agro'o sa la
NK107(tse)001:5508: rab tu 'phrims shing dwangs pa yin no me la
NK107(tse)001:5509: 'phra bar 'gyur ba yin no rlung la ye shes
NK107(tse)001:5510: gsal ba ma yin no 'di ltar 'byung ba'i 'gro
NK107(tse)001:5511: ba ni 'phen pa las kyi rlung ma dag pa
NK107(tse)001:5512: las ngan song du 'gro ba'i bltas so de yang
NK107(tse)001:5513: 'byung ba byer zug las kyi 'gyur ba 'phos pas
NK107(tse)001:5514: sems can gcig gi tshe'i dus byed do zhes gnyis
NK107(tse)001:5515: pa dus kyi 'byung ba las kyi rlung 'pho ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5516: dus bstan nas da ni gsum pa sems can gyis
NK107(tse)001:5517: tshe'i bye brag las ji ltar 'grib pa mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:5518: bstan pa ni sems can gyis dus la sogs par
NK107(tse)001:5519: gzhung gsal lo zhus don bcu bdun pa la gsum
NK107(tse)001:5520: du byas nas bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i
NK107(tse)001:5521: zhus don bco brgyad pa phyi rol 'byung ba lnga'i
NK107(tse)001:5522: chags 'jig gi bye brag ji ltar yin pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5523: pa la yan lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5524: dang po phyi snod kyi rim pa ji ltar chags
NK107(tse)001:5525: pa bstan pa ni phyi rol 'byung ba lung las
NK107(tse)001:5526: yang zhes pa gzhan du rgyas par bstan pas 'di
NK107(tse)001:5527: ni gzhung gis shes so gnyis pa nang bcud kyi
NK107(tse)001:5528: sems can ji ltar chags yang gzhung gsal lo gsum
NK107(tse)001:5529: pa chags 'jig gi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni don
NK107(tse)001:5530: ni 'jig dang zhes pa gzhung gsal lo zhus don
NK107(tse)001:5531: bco brgyad pa la gsum du byas nas bstan no
NK107(tse)001:5532: de ni le'u dang po'i zhus don bcu dgu pa
NK107(tse)001:5533: bskal pa'i rim pa'i nye bar mtshon pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5534: la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:5535: po bskal chen dang bskal chung gi rim pas dus
NK107(tse)001:5536: kyi 'pho ba bstan pa ni dus kyi 'pho ba
NK107(tse)001:5537: 'di lta ste zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te
NK107(tse)001:5538: dus ni 'jig pa dang chags pa dang gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:5539: la sogs pa'o 'pho ba ni las kyi rim pa
NK107(tse)001:5540: 'gyur ba'o 'di lta ste ni bstan par bya zhes
NK107(tse)001:5541: pa'i don no de yang thog ma tshe lo dpag
NK107(tse)001:5542: tu med pa thub pa nas mar la rims kyis
NK107(tse)001:5543: bri nas de yang brgya brgya'i bar la re re
NK107(tse)001:5544: bri ba las tha ma bcu'i bar dag las yang
NK107(tse)001:5545: de las brgya brgya la re re skyes te de
NK107(tse)001:5546: ltar yang skye ba dang zhes so mar 'grib pa
NK107(tse)001:5547: zhes pa yang tshe lo dpag tu med pa las
NK107(tse)001:5548: de yang brgya brgya la re re bri nas yang
NK107(tse)001:5549: bcu pa la thug pa dang de nas yar skye
NK107(tse)001:5550: ba ni bcu nas brgyad khri la thug par skye
NK107(tse)001:5551: ba dang mar 'grib pa bcu'i dus na nad kyi
NK107(tse)001:5552: bskal pa ste ji skad byas pa ci dang ci
NK107(tse)001:5553: byas pa thams cad nad du gyur pa lo brgya'i
NK107(tse)001:5554: bar la 'ong ba bkod pa chen po nas bshad
NK107(tse)001:5555: do de 'das nas mu ge lo brgya dang de
NK107(tse)001:5556: 'das nas ci blangs mtshon du song nas 'chib lo
NK107(tse)001:5557: brgya dang ni bskal chung gsum gyis mtshams sbyar nas
NK107(tse)001:5558: sems can rnams sdug basngala du byed pa ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:5559: dag gis dus na 'gro ba srid pa tsam las
NK107(tse)001:5560: yang mched nas 'gro ba mang por las dang nyon
NK107(tse)001:5561: mongs pa'i dbang gis 'phel ba'o de ltar bskal chung
NK107(tse)001:5562: gsum gyis 'gro ba ma lus par byas kyang mang
NK107(tse)001:5563: du 'phel ba mi sdug basngala gyis mtha' ma stongs
NK107(tse)001:5564: pa las byung ba'o de dag bskal pa 'jog pa
NK107(tse)001:5565: 'gal ba ni ma yin no de yang 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:5566: ma lus pa'i phung po 'jig par byed pas na
NK107(tse)001:5567: bskal pa zhes sdug basngala rag pa la dgongs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:5568: de ltar yar skye ba dang mar 'grib pa'i bar
NK107(tse)001:5569: la brtsis pa'i ya tha dang ma tha'i drug cu
NK107(tse)001:5570: dag ni thal nas yang 'jig pa'i bskal pa 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5571: ste 'og gi 'jig rten las 'byung ba rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:5572: rang sgra'i 'dod pa g.yos pa las lhab lhab sgra
NK107(tse)001:5573: 'byung chu las spir ba'i sgra 'byung gnyis 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:5574: las me'i phung po cig tu rlung dang chu'i bar
NK107(tse)001:5575: du gyur pa las 'og tu rlung gi dal bsregs
NK107(tse)001:5576: shing stongs par byas so de las yang rang 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5577: du byung bas na 'byung ba ste rlung gi dal
NK107(tse)001:5578: nam makha'i sgra yangs 'byed zhes bya ba la brten
NK107(tse)001:5579: nas chags te de las rang 'byung du me'i rdo
NK107(tse)001:5580: rje chen po gcig tu gyen la 'phros pas chu'i
NK107(tse)001:5581: dal skams par byas so de las sa'i dal ma
NK107(tse)001:5582: zhig par gnas pa las nam makha'i bsil byed me'i
NK107(tse)001:5583: thigs par rang shar bas sa yang bsregs shing stong
NK107(tse)001:5584: par byas so de las chu'i dal rab tu srab
NK107(tse)001:5585: pa khod snyoms pa rlung gis sa bon la brten
NK107(tse)001:5586: nas chags so de las nam mkha' la rlung chen
NK107(tse)001:5587: por gyur te sprin gyi phung por rnam par sprus
NK107(tse)001:5588: pa tsam zhig chags pa las me'i char 'khor lo'i
NK107(tse)001:5589: rnam pa dang 'dra ba babs pas rlung gi dal
NK107(tse)001:5590: dang chu'i dal la sogs pa thams cad lan gcig
NK107(tse)001:5591: bsregs so yang 'byung ba'i rang sgra las lan cig
NK107(tse)001:5592: chags gong ltar 'byung ba'i dal bzhi ka res shig
NK107(tse)001:5593: bsregs so de ltar bzhi ste me yis mdun du
NK107(tse)001:5594: byas pa ni gong gi bstan pa rim pa mdun
NK107(tse)001:5595: du gnas pa las 'phel 'grib kyis rnam pa las
NK107(tse)001:5596: byung ba'i bye brag gis las so 'di nyid la
NK107(tse)001:5597: nyi ma bdun 'char bar 'dod pa ni theg pa
NK107(tse)001:5598: chung ba'i blo can rnams la yin no de nas
NK107(tse)001:5599: yang 'byung ba'i rang sgra las yang gong ma'i de
NK107(tse)001:5600: dag rnam par rang byung du chags te yang gong
NK107(tse)001:5601: ltar rlung gi sgra dang chu'i sgra nang 'thab pa
NK107(tse)001:5602: las gong ltar chu'i rlung zhig pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5603: snga ma ltar chus bdun du byed do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:5604: me chu gnyis la skye ba dang 'grib pa nyi
NK107(tse)001:5605: shu nyi shu ste bzhi bcu la me chu'i bcu
NK107(tse)001:5606: bzhi rdzogs nas ni rang byung gis 'byung ba las
NK107(tse)001:5607: sus kyang byas pa med par nam mkha' rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:5608: sgra byung bas de nas rlung gis dal snga ma
NK107(tse)001:5609: dang 'dra bar chags so de las chu'i rlung byung
NK107(tse)001:5610: bas chu'i dal chags de las me'i mdangs byung bas
NK107(tse)001:5611: sa'i dal snga ma dang 'dra bar chags so yang
NK107(tse)001:5612: nam makha'i 'og nas rang byung gser gyis rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:5613: skad myur la shugs che rab tu sbir ba'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:5614: dang bcas pas rang byung du byung nas 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5615: dal thams cad dkrugs pas thams cad gcig tu 'dres
NK107(tse)001:5616: pa las rdo rje'i gong shul nas yang rlung gdung
NK107(tse)001:5617: shing gi rnam pa dang 'dra ba langs pa las
NK107(tse)001:5618: rab tu mched pas thams cad rlung gi rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:5619: du 'gyur nas 'dres pa'i lhag ma rlung gis nyi
NK107(tse)001:5620: shu'i bar la 'jig pa yin no zhes dang po
NK107(tse)001:5621: bskal chen dang bskal chung gi rim pa dus kyis
NK107(tse)001:5622: 'pho ba bstan nas da ni gnyis pa bskal pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5623: grangs dang tshad kyi rim pa bstan pa chen po
NK107(tse)001:5624: ji ltar brtsi ba bstan pa ni bskal pa rab
NK107(tse)001:5625: 'bring tha ma gsum las khyad par du bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:5626: ni b+hud d+ha'i skabs nas brtsis pa'o brtsis pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5627: gzhung gis shes so zhus don bcu dgu pa la
NK107(tse)001:5628: gnyis su byas nas bstan no da ni rgyud kyi
NK107(tse)001:5629: le'u dang po'i zhus don nyi shu pa zhag dang
NK107(tse)001:5630: zla ba dang po la brten nas 'byung ba brtsis
NK107(tse)001:5631: sbyor gyi gzhi bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:5632: gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po zhag la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:5633: lo'i bye brag bstan pa ni zhag ni bcu phrag
NK107(tse)001:5634: gsum la yang zhes pa las bsogs pa gzhung gis
NK107(tse)001:5635: shes so da ni gnyis pa nang nub dag nas
NK107(tse)001:5636: las zhag dang po bstan pa ni nang dang dgongs
NK107(tse)001:5637: mo yang zhes pa gzhung gis shes so da ni
NK107(tse)001:5638: gsum pa 'byung ba pho mo'i las kyi dbye ba
NK107(tse)001:5639: la brten nas lo'i smin so 'byung ba byer zug
NK107(tse)001:5640: gi lus ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni zhag ni
NK107(tse)001:5641: pho nyin mo la mo mtshan mo'i las kyis dbye
NK107(tse)001:5642: ba ni nang gi dus bcu ste mkha' lding gi
NK107(tse)001:5643: dus dang 'phur rkyen la sogs pa'i dus bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:5644: te nyin drug la pho brtsis la mtshan drug la
NK107(tse)001:5645: mo brtsis so de yang phyi dus ni zla ba
NK107(tse)001:5646: ston zla ba gsum rlung gi dus yin la dpyid
NK107(tse)001:5647: gsum sa'i dus yin la dbyar gsum me'i dus yin
NK107(tse)001:5648: no dgun gsum chu'i dus yin no de ltar ston
NK107(tse)001:5649: dpyid la sogs par re re dag la zla ba
NK107(tse)001:5650: gsum gsum gyis sa dang chu dang me dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:5651: la 'jug cing 'byung ba byer zug snyoms pa'i 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5652: ba'i las rlung dang mkhris pa dang bad kan dang
NK107(tse)001:5653: 'dus pa dang de las skyes pa dang rgas pa
NK107(tse)001:5654: dang na ba dang 'chi ba rnams su byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:5655: de ltar 'byung ba'i byed las bcu gnyis las smin
NK107(tse)001:5656: so lo bcu gnyis su byung ste chu zug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5657: dus las byi ba'i lor smin pa ni lus chu'i
NK107(tse)001:5658: sa'i lus la 'khrul pa ma rig pa'i byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5659: las ma dag pa las 'khrul lo yang byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5660: dus las glang du smin pa ni chu'i me'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5661: su byung la 'khrul pa 'du byed ma dag pa
NK107(tse)001:5662: las so snyoms pa las stag nyid du smin pa
NK107(tse)001:5663: ni chu'i rlung gi lus te 'khrul pa rnam par
NK107(tse)001:5664: shes pa las so chu'i chu'i lus ni de dag
NK107(tse)001:5665: gsum 'dus pa ste 'di ni ngo mtshar gyis 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5666: ba las bskyed pa dbang po'i sgo lhag pa'am mdun
NK107(tse)001:5667: na so lhag pa yod pa rnams so yang na
NK107(tse)001:5668: stag khung gi nas skra tshoms gcig gyen la langs
NK107(tse)001:5669: pa dag yin no sna rings la sogs pa gsum
NK107(tse)001:5670: ni gong ltar sa'i lus so rta dang ni me'i
NK107(tse)001:5671: 'o bya dang ni rlung gi ste gong ltar zug
NK107(tse)001:5672: pa la sogs pa'o de yang zug byer la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5673: pa gsum gyis smin pa yang thog ma ma'i mngal
NK107(tse)001:5674: nas 'byung ba bzhi yis gcig tu bsdus pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:5675: na dmigs chags pa la zug par song la so
NK107(tse)001:5676: sor zhig pa'i dus la byer ba zhag bdun gyis
NK107(tse)001:5677: rim pa rdzogs pa'i dus las snyoms pa'o de rnams
NK107(tse)001:5678: rang bzhin du 'gyur ba las lhag pa'i 'byung bar
NK107(tse)001:5679: gyur pa'o de yang 'khrul so'i dbang du brtsis na
NK107(tse)001:5680: ma rig pas rmongs shing ma rungs pa'i las la
NK107(tse)001:5681: dga' la 'du byed kyis bya ba sna tshogs la
NK107(tse)001:5682: 'jug par byed la rnam par shes pa gsal zhing
NK107(tse)001:5683: rang bzhin gyis bya ba la mkhas la ming dang
NK107(tse)001:5684: gzugs kyis 'jug pa'i rnam pa la mkhas shing tha
NK107(tse)001:5685: snyad kyi gtso bor gyur pa ste skye mched drug
NK107(tse)001:5686: gis dga' bde sna tshogs pa'i 'phrul gyis gnas la
NK107(tse)001:5687: reg pas shes pa sna tshogs pa'i lus can du
NK107(tse)001:5688: 'gyur zhing tshor ba'i myong ba'i bya ba la brtson
NK107(tse)001:5689: pa srid pas 'jig rten gyi bya ba la mkhas
NK107(tse)001:5690: la sred pas 'dod pa'i don bslabs che zhing chog
NK107(tse)001:5691: mi shes len pas yin min gyi bya ba kun
NK107(tse)001:5692: la 'jug par byed do skye bas glo bur gyi
NK107(tse)001:5693: dran pa'i khyab byed pa can rga shis snyoms las
NK107(tse)001:5694: kyi phung po rnams su byed do de dag gis
NK107(tse)001:5695: ni nang gi 'byung brtsis phung po dang khams dang
NK107(tse)001:5696: skye mched dang dus dang na ba dang 'chi ba
NK107(tse)001:5697: dang tshe dang dbang thang dang longs spyod dang dga'
NK107(tse)001:5698: ba dang mi dga' ba dang las dang las kyi
NK107(tse)001:5699: mtha' rnams dang 'byung ba spo ba dang snyoms pa
NK107(tse)001:5700: dang gso ba dang bshig pa dang nad 'joms pa
NK107(tse)001:5701: dang shed la 'bebs pa dang spel ba rnams byed
NK107(tse)001:5702: pa'o zhes zhus don nyi shu la zhag dang zla
NK107(tse)001:5703: ba dang lo la brten nas 'byung ba brtsis sbyor
NK107(tse)001:5704: gyi gzhi bstan pa la gsum du byas nas bstan
NK107(tse)001:5705: no da ni le'u dang po'i gzhung don nyer gcig
NK107(tse)001:5706: pa 'byung ba tshe sbyor gyi rnam pa la brten
NK107(tse)001:5707: nas 'jig rten thun mong gis las bsgrub par bstan
NK107(tse)001:5708: pa la yan lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5709: dang po tshe spyod kyi rnal 'byor gyi rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:5710: bsgrub pa'i bya ba dang rten 'brel bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5711: tshe ni spel dang gso ba dang zhes pa la
NK107(tse)001:5712: sogs pas bstan te de yang tshe ni zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:5713: gnas skabs gcig la mtshams ma chod pa la dmigs
NK107(tse)001:5714: pa ste de la lus dang 'brel bas 'jug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5715: las dang thob pa'i las gnyis kyis 'byung ba'i bye
NK107(tse)001:5716: brag so so'i bcud las grub bo spel dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:5717: pa ni 'byung ba so so'i lus ngos zin par
NK107(tse)001:5718: byas la me zug pas rtag tu 'o ma brten
NK107(tse)001:5719: byer bas rdo'i sbyor ba brten snyoms pas sman sna
NK107(tse)001:5720: tshogs brten chu zug pas ba ti ba'i sman mar
NK107(tse)001:5721: brten byer bas sin d+hu ra'i thig le gnas gsum
NK107(tse)001:5722: du rgyun du bya snyoms pas mthil bzhi la sku
NK107(tse)001:5723: gnye brten yangs zug pas shing sbyor ba lnga la
NK107(tse)001:5724: brten byer bas sngo sbyor sna tshogs pa brten snyoms
NK107(tse)001:5725: pas chang nyung zad brten par bya'o yang rlung zug
NK107(tse)001:5726: pas b+ha la sha'i sman mar brten byer bas mu
NK107(tse)001:5727: zi cong zi'i gam phye brten snyoms pas tsan+dana dang
NK107(tse)001:5728: seng ldeng gi phye ma brten no gso ba dang
NK107(tse)001:5729: zhes pa ni chu khams kyis rang gis lus la
NK107(tse)001:5730: chu sna tshogs pa'i rten 'brel gyis bya'o sa lus
NK107(tse)001:5731: sa'i me lus me'i rlung lus rlung gis bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:5732: dag so so'i thug pas bsogs pa'i las bya byer
NK107(tse)001:5733: bas bsgrang ba'i sbyor ba bya snyoms pas spo ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5734: rten 'brel byas pas na ba dang 'chi ba'i ltas
NK107(tse)001:5735: byung ba rnams las rab tu thar bar 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:5736: bsgrub dang zhes pa ni tshe bsgrub pa'i las kyi
NK107(tse)001:5737: rim pa rdzogs pa rang 'byung gi rgyud kyi skabs
NK107(tse)001:5738: nas ston te spros pa la dga' na der blta'o
NK107(tse)001:5739: mi dga' na 'di ltar 'sgrub ste so so'i 'go
NK107(tse)001:5740: lnga 'dus pa'i lus nges pa la mam tal dmar
NK107(tse)001:5741: por rang gi khru gang gi tshad dang ldan pa
NK107(tse)001:5742: byas la dbus su rin po che dang 'bru sna
NK107(tse)001:5743: tshogs pa spungs te de'i steng du bum pa mtshan
NK107(tse)001:5744: dang ldan pa'i nang du chu srog chags med pas
NK107(tse)001:5745: bltam te rin po che dang dri sna tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:5746: yang blugs la ras dmar po dri ma med pas
NK107(tse)001:5747: mgul pa bcings la shing mya ngan med pas kha
NK107(tse)001:5748: brgyan byas la ras mtshon lnga bsgril ba'i tha gus
NK107(tse)001:5749: gzungs thag btags te rnal 'byor pa rang gi lus
NK107(tse)001:5750: la dri sna tshogs pa'i khrus nas ston la ras
NK107(tse)001:5751: dmar pos thod byas te rang gi bla ma la
NK107(tse)001:5752: gsol ba btab steh bum pa de stong bar bsgom
NK107(tse)001:5753: de nas 'brumm zhes rin po che'i gzhal yas khang
NK107(tse)001:5754: du bsgom de'i ngang las a yongs su gyur pa
NK107(tse)001:5755: las tshe'i lhas sku mdog dmar gsal zhal gcig phyag
NK107(tse)001:5756: gnyis pa g.yon na rin po che'i bum pa 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:5757: pa g.yas na rin po che'i snye ma 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:5758: cig bum pa'i nang du gsal bar bsgom mo de
NK107(tse)001:5759: las nam mkha' la 'od dmar po dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:5760: pa spros pas rang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa spyan
NK107(tse)001:5761: drangs te rang 'dra ba dpag tu med pa thugs
NK107(tse)001:5762: khar gzhug go snang ba mtha' yas kyis dbu brgyan
NK107(tse)001:5763: pa'o de nas rang gi lag pa g.yon pa'i srin
NK107(tse)001:5764: lag tu gzungs thag bzungs te rlung re re'i khongs
NK107(tse)001:5767: +aa +aa zhes sgra ha cang che ba yang ma
NK107(tse)001:5768: yin chung ba yang ma yin drag pa yang ma
NK107(tse)001:5769: yin zhan pa yang ma yin ring pa ma yin
NK107(tse)001:5770: thung ba ma yin par barjoda par bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:5771: rlung gi 'gyur rang gi lo grangs tsam las lo
NK107(tse)001:5772: grangs su 'dabs pa bsgrangs na nyi zla dag dang
NK107(tse)001:5773: mnyam par 'gyur ro yang tshe lo rgyas pa'i cho
NK107(tse)001:5774: ga nyid ji ltar bya ba ni yang so so'i
NK107(tse)001:5775: mgo lnga'i dus la tshogs bsags pa'i bya ba ste
NK107(tse)001:5776: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang myong ba dang 'dag
NK107(tse)001:5777: pa dang btung ba la sogs pas rang gi bla
NK107(tse)001:5778: ma dang 'gro ba rnams mnyes par byas na yang
NK107(tse)001:5779: rgyas bar 'gyur ro gal te mgo lnga 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:5780: dag la ma grub na dbyar dgun snyoms dus gnyis
NK107(tse)001:5781: la bya'o 'di'i dus na bla ma rdo rje'i spun
NK107(tse)001:5782: sring la mchog tu bzang ngo 'di ltar bzhi rnal
NK107(tse)001:5783: 'byor pa yis sbyor ba ni yang na chu'i lus
NK107(tse)001:5784: kyis spel ba'i sbyor ba bya sa'i lus kyis gso
NK107(tse)001:5785: bar bya mes bsgrub rlung gis rgyas pa'i sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:5786: shes na rnal 'byor pa de dag gi tshe nyi
NK107(tse)001:5787: zla dag dang mnyam par 'gyur ro zhes dang po
NK107(tse)001:5788: rang gi tshe spyod kyi bya ba dang rten 'brel
NK107(tse)001:5789: la brten pa bstan nas da ni gnyis pa gzhan
NK107(tse)001:5790: gyi nyams shing gzhig par bya ba las kyi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5791: ba bstan pa ni gzhan ni zhes pa bla ma
NK107(tse)001:5792: dang dkon mchog dang b+hud d+ha'i bstan pa la gnod
NK107(tse)001:5793: pa'i 'gro ba dag nyams par byed pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5794: ste ma rungs pa'i las bstan pa ni nyams dang
NK107(tse)001:5795: zhes pa pha rol po chu yin na 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:5796: 'phen pa'i las bya sa yin na dri'i sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:5797: bya me yin na sbar zhing gsad pa'i sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:5798: bya rlung yin na 'byung ba gnan pa'i las sna
NK107(tse)001:5799: tshogs pa bya'o de yang so so nyams pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:5800: la bya'o de la las kyi bye brag gis kho
NK107(tse)001:5801: rang gi lo grangs tsam dang de nyid gnyis 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:5802: dang sum 'gyur dang tha ma yang bdun 'gyur du
NK107(tse)001:5803: 'khrul ma nor bar byas na nges par 'grub bo
NK107(tse)001:5804: grub pas ni lus dang ngag dang yid rab tu
NK107(tse)001:5805: nyams par 'gyur ro de yang bsgrub bya nus pa
NK107(tse)001:5806: dang bral ba dang las kyi 'gyur gyis dbye ba'o
NK107(tse)001:5807: gzhig pa dang zhes pa ni pha rol chu yin
NK107(tse)001:5808: na me'i sbyor ba sna tshogs pa phyin ci log
NK107(tse)001:5809: tu bya'o sa yin na chu me yin na yang
NK107(tse)001:5810: sa dang rlung gis bya'o rlung yin na sa dang
NK107(tse)001:5811: mes bya'o de yang so so'i 'jig par 'gyur ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5812: dus la bya'o de nyid grub pas so so'i 'byung
NK107(tse)001:5813: ba'i phung po 'jig pa'o yang dgugs dang zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:5814: ni chu la bri ba'i sbyor bas khugs la sa
NK107(tse)001:5815: la gnas pas so me la ming dbyi ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:5816: bya'o rlung la ming bsgyur ba'i sbyor bas bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:5817: yang bri ba'i rgyu ni chu la dar sa la
NK107(tse)001:5818: / rgya shog / me la ta la'i lo ma
NK107(tse)001:5819: rlung la ras dmar po snag tsha ni chu la
NK107(tse)001:5820: li khri dang mtshal sa la a la ka'i khu
NK107(tse)001:5821: ba me la ldong ros ba dmar mo'i 'o ma
NK107(tse)001:5822: rlung la tshil chen gyi dud pas bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:5823: gang 'gugs pa lo grangs tsam byas pas ma khugs
NK107(tse)001:5824: na sum 'gyur gyis nges par 'grub bo nor dang
NK107(tse)001:5825: 'khor du bcas pa dbang du 'gyur ba las the
NK107(tse)001:5826: tshom med do bcing dang zhes pa ni chu la
NK107(tse)001:5827: 'byung ba gzhan gsum po sum sbyor du bya'o me
NK107(tse)001:5828: la sa dang chu'o sa la rlung dang chu'o rlung
NK107(tse)001:5829: la sa'i sbyor ba bya'o lan grangs gong dang 'dra'o
NK107(tse)001:5830: gshed la dbab ces pa ni chu la sas bya
NK107(tse)001:5831: sa la rlung gis me la chus rlung la sas
NK107(tse)001:5832: bya'o spo zhing zhes pa ni rang gi nad la
NK107(tse)001:5833: sogs pa gzhan la spo ba gnad de chu la
NK107(tse)001:5834: sngo ba grangs dang bcas pa la dmigs pa mi
NK107(tse)001:5835: 'gyur bar bya'o sa la a li yis 'grub rlung
NK107(tse)001:5836: la sa tri zhes pa 'bum phrag gcig gis 'grub
NK107(tse)001:5837: bo 'di'i dus na dmigs pa ni so so'i mthun
NK107(tse)001:5838: pas 'grub pa yin no gsad pa'i las rnams yang
NK107(tse)001:5839: zhes pa ni chu la sbyin bsreg gis 'grub sa
NK107(tse)001:5840: la 'phang ba'i las kyis 'grub me la zor gyis
NK107(tse)001:5841: 'grub rlung la gnan pas 'grub bo rnal 'byor pa
NK107(tse)001:5842: yis dkrug pa ni chu la sna tshogs bsgyur bas
NK107(tse)001:5843: las bya me la sna tshogs spo ba'i las bya
NK107(tse)001:5844: rlung la sna tshogs 'phyar ba'i las bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:5845: 'khrul 'khor ma log par byas la 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:5846: ni dbang du 'dus pa'o zhes gnyis pa gzhan gyi
NK107(tse)001:5847: lus nyams shing zhig pa las kyi 'gyur bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:5848: da ni gsum pa rang gzhan gyi dbang thang gi
NK107(tse)001:5849: las kyi 'gyur bstan pa ni de yang dbang gi
NK107(tse)001:5850: 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa'i 'dod pa'i don thang
NK107(tse)001:5851: ni las kyi 'gyur gyis longs spyod pa'i bye brag
NK107(tse)001:5852: bstan pa'o de nyid spel bar byed na mnyam dus
NK107(tse)001:5853: gnyis la lus bzhi kas ston mo bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:5854: rang gi bla ma mnyes pa'i yon dbul bar bya'o
NK107(tse)001:5855: gso bar 'dod na chus rang gi dus la chus
NK107(tse)001:5856: rten 'brel bya'o de bzhin du sa dang me dang
NK107(tse)001:5857: rlung la yang so so'i dus la rang rang gi
NK107(tse)001:5858: rten 'brel sna tshogs pa bya'o de nyid yun ring
NK107(tse)001:5859: par gnas shing tshags par byed na lus bzhi ka
NK107(tse)001:5860: mgo lnga 'dus pa'i gong ma la tshogs kyi 'khor
NK107(tse)001:5861: lo bya'o gzhan bstan pa la gnod pa'i dbang thang
NK107(tse)001:5862: dang ni longs spyod nyams par 'dod na dri sna
NK107(tse)001:5863: tshogs pa'i dud pa'i sbyor ba bya'o de yang kho
NK107(tse)001:5864: rang gi nyams pa'i dus nges pa la ming rus
NK107(tse)001:5865: la gdug go de ltar ma 'khrul bar byas na
NK107(tse)001:5866: nges par 'grub bo de yang med par 'dod na
NK107(tse)001:5867: rlung la bskur ba dang nor gang yod pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5868: ming du bris te chu la bskur ba la sogs
NK107(tse)001:5869: pa byas na nges par 'grub par 'gyur ro las
NK107(tse)001:5870: de dag rnal 'byor pa yis brtsam par bya'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:5871: pa ni rang don dang gzhan la dgongs pa ste
NK107(tse)001:5872: thun mong gi rnam pa la dgongs pa'o zhes zhus
NK107(tse)001:5873: don nyer gcig pa 'byung ba tshe sbyor gyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:5874: pa la brten nas 'jig rten thun mong gi las
NK107(tse)001:5875: mtha' bsgrub par bstan pa la gsum du byas nas
NK107(tse)001:5876: bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i zhus don nyer
NK107(tse)001:5877: gnyis pa lus rnam par bzhag pa 'byung ba byer
NK107(tse)001:5878: zug gi las kyi rnam grangs la brten nas las
NK107(tse)001:5879: kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa la yan lag gi don
NK107(tse)001:5880: gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po sa chu me rlung
NK107(tse)001:5881: so so'i las kyi 'brel brtsi ba bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:5882: byer ba ni las kyi mtha' yas pa la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:5883: pa'o zug pa ni 'byung ba 'dus pa la dgongs
NK107(tse)001:5884: la snyoms pa ni 'byung ba bzhi cha snyam pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5885: 'gyur te de ltar 'byung ba bzhi gsum gsum du
NK107(tse)001:5886: brtsis pas bcu gnyis te de yang gong du bstan
NK107(tse)001:5887: pa dang 'dra bas sa chu me rlung bzhi la
NK107(tse)001:5888: yang gsum gsum nyid de bcu gnyis su brtsis pas
NK107(tse)001:5889: chu'i zug pas la sogs pa 'di dag ni lus
NK107(tse)001:5890: kyi dus yin no tshig don ni gzhung gis shes
NK107(tse)001:5891: soh da ni gnyis pa byer zug gis las kyi
NK107(tse)001:5892: mtha' bstan pa ni gsum gyis byed pa'i mtha' 'adi'o
NK107(tse)001:5893: zhes pa la sogs pa gzhung na gsal lo da
NK107(tse)001:5894: ni le'u dang po'i zhus don nyer gsum pa rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:5895: pa chen po mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba
NK107(tse)001:5896: la brten nas 'gro ba'i las rgyun bcad pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:5897: pa la yan lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5898: dang po mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba'i rang
NK107(tse)001:5899: bzhin bstan pa ni 'khor ba'i lam rgyun bcad 'dod
NK107(tse)001:5900: pas zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de yang
NK107(tse)001:5901: 'khor ba'i rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa rkyen rnams
NK107(tse)001:5902: rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa 'bras bu khams
NK107(tse)001:5903: gsum du 'khor ba'i phyir sdug basngala dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:5904: pa las 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can skye
NK107(tse)001:5905: ba bzhi dang lam rgyud lngas bsdus pas 'khor ba'o
NK107(tse)001:5906: de nyid gcad pa'i man ngag ni bya bral chen
NK107(tse)001:5907: po nam mkha' yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:5908: ba ni mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba ste
NK107(tse)001:5909: de yang yod pa'i mtha' dang bral bas dngos po'i
NK107(tse)001:5910: phyogs su ma lhung ba la med pa'i mtha' dang
NK107(tse)001:5911: bral bas stong pa'i 'dzin pa zad la yod med
NK107(tse)001:5912: gnyis kyi mtha' dang bral bas 'dzin pa rang rgyud
NK107(tse)001:5913: du bzung ba dang bral gnyis ka ma yin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5914: mtha' dang bral bas gsal zhes stong zhes gang yang
NK107(tse)001:5915: mi rtog pa'o gnyis ka ma yin pa dang bral
NK107(tse)001:5916: bas dgags bsgrub gang du yang med pa'o de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:5917: du snang ba la sogs pa'i mtha' dang bral ba
NK107(tse)001:5918: la sogs pa kun la basgre'o de yang mtha' dang
NK107(tse)001:5919: bral bas du mar ma grub la yongs su rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:5920: pas gcig tu ma grub pa'o de ltar gcig dang
NK107(tse)001:5921: du ma las 'das pas barjoda med mthar lhung dang
NK107(tse)001:5922: bral ba'i chos nyid do 'o na rdzogs chen ma
NK107(tse)001:5923: yin te mtha' spong bar 'jug go zhe na yod
NK107(tse)001:5924: par yongs su rdzogs pas btsal du med pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:5925: dang med par yongs su rdzogs pas spang du med
NK107(tse)001:5926: pa'i don dang gnyis ka rdzogs pas spang blang las
NK107(tse)001:5927: 'das pa'i don dang gnyis ka ma yin par rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:5928: pas thams cad chos nyid du gyur pa'o de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:5929: du stong pa dang stong pa ma yin pa la
NK107(tse)001:5930: sogs pa ni yongs su rdzogs pas na de nas
NK107(tse)001:5931: rdzogs pa chen po re dogs dang mthar lhung med
NK107(tse)001:5932: pa'i don zhes bya'o de yang gcig yin pas spros
NK107(tse)001:5933: pa chod la du ma yin pas spang mi dgos
NK107(tse)001:5934: so de yang mtha' yin pas dbus rnam par gcad
NK107(tse)001:5935: la dbus yin pas mtha' rnam par gcad pa lta
NK107(tse)001:5936: bu'o de ltar cis shes na mtha' dang bral bas
NK107(tse)001:5937: dbus mi gnas pa'i phyir na mtha' bkag pas dbus
NK107(tse)001:5938: stong pa dbus bkag pas mtha' gang du yang ma
NK107(tse)001:5939: dmigs pa bzhin no des na yongs su rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:5940: bsngo dang bral zhes bya ste lhag ma med par
NK107(tse)001:5941: cha shas min zhes pa la sogs pa gzhung gsal
NK107(tse)001:5942: lo zhes dang po mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi lta
NK107(tse)001:5943: ba'i rang bzhin bstan nas da ni gnyis pa mngon
NK107(tse)001:5944: gsum gnad kyi man ngag la brten nas 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5945: lam gyis rgyun gcad pa bstan pa ni de yang
NK107(tse)001:5946: dad pa dang ldan pa'i gang zag gis sngon du
NK107(tse)001:5947: 'gro ba lus ngag yid kyi bya ba'i rim pa
NK107(tse)001:5948: rdzogs nas dngos gzhi'i don nyams su len pa la
NK107(tse)001:5949: lus ngag yid kyi gnad gzir ba las byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5950: yang gnad rnam pa gsum la brten nas mngon sum
NK107(tse)001:5951: gyi gnad gzir ba ni sgo dang yul dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:5952: rigs gsum 'dus pa las mngon sum gyi chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:5953: zhes bya'o de la dus thams cad du goms par
NK107(tse)001:5954: byas pa'i stobs kyis snang ba bzhi shar nas phyi
NK107(tse)001:5955: rol 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'jig par 'gyur te de
NK107(tse)001:5956: nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i chos nyid rnam par
NK107(tse)001:5957: dag pas na chos nyid rang gi ngo bo la
NK107(tse)001:5958: yengs pa med pa mngon sum du gsal ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:5959: la mtha' rten gyi man ngag gis mi 'gul ba
NK107(tse)001:5960: gsum la gzhi bcas pas de dang rgyun du gnas
NK107(tse)001:5961: pas chos nyid kyi don las dus thams cad du
NK107(tse)001:5962: 'bral ba med pa'o de kha na rang snang gi
NK107(tse)001:5963: snang ba yin pas da de nyid la gtad pa
NK107(tse)001:5964: tsam gyis rnam rtog zad par 'gyur ro de yang
NK107(tse)001:5965: gang las byung na gong du rlung dal brten pa
NK107(tse)001:5966: las byung bas na de ltar gnas pas tha ma
NK107(tse)001:5967: rlung gi 'gro 'ong zad pa dang da ye shes
NK107(tse)001:5968: nyid la spyod pa yin te de la gnyis kyi
NK107(tse)001:5969: snang ba dang 'od gsal dag pa dang rig pa
NK107(tse)001:5970: dang ye shes kyi rang gdangs 'di la 'bral ba
NK107(tse)001:5971: med par nyams su blangs pa yis 'gro ba lha
NK107(tse)001:5972: dang mi dang lha min dang dmyal ba dang yi
NK107(tse)001:5973: dwags dang byol song dang drug gi lam khams gsum
NK107(tse)001:5974: gyi gzugs kyis bsdus pa rnams rgyun chad do ni
NK107(tse)001:5975: thams cad rang 'byung ye shes kyi kha dog dang
NK107(tse)001:5976: dbyibs la sogs pa rnams snang ba 'od gsal chen
NK107(tse)001:5977: por grol ba'i phyir ro zhes gnyis pa mngon sum
NK107(tse)001:5978: gyi gnad kyis man ngag la brten nas 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5979: lam rgyun gcad pa'i gnad bstan nas da ni gsum
NK107(tse)001:5980: pa rang bzhin gnas lugs kyis 'khrul pa'i rang rgyun
NK107(tse)001:5981: gcad pa bstan pa ni de ltar chos nyid mngon
NK107(tse)001:5982: sum gyi don la ma yengs pas da de la
NK107(tse)001:5983: gang zag gis byas pa ma yin pa'i chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:5984: ni 'dus ma byas pas skye 'jig med pa grangs
NK107(tse)001:5985: las 'das pas thig yin la gcig tu mi gnas
NK107(tse)001:5986: pas du ma yin la chos dang chos nyid kyis
NK107(tse)001:5987: bcos pa med pa'i phyir na rang sor gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5988: chos nyid la bcos mi dgos la lugs su byung
NK107(tse)001:5989: ba'i gnas lugs la lta mi dgos la rang sar
NK107(tse)001:5990: grol ba'i dgongs pa la bsgom mi dgos la shugs
NK107(tse)001:5991: su spyad pa'i spyod pas 'khrul pa dag pas na
NK107(tse)001:5992: spyad mi dgos la ma btsal grol ba'i 'bras bu
NK107(tse)001:5993: la thob mi dgos la lugs mar byung bas skye
NK107(tse)001:5994: ba med pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya'o de'i phyir na
NK107(tse)001:5995: yi ge med pa las skye ba med pa'i mngon
NK107(tse)001:5996: sum sangs rgyas kyis yul med rnam par dag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:5997: snang ba mthong zhes pa'o de ltar shar ba'i snang
NK107(tse)001:5998: ba de la 'dzin chags med pas na snang ba'i
NK107(tse)001:5999: chos thams cad ci dgar rol bas na snang ba
NK107(tse)001:6000: snang thog nas grol bas rang snang la dgag bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:6001: med cir snang chos nyid yin pas bcos mi dgos
NK107(tse)001:6002: rang byung rang la shar bas gzhan rnam par gcad
NK107(tse)001:6003: do de ltar snang stong thams cad chos nyid du
NK107(tse)001:6004: rnal du pheb pas rnam par rtog pa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:6005: rang bzhin gyis sangs kahns dag pas bsgrub mi dgos
NK107(tse)001:6006: lhun gyis grub pas bcos mi dgos phyogs lhung med
NK107(tse)001:6007: pas mnyam pa chen po zhes bya'o de yang sems
NK107(tse)001:6008: can thams cad la rang bzhin du gnas pa yin
NK107(tse)001:6009: pas thabs las 'das pas mtshon mi dgos la barjoda
NK107(tse)001:6010: du med pas tshig gis gtan la mi phebs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:6011: nges nas chos nyid kyi gshis 'dis kyang khams gsum
NK107(tse)001:6012: du 'khor ba'i sgo 'gag go zhes so zhus don
NK107(tse)001:6013: nyer gsum pa la yan lag gi don gsum du
NK107(tse)001:6014: byas nas bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i zhus
NK107(tse)001:6015: don nyer bzhi pa b+hud d+ha rnams kyi yon tan
NK107(tse)001:6016: bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan
NK107(tse)001:6017: pa'i dang po phun sum tshogs pa'i rnam grangs la
NK107(tse)001:6018: brten nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gnas pa'i yan
NK107(tse)001:6019: lag bstan pa ni ston pa ni gdul bya la
NK107(tse)001:6020: dmigs pa dang rang gi yon tan la dmigs pa
NK107(tse)001:6021: gnyis so gdul bya ni nges par dam pa'i skal
NK107(tse)001:6022: ba yod pa rnams la mtshan dang dpe byad du
NK107(tse)001:6023: snang la las ma dag pa rnams la nges med
NK107(tse)001:6024: du snang ba'o yon tan la dmigs pa'i ston pa
NK107(tse)001:6025: ni sku blta bas chog mi shes pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:6026: pa'i chos stong phrag bdun gnas pas mthong na gzi
NK107(tse)001:6027: brjid 'jug cing lus bde lugs su 'byung bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:6028: ro de yang ba spu zing ba dang mchil ma
NK107(tse)001:6029: bsku ba la sogs pa la brten nas lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:6030: bde ba khyad par can skye ba yin no yang
NK107(tse)001:6031: gsung yan lag drug cu dang ldan pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:6032: te chos nyid khri phrag drug cu gnas pas thos
NK107(tse)001:6033: pa tsam gyis 'khrul gtam 'gag pa dang rab tu
NK107(tse)001:6034: spro zhing dga' ba la brten nas ngag la bde
NK107(tse)001:6035: ba'i nyams khyad par can skye ba'o yang thugs ting
NK107(tse)001:6036: nge 'dzin bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs te chos
NK107(tse)001:6037: nyid sum stong drug brgya gnas pas gang zhig bsam
NK107(tse)001:6038: pa tsam gyis rab tu gdung ba dang brtse ba
NK107(tse)001:6039: dang yid g.yo ba dang sems rnal du phebs pa
NK107(tse)001:6040: la brten nas sems la gnas pa thun mong ma
NK107(tse)001:6041: yin pa skye ba'o sangs pa ni mtha' dang bral
NK107(tse)001:6042: bas gnyis snang gi mtha' thams cad sangs la yongs
NK107(tse)001:6043: su rdzogs pas spang blang gi 'dzin pa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:6044: sangs pa'o rgyas pa ni mtha' dang bral bas stong
NK107(tse)001:6045: pa ris med du rgyas la yongs su rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:6046: thams cad mnyam pa ris med du rgyas pa'o bcom
NK107(tse)001:6047: pa ni mtha' dang bral bas gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog
NK107(tse)001:6048: pa thams cad bcom pa dang yongs su rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:6049: bzang ngan dang re dogs thams cad bcom pa'o ldan
NK107(tse)001:6050: pa ni mtha' dang bral bas mnyam nyid mu mtha'
NK107(tse)001:6051: med par ldan la yongs su rdzogs pas 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:6052: thams cad yongs su grol bar ldan pa'o 'das pa
NK107(tse)001:6053: ni mtha' dang bral bas 'khor 'das gang du yang
NK107(tse)001:6054: ma grub par 'das la yongs su rdzogs pas snod
NK107(tse)001:6055: bcud thams cad spang blang med par 'das pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:6056: la sogs pa'i yon tan barjoda kyis mi lang ba
NK107(tse)001:6057: la sogs pa ni gzhung na gsal lo gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:6058: de lta bu'i yon tan gyi rnam grangs de yang
NK107(tse)001:6059: bstan pa dngos kyi byin brlabs las byung bar bstan
NK107(tse)001:6060: pa ni de ni gang la byung zhe na zhes
NK107(tse)001:6061: pa la sogs pa gzhung na gsal lo zhus don
NK107(tse)001:6062: nyer bzhi pa la gnyis su byas nas bstan no
NK107(tse)001:6063: da ni le'u dang po'i zhus don nyer lnga pa
NK107(tse)001:6064: lus rnam par bzhag pa sku gsum gyi sna khrid
NK107(tse)001:6065: par byed pa 'byung ba'i sgra don la bslab pa
NK107(tse)001:6066: la yan lag gi don lngas bstan pa'i dang po
NK107(tse)001:6067: 'byung ba'i grangs nges pa las khyad par du chu'i
NK107(tse)001:6068: sgra don la bslab pa bstan pa ni sku ni
NK107(tse)001:6069: chos sku la ngo bo stong pa nyid mtha' dang
NK107(tse)001:6070: bral ba rang bzhin dmigs pa rnam par dag pa
NK107(tse)001:6071: thugs rje bri bskor las 'das pa zhing khams rang
NK107(tse)001:6072: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'o longs sku'i ngo bo
NK107(tse)001:6073: gsal rig rnam par rdzogs pa rang bzhin 'od dang
NK107(tse)001:6074: 'od khyim gyi dkyil 'khor las ma 'das pa thugs
NK107(tse)001:6075: rje chos nyid kyi rang sgra'i rnam pa las ma
NK107(tse)001:6076: 'das pa zhing khams ni zhing rgyan rnam par bkod
NK107(tse)001:6077: pa'o sprul sku'i ngo bo skye mched khyad par can
NK107(tse)001:6078: las grub pa dang rang bzhin ma nges pa thugs
NK107(tse)001:6079: rje phyogs med du 'char bas zhing khams sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:6080: su snang zhing 'jug pa'o de ltar gsum la bslab
NK107(tse)001:6081: pa'i rim pa nyid ni 'byung ba bzhi'i 'dod yon
NK107(tse)001:6082: rnams la gtsor byas te de ni sgra'i mtshams sbyor
NK107(tse)001:6083: nas bstan no de dag las kyang khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:6084: mchog gi dngos grub 'dod pa rnams kyis sa'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:6085: sgong gi rnam pa la bslab pa dang chu'i sgra
NK107(tse)001:6086: lung pa mthur gzugs la gshang ba'i sgra la bslab
NK107(tse)001:6087: pa dang me'i sgra tsan dan gyi me dpung la
NK107(tse)001:6088: bslab pa dang rlung gi sgra phyogs kyi skar khung
NK107(tse)001:6089: la bslab pa ni gsang ba'i yi ge dang sbyar
NK107(tse)001:6090: te sgra la bslabs pas nges par 'grub bo de'anga
NK107(tse)001:6091: 'byung ba so so'i lus dang sbyar te rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:6092: pa de chu'i lus yin na chu'i sgra ni bshang
NK107(tse)001:6093: ba la zhes pa ni lung pa kha lhor blta
NK107(tse)001:6094: ba rab tu gzugs la mthur la chu drag po
NK107(tse)001:6095: 'bab pa chu'i sgra mchog tu che bar song ste
NK107(tse)001:6096: de yang sngon du bla ma la tshogs bsag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:6097: yan lag du ma bya'o de nas mchod pa dang
NK107(tse)001:6098: bstod pa'i yan lag du ma bya'o da nas rang
NK107(tse)001:6099: gi 'tsho ba'i yo byad khyer la rlung la shis
NK107(tse)001:6100: pa'i kha zas bag tsam yang brten no de yang
NK107(tse)001:6101: rab tu gshang na las sna tshogs pa 'grub pa'o
NK107(tse)001:6102: shwa na bsil 'byin zhes pa'i sgra la mkhas par
NK107(tse)001:6103: 'gyur ro bslab pa'i thabs dngos ni gsang ba'i yi
NK107(tse)001:6104: ge snying tig tu shes par bya'o de yang thog
NK107(tse)001:6105: ma zla ba ga cig tshun chad du chu sna
NK107(tse)001:6106: tshogs pa'i sgra 'byung zhing khams kyang 'khrug par snang
NK107(tse)001:6107: ngo de nas tshangs pa'i skad kyi gdangs g+ha tsam
NK107(tse)001:6108: snang ngo de nas 'dre'i skad lce dang mchus ma
NK107(tse)001:6109: bsgyur pa dag snang ngo de nas nam mkha' lding
NK107(tse)001:6110: gi skad ka hring zhes pa skabs su snang ngo
NK107(tse)001:6111: de nas brgya byin gyi skad pra ti breng zhes
NK107(tse)001:6112: pa drag par 'gyur ro de ltar zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:6113: 'das nas rigs drug phal pa'i skad di ri ri
NK107(tse)001:6114: drag pa dag 'byung ngo de nas zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:6115: na ka la ping ka'i sgra rab tu dbyangs kyis
NK107(tse)001:6116: snyan pa dag 'byung ngo de nas zla ba phyed
NK107(tse)001:6117: na mkha' 'gro ma'i sgra ni sngon du b+hud d+ha
NK107(tse)001:6118: dak+ki ni d+harma ka su zhes rab tu ring bar
NK107(tse)001:6119: grags so de nas de nyid kyi dbyangs rab tu
NK107(tse)001:6120: gdung ba dang bsing ba dang 'phra zhing gdangs pa
NK107(tse)001:6121: thos pas lus kyang 'dar zhing ring pas myos pa'i
NK107(tse)001:6122: nyams 'byung ngo de nas rab reg 'joms kyi myong
NK107(tse)001:6123: ba dag la spyod do de nas yang badz+ra d+aak+ki
NK107(tse)001:6124: ni nga du pu ka ho zhes pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:6125: lus kyi reg shes la brten nas khyad par gyi
NK107(tse)001:6126: snang ba dag kyang mthong ngo de nas yang rat+na
NK107(tse)001:6127: d+aak+ki ni ma h+aa d+ha ra ho zhes pa thos
NK107(tse)001:6128: pa tsam gyis ngag gi bde ba nyams su myong
NK107(tse)001:6129: ba dang 'khrul snang gtan la phebs par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:6130: de nas pad+ma d+aa k+ki ni dz+ny+aa na d+harma su
NK107(tse)001:6131: ka d+ha ra zhes pa thos pa tsam gyis sems
NK107(tse)001:6132: kyi rangs pa rab tu dga' bde'i rnam pa la
NK107(tse)001:6133: spyod cing rang bzhin snang ba'i don rnams gtan la
NK107(tse)001:6134: phebs pa'o de nas yang kar+m+aa ma h+aa d+aak+ki ad
