NK107(tse)001:7378: de ltar yang bshad pa'i rgyud las dgos pa dgu
NK107(tse)001:7379: dang bcas pa'o ces gsungs so de nas rnal 'bebs
NK107(tse)001:7380: pa zhag gsum du byas te lus rnal 'beb sems
NK107(tse)001:7381: sor chud par byeed pa ni mal du nyal la
NK107(tse)001:7382: lus kyi yan lag la sogs pa mgul gcig kyang
NK107(tse)001:7383: mi byed par 'gro ba dang 'dug pa'i rnam pa
NK107(tse)001:7384: gang yang mi bya ba gnas pa zhag gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:7385: byas pas lus nyams su len pa la 'grus pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7386: dgos pa yod do de nas zhag gcig tu 'bugs
NK107(tse)001:7387: tsam gcig mi smra ba la zhag du byas pas
NK107(tse)001:7388: ngag nyams len la 'grus par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:7389: yod do de nas sems rnal du dbab pa ni
NK107(tse)001:7390: sems kyi 'phro 'du gcad la 'du shes gcad par
NK107(tse)001:7391: bya'o de ltar zhag gcig tu byas pas sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:7392: nyams len la 'grub par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod
NK107(tse)001:7393: do de ltar sngon du 'gro ba la zhag bco
NK107(tse)001:7394: lnga la thang gcad nas byas pas lus ngag gi
NK107(tse)001:7395: gnad khyad par can skye ba'o rnal 'bebs ni 'og
NK107(tse)001:7396: nas kha bskang ngo de yang dkyus dang sbyar na
NK107(tse)001:7397: ngag ni gang la byung ba'i tshig don la blta
NK107(tse)001:7398: ba'o h+aum ni dbyangs dang bcas ste rlung dang bsre
NK107(tse)001:7399: ba ni gnad do zhes de ltar byas pa la
NK107(tse)001:7400: sems gnas pa dag kyang 'byung ngo 'di'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:7401: dngos gzhi nyams su myong ba dag skye ba dag
NK107(tse)001:7402: yin no rgyas ni phyi snang ba dang nang phung
NK107(tse)001:7403: po gnyis mi 'gyur bar gdab pa dang chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:7404: las 'das pa med pa'i gnad do btsal ni phyi
NK107(tse)001:7405: snang ba dang nang phung po nyid la sbyangs pas
NK107(tse)001:7406: de nyid zang thal du 'gro ba'i dgos pa yod
NK107(tse)001:7407: do gnyan pa rlung btsal rig pa rlung rig gnyis
NK107(tse)001:7408: su med pa ste lam ni sngon du 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:7409: bzhugs pa yis ni phyir mi ldog par byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7410: thabs so de ltar sbyangs pas sems gnas lugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:7411: steng du 'gro ba la phan no sems ni sems
NK107(tse)001:7412: kyi ngo bo dang nges tshig la sogs pa rgyas
NK107(tse)001:7413: par gzhan du shes par bya'o de ltar sems sbyangs
NK107(tse)001:7414: pas rang gi sems kyi gnas lugs shes par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:7415: ba'i dgos pa'o tshig ni gzhung gis shes pa'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:7416: gnyis pa lus ngag yid kyi sngon du 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:7417: sems kyi sna khrid pa dngos bstan nas da ni
NK107(tse)001:7418: dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyis don
NK107(tse)001:7419: rnal 'byor pa'i rgyud la brten pa ni de la
NK107(tse)001:7420: lus ngag yid kyi gnad gzir ba dang gnad rnam
NK107(tse)001:7421: pa gsum la brten nas mngon gsum rang thog tu
NK107(tse)001:7422: dbab pa la sogs pa ni 'og nas ston pa
NK107(tse)001:7423: dang 'di gnyis dang sbyar ro de la dang po
NK107(tse)001:7424: ni 'dra min dang mi 'dra ba med pa la
NK107(tse)001:7425: byas la gzhi ni ma bcos pa'am mi 'gyur ba'i
NK107(tse)001:7426: cha nas bzhag go rang gi ni gzhan rnam par
NK107(tse)001:7427: gcod rang stobs las 'grub ces pa'o rgyud ni rang
NK107(tse)001:7428: shes rig gi rgyal po 'dus ma byas pa chos
NK107(tse)001:7429: nyid kun tu bzang po thams cad kyi ngo bor
NK107(tse)001:7430: shar ba nyid do brten ni rgyun du goms par
NK107(tse)001:7431: byed pa'o lus kyi gnad dang ni bzhugs stangs gsum
NK107(tse)001:7432: las mi 'da' bar dus rgyun du bya'o ngag dang
NK107(tse)001:7433: yang ni smra ba gcad pas barjoda pa'i tshig gi
NK107(tse)001:7434: gzhi stongs pa'o sems kyi gnad la brten pa yis
NK107(tse)001:7435: ni dus thams cad du gtad pa'i 'ben dang mi
NK107(tse)001:7436: 'bral bar bya'o rlung rig gi gnad ni rlung ci
NK107(tse)001:7437: nas kyang dal bar byas te phyir rab tu 'phangs
NK107(tse)001:7438: pa las ye shes 'byung ba ni 'khor 'das lus
NK107(tse)001:7439: kyi rnam pa las grol te lus dang sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:7440: 'brel chad de rgyu 'bras kyi 'ching byed gnyis las
NK107(tse)001:7441: grol bas khams gsum 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs
NK107(tse)001:7442: med pa gsum du'anga skal ldan 'di ldog pa min
NK107(tse)001:7443: no zhes zhus don nyer dgu pa sems kyi sna
NK107(tse)001:7444: khrid par byed pa'i sngon 'gro la brten nas rang
NK107(tse)001:7445: gi sems 'dul bar byed pa la yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:7446: don gsum du byas nas bstan nas da ni le'u
NK107(tse)001:7447: dang po'i zhus don sum cu pa rlung gi dgos
NK107(tse)001:7448: pa dang bcas pa bstan pa la yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:7449: don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po 'jig rten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7450: dgos pa bstan pa ni rlung gi dgos pa rnam
NK107(tse)001:7451: pa gnyis la sogs pa gzhung gis shes so gnyis
NK107(tse)001:7452: pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i dgos pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:7453: ni 'das pa'i sku dang la sogs pa gzhung gis
NK107(tse)001:7454: shes so zhus don sum cu pa la gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:7455: byas nas bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i zhus
NK107(tse)001:7456: don sum cu so gcig pa rtsa'i gnad dang rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7457: la brten pa'i 'gyu ba dang bcas pa'i rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:7458: grangs tshad bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis
NK107(tse)001:7459: kyis bstan te rtsa gnad rin po che la brten
NK107(tse)001:7460: nas btsan thabs su sangs rgyas pa'i gnad bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:7461: dang de ltar rtsa la brten pa'i rlung gis grangs
NK107(tse)001:7462: tshad kyis rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par gyis las bstan
NK107(tse)001:7463: pa'o de la rtsa gnad rin po che la brten
NK107(tse)001:7464: nas btsan thabs su sangs rgyas pa bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:7465: nyid don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po lus gnad
NK107(tse)001:7466: rtsa'i chos bstan pa ni lus kyi gnad ni rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7467: yin te zhes te de la rtsa'i chos gnad du
NK107(tse)001:7468: phab nas bstan na bco lnga ste rtsa'i gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:7469: bstan pa dang bkod pa dang 'gyu ba dang lus
NK107(tse)001:7470: kyi 'khor lo bzhin ji ltar gnas pa dang de
NK107(tse)001:7471: dag la brten pa'i thig le'i 'phel 'grib dang rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7472: de dag gis lus kyi srog ji ltar gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:7473: dang rtsa'i ming gi rnam grangs dang rtsa de dag
NK107(tse)001:7474: gi bye brag ji ltar 'gyur ba dang de rgyu
NK107(tse)001:7475: gang las bskyed pa dang rkyen gyis ji ltar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:7476: ba dang byed pa'i las kyis gang dang gang byed
NK107(tse)001:7477: pa dang rtsa'i mtshan nyid ji ltar yin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7478: de las nyon mongs pa 'gyu ba ngos bzung ba
NK107(tse)001:7479: dang las kyi mtha' ji ltar 'gyur zhing ye shes
NK107(tse)001:7480: 'gyu ba'i rnam grangs ngos bzung ba dang dmigs pa
NK107(tse)001:7481: las kyi khyad par la brten nas 'khor 'das kyi
NK107(tse)001:7482: chos bstan pa dang bco lnga pa'i chos bstan pa'o
NK107(tse)001:7483: de la dang po rtsa'i gnas pa ni spyir lus
NK107(tse)001:7484: la rtsa brten pas gzhi lus yin la de la
NK107(tse)001:7485: lus chags pa'i dus na 'phra 'gyur gyi rtsar gnas
NK107(tse)001:7486: pas lus dang shes pa ma rgyas pa'i gnad ni
NK107(tse)001:7487: de las ma'i mngal du lus su 'grub pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7488: na rkyang ma'i rtsar gnas pas 'gul zhing 'phrig pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7489: gnad de las byung de nas lus su mngal nas
NK107(tse)001:7490: thon pa'i dus na rlung dang shes pa 'dres pas
NK107(tse)001:7491: lus ngag yid kyi rtag pa dngos su byung ste
NK107(tse)001:7492: de yang lus dngos su byung bas dri chen dang
NK107(tse)001:7493: dri chu dor ba'i las de las byung ngag gi
NK107(tse)001:7494: a ham la sogs pa'i sgra dngos su byung ba
NK107(tse)001:7495: dang yid kyi bya ba rlung dngos su 'gyu ba
NK107(tse)001:7496: dang bcas pa dngos su byung ba'o de yang lus
NK107(tse)001:7497: kyi gnad ni rtsa yin te de yang dang po
NK107(tse)001:7498: lus chags pa'i dus na rtsa'i sa bon thams cad
NK107(tse)001:7499: me tog un d+ha'i rnam pa ltar gnas las shes
NK107(tse)001:7500: pa nang du 'khyims pa de'i gnad yin 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7501: na ma'i ltag pa'i bdud sgor bcod kyi me btsa'
NK107(tse)001:7502: ja ma tsam bsregs na shes rab rgyas par nges
NK107(tse)001:7503: so de yang ma'i mngal nas thog ma rtsa 'phra
NK107(tse)001:7504: bas rtsa nang gi rlung 'phra bas 'gul bskyod pa
NK107(tse)001:7505: de'i gnad la de nas bdun tshan brgyad rdzogs nas
NK107(tse)001:7506: rtsa de bas bag tsam sbom du song bas lte
NK107(tse)001:7507: ba'i rlung gis g.yo ba byung de'i rtags su ma'i
NK107(tse)001:7508: lus la 'dar ba'am grang shum khyer bas byung 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:7509: dus na mas bsreg pa'i sha zos na shes pa
NK107(tse)001:7510: rab tu gsal bar 'gyur ro de nas de tsam
NK107(tse)001:7511: zhig na rtsa snga ma bas log 'gyur gyis rags
NK107(tse)001:7512: su song bas snying khar dran pa 'dus shing 'phros
NK107(tse)001:7513: pas lus 'gul zhing 'phrig pa'i las 'byung ngo 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:7514: dus na ma rta rkyang gi sha zos na klan
NK107(tse)001:7515: cing lkug par smin par 'gyur bas srung par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:7516: de'i phyir na lus la rtsa brten yang lus gnad
NK107(tse)001:7517: rtsa la rtsa la rlung brten yang rlung gnad rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7518: rlung la sems brten yang rlung gnad sems zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:7519: 'di'i gnad kyis lus chags pa yang rtsa la brten
NK107(tse)001:7520: nas chags la bskyed pa yang rtsa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:7521: bskyed la gnas pa yang rtsa la brten nas gnas
NK107(tse)001:7522: pas tha ma 'jig pa yang rtsa'i las bral nas
NK107(tse)001:7523: 'jig pas na 'gro ba'i tshe na yang dbang dang
NK107(tse)001:7524: nad dang las kyi bye brag rnams rtsa la brten
NK107(tse)001:7525: nas 'gyu ba gnad de la brten nas 'byung ste
NK107(tse)001:7526: de'i phyir na reg pa rtsa'i rtsis shes na nad
NK107(tse)001:7527: la sogs pa'i bye brag dang gdon dang tshe la
NK107(tse)001:7528: sogs pa'i dus shes pa'i gnad de las byung ngo
NK107(tse)001:7529: de la rtsa'i gnas pa ni khyad par du gnas
NK107(tse)001:7530: pa dang thun mong du gnas pa gnyis te lus
NK107(tse)001:7531: spyi la gnas pa dang lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi
NK107(tse)001:7532: la gnas pa ste rtsa rtsa gnas kyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:7533: che chung na zhib par ston pas 'dir ma bris
NK107(tse)001:7534: so khyad par du gnas pa ni 'khor ba'i rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7535: rten 'brel bcu gnyis las 'khrul pas lus mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7536: ba bcu gnyis su byung yang rtsa'i gnas pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:7537: las mi 'da' ba ni rten 'brel gyi thog ma
NK107(tse)001:7538: ma rig pa la thug pa'i gnad dang ma rig
NK107(tse)001:7539: pa las gti mug lus kyi gzhi 'dzin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7540: 'dod chags ngag gi gzhi 'dzin pa dang zhe sdang
NK107(tse)001:7541: sems kyi gzhi 'dzin pa'i gnad las lus lte ba
NK107(tse)001:7542: nas bskyed pa'i gnas kyis lte ba na ro ma
NK107(tse)001:7543: gnas te de nyid las phung po lnga'i so so'i
NK107(tse)001:7544: byed pa'i las dang khams dang skye mched dang dbang
NK107(tse)001:7545: po dang yul gyi las so sor smin pa de
NK107(tse)001:7546: las byung la snying ga nas sems dran pa la
NK107(tse)001:7547: brten nas sems gnas pa'i gnad kyis kun d+ha rma
NK107(tse)001:7548: gnas te de nyid kyi bde sdug dga' dang btang
NK107(tse)001:7549: snyoms kyi bye brag sna tshogs su ston pa de
NK107(tse)001:7550: las byung ngag mgrin pa nas bskyed pa'i gnad kyis
NK107(tse)001:7551: mgrin pa na rkyang ma gnas te de nyid kyi
NK107(tse)001:7552: barjoda gzhi dang barjoda bya dang tshig dang yi ge
NK107(tse)001:7553: las thams cad kyi gzhi de las 'byung ngo de
NK107(tse)001:7554: yang lus ngag yid kyi las spyi bo nas ston
NK107(tse)001:7555: pas spyi bo na shel sbug ma 'khor ba'i tshul
NK107(tse)001:7556: du gnas pas snang ba dang shes pa'i rtsal sna
NK107(tse)001:7557: tshogs su ston pa de las 'byung ngo de ltar
NK107(tse)001:7558: byas pas lus ngag yid kyi gzhi byas pas gnad
NK107(tse)001:7559: dang ces pa'o gnyis pa rtsa de dag gi bkod
NK107(tse)001:7560: pa ni bskyed byed dang po la bkod pas lus
NK107(tse)001:7561: kyi smad kyi 'gyur ston la dran pa 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:7562: na bkod pas lus kyi bar gyi 'gyur ston pa
NK107(tse)001:7563: ro rnams 'dus pas na bkod pas lus kyi stod
NK107(tse)001:7564: kyi 'gyur ston la rtse mo rnam par bkod pa
NK107(tse)001:7565: na bkod pas lus spyi'i 'gyur ston te de yang
NK107(tse)001:7566: bkod lugs ni bskyed byed na 'phra zhing 'gyur bar
NK107(tse)001:7567: bkod pas so so'i gnas su thang gcad de sbra'i
NK107(tse)001:7568: chon thag brgyangs pa ltar gnas pas lus kyi 'brel
NK107(tse)001:7569: pa nye bar ston mi nus dran pa na rags
NK107(tse)001:7570: shing rgal bar bkod pas lus kyi mtshan nyid nye
NK107(tse)001:7571: bar rtogs pa'i khyad par ston par byed ro rnams
NK107(tse)001:7572: na lug cing 'khril ba'i tshul du bkod pas rlung
NK107(tse)001:7573: mkhris bad kan gyi 'gyur byed du byed rtse mo
NK107(tse)001:7574: na gdang zhing gsal bar bkod pas dbang po yul
NK107(tse)001:7575: gyi 'gyur ston pa'o bkod pa zhes pas so gsum
NK107(tse)001:7576: pa rtsa'i 'gyu ba ni rang bzhin du 'gyu ba
NK107(tse)001:7577: dang nad kyi rkyen gyis nas 'gyu ba dang gdon
NK107(tse)001:7578: gyis rkyen nas 'gyu ba dang gsum mo rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:7579: du 'gyu ba ni bdag gi lus la nad dam
NK107(tse)001:7580: pos ma zin na na tshod dar la bab pa
NK107(tse)001:7581: dang nad pa yang de dang 'dra ba cig gi
NK107(tse)001:7582: dbang du brtsis pa ste rlung chen po cig la
NK107(tse)001:7583: rtsa'i 'gyu ba gsum gsum du 'gyu ba ni dang
NK107(tse)001:7584: po lus kyi mtshan nyid ston la gnyis pas ngag
NK107(tse)001:7585: gi gsum pas yid kyi mtshan nyid ston par byed
NK107(tse)001:7586: pa'o de'i gnad kyis sor mo ste dang po mtshon
NK107(tse)001:7587: zhes byas te lus chags pa dang gnas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7588: 'jig pa'i bye brag la dbang gnyis pa chags zhes
NK107(tse)001:7589: ngag gi barjoda bya'i gnas dang rgyu dang rkyen la
NK107(tse)001:7590: dbang gsum pa skan zhes yid kyi las dang bag
NK107(tse)001:7591: chags dang 'brel so la dbang de yang mtshon gyis
NK107(tse)001:7592: 'og gis lus kyi spyod pa drag pa dang zhan
NK107(tse)001:7593: pa dang zas dang 'gro 'dug pha rol rkyen las
NK107(tse)001:7594: nad dang gdon gyi bye brag brtag par bya'o chag
NK107(tse)001:7595: gi 'og tu ngag gi barjoda pa drag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7596: zhan pa la sogs pas las nad dang gdon gyi
NK107(tse)001:7597: bye brag bzhugs pa brtag skan gyi 'og tu sems
NK107(tse)001:7598: kyi mya ngan sdug basngala la sogs pa 'gyur zhing
NK107(tse)001:7599: 'khrugs pa las nad dang gdon du gyur pa'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:7600: nyid brtag par bya'o de yang rang dang pha rol
NK107(tse)001:7601: gyi na tshod brtsi ba gal che'o de ltar 'gyu
NK107(tse)001:7602: ba las lhag pa dang chad pa dang 'khrugs pa
NK107(tse)001:7603: rnams ni nad dang gdon du shes par bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:7604: la nad kyis 'gyu ba ni sor mo dang po
NK107(tse)001:7605: las bad kan gyi nad du ngos bzung gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:7606: las mkhris pa ngos bzung gsum pa las rlung du
NK107(tse)001:7607: shes par bya'o de dag gsum 'khrugs shing rgal ba
NK107(tse)001:7608: las 'dus bar shes par bya ste de yang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:7609: dang gsum 'khrugs pa'i mtshan nyid shes par bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:7610: ltar gsum rim gyis tsha na tsha ba reg pa
NK107(tse)001:7611: grang na grang ba de yang drag pa tsha la
NK107(tse)001:7612: 'phra zhing zhan pa grang de ltar sor mo gsum
NK107(tse)001:7613: gyis bltas la gzhan gyis mi blta ba ni rigs
NK107(tse)001:7614: gsum la dgongs la pho rtsa drag cing thung la
NK107(tse)001:7615: mo rtsa 'phra zhing rgal ba dang byang chub sems
NK107(tse)001:7616: dapa'i rtsa dal zhing rgyud ring pa'o des na rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7617: nad gsum dang lus ngag yid dang thams cad gsum
NK107(tse)001:7618: tshan la dgongs pa'o de yang de dag spyir lhag
NK107(tse)001:7619: pa dang chad pa dang sdod pa dang gsum gyis
NK107(tse)001:7620: rtsa'i gnas 'gyur ba ni 'byung ba byer zug snyoms
NK107(tse)001:7621: pa gsum gyis yang 'gyur ba las byung ba ste
NK107(tse)001:7622: de dag las na ba dang gdon dang rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:7623: 'khrugs pas gsum du shes par bya'o de yang lhag
NK107(tse)001:7624: pa ni spyir bdag gi rlung bdun la nyer gcig
NK107(tse)001:7625: tu shes par byas te de yang gsum lhag na
NK107(tse)001:7626: nad yun thung ste zhag gsum na ci yang bya
NK107(tse)001:7627: mi dgos par 'gro la gzhi gdon yin pas gdon
NK107(tse)001:7628: gyi cho ga bya lnga lhag na nad yun ring
NK107(tse)001:7629: par sbyong bas sman chos dang rten 'brel gyi sbyong
NK107(tse)001:7630: ba la 'bad de bas na mang pa rnams ni
NK107(tse)001:7631: phal cher du tshe'i dus byed do chad pa yang
NK107(tse)001:7632: de'i 'dres kyis shes par bya'o stod pa ni gcig
NK107(tse)001:7633: 'phar nas gnyis par la bstod pa ni nad yin
NK107(tse)001:7634: pas gsum pa gang byung ba ngos bzung la rten
NK107(tse)001:7635: 'brel dang sman chos bya'o gnyis 'phar nas gcig stod
NK107(tse)001:7636: pa gdon du shes par bya'o de nas mang ba
NK107(tse)001:7637: ni phal cher tshe'i dus byed par shes par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:7638: de yang 'phar gyi khyad par gyis nad pa yin
NK107(tse)001:7639: na zhag de'i grangs dang mnyam par dus byed do
NK107(tse)001:7640: gdon gyis 'phar ba ni sor mo dang po la
NK107(tse)001:7641: pho gdon brtag gnyis pa la mo gdon gsum pa
NK107(tse)001:7642: la gshin rje de yang sor mo dang po la
NK107(tse)001:7643: bdud gnyis pa la btsan gsum pa la rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:7644: klu dang sa bdag de yang bdud myur la btsan
NK107(tse)001:7645: drag rgyal po rgal klu 'thib cing 'gum gshin rje
NK107(tse)001:7646: 'dar zhing 'phra brten pa'i lha ma dga' na 'phir
NK107(tse)001:7647: la thang dam tshig nyams na 'gyur zhing mtha' thung
NK107(tse)001:7648: de'i pho gdon gyis zin pa 'phir pa drag mo
NK107(tse)001:7649: 'khun cing sdigs pa'o de dag rnams ni gdon yin
NK107(tse)001:7650: par shes par bya'o spyir rtsa la 'gyu ba la
NK107(tse)001:7651: na bar 'gyur ba dang 'chi bar 'gyur ba dang
NK107(tse)001:7652: ma bcos kyang 'tsho la bcos na ni 'tsho la
NK107(tse)001:7653: ma bcos na 'chi ba rnams su shes par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:7654: yang 'gro ba mi'i bsod nams dang tshe ring thung
NK107(tse)001:7655: dang stobs drag zhan dang dpal che chung la sogs
NK107(tse)001:7656: pa yang rtsa'i gnad la brten nas shes par bya
NK107(tse)001:7657: ba dang de'i 'gyu ba 'dra bzhi la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:7658: gtan la dbab pa ni gzhu'i rgyud ltar thang chad
NK107(tse)001:7659: na bad kan gyi nad du shes par bya'o khang
NK107(tse)001:7660: rul gyi thig pa 'dra na mkhris pa bye'u chags
NK107(tse)001:7661: sar btsir ba 'dra na rlung ngo 'dus pa yang
NK107(tse)001:7662: de dag gi ngos nas shes par bya'o yang dar
NK107(tse)001:7663: po che rlung gis bskyod pa 'dra na bsod nams
NK107(tse)001:7664: che la yon tan lobs thig gu bsgril ba 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7665: na stobs che rta rnga'i nyag 'dra na skyid sdug
NK107(tse)001:7666: bar skabs can du 'ong pad+ma kha bye ba 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7667: na dpal che dar gyi bsnal ma la reg pa
NK107(tse)001:7668: 'dra na tshe ring nyungs 'bru'i rdog ma 'dril ba
NK107(tse)001:7669: 'dra na tshe thung spang la me shor ba 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7670: na nor dang dbang thang rgyas chu'i sbu ba ltar
NK107(tse)001:7671: mthol na zla ba phyed na 'chi sran ma'i rdog
NK107(tse)001:7672: ma 'dril ba 'dra na zla ba gcig na 'chi
NK107(tse)001:7673: nyag thag brkyang pa 'dra na lo gcig na'o lcags
NK107(tse)001:7674: kyu ltar khugs pa yod na na ba yun ring
NK107(tse)001:7675: grogs ma'i lus ltar dga' ma nyag tu 'gyu na
NK107(tse)001:7676: 'tsho dka' dru gu gzhung ba ltar yar 'gro mar
NK107(tse)001:7677: 'gro byed na mtsho bsla barlangasa pa ltar 'phyur na
NK107(tse)001:7678: gdon drag po yin par shes par bya'o yang rtsa'i
NK107(tse)001:7679: 'gyu ba'i 'gyur la brten nas mtho ris dang ngan
NK107(tse)001:7680: song du la sogs te skye gnas gang du skyes
NK107(tse)001:7681: pa brtags pa ni yang rtsa'i phyir zhing 'khyug na
NK107(tse)001:7682: lha'i skye ba len thur zhing spir na lha ma
NK107(tse)001:7683: yin dal zhing 'dar na mi 'khun zhing yed na
NK107(tse)001:7684: byol song 'phra zhing grib na yi dwags 'dar zhing
NK107(tse)001:7685: yed na dmyal ba'i skye gnas su skye ba ste
NK107(tse)001:7686: 'di dag ni dus bstan pa la dgongs pa'o yang
NK107(tse)001:7687: 'gyu ba chung ba'i rlung la mthun pa dang mi
NK107(tse)001:7688: mthun pa dang skyid sdug dus kyi bye brag nges
NK107(tse)001:7689: par bstan pa yod de 'dir ma spros so bzhi
NK107(tse)001:7690: pa lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi na ji ltar gnas
NK107(tse)001:7691: pa ni bskyed byed dang po'i 'khor lo na rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7692: 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi gnas te de ni srid
NK107(tse)001:7693: pa las kyi 'gyur byed drug cu rtsa bzhi'i rnam
NK107(tse)001:7694: pa ston pa'i rtags so dran pa 'dus pa na
NK107(tse)001:7695: bcu drug tu gnas pa ni 'byung ba'i byed las
NK107(tse)001:7696: la bcu drug tu ston pa'o ro rnams na brgyad
NK107(tse)001:7697: du gnas pa ni rnam pa shes pa'i tshogs brgyad
NK107(tse)001:7698: kyi brten byed rtse mo na sum brgya dang drug
NK107(tse)001:7699: cu gnas pa ni sgo lnga'i yul gyi rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:7700: mi 'dra ba de tsam la 'jug par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:7701: spyir lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi na rtsa'i las byed
NK107(tse)001:7702: pa'i rtsa bzhi brgya dang bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad du
NK107(tse)001:7703: gnas pa ni lus kyi tshe dang dbang thang dang
NK107(tse)001:7704: nad dang las kyi bye brag sna tshogs par byed
NK107(tse)001:7705: pa'o lnga pa rtsa de dag la brten pa'i thig
NK107(tse)001:7706: le'i 'phel 'grib bstan pa ni de yang rtsa rnams
NK107(tse)001:7707: kyi nang na rgyu rkyen gyi thig le dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:7708: sems kyi thig le gnyis kyis don dam pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7709: kun rdzob kyi snang ba ston par byed la de
NK107(tse)001:7710: yang rlung sems kyi thig les mya ngan las 'das
NK107(tse)001:7711: pa'i rgyu 'bras dang mtshan nyid du byed la rgyu
NK107(tse)001:7712: rkyen gyis 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras dang mtshan nyid du
NK107(tse)001:7713: byed pa'o 'khor ba'i 'phel 'grib tu byed pa ni
NK107(tse)001:7714: rgyu'i thig le dmar po nyungs 'bru'i sum cha tsam
NK107(tse)001:7715: yang lus kyi dus na sha dang khrag dang drod
NK107(tse)001:7716: du smin par byed la rkyen pha'i thig le dkar
NK107(tse)001:7717: po nyungs 'bru tsam las lus kyi dus na rus
NK107(tse)001:7718: pa dang chu rgyus dang lha rkang dang bkrag dang
NK107(tse)001:7719: gzi mdangs la sogs pa smin par byed do sems
NK107(tse)001:7720: kyi thig le sna tshogs 'od kyi dngas ma sran
NK107(tse)001:7721: ma'i ga'u kha sbyar ba tsam las sku dang ye
NK107(tse)001:7722: shes kyi rtsal sbyong bar byed rlung gi thig le
NK107(tse)001:7723: ljang khu b+ha sing ge 'brus tsam las shes rab
NK107(tse)001:7724: dang blo dang shes pa'i rtsal sbyong bar byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:7725: de yang so so'i dus na rgyu rkyen 'dus pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7726: thig le dkar dmar phyed ma las sra ba sa'i
NK107(tse)001:7727: mtshan nyid du byed pa dang gsher ba chu'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:7728: nyid du byed pa ni ma'i rgyu las gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:7729: 'dus par song de dag smin pa las sra ba
NK107(tse)001:7730: sa'i 'phrang las phor smin pas dbang po la 'khrang
NK107(tse)001:7731: ba'i stobs yod pa'i gnad de las byung gsher ba
NK107(tse)001:7732: chu'i bsdud las su dmar po smin pa de dod
NK107(tse)001:7733: pa g.yos pa'i dus na chu 'dzag pa'i gnad de
NK107(tse)001:7734: las byung yang tsha ba me'i mtshan nyid du byed
NK107(tse)001:7735: pa dang yang ba rlung gi mtshan nyid du byed
NK107(tse)001:7736: pas pha ma'i rgyu rkyen gnyis 'dus par song de
NK107(tse)001:7737: smin pa las tsha ba me'i smin pas tsha ba'i
NK107(tse)001:7738: nad du byung bas lus kyi 'tsho ba dang 'chi
NK107(tse)001:7739: ba'i gnad de las byung yang pa rlung gis bskyod
NK107(tse)001:7740: pas grangs ba'i nad du byung bas lus 'gro 'dug
NK107(tse)001:7741: bskyed pa'i gnad de las byung de ltar rgyu rkyen
NK107(tse)001:7742: gnyis las kun rdzob kyi 'byung bar smin pa ni
NK107(tse)001:7743: sa las sha 'phel chu las khrag tu 'phel me
NK107(tse)001:7744: las drod du 'phel rlung las sbugs su 'phel bas
NK107(tse)001:7745: lus su chags pa dang gnas pa dang bskyed pa
NK107(tse)001:7746: dang 'jigs pa rnams su byung ba'o rlung sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:7747: thig le las rgyu'i dus na sku dang ye shes
NK107(tse)001:7748: dang thabs dang shes rab tu byung la rkyen gyi
NK107(tse)001:7749: dus na 'od dang kha dog dang dbyibs dang rig
NK107(tse)001:7750: pa bzhir byung la 'bras bu'i dus na shes rab
NK107(tse)001:7751: rang byung gi sgron ma dang thig le stong pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7752: sgron ma dang dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma
NK107(tse)001:7753: dang rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma dang bzhir byung ba'o
NK107(tse)001:7754: mthar phyin pa'i dus na chos sku longs sku sprul
NK107(tse)001:7755: sku ngo bo nyid kyi dang rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7756: dang bzhir byung pas na lus kyi dus na 'khor
NK107(tse)001:7757: lo bzhi'i gtan tshigs de las byung ba'o thig le
NK107(tse)001:7758: de dag gzhi 'od kyi gong bu gcig gis 'thums
NK107(tse)001:7759: te lus chags pa'i dus na bskyed byed dang po
NK107(tse)001:7760: na gnas pas rnam par rtog pa du ma'i gzhi
NK107(tse)001:7761: de las byung lus bskyed pa'i dus na dran pa
NK107(tse)001:7762: 'dus pa na gnas pas dran bsam gyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:7763: sna tshogs su bsdud pa de las byung lus gnas
NK107(tse)001:7764: pa'i dus na ro rnams na gnas pas brda' dang
NK107(tse)001:7765: skad dang smra byed kyi gzhi thams cad de las
NK107(tse)001:7766: byung lus 'jig pa'i dus na rtse mo na gzhi
NK107(tse)001:7767: cher gnas pas sgo lnga'i yul la 'jug pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:7768: tha dad pa de las byung ba'o de yang thig
NK107(tse)001:7769: le de dag gi yar 'phel ba dang mar 'grib
NK107(tse)001:7770: pa'i dus ni lo gcig dang zla ba dang zhag
NK107(tse)001:7771: gi bye brag dus nges pa'i bye brag rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:7772: pa'i dge sbyor gyi bya lugs dang lus kyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:7773: ba'i dar gud dang tshe la sogs pa'i nyams pa
NK107(tse)001:7774: dang 'phel ba dang zad pa la sogs pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7775: nges par shes so de yang lo gcig la zla
NK107(tse)001:7776: ba dang po nas bzung pa'i rgun gyi mnyam dus
NK107(tse)001:7777: la thug pa las kun rdzob kyi thig le 'phel
NK107(tse)001:7778: bas mnyam pa'i nyi ma la dge sbyor ci byas
NK107(tse)001:7779: pa 'grub bo de nas yang zla ba'i rim pas
NK107(tse)001:7780: mar 'grib pa ste yang mar gyi nam nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:7781: mnyam pa'i nyi ma la las dang bag chags kyi
NK107(tse)001:7782: mtha' stongs pa zhes bya ste lhag par stong nyid
NK107(tse)001:7783: bsgoms par bzang ngo zla ba la yar 'phel mar
NK107(tse)001:7784: 'grib tu byed pa ni zla ba gcig gi tshes
NK107(tse)001:7785: gcig nas rkang mthil nas tshes bzhi la lte bar
NK107(tse)001:7786: 'phel bas 'di'i dus na srid pa'i gzhi chags par
NK107(tse)001:7787: byed pa ste 'di'i dus na na na 'tsho dka'
NK107(tse)001:7788: skyes na tshe ring shi na srid pa'i las dag
NK107(tse)001:7789: pas mtho ris su 'gro 'di'i dus na rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:7790: pas lus kyi dge sbyor ci byas brgya stong du
NK107(tse)001:7791: 'phel de nas brgyad na snying khar 'phel bas dran
NK107(tse)001:7792: gzhi snyeng pa'i dus te skyes na rtag tu sems
NK107(tse)001:7793: sdug na na 'tsho ba sla shi na ngan song
NK107(tse)001:7794: du 'gro sems gtso bo'i dge sbyor byas na brgya
NK107(tse)001:7795: stong du 'gro de nas tshes bcu gnyis la mgrin
NK107(tse)001:7796: par smra byed tshig gi mtsho rdol te 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7797: ni ngag gi dge sbyor ci byas pa brgya stong
NK107(tse)001:7798: du 'phel lo na na lo nang du 'gro skyes
NK107(tse)001:7799: na longs spyod che shi na yi dwags su skye
NK107(tse)001:7800: 'di'i dus na ngag gtso ba'i dge sbyor byas na
NK107(tse)001:7801: nges par brgya stong du 'phel lo de ltar yar
NK107(tse)001:7802: 'phel ba'i grangs nya'i nyi ma la rdzogs pas 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:7803: dus na phung po dang khams dang byang sems zla
NK107(tse)001:7804: ba nya gang ba'i rnam pa ltar spyi gtsug tu
NK107(tse)001:7805: rgyas pas rnal 'byor pa nyams kyi 'phel rdzogs pas
NK107(tse)001:7806: na na 'chi skyes na longs spyod che shi na
NK107(tse)001:7807: lha'i gnas su skye'o lus ngag gi dge sbyor ci
NK107(tse)001:7808: byas tshad 'bum phrag tu 'phel spyi bo gcig tu
NK107(tse)001:7809: skra theb gang ba gcig gzhar nas dza ti dang
NK107(tse)001:7810: gla rtsi dang ga bur 'bru mar dang sbyar nas
NK107(tse)001:7811: byugs nas nyi ma la bsregs nas lus kyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:7812: ba 'khrugs mi srid rnal 'byor pa bsgrub pa pos
NK107(tse)001:7813: lus la me btsa' dang gtar ka byas na nyams
NK107(tse)001:7814: kyi 'phel 'chad do de nas mar 'grib pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7815: der tshes bcu dgu la mgrin par babs te 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:7816: dus na smra byed kyi gzhi zad pa ste ngag
NK107(tse)001:7817: gi las ci byas kyang mi 'grub de nas nyi
NK107(tse)001:7818: shu gnyis la mar 'grib pas snying khar slebs pas
NK107(tse)001:7819: sems kyi bsam pa ci yang mi 'grub skyes na
NK107(tse)001:7820: pha ma 'chi na na 'tsho bar dka' shi na
NK107(tse)001:7821: byol song du 'agro'o de nas nyer drug pa lte
NK107(tse)001:7822: bar babs te 'byung ba las kyi gral zhig pas
NK107(tse)001:7823: na na 'chi skyes na yul mi kun mi bde
NK107(tse)001:7824: bar 'ong shi na lha tshe ring po'i gnas su
NK107(tse)001:7825: skye'o de nas gnam stong gi nyin bar la rkang
NK107(tse)001:7826: mthil du babs te 'di'i dus na 'khor bar 'jug
NK107(tse)001:7827: gi lam zad pa zhes bya ste phung po'i len
NK107(tse)001:7828: gtor khams kyi mched chad byang sems kyi 'gyus yal
NK107(tse)001:7829: ba zhes bya ste sbyin pa la sogs pa dge
NK107(tse)001:7830: ba'i las gang la 'bad kyang 'bum phrag mang por
NK107(tse)001:7831: 'phel na na yid mi bde bar byed skyes na
NK107(tse)001:7832: 'jig rten gyi bya ba mi 'grub cing tha ma
NK107(tse)001:7833: chos byed pa'i mir 'ong shi na chos byas pa
NK107(tse)001:7834: yin na b+hud tha sdig can yin na dmyal ba
NK107(tse)001:7835: lung ma bstan yin na lha min du skye'o 'di
NK107(tse)001:7836: dus yang gong gi rdzas de dag gis rkang mthil
NK107(tse)001:7837: du byugs nyi ma la bsregs na lus la 'byung
NK107(tse)001:7838: ba 'khrugs pa'i nad mi 'byung ngo zhag gcig la
NK107(tse)001:7839: yar 'phel mar 'grib pa'i dus ste srod la rkang
NK107(tse)001:7840: 'thil nas lte bar 'phel bas dbang po gnas su
NK107(tse)001:7841: bsdud pa'i man ngag gi gnad la sbyang de nas
NK107(tse)001:7842: nam phyed yol la snying khar 'phel bas shes bya
NK107(tse)001:7843: bum par gzhug pa'i man ngag la sbyang de nas
NK107(tse)001:7844: tho rangs mgrin par 'phel bas ye shes rang gsal
NK107(tse)001:7845: ba'i ngang la gnas de nas nam langs pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7846: na spyi bor rgyas pa'i dus te dge sbyor la
NK107(tse)001:7847: 'bad pa cher byas pas 'grub mchog tu chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:7848: mngon gsum gyi gnad gzir ba gal che'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:7849: nyi ma shar gros yal mgrin par babs te ngag
NK107(tse)001:7850: gi dge sbyor la 'bad na rang gi 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:7851: nyams de'i dus na na yun ring skyes na longs
NK107(tse)001:7852: spyod rgyas shi na mtho ris su 'gro de nas
NK107(tse)001:7853: nyi ma phyed na snying babs te bskyed rdzogs sgom
NK107(tse)001:7854: pa la 'bad na skyes na rtag tu mya ngan
NK107(tse)001:7855: dang sdug basngala na na 'tsho ba ma yin shi
NK107(tse)001:7856: na byol song phal bar skye'o de nas phyi 'bred
NK107(tse)001:7857: lte bar babs te 'di'i dus rten 'brel gyi las
NK107(tse)001:7858: bya zhing zhi rgyas kyi sbyin bsregs byas na 'grub
NK107(tse)001:7859: skyes na 'gro ba'i kha lo sgyur ba 'ong na
NK107(tse)001:7860: na myur du grol shi na mkha' la rgyu ba'i
NK107(tse)001:7861: yi dwags su skye'o de nas nyi ma nub pa
NK107(tse)001:7862: la rkang 'thil du babs pas las kyi 'gyur ston
NK107(tse)001:7863: pa ste yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul ba
NK107(tse)001:7864: bzang skyes na dbul zhing 'phongs par 'gyur na na
NK107(tse)001:7866: shi na grang ba'i dmyal bar skye'o de dag kyang
NK107(tse)001:7867: so so'i 'byung ba'i dang dus nges pa'i dbang du
NK107(tse)001:7868: byas te ma nor bar sbyangs pas nges par 'grub
NK107(tse)001:7869: pa'o lo'i 'phel 'grib ni zla ba'i rim pas brtsis
NK107(tse)001:7870: pa'o zla ba ni phyi'i zla ba cher 'phel ba
NK107(tse)001:7871: dang 'dra bar thig le yang de dang 'dra'o nya
NK107(tse)001:7872: gang ba'i dus na byang chub kyi sems rgyas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:7873: de nas mar 'grib pa yang zla ba dang 'dra'o
NK107(tse)001:7874: gnam stong gi nub mo zla ba zad pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7875: 'dra bar kun rdzob kyi las kyi 'gyur zad pas
NK107(tse)001:7876: dge ba'i las ci byas pa 'phel che ba'o dus
NK107(tse)001:7877: de dag ma yin pa rnams su skyes pa dang
NK107(tse)001:7878: na ba dang shi ba rnams su la nges pa
NK107(tse)001:7879: med do don dam pa'i thig le 'phel 'grib ni
NK107(tse)001:7880: rtsa la rgyu ba'i rlung nam gyi mtha' yas byung
NK107(tse)001:7881: ba nas brtsis pa'o stong phrag gsum gyi yun la
NK107(tse)001:7882: 'grib pas dge sbyor byas kyang dgos med do de
NK107(tse)001:7883: nas brtsis pa'i sum brgya'i bar la 'phel bas dge
NK107(tse)001:7884: ba'i las ci byas kyang 'grub khyad par du rlung
NK107(tse)001:7885: bsgoms pa'am chos nyid mngon gsum gyi gnad gzir na
NK107(tse)001:7886: 'bras bu mngon du phyin pa'o de ka ltar brtsis
NK107(tse)001:7887: pa'i sum brgya'i bar la gnad bstun pas gzhan du
NK107(tse)001:7888: thang gcad nas byas pas 'phel che'o drug pa rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7889: de dag gis lus kyi srog ji ltar 'dzin pa
NK107(tse)001:7890: ni de yang thog ma ma'i mnga' du lus chags
NK107(tse)001:7891: pa'i dus na rtsa shin tu phra zhing nyal nyol
NK107(tse)001:7892: du yod pas nang du shes pa'i rtsal ma rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:7893: phyi lus kyi bskyed ma rdzogs gnyis med du kun
NK107(tse)001:7894: gzhi dang sems kyi 'gris ma snyed pa'i gnad de
NK107(tse)001:7895: las byung ba'o de nas rtsa rags su song bas
NK107(tse)001:7896: rlung lam du tshud te lus grub pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:7897: 'gul ba dang 'phrig pa'i gnad de las byung de
NK107(tse)001:7898: nas zla dgu ngo dang bcu na lus rdzogs nas
NK107(tse)001:7899: ma'i mngal nas mthon pa'i dus na rtsa'i kha bag
NK107(tse)001:7900: tsam bye nas 'byung ba'i 'gyur byed 'jug pa'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:7901: kyis skye byed kyi rtsa mdud kyi dbus na skye
NK107(tse)001:7902: ba med pa la skyes pa'i rtags su yi ge
NK107(tse)001:7903: a la'i rang bzhin du srog gnas pa dang rtse
NK107(tse)001:7904: mo'i rtsa'i mdud pa'i dbus na skye med las 'gag
NK107(tse)001:7905: med kyi las tha dad par shar ba'i rtags su
NK107(tse)001:7906: srog gi yi ge ha'i rnam par gnas pa dag
NK107(tse)001:7907: gis gnyis kyis sgra 'og mas snying khar phul bas
NK107(tse)001:7908: dran pa'i rtsa mdud kyi dbus na srog yi ge
NK107(tse)001:7909: h+aum du gnas pa las skye med kyi brda' mtshon
NK107(tse)001:7910: pa'i sgra 'od dang bcas par 'byung ha las mas
NK107(tse)001:7911: ro rnams kyi dbus na ring byed kyi yi ge
NK107(tse)001:7912: 'a lta bu gnas pa la phog pas lus dang
NK107(tse)001:7913: sems kyi rtsal gnyis ngag la lhung bas a ham
NK107(tse)001:7914: gi sgra byung ba ni lus ngag yid kyi sa
NK107(tse)001:7915: bon gyis rtsal tsam du gnas pa las 'byung ba'o
NK107(tse)001:7916: de nas zla ba re lon cing rtsa rags shing
NK107(tse)001:7917: 'khrang du song ba las rlung phyir 'gro nang du
NK107(tse)001:7918: 'gengs pa'i rtsal la zla ba re la mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7919: ba re re 'byung bas lus stobs dang ngag brda'i
NK107(tse)001:7920: rnam pa dang sems shes pa'i rnam pa mi 'dra
NK107(tse)001:7921: ba re 'ong ba'i gnad de las 'byung ngo de
NK107(tse)001:7922: yang lus kyi srog 'byung ba'i stobs bskyed pas thog
NK107(tse)001:7923: ma tsog pur sdod pa'i gnad de las byung de
NK107(tse)001:7924: nas 'byung ba'i las mas bskyed pas gzugs bzhi sa
NK107(tse)001:7925: la 'dzugs pa sa chu me rlung gi btsal 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:7926: pa'i rtags de nas srog bstan pas lo gcig rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:7927: pa dang 'gro zhing 'dug pa rlung gi 'gro 'ong
NK107(tse)001:7928: gis 'gyur brtan pa'i gnad de ltar lus ngag brten
NK107(tse)001:7929: pa'i rtags su rtsa gnas kyi yi ge tshad du
NK107(tse)001:7930: ma rdzogs pa'i bar la ngag tu brda' mi gsal
NK107(tse)001:7931: bas rim gyis bskyed nas tha ma gsal bar smra
NK107(tse)001:7932: ba la sogs pa de las 'byung ba'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:7933: lus ngag gnyis sems rten pa'i rtags su ngag gi
NK107(tse)001:7934: barjoda pa dag tu song ba dang lus kyi stobs
NK107(tse)001:7935: cher song bas sems la rten pa'i blo dang shes
NK107(tse)001:7936: pa yang rgya che zhing gsal du 'gro ba'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:7937: de las byung ba'o de ltar lus kyi srog rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7938: la brten pas 'phel ba'i dus rnams su srog rgyas
NK107(tse)001:7939: pa'i gnad rin po che'i tshe bsgrub pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:7940: pa bcud len gyi rten 'brel la byas nas tshe
NK107(tse)001:7941: rgyas par 'ongs la de nas rgas nas yang lus
NK107(tse)001:7942: dang ngag dang sems la sogs pa mar 'grib pas
NK107(tse)001:7943: tshe dang srog thung du song ba las 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:7944: na srog rnam par dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgoms
NK107(tse)001:7945: na srog gi dbang po yun ring du mi 'gag
NK107(tse)001:7946: go de yang lus kyi srog rtsa yin pa'i rtags
NK107(tse)001:7947: su mtshon dang lus kyi spyod lam gyis rtsa thems
NK107(tse)001:7948: pa dang rtsa chad pa dang rtsa brdubs pa la
NK107(tse)001:7949: brten nas srog gi dbang po 'gag par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:7950: de nyid las grol ba'i gnad du rtag tu tsan+dana
NK107(tse)001:7951: gyi mar gyis rtsa sro ba dang thig le rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7952: la btab pas tshe rgyas shing 'phel bar nges so
NK107(tse)001:7953: de yang lus su chags pa dang bsgrub pa'i bar
NK107(tse)001:7954: bskyed byed kyi rtsa rnams kyis srog 'dzin pa ste
NK107(tse)001:7955: thog ma lte ba la brten pa'i gnad de las
NK107(tse)001:7956: byung de nas ma'i mngal nas mthon nas gzhon pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7957: bar la dran pa 'dus pa'i rtsa rnams kyi srog
NK107(tse)001:7958: 'dzin pas snying nas 'das pa dang ma 'ongs da
NK107(tse)001:7959: lta'i dran bsam gyi 'khor lo la 'jug pa'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:7960: de las byung de nas dar la babs nas dar
NK107(tse)001:7961: yol gyi bar la ro rnams kyi rtsa rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:7962: lus kyi srog 'dzin pas zas kyi dngas mas lus
NK107(tse)001:7963: rdzogs la snyigs mas phyi sa che chung dor ba
NK107(tse)001:7964: dang ngag gi barjoda pa'i 'gyur sna tshogs su 'phro
NK107(tse)001:7965: ba'i gnad de las byung de nas rgas shing khogs
NK107(tse)001:7966: pa la thug par rtse mo rnam par bkod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7967: rtsa rnams kyis srog lus kyi srog 'dzin pas dbang
NK107(tse)001:7968: po mi gsal zhing skra dkar gnyer mar 'gyur ba'i
NK107(tse)001:7969: gnad de las byung ngo de dag thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:7970: 'gyur byed pa ni rtsa'i rnam grangs bsdus pa nyi
NK107(tse)001:7971: shu rtsa dgus byed de spyir khyad par dang thun
NK107(tse)001:7972: mong gi las byed pa la rtsa sum cu rtsa
NK107(tse)001:7973: gnyis yod de gsum pa ni gtso bo yin pas
NK107(tse)001:7974: na de yang lus kyi srog 'dzin pa la bskyed
NK107(tse)001:7975: byed na brgyad kyis byed te sa'i srog 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7976: gnyis yod de mos pa'i srog bzung bas rdul 'phra
NK107(tse)001:7977: rab gyi bsdud byas pas yas su mi ster phos
NK107(tse)001:7978: de dag gcig la gcig chags pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:7979: rags pas gzugs kyi 'phel yal nas yan lag la
NK107(tse)001:7980: sogs pa rags shing rgyas par byed chu'i srog 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:7981: pa gnyis te mos srog bzung bas barlana tsam las
NK107(tse)001:7982: barlangasa su mched pa'i gzhi byas phos bsher ba khrag
NK107(tse)001:7983: gi bsdud byas pas mang nyung dang 'phel 'grib tu
NK107(tse)001:7984: mi byed pa'i gnad de las byung de gnyis gcig
NK107(tse)001:7985: tu gnas pas srog 'dzin pa'o yang me'i srog 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:7986: pa'i rtsa gnyis ni mos 'phra ba'i rlangs pa las
NK107(tse)001:7987: rta rnga'i drug cha tsam gyis drod 'bebs phos rlung
NK107(tse)001:7988: dang shes pa gcig tu bsdus nas 'bar ba'i drod
NK107(tse)001:7989: la gsal 'grib dang che chung du mi byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7990: gnad de las byung rlung gi srog 'dzin pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:7991: ni mos 'gyu ba 'phra ba la brten nas dran
NK107(tse)001:7992: pa'i gzhi 'dzin phos thog ma rtsa'i 'gyu ba la
NK107(tse)001:7993: brten nas lon pa'i barlangasa pas lus kyi 'khes bting
NK107(tse)001:7994: bas lus sems dam du bcings pa'o dran pa na
NK107(tse)001:7995: brgyad kyis srog bzung ba ni 'das pa'i dran bsam
NK107(tse)001:7996: gyis srog 'dzin pa gnyis te mos sngon ma dang
NK107(tse)001:7997: yang lhun la sogs pa'i rjes gnang las 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:7998: las rmi lam rmi ba de nas byung phos de
NK107(tse)001:7999: dag gis mtshams sbyar bas 'das pa dang da lta'i
NK107(tse)001:8000: bag chags mtshams sbyor ba'i gnad de las byung da
NK107(tse)001:8001: lta'i dran bsam gyi srog 'dzin pa gnyis ni mos
NK107(tse)001:8002: nyon mongs pa lnga'i gzhi 'dzin par byed pas nyon
NK107(tse)001:8003: mongs pa bag la nyal nas dgogs par dka' ba
NK107(tse)001:8004: de las byung phos sgo lnga yi yul la brten
NK107(tse)001:8005: pa'i dran bsam sna tshogs pa bsdud par byed pas
NK107(tse)001:8006: yul gyi rjes su nyon mongs pa gsum gyis dbang
NK107(tse)001:8007: btsan par byas nas bdag gzhan du 'dzin pa de
NK107(tse)001:8008: las byung ma 'ongs pa'i dran bsam gyis lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:8009: srog 'dzin pa gnyis ni mos ma mthong ba'i yul
NK107(tse)001:8010: la 'jug par byed de dran bsam gyi rjes su
NK107(tse)001:8011: lus 'brengs te sdug basngala ba de las byung phos
NK107(tse)001:8012: nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa'i rgyu dang rkyen byas
NK107(tse)001:8013: te ma 'ongs pa'i rmi lam sna tshogs su rmi
NK107(tse)001:8014: ba de las 'byung ngo dran bsam 'dra min la
NK107(tse)001:8015: chal chol gyis lus kyi srog 'dzin pa gnyis ni
NK107(tse)001:8016: mos rang gzhan gyi 'khrul pa sna tshogs pa bsdud
NK107(tse)001:8017: pas med pa la rtog pa 'dzud pa de las
NK107(tse)001:8018: 'byung phos bag chags sna tshogs pa'i gzhi 'dzin par
NK107(tse)001:8019: byed pa ste rmi lam 'dra min dang chal chol
NK107(tse)001:8020: du rmi ba de las byung de dag ni dran
NK107(tse)001:8021: bsam sngon du rgyu dang bag la nyal 'dus shing
NK107(tse)001:8022: 'phros pa las grub 'dzin pa'o ro rnams na lus
NK107(tse)001:8023: kyi srog 'dzin pa'i rtsa drug yod do mos skad
NK107(tse)001:8024: dang gdangs la 'jug pa ste ro mngar ba la
NK107(tse)001:8025: mched cing 'dzin pa de las 'byung de las khyad
NK107(tse)001:8026: par du gyur pa las ro kha ba 'dzin cing
NK107(tse)001:8027: mched pa las phos bad+ha las khyad par gyi srog
NK107(tse)001:8028: bzung bas ro btsub pa la dad cing mched pa
NK107(tse)001:8029: de las byung de'i 'dus shing brgal ba las skyur
NK107(tse)001:8030: ba'i ro'i rjes su 'dzin par snang la yang grags
NK107(tse)001:8031: sgra'i las rtog pa las gsal ba dang mi gsal
NK107(tse)001:8032: ba'i srog 'dzin pa gnyis ni mos smra ba tshig
NK107(tse)001:8033: sdebs sbyor ba dang phos bsgyur byed mkhas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:8034: mi mkhas pa las ro bska ba dang kleg pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8035: 'gyur byed myong ba de las byung ngo de nyid
NK107(tse)001:8036: 'dus pa las rtog la 'phros pas khyad par gyi
NK107(tse)001:8037: gzhi ston par byed pa'o rtse mo na bdun gnas
NK107(tse)001:8038: pas yul dang shes pa'i las sna tshogs ston par
NK107(tse)001:8039: byed pa ni dbang po'i 'jug pa nges pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:8040: ni de nyid g.yas su 'phar bas mig gi mthong
NK107(tse)001:8041: byed du mar byed pa ste mig gi a 'bras
NK107(tse)001:8042: dkar nag phyed pa de las byung g.yon du 'phar
NK107(tse)001:8043: bas rna ba'i nyin byed du mar byed pa ste
NK107(tse)001:8044: de'i rtsal mig tu gyur pas rna ba sgra'i byed
NK107(tse)001:8045: pa 'gag ste rna ba sgra'i srog nyams pas rna
NK107(tse)001:8046: ba 'on pa'i mig rtsa drung ba de las byung
NK107(tse)001:8047: de nyid dbus su 'phar ba las lce'i myong byed
NK107(tse)001:8048: du mar ston pa ste de'i srog nyams pa las
NK107(tse)001:8049: tshe'i dus byed pa dang 'byung ba'i nad kyis btab
NK107(tse)001:8050: pa'i lce ldib pa de las byung de steng du
NK107(tse)001:8051: 'phar ba las sna'i snom byed du mar ston par
NK107(tse)001:8052: byed pa ste de'i srog nyams pas sna zhom zhing
NK107(tse)001:8053: mang spri 'ong ba de las byung de 'og tu
NK107(tse)001:8054: 'phar ba las lus kyi rig byed du mar ston
NK107(tse)001:8055: te de'i srog nyams pa las na ba'i dus su
NK107(tse)001:8056: lus ldang mi nus pa de las byung ba'o phos
NK107(tse)001:8057: yul rnams la 'jug cing 'dzin par byed de mthong
NK107(tse)001:8058: byed gzugs kyi srog nyams pas mig mi gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:8059: de las byung nyan byed sgra'i srog nyams pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:8060: na rna bas mi thos pa de las 'byung bsnom
NK107(tse)001:8061: byed dri'i srog nyams pa'i dus su snas dri mi
NK107(tse)001:8062: tshor ba de las byung lhag ma gnyis po des
NK107(tse)001:8063: shes so yang dbang po yul gyi 'gyur byed rnams
NK107(tse)001:8064: ni mos dbang po dang dbang po la brten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8065: chos rnams kyi srog 'dzin pa'i las kyis dbang po
NK107(tse)001:8066: rno ba dang brtul ba'i bye brag de nas byung
NK107(tse)001:8067: phos skye ba dang mched pa'i las nye bar bsdus
NK107(tse)001:8068: nas lus kyi tsha dang na ba'i 'jug pa de
NK107(tse)001:8069: las byung yang yul gyi 'jug pa'i bye brag ston
NK107(tse)001:8070: pa gnyis ni mos gzugs sdug pa la 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:8071: chags pa'i las dang de bzhin sgra dang dri dang
NK107(tse)001:8072: ro dang reg la yang ngo phos mi sdug pa
NK107(tse)001:8073: la zhe sdang pa rnams su byung la yang gcig
NK107(tse)001:8074: pus ni bar pa la gti mug pa'i las byed
NK107(tse)001:8075: pa ste de ltar cha gsum du gnas pas lus
NK107(tse)001:8076: ngag yid kyi 'gyur byed las lus kyi srog chad
NK107(tse)001:8077: pas bem por 'gyur ba 'byung ba'i byed las zad
NK107(tse)001:8078: pa rtsas byed ngag gi srog chad pas smra byed
NK107(tse)001:8079: kyi tshig nam mkha' la yal ba dang 'gyu ba
NK107(tse)001:8080: yid kyis srog chad pas lus sems gcig tu mi
NK107(tse)001:8081: gnas par byed pa'o bdun pa rtsa de dag gi
NK107(tse)001:8082: ming gi rnam grangs bstan pa ni spyir lus la
NK107(tse)001:8083: rtsa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa lnga gnas pa las
NK107(tse)001:8084: khyad par du lus byed pa'i rtsa bzhi brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:8085: bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad gnas te de dag las khyad
NK107(tse)001:8086: par du rlung 'gyu ba'i rtsa brgyad cu rtsa bzhi
NK107(tse)001:8087: gnas pa'i ming ni rtsa gnas nas bshad pas de
NK107(tse)001:8088: dag la brten du rung ba dang mi rung ba
NK107(tse)001:8089: dum dum khrigs su blta'o de las khyad par du
NK107(tse)001:8090: bsdus pas rnal 'byor pa'i las kyi khyad par brtsi
NK107(tse)001:8091: ba sum cu rtsa gnyis gnas pa ni bskyed byed
NK107(tse)001:8092: na brgyad du gnas te mo rtsa bzhi la las
NK107(tse)001:8093: rnams bgrangs 'byung ba'i nang 'gyur byed de chu sa
NK107(tse)001:8094: me rlung bzhi'i rtsa ba ston par byed pas na
NK107(tse)001:8095: dge ma na yi ge a gnas pa dang lhan
NK107(tse)001:8096: ma na ra rab tu gru ma na i mchod
NK107(tse)001:8097: ma na ha gnas pa dang bazhi'o pho rtsa bzhis
NK107(tse)001:8098: 'byung ba las kyi 'gyur byed pa ni bskyod pa
NK107(tse)001:8099: pha na yi ge u gnas pa dang bsdud pa
NK107(tse)001:8100: pha na nya smin pa pha na ri bskyod pa
NK107(tse)001:8101: pha na yi gnas pa'o yang dran pha na khyad
NK107(tse)001:8102: par du bsdus pa brgyad yod de mo bzhis dran
NK107(tse)001:8103: bsam gyi gzhi 'dings par byed de grags byin ma
NK107(tse)001:8104: na yi ge kha gnas pa dang rkyang ma na
NK107(tse)001:8105: rnga gnas pa dang phra ba mo na pa shugs
NK107(tse)001:8106: can mo na sa gnas pa'o pho bzhis shes byed
NK107(tse)001:8107: du ma'i 'phro 'du byed pa ni theg par byed
NK107(tse)001:8108: pa na yi ge rtsa gnas pa dang bsdud par
NK107(tse)001:8109: byed pa na ta dang 'bar bar byed pa na
NK107(tse)001:8110: ya dang 'khor bar byed pa na he gnas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:8111: yang ro rnams na khyad par nges pa bsdus pa
NK107(tse)001:8112: drug gnas pa ni mo gsum gyis grag pa sgra
NK107(tse)001:8113: dang barjoda pa tshig gi gzhi byed pa ni sdug
NK107(tse)001:8114: gu ma na yi ger gnas pa dang rab tu
NK107(tse)001:8115: ldan byed ma na ra tsha ba mo na li
NK107(tse)001:8116: pho gsum gyis sgra tshig ming gis gsal 'debs pa
NK107(tse)001:8117: ni drug 'gyur pha na l+ai rab tu 'gyur byed
NK107(tse)001:8118: pha na a 'byed byed pha na am gnas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:8119: yang rtse mo na bdun gyis dbang po khyad par
NK107(tse)001:8120: gyi 'jug pa ston pa ni mo gsum gyis las
NK107(tse)001:8121: dang rtogs pa bsdud pa ni grags na mo na
NK107(tse)001:8122: m+aa dri sna mo na mi ro sna mo na
NK107(tse)001:8123: m+ai gnas pa'o pho gsum gyis ye shes kyi las
NK107(tse)001:8124: dang 'gyur ston pa ni mched pa pha na pha
NK107(tse)001:8125: 'dzin pa pha na ph+aa sbyor ba pha na ph+ai
NK107(tse)001:8126: gnas pa'o ya ni ma ning stong pa'i rtsas ye
NK107(tse)001:8127: shes stong pa'i gzhi mtshon pa ni spyi bo tshangs
NK107(tse)001:8128: pa'i srog 'dzin par byed cing sgron ma ye shes
NK107(tse)001:8129: kyi mdangs ston par byed pa'o de ltar lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:8130: rtsa 'khor lo'i dbus na yar rtsa ro ma dang
NK107(tse)001:8131: rkyang ma dang kun d+har ma gsum ni dbus na
NK107(tse)001:8132: yar rta rnga'i nyag theg pa ltar drang por gnas
NK107(tse)001:8133: te de gsum pa shel sbub can dar dkar gyi
NK107(tse)001:8134: ba rnal ma 'khril ba ltar gnas de gsum gcig
NK107(tse)001:8135: tu sdom la 'khril nas mgo 'jug med par bkris
NK107(tse)001:8136: nas gnas nang na yi ge +amo dbus kun d+harma
NK107(tse)001:8137: na a g.yas ro ma na h+aum g.yon rkyang ma
NK107(tse)001:8138: na shel sbub can k+sha gnas pas 'gyur byed med
NK107(tse)001:8139: cing khrag dang chu ser mi rgyu'o de ltar bzhi
NK107(tse)001:8140: po sdong po lta bu la bskyed byed na rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8141: gzhan rnams dpag bsam gyi shing gi yal ga rgyas
NK107(tse)001:8142: pa ltar gnas dran pa na gser gyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:8143: spras pa ltar gnas ro rnams ni zangs kyi mo
NK107(tse)001:8144: khab bkram pa ltar gnas rtse mo ni shing gi
NK107(tse)001:8145: lo 'dab rgyas pa'am gdugs kyi rtsibs ma ltar gnas
NK107(tse)001:8146: so so so'i ming ni rtsa tig chen mo'am dum
NK107(tse)001:8147: dum khrigs nas ston no de dag gis ming bstan
NK107(tse)001:8148: pa de la dgos pa ci yod na lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:8149: gnad kyi bye brag dang ye shes dang nyon mongs
NK107(tse)001:8150: pa rnams kyi tshad zin pa'i dgos pa yod do
NK107(tse)001:8151: brgyad pa rtsa de dag gi bye brag ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:8152: 'gyur ba ni bskyed byed na rtsa'i mdud pa 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8153: pa'i dbus na yi ge +aa gnas te de rlung
NK107(tse)001:8154: gi las rdzogs pa'i dus na yam du 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:8155: shes pa yam lci dang 'khrog pa dang mi 'khrogs
NK107(tse)001:8156: pa ba rnal ma'i gnad de las byung yang sa'i
NK107(tse)001:8157: las rdzogs pa'i dus na de pam du 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:8158: lci zhing 'thibs pa dang lus lci zhing bsgyid pa
NK107(tse)001:8159: bskyur ba dang rgyu ba ngan pa de las byung
NK107(tse)001:8160: chu'i las rdzogs pa'i dus na kham du gyur pas
NK107(tse)001:8161: gnyid dang rmi lam gyi rnam pa de las byung
NK107(tse)001:8162: yang ma'i las rdzogs pa'i dus na ram du 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8163: pas lus kyi stobs grag zhan du byed pa de
NK107(tse)001:8164: las byung yang dran pa na e gnas pas sa
NK107(tse)001:8165: chu me rlung gi gong ma ltar rdzogs pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:8166: su yang snga ma ltar kham du 'gyur bas 'du
NK107(tse)001:8167: shes nang du 'khums pa de las byung de pam
NK107(tse)001:8168: du 'gyur bas shes pa rang sa na mi 'phro
NK107(tse)001:8169: ba de las byung de kham du 'gyur bas dran
NK107(tse)001:8170: bsam tha dad pa'i las de las byang de ram
NK107(tse)001:8171: du 'gyur bas dran bsam gyi 'khor lo sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:8172: su 'phro mched pa de byung de yam du 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8173: bas dga' ba dang mi dga' ba'i rtog pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:8174: de las 'byung ngo yang ro rnams na yi ge
NK107(tse)001:8175: am gnas pas de pam du 'gyur bas zas mi
NK107(tse)001:8176: len pa dang yi ga mchus pa de las byung
NK107(tse)001:8177: de kham du 'gyur bas bskyug cing 'byang ba de
NK107(tse)001:8178: las byung de yam du 'gyur bas skom zhing zad
NK107(tse)001:8179: 'dod pa de las byung de ram du 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:8180: lto che zhing khams 'khrug pa de las byung ngo
NK107(tse)001:8181: yang rtse mo na yi ge h+aum gnas pas de
NK107(tse)001:8182: ram du 'gyur bas dbang po'i yul la rtog cing
NK107(tse)001:8183: 'jug pa de las byung de kham du 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:8184: dbang po gsal ba dang mi gsal ba'i 'phar shi
NK107(tse)001:8185: ba de las byung de pam du 'gyur bas dbang
NK107(tse)001:8186: po'i yul rnams la the tshom dang yid dpyod dang
NK107(tse)001:8187: log pa'i shes pa de las byung de yam du
NK107(tse)001:8188: 'gyur bas blo'i 'gyur ldog sna tshogs pa de las
NK107(tse)001:8189: byung ngo de ltar yi ge de dag gi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8190: byed dang byed las kyis lus kyi bskyed dang shes
NK107(tse)001:8191: pa'i rtsal dang lus kyi stobs che chung du 'ong
NK107(tse)001:8192: ba'i gnad de las byung ba'o de dag bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:8193: la dgos pa ci yod na rnal 'byor pa de
NK107(tse)001:8194: ltar byung ba zungs su zin par byas la 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8195: de dag byung pa'i dus so so'i yi ge de
NK107(tse)001:8196: dag la rang gi lo grangs tsam re barjoda pas
NK107(tse)001:8197: phung po snyoms pa dang dge sbyor rnams kyi gsal
NK107(tse)001:8198: 'debs pa dang nyams su myong ba skye bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8199: bas gal che'o de dag gi gnad kyis rtse mo
NK107(tse)001:8200: nas rlung las rdzogs par yod pa las bskyed byed
NK107(tse)001:8201: nas ro rnams na me dran pa na chu rtse
NK107(tse)001:8202: mo na yam bshad pa yang yod de de dag
NK107(tse)001:8203: ni gnas pa'i dbang du byas pa ste don gyis
NK107(tse)001:8204: yi ge'i 'gyur gyis nges pa myed pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:8205: bskyed byed na rlung gi las 'dus pas rtsa'i 'phar
NK107(tse)001:8206: ba'i las de las byung sa 'dus pas nad kyi
NK107(tse)001:8207: bye brag ston par byed me 'dus pas ye shes
NK107(tse)001:8208: kyi rtsal 'byin par byed chu 'dus pas gnyid dang
NK107(tse)001:8209: rmi lam gyi 'gyur ston par byed do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:8210: dran par sas 'phros shing 'dus par 'gyur chus bsdud
NK107(tse)001:8211: cing mthen mes 'bar zhing mched rlung gis yang zhing
NK107(tse)001:8212: bskyod ro rnams su sas barjoda pa'i gzhi byed rlung
NK107(tse)001:8213: gis tshig gis gsal 'debs chus sna tshogs la sgro
NK107(tse)001:8214: 'dogs mes sgra'i 'gyur ston rlung gis tshig rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:8215: 'jug pa byed pa'o yang brtse mor sa 'dus pas
NK107(tse)001:8216: lcid kyis non pa'i las byed chus bsdud par byed
NK107(tse)001:8217: mes 'phen par byed rlung gis 'dzin par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:8218: de dag gis dgos pa ni phung po dang khams
NK107(tse)001:8219: dang bskyed mched kyi 'tshogs pa'i 'gyur ston par byed
NK107(tse)001:8220: pa'o dgu pa rtsa de dag rgyu gang las bskyed
NK107(tse)001:8221: pa ni mo rtsa thams cad ma'i rgyu las bskyed
NK107(tse)001:8222: pas phyi dkar la nang dmar bar yod pho rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8223: thams cad pha'i rkyen las bskyed pas phyi dmar la
NK107(tse)001:8224: nang dkar bar yod shes rab dang ye shes kyi
NK107(tse)001:8225: rtsa thams cad sems las bskyed pas khrag dang chu
NK107(tse)001:8226: ser mi rgyu thabs dang rtogs pa'i rtsa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:8227: rlung las bskyed pas las dang nyon mongs pa ma
NK107(tse)001:8228: yin par rlung dang thig le rgyu'o phung po dang
NK107(tse)001:8229: khams kyi rtsa thams cad 'byung ba gnyis 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:8230: dang gsum dang bzhi 'dus pa las bskyed pas de
NK107(tse)001:8231: dag nas sa chu me rlung gi 'gyur byed rgyu'o
NK107(tse)001:8232: nyon mongs pa dang rnam par rtog pa'i rtsa rnams
NK107(tse)001:8233: dran pa dang yid las bskyed pas de dag nas
NK107(tse)001:8234: 'das ma 'ongs kyis 'dzin rjes rgyu'o nad dang sdug
NK107(tse)001:8235: basngala gyi rtsa rnams 'byung ba byer zug gi las
NK107(tse)001:8236: 'khrugs pa las bskyed de de dag nas rlung mkhris
NK107(tse)001:8237: bad kan so so dang gnyis 'dus pa dang gsum
NK107(tse)001:8238: 'dus pa la sogs pa'i rgyu'o bcu pa rtsa de
NK107(tse)001:8239: dag gi rkyen gyis ji ltar 'gyur ba ni rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8240: spyi'i bye brag 'dir ma smos so 'di'i 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:8241: bzhi'i gtso bo zhes bya ba'i rtsa'i nges pa bshad
NK107(tse)001:8242: par bya'o de yang bskyed byed la sogs pa'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:8243: lo bzhi po yang so so'i skye bo dang rnal
NK107(tse)001:8244: 'byor pa gnyis kyis dbang du brtsis na thog ma
NK107(tse)001:8245: so so'i skye bo'i dus na srid pa lugs bzlog
NK107(tse)001:8246: dang chal chol du gnas pa ste 'dir ma bshad
NK107(tse)001:8247: do 'di ni rnal 'byor pa'i dbang du byas pa
NK107(tse)001:8248: ste rnal 'byor pas dbang bskur zhing bla ma'i man
NK107(tse)001:8249: ngag gis sgor zhugs pa tsam gyis bskyed byed na
NK107(tse)001:8250: 'byung ba rlung gi rtsa gtso che bas lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:8251: 'byung ba 'khrugs pas rkyen byed pas lus kyi na
NK107(tse)001:8252: tsha dang sems kyi sdug basngala sna tshogs pa'i rkyen
NK107(tse)001:8253: byas pas kun rdzob kyi dus na rlung mkhris bad
NK107(tse)001:8254: kan gsum gyis lus ngag yid gsum 'bral ba'i rkyen
NK107(tse)001:8255: byas bas sems dang lus kyi 'brel che 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:8256: kyis mtshams phyed pa zhes bya ste lus 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:8257: bag la nyal sems chos nyid kyi bar ma do
NK107(tse)001:8258: la 'od gsal chos kyi sku 'khor lor tshud pas
NK107(tse)001:8259: 'khor 'das kyi mtshams phyed pa zhes bya'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:8260: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum gyi rkyen gyis
NK107(tse)001:8261: nyon mongs pa sna tshogs pa dang bag chags snga
NK107(tse)001:8262: phyi'i mtshams sbyor bar byed pas na de'i rkyen gyis
NK107(tse)001:8263: ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i 'bras bu nye bar
NK107(tse)001:8264: len par byed pa'o don dam gyi dbang du brtsis
NK107(tse)001:8265: na lus la gnas pa'i ye shes kyi stobs kyis
NK107(tse)001:8266: bdag nyid kyi bzlas pa dang bsgom pa dang klag
NK107(tse)001:8267: pa la sogs pa'i dge ba'i sbyor ba 'phra mo
NK107(tse)001:8268: la brten pa'i stobs sam rkyen gyis rnam par gsal
NK107(tse)001:8269: ba dang dag pa la sogs pa'i rkyen du song
NK107(tse)001:8270: ste de'i 'bras bu mtho ris kyi gnas nye bar
NK107(tse)001:8271: len par byed pa'o yang rnal 'byor pa dge sbyor
NK107(tse)001:8272: bzhugs pa rnams ni bskyed byed na 'byung gnyis 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8273: par gnas pas de la rkyen gyis shes rab dang
NK107(tse)001:8274: nyams la brten nas ye shes thun mong tsam du
NK107(tse)001:8275: gnas pa'o bsgom bsgrub mtha' bskyol ba rnams la 'byung
NK107(tse)001:8276: ba bzhi ka'i nus pa bskyed na nyon mongs pa
NK107(tse)001:8277: zad par gnas pas ye shes b+ha zhig la gnas
NK107(tse)001:8278: pa'o rang bzhin du ni tha mal pa dang 'gro
NK107(tse)001:8279: ba kun la bskyed byed na sa'i rtsa gtso che
NK107(tse)001:8280: bas des 'byung ba sha'i byed las byed par byas
NK107(tse)001:8281: pas rdul phra rab kyi bsdud zhig pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:8282: tshe'i dus byed pa'i rkyen du byed la de'i rtags
NK107(tse)001:8283: su byed pa'i skyes bu 'byung ba bag chags kyis
NK107(tse)001:8284: thim pa'i 'chi lugs kyi dbang du brtsis na lus
NK107(tse)001:8285: kyi stobs zhan cing langs mi nus pa'i gnad de
NK107(tse)001:8286: las byung pa ni rtsa ro ma bag la nyal
NK107(tse)001:8287: ba las byung ba'o yang dran pa na 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:8288: chu'i rtsa gtso che bar gnas pas des 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:8289: khrag gi byed pa las zug par byas pas grang
NK107(tse)001:8290: pa barlana gyi bskyed zhig pa'i tshe na tshe'i dus
NK107(tse)001:8291: byed pa'i rkyen du byed pa ste de yang bye
NK107(tse)001:8292: brag tu sa'i lus kyi yo gi la 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:8293: dang po'i rtsa ro ma phrad pa las tsha ba'i
NK107(tse)001:8294: nad kyi rkyen du byed rgal bas grang pa'i rkyen
NK107(tse)001:8295: du byed 'dar bas rlung 'khyims pas bad kan gseng
NK107(tse)001:8296: pas mkhris pa de dag kun du 'gyur bas 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8297: pa chad pas tshe'i dus byed pa'i rkyen du byed
NK107(tse)001:8298: pa'o yang de nyid 'phar skyen pas shes pa dga'
NK107(tse)001:8299: ba'i rkyen du byed gul bas mi dga' zhing sdug
NK107(tse)001:8300: basngala bar byed sna tshogs su 'gyur bas kun rdzob
NK107(tse)001:8301: kyi las sna tshogs ston pa'i rkyen byed brtan pas
NK107(tse)001:8302: don dam pa'i rnam grangs du ma ston par byed
NK107(tse)001:8303: pa'o yang chu'i lus gnyis la 'khor lo gnyis par
NK107(tse)001:8304: rkyang ma gong ltar 'gyur ba las de dag gi
NK107(tse)001:8305: rkyen du byed pa'o me'i lus can rnams la 'khor
NK107(tse)001:8306: lo gsum par kun d+harma gong ltar 'gyur bas las
NK107(tse)001:8307: de dag gi rkyen du 'gyur ba'o rlung gi lus
NK107(tse)001:8308: can rnams la 'khor lo bzhi par shel sbubs can
NK107(tse)001:8309: gong ma ltar 'gyur bas sa las de dag gi
NK107(tse)001:8310: rkyen byed pas na rkyen ces bya'o yang bcu gcig
NK107(tse)001:8311: pa byed pa'i las kyi gang dang gang byed pa
NK107(tse)001:8312: ni ro mas skyes pa rnams kyis g.yas pa'i bya
NK107(tse)001:8313: ba ci dang ci byed pa'i las su byed cing
NK107(tse)001:8314: g.yas na gnas la rkyang mas g.yon gyis kun d+har
NK107(tse)001:8315: mas dbus kyi shel sbub can steng nas skyes pa
NK107(tse)001:8316: bud med gnyis la 'khor ba'i tshul du gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:8317: gyen du 'phen cing mthur du sel ba'i las thun
NK107(tse)001:8318: mong du byed do kun d+har ma dbus na gnas
NK107(tse)001:8319: shing dbus kyi las byed bar mthun bud med la
NK107(tse)001:8320: ro ma g.yon na gnas shing g.yon gyi las byed
NK107(tse)001:8321: pas rtsa de'i sna rigs can bzhi 'thums pas bsgul
NK107(tse)001:8322: bskyod kyi las nyungs pas ro dang 'dra bas ro
NK107(tse)001:8323: ma zhes bya ste byang sems dngos su 'bab pa
NK107(tse)001:8324: med pa'i gnad de las byung ngo rkyang ma g.yas
NK107(tse)001:8325: na gnas te rtsa de la khug pa med pas
NK107(tse)001:8326: bud med rnams la khrag dngos su 'bab pa de
NK107(tse)001:8327: las byung ba'o spyi'i dbang du byas na ro mas
NK107(tse)001:8328: 'gro ba rnams kyis lus bskyed par byed pas tha
NK107(tse)001:8329: ma lus sems 'bral ba'i dus na yang lus la
NK107(tse)001:8330: ro zhes 'dogs pa'i gnad de las byung rkyang mas
NK107(tse)001:8331: ahngaga bskyed par byed pas thog ma mngal nas 'thon
NK107(tse)001:8332: pa'i dus na ngag tu a zhes rkyang pa la
NK107(tse)001:8333: ham zhes mtha' rkyang par drag pa dang tshe'i dus
NK107(tse)001:8334: byed pa'i dus na ig zhes pa'i rlung sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:8335: bcas pa 'ong ba'i gnad de las byung kun d+har
NK107(tse)001:8336: mas sems bskyed par byed pas tha ma 'chi bas
NK107(tse)001:8337: 'jigs shing sems 'dar zhing yang ba de las byung
NK107(tse)001:8338: shel sbub can lus ngag yid du 'brel ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:8339: byed de 'bras bu chos nyid kyi sa la mngon
NK107(tse)001:8340: par byang chub pa'i bar lus ngag sems lhan cig
NK107(tse)001:8341: tu 'tshogs cing 'brel ba byed pa'i gnad de las
NK107(tse)001:8342: byung rang bzhin du ro ma chu 'bab cing lus
NK107(tse)001:8343: kyi bye brag mi 'dra bar byed rkyang mas khrag
NK107(tse)001:8344: 'bab cing ngag gi barjoda pa mi 'dra ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:8345: byed kun d+har mas byang sems 'bab par byed cing
NK107(tse)001:8346: sems kyi rtog pa mi 'dra ba'i las byed do
NK107(tse)001:8347: shel sbub can gyis ni spyi kun la khyab pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8348: las byed pa'o don dam pa'i dus na kun d+harmasa
NK107(tse)001:8349: chos sku'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i las byed pas sems
NK107(tse)001:8350: gnas pa'i bye brag ston par byed rkyang mas longs
NK107(tse)001:8351: sku'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i barjoda bya yang dag pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8352: las byed do ro mas sprul pa'i sku'i rnam par
NK107(tse)001:8353: 'phrul pas lus ngag sems kyi bde ba khyad par
NK107(tse)001:8354: can ster bar byed pa'o bcu gnyis pa rtsa'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:8355: nyid ji lta bu yin pa ni rtsa zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:8356: ba nges pa'i don ston par byed pa ste dper
NK107(tse)001:8357: na lo rgyus bshad pa rtsa nas 'ongs pas bshad
NK107(tse)001:8358: pa la 'gyur ba med pa dang 'dra'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:8359: rtsa spyi'i mtshan nyid dang bye brag la gnyis te
NK107(tse)001:8360: dang po lus chags par byed pa yang rtsa la
NK107(tse)001:8361: brten nas chags te rtsa la rlung brten lus la
NK107(tse)001:8362: rtsa brten rlung la ye shes dang nyon mongs pa
NK107(tse)001:8363: brten ye shes la chos nyid dang bde ba brten
NK107(tse)001:8364: pas de gnyis 'dus pa las 'das pa'i mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:8365: du byung la nyon mongs pa la nad dang sdug
NK107(tse)001:8366: basngala brten pas de gnyis 'dus pa las sdug basngala
NK107(tse)001:8367: gyi bye brag sna tshogs par byung bas 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:8368: mtshan nyid du byung ba'o rtsa bye brag pa'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:8369: nyid ni 'khor lo dang po'i rtsa rnams kyi mtshan
NK107(tse)001:8370: nyid sra zhing brtan pas lus kyi gzhi 'dzin gnyis
NK107(tse)001:8371: pa'i rtsa rnams kyis 'jug cing khyab pa'i las mtshan
NK107(tse)001:8372: nyid 'dzin pas lus kyi yan lag dang dbang po
NK107(tse)001:8373: rnams kyi las ston 'khor lo gsum pas tsha zhing
NK107(tse)001:8374: smin pa'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pas lus kyi stobs dang
NK107(tse)001:8375: kha dog dang gzi brjid dang bkrag dang mdangs ston
NK107(tse)001:8376: par byed bzhi pas yang zhing bskyod pa'i mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:8377: 'dzin pas lus kyi las sna tshogs ston par byed
NK107(tse)001:8378: pas na mtshan nyid ces pa'o bcu gsum pa rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8379: de dag las nyon mongs pa rgyu ba ngos bzung
NK107(tse)001:8380: ba ni nyon mongs pa gti mug 'khor lo dang
NK107(tse)001:8381: po'i rtsa'i gtso bo la rgyu zhe sdang gsum pa
NK107(tse)001:8382: las dug gsum cha snyoms par gnyis pa las 'dod
NK107(tse)001:8383: chags bzhi pa'i gtso bo las rgyu ba'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:8384: na nyon mongs pa ces pa'o bcu bzhi pa rtsa'i
NK107(tse)001:8385: de dag gi las kyi mtha' ji ltar 'gyur zhing
NK107(tse)001:8386: ye shes rgyu ba'i rtsa'i rnam grangs ngos bzung ba
NK107(tse)001:8387: ni spyir na 'gro ba'i lus mi 'dra ba bzhi
NK107(tse)001:8388: brgya dang bzhi la rtsa yang mi 'dra ba de
NK107(tse)001:8389: nyid du yod kyang bsdus na mi 'dra ba brgya
NK107(tse)001:8390: tham pa dang bzhir 'dus de dag la sum cu
NK107(tse)001:8391: rtsa gnyis su bsdus de las bcu drug tu 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8392: de las bcu gnyis su 'dus de las brgyad du
NK107(tse)001:8393: 'dus de las bzhi 'byung ba sa chu me rlung
NK107(tse)001:8394: bzhi'i rtsar 'dus so de dag kun las pho rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8395: mo rtsa byang chub sems dapa'i rtsa dang gsum las
NK107(tse)001:8396: mi 'da' ba'o pho rtsa la rgyas pa shas che
NK107(tse)001:8397: na 'khor dang longs spyod mtha' rgyas par 'gyur rags
NK107(tse)001:8398: na bu mang zhing 'khor 'dab rags pa rgyas 'phra
NK107(tse)001:8399: na dbang chung zhing longs spyod chung zhar na tshe
NK107(tse)001:8400: thung dbang thang nyams par 'gyur ro rgal na rgo
NK107(tse)001:8401: drag mi kha sdang bar 'gyur 'phril la rtag tu
NK107(tse)001:8402: na tsha dang sdug basngala la spyod 'dar na lus
NK107(tse)001:8403: stobs dang rgyu rtsal mi 'ong 'khyig na ser sna
NK107(tse)001:8404: che zhing slong pa la dga' 'gyur na blo sna
NK107(tse)001:8405: mang zhing gcig tu mi 'phebs zhan pas dpa' chung
NK107(tse)001:8406: la sems sdug / thang na las dang bya ba
NK107(tse)001:8407: la dga' zhing blo rtsal chung par 'gyur ro mo
NK107(tse)001:8408: rtsal de ltar byung ba la ni de dag las
NK107(tse)001:8409: bzlog pas shes par bya'o byang sems la zhi ba'i
NK107(tse)001:8410: las 'grub pa dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag
NK107(tse)001:8411: po dang dgug pa dang bskrad pa dang dbye ba
NK107(tse)001:8412: dang lus kyi dge ba dang ngag dang sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:8413: dge ba 'grub par 'gyur ro yang pho'i rtsa 'chus
NK107(tse)001:8414: pas chu rgyus kyi nad du 'gyur 'thems shing btsan
NK107(tse)001:8415: pas rus pa'i nad chad pas 'dus pa'i nad kyis
NK107(tse)001:8416: tshe'i dus myur du byed gyes pa las rlung gi
NK107(tse)001:8417: nad gcig 'dus pa las bad kan stod smad btsan
NK107(tse)001:8418: zhing bsdus pa las gzer ba'i nad 'gyur mo la
NK107(tse)001:8419: de dag las bzlog pa las de ltar 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:8420: yin no de la rtsa'i mtha' nges pa'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:8421: gyi 'gyur byed ni mgo dang lus po spyi'i rtsa'i
NK107(tse)001:8422: khyad par las mgo'i dpral ba'i skra yod med kyi
NK107(tse)001:8423: mtshams nas mtshon gang gyen du btsal ba na klad
NK107(tse)001:8424: pa'i 'gyur byed gnas pas de mtshon la sogs pa'am
NK107(tse)001:8425: rang bzhin gyis chod na skad 'gyur zhing sna 'gag
NK107(tse)001:8426: pa'i skad byung nas zhag gsum mam bcu gcig na
NK107(tse)001:8427: tshe'i dus byed par 'gyur rwa g.yas g.yon thur ma
NK107(tse)001:8428: gang na mchin pa'i mkhris mdung ste chod na rtse
NK107(tse)001:8429: chung g.yas g.yon la babs ste rkang pa'i rne'u lhag
NK107(tse)001:8430: pa'i rtags byung nas skyug cing lag pa g.yob pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8431: dang mig mi mthong zhing 'dzum mi shes na zhag
NK107(tse)001:8432: bdun nam dgu na tshe'i dus byed gtsug nas thur
NK107(tse)001:8433: la mtshon don dung 'khyil pa yod de de chad
NK107(tse)001:8434: na lus grang shum byed cing tshad pa skyes nas
NK107(tse)001:8435: zhag lnga'am nyi shu na tshe'i dus byed de nas
NK107(tse)001:8436: gyen na mtshon gang na tshangs bskud bsgril ma gnas
NK107(tse)001:8437: pa de chod na mgo lus med pa skrang ste
NK107(tse)001:8438: dran pa nyams shing shes pa 'thibs nas na ba
NK107(tse)001:8439: la zhag gsum mam bdun nam dgu na dus byed
NK107(tse)001:8440: de nas ldan par thug gang na rgyug rtsa gnas
NK107(tse)001:8441: pa de chod na rgal 'dabs gzhungs pa rengs nas
NK107(tse)001:8442: zla ba phyed na 'bogs nas tshe'i dus byed do
NK107(tse)001:8443: mig gi g.yas g.yon mtshon gang na mig rtsa 'greng
NK107(tse)001:8444: bu chod nas ni mig lug nas dran pa nyams
NK107(tse)001:8445: na zhag lnga na tshe'i dus byed de dag ni
NK107(tse)001:8446: klad pa'i phyi rtsa bcu gcig gnyan pa'i 'gyur byed
NK107(tse)001:8447: do don snod 'gyur byed kyi rtsa sum cu las
NK107(tse)001:8448: smin phrag g.yon pa'i mdun na mkhris rtsa nag po
NK107(tse)001:8449: gnas te de chod na mkhris bsgyumg cing mig mi
NK107(tse)001:8450: mthong nas zhag bcu bdun nam bcu dgu na tshe'i
NK107(tse)001:8451: dus byed de'i gong na nas gang na mig rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8452: 'khor ba chod na so 'thams nas zhag bdun na
NK107(tse)001:8453: tshe'i dus byed de dag ni nges pa'i yu sa
NK107(tse)001:8454: bsdus pa ste de'i las kyi mtha' 'gyur bas lus
NK107(tse)001:8455: spyi la 'bab pa dang yan lag dang byang khog
NK107(tse)001:8456: stod smad dang don snod la babs na tshe'i dus
NK107(tse)001:8457: byed pa'i 'gyur tshad rgyas par 'dir ma bstan no
NK107(tse)001:8458: lus spyi'i 'gyur byed ni rdo dbyug mtshon la sogs
NK107(tse)001:8459: pa rnams kyis btsan pa dang chod pa dang 'thems
NK107(tse)001:8460: pa dang rnags pa las lus kyi nad du 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8461: ba dang tshe'i dus byed de de la rten 'brel
NK107(tse)001:8462: sman gyi sbyor bas bcos na 'tsho la ma bcos
NK107(tse)001:8463: na 'chi ba dang bcos ma bcos med par 'chi
NK107(tse)001:8464: ba dang bcos mi dgos pa rnams kyi bye brag
NK107(tse)001:8465: ni bla ma'i zhal las shes par bya'o yang rang
NK107(tse)001:8466: bzhin du spyod lam drag shul gyis btsan thabs su
NK107(tse)001:8467: chod pa la sogs pa ni rten 'brel sman sbyor
NK107(tse)001:8468: gyi bye brag gis 'tsho bar 'gyur ba ste btsan
NK107(tse)001:8469: pa lus sgrid cing rengs pa ste de la ni
NK107(tse)001:8470: dri dang ldan pa'i sngo sna tshogs pa sla nga'i
NK107(tse)001:8471: nang du bslangs thon tsam bsros pa la phabs btab
NK107(tse)001:8472: la dug byas pas 'tsho bar 'gyur ro chad na
NK107(tse)001:8473: lus kyi yan lag 'khums shing mig mi gsal te
NK107(tse)001:8474: de la ni ltor mkhris pa sna tshogs pa'i grang
NK107(tse)001:8475: thang btang zhing phyi nas rdo la sogs pa'i grang
NK107(tse)001:8476: dugs byas pas 'tsho 'thoms nas lhu tshigs na zhing
NK107(tse)001:8477: rkang lag na ba zug che bas de la seng
NK107(tse)001:8478: ldeng gi sman dmar btang zhing phyi nas 'jag gis
NK107(tse)001:8479: rgya gram du bcings pas 'tsho gnags na sha skor
NK107(tse)001:8480: ling du na zhing nad 'gyur la yan lag bya
NK107(tse)001:8481: byed mang ba ste de la shing n+ri gro ta'i
NK107(tse)001:8482: lo ma'i nang du nyal te lus chu la lan
NK107(tse)001:8483: rang lo grangs tsam gyis khrus byas na 'tsho bar
NK107(tse)001:8484: nges so 'gyur na skrang zhing skra dang kha spu
NK107(tse)001:8485: dang ldang zhing 'byi sdong zhing 'gyur ba ste de
NK107(tse)001:8486: la sga dang g.yer ma dang gnya' lo'i rtsa ba
NK107(tse)001:8487: spangs pa'i lums byas pas 'grol lo de ltar de
NK107(tse)001:8488: dag la mtha' dus kyi nges par na ba dang
NK107(tse)001:8489: 'chi ba dang 'tsho ba dang dbul ba dang 'phongs
NK107(tse)001:8490: pa dang dgra dang grogs la sogs pa'i nges 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8491: nges pa ni rtsa tig chen mo nas bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:8492: ltar shes par bya'o de yang lus can kun rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8493: la lus brten pa dang lus kyis rtsa brten pa
NK107(tse)001:8494: ste de yang rtsa la nad brten pa dang nad
NK107(tse)001:8495: la sdug basngala brten pa dang sdug basngala la sdig
NK107(tse)001:8496: pa brten pa dang sdig pa la ngan song 'khor
NK107(tse)001:8497: ba brten nas 'phel bar byed pa dang yang rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8498: la ye shes brten pa dang ye shes la rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8499: brten pa las ye shes la bde ba brten bde
NK107(tse)001:8500: ba la chos nyid brten chos nyid las 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8501: sku dang ye shes 'phel bar byed pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:8502: lus la rtsa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa lnga gnas
NK107(tse)001:8503: te de dag la la nas sha'i dngas ma rgyu
NK107(tse)001:8504: la la la nas khrag gi dngas ma dang chu
NK107(tse)001:8505: ser dang rus pa'i dang drod kyi dngas ma rgyu
NK107(tse)001:8506: la la la nas las kyi rlung b+ha zhig rgyu
NK107(tse)001:8507: la la la stong pa ci yang mi byed pa
NK107(tse)001:8508: yod la las ni ye shes kyis rlung rgyu ba
NK107(tse)001:8509: dang de yang ye shes kyi rlung rnam par dag
NK107(tse)001:8510: pa las ye shes kyi ngo bo 'gyu ba ste
NK107(tse)001:8511: lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi la srod la lte ba'i
NK107(tse)001:8512: rtsa'i gtso bo ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes
NK107(tse)001:8513: su gnas nam phyed na snying kha na me long
NK107(tse)001:8514: lta bu'i ye shes su gnas thor rangs mgrin pa
NK107(tse)001:8515: na mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su gnas skya
NK107(tse)001:8516: rengs shar nas nam dag pa'i dus spyi bo na
NK107(tse)001:8517: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su gnas pa ste
NK107(tse)001:8518: de yang gnas pa'i gnad kyis phal du las dang
NK107(tse)001:8519: po pa'i dus na mtshan mo ting nge 'dzin gsal
NK107(tse)001:8520: ba'i gnad de las byung ngo de nas nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:8521: dros pa la mig g.yas pa nas bya ba grub
NK107(tse)001:8522: pa'i ye shes thabs kyi cha dang bcas pa 'gyu
NK107(tse)001:8523: bas thabs zab mo la 'bad na nges par grol
NK107(tse)001:8524: de nas nyi ma phyed dus na g.yon pa nas
NK107(tse)001:8525: shes rab dang bcas te 'gyu bas rtogs pa rgyud
NK107(tse)001:8526: la brten pa bzang ngo de nas shar du rang
NK107(tse)001:8527: bangs gnyis kyi grib mas slebs pa la mig gnyis
NK107(tse)001:8528: nas thabs shes rab res 'jog dang bcas par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8529: te rlung gi gnad la 'bad pas grol lo de
NK107(tse)001:8530: nas mi ngo ma shes pa la mig gnyis nas
NK107(tse)001:8531: thabs dang shes rab zung 'jug tu rgyu bas mngon
NK107(tse)001:8532: sum gnad la sbyang pa gal che'o de ltar nyin
NK107(tse)001:8533: par 'das pa'i cha yin pas bya ba grub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8534: ye shes dngos rgyu bas bya ba'i las khyad par
NK107(tse)001:8535: can dang chos nyid bya ba'i las 'grub pa'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:8536: do de ltar na ye shes las zhes so da
NK107(tse)001:8537: ni bco lnga pa dmigs pa las kyi khyad par
NK107(tse)001:8538: la brten nas 'khor 'das kyi chos bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:8539: spyir 'gro ba thams cad rtsa'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa
NK107(tse)001:8540: ba phyed pa lta bur gnas pa las 'gro bas
NK107(tse)001:8541: na rlung gnas pas na rtsa khyab pas na 'khor
NK107(tse)001:8542: 'das kyi 'brel par byung ba'o 'khor ba'i rtsa'i khyab
NK107(tse)001:8543: byed mang yang rigs drug bskyed 'jug gi rtsar 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8544: pas 'das pa'i khyab byed rtsa bzhi las med de
NK107(tse)001:8545: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu dang mthar phyin pa
NK107(tse)001:8546: bzhi 'dus so de la 'khor ba'i bskyed 'jug gi
NK107(tse)001:8547: rtsa ni bskyed pa'i dus na spyi bor 'phra zhing
NK107(tse)001:8548: 'khyil ba'i nang na yi ge a dang bcas pa
NK107(tse)001:8549: gnas pa ni lha'i 'gro ba'i rgyu rkyen dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:8550: pa'o lha min gyi mgrin pa sbom zhing rags pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8551: nang na yi ge pre dang bcas te gnas mi'i
NK107(tse)001:8552: snying kha na 'phar zhing gyes pa'i nang na yi
NK107(tse)001:8553: ge n+ri dang bcas te gnas byol song gi lte
NK107(tse)001:8554: ba na 'khyil zhing sdod pa'i nang na yi ge
NK107(tse)001:8555: tri dang bcas te gnas yi dwags kyi yul mo
NK107(tse)001:8556: na 'gyur zhing sbring pa'i nang na yi ge su
NK107(tse)001:8557: dang bcas ste gnas dmyal ba'i rkang pa'i mthil na
NK107(tse)001:8558: 'khor zhing drag pa'i nang na yi ge du dang
NK107(tse)001:8559: bcas te bskyed pa'i dus na gnas pa'o 'jug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8560: dus na yi ge de dag gsang ba'i mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:8561: rigs drug so so'i rtsa'i 'dab ma la 'babs te
NK107(tse)001:8562: skye gnas bzhi'i rgyu dang rkyen gyis nye bar len
NK107(tse)001:8563: pa'i dbang gis so so'i yi ge'i rtsa la rlung
NK107(tse)001:8564: gis byas te rang re'i skye gnas su 'phen pa
NK107(tse)001:8565: dang gzhan du gnas 'gyur ba gnyis ni rtsa pho
NK107(tse)001:8566: mo'i byed pa'i las kyis lus kyang pho mo gnyis
NK107(tse)001:8567: su smin par byed do de yang thog ma 'gro
NK107(tse)001:8568: ba drug gi skye gnas las 'phos te gnas 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8569: ba dang thog ma'i skye gnas kyis nye bar len
NK107(tse)001:8570: pa'i bye brag la sogs pa mang po yod de
NK107(tse)001:8571: 'dir ma spros so 'di dang phyi rol gnyis ka'i
NK107(tse)001:8572: bde ba dang sdug basngala bye brag ji ltar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:8573: ba thams cad kyang rtsa'i byed pa'i las kyis byed
NK107(tse)001:8574: pa la sogs pa ma rtogs pa gang yang med
NK107(tse)001:8575: pas na lo gcig pa zla ba bcu gnyis la
NK107(tse)001:8576: dgun gyi dang po dang 'bring po gnyis la lha'i
NK107(tse)001:8577: rtsa'i byed pa'i las kyi dus te de la tshe
NK107(tse)001:8578: 'phos na lha'i skye gnas nye bar len tha ma
NK107(tse)001:8579: dang dpyid kyi dang po gnyis lha min dpyid kyi
NK107(tse)001:8580: gnyis pa dang tha ma gnyis mi'i dbyar gyi dang
NK107(tse)001:8581: po dang gnyis pa gnyis byol song de'i tha ma
NK107(tse)001:8582: dang ston gyi dang po gnyis yi dwags ston gnyis
NK107(tse)001:8583: pa dang tha ma gnyis dmyal ba'i rtsa'i phyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:8584: las la bab pas dmyal ba'i skye gnas len par
NK107(tse)001:8585: byed do de so so'i zla ba'i tshes gcig nas
NK107(tse)001:8586: lnga'i bar lha'i de'i 'gres kyis kun la shes par
NK107(tse)001:8587: bya'o rang zla rang gi tshes grangs nges pa dang
NK107(tse)001:8588: dus nges pa'o nyin zhag gi dus bcu gnyis kyang
NK107(tse)001:8589: de mi 'dres kyis shes par bya'o tshes dang zhag
NK107(tse)001:8590: dang dus nges pa la dus byas pas phyi ma
NK107(tse)001:8591: la de ltar 'gyur ba'i gnad do don gyis rtsa
NK107(tse)001:8592: yis byed pa na dmyal ba'i skye gnas 'gegs pa
NK107(tse)001:8593: la rtag tu rtsa yengs la bor ba gnad yin
NK107(tse)001:8594: yi dwags la ldem byol song la bcud mi la
NK107(tse)001:8595: bskyil lha min la bsdam lha la gseng ba gnad
NK107(tse)001:8596: yin de dag gis rang lus dus nges pa la
NK107(tse)001:8597: bya ba las gang dga' la ni ma yin no
NK107(tse)001:8598: des na rtsa la brten pas rigs drug gi skye
NK107(tse)001:8599: gnas bkag ste btsan thabs su b+hud tha ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:8600: yang gzhung dang bstun na lus kyi ni phung po
NK107(tse)001:8601: dang khams dang skye mched dang las dang bag chags
NK107(tse)001:8602: sna tshogs pa la sogs pa 'khor ba'i chos 'dus
NK107(tse)001:8603: pa dang sku dang ye shes dang 'od dang thig
NK107(tse)001:8604: le la sogs pa 'dus pa la bya'o gnad ni
NK107(tse)001:8605: 'khor lo bzhi la sogs pa'o rtsa yin te ni
