NK107(tse)001:9836: lngar bcur brtsis pas zhag gcig zla ba ni chu'i
NK107(tse)001:9837: zla ba dang po la brtsis pas 'byung ba me
NK107(tse)001:9838: rlung gi las ma rdzogs la lo zla'i 'khrul 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9839: ba'i rtags te lo ni 'byung ba'i byer zug gi
NK107(tse)001:9840: las sum las smin so lo bcu gnyis su 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9841: ba'o de yang 'byung ba'i byer zug snyoms pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:9842: kyis yang thog ma skyes pa'i nyi ma dang zla
NK107(tse)001:9843: ba dang skar ma dang gdon dang gza' la sogs
NK107(tse)001:9844: pa'i dus ma 'khrul bar shes na rnal 'byor pa
NK107(tse)001:9845: des ji ltar brtsam pa bzhin du 'grub te rgas
NK107(tse)001:9846: dang zhes pa ni 'byung ba snyings pa'i dus kyi
NK107(tse)001:9847: shes pa dang rlung gi stobs sbyar ba ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9848: ba 'khrul 'khor gyi rtsis la brten nas dus 'di
NK107(tse)001:9849: la na ba dang dus 'di la 'tsho ba dang
NK107(tse)001:9850: zhag las sogs pa'i rim pas shes so yang na
NK107(tse)001:9851: dus rnam pa sum mam bzhir phye ste skyes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:9852: dus na lo nyi shu phan chod la tshe'i stod
NK107(tse)001:9853: de nas nyi shu ste bzhi bcu la tshe'i bar
NK107(tse)001:9854: de nas nyi shu ste drug cu tham pa la
NK107(tse)001:9855: tshe'i tha ma dang gsum dabye'o de bzhin du nges
NK107(tse)001:9856: pa med par 'chi ba'i lugs dang tshe zad nas
NK107(tse)001:9857: 'chi ba'i dus rnams rnal 'byor pas bzung bas mngon
NK107(tse)001:9858: par shes pa la sogs pa 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:9859: de yang 'byung ba'i gnad 'byed pa'i skabs nas 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9860: ngo gza' dang ni 'byung ba'i dus dang ldog pa
NK107(tse)001:9861: dang 'thon pa'i dus dang sum du brtsi ba gnad
NK107(tse)001:9862: byed kyi skabs nas ston no skar ma zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:9863: ni chu'i skar ma bdun dang sa'i bdun dang me'i
NK107(tse)001:9864: bdun dang rlung gi bdun ste so so'i dus la
NK107(tse)001:9865: brtsi ba'o chu nas brtsis pa'i dbang du byas na
NK107(tse)001:9866: lo gcig la rlung gi skar ma bzhi ma rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:9867: pas lo gcig la zla ba dang lo'i zhag gi
NK107(tse)001:9868: drangs res mang ba res nyung bar 'gyur ba'o gdon
NK107(tse)001:9869: rnams ni bac+wo brgyad la sogs pa chu la sogs
NK107(tse)001:9870: pa la dbang po'i dus ni nyi ma ni chu
NK107(tse)001:9871: zug pa la sogs ma nor ba'i rim pa yis
NK107(tse)001:9872: gza' dang skar ma dang gdon dang 'di dag gi
NK107(tse)001:9873: dus ma 'khrul pa gal che'o 'byung ba brtsis nas
NK107(tse)001:9874: 'byung ba bzhin du bzang dang ngan pa'i bye brag
NK107(tse)001:9875: bartsi'o de bzhin du 'jig rten gyi tshong bya ba
NK107(tse)001:9876: dang mi bya ba dang dmag drang ba dang gnyen
NK107(tse)001:9877: sbyor dang phyogs bzang ngan dang gzhan yang zhi ba'i
NK107(tse)001:9878: las bya ba dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag
NK107(tse)001:9879: po'i las bya ba dang mi bya ba rnams brtsis
NK107(tse)001:9880: la mkhas pas bzung bar bya'o 'byung ba so so'i
NK107(tse)001:9881: gzugs la brtags pa dang de bzhin du sgra dang
NK107(tse)001:9882: dri dang ro gang la dad pa la sogs pas
NK107(tse)001:9883: tshe rabs snga phyi'i 'brel la brtag pa ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9884: ba gnas byed kyi skabs nas ston no de yang
NK107(tse)001:9885: 'byung ba chu dang sa dang me dang rlung la
NK107(tse)001:9886: sogs pa'i so so'i 'gyur byed kyis lus ngag dge
NK107(tse)001:9887: sbyor 'phel ba dang 'gyur dpag tu med par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:9888: ba dang ngag gi 'byung ba rgud pa'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:9889: dge sbyor log nas gnon par 'gyur bas de dag
NK107(tse)001:9890: gi dus bzung bar bya'o nang mthun dbye ba bcu
NK107(tse)001:9891: drug gis ni chu'i chu dang sa dang me dang
NK107(tse)001:9892: rlung ste bzhi bzhi bcu drug tu 'gyur ro de
NK107(tse)001:9893: ltar 'byung ba las grub pa'i lus la las kyi
NK107(tse)001:9894: mtha' rnam par smin pa dang nyon mongs pa'i mtha'
NK107(tse)001:9895: bdag rtog ye shes kyi mtha' rang gi ngo bo
NK107(tse)001:9896: zhes gnyis pa 'byung ba rtsis sbyor gyi gzhi ma
NK107(tse)001:9897: bstan nas da ni gsum pa 'byung ba las kyi
NK107(tse)001:9898: 'phel 'grib kyi rnam pa bstan pa ni de yang
NK107(tse)001:9899: 'gro ba rnams kyi lus thog ma yang 'byung bas
NK107(tse)001:9900: bskyed dang zhes pa ni gong ma'i 'phen pa'i shugs
NK107(tse)001:9901: kyis bar ma do'i shes pa de rlung dang sems
NK107(tse)001:9902: kyi bdag nyid can du 'gyur ba las de gnyis
NK107(tse)001:9903: kyi rgyu ma'i thig le khrag gi dngas mas bya'o
NK107(tse)001:9904: rkyen pha'i thig les byas so de yang ma'i mngal
NK107(tse)001:9905: du zhugs pa'i dus na de la lus len pa'i
NK107(tse)001:9906: rlung gis 'phen pa'i las byas pas snyigs ma kun
NK107(tse)001:9907: rdzob kyi 'byung ba rlung gi rgyur song la dwangs
NK107(tse)001:9908: mas las dag byed khyad par gyi rlung du grub
NK107(tse)001:9909: par byas so sems las snyigs ma las lus pa
NK107(tse)001:9910: nam makha'i rten byed dwangs ma las dag pas gsal
NK107(tse)001:9911: ba'i sar 'grub par byas so rgyu las snyigs ma
NK107(tse)001:9912: gsal ba me'i char byas dwangs ma las dag byed
NK107(tse)001:9913: me'i drod bskyed do pha'i rkyen gyi snyigs ma las
NK107(tse)001:9914: sdud byed chu'i gzhi byas dngas ma las dag byed
NK107(tse)001:9915: gsal ba'i lam byas so de dag gi bar snyigs
NK107(tse)001:9916: ni rgyu las smin byed drod kyi brdar 'gyur rkyen
NK107(tse)001:9917: las sdud byed khrag gis mdangs byas so rlung las
NK107(tse)001:9918: 'gyu ba dbugs kyi rta byas sems las 'jug pa
NK107(tse)001:9919: sa'i gzhi byas kun gyi rdzob kyi 'byung ba gzhi
NK107(tse)001:9920: bskyed pa ni pha'i rgyus khrag tu smin par byas
NK107(tse)001:9921: ma'i rkyen gyis drod du smin par byas rlung gis
NK107(tse)001:9922: dbugs su sems kyis shar smin par bya'o don dam
NK107(tse)001:9923: gyis dus na rgyus pa rgyangs zhags chu'i sgron ma
NK107(tse)001:9924: smin par byas la rkyen gyis shes rab rang byung
NK107(tse)001:9925: gi sgron ma rlung gis thig le stong pa'i sgron
NK107(tse)001:9926: ma sems kyis dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma
NK107(tse)001:9927: smin par byas so de ltar ma'i mngal du lus
NK107(tse)001:9928: su bskyed nas nur nur por chu'i las byas mer
NK107(tse)001:9929: mer bdun du me'i las byas ltar ltar po bdun
NK107(tse)001:9930: du sa'i las byas so gor gor po bdun du
NK107(tse)001:9931: rlung gis byas so nya'i rnam pa 'dra ba bdun
NK107(tse)001:9932: du rgyu'i nus pas byas so rus sbal gyi rnam
NK107(tse)001:9933: pa dang 'dra ba rkyen gyi nus pas byas so
NK107(tse)001:9934: de nas sbal pa'i rnam pa dang 'dra ba zhag
NK107(tse)001:9935: bdun du rlung sems gnyis 'dus pa'i nus pa byas
NK107(tse)001:9936: nas lus bskyed do rgyu'i rang bzhin lte ba na
NK107(tse)001:9937: gnas pas gzugs bsdus rkyen gyis rnam pa dran pa
NK107(tse)001:9938: 'dus pa na gnas pas mtshan mar 'dzin cing gnas
NK107(tse)001:9939: par byas rlung gi rang bzhin ro rnams na gnas
NK107(tse)001:9940: pas 'du shes kyi rkyen byas sems kyi rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:9941: du rtse mo rnam par bkod pa na gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:9942: rnam par bkod pa na gnas pas rnam par shes
NK107(tse)001:9943: pa 'tshogs pa'i rten byas so de ltar bzhi'i rang
NK107(tse)001:9944: bzhin du gnas pas 'du byed sna tshogs pa gnas
NK107(tse)001:9945: pa'i rten byas so de yang rgyu'i 'phel chen tshe
NK107(tse)001:9946: ring bar gnas rkyen gyis 'phel chen lus kyi bkrag
NK107(tse)001:9947: dang gzi mdangs su gnas par byas rlung gis 'byed
NK107(tse)001:9948: chen lus kyi shed dang stobs gnas par byas sems
NK107(tse)001:9949: kyi sdug che na dran pa dang dbang po gsal
NK107(tse)001:9950: bar bya'o tha ma 'jig pa yang na rgyu 'dus
NK107(tse)001:9951: pa dang rkyen yal ba dang rlung yas pa dang
NK107(tse)001:9952: sems 'thor ba las lus kyi phung po 'jig par
NK107(tse)001:9953: byed de sa sa la thim pas rgyu byas chu
NK107(tse)001:9954: chu la thim pas las kyi rkyen byas me me
NK107(tse)001:9955: la thim pa'i las sems kyi byas rlung rlung la
NK107(tse)001:9956: thim pa'i las rlung gis byas rlung rnam par shes
NK107(tse)001:9957: pa la thim pa'i las bzhi po gnas 'gyur bas
NK107(tse)001:9958: byas rnam par shes pa nam mkha' la 'pho ba'i
NK107(tse)001:9959: las gzhi rten 'pho bas byas te rgyu rkyen gnyis
NK107(tse)001:9960: mar 'phos rlung sems gnyis yar 'phos so nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:9961: 'od gsal la thim pa'i las rlung gis bskyod pas
NK107(tse)001:9962: byas 'od gsal zung 'jug la thim pa'i las sems
NK107(tse)001:9963: kyi dri ma dag nas rig pa rang gsal bas
NK107(tse)001:9964: byas zung 'jug gnyis med la thim pa'i las rlung
NK107(tse)001:9965: sems kyi gzhi stongs pas byas nas ma la bu
NK107(tse)001:9966: thim du sangs rgya'o 'byung ba'i las stongs pa ni
NK107(tse)001:9967: 'khrug pa'i rnam pa ste las kyi mtha' stongs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:9968: dus bcu gnyis kyi mgo zug pa'i dus na lus
NK107(tse)001:9969: kyi dge ba mi 'grub 'byams pa ni sa'i zug
NK107(tse)001:9970: pa rnams la me dang rlung gis zhi rgyas kyi
NK107(tse)001:9971: las gang yang mi 'grub 'khyil ba dang ni chu
NK107(tse)001:9972: dang rlung gi byer ba la sa dang mes dge
NK107(tse)001:9973: sbyor mi 'grub 'khor ba dang zhes pas sa dang
NK107(tse)001:9974: chu'i snyoms pa la rlung dang mes las mi 'grub
NK107(tse)001:9975: log pa dang zhes pa ni rlung dang me'i byer
NK107(tse)001:9976: ba la chu dang sa'i las mi 'grub ldebs dang
NK107(tse)001:9977: zhes pa ni chu dang sa'i byer ba la me
NK107(tse)001:9978: dang rlung gis las mi 'grub gtugs dang zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:9979: ni sa dang me'i zug pa la chu dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:9980: gis las mi 'grub drag dang zhes pa rlung dang
NK107(tse)001:9981: me'i byer ba la sa dang chus mi 'grub bo
NK107(tse)001:9982: zhan dang zhes pa chu'i zug pa la me snyoms
NK107(tse)001:9983: pas mi 'grub dgra dang zhes pa rlung gi byer
NK107(tse)001:9984: ba la me'i zug pas mi 'grub gshed dang zhes
NK107(tse)001:9985: pa rlung gis byer ba la sa'i snyoms pas mi
NK107(tse)001:9986: 'grub bo grogs dag gis zhes pa me'i zug pa
NK107(tse)001:9987: la chu'i snyoms pas mi 'grub bo de ltar 'byung
NK107(tse)001:9988: ba rang rang gis las kyi rnam grangs brtsis pas
NK107(tse)001:9989: na mi 'grub pa rnams spangs la lhag ma ni
NK107(tse)001:9990: 'grub pa yin pas de nyid la gtad do phyi
NK107(tse)001:9991: rol ni sa chu me rlung 'byung ba'i gzugs ni
NK107(tse)001:9992: sa gru bzhi sam chu z+l+aum bo me gru gsum
NK107(tse)001:9993: rlung zla kham dag gis sa'i la sogs pa gzhi
NK107(tse)001:9994: nas gzung ste rnal 'byor pa rang gi dang bstun
NK107(tse)001:9995: nas rtsis kyi rim pa la mkhas par bya'o rang
NK107(tse)001:9996: rang gi 'byung ba ni chu zug pa dang sa
NK107(tse)001:9997: zug tu mthun pa dang de bzhin du byer ba
NK107(tse)001:9998: byer bar mthun pa de bzhin du sa zug dang
NK107(tse)001:9999: me zug tu mthun pa dang byer ba la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10000: pa kun la'o me zug dang rlung zug la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10001: pa'o de ltar 'byung ba'i sdebs ka yis pho mo
NK107(tse)001:10002: sdebs pa dang gzhan la yang rnal 'byor pa'i grogs
NK107(tse)001:10003: la sogs pa mthun pa yis tshe 'phel ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10004: dbang thang dar ba dang 'byung ba rgyas pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10005: rnams la bzung ste byas pas so so'i las kyi
NK107(tse)001:10006: bye brag 'grub pa ni de yang dang po skyes
NK107(tse)001:10007: pa'i dus na dus gang la skyes pa dang nyi
NK107(tse)001:10008: ma dang gza' dang skar ma dang zla ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:10009: shes pa ni rtsis kyi 'khor lo gang la yang
NK107(tse)001:10010: thogs pa med par shes so de ltar na dus
NK107(tse)001:10011: 'di tsam na na ba dang 'di tsam na 'chi
NK107(tse)001:10012: ba rnams ni shes par nges so de yang 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10013: ba'i gnas 'byed kyi skabs nas bshad do de ltar
NK107(tse)001:10014: rnal 'byor pa rang dang gzhan gyi dus nges par
NK107(tse)001:10015: dpyad pas nges par rtsis kyi 'khor lo 'grub pa'o
NK107(tse)001:10016: zhes gsum pa 'byung ba'i las kyi 'phel 'grib kyis
NK107(tse)001:10017: rnams bstan nas da ni bzhi pa lo zla zhag
NK107(tse)001:10018: gi rim pa la brten nas 'gro ba'i las dang
NK107(tse)001:10019: nyi ma 'pho ba'i dus bstan pa ni de la
NK107(tse)001:10020: zla ba ni dgun zla ra ba la chu zug
NK107(tse)001:10021: pa sa bzung ngo 'bring po'i byer tha chung snyoms
NK107(tse)001:10022: pa'o dbyar zla ra ba me zug pa 'bring byer
NK107(tse)001:10023: tha chung snyoms pa'o dpyid zla ra ba sa zug
NK107(tse)001:10024: 'bring byer tha chung snyoms pa'o ston zla ra ba
NK107(tse)001:10025: rlung zug gnyis byer gsum pa snyoms pa'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:10026: 'byung ba bzhi la gsum gsum gyi grangs kyis brtsis
NK107(tse)001:10027: pas bcu gnyis la lo gcig ste de ltar zla
NK107(tse)001:10028: ba gcig la zhag bcu phrag sum la zla ba
NK107(tse)001:10029: gcig skar ma ni dgun zla ra ba'i mgo la
NK107(tse)001:10030: nya ba la sogs pa 'gres kyis shes par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:10031: de ltar zla ba gcig la zhag sum cu pa
NK107(tse)001:10032: la skar ma nyer brgyad pa las med pas zhag
NK107(tse)001:10033: gi 'jug pa cha gnyis med pas lo gcig la
NK107(tse)001:10034: res zhag nyer bzhi ldems pas ma tshang res rtsegs
NK107(tse)001:10035: mar 'gyur bas lhag par byed do zla ba re
NK107(tse)001:10036: la zhag gnyis kyis 'phel 'grib tu byed do de
NK107(tse)001:10037: nas lo gcig gi zhag gi rim pa brtsis na
NK107(tse)001:10038: nyin mo ring ba dang mtshan mo ring pa'i 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10039: la lo gcig la nyin mtshan mnyam pa'i dus gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10040: su 'gyur te de yang dgun 'bring po nas brtsis
NK107(tse)001:10041: pa'i zhag brgya dang brgyad bcu na nyin mtshan mnyam
NK107(tse)001:10042: pa'o 'di'i dus na dge sbyor bya ba ci dang
NK107(tse)001:10043: ci byas pa 'phel che'o khyad par ston mo byas
NK107(tse)001:10044: byas na dge ba 'grub bo 'di ni chu'i dbang
NK107(tse)001:10045: du brtsis pa'o rang bzhin du 'byung ba spyi'i khyab
NK107(tse)001:10046: byed du brtsis na ston gyi tha chung nas zhag
NK107(tse)001:10047: brgya dang brgyad cu na mnyam mo ston gyi tha
NK107(tse)001:10048: chung pa'i tshes gcig zhes bya ba nas gsum gsum
NK107(tse)001:10049: bzhi bzhi la sogs pa rnam par grags pa las
NK107(tse)001:10050: yar gyi ngo brgyad la mtshan mo ring ngo de
NK107(tse)001:10051: las yang nyin mo skyes pas de nas zhag brgya
NK107(tse)001:10052: dang brgyad cu'i mar ngo'i nyi shu brgyad la nyin
NK107(tse)001:10053: mo ring ngo de ltar nyin mtshan ring par byed
NK107(tse)001:10054: pa dang thung par byed pa'i rgyu ni 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10055: bzhi pho mo'i mtha' dbye ba las zug byed bcu
NK107(tse)001:10056: gnyis rim pa bzhin nyin mtshan la ring thung gi
NK107(tse)001:10057: khyad par du byung ste nyi ma log pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10058: ni dgun log me byer ba'i nyi ma'i dus kyang
NK107(tse)001:10059: me byer ba la ldog go de nas dbyar gyi
NK107(tse)001:10060: dang po'i sa zug pa'i nyi ma la sa zug
NK107(tse)001:10061: pa'i dus na dbyar ldog de ltar log pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10062: de mkhas pas bzung bas dge sbyor gyi 'phel 'grib
NK107(tse)001:10063: rnams shes par 'gyur ro de'i phyir ni nyin ring
NK107(tse)001:10064: pa'i dus na phal cher dge dang zhes pas 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10065: la mtshan mo'i ring pa'i dus na mi 'grub pas
NK107(tse)001:10066: thung pa'i dus na 'grub mtshan mo ring pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10067: na mi dge ba'i bya bas g.yengs pas mi 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10068: pas na de gnyis dbye ba shes pa ni gnad
NK107(tse)001:10069: do zhes bzhi pa lo zla zhag gi rim pa
NK107(tse)001:10070: la brten nas 'gro ba'i las dang nyi ma'i 'pho
NK107(tse)001:10071: dus bstan nas da ni lnga pa 'byung ba byer
NK107(tse)001:10072: zug gi 'gyur la brten nas 'byung ba brtsis kyi
NK107(tse)001:10073: 'grel bstan pa ni de ltar nyin mtshan bdun brgya
NK107(tse)001:10074: dang nyi shu'i 'dres kyis zhag la sum brgya dang
NK107(tse)001:10075: drug cur yang 'gyur ro de rnams zla ba bcu
NK107(tse)001:10076: gnyis te de la lo ste sa chu me rlung
NK107(tse)001:10077: bzhi la zug pa dang byer ba dang snyoms pa
NK107(tse)001:10078: dang gsum gsum ste zhag la yang dus bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10079: zhag gi rim pa la lo gcig la byer zug
NK107(tse)001:10080: gi las sum brgya dang drug cu 'byung ba bzhi
NK107(tse)001:10081: rdzogs pa la byer zug snyoms pa'i las bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10082: sbyar ro de ltar thams cad ni lo bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10083: dang zla ba dang dus dang byer zug gi rim
NK107(tse)001:10084: pa shes nas 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyis sems can
NK107(tse)001:10085: gyi rtsis kyi bskor mgo mi 'dra ba sum brgya
NK107(tse)001:10086: dang drug cu ni zhag re la brtsi ba la
NK107(tse)001:10087: dgongs la 'di gang zag 'di sgo brtsis 'dis mkhyen
NK107(tse)001:10088: pa rdzogs so zhes lnga pa 'byung ba byer zug
NK107(tse)001:10089: gi 'gyur ba la brten nas 'byung ba'i rtsis 'dral
NK107(tse)001:10090: bstan nas da ni drug pa phyi rol gyi 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10091: ba'i cho 'phrul la brten nas 'jig rten du dge
NK107(tse)001:10092: ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyi bye brag bstan
NK107(tse)001:10093: pa ni phyi rol gyi nam mkha' dang rlung dang
NK107(tse)001:10094: sa g.yo ba dang ltas ngan gyi cho 'phrul rnams
NK107(tse)001:10095: la brtags las dge ba dang mi dge ba'i bye
NK107(tse)001:10096: brag ston pa ni 'og nas zhib tu ston no
NK107(tse)001:10097: de yang gang las byung zhe na nyin mtshan ring
NK107(tse)001:10098: ba dang thung bar 'gyur ba'i rnam grangs kyis las
NK107(tse)001:10099: 'gyur ba las 'byung ba bzhi po'i lo bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10100: po'i dus tshod du sbyar bas nges par 'grub bo
NK107(tse)001:10101: lo ni 'byung ba so so'i 'gres dang sbyar te
NK107(tse)001:10102: bzung bar bya'o de la cho 'phrul nam byung gi
NK107(tse)001:10103: dus na mgo la rang dus ni 'byung ba bzhi'i
NK107(tse)001:10104: byer zug snyoms pa'i las kyi dus mnyam par sbyar
NK107(tse)001:10105: nas brtsi ba ni gnad do de yang gzhan du
NK107(tse)001:10106: brtsi ba ma yin te lo gang shar ba'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10107: tshod dang zla ba'i 'gyur ba brtags la rlung nag
NK107(tse)001:10108: chen po 'byung ba dang 'od dang sgra chen po
NK107(tse)001:10109: 'byung ba dang sa g.yos te phyogs bzung ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10110: gzugs brnyan gyis rnam pa byung ba dang nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:10111: dag ni yal lugs dang drug gis shar lho la
NK107(tse)001:10112: sogs pa'i phyogs bzung ste gang nas 'byung so so'i
NK107(tse)001:10113: phyogs dang nges par bstun nas brtsis par bzung bas
NK107(tse)001:10114: rgyal khams su sad 'ong ba'i dus dang char chen
NK107(tse)001:10115: po 'ong ba dang char chad par sangs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:10116: mu ge 'byung ba dang nad 'byung ba'i dus dang
NK107(tse)001:10117: gdon gyi rigs mi 'dra ba 'di lta bu 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10118: ba'i dus dang brtsod pa chen po 'byung bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10119: ba dang ri khri zhes bya ste yul mthon po
NK107(tse)001:10120: la sogs pa'i 'gro ba g.yo ba ni gong ma
NK107(tse)001:10121: so so'i dus su de'i rigs pas shes so gzhan
NK107(tse)001:10122: rgyal po la ngan pa dang dmangs la ngan pa
NK107(tse)001:10123: dang dge sbyong la ngan pa dang btsun mo rnams
NK107(tse)001:10124: la ngan pa dang rgyal po'i blon po rnams la
NK107(tse)001:10125: ngan pa dang pan ti ta rnams la ngan pa
NK107(tse)001:10126: dang de bzhin rgan pa rnams la ngan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:10127: gzhon pa rnams la ngan pa dang phyugs pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:10128: la ngan pa dang gzhan yang byol song gi bye
NK107(tse)001:10129: brag rnams la ngan pa dang de bzhin du skyes
NK107(tse)001:10130: pa rnams dang bud med kyi gzugs su gyur pa
NK107(tse)001:10131: rnams la ngan pa dang shing thog dang lo thog
NK107(tse)001:10132: rnams la ngan pa dang rtsi thog rnams la ngan
NK107(tse)001:10133: pa dang de yang de dag rnams legs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:10134: nyes pa dang bzang ngan gyi rim pa rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:10135: pas shes par bya'o zhes dris lan so dgu pa
NK107(tse)001:10136: 'byung ba'i brtsis sbyor gyi rim pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:10137: gang zag gi sgo brtsis bstan pa la yan lag
NK107(tse)001:10138: gi don drug du byas nas bstan no da ni
NK107(tse)001:10139: le'u dang po'i zhus don bzhi bcu pa 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10140: bzhi'i 'dod yon la bslab pa'i khyad par du sgra
NK107(tse)001:10141: bzhi'i rnal 'byor ji ltar brtsam pa bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:10142: yan lag gi don bzhis bstan pa'i dang po 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10143: ba'i bye brag gi sgo bstan pa la btud pa
NK107(tse)001:10144: la bstan zhing rgyu dag gis che ba nges par
NK107(tse)001:10145: bstan pa ni e ma ngo mtshar rmad du 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10146: ba yis zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te de
NK107(tse)001:10147: la e drag pa'i don no ma mnyam pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:10148: ngo mtshar thun mong ma yin pa'i don rmad du
NK107(tse)001:10149: 'byung ba zhes pa khyad par bstan pa'i don no
NK107(tse)001:10150: de yang phyi 'byung ba bzhi la brten pa'i bde
NK107(tse)001:10151: ba 'di lta bu rab tu zab pa'i don bstan
NK107(tse)001:10152: pa gzhan du tshig tsam du ma grags pa yang
NK107(tse)001:10153: nas yang du gsang ba bla na med pa nyid
NK107(tse)001:10154: rab tu gsang ba'i don 'di lha'i bu dga' byed
NK107(tse)001:10155: dbang phyug khyod rdzogs pa chen po'i skal ldan yin
NK107(tse)001:10156: par khyod ngo mtshar che bas na gzhan su la
NK107(tse)001:10157: ma bstan pa 'di khyod kyi ngo mi tshogs pas
NK107(tse)001:10158: na khyod la bshad par bya'o zhes bshad par dam
NK107(tse)001:10159: bcas so de la dad pa dang ldan pa'i 'gro
NK107(tse)001:10160: ba mchog tu theg pa chen po la mos pa
NK107(tse)001:10161: rdzogs pa chen po'i skal ba dang ldan pa brtson
NK107(tse)001:10162: 'grus can 'jig rten 'di'i bya ba dang don gyis
NK107(tse)001:10163: 'khor ba'i rnam pa yid la byed pa dang bral
NK107(tse)001:10164: ba yis 'di nyid nyams su len pa'i thog ma
NK107(tse)001:10165: rang gi bla ma la mchod pa rgya chen po
NK107(tse)001:10166: bya ba dang gzhan yang 'gro ba sems can la
NK107(tse)001:10167: zas la sogs pa dag gtong ba dang mkha' 'gro
NK107(tse)001:10168: ma dang chos skyong la tshogs dang gtor mas mnyes
NK107(tse)001:10169: par bya ste de nas rkyen gyis mi gnod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10170: dgon par song la 'jig rten 'di'i las dang so
NK107(tse)001:10171: nams kyi bya ba btang la lus dal ba brten
NK107(tse)001:10172: ngag tu smra ba gcad sems rnam par rtog pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10173: bya ba kun 'khor dang longs spyod la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:10174: spangs la bsgrub bo rlung yin na rlung la de
NK107(tse)001:10175: ltar rnal 'byor pa so so'i lus dang bstun cing
NK107(tse)001:10176: de rnams dang nges par sbyar te 'byung ba so
NK107(tse)001:10177: so'i ni chu la gsum dang sa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:10178: gsum gsum gyi go rim gyis ni 'byung ba'i lus
NK107(tse)001:10179: la bya'o dngos po'i gzugs ni sa dang chu dang
NK107(tse)001:10180: me dang rlung dngos po dang bcas pa ma nges
NK107(tse)001:10181: par bslab par bya'o de yang chu gcig tu rang
NK107(tse)001:10182: la yang gzugs la bslab pa dang sgra dang dri
NK107(tse)001:10183: dang ro la bslab pa la sogs 'byung ba'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:10184: yig nas ston no lhag ma gnyis po yang so
NK107(tse)001:10185: so'i 'dod pa'i yon tan la thog ma gang yin
NK107(tse)001:10186: pa la sgra nas btsam ste bslab par bya'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:10187: yan lag gi don dang po 'byung ba'i 'dod yon
NK107(tse)001:10188: gyi sgo bstan pa bsdud pa la gdams shing rgyud
NK107(tse)001:10189: kyi che ba nges par bstan nas da ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10190: pa 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la bslab pa phan yon
NK107(tse)001:10191: dang bcas pa bstan pa ni de yang 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10192: yon tan las khyad par du gyur pa sgra la
NK107(tse)001:10193: bslab ces pa'o de yang rnal ma lus kyi gnad
NK107(tse)001:10194: la brten nas nyams su len pa'o 'byor pa ni
NK107(tse)001:10195: 'byung ba'i sgra la slob pa'i tshe na rdzas kyi
NK107(tse)001:10196: bye brag dang rang gi 'tshogs rnams 'tshogs par byed
NK107(tse)001:10197: pa'o de yang gang rung rung gis ma yin la
NK107(tse)001:10198: rdzogs pa chen po'i skal ba dang ldan pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:10199: gis bsgrub ces pa'o de yang bdag lus me yin
NK107(tse)001:10200: na me'i sgra la bslab ste tsan dan la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10201: pa'i shing mang po rab tu dben pa'i phyogs su
NK107(tse)001:10202: song la rang la dgos pa'i rdzas dang yo byad
NK107(tse)001:10203: la bgegs bskrad cing byin gyis bslabs pa'i sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:10204: bya'o de nas shing gis me bya ste mgo 'jug
NK107(tse)001:10205: ma log par bslangs te btser la me rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:10206: bsod nams dang ldan pa'am blon po'am su bsod nams
NK107(tse)001:10207: che ba la bslangs te me sbar la rang kha
NK107(tse)001:10208: shar phyogs su bltas te lus glang po che nyal
NK107(tse)001:10209: ba ltar byas la dngos po dkar ba dang sngo
NK107(tse)001:10210: nag dang ser gsal dang dmar gdangs la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:10211: so so ni zhi ba dang rgyas pa dang dbang
NK107(tse)001:10212: dang mngon spyod rnams ji ltar 'grub pa'i kha dog
NK107(tse)001:10213: dang zhes zhi ba la dkar rgyas pa la ser
NK107(tse)001:10214: dbang la dmar ste mngon spyod sngo zhes pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:10215: nas me'i dbyibs la brtags pa ni sna tshogs mtshon
NK107(tse)001:10216: cha'i 'khor lo dang mchod rten brtsegs pa dang pad+ma'i
NK107(tse)001:10217: dbyibs gdugs dang rgyal mtshan 'gro ba'i gzugs thun mong
NK107(tse)001:10218: rnams ni 'grub pa'i rtags 'khor lo rdo rje rin
NK107(tse)001:10219: po che pad ma ral gri be con dang lha'i
NK107(tse)001:10220: sku dang po thi dang dung dang brtsegs shing 'khyil
NK107(tse)001:10221: ba'o dbyibs mchog bya ba rdzogs par 'grub ces pa'o
NK107(tse)001:10222: legs par mig ma yengs par brtags la dngos grub
NK107(tse)001:10223: kyi bye brag gang byung ba la spyod de la
NK107(tse)001:10224: thun mong ni mi snang ba dang bcud kyis len
NK107(tse)001:10225: pa dang ri lu dang sa 'og dang mig sman
NK107(tse)001:10226: dang mkha' spyod dang rkang mgyogs dang 'byung ba lnga
NK107(tse)001:10227: dbang du 'dus pa'o mchog gi bsgrub pa ni sprul
NK107(tse)001:10228: sku dang chos sku longs sku dang ngo bo nyid
NK107(tse)001:10229: kyi sku dang bzhi las mthong ba rnam par dag
NK107(tse)001:10230: pa rnams dang shes pa rnam par dag pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:10231: dang thob pa rnam par dag pa rnams dang rtogs
NK107(tse)001:10232: pa rnam par dag pa rnams ni rab dang sbyar
NK107(tse)001:10233: ro de nas so so'i sgra la sbyangs pa ni
NK107(tse)001:10234: 'byung bzhi'i gnad yig dang gsang ba'i yi ge ru
NK107(tse)001:10235: barda'o 'byung ba'i sgra la nges pa'i so so'i rtags
NK107(tse)001:10236: tshad la nges par phebs te 'byongs pa yis lhag
NK107(tse)001:10237: ma gzugs la sogs pa rnams la brtsam pas 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10238: bo yang na 'byung ba gang rung gcig gi sgra
NK107(tse)001:10239: la 'byongs pas lhag ma'i sgra rnams la nges par
NK107(tse)001:10240: brtsam pa tsam gyis 'grub bo zhes gnyis pa 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10241: ba bzhi'i sgra la bslab pa phan yon dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:10242: pa bstan nas da ni gsum pa sgra don la
NK107(tse)001:10243: bslab pa'i rtags dang tshad bstan pa ni de ltar
NK107(tse)001:10244: ni gong ma la bslab pas phyi rol ni sa
NK107(tse)001:10245: chu me rlung gi sgra la sogs pa'i 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10246: bzhi la bslab pas ni 'dir ni brtson 'grus kyi
NK107(tse)001:10247: khyad par gyis rab la zhag rang gi lo grangs
NK107(tse)001:10248: tsam gyis 'grub pa yang yod 'bring la zla ba
NK107(tse)001:10249: rang gi lo grangs tsam gyis 'grub tha ma la
NK107(tse)001:10250: lo rang gi lo grangs tsam gyis 'grub pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:10251: kyis 'grub pa so so'i tshad yin la rtags ni
NK107(tse)001:10252: dngos kyis shes pas na 'grub bo zhes gsum pa
NK107(tse)001:10253: sgra don la bslab pa'i rtags tshad bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:10254: ni bzhi pa so so'i sgra don la bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10255: 'bras bu dang sgra'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:10256: ltar su yis bsgrub pa la sogs pa'i tshig lnga
NK107(tse)001:10257: gzhung gis shes so sgra la sogs pa'i dbye ba
NK107(tse)001:10258: ni zhes pa chu'i sgra la yang sgra gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10259: dus la bsam pa'i sbyor ba rnams shes la 'jug
NK107(tse)001:10260: pa'i dus la las dang las kyi bye brag shes
NK107(tse)001:10261: sgra 'byung ba'i dus su 'chi 'pho dang skye ba
NK107(tse)001:10262: rnams shes sgra bzlog pa'i dus kyis rang gi rtogs
NK107(tse)001:10263: pa dang ye shes kyi tshad zin pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:10264: sgra'i dus bzhi'i nyin bzhi mtshan bzhi brgyad du bartsi'o
NK107(tse)001:10265: de ltar 'byung 'jug gnas ldog so so'i bye brag
NK107(tse)001:10266: la brten nas 'di sngon du 'jig rten thun mong
NK107(tse)001:10267: las kyi sbyor ka ni sgra byung ba'i dus la
NK107(tse)001:10268: mkha' 'gro ma'i sgra shes te de shes pas thun
NK107(tse)001:10269: mong gis rnam grangs dpag tu med pa la spyod
NK107(tse)001:10270: do 'jug pa'i dus rigs drug gi skad shes te
NK107(tse)001:10271: de las bye brag tu 'byung ba lha rnams kyi
NK107(tse)001:10272: shes 'jug pa la lha min dang mi rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:10273: shes gnas pa byol song rnams kyi bzlog pa la
NK107(tse)001:10274: dmyal ba yi dwags gnyis kyis shes so yang gnas
NK107(tse)001:10275: pa'i dus na 'byung ba chu dang sa'i sgra shes
NK107(tse)001:10276: so bzlog pa'i dus na me dang rlung gi so
NK107(tse)001:10277: so'i skad rnams la brten nas nang du mngon par
NK107(tse)001:10278: shes pa drug 'grub bo thun mong gi las 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:10279: dus khams kyi zas dang bral ba dang gos dang
NK107(tse)001:10280: bral nas gcer bur 'gro ba dang 'byung bzhi'i sa
NK107(tse)001:10281: chu'i sgras mi 'bying pa dang mes mi tshig pa
NK107(tse)001:10282: dang rlung gis mi 'khyer ba dang sas ri brag
NK107(tse)001:10283: rnams la zang thal bar 'gyur ba dang de rnams
NK107(tse)001:10284: dang bral nas nam mkha' la dbang bsgyur te bya
NK107(tse)001:10285: bzhin du 'gyur ro lus kyi sha khrag rang ka
NK107(tse)001:10286: mar 'gyu 'dzin pa'i 'byung ba bzhi zad pa dang
NK107(tse)001:10287: kun gyis mthong bar me'i 'grib ma bzhin du zang
NK107(tse)001:10288: thal du mthong ba dag tu 'gyur ro de ltar
NK107(tse)001:10289: 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra don la sbyangs pa'i gnad kyis
NK107(tse)001:10290: rgas pa'i lus 'pho ba gnyer ma dang skra dkar
NK107(tse)001:10291: la sogs pa med cing rab tu gzhon pa'i sha
NK107(tse)001:10292: dang ldan par 'gyur ro shi ba'i sdug basngala dang
NK107(tse)001:10293: bral nye bar bral nas tshe nyi zla gnyis ji
NK107(tse)001:10294: srid gnas pa'i bar la gnas par dag tu 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10295: zhing de nyid dang mnyam par 'gyur ro 'di la
NK107(tse)001:10296: dus ji tsam na 'gyu ba chen mo'i rlung chen
NK107(tse)001:10297: mo'i rlung phyi nang du 'gyu ba'i dbugs ni rgyun
NK107(tse)001:10298: chad nas lus kyang yod pa'i 'du shes dang bral
NK107(tse)001:10299: la 'di'i dus na mchog gi las khyad par can
NK107(tse)001:10300: gyi stobs kyis rnam par rtog pa thams cad kyang
NK107(tse)001:10301: 'gag par nges so de ltar chags pas mi rtog
NK107(tse)001:10302: pa'i bsam gtan rang gi rgyud la brten nas chos
NK107(tse)001:10303: kyi dbyings kyi stong pa nyid dang 'di nas shin
NK107(tse)001:10304: tu nye bar dbyings rig gnyis sbyor ba'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:10305: slar 'jig rten du thun mong gi rang rgyud pa
NK107(tse)001:10306: ltar lus bzung nas de nas sems can dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:10307: med pa'i don byas nas yang lus 'di nyid du
NK107(tse)001:10308: zad par byas nas 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs
NK107(tse)001:10309: med pa khams gsum du 'byung ba bzhi la sbyangs
NK107(tse)001:10310: pa'i mi 'di ldog pa ma yin no zhes zhus
NK107(tse)001:10311: lan bzhi bcu pa 'byung ba bzhi'i 'dod yon la
NK107(tse)001:10312: bslab pa khyad par du sgra bzhi'i rnal 'byor bstan
NK107(tse)001:10313: pa la yan lag gi don gzhir byas nas bstan
NK107(tse)001:10314: nas da ni le'u dang po'i zhus don bzhi bcu
NK107(tse)001:10315: rtsa gcig pa spo ba'i las khyad par can rnal
NK107(tse)001:10316: 'byor gyi khyad par gyi 'jug pa dngos po dang
NK107(tse)001:10317: stong pa'i yal bas ji ltar 'dod pa'i don grub
NK107(tse)001:10318: par bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis
NK107(tse)001:10319: bstan pa'i dang po dngos po la spo ba'i las
NK107(tse)001:10320: ji ltar spos pa bstan pa ni spo ba'i tshig
NK107(tse)001:10321: rang 'di nyid kyis shes so dngos po gzugs ni
NK107(tse)001:10322: dngos po rags pa bem po dang rig sha khrag
NK107(tse)001:10323: gis bsdus pa'o de ltar 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra don
NK107(tse)001:10324: la 'byongs nas da gang du yang dmigs pa bsgyur
NK107(tse)001:10325: bas 'grub ste de nas sdod 'pho ba chen mo'i
NK107(tse)001:10326: rlung la goms pa brtan pa byas na de nyid
NK107(tse)001:10327: las su rung na gong ma'i 'byung bzhi'i sgra la
NK107(tse)001:10328: ma goms kyang 'grub bo rlung de dag 'byongs pa
NK107(tse)001:10329: dang rang sa'i cho ga ni dngos po'i gzugs can
NK107(tse)001:10330: ni bem po dang rigs bcas te de las shing
NK107(tse)001:10331: bu dang rde'u dang gseg ma la sogs pa gang
NK107(tse)001:10332: rung ba gcig la rnal 'byor pa rlung 'byongs pa
NK107(tse)001:10333: de'i shes pa bcug pa tsam gyis don de nyid
NK107(tse)001:10334: 'gul bar nus pa'am 'dar sig sig pa dag 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10335: ngo de ltar byung tsam na dngos po la spo
NK107(tse)001:10336: ba'i las 'grub bo de las khyad par du dngos
NK107(tse)001:10337: po'i gzugs can thams cad la gtad pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:10338: 'grub ste de nas dngos po'i spo ba tsam mo
NK107(tse)001:10339: 'di ni gang la shes pa bcug pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:10340: pha rol gyi nor zas la sogs pa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:10341: kyang rang gi dbang du bya ba la the tshom
NK107(tse)001:10342: med do zhes dang po dngos po la ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:10343: spo ba bstan nas da ni gnyis pa stong pa
NK107(tse)001:10344: la spo ba sems kyi khyad par gyi las bstan
NK107(tse)001:10345: pa ni stong pa zhes bya ba da res yid
NK107(tse)001:10346: kyi spyod yul du gyur tshad la bya'o 'di nyid
NK107(tse)001:10347: la spo ba rnal 'byor pa'i rang sems kyi goms
NK107(tse)001:10348: pa gtso che ba yin pas na sems lung sgoms
NK107(tse)001:10349: khrigs la sbyangs pa'am sems kyi dmigs drug la sbyang
NK107(tse)001:10350: bar bya'o de la chos kyi sku stong pa ngo
NK107(tse)001:10351: bo ngos bzung du ma grub pas mtha' stongs pas
NK107(tse)001:10352: dkyil ma dmigs la dkyil stongs pas mtha' ma dmigs
NK107(tse)001:10353: so de nyid kyi ngang las bcos med rang gsal
NK107(tse)001:10354: ba las chos nyid rang snang ba las chos kyi
NK107(tse)001:10355: sku'o de tha dad pa ma yin pas gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:10356: med dngos dang dngos ma yin pa las 'das pas
NK107(tse)001:10357: grub bya gang du yang mi sbyor la de yang
NK107(tse)001:10358: ngo bo stong pas gzugs can ma yin pa rang
NK107(tse)001:10359: bzhin gyis stong pas rgyun chad ma yin pa thugs
NK107(tse)001:10360: rjes stong par shes pas ris med mnyam pa chen
NK107(tse)001:10361: po'i dal las ma 'das pa'o de ltar rgyun chad
NK107(tse)001:10362: phyang chad dang mtha' dgag stong par ma song bas
NK107(tse)001:10363: chos thams cad stong pa nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK107(tse)001:10364: gsal ba'i rang bzhin las rnal 'byor pa'i sems kyang
NK107(tse)001:10365: ris med phyogs lhung med pa'i ngang chos kun stong
NK107(tse)001:10366: pa rang dag pa'i gzhi gnas pa la 'gag pa
NK107(tse)001:10367: med pas cir snang chos nyid du gtan la phebs
NK107(tse)001:10368: sna tshogs rang sar grol bas 'bad rtsol dang skyar
NK107(tse)001:10369: gzhi med pa'o dus thams cad du de'i ngang la
NK107(tse)001:10370: gnas pas da de las bcos su med pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:10371: yang nyid chu yin na sngon du chu'i sbyang ba
NK107(tse)001:10372: byas la de nas brten pa chos nyid 'bral ba
NK107(tse)001:10373: sems nyid cho ga sems nyid dbyer med pa de
NK107(tse)001:10374: yang lus gang yin pa'i rten 'brel lan lnga dang
NK107(tse)001:10375: bdun du rdzogs pa yis rnal 'byor pa'i lus la
NK107(tse)001:10376: nad yod na pha rol gyi lus la spo ste
NK107(tse)001:10377: de yang skye pa la spo na g.yas brkyang pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10378: stangs stabs bya bud med la spo na rkyang pa'o
NK107(tse)001:10379: de nyid byas pas de la skad 'ong ste barjoda
NK107(tse)001:10380: pa las shes par bya ste las kyi khyad par
NK107(tse)001:10381: gyis 'bras bu nges par thob pa'o so so'i 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10382: ba ni sa lus pa dang phrad pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10383: pa'i lus nang phrad pa yis de nyid mthong ba
NK107(tse)001:10384: tsam gyis rang gi nad kho la 'pho bar bya
NK107(tse)001:10385: ste 'jug pa dang 'pho ba'i las nges par 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10386: bo gal te 'pho bar 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK107(tse)001:10387: byol song dag gi gzugs mthong na rlung kha sna
NK107(tse)001:10388: dang sbyar te rlung la mkhas pas spo'o 'on te
NK107(tse)001:10389: dngos grub la mchog gi dngos grub la thug na
NK107(tse)001:10390: 'di'i dus na rang gi lus mi snang bar 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10391: te de'i gzugs su song ba tsam gyis las 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10392: bo gal te zhen pa can dngos po la chags
NK107(tse)001:10393: pa'i rdzas mthong na de nyid spo ba'i sbyor ba
NK107(tse)001:10394: byas te rang gi bla ma la mchod pa bya
NK107(tse)001:10395: ba'i phyir spo bas blang ngo gzhan du rang 'dod
NK107(tse)001:10396: pa'i sems kyis bya ba ma yin no de bzhin
NK107(tse)001:10397: du yang lus spo la bdag dang lus mthun pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10398: gzhon pa'i ro'i gzugs la sogs pa la yang rang
NK107(tse)001:10399: gi lus spo ba rang gi bla ma dpa' bo
NK107(tse)001:10400: dang 'dra bas 'phos shig par bka' stsol na rnal
NK107(tse)001:10401: 'byor pa rlung la goms pas 'di yang 'di'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10402: su dgug pa'i sems dang ldan pa yin no the
NK107(tse)001:10403: tshom mi za bas bya'o 'di yang rlung gis sbyor
NK107(tse)001:10404: ba dang chos nyid dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK107(tse)001:10405: ni spo bar bya'o zhes zhus don zhe gcig pa
NK107(tse)001:10406: spo ba'i lus khyad par can bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:10407: lag gi don gnyis su byas nas bstan no da
NK107(tse)001:10408: ni le'u dang po'i dris lan zhe gnyis pa lus
NK107(tse)001:10409: rnam par bzhag pa rig bcas las kyi spo ba
NK107(tse)001:10410: khyad par can la brten nas lus rang bzhin gyi
NK107(tse)001:10411: rten 'brel gyis spo ba'i las khyad par can bstan
NK107(tse)001:10412: pa la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10413: dang po srog dang bcas pa la spo ba khyad
NK107(tse)001:10414: par can gyi las bstan pa ni rig bcas la
NK107(tse)001:10415: spo ba dang bem po la spo bar 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10416: rnal 'byor pa rdzogs pa chen po'i skal ba chen
NK107(tse)001:10417: po yod pa 'gro ba rig pa dang bcas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10418: sems kyis bsdus pa la 'byung ba spo ba'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:10419: ji ltar bya ba dang de yang phyi bem po
NK107(tse)001:10420: las nang 'byung ba sha khrag gi gzugs su snang
NK107(tse)001:10421: ba'i sems can srog chags rnams la 'byung ba'i gnad
NK107(tse)001:10422: la brten nas spo bar 'dod na nang chu yin
NK107(tse)001:10423: na phyi rol chu dang mthun pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:10424: bzhi'i rim pa la las ni phral gyi las la
NK107(tse)001:10425: brten nas phugs kyi lhung bar 'gyur ba dag gis
NK107(tse)001:10426: lus ngag yid gsum du khrid la de la ni
NK107(tse)001:10427: chos nyid kyi gnad bya'o rnal 'byor pa rang gi
NK107(tse)001:10428: lus la 'byung gdon gyi nad tsha ba dang grangs
NK107(tse)001:10429: ba las khyad par du 'gyur pa rlung mkhris bad
NK107(tse)001:10430: kan 'dus pa bzhi la sogs pa'i nad tha dad
NK107(tse)001:10431: pa la sogs pa 'gro ba gzhan gyi lus la
NK107(tse)001:10432: 'pho ba'i las khyad par can byed na rang dang
NK107(tse)001:10433: mthun pa'i 'byung ba'i lus mthong na rlung dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:10434: pa'i rig pa bcug na rang gi nad gang yin
NK107(tse)001:10435: pa pha rol la de ltar spo bas nad kyi
NK107(tse)001:10436: dngos po las grol bar nges so 'di dag ni
NK107(tse)001:10437: rlung sbyang ba'i yan lag tu gal che'o sems can
NK107(tse)001:10438: gzhan la don byed na ni so so'i rten 'brel
NK107(tse)001:10439: gyi 'khor lo'i sbyor bas bya'o zhes dang po srog
NK107(tse)001:10440: dang bcas pa la rang gi nad spo ba khyad
NK107(tse)001:10441: par can gyis las bstan nas da ni gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:10442: rten 'brel gyi 'khor lo dmigs pa gtso ba'i khyad
NK107(tse)001:10443: par la brten nas bem po la spo ba'i khyad
NK107(tse)001:10444: par gyi bya ba bstan pa ni bem po ni
NK107(tse)001:10445: rnam par shes byed du ma 'gyur ba 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10446: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung bzhi dag las
NK107(tse)001:10447: dngos por sa'i 'dus pa'i rten 'brel dngos po la
NK107(tse)001:10448: brten pa'i rten 'brel bya'o de yang sa'i rigs mi
NK107(tse)001:10449: 'dra ba rang gi lo grangs tsam zhig bya ba
NK107(tse)001:10450: dang sa phung de snyed du bya ba dang gtor
NK107(tse)001:10451: ba dang blugs pa dang spo ba dang phyar ba
NK107(tse)001:10452: dang 'phang ba dang gcig nas gcig tu spo ba
NK107(tse)001:10453: dang bsre ba dang chu la bskur ba dang mer
NK107(tse)001:10454: da bo ba dang sa'i dong bya ba dang 'di
NK107(tse)001:10455: ltar go rim gyis dus bcu gnyis su sbyar nas
NK107(tse)001:10456: byas pas rang bzhin du 'byung ba'i nad las grol
NK107(tse)001:10457: bar nges so gal te de dag gis ma grol
NK107(tse)001:10458: na lo bcu gnyis kyi gzugs byas te 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:10459: kha dog gis bsgyur la ngag tu gcig gcig gcig
NK107(tse)001:10460: zhes grangs med par barjoda cing rang gang du na
NK107(tse)001:10461: ba'i yul la btug cing pha rol dang rang 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10462: ba mthun pa la dmigs pa gtad cing byas pas
NK107(tse)001:10463: 'byung ba'i nad gzhan la 'pho bar nges so chu
NK107(tse)001:10464: la sogs pa sum po la yang de'i 'gres kyis
NK107(tse)001:10465: shes par bya'o gal te ngag gi sbyor bas gzhan
NK107(tse)001:10466: la spo bar 'dod na rang las 'pho ba'i dmigs
NK107(tse)001:10467: pa rang las 'phos pa'i dmigs pa dang ma bral
NK107(tse)001:10468: bar byas la ngag tu gcig gcig gcig zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:10469: dang bcu bcu zhes pa dang nyi shu nyi shu
NK107(tse)001:10470: zhes pa dang sum cu sum cu bzhi bcu bzhi
NK107(tse)001:10471: bcu lnga bcu lnga bcu zhes pa dang drug cu
NK107(tse)001:10472: dang bdun bcu dang brgyad bcu dang dgu bcu dang
NK107(tse)001:10473: brgya brgya zhes pa dang stong stong khri khri 'bum
NK107(tse)001:10474: 'bum dang bye ba bye ba sa ya sa ya
NK107(tse)001:10475: dung phyur dung phyur khrag khrig khrag khrig nyal nyil
NK107(tse)001:10476: nyal nyil grangs med grangs med thar ther thar ther
NK107(tse)001:10477: phyal phyol phyal phyol yal yol yal yol barjoda med
NK107(tse)001:10478: barjoda med zhes grangs rnams dang brda' lus dang ngag
NK107(tse)001:10479: dang yid la sogs pa yis bya'o skad ni gong
NK107(tse)001:10480: du bstan pa'i tshangs pa la sogs pa yis bya'o
NK107(tse)001:10481: dmigs pa chu la chu bur du bsgyur sa la
NK107(tse)001:10482: rlangs par bsgyur me la dud pa rlung la na
NK107(tse)001:10483: bun ltar bsgyur te rang gi nad 'gro ba gzhan
NK107(tse)001:10484: nam bem po la sogs pa la spo'o yang dngos
NK107(tse)001:10485: po shing bu la sogs pa dngos po'i rdzas de
NK107(tse)001:10486: gang la spo ba de nyid kyi ming nas grangs
NK107(tse)001:10487: med pa barjoda cing rgyab tu bor ba dang de
NK107(tse)001:10488: bzhin du mdun dang g.yas g.yon du bor ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10489: bskor ba'i tshul gyis bor ba dang phyi ba'i tshul
NK107(tse)001:10490: gyis dang 'phrog pa'i tshul gyis 'thor bas 'grub bo
NK107(tse)001:10491: 'byung ba chu la spo na chu chu zhes mang
NK107(tse)001:10492: po barjoda cing bya'o de bzhin du lhag ma rnams
NK107(tse)001:10493: la yang bya'o sems can gzhan gyi spo bar 'dod
NK107(tse)001:10494: na gang la spo ba'i las byed pa de mgo
NK107(tse)001:10495: 'jug bsgyur ba dang dum bur bcag pa dang bslang
NK107(tse)001:10496: ba dang bsnyal ba dang sbyi ba dang rang gi
NK107(tse)001:10497: lus btugs shing bsgyur ba dang 'gro ba gzhan ser
NK107(tse)001:10498: sna can dag mthong na dmigs pa dag pa'i spo
NK107(tse)001:10499: bas bslang ste rang gi bla ma la dbul bar
NK107(tse)001:10500: bya'o rnal 'byor pa rang gi sems la dmigs pa
NK107(tse)001:10501: gsal ba byas na rten 'brel gyis bya ba ma
NK107(tse)001:10502: log par byas nas nges par 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK107(tse)001:10503: lhag ma ni gzhung gis shes so zhes dris lan
NK107(tse)001:10504: zhe gnyis pa rig bcas kyi spo ba khyad par
NK107(tse)001:10505: can la brten nas lus kyi rang bzhin khyad par
NK107(tse)001:10506: can bstan pa la yan lag gi don gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:10507: byas nas bstan nas da ni le'u dang po'i dris
NK107(tse)001:10508: lan zhe gsum pa lus kyi nad gdon pa khyad
NK107(tse)001:10509: par can la brten nas rnal 'byor gyi bar chad
NK107(tse)001:10510: nye bar zhi ba'i gnad bstan pa la yan lag
NK107(tse)001:10511: gi don gsum gyis byas pa'i dang po nad so
NK107(tse)001:10512: so'i dbye ba la brten nas khyad par gyi gdon
NK107(tse)001:10513: thabs bstan pa ni de yang bya ba'i rgyud dang
NK107(tse)001:10514: gnyis ka'i rgyud dang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang bskyed
NK107(tse)001:10515: pa'i dang rdzogs pa'i dang rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:10516: gzhan kun tu ma bshad pa'i gnad 'byung ba las
NK107(tse)001:10517: kyi 'khor lo la brten nas lus kyi sdug basngala
NK107(tse)001:10518: las grol bar byed pa ni 'byung ba sa'i brtan
NK107(tse)001:10519: 'gyur ba las bad kan gyi nad du 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:10520: yang yod do 'di phal cher 'dus pa'i nad du
NK107(tse)001:10521: 'gro ba yin no chu'i sdud 'gyur ba las bad
NK107(tse)001:10522: kan gyi nad du 'gro ba yang me'i smin 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10523: ba las mkhris nad du 'gro rlung gi khyad 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10524: ba las rlung gi nad du 'agro'o nad de rnams
NK107(tse)001:10525: rlung gi grangs ba'i nad kyis lus kyi khog gi
NK107(tse)001:10526: nad las grol la shes pas ldog pas lus phyi'i
NK107(tse)001:10527: nad las grol bar byed pa'o de lta bu'i don
NK107(tse)001:10528: zab mo nges par bshad kyis nyon zhes sdud pa
NK107(tse)001:10529: po la gdams pa'o rlung dang zhes pa la dbye
NK107(tse)001:10530: na rlung gi rlung dang bad kan dang 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:10531: dang mkhris pa bazhi'o de bzhin du lhag ma gsum
NK107(tse)001:10532: la yang ngo 'dus pa'i dbang du byas na rlung
NK107(tse)001:10533: mkhris gnyis 'dus pa dang de bzhin du gsum ka
NK107(tse)001:10534: 'dus pa yang 'ong ste gong ma'i bcu drug tu
NK107(tse)001:10535: phye ba las kun 'dus pa ni mi 'ongs te
NK107(tse)001:10536: bcu drug gi cha brtsis pa de'i phyed dang bcu
NK107(tse)001:10537: gnyis kyi cha las 'dus par 'gro ba ni nye
NK107(tse)001:10538: dus las nad zhugs pa'i mtshan nyid du rig par
NK107(tse)001:10539: bya'o de yang rim pas 'byung ba'i gnas dang 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10540: ba'i dus dang nges par sbyar na nad kyi nye
NK107(tse)001:10541: ba'i rgyu 'byung ba lus drag shul las te rlung
NK107(tse)001:10542: la brgya dang mkhris pa la brgya yis byed do
NK107(tse)001:10543: ring ba'i rgyu dang gnyis ni sems kyi dran pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10544: lto 'khrugs pa la gyur pa ste bad kan la
NK107(tse)001:10545: brgya dang 'dus pa la brgya tham pa sems las
NK107(tse)001:10546: byung ba'i nad du 'agro'o de gnyis las nad kyi
NK107(tse)001:10547: rkyen 'dod chags dang chang bag med pa 'thungs ba
NK107(tse)001:10548: dang lus khur drag po dang gnyid 'thug pa las
NK107(tse)001:10549: glo bur du bslang pa dang gdon pho mo las
NK107(tse)001:10550: 'gyur ba dang glo bur mtshon cha'i rkyen dang a
NK107(tse)001:10551: la dang sbrid pa las dang sems kyi sdug basngala
NK107(tse)001:10552: las gyur pa brgyad ni sems can gyi lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:10553: sdug basngala du byed pa'o de yang bsdu na tsha
NK107(tse)001:10554: ba dang grang ba'i nad gang yin pa ngos bzung
NK107(tse)001:10555: ste de yang phyi'i lus kyi kha dog la brtag
NK107(tse)001:10556: pa dang nang gi lus zas kyi phan gnod dang
NK107(tse)001:10557: gang na na ba'i yul dang de yang tsha grang
NK107(tse)001:10558: gnyis su zung sbyar la lus stod smad kyi phyi
NK107(tse)001:10559: nang la de yang phyi'i stod rlung gi yul nang
NK107(tse)001:10560: mkhris pa'i yul smad kyi 'dus pa'i yul nang bad
NK107(tse)001:10561: kan gyi yul lo yang yan lag rnams ni so
NK107(tse)001:10562: so'i rtags las mkhas pas dabye'o de yang khrag dang
NK107(tse)001:10563: chu ser nad kyi 'phel gyen 'thur 'khrug pa nad
NK107(tse)001:10564: kyi las gzeg dang 'khyig pa nad kyi lcags spo
NK107(tse)001:10565: zhing rdzings pa nad kyi gzhi 'khrus shing bzlog pa
NK107(tse)001:10566: nad kyi rlangs zug cing 'pho ba nad kyi 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:10567: ro myos shing tshig pa nad kyi gzer de stong
NK107(tse)001:10568: tsha ba'i yul yin smad grang ba'i grang gi gnad
NK107(tse)001:10569: ni gnyis pa'i yul yin pas de nyid dang sbyar
NK107(tse)001:10570: te rten 'brel gyi 'khor los bya'o zhes yan lag
NK107(tse)001:10571: dang po so so'i dbye ba la brten nas nad
NK107(tse)001:10572: kyi gdon thabs kyi gzhi bstan nas da ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10573: pa lus ngag yid kyi dbye gnad la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:10574: 'byung ba'i nad ji ltar gdon pa bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:10575: de yang lus kyi gnad ma shes na 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10576: bzhi'i nus pa 'byin mi nus ngag gi gnad ma
NK107(tse)001:10577: shes na rus dang rtsa la zhen pa'i nad phyir
NK107(tse)001:10578: mi thon no yid kyi gnad ma shes na bcud
NK107(tse)001:10579: pa las kyi mi khegs te de ltar na man
NK107(tse)001:10580: ngag gsum dang ldan pas lus kyi nad dang sems
NK107(tse)001:10581: kyi nad rnams 'don par nges so rnal 'byor pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10582: lus kyis 'khrul 'khor sna tshogs dang ni me'i lus
NK107(tse)001:10583: yin na smad na na lag pa 'gal me'i 'khor
NK107(tse)001:10584: lo ltar bya ba'o smad kyi rgyu ma gyen la
NK107(tse)001:10585: drang bar na na srin gyi nur 'gros su bya'o
NK107(tse)001:10586: yan lag la gyad kyi dor stabs su bya'o ngag
NK107(tse)001:10587: kyang go rim gyis ka ka zhes pa dang nya
NK107(tse)001:10588: ha zhes pa dang ha li hu li zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:10589: dang nga ngi ngu zhes pa'o dbang po'i nad la
NK107(tse)001:10590: lcags sdong kyi dril lugs dang ngag ha h+aa he
NK107(tse)001:10591: h+ae zhes pa'o sems de dag gis dngos po bzlog
NK107(tse)001:10592: pa la gtad do yang chu'i lus yin na sdod
NK107(tse)001:10593: la lus seng ge'i 'gying tshugs ngag 'dre sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:10594: pa'i skad bar la wa mo'i zur 'gros ngag stod
NK107(tse)001:10595: mgo'i ig skad smad la g.yang mo'i sprugs stangs ngag
NK107(tse)001:10596: tshangs pa'i skad yan lag skyes bu'i brgyangs stabs ngag
NK107(tse)001:10597: nam mkha' lding gi skad dbang po rnams la la
NK107(tse)001:10598: lus bya rgod kyi sbungs stangs ngag la e kring
NK107(tse)001:10599: e kring zhes pa sems nad kyi dngos po las
NK107(tse)001:10600: bzlog pa kun mthun no yang sa la sdod la
NK107(tse)001:10601: phog g.yas g.yon du bcud ngag a +aa +ai zhes
NK107(tse)001:10602: smad la rgyu ma rgyab tu phul ngag seng ge'i
NK107(tse)001:10603: ngar skad bar la brgya mdud kyi dril lugs ngag
NK107(tse)001:10604: phyang mo'i ngu skad yan lag la brkyang bskum gyi
NK107(tse)001:10605: las ngag grul bum gyi lcong skad dbang po rnams
NK107(tse)001:10606: la stag mo'i 'gyur stangs nga rgyal byin gyi 'dar
NK107(tse)001:10607: skad sems ni gong dang 'dra'o khyad par du rang
NK107(tse)001:10608: gi lus dang mthun pa'i 'byung ba la gtad do
NK107(tse)001:10609: rlung yin na smad la dpal mo'i mdung bskor ngag
NK107(tse)001:10610: srin mo'i 'khros skad smad sgeg mo'i zur 'gros bar
NK107(tse)001:10611: 'khor lo'i bskor thabs ngag mkha' 'gro ma'i 'dir skad
NK107(tse)001:10612: yan lag phyag rgya'i bsgyur tshul ngag la gtum chen
NK107(tse)001:10613: gyi rngam skad dbang po la lus seng ge'i sprugs
NK107(tse)001:10614: kyi 'phyongs stabs ngag bung ba'i gzir skad do sems
NK107(tse)001:10615: nad kyi dngos po las bsgyur ba'o de'i steng du
NK107(tse)001:10616: so so'i 'byung ba gang yin pa'i dkyil du gtad
NK107(tse)001:10617: pa ni gnad yin no lhag ma ni gzhung gis
NK107(tse)001:10618: shes so zhes gnyis pa lus ngag gi gnad la
NK107(tse)001:10619: brten nas 'byung ba'i nad ji ltar gdon pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:10620: nas da ni gsum pa 'byung ba so so'i dus
NK107(tse)001:10621: nges pa dang rten 'brel la brten nas gzhan gyi
NK107(tse)001:10622: nad las grol ba'i sbyor ba bstan pa ni so
NK107(tse)001:10623: so'i lo'i grangs dang grol ba'i tshad dngul 'dar ba
NK107(tse)001:10624: dang ba spu zing ba dang snying gdung ba la
NK107(tse)001:10625: sogs pa byung na grol ba'i rtags yin pas lo
NK107(tse)001:10626: grangs kyis ni lus kyi nges par lus 'dar ba
NK107(tse)001:10627: la sogs pa'i grol ba'i mtshams ni a la ngag
NK107(tse)001:10628: sprid pa 'byung ba dang shugs nar gyis byung na
NK107(tse)001:10629: grol ba'i 'tshams yin no de la rang rang gi
NK107(tse)001:10630: lo dang zla ba dang dus tshod la nges par
NK107(tse)001:10631: shes pa yis ni nad zhugs pa'i dus shes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10632: sa bzlog pa'i gnad shes pa'o zug pa la zhugs
NK107(tse)001:10633: na zug 'tshams nyi ma rang dus mi 'dra na
NK107(tse)001:10634: bas bsgyur zla ba dang lo ma mthun pa la
NK107(tse)001:10635: zhugs na nad kyis bzlog lo dang dus ma mthun
NK107(tse)001:10636: rten 'brel gyis bya zla ba dang dus ma mthun
NK107(tse)001:10637: na sems kyi dmigs pa gtso che 'di dag kun
NK107(tse)001:10638: mthun pa la nad zhugs pa ni bzlog pa dka'
NK107(tse)001:10639: bar shes par bya'o de ltar ma nor bar shes
NK107(tse)001:10640: pas rang lus nad gang yin pa las grol ba
NK107(tse)001:10641: dang gzhan gyi lus la 'don na rten 'brel gyi
NK107(tse)001:10642: sbyor bas bya'o de yang sa lus sa'i la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10643: pa'o 'di ltar dus dang rten 'brel ma 'khrul bar
NK107(tse)001:10644: byas pas na rang gzhan gyi don thams cad 'grub
NK107(tse)001:10645: pa'o zhes dris lan zhe gsum pa lus sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:10646: nad gdon pa khyad par can la brten nas rnal
NK107(tse)001:10647: 'byor gyi bar chod nye bar zhi ba bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:10648: la yan lag gi don gsum du byas nas bstan
NK107(tse)001:10649: nas da ni le'u dang po'i dris lan zhe bzhi
NK107(tse)001:10650: pa lus rnam par bzhag pa shes par bya ba'i
NK107(tse)001:10651: chos grub pa'i matha'i dgos pa bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:10652: lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po 'jig
NK107(tse)001:10653: rten pa lam srol du 'jug pa'i dgos pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:10654: pa ni grub zhes pa bsgrub bya'i dgos pa la
NK107(tse)001:10655: yid ches pa'i dgos pa matha'i lta ba tshig gi
NK107(tse)001:10656: matha'i dgos pa dang nyams len gyi don gyis matha'i
NK107(tse)001:10657: dgos pa'o de ltar rnam pa gnyis la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:10658: sangs rgyas kyi sar 'gro bar byed pa'i dgos pa
NK107(tse)001:10659: yod do da res kyi skabs su 'jig pa lus
NK107(tse)001:10660: brten pa sems de gnyis lam du 'jug pa'i dgos
NK107(tse)001:10661: pa dang gsang pa'i ni dbang po la dgongs ste
NK107(tse)001:10662: bka' stsal pa ni 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10663: theg pa la sogs pa'o de yang dam ni gnad
NK107(tse)001:10664: du 'gro ba'i man ngag don gyi ni chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:10665: mngon gsum du gang zag gi rgyud la skye ba
NK107(tse)001:10666: de lta bu'i don gyis khams gsum du mi ldog
NK107(tse)001:10667: pa'o de nyid kyi dgongs pas khams gsum du mi
NK107(tse)001:10668: ldog pas na sangs rgyas nges pa'o de yang 'jig
NK107(tse)001:10669: rten pa bsgrub mtha' rjes su 'dzin pa'i dbang du
NK107(tse)001:10670: byas na gang zag so so'i las 'phro bzhi dang
NK107(tse)001:10671: dbang po'i rim pa rab 'bring tha ma'i dbang du
NK107(tse)001:10672: byas pa yis mos pa gnyis la dgongs te 'jig
NK107(tse)001:10673: rten pa la mos pa la 'jig rten gyi theg
NK107(tse)001:10674: pa gnyis 'das pa la mos pa la 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10675: theg pa gnyis theg pa zhes bya ba ni dong
NK107(tse)001:10676: bas na dang khyab pas na dang bskyed pas na
NK107(tse)001:10677: dang 'dus pas na dang yang pas na theg pa
NK107(tse)001:10678: zhes bya'o dag ni 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa
NK107(tse)001:10679: gnyis su 'dod do de la theg pa thams cad
NK107(tse)001:10680: kyi gzhi ni 'jig rten pa yin te theg pa
NK107(tse)001:10681: la snga ma lha dang mi'i theg pa med na
NK107(tse)001:10682: gzhi stongs ste theg pa zhes 'ong ba'i rgyu med
NK107(tse)001:10683: do 'jig rten pa 'di la 'dod pa 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:10684: sor bzhag dang phyin ci log gnyis yin no de
NK107(tse)001:10685: yang 'jig rten sor bzhag ni lha dang mi lung
NK107(tse)001:10686: du ma bstan pa theg pa'i gzhi yin pas 'di
NK107(tse)001:10687: la brten nas 'das pa'i nang du yang 'jug pas
NK107(tse)001:10688: theg pa yin la phyin ci log la yang 'jug
NK107(tse)001:10689: tu yod pas theg pa'o de ltar yang theg pa
NK107(tse)001:10690: la snga ma lha dang mi'i theg pa'o zhes pa'o
NK107(tse)001:10691: de yang lha dang mi'i med na theg pa la
NK107(tse)001:10692: 'byung ba'i don med pa'o 'jig rten phyin ci log
NK107(tse)001:10693: gi theg pa la spyir lta ba ngan pa sum
NK107(tse)001:10694: brgya dang drug cu yod pa la de dag kyang
NK107(tse)001:10695: lta ba phyin ci log tu smra ba la brgya
NK107(tse)001:10696: bsgoms pa phyiin ci log tu smra ba la brgya
NK107(tse)001:10697: spyod pa phyin ci log tu smra ba la brgya
NK107(tse)001:10698: de dag rnams chad par smra ba la nyi shu
NK107(tse)001:10699: rtag par smra ba la nyi shu de yang so
NK107(tse)001:10700: so'i 'dod pa'i bye brag dpag tu med do grub
NK107(tse)001:10701: mtha' la rjes su 'dzin pa'i gang zag la spros
NK107(tse)001:10702: na barjoda kyis mi long 'di dag ni don gyis
NK107(tse)001:10703: 'byung ba snod kyi khyad par min par don dam
NK107(tse)001:10704: du 'dod pa khams gsum du 'khrid pa'i lta ba
NK107(tse)001:10705: zhes bya'o 'di rnams kun 'byung ba bzhi la chad
NK107(tse)001:10706: pas don dam du 'dod pa dang rtag pa don
NK107(tse)001:10707: dam du 'dod pa dang chad pa gnyis med la
NK107(tse)001:10708: don dam du 'dod pa la sogs pa'o brtag pa
NK107(tse)001:10709: ni 'byung ba bzhi rang rgyud pa dus la snga
NK107(tse)001:10710: phyi med par 'dod la chad pas ni 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:10711: sems kyi bag la nyal du 'dod la dus snga
NK107(tse)001:10712: phyi ni mi bden da lta'i shes pa 'di glo
NK107(tse)001:10713: bur ba 'byung ba la khyab pa'i sems bag la
NK107(tse)001:10714: nyal ba langs pas da lta rgyu rkyen dang phrad
NK107(tse)001:10715: nas da lta byung la da lta lus gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:10716: grub pa las snga ma'i yang 'di min la phyi
NK107(tse)001:10717: nas kyang sems 'di lus la 'jug mi srid do
NK107(tse)001:10718: de ltar lus tha dad pa bzhin du sems kyang
NK107(tse)001:10719: tha dad che chung yang lus dang 'dra ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10720: de ltar tha dad pa'i sems de rgyu rkyen mthun
NK107(tse)001:10721: pa'i lus nam byung tsam na 'jug pa yin zhes
NK107(tse)001:10722: 'dod do de dag la bye brag tu bshad na
NK107(tse)001:10723: dpag tu med do de yang 'jig rten pa ni
NK107(tse)001:10724: gzhi nyon mongs pa gsum gyis lam skye gzhis bsdus
NK107(tse)001:10725: nas 'bras bu khams gsum du 'khor bas na 'khor
NK107(tse)001:10726: ba'i theg pa zhes bya'o 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10727: theg pa rgyu la lam du byed pa dang 'bras
NK107(tse)001:10728: bu lam du byed pa gnyis las de la rgyu
NK107(tse)001:10729: la lam du byed pa'i theg pa la gsum ste
NK107(tse)001:10730: blo phyir la dgongs pa ste blo chung ba'i chung
NK107(tse)001:10731: ba la nyan thos kyi theg pa 'di yang phyi
NK107(tse)001:10732: rol pa ni ci nas kyang bdag rtog pa'i rang
NK107(tse)001:10733: bzhin chad pa'i rang bzhin gnyis su 'dod pa las
NK107(tse)001:10734: 'dir ni chos thams cad med par khas len no
NK107(tse)001:10735: phyi rol pa ni chos dang gang zag gnyis la
NK107(tse)001:10736: bdag med la khyad par du gang zag la bdag
NK107(tse)001:10737: med la bye brag pa na re bdag gam bdag
NK107(tse)001:10738: yod do re shes na chos kyi khams kyi phyogs
NK107(tse)001:10739: gcig tsam la yod pa srid de de yang phyi
NK107(tse)001:10740: rol gyi snang ba 'di rdul 'phra rab kyis gzhig
NK107(tse)001:10741: pa'i dus na 'phra rab kyis rdul yan chad brtsir
NK107(tse)001:10742: btub pas gang gis stobs su rung ste 'phra rab
NK107(tse)001:10743: la khyab pa'i cha med pa'i rdul gcig rtog dpyod
NK107(tse)001:10744: kyis ma nges pas de mi khegs pas de yod
NK107(tse)001:10745: du rung zer ro de yang snang ba gzugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:10746: gzhi'i skabs su 'di ltar snang ba g.yag rnga dang
NK107(tse)001:10747: ne seng gi snang ba ltar mthong ba'i dus na'o
NK107(tse)001:10748: phyi rol pa thams cad rtag par khas len pa
NK107(tse)001:10749: 'dus ma byas rtag par yang mi 'gegs la 'dus
NK107(tse)001:10750: byas thams cad mi rtag par mngon gsum gyis gsal
NK107(tse)001:10751: lo chad pa yang ma yin pa ste 'dus byas
NK107(tse)001:10752: chad kyang 'dus ma byas ye nas rtag par bzhugs
NK107(tse)001:10753: pas phyi rol bde sdug mnyam zhes pa ste de
NK107(tse)001:10754: la nyan thos na re zag bcas thams cad sdug
NK107(tse)001:10755: basngala ba'o zhes khas len no de ltar bzhi po
NK107(tse)001:10756: de khas len na ni 'das pa'i theg pa yin
NK107(tse)001:10757: te mi len na don gyis phyi rol par 'gro
NK107(tse)001:10758: ba'o blo chung ba'i 'bring po rang rgyal ba bse
NK107(tse)001:10759: ru lta bu dang ne tso ltar 'tshogs pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:10760: pa gnyis so de yang rten cing 'brel par 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10761: ba'i 'khor lo la don dam du lta ba'o lta
NK107(tse)001:10762: ba ni de dag gis rjes su 'gro ldog pa
NK107(tse)001:10763: lta la bsgom pa ni de rnams la lugs 'byung
NK107(tse)001:10764: dang lugs zlog tu bsgom pa'o blo chung ba'i rab
NK107(tse)001:10765: byang sems kyi theg pa ni dngos por smra ba
NK107(tse)001:10766: sems tsam pa dang stong par smra ba dbu ma
NK107(tse)001:10767: gnyis pa'o sems tsam ni rnam pa dang shes pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10768: rnam pa rnams bardzuna pa don dam du 'dod pa
NK107(tse)001:10769: dang bden par 'dod pa'o de dag gi bye brag
NK107(tse)001:10770: ni 'dir mi spro'o dbu ma la rang rgyud du
NK107(tse)001:10771: 'dod pa dang thal 'gyur du 'dod pa gnyis so
NK107(tse)001:10772: de la bye brag mang yang bden pa bzhi la
NK107(tse)001:10773: spyod pa dang bsgom pa dang lta ba yang bden
NK107(tse)001:10774: pa gnyis su 'dod pa'o 'bras bu la lam du
NK107(tse)001:10775: byed pa ni phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud dang nang
NK107(tse)001:10776: pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa dang gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:10777: 'dod pa'o de yang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:10778: ni rgyu ni dper na sa bon btab nas chu
NK107(tse)001:10779: lud pa la sogs pa'i bya ba dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:10780: pa byed dgos so 'bras bu ni 'bras la sogs
NK107(tse)001:10781: pa smin pa de las brtsol ba dang bsgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:10782: la sogs pa byas pas tshegs chung bar zas su
NK107(tse)001:10783: 'gro ba dang 'dra'o sngags dang pha rol tu phyin
NK107(tse)001:10784: pa'i khyad par kyang de tsam mo de la phyi
NK107(tse)001:10785: pa ni dper na rgyal po'i dkor mdzod kyi phyi
NK107(tse)001:10786: sgo mthong yang nang na ci yod mi shes pa
NK107(tse)001:10787: ltar sngags tsam las lta bsgom gyi mtshan nyid mi
NK107(tse)001:10788: shes pa'o thub pa ni lus kyi thub pa tshangs
NK107(tse)001:10789: par spyod pa dang brten pa dang ngag gi thub
NK107(tse)001:10790: pa sngags bzlas pa la brten pa dang yid lha'i
NK107(tse)001:10791: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan la dmigs pa'o nang pa
NK107(tse)001:10792: ni rgyal po'i dkor mdzod kyi nang du phyin pas
NK107(tse)001:10793: ci dang ci yod pa shes pa ltar sems dang
NK107(tse)001:10794: sems las byung ba'i chos thams cad shes pas cir
NK107(tse)001:10795: snang sems dang chos nyid du 'khyer ba'o thabs ni
NK107(tse)001:10796: thabs la brten nas tshegs med par b+hud tha'o rgyud
NK107(tse)001:10797: ni sems dang chos su 'dres par byed pa'o theg
NK107(tse)001:10798: pa ni sems nyid kyi khongs su chos nyid sna
NK107(tse)001:10799: tshogs bskyed par byed pa'o de ltar phyi nang gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10800: po las phye na phyi pa la kri ya'i theg
NK107(tse)001:10801: pa dang u pa ya'i theg pa dang yo ga'i
NK107(tse)001:10802: theg pa dang gsum nang pa la ma h+aa yo
NK107(tse)001:10803: ga dang a nu las a ti yo ga'i theg
NK107(tse)001:10804: pa dang drug tu 'gyur ro phyi nang gi khyad
NK107(tse)001:10805: par ni zas kyi rnal 'byor gyis phye ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10806: bskyed pa dang lta bas khyad par byas pa'o phyi
NK107(tse)001:10807: pas dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod mi
NK107(tse)001:10808: nus la lha yab yum zhal sbyor bsgom mi nus
NK107(tse)001:10809: la lta ba yang gsal stong dbyer med par bsgom
NK107(tse)001:10810: par mi nus so 'di ltar dbang po'i rim pa
NK107(tse)001:10811: ni 'bring gi tha ma la kri ya 'bring po'i
NK107(tse)001:10812: 'bring la u pa ya 'bring po'i rab la yo
NK107(tse)001:10813: ga de bzhin rab kyi tha ma la ma h+aa
NK107(tse)001:10814: 'bring a nu rab kyi rab la a ti yo
NK107(tse)001:10815: ga'o de ltar na rdzogs pa chen po 'di theg
NK107(tse)001:10816: pa gzhan las khyad par 'phags pas na ma rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:10817: pa med la 'di'i gong na gzhan med pas chen
NK107(tse)001:10818: po zhes bya la 'di nyid gdod ma nas skye
NK107(tse)001:10819: ma myong de ltar skye ma myong pas da lta
NK107(tse)001:10820: skye ba la mi gnas de ltar mi gnas pas
NK107(tse)001:10821: na tha ma skye mi srid pas na a zhes
NK107(tse)001:10822: bya la de ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs
NK107(tse)001:10823: la 'gyur mi srid do ye nas grol zin pas
NK107(tse)001:10824: na da skyar nas grol rgyu ci yang med la
NK107(tse)001:10825: de nyid rang grol yin pas gnyen po med de
NK107(tse)001:10826: nyid mthong ba tsam gyis grol bas da lta'i shes
NK107(tse)001:10827: pa 'di cer grol mthong ba tsam gyis grol bas
NK107(tse)001:10828: da lta'i shes pa 'di gcer grol mthong ba tsam
NK107(tse)001:10829: gyis yal lo de nyid bzhag pas grol bas 'bad
NK107(tse)001:10830: rtsol las 'das la dus kyi grol ste khyung phrug
NK107(tse)001:10831: sgong rgya dang bral ba lta bu'o gnad kyi grol
NK107(tse)001:10832: bas 'gyur ba med pas na ti zhes bya'o yongs
NK107(tse)001:10833: su rdzogs shing 'dus pa 'khor 'das go log gi
NK107(tse)001:10834: man ngag la brten nas snang srid ltor mid nas
NK107(tse)001:10835: b+hud tha'o 'khor 'das go bzlog pas thams cad chos
NK107(tse)001:10836: nyid du shar ba'o de lta bu'i rdzogs pa chen
NK107(tse)001:10837: po las kyang 'di nyid khyad par du 'phags te
NK107(tse)001:10838: mtha' bral yongs rdzogs spros gzhi dang bral ba zhes
NK107(tse)001:10839: bya'o de yang yod pa'i mtha' dang bral bas stong
NK107(tse)001:10840: pa ngos bzung las 'das la med pa'i mtha' dang
NK107(tse)001:10841: bral bas rang rig pa 'od gsal gyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:10842: chad pa'i mu las 'das la gnyis ka dang bral
NK107(tse)001:10843: bas rtag chad mthar 'dzin pa las 'das gnyis ka
NK107(tse)001:10844: ma yin pa dang bral bas zhe 'dod phyogs lhung
NK107(tse)001:10845: dang bral ba'o de bzhin du snang ba dang mi
NK107(tse)001:10846: snang ba dang gnyis ka dang gnyis ka ma yin
NK107(tse)001:10847: pa dang gsal ba dang mi gsal ba dang de'i
NK107(tse)001:10848: mtha' gnyis dang yin pa dang min pa dang la
NK107(tse)001:10849: sogs pa thams cad kyi mtha' dang bral bas gang
NK107(tse)001:10850: gi yang phyogs su ma lhung la de yang 'bral
NK107(tse)001:10851: lugs ma spangs yongs rdzogs su bral ba'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:10852: rang byung du bral bas 'bad mi dgos rang rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:10853: su bral bas dgag bsgrub med rang grol du bral
NK107(tse)001:10854: bas gnyen po med rang dag tu dag pas ka
NK107(tse)001:10855: nas dag pa'o rang snang du bral bas chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:10856: btsal mi dgos rang shar du bral bas bya btsal
NK107(tse)001:10857: las 'das de lta bu de ye nas bral bas
NK107(tse)001:10858: bskyar nas grol rgyu med do shugs kyis bral bas
NK107(tse)001:10859: snga dang phyi mtha' la mi ltos so yongs su
NK107(tse)001:10860: rdzogs pas gang yang spang mi dgos snang stong rtag
NK107(tse)001:10861: chad 'khor 'das thams cad chos nyid las 'das pa
NK107(tse)001:10862: med pa'o de ltar na yongs su rdzogs pa gnad
NK107(tse)001:10863: kyis mngon sum chos nyid rang thog na gsal ba
NK107(tse)001:10864: la 'khor 'das dus gcig la grol ba zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:10865: theg pa rim pa dgu la brten nas khams 'dod
NK107(tse)001:10866: pa dang gzugs dang gzugs med pa gsum po yang
NK107(tse)001:10867: dag pa'i lam du 'jug par byed pa'o zhes 'jig
NK107(tse)001:10868: rten pa lam du 'jug pa'i dgos pa bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:10869: da ni gnyis pa dam pa'i don mngon gsum gnad
NK107(tse)001:10870: la la brten nas gcig char du grol ba'i dgos
NK107(tse)001:10871: pa bstan pa ni de la dam pa ni b+hud
NK107(tse)001:10872: d+ha'i dgongs pa ste de'i don ni chos nyid mngon
NK107(tse)001:10873: sum du skye ba nyid la yid spyod tshig gi
NK107(tse)001:10874: blo dang bral nas gang zag dbang po gcig char
NK107(tse)001:10875: ba rnams bla ma'i man ngag de nyid bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:10876: tsam gyis rang grol la 'gro bas na de yang
NK107(tse)001:10877: gang las byung zhe na chos nyid mngon sum dbang
NK107(tse)001:10878: po la snang ba'o de yang sgo'i gzigs stangs gsum
NK107(tse)001:10879: las mi 'da' ba dang yul gyi gnad nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:10880: sprin dang bral ba la rig pa bzhag pa dang
NK107(tse)001:10881: rlung rig gi gnad rig pa nam mkha' 'phangs te
NK107(tse)001:10882: rlung dal ba brten pas rig pa rang ngo na
NK107(tse)001:10883: gsal ba dang gsum dbang po'i yul du mthong ba'i
NK107(tse)001:10884: gnad kyis ni tshig tu 'dzin pa'i rang grub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10885: mtha' yid spyod du 'dzin pa rnams zhig nas tshig
NK107(tse)001:10886: tu 'dzin pa las blo ldog pa'o de ltar chos
NK107(tse)001:10887: nyid mngon sum don la gnas pas dngos stong gang
NK107(tse)001:10888: du yang 'dzin pa'i shes pa dang bral te snang
NK107(tse)001:10889: ba dang shes pa la sogs pa'i gang du yang
NK107(tse)001:10890: zhen pa dang 'dzin pa med par rang rig rang
NK107(tse)001:10891: sar shes pas grol ba ni bya ba med pas
NK107(tse)001:10892: grol bas grol zhes pa'o de yang mngon sum gyis
NK107(tse)001:10893: gnad kyis man ngag gis yang dag pa'i chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:10894: bde ba chen po'i ro mngon gsum yid dpyod dang
NK107(tse)001:10895: bral bar myong nas khams ni 'tshogs shing 'dus pa
NK107(tse)001:10896: 'dus shing 'jig pa 'dod chags las 'dod khams su
NK107(tse)001:10897: chags pa dang zhe sdang las gzugs su chags pa
NK107(tse)001:10898: dang gti mug las gzugs med du ldog pa'i 'dod
NK107(tse)001:10899: chags ma byung ma skyes rang byung gi ye shes
NK107(tse)001:10900: nyid de bzhin du zhe sdang ma byung ma skyes
NK107(tse)001:10901: rang byung gi ye shes nyid yin de bzhin du
NK107(tse)001:10902: gti mug ma byung ma skyes rang byung gi ye
NK107(tse)001:10903: shes su song bas de nyid med par rang snang
NK107(tse)001:10904: rang grol du song ba ni grol ba rang byung
NK107(tse)001:10905: gzhan las min zhes so dper na nam mkha' la
NK107(tse)001:10906: nam mkha' nyid thim pa ltar ris med mnyam pa
NK107(tse)001:10907: nyid chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos par zag bcas
NK107(tse)001:10908: mi snang bar b+hud tha ba ni rnal 'byor mchog
NK107(tse)001:10909: ces bya ste 'byung ba'i zag pa zad nas de
NK107(tse)001:10910: nyid kyang de bzhin du zag pa mi snang ba
NK107(tse)001:10911: yin no zhes dris lan zhe bzhi pa shes par
NK107(tse)001:10912: bya ba'i chos grub pa'i matha'i dgos pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:10913: la gnyis su byas nas bstan no da ni le'u
NK107(tse)001:10914: dang po'i dris lan zhe lnga pa lus rnam par
NK107(tse)001:10915: bzhag pa man ngag mthar thug gi dgos pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:10916: pa la yan lag gi don drug gis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:10917: dang po bskyed pa'i rim pa bsgom pa'i mtha' gang
NK107(tse)001:10918: la thug bstan pa ni 'di dag ni ston pas
NK107(tse)001:10919: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'di lta bu'i man ngag
NK107(tse)001:10920: 'byung bas 'gyur ba la dgongs pa'o de yang mtha'
NK107(tse)001:10921: zhes pa 'di las lhag pa med pa'i don te
NK107(tse)001:10922: thug pa'i zhes pa 'di las 'gro sa med pas
NK107(tse)001:10923: slar 'khor ba'i gnad do dgos pa ni theg pa
NK107(tse)001:10924: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i don no 'di la
NK107(tse)001:10925: bskyed zhes pa 'di la dngos po'i rnam 'phrul du
NK107(tse)001:10926: bskyed pa dang dngos de 'dra men du bskyed pa
NK107(tse)001:10927: dang gnas skabs bsgyur nas bskyed pa'o de la 'dir
NK107(tse)001:10928: gnas skabs bsgyur nas bskyed pa'i mtha' ni rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:10929: pa'i lus la brten pa yin te de yang lha
NK107(tse)001:10930: bsgom pa la dngos po sum cu rtsa gnyis dag
NK107(tse)001:10931: par byed pa ni gnad yin no dngos po de
NK107(tse)001:10932: dag rnams dag par byed pa la rgya gar gyi
NK107(tse)001:10933: yi ge'i dbyibs shes par byed dgos te de yang
NK107(tse)001:10934: dang po lha'i sku la dmigs pa gsal ba dang
NK107(tse)001:10935: gnyis pa rang gi lus kyi dngos po sbyang ba
NK107(tse)001:10936: dang gsum pa khyad par gyi 'jug pas yi dam
NK107(tse)001:10937: lha'i ngo bo lta ba dang bzhi pa rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:10938: rnam par dag pa yis rgyas gdab pa dang lnga
NK107(tse)001:10939: pa chos nyid sgyu ma la ye shes sgyu ma
NK107(tse)001:10940: rol pa'i tshad bzung ba'o de dag ni bsam gtan
NK107(tse)001:10941: mig gis 'khor lo'i gnas skabs nas rgyas par ston
NK107(tse)001:10942: no de ltar rdzogs pa las yo ga'i lus de
NK107(tse)001:10943: nyid lha dang zung du 'jug pas gnyis su med
NK107(tse)001:10944: cing blang dor med pa zhes pa'i don no de'i
NK107(tse)001:10945: mtha' lus kyi dngos po sum cu rtsa gnyis zad
NK107(tse)001:10946: pa nyid la thug go zhes pa'i bskyed pa'i mtha'
NK107(tse)001:10947: thug pa'i dgos pa bstan nas da ni gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:10948: rdzogs pa'i rim pa mtha' gang la thug pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:10949: pa ni rdzogs zhes pa rang bzhin 'dug tshul gyis
NK107(tse)001:10950: rdzogs pas bskyed mi dgos pa dang rang gi ngo
NK107(tse)001:10951: bo la rdzogs pas gzhan ltos tha snyad las 'das
NK107(tse)001:10952: pa dang rtog med rang du rdzogs pas bcos mi
NK107(tse)001:10953: dgos pa'o rim pa ni dang po lus sbyangs ba'i
NK107(tse)001:10954: cho ga dang sems 'dul ba'i cho ga dang nyams
NK107(tse)001:10955: su myong ba'i drod tshad bzung ba dang gal te
NK107(tse)001:10956: dngos grub med na spogs pa'i cho ga rlung gnad
NK107(tse)001:10957: la bor ba'i rim pa ji ltar bya ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:10958: rtsi yang zhun gyi skabs nas ston no de nyid
NK107(tse)001:10959: kyi mtha' ni rlung 'gyu zhing rnam par rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:10960: tha dad pa sdud cing 'dzin par byed pas na
NK107(tse)001:10961: rlung dang zhes pa la brgyad rlung zhags pa 'ching
NK107(tse)001:10962: ba'i tshul gyis bsgom pa dang 'khor lo la 'khor
NK107(tse)001:10963: ba'i tshul gyis dang lcags kyu ma 'dzin pa'i tshul
NK107(tse)001:10964: gyis bsgom pa dang spu gri ma 'debs pa'i tshul
NK107(tse)001:10965: gyis bsgom pa dang gri ma gcod pa'i tshul gyis
NK107(tse)001:10966: bsgom pa dang bum pa ma 'gengs pa'i tshul gyis
NK107(tse)001:10967: dang rin chen ma spel ba'i tshul gyis dang pad+ma
NK107(tse)001:10968: ma 'byed pa'i tshul gyis de ltar brgyad la gang
NK107(tse)001:10969: zag brgyad kyis bsgoms pas shes pa dang rlung gnyis
NK107(tse)001:10970: zung 'jug dbyer med pas na de'i mtha' rlung zad
NK107(tse)001:10971: pas rnam par rtog pa zad pa nyid la thug
NK107(tse)001:10972: go zhes gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa mtha' gang
NK107(tse)001:10973: la thug pa bstan nas da ni gsum pa grub
NK107(tse)001:10974: pa'i mtha' gang la thug pa bstan pa ni grub
NK107(tse)001:10975: pa'i zhes pa ye nas grub zin pa gcig la
NK107(tse)001:10976: tha snyad tshig gi gzhal byar gyur pa'o de'i tha
NK107(tse)001:10977: ma ni lam rjes su 'dzin pas barjoda du med
NK107(tse)001:10978: pa yin la grub mtha' rjes su 'dzin pas barjoda
NK107(tse)001:10979: bya tshig gi mtha' 'di yin zhes pa la thug
NK107(tse)001:10980: de yang rang 'dod grub pa dang gzhan 'dod dgag
NK107(tse)001:10981: pa gnyis zung du 'jug pas na dam bca' ba
NK107(tse)001:10982: dang gtan tshigs dang bsgrub bya dang skyon yon la
NK107(tse)001:10983: sogs pa ste de yang rang gi dam baca'i skyon
NK107(tse)001:10984: shes pas kyang ngo shes pa nyid la thug go
NK107(tse)001:10985: de yang rdzong gsum dang rigs pa gsum dang dam
NK107(tse)001:10986: bca' gsum dang gtan tshigs bzhi dang dngos por smra
NK107(tse)001:10987: ba dang stong par smra ba la sogs pa a
NK107(tse)001:10988: ti rnams dgongs kyi skabs nas ston no zhes gsum
NK107(tse)001:10989: pa grub pa'i mtha' gang la thug pa bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:10990: da ni bzhi pa phyag rgya chen po'i mtha' gang
NK107(tse)001:10991: la thug pa bstan pa ni phyag bzung bya rgya
NK107(tse)001:10992: gdab bya de ltar na gdab bzung gnyis gnyis su
NK107(tse)001:10993: med pa chen po gong na med pa nyid kyi
NK107(tse)001:10994: ma bcos pa mtha' bsgyur bar byed pa dang snang
NK107(tse)001:10995: ba yul la 'debs pa dag yin te de yang
NK107(tse)001:10996: bsgyur ba las bde ba dang bde ba las stong
NK107(tse)001:10997: pa ste de yang bde stong gnyis zung du 'jug
NK107(tse)001:10998: pas zung 'jug phyag rgya chen po zhes bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:10999: yang mu tra bzhi dang dbang bzhi dang lhan cig
NK107(tse)001:11000: skyes pa bzhi dang dran sogs bzhi dang dga' ba
NK107(tse)001:11001: bzhi dang skad cig ma bzhi la sogs pa phyag
NK107(tse)001:11002: rgya bsdus pa'i skabs nas bshad do de dag gi
NK107(tse)001:11003: don phyag rgya chen po yid la bya ba gang
NK107(tse)001:11004: yang mi byed pa nyid la thug go zhes bzhi
NK107(tse)001:11005: pa phyag rgya chen po'i mtha' gang la thug pa
NK107(tse)001:11006: bstan nas da ni lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:11007: mtha' gang la thug pa bstan pa ni de yang
NK107(tse)001:11008: rang chos nyid bzhin snang ba de ltar snang ba
NK107(tse)001:11009: dang chos nyid gnyis gnyis su med par rdzogs pa
NK107(tse)001:11010: chen po gong na med pa mtha' ni bzhag pa
NK107(tse)001:11011: tsam gyis grol ba chu'i snyoms ma bzhag tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:11012: sangs pa lta bu'o gnad kyis grol ba skyes bu'i
NK107(tse)001:11013: snying la mdas zin pa lta bu dang de yang
NK107(tse)001:11014: snang ba snang sar bzhag pas grol ba dang shes
NK107(tse)001:11015: pa 'gyus sar bzhag pas grol ba dang 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:11016: kyis chos rnams rang sar bzhag pa ste zhes pas
NK107(tse)001:11017: so de yang 'khor ba'i chos snang shes gnyis chos
NK107(tse)001:11018: nyid du zung du 'jug pas na rdzong gsum ni
NK107(tse)001:11019: gangs la nyi ma shar ba ltar bu la sogs
NK107(tse)001:11020: pa rig pa sum ni rgyu mtshan go ldog la
NK107(tse)001:11021: sogs pa dang gtan tshigs ni gcig shes kun grol
NK107(tse)001:11022: la sogs pa dang de yang thams cad chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:11023: stong rar dam bca' ba dang de yang grol lugs
NK107(tse)001:11024: bzhi la sogs pas grol ba'i gnad ni ye grol
NK107(tse)001:11025: la bskyar gzhi med pa la sogs pa'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:11026: blo snga phyi'i bar du ngo sprad pa dang chos
NK107(tse)001:11027: nyid snga phyi dang snang shes snga phyi'i bar du
NK107(tse)001:11028: ngo sprad pa tsam gyis phrad phrad pa tsam gyis
NK107(tse)001:11029: rtogs la rtogs pa tsam gyis grol ba'o grol ba
NK107(tse)001:11030: la brten nas mthar phyin pa'o de'i phyir na ye
NK107(tse)001:11031: grol la bskyar gzhi med pas snang ba gang snang
NK107(tse)001:11032: gi steng du bzhag pa nyid la thug go de
NK107(tse)001:11033: ltar khyung chen mkha' lding gi skabs nas zhib tu
NK107(tse)001:11034: ston no zhes lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po'i mtha'
NK107(tse)001:11035: gang la thug pa bstan nas da ni drug pa
NK107(tse)001:11036: mthar thug gi man ngag lnga'i dgos pa bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:11037: ni dgos pa blo las 'das pa la sogs go
NK107(tse)001:11038: rim gyi gzhung gsal lo zhus don bzhi bcu zhe
NK107(tse)001:11039: lnga pa man ngag mthar thug gi dgos pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:11040: pa la drug tu byas nas bstan no da ni
NK107(tse)001:11041: le'u dang po'i zhus don zhe drug pa bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11042: thabs zab mo khyad par gyis sngags bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:11043: yan lag gi don bdun gyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK107(tse)001:11044: bsgrub pa'i thabs thun mong ma yin pa'i yan lag
NK107(tse)001:11045: thun mong gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:11046: ni e ma gsang sngags mthar thug pa'i zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:11047: la sogs pa gzhung gsal lo da ni gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:11048: shes rab gtso bor gyur pa rnal 'byor ma'i bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11049: pa'i thabs zab mo bstan pa ni de la re
NK107(tse)001:11050: shig zhes pa ni thog ma'am yang mang po la
NK107(tse)001:11051: dgongs pa la 'dir shes rab gtso bor 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:11052: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i sgrub thabs rnam par bshad
NK107(tse)001:11053: ces dam bca' ba'o byin brlabs ni phyi'i snang ba
