NK107(tse)001:11054: bsgyur nus pa nang gi snang ba 'byin nus pa
NK107(tse)001:11055: gsang ba'i byin brlabs ye shes 'bar nus pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:11056: yang gang gis ston pa ni phyi mchod chang dang
NK107(tse)001:11057: ma d+hal la brten nas ston no nang 'tshogs 'khor
NK107(tse)001:11058: dang sin d+hu ra'i thig le la brten nas ston
NK107(tse)001:11059: no gsang ba sngags dang g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i bskor
NK107(tse)001:11060: lugs la brten nas ston no de yang rnal ba
NK107(tse)001:11061: bde ba 'byor ba'i chang ba ma bde ba 'bar
NK107(tse)001:11062: ba la brten nas ye shes kyi nus pa rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:11063: pa dang yang na chos nyid dang sems nyid de
NK107(tse)001:11064: chos nyid dang sems nyid la brten nas skye med
NK107(tse)001:11065: kyi nus pa rdzogs pa'o de la bye brag tu
NK107(tse)001:11066: bshad na phyi'i rnal 'byor ma spyod pa rgyun gyis
NK107(tse)001:11067: 'khor lo yin la nang gi rnal 'byor ma bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11068: pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo la gsang ba'i lta ba
NK107(tse)001:11069: rgyun gyi 'khor lo de yang rnal ba nyams la
NK107(tse)001:11070: 'byor myong la ma rtogs pa'o de ltar nyams myong
NK107(tse)001:11071: dang rtogs pa la rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma zhes
NK107(tse)001:11072: bya'o de'i phyi rnal ma la brten nas lus rnal
NK107(tse)001:11073: 'byor ma'i rgyan dang cha lugs las mi 'da' nang
NK107(tse)001:11074: ngag 'byor pa la brten nas ngag sngags kyi 'khor
NK107(tse)001:11075: lo las mi 'da' gsang ba ma la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:11076: sems chos nyid kyi 'khor lo las mi 'da' 'o
NK107(tse)001:11077: de yang phyi ltar rnal 'byor ma nang ltar mkha'
NK107(tse)001:11078: 'gro ma gsang ba ltar phag mo'o de la lnga
NK107(tse)001:11079: lnga yod do rdo rje rnal 'byor ma rat+na rnal
NK107(tse)001:11080: 'byor ma pad+ma rnal 'byor ma karma rnal 'byor ma
NK107(tse)001:11081: b+hud d+ha rnal 'byor ma mkha' 'gro la yang lnga
NK107(tse)001:11082: rdo rje phag mo la sogs pa lnga'o de yang
NK107(tse)001:11083: 'gro ba'i mos pa'i bye brag gis phyi ltar rdo
NK107(tse)001:11084: rje dbyings phyug ma la sogs pa lnga yin la
NK107(tse)001:11085: nang ltar b+hud d+ha kro ti shwa ri la sogs
NK107(tse)001:11086: pa lnga yin la gsang ba ltar rdo rje rigs
NK107(tse)001:11087: kyi phag mo la sogs pa lnga'o de gang la
NK107(tse)001:11088: dgongs na phyi phung po lnga dag par byed do
NK107(tse)001:11089: nang 'byung ba lnga dag par byed gsang ba mkha'
NK107(tse)001:11090: 'gro ma lngas nyon mongs pa lnga dag par byed
NK107(tse)001:11091: do de lta na gsang ba khro mo bkod pa
NK107(tse)001:11092: las 'dod chags pad+ma phag mo dmar mo dang zhe
NK107(tse)001:11093: sdang rdo rje phag mo dkar mo dang gti mug
NK107(tse)001:11094: bde gshegs phag mo nag mo dang nga rgyal rat+na
NK107(tse)001:11095: phag mo ser mo dang phrag dog las kyi phag
NK107(tse)001:11096: mo sngon mor bshad do de yang phyi nang gsang
NK107(tse)001:11097: ba'i khyad par las kyi tshig don bstan pa ni
NK107(tse)001:11098: rnal 'byor ma ni bshad pa ste mkha' dbyings 'gro
NK107(tse)001:11099: rig pa ma dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa phag
NK107(tse)001:11100: las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad klog pa mos
NK107(tse)001:11101: chos thams cad bskyed cing 'byung bar byed pa'o de
NK107(tse)001:11102: lta bu'i rnal 'byor ma 'di las bsgrub pa'i thabs
NK107(tse)001:11103: ni bde bar gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor ma'i bsgrub thabs
NK107(tse)001:11104: 'khor lo mdzes ldan dang rdo rje'i rigs la khro
NK107(tse)001:11105: mo sngon 'byung dang rat+na'i rigs la lha mo sngon
NK107(tse)001:11106: spyod dang pad+ma'i rigs la mkha' 'gro ma sngon 'byung
NK107(tse)001:11107: dang las kyi rigs la mkha' 'gro ma kun tu
NK107(tse)001:11108: spyod pa'i bsgrub thabs rnal 'byor ma 'khor dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:11109: pa'i bsgrub thabs sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las
NK107(tse)001:11110: la mkha' 'gro ma rab tu rngam pa'i bsgrub thabs
NK107(tse)001:11111: dang rdo rje phag mo ro la zhon pa'i bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11112: thabs dang bdun du 'gyur ro de la 'dir rdo
NK107(tse)001:11113: rje phag mo rgyan gcig ma'i bsgrub thabs bshad par
NK107(tse)001:11114: bya'o 'di la chos kyi rnam grangs bcu phrag gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11115: kyis rnal 'byor ma dngos su 'grub ste de yang
NK107(tse)001:11116: bsdu na sum ste sngon du rnal 'byor pa dam
NK107(tse)001:11117: tshig dang ldan pas rab tu dben pa'i gnas su
NK107(tse)001:11118: rnal 'byor ma'i rnal 'byor du byas te bsnyen pa
NK107(tse)001:11119: ji ltar bya ba dang gcig de nas dal bzhengs
NK107(tse)001:11120: te bsgrub pa'i rim pa ji ltar bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:11121: gnyis de nas las kyi bsgyur ba las tshogs kyi
NK107(tse)001:11122: don gtan la dbab pa dang gsum mo de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11123: gsum las khyad par gyi rnam grangs bcu drug tu
NK107(tse)001:11124: 'gyur te rnal 'byor ma'i so so'i bsnyen bsgrub kyi
NK107(tse)001:11125: sngags kyi mthus ji ltar sbyar ba dang gcig yi
NK107(tse)001:11126: ge'i sbyor 'brel la brten nas rnal 'byor ma'i rtsa
NK107(tse)001:11127: ba'i sngags ngos bzung dang gnyis de ltar sngags shes
NK107(tse)001:11128: par byas la bsgrub pa pos bzlas pa ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:11129: bya ba dang gsum 'di'i dus su sku bskyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11130: gsal byed kyis yi ge'i 'phro 'dus gsal bya dang
NK107(tse)001:11131: bzhi de ltar sa bon gyis 'phro 'dus snod sbyangs
NK107(tse)001:11132: pa la bskyed pa'i cho ga ji ltar rdzogs par
NK107(tse)001:11133: bya dang lnga de las lha mo'i sku mdog dang
NK107(tse)001:11134: mthun pa'i 'od kyis bdag gzhan gyis las dang nyon
NK107(tse)001:11135: mongs pa ji ltar sbyang ba dang drug de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11136: sbyangs nas sa bon las 'od 'phros nas khro mo'i
NK107(tse)001:11137: skur bzhengs pa dang bdun de nas ye shes sems
NK107(tse)001:11138: dpa' lha mo'i lus gzi byin dang ldan par bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11139: pa dang brgyad de nas dbang bskur gyis mi bskyod
NK107(tse)001:11140: pas dbu brgyan pa dang dgu de nas lha mo
NK107(tse)001:11141: bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas thun bzhir byas te bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11142: pa'i dus bstan pa dang bcu lha mo'i thugs khar
NK107(tse)001:11143: a li dang ka li las nyi zla'i gdan dang
NK107(tse)001:11144: bcas pa dmigs te bzlas pa dang de nyid blo
NK107(tse)001:11145: gnas pa bstan pa dang bcu gcig de ltar gsal
NK107(tse)001:11146: bar byas te gzugs bsdu ba dang bcu gnyis de
NK107(tse)001:11147: nas stong pa nyid kyis rgyas btab ste rang sems
NK107(tse)001:11148: ngos bzung ba dang bcu gsum de la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:11149: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa dang bcu bzhi 'o
NK107(tse)001:11150: de ltar rdzogs pa'i rim pas rgyas btab cing slar
NK107(tse)001:11151: bskyed pa'i rim pa la blo gnas par bya ba
NK107(tse)001:11152: dang bco lnga bsgrub pa'i rtags tshad bstan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11153: bcu drug gis rnal 'byor ma'i bsgrub thabs khyad par
NK107(tse)001:11154: bstan no de ltar rnal 'byor ma'i rnal 'byor du
NK107(tse)001:11155: ji ltar bya ba ni de sngon du rang gi
NK107(tse)001:11156: bla ma la tshogs bsags pa la sogs pa'i bya
NK107(tse)001:11157: ba rdzogs par byas nas dur khrod la sogs par
NK107(tse)001:11158: gnas rab tu dben par song nas 'khor dang 'du
NK107(tse)001:11159: 'dzi spangs la rang gcig pu stan bde ba'i steng
NK107(tse)001:11160: du 'dug la sngon du gtor ma dang mchod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11161: bye brag rnam pa sna tshogs pa byas te rang
NK107(tse)001:11162: gis sa ma ya yo gis 'adza zhes pas se
NK107(tse)001:11163: gol sgra dang bcas pa barjoda pas sangs rgyas dang
NK107(tse)001:11164: byang chub sems dpa' dang rnal 'byor ma dang rang
NK107(tse)001:11165: gi bla ma dang bcas pa mdun gyi nam mkhar
NK107(tse)001:11166: la spyan drangs la de dag gi spyan sngar thal
NK107(tse)001:11167: lo sbyar la bla ma dang b+hud d+ha dang byang
NK107(tse)001:11168: chub sems dpa' rnal 'byor ma dang bcas pa la
NK107(tse)001:11169: bdag gis lus gus pas phyag 'tshal lo zhe sdang
NK107(tse)001:11170: skyon gcod rdo rje rnal 'byor ma mchod pa lnga
NK107(tse)001:11171: yis mchod par bgyi sdig pa ma lus so sor
NK107(tse)001:11172: bshags chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad nas mya ngan
NK107(tse)001:11173: mi 'da' gsol ba 'debs 'gro ba'i dge la rjes
NK107(tse)001:11174: yi rang kun kyang sems can don du bsngo zhes
NK107(tse)001:11175: barjoda cing bdag nyid rnal 'byor du 'jug par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:11176: de nas rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la blo mos
NK107(tse)001:11177: par bya ste 'og nas 'byung ba'i yi ge 'bru
NK107(tse)001:11178: brgyad la bsnyen pa 'bum phrag gcig bskyal lo de
NK107(tse)001:11179: ltar bsnyen pa rdzogs nas bsgrub pa byed pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:11180: na 'og ma'i bcu gnyis pa 'dir sbyor de la
NK107(tse)001:11181: 'dir rnal 'byor ma rgyan gcig ma bsnyen bsgrub kyi
NK107(tse)001:11182: sngags bsdu ba ni a li dang po'i 'og ma
NK107(tse)001:11183: bzung ba ni +aa tha ma gnyis kyi gong ma
NK107(tse)001:11184: +amo ka li sde tshan lnga po'i gong ma ste
NK107(tse)001:11185: zhes sde tshan lnga'i gsum pa ba sde tshan gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11186: pa'i gsum pa dz+aa sde tshan gnyis pa'i drug pa
NK107(tse)001:11187: gnyis te badz+ra zhes bya'o yang sde tshan lnga pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11188: gsum pa ba gnyis pa'i gsum pa dzah drug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11189: gnyis pa ra a li'i gsum pa +ai badz+ra zhes
NK107(tse)001:11190: bya'o ka li'i tha ma'i steng ma h+aa yang sde
NK107(tse)001:11191: tshan drug pa'i thog ma wa de'i gnyis pa ra
NK107(tse)001:11192: sde tshan gsum pa'i lnga pa na sde tshan drug
NK107(tse)001:11193: pa'i gnyis pas de mgo brgyan ni rna ka li
NK107(tse)001:11194: tha ma gnyis kyi steng ni sa de'i bzla ni
NK107(tse)001:11195: swa ka li'i tha ma'i steng ni ha de nas
NK107(tse)001:11196: badz+ra badz+ra ha warna s+w+aa h+aa zhes yig gar rdza
NK107(tse)001:11197: 'bru brgyad pa bsnyen pa'i sngags so bsgrub pa la
NK107(tse)001:11198: brdu ba bsgrub thabs ni badz+ra badz+ri dak+ki ni h+aum
NK107(tse)001:11199: h'u ha h+aa s+w+aa h+aa yig 'bru bcu gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:11200: bsgrub pa'i sngags so yang las kyi mtha' bsgyur ba
NK107(tse)001:11201: dak+ki ni hring hring dak+ki ni phem phem h+aum h'u
NK107(tse)001:11202: dak+ki ni ga dza g+ha dza n+aa sha ya na
NK107(tse)001:11203: sh+aa ya phata phata k+sha ni k+sha ni k+shi na
NK107(tse)001:11204: k+shi na h+aum h+aum swa h+aa badz+ra dak+ki ni ma
NK107(tse)001:11205: da la sa ra y+ae dak+ki ni g+ha na d+he
NK107(tse)001:11206: a h+aum d+hush+pe a h+aum push+pe +aahh+aum +aahlo ke +aahh+aum
NK107(tse)001:11207: ne p+tee +aahh+aum badz+ra dak+ki ni ba lin b+hud dza
NK107(tse)001:11208: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi he he sti sta
NK107(tse)001:11209: sti sta ho ho s+w+aa h+aa rtsa ba'i sngags warna
NK107(tse)001:11210: b+hud d+ha sa dwa dak+ki ni badz+ra yo gi ni
NK107(tse)001:11211: sarba d+harma lo gi sa ra h+aum h+aum h+aum phata
NK107(tse)001:11212: phata s+w+aa h+aa zhes so so'i las kyis mthus dang
NK107(tse)001:11213: sbyar ro yi ge sbyor 'brel ni bsgrub thabs na
NK107(tse)001:11214: gsal lo sgrub pa pos bzlas pa ni sngags tshangs
NK107(tse)001:11215: sprugs su bzlas pa stong phrag gsum bzlas so 'di'i
NK107(tse)001:11216: dus na khro mo'i sku bsgom pa ni ma yin
NK107(tse)001:11217: te mos pa ma log pa bya'o de nas gsal
NK107(tse)001:11218: byed kyi yi ge'i 'du ni bsgrub thabs nas h+r+aihls
NK107(tse)001:11219: 'byung ba pad+ma'i steng +aa li'i 'od zer stong phrag
NK107(tse)001:11220: gis so so'i lus dang snod sbyang bya zhes pas
NK107(tse)001:11221: na h+r+aihls rang gi snying pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa
NK107(tse)001:11222: kha dog dmar po rab tu gsal ba'i steng du
NK107(tse)001:11223: a sngon po las 'od zer stong phrag dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:11224: med pa 'phros pas bdag dang sems can gyis lus
NK107(tse)001:11225: ngag yid la phog pas lus ngag gi sdig pa
NK107(tse)001:11226: ma lus pa yongs su dag par mdzad yar 'phros
NK107(tse)001:11227: nas nam makha'i b+hud tha dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK107(tse)001:11228: rnams la phog pas phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:11229: kyis mchod nas mi mnyes pa med par mnyes par
NK107(tse)001:11230: bya'o de lta bu'i 'phro 'dus phyi snod kyi 'jig
NK107(tse)001:11231: rten kyang 'od kyis sbyangs nang lus kyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:11232: yang sbyangs so bskyed pa'i cho ga rdzogs par bya
NK107(tse)001:11233: ba ni dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK107(tse)001:11234: pa dang de nas bsrung ba'i 'khor los bsgom pa
NK107(tse)001:11235: dang stong pa nyid du bsgom pa dang de'i ngang
NK107(tse)001:11236: du las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11237: pa dang de nas sa bon gyi 'phro 'dus gsal
NK107(tse)001:11238: ba dang mngon par byang chub pa lnga las khro
NK107(tse)001:11239: mo'i skur bzhengs pa las so gzhan ni gong ma'i
NK107(tse)001:11240: sdebs kyis shes so sems bskyed pa ni kun rdzob
NK107(tse)001:11241: dang don dam mo de yang de dag gnyis ka
NK107(tse)001:11242: la brten pa dang rten gyi khyad par la brten
NK107(tse)001:11243: nas sems bskyed pa'o kun rdzob tu brten ma d+ha
NK107(tse)001:11244: la dang gtor ma brten nas bskyed la rten gyi
NK107(tse)001:11245: khyad par ni bdag gis rdo rje rnal 'byor ma
NK107(tse)001:11246: bsgoms la sems can gyi don bya'o snyam pa las
NK107(tse)001:11247: mi 'da' bar bya'o don dam pa ni brten pa
NK107(tse)001:11248: sems kyi dkyil rnam par dag pa la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:11249: bskyed la rten gyi khyad pa ni bdag b+hud tha
NK107(tse)001:11250: bar byas la sems can thams cad bla na med
NK107(tse)001:11251: pa'i sa la dgod par bya'o mnyam pa las mi
NK107(tse)001:11252: 'da' bar bya'o de yang 'di dag gi dus na
NK107(tse)001:11253: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje khyad par can
NK107(tse)001:11254: la dmigs pa mchog tu ces so de nas bsrung
NK107(tse)001:11255: ba'i 'khor lo bsgom pa ni badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h+aum
NK107(tse)001:11256: h+aum zhes pa lan gsum barjoda pas sna tshogs rdo
NK107(tse)001:11257: rje 'bar ba'i 'khor lo rtsibs sum cu rtsa drug
NK107(tse)001:11258: pa gcig bsgom mo rdo rje phra mo'i me stag
NK107(tse)001:11259: 'phro bar bsgom mo de'i phyi rim na me ri
NK107(tse)001:11260: dang me'i rdo rje sna tshogs su 'khrug par bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11261: par bya'o de'i ngang las a'i 'phro 'du las phyi
NK107(tse)001:11262: snod kyi 'jig rten la phog pas de nyid zhu
NK107(tse)001:11263: ba las thams cad stong sangs kyis bsgom bdag la
NK107(tse)001:11264: sogs pa bcud kyi sems can rnams kyang stong sangs
NK107(tse)001:11265: kyis bsgom la bdag gi sems nyid a las ma
NK107(tse)001:11266: rtogs pa bdag dang dngos po thams cad stong pa
NK107(tse)001:11267: nyid du bsgom mo de'i ngang las e brum zhes
NK107(tse)001:11268: barjoda pas barjoda pa bdag rang gis barjoda kyang sgra
NK107(tse)001:11269: a las byung bar dmigs la chos kyi 'byung gnas
NK107(tse)001:11270: gru gsum pa rtse mo thur la bstan pa kha
NK107(tse)001:11271: dog dmar po bskal pa'i me ri sna tshogs pa
NK107(tse)001:11272: 'phro ba shin tu rgya che ba'i nang na g.yung
NK107(tse)001:11273: drung 'khyil pa myur du 'khor ba'i nus pa yod
NK107(tse)001:11274: pa gcig bsgom de'i dbus su gzhal yas khang gru
NK107(tse)001:11275: bzhi pa sgo bzhi rta babs bzhi dang bcas pa
NK107(tse)001:11276: kun tu 'bar ba'i 'phreng ba'i 'od kyis 'khrigs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11277: dbus gru gsum la zla kham dkar po gsum gyis
NK107(tse)001:11278: rab tu mdzes pas bskor ba mu khyud la sna
NK107(tse)001:11279: tshogs pad ma'i 'od kyis 'khrugs pa yis bskor ba
NK107(tse)001:11280: g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i gdan myur du bskor ba la
NK107(tse)001:11281: dmigs la bsgom par bya'o de ltar gsal ba'i ngang
NK107(tse)001:11282: las sa'i lha mo ser mo dang chu'i lha mo
NK107(tse)001:11283: dkar mo dang me'i lha mo dmar mo dang rlung
NK107(tse)001:11284: gi lha mo sngon mos gzhal yas khang gi gru
NK107(tse)001:11285: 'degs pa la dmigs pa gsal bar bsgom pa'i ngang
NK107(tse)001:11286: las bam yongs su gyur pa las ro'i gdan bsnol
NK107(tse)001:11287: ma mgo kha sbub tu g.yas g.yon du bsnol ba
NK107(tse)001:11288: bsgom de'i steng du a li'i 'phreng ba dkar po
NK107(tse)001:11289: g.yas su bskor ba las zla ba'i gdan bsam de'i
NK107(tse)001:11290: steng du ka li'i 'phreng ba dmar po g.yon du
NK107(tse)001:11291: bskor ba las nyi ma'i gdan bsgom mo de nas
NK107(tse)001:11292: sa bon gyis 'phro 'du las mngon par byang chub
NK107(tse)001:11293: pa lngas khro mo'i bskur bzhengs pa ni de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11294: nyi ma dang zla ba gwa'u kha sbyar ba'i nang
NK107(tse)001:11295: du +amo gyis 'od 'phros pas snod kyi 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:11296: gsal bar byas pa ni byang chub na dang po
NK107(tse)001:11297: ye shes na chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so
NK107(tse)001:11298: tshul 'dus nas rang gi lus sbyangs nas bskyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11299: ting nge 'dzin rig pa yid la gsal bar byar
NK107(tse)001:11300: rung ba'o byang chub pa gnyis pa de nas sa
NK107(tse)001:11301: bon 'od du zhu ba las phyag mtshan kha t+wam
NK107(tse)001:11302: kha thod pa gsum gyis mtshan pa gcig tu bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11303: mo de'i 'od sna tshogs su 'phros pa las yang
NK107(tse)001:11304: 'dus yang 'phros pas 'od zer dmar po dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:11305: med pas nam mkha' gang bar 'phros pas bdag gis
NK107(tse)001:11306: dngos por gyur pa'i bag chags lhag ma rnams sbyangs
NK107(tse)001:11307: so byang chub pa gsum pa'o de nas sa bon
NK107(tse)001:11308: phyag mtshan 'grengs pa las rdo rje phag mo sku
NK107(tse)001:11309: mdog dmar zhal gcig khro mo 'jigs pa'i zhal spyan
NK107(tse)001:11310: gsum pa skra grol ba thod pa'i 'phreng bas brgyan
NK107(tse)001:11311: pa yan lag rus pas 'phreng bas brgyan pa mgrin
NK107(tse)001:11312: pa'i 'og na phag zhal nag po mche ba gtsigs
NK107(tse)001:11313: pa skyil krung phyed pa'i gar gyis ro mnan pa
NK107(tse)001:11314: phyag gnyis pa g.yas gri gug thod pas mtshan pa
NK107(tse)001:11315: bsnams pa g.yon pa thod pa rdo rjes mtshan pa
NK107(tse)001:11316: thugs khar 'dzin pa g.yon pa'i sgyid khung nas mchan
NK107(tse)001:11317: khung g.yon pa nas kha tram kha thod pa skam
NK107(tse)001:11318: po gsum gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa'o de lta bu'i
NK107(tse)001:11319: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gsal ba me ri dang
NK107(tse)001:11320: me dpung gi nang na bzhugs pa sna tshogs 'od
NK107(tse)001:11321: 'phro ba'i zla bas rgyab yol du byas pa'o de'i
NK107(tse)001:11322: snying khar zla ba'i dal de'i steng du ah de
NK107(tse)001:11323: las 'od zer gyis tshogs dmar po dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:11324: pa 'phros pas nam mkha' 'od kyis gang pa las
NK107(tse)001:11325: lha mo de ci 'dra ba dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:11326: spyan drangs te rnal 'byor ma'i thugs khar bcug pas
NK107(tse)001:11327: lha mo de gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsgom de
NK107(tse)001:11328: rnams gcig tu gyur pa las ye shes sems dapa'i
NK107(tse)001:11329: mtshon gang ba rab tu gsal ba gcig bsgom de'i
NK107(tse)001:11330: snying gar zla ba'i dal nyungs 'bru tsam de'i dkyil
NK107(tse)001:11331: du thod pa kha t+wam gyis mtshan pa spus bris
NK107(tse)001:11332: pa tsam de'i dkyil du g.yung drung 'khyil ba myur
NK107(tse)001:11333: du bskor ba'i dbus su am la dmigs la bzlas
NK107(tse)001:11334: pa bya'o de ltar bsgom pa'i spyi bo nas lha
NK107(tse)001:11335: mo dmar mo bum pa thogs pa dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:11336: pas dbang bskur bar bsgom des dbang bskur ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:11337: nas dbang bskur bas snang ba mtha' yas dmar pos
NK107(tse)001:11338: dbu brgyan par bsgom mo de ltar thun bzhir bcad
NK107(tse)001:11339: pa bsgom bzlas pa la brtson par bya'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11340: bsgom pa la thugs ka'i ye shes sems dapa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:11341: sa bon dang phyag mtshan la dmigs la a li'i
NK107(tse)001:11342: 'phreng bas bskor zhing 'od 'phro ba ka li la
NK107(tse)001:11343: 'od 'phros pa la dmigs shing bzlas pa bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:11344: ltar gsal bar byas la bstod pa dang mchod pa
NK107(tse)001:11345: dang byin gyis brlabs kyis go cha bsam zhing gsol
NK107(tse)001:11346: ba gdab pa dang smon lam gdab pa rnams byas
NK107(tse)001:11347: la lha mo'i gzugs sa bon la bsdu sa bon
NK107(tse)001:11348: sems la bsdu sems nyid stong pa nyid kyis rgyas
NK107(tse)001:11349: btab la smon lam dang 'dod pa'i don la gsol
NK107(tse)001:11350: ba gdabs pa yang yang bya'o de nas bsgrub thabs
NK107(tse)001:11351: nas 'byung ba bzhin du rnal 'byor ma'i rdzogs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11352: rim pa bsgom pa dang de nyid la rgyas btab
NK107(tse)001:11353: te yang bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug su bsgom par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:11354: 'di ltar zla ba lnga bsgom bzlas la brtson par
NK107(tse)001:11355: byas pas rnal 'byor ma'i dngos grub chen por 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:11356: ro de dag dkyus dang sbyar na bsnyen pa rnal
NK107(tse)001:11357: 'byor ma'i tshogs bsnyen par byed la gang zag su
NK107(tse)001:11358: yis bsnyen par byed na rdo rje rnal 'byor ma
NK107(tse)001:11359: la mos pa yis thabs gang gis byed na bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11360: bzlas kyi go ma log pas byed do bsgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:11361: ni rnal 'byor ma bsgrub pas mchog dang thun mong
NK107(tse)001:11362: gi dngos grub thob par byed pa'o las kyi mtha'
NK107(tse)001:11363: ni 'gugs pa'i cho ga dang spra brtags pa'i cho
NK107(tse)001:11364: ga dang chang 'gugs pa'i cho ga dang tshangs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11365: las kyi rnam grangs lnga dang 'gro ba 'dul ba'i
NK107(tse)001:11366: cho ga dang nor 'gugs pa'i cho ga dang thod
NK107(tse)001:11367: pa'i sbyor ba'i ji ltar bya ba dang gdug pa
NK107(tse)001:11368: can tshar gcad pa la sogs pa'i cho ga rnams
NK107(tse)001:11369: so so'i sngags kyi thus dang sbyar ba ni sgrub
NK107(tse)001:11370: thabs bdun po re re'i sngags la smos pa'o 'dir
NK107(tse)001:11371: ni gong du bstan pa'i bsnyen bsgrub kyi sngags phye
NK107(tse)001:11372: ba las shes par bya'o ji ltar ni sgrub thabs
NK107(tse)001:11373: nas byung ba'i yi ge sbyor 'brel ni sngags bsdu
NK107(tse)001:11374: ba'i 'khor lo las shes pa'o sgrub thabs so so'i
NK107(tse)001:11375: rtsa ba'i sngags bzung la zhes pa ni 'di'i gong
NK107(tse)001:11376: du bstan pa las shes par bya'o de yang bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11377: pa pos ni rnal 'byor ma la mos pa'i gang
NK107(tse)001:11378: zag gis bzlas pa brtsam pa ni lha'i sku mdog
NK107(tse)001:11379: dang phyag mtshan gsal bar dmigs la bstod bzlas pa
NK107(tse)001:11380: bya ste zhes pa'i don no de la rdo rje
NK107(tse)001:11381: rnal 'byor ma'i bskyed par byed pa'i yi ge ni
NK107(tse)001:11382: a'i gsal byed 'od du 'phros pa las las dang
NK107(tse)001:11383: bag chags sbyangs te cho ga ni sems bskyed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11384: ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i thabs so yan lag ni
NK107(tse)001:11385: bcu drug tu byas pa'o kun rdzogs pa ni dang
NK107(tse)001:11386: po bsnyen pa dang sems bskyed pa dang smon lam
NK107(tse)001:11387: gdab pa yan chad rdzogs pa'o bskyed pa'i ting nge
NK107(tse)001:11388: 'dzin bsgom pa'i skabs su so so ni sgrub thabs
NK107(tse)001:11389: bdun la mos la kha dog ni dkar ba dmar
NK107(tse)001:11390: nag dang ser ba la sogs pa dang sbyar te
NK107(tse)001:11391: 'dir ni kha dog dkar ba dmar nag dang ser
NK107(tse)001:11392: ba la sogs so so dang sbyar te 'dir ni
NK107(tse)001:11393: kha dog dmar po'i 'od 'phro ba las rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:11394: mar bsgom mo des go phye nas so so'i khro
NK107(tse)001:11395: mo la mos par bya'o de yang ji ltar bya
NK107(tse)001:11396: zhe na bcom pa ni rnal 'byor pa btsun mo'i
NK107(tse)001:11397: b+ha ga las yangs dog gnyis su 'dzin pa'i rtog
NK107(tse)001:11398: pa med pas ngan song gsum gyis sdug basngala bcom
NK107(tse)001:11399: pa las skye ba'i rgyun bcad de nyid la rnam
NK107(tse)001:11400: par rtog pa las kyi rgyun chad pas nyon mongs
NK107(tse)001:11401: pa ma lus pa bcom la tha mal gyi lus
NK107(tse)001:11402: su mi gnas te rnal 'byor ma'i skur bzhengs pas
NK107(tse)001:11403: lus la bdag tu 'dzin pa'i zhen pa bcom la
NK107(tse)001:11404: khro mo'i rgyan cha lugs dang ldan te ngag bzlas
NK107(tse)001:11405: pa sngags kyi 'phreng ba dang sems bskyed rdzogs zung
NK107(tse)001:11406: 'jug gnyis su med par ldan pas na ldan no
NK107(tse)001:11407: de ltar na lus ngag yid gsum du 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11408: zhen pa las 'das pas 'khor ba'i nyes skyon med
NK107(tse)001:11409: pas sku mdog dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:11410: khro mo'i gzugs su ldan pa ni tha mal pa
NK107(tse)001:11411: las lha mo'i skur bzhengs pa'o de ka bzhengs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11412: thugs ka nas 'od dmar po 'phros pa las ye
NK107(tse)001:11413: shes ni me long lta bu la sogs te mtshan
NK107(tse)001:11414: nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga las grub pa'i sems
NK107(tse)001:11415: dpa' spyan drangs te lha mo dang gnyis su med
NK107(tse)001:11416: par bstim mo de nas lha mo dmar mo dpag
NK107(tse)001:11417: tu med pa rnams kyis dbang bskur bar bsam rigs
NK107(tse)001:11418: kyi bdag po snang ba mtha' yas kyis dbu brgyan
NK107(tse)001:11419: no de ltar khro mo'i sku la brten nas grub
NK107(tse)001:11420: pa de nyid dngos su grub pas byin gyis brlabs
NK107(tse)001:11421: kyi tshogs dpag tu med pa la longs spyod do
NK107(tse)001:11422: 'di nyid thob par 'dod pas dus rtag tu bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11423: na thun mong dang mchog gi 'bras bu nges par
NK107(tse)001:11424: thob bo de yang a sa bon li khro mo
NK107(tse)001:11425: de gnyis 'dus pa las khro mo dbang phyug mngon
NK107(tse)001:11426: par 'byung ba'o ka rdzogs pa li ye shes de
NK107(tse)001:11427: gnyis 'dus pa las lha cig skyes ba'i don rgyud
NK107(tse)001:11428: la skyes pa'o 'phreng ba bzlas pa'o dmigs te ni
NK107(tse)001:11429: khro mo'i sku rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs pa las
NK107(tse)001:11430: dmigs pa dang thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' la
NK107(tse)001:11431: dmigs pa dang ye shes sems dapa'i thugs ka'i sa
NK107(tse)001:11432: bon phyag mtshan a li ka li'i 'phreng ba la
NK107(tse)001:11433: dmigs pa'o rnal ba sems 'byor pa bskyed pa'i rim
NK107(tse)001:11434: pa'o de ltar na sems dang lha mo'i skur 'byor
NK107(tse)001:11435: pa'o blo ni 'gyur ba dang bcas pa rtog pa
NK107(tse)001:11436: tha dad pa'i 'phro lu gcod gnas par bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:11437: ltar bskyed pa'i snying po'i ting nge 'dzin rig pa
NK107(tse)001:11438: yid la gsal bar byas pas rang lus sku phyag
NK107(tse)001:11439: rgya chen po'i rnal 'byor du byas te stong pa
NK107(tse)001:11440: nyid kyi rgyas gdab par bya'o de ltar rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:11441: pa'i sems rdzogs pa'i rim pa la brten no de
NK107(tse)001:11442: ltar bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu byas te stong pa
NK107(tse)001:11443: nyid las slar sa bon dang phyag mtshan la sogs
NK107(tse)001:11444: te khro mo ye shes kyi sku lus su byas
NK107(tse)001:11445: te de nyid kyis ni de ltar bskyed rdzogs gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11446: la yang nas yang du goms par spyod na sgrub
NK107(tse)001:11447: thabs so so'i zla ba drug dang bdun dang dgu
NK107(tse)001:11448: ste gcig dang gnyis dang gsum dang 'di ni lnga
NK107(tse)001:11449: yis ni gdon mi za bar 'grub pa'o zhes shes
NK107(tse)001:11450: rab gtso bor gyur pa rnal 'byor ma'i bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11451: thabs bstan nas da ni gsum pa lha mo 'od
NK107(tse)001:11452: zer can gyi sgrub thabs khyad par can bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:11453: ni gong ma ni sgrub thabs gtso bor 'gyur ba'i
NK107(tse)001:11454: byin brlabs yin la 'dir ni dngos grub ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11455: te thun mong du bsgrub pa dang mchog gi dngos
NK107(tse)001:11456: grub 'dod pa'i phyir bsgrub pa'o thun mong la gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11457: te 'jig rten pa'i thun mong ni mig sman gyis
NK107(tse)001:11458: khams gsum gsal bar bya ba dang mi snang bas
NK107(tse)001:11459: sgrib shing bsgrub pa dang bcud kyis len pas rgyun
NK107(tse)001:11460: gcad bsgrub pa dang rkang mgyogs kyis rdzu 'phrul bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11461: pa dang ri lus las kyi mtha' sna tshogs bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11462: pa'o sa 'og gis lta stangs bsgrub pa dang 'di
NK107(tse)001:11463: ltar drug gis 'jig rten pa'i thun mong gi las
NK107(tse)001:11464: thogs pa med pa'o 'jig rten pa'i mchog gi bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11465: pa ni rin po che gter gyi bsgrub pas nor
NK107(tse)001:11466: la longs spyod pa dang rin po che tshe bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11467: kyis tshe la longs spyod pa dang spo ba khyad
NK107(tse)001:11468: par can gyis bsgrub pas gzhan gyi longs spyod la
NK107(tse)001:11469: dbang bsgyur ba dang gsad pa thun mong ma yin
NK107(tse)001:11470: pa'i bsgrub pas 'gal byed kyi srog 'phrog pa'o mchog
NK107(tse)001:11471: gi dngos grub ni sprul pa sku'i 'od kyi khyim
NK107(tse)001:11472: la bslabs pas snang ba 'od la goms pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11473: longs sku'i bsgrub pa snang ba sku'i rang bzhin la
NK107(tse)001:11474: bslab pa dang chos nyid kyi bar ma do'i tshad
NK107(tse)001:11475: 'di nyid la zin pa dang chos kyi sku'i bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11476: pa nam mkha' la bslabs pas stong pa nyid la
NK107(tse)001:11477: goms pas stobs su 'gyur ba'o mchog gi thun mong
NK107(tse)001:11478: gi bsgrub pa 'jig rten pa'i bsgrub pa ni 'byung
NK107(tse)001:11479: ba bzhi'i sgra la bslab pa bem po'i bsgrub pas
NK107(tse)001:11480: lam nye bar mtshon pa'o spyir de dag ston par
NK107(tse)001:11481: byed pa ni lha mo 'od zer can gyis bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11482: pa ste 'di la rgya gar na bsgrub lugs mi
NK107(tse)001:11483: 'dra ba stong dang bdun bzhugs so 'di la tshul
NK107(tse)001:11484: bzhin du bsgrubs na dngos grub myur du thob pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11485: sgrub thabs la 'di las lhag pa med do de
NK107(tse)001:11486: la 'dir ston pa rdo rje 'chang gis bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11487: thabs sku'i sgrub pa thun mong ma yin pa la
NK107(tse)001:11488: brten nas khyad par gyi las bsgrub par byed pa
NK107(tse)001:11489: stobs 'byin par byed pa dang gsung gi sgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:11490: thun mong ma yin pa la brten nas thun mong
NK107(tse)001:11491: ma yin pa'i sgrub pa gsal ba'i sgron ma dang
NK107(tse)001:11492: thugs kyi bsgrub pa thun mong ma yin pa la
NK107(tse)001:11493: brten nas thun mong dang mchog gnyis ka'i sgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:11494: yan lag drug rdo rje gsang ba phyag rgya can
NK107(tse)001:11495: dang gsum du b+hud d+ha yis gsungs pa las 'dir
NK107(tse)001:11496: thugs kyi sgrub thabs 'gro ba'i sems kyis las stongs
NK107(tse)001:11497: pas 'gyur bar gsungs pa ni de yang yan lag
NK107(tse)001:11498: 'dus pa'i cho ga'i rim pa ji ltar bya ba
NK107(tse)001:11499: dang bzlas pa dang bsgrub pa'i dus bstan pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11500: las 'dir yan lag 'dus pa la gsum ste sngon
NK107(tse)001:11501: du bsnyen pa ji ltar bya ba'i rim pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11502: de nas sgrub pa'i man ngag dang bsgrub pa las
NK107(tse)001:11503: kyi matha'i sbyor ba dang gsum mo de la bsnyen
NK107(tse)001:11504: pa ni yi ge bco lnga pa la 'bum phrag
NK107(tse)001:11505: bdun du bskyal lo de ltar bsnyen pa rdzogs nas
NK107(tse)001:11506: sgrub pa la dgu ste dang po byang chub mchog
NK107(tse)001:11507: tu sems bskyed pa dang de nas sdom pa bzung
NK107(tse)001:11508: ba dang gnyis bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11509: gsum stong pa nyid du ba sgom pa dang bzhi
NK107(tse)001:11510: de'i ngang las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa
NK107(tse)001:11511: bsgom pa dang lnga sa bon dang phyag mtshan gsal
NK107(tse)001:11512: bas lha mo'i sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gsal bar
NK107(tse)001:11513: bsgom pa dang drug de la ye shes sems dpa'
NK107(tse)001:11514: gzhug cing lha mo'i sku'i gzi mdangs bskyed pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11515: bdun dbang bskur bas lha so so'i gtso bos brgyan
NK107(tse)001:11516: pa dang brgyad de las skyo na gzugs bsdu zhing
NK107(tse)001:11517: bzlas pa bya ba'i rim pa'o de la byang chub
NK107(tse)001:11518: mchog gi sems bskyed pa ni 'gro ba drug gi
NK107(tse)001:11519: skye gnas thams cad rgyun chad par bya'o de la
NK107(tse)001:11520: blo yang nas yang du mos par bya'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:11521: sdom pa bzung ba ni bdag gis sdig pa mi
NK107(tse)001:11522: dge ba'i las ci byas pa thams cad la 'gyod
NK107(tse)001:11523: bshags la phyis mi byed par bla ma dang sangs
NK107(tse)001:11524: rgyas rnams mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs la de
NK107(tse)001:11525: dag gi spyan sngar dam bca' 'o de'i steng du
NK107(tse)001:11526: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rjes sems can rnams
NK107(tse)001:11527: 'khor ba las bsgral bar bya'o dam bca' 'o de
NK107(tse)001:11528: dag kun gyi sngon du rang gi bla ma la
NK107(tse)001:11529: ci 'byor pa'i tshogs kyis mchod pa gal che'o de
NK107(tse)001:11530: nas bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom pa ni yi ge
NK107(tse)001:11531: ra las sna tshogs rdo rje kha dog sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:11532: pa rgya chen po gcig bsgom par bya'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:11533: badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes lan gsum barjoda
NK107(tse)001:11534: pas brtan par bya'o de'i ngang las h+aum zhes barjoda
NK107(tse)001:11535: pas h+aum las 'od 'phros pas phyi snod kyi 'jig
NK107(tse)001:11536: rten rnams 'od du zhu tshur 'dus pas bdag dang
NK107(tse)001:11537: snod kyi sems can rnams zhu nas de ltar 'od
NK107(tse)001:11538: du gnas pa'i rang bzhin las phyi snod dang nang
NK107(tse)001:11539: bcud gnyis ga h+aum gi zhabs bskyed la bsdu zhabs
NK107(tse)001:11540: kyu ha la ha zla tshes la zla tshes sems
NK107(tse)001:11541: kyis rang bzhin du dmigs pa'o de ltar bdag dang
NK107(tse)001:11542: phyi nang gi dngos po rnams stongs sangs kyis bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11543: mo de'i ngang las e yam kham pam ram zhes
NK107(tse)001:11544: barjoda pas zla tshes las sgra de 'byung bas nam
NK107(tse)001:11545: makha'i dal gru gsum pa kha dog mthing kha rgya
NK107(tse)001:11546: chen por bsgom mo de'i steng du rlung gi dal
NK107(tse)001:11547: zla kham du bsgom de'i steng du chu'i dal zlum
NK107(tse)001:11548: por bsgom de'i steng du sa'i dal gru bzhi ser
NK107(tse)001:11549: por bsgom de'i steng du ram las me'i dal gru
NK107(tse)001:11550: gsum dmar po rgya khyon dpag tu med pa bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11551: de nas b+h+r+aum zhes barjoda pas gzhal yas khang gru
NK107(tse)001:11552: bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs dang bcas pa rin po
NK107(tse)001:11553: che'i 'phreng ba dang 'chun 'phyang dang rnga yab la
NK107(tse)001:11554: sogs pas bklubs pa lte ba tsakra rtsibs bzhi pad
NK107(tse)001:11555: mas mtshon pa mu khyud gsum dang bcas pa phyi
NK107(tse)001:11556: ma rdo rje rwa ba me ri dang me ri
NK107(tse)001:11557: sna tshogs 'od 'phro bar bsgom mo de ltar bskyed
NK107(tse)001:11558: pa'i dbus kyi lte ba la h+aum sngon po 'od
NK107(tse)001:11559: zer brgya phrag dpag tu med pa 'phros pa las
NK107(tse)001:11560: ka la'i tshogs kyis bskor ba de dag las 'od
NK107(tse)001:11561: 'phros pas zla ba dang nyi ma dang pad+ma'i gdan
NK107(tse)001:11562: du bsgom mo de'i steng du sa bon h+aum sngon
NK107(tse)001:11563: po a li dang ka li'i 'phreng ba'i bar du
NK107(tse)001:11564: bsgom mo de 'od du zhu ba las lcags kyu
NK107(tse)001:11565: 'od du 'phro ba 'od kyi gzi mdangs yod pa
NK107(tse)001:11566: gcig tu bsgom mo de nyid 'phros 'dus don gnyis
NK107(tse)001:11567: byas pa las h+aum chen po de las lha mo
NK107(tse)001:11568: dmar mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi ma btsan dkyil du
NK107(tse)001:11569: bzhugs pa phyag g.yas pa gnyis na lcags kyu dang
NK107(tse)001:11570: mda' bsnams pa g.yon pa gnyis na zhags pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11571: gzhu bsnams pa sku la rin po che sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:11572: pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa dbu skra ser po thur
NK107(tse)001:11573: la bsgrol ba spyan gsum pa zhal bsgrad cing mche
NK107(tse)001:11574: ba gtsigs pa ljags dril zhing zhal gyi sgo nas
NK107(tse)001:11575: h+aum zhes bsgrogs pas 'od zer dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:11576: 'phro ba sgom par bya'o de nas lha mo'i snying
NK107(tse)001:11577: kha nas 'od zer dmar po dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:11578: 'phros pas nam makha'i khams khengs par gyur pa las
NK107(tse)001:11579: rang 'dra ba'i sems dpa' mang po spyan drangs te
NK107(tse)001:11580: khro mo'i snying khar bzhug go lha mo'i thugs khar
NK107(tse)001:11581: zla ba'i dal me long kha bub pa tsam de'i
NK107(tse)001:11582: steng du nyi ma'i dal de'i steng du ye shes
NK107(tse)001:11583: pa chag gang ba de'i thugs khar lcags kyu de'i
NK107(tse)001:11584: dbus su h+aum la a li dang ka li'i 'phreng
NK107(tse)001:11585: bas rnam par bskor bar bsgom pas khro mo yang
NK107(tse)001:11586: rab tu 'jigs pas gzi brjid dang ldan pa 'jig
NK107(tse)001:11587: rten pa rnams rab tu sdig par mdzad pa khro
NK107(tse)001:11588: bo dang khro mo rnams rab tu dpa' bkod par
NK107(tse)001:11589: byed pa bsgom mo de nas ye shes sems dapa'i
NK107(tse)001:11590: thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od 'phros pas nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:11591: la lha mo bum pa thogs pa grangs med pa
NK107(tse)001:11592: sprin 'thibs pa tsam 'thibs nas dbang bskur te de
NK107(tse)001:11593: bdud rtsi lnga'i chu rgyun 'babs pas rdo rje mi
NK107(tse)001:11594: bskyod pas dbu brgyan par bsgom mo de ltar gsum
NK107(tse)001:11595: du gsal bar bsgom mo de nas lha mo'i gzugs
NK107(tse)001:11596: ye shes sems dpa' la bsdu ye shes sems dpa'
NK107(tse)001:11597: sa bon la dang phyag mtshan la bsdu de sems
NK107(tse)001:11598: la bsdu sems nyid stong pa nyid kyi ngang las
NK107(tse)001:11599: gong ma la mos pa byas la spyan drangs zhing
NK107(tse)001:11600: bzhugs su gsol ba dang de la bstod pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11601: mchod pa dang gtor ma dbul ba dang 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11602: don la gsol ba gdab cing smon lam gdab pa
NK107(tse)001:11603: rnams byas la bzlas pa bya ba ni de la
NK107(tse)001:11604: 'dir ni thog ma'i yi ge gtso bo +amoh sde
NK107(tse)001:11605: tshan drug pa'i 'og mar des brgyan sde tshan bzhi
NK107(tse)001:11606: pa'i tha ma a li'i gsum pas de mgo bzung
NK107(tse)001:11607: ni smi sde tshan lnga ba'i bzhi pa ba sde
NK107(tse)001:11608: tshan gnyis pa'i gsum pa dza drug pa'i gnyis pa
NK107(tse)001:11609: de la sbyar zhes badz+ra'o sde tshan gsum pa'i dang
NK107(tse)001:11610: po 'char byed la ta a li bcu gsum pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11611: brgyan to de la a li gsum pas bzung te
NK107(tse)001:11612: sde drug pa'i bzhi pa la shwa i dgu pa
NK107(tse)001:11613: dang ldan ri sde tshan lnga pa'i tha ma ma
NK107(tse)001:11614: ka'i tha ma'i steng mas si ni ha sde tshan
NK107(tse)001:11615: gnyis pa'i la tsa a li lnga pa +au de'i
NK107(tse)001:11616: zhabs nas bzung pa ni thu sde tshan drug pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11617: dang po ra a li gsum pas bzung du yang
NK107(tse)001:11618: de dag gnyis pa la ni tsu ru tsu ru
NK107(tse)001:11619: ka li tha mi steng ma la ha a li
NK107(tse)001:11620: lnga pas bzung h+aum stong pas gnan h+aum gnyis 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:11621: h+aum h+aum sde tshan drug pa'i lnga pa la swa
NK107(tse)001:11622: ka'i tha ma'i steng ma la ha +amo rasmi badz+ra
NK107(tse)001:11623: ta to shwa ri tsu ru tsu ru h+aum h+aum
NK107(tse)001:11624: s+w+aa h+aa zhes bsnyen sngags so 'di dag bsgrub pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11625: thabs las shes so badz+ra tsan d+ha sa dwa lo
NK107(tse)001:11626: ra sti sta pa ma lo ka h+aum h+aum s+w+aa
NK107(tse)001:11627: h+aa ma h+aa b+he sha d+ha ra d+h+aa r+aa ye
NK107(tse)001:11628: s+w+aa h+aa sa dwa ma h+aa a ra rnam pu
NK107(tse)001:11629: tsa pra ti dzahho ma h+aa b+ha lim sti sta
NK107(tse)001:11630: sti sta b+hun dza ho ho ha ha kha hi
NK107(tse)001:11631: kha hi +amo badz+ra sa man+ta h+aum h+aum ma ra
NK107(tse)001:11632: ya ma ra ya sho sha sho sha ya ki
NK107(tse)001:11633: li ki li phata phata a mo ka h+aum h+aum
NK107(tse)001:11634: b+hun dza ma ra ya ma ra ya s+pho ta
NK107(tse)001:11635: phata phata sa dwa ba pam ma h+aa d+ha d+hu
NK107(tse)001:11636: ra ha ha he he tsan tra phata su ra
NK107(tse)001:11637: h+ya h+aum s+t+aam ya zhes pa 'di nyid sngags kyi
NK107(tse)001:11638: rim pa la rnal 'byor pa yis dal ba med
NK107(tse)001:11639: par bzlas na dngos grub 'byung ngo de dag gi
NK107(tse)001:11640: bsgrub pa'i tshad ni zla ba lnga na gdon mi
NK107(tse)001:11641: za bar 'grub bo mtha' las sbyor la bsdu ba
NK107(tse)001:11642: ni rengs pa dang dbye ba dang bskrad pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11643: bsad pa dang gso ba dang rab tu bcing ba
NK107(tse)001:11644: la sogs pa bsgrub thabs nas gsungs so dkyus dang
NK107(tse)001:11645: sbyar na yan lag gi cho ga'i rnam grangs dgur
NK107(tse)001:11646: bsdus pa las lha mo 'od zer can gyi cho
NK107(tse)001:11647: ga'i las rdzogs pa'o de las bsdus na bsnyen pa
NK107(tse)001:11648: dang sgrub pa dang mthar sdud sngar dang mtshungs zhes
NK107(tse)001:11649: pa ni rnal 'byor ma'i dang spyi lto 'dra zhes
NK107(tse)001:11650: pa'o lha mo ni khro mo yin yang zhal yid
NK107(tse)001:11651: tsam 'dzum pa'i mdangs yod pa'o mdog da nga ni
NK107(tse)001:11652: dmar mo 'od dang ldan pa zhal gcig pa spyan
NK107(tse)001:11653: gsum pa rab tu khros pa phyag ni bzhi pa
NK107(tse)001:11654: ste lcags kyu dang mda' dang zhags pa dang gzhu
NK107(tse)001:11655: bsnams pa'o thugs ni ye shes sems dpa' dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:11656: pa la gsal bar rnal 'byor ma'i lus kyis phung
NK107(tse)001:11657: po gnas par bya ste bzlas pas dus na ye
NK107(tse)001:11658: shes sems dapa'i thugs ka'i a li dang ka li'i
NK107(tse)001:11659: 'od kyi 'phreng ba la dmigs shing bzlas pa la
NK107(tse)001:11660: brtson par bya'o 'di'i dus na rang gi yi dam
NK107(tse)001:11661: la ci 'dod pa'i gsol ba gdab bo ci ltar
NK107(tse)001:11662: 'dod pa'i don bdag la ster bar bsgom mo sems
NK107(tse)001:11663: kyi yi ge ni h+aum sngon po las 'od dmar
NK107(tse)001:11664: po rab tu gsal bar 'phros pa las rang ci
NK107(tse)001:11665: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu la dmigs te rengs pa'i las
NK107(tse)001:11666: 'grub par 'dod na 'od dkar po gyen la langs
NK107(tse)001:11667: pa spro bskrad na ser pos bya dbye na ljang
NK107(tse)001:11668: khu bya bu 'dod na ser pos nor 'dod na
NK107(tse)001:11669: dkar pos zhi rgyas kyi las sna tshogs su 'phro
NK107(tse)001:11670: 'jigs pa brgyad spong bar 'dod pas dmar pos spro
NK107(tse)001:11671: lha rnams dbang du bsdu bar 'dod na dkar po
NK107(tse)001:11672: la ser po'i mdangs yod par spro mi rnams dbang
NK107(tse)001:11673: du bsdu bar 'dod na dmar po la dkar po'i
NK107(tse)001:11674: 'tsher yod par spro lha min dang gnod sbyin rnams
NK107(tse)001:11675: dbang du bsdu bar 'dod na sngon por spro gsad
NK107(tse)001:11676: pa'i las 'grub par 'dod na nag por spro sngags
NK107(tse)001:11677: kyi bzlas pa dang kha dog bstun la bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:11678: ltar dmigs pa gsal na gang yang 'grub par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:11679: ba la the tshom med do de ltar na bskyed
NK107(tse)001:11680: pa dang rdzogs pa gnyis rnal 'byor pas zung 'jug
NK107(tse)001:11681: tu bsgom pas rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po cog
NK107(tse)001:11682: bzhag gi dgongs pa la dus rgyun du gnas pa'o
NK107(tse)001:11683: de ltar dus rtag tu bsgom pa'am yang na nyin
NK107(tse)001:11684: zhag phrug gcig la thun drug tu byas te rang
NK107(tse)001:11685: gi rgyud la brten na sku'i sgrub pa la zla
NK107(tse)001:11686: ba dgu dang zhes pa grub pa'i rtags so gsung
NK107(tse)001:11687: la zla ba bdun dang zhes rtags 'ong ngo 'di
NK107(tse)001:11688: la zla ba lnga bsgom pa yis grub pa'i rtags
NK107(tse)001:11689: 'ong ste 'di dag la nges par 'grub par gdon
NK107(tse)001:11690: mi za'o zhes gsum pa lha mo 'od zer can
NK107(tse)001:11691: gyi sgrub pa thun mong ma yin pa bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:11692: da ni las thams cad kyi mthar thug pa shes
NK107(tse)001:11693: rab gtso bor gyur pa lha mo tsan ti ka'i
NK107(tse)001:11694: sgrub pa thun mong ma yin bstan pa ni las
NK107(tse)001:11695: ni 'phrin las bzhi'i las kyi mtha' zhi rgyas dbang
NK107(tse)001:11696: drag rnams la thug pas na de dag gi mtha'
NK107(tse)001:11697: phye ba las sems can gzhan zhi bar byed pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11698: las kyi mtha' dang rgyas par byed pa dang dbang
NK107(tse)001:11699: dang tshar gcad pa'i las kyi 'gal byed cham la
NK107(tse)001:11700: 'bebs pa'i sngags kyi nus pa'o rnams zhes bya ba
NK107(tse)001:11701: ni thog dang ser ba dang gaza'i 'phrul 'khor bskor
NK107(tse)001:11702: ba dang 'byung po rnams tshar gcod pa'i las so
NK107(tse)001:11703: ston pa ni lha mo tsan ti ka bsgrubs nas
NK107(tse)001:11704: las gang la byas kyang thogs pa med par 'grub
NK107(tse)001:11705: bo lha mo tsan ti ka 'di la'ng sku dang
NK107(tse)001:11706: gsung dang thugs dang gsum las 'di sku'i sgrub pa'o
NK107(tse)001:11707: 'di la mngon par rtogs pa lam gyis chos drug
NK107(tse)001:11708: ste dang po sngon du 'gro ba la bsnyen pa
NK107(tse)001:11709: byas nas cho ga ldan pa'i rnal 'byor du bya
NK107(tse)001:11710: ba dang rang gi sems kyi dag bya bsam zhing
NK107(tse)001:11711: sems bskyed pa dang bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom zhing
NK107(tse)001:11712: stong pa nyid du bsgom pa dang gsum gzhal yas
NK107(tse)001:11713: khang gdan dang bcas pa bsgom zhing sa bon dang
NK107(tse)001:11714: phyag mtshan gyi rnam pa gsal bar bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:11715: bzhi lha mo'i sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gsal bar
NK107(tse)001:11716: bsgom zhing yi ge gzhug pa'i sbyor ba yis ye
NK107(tse)001:11717: shes sems dpa' dang gnyis su med par bstim pa
NK107(tse)001:11718: dang lnga lha dbang bskur zhing bsdu ba dang bzlas
NK107(tse)001:11719: pa'i rnal 'byor ji ltar bya ba dang dus nam
NK107(tse)001:11720: grub pa bstan pa'o de la sngon du bsnyen pa
NK107(tse)001:11721: bya ba ni rang gi bla ma la tshogs bsags
NK107(tse)001:11722: pa dang 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i sems spangs la
NK107(tse)001:11723: gnas dben par bsgrub pa bya'o sngon du yi ge
NK107(tse)001:11724: dgu pa la bsnyen pa 'bum phrag bdun bskyal nas
NK107(tse)001:11725: de nas bsgrub pa'i dus su rang gi sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:11726: dag bya bsam pa ni sems lha'i sku la gtad
NK107(tse)001:11727: cing yang nas yang du bsgom par bya'o de'i rjes
NK107(tse)001:11728: la sems bskyed de khams gsum gyi sems can 'di
NK107(tse)001:11729: dag sdug basngala dang bral bar byas la bde ba
NK107(tse)001:11730: dang 'phrad par ci nas kyang bya'o snyam pa'i blo
NK107(tse)001:11731: yis sems bskyed do de nas de'i ngang las bsrung
NK107(tse)001:11732: ba bsgom pa snga ma dang 'dra'o stong pa yang
NK107(tse)001:11733: 'dra'o de'i ngang las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo
NK107(tse)001:11734: bzhi pa gdan yang snga ma dang 'dra'o sa bon
NK107(tse)001:11735: h+aum phyag mtshan 'khor lo dang gzhan dang 'dra'o sa
NK107(tse)001:11736: bon dang phyag mtshan las 'phros 'dus pa las lha
NK107(tse)001:11737: mo sku mdog dkar mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi ma
NK107(tse)001:11738: g.yas 'khor lo dang thod pa g.yon sbrul zhags dang
NK107(tse)001:11739: glog gi 'phreng ba bsnams pa sku la sbrul gdug
NK107(tse)001:11740: pa sna tshogs pas brgyan pas zhal bzhad cing zhi
NK107(tse)001:11741: ba'i tshul yod par bsgom mo de ltar rang gi
NK107(tse)001:11742: snying kha'i sa bon las 'od 'phros pa las nam
NK107(tse)001:11743: mkhar ye shes sems dpa' dpag tu med pa spros
NK107(tse)001:11744: te lha mo'i thugs khar bzhug go de'i thugs khar
NK107(tse)001:11745: zla ba dang nyi ma'i steng du a li dang
NK107(tse)001:11746: ka lis bskor ba'i dbus su 'od zer dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:11747: med pa 'phro ba gcig phyag mtshan 'khor lo rtsibs
NK107(tse)001:11748: bzhi dang bcas pa bsgom mo de la gong ltar
NK107(tse)001:11749: lha mos dbang bskur rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbu
NK107(tse)001:11750: brgyan pa'o de ltar gsal bar byas pa de la
NK107(tse)001:11751: skyo na gzugs bsdu ba byas pa rgyas gdab po'o
NK107(tse)001:11752: de nas spyan drangs pa dang bzhugs su gsol ba
NK107(tse)001:11753: dang bstod pa dang mchod pa dang gsol ba gdab
NK107(tse)001:11754: pa dang smon lam gdab pa rnams bya'o de nas
NK107(tse)001:11755: bzlas pa bya ste +amo tsan ti d+hi ka tsan
NK107(tse)001:11756: d+ha tsan d+he ye s+w+aa h+aa bsnyen pa'o +amo tsan
NK107(tse)001:11757: d+hi ka su ru su ru sma ra sma ra
NK107(tse)001:11758: h+aum h+aum phata phata +amo +amo h+aum yam ram kham
NK107(tse)001:11759: b+h+r+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum dza h+aum bam hoh b+ha ling
NK107(tse)001:11760: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi ha ha he he +amo +aa
NK107(tse)001:11761: s+w+aa h+aa +amo b+ha s+w+aa h+aa ke s+w+aa h+aa ri
NK107(tse)001:11762: s+w+aa h+aa +amo k+sha s+w+aa h+aa g+h+yu b+h+ya pyam d+yam
NK107(tse)001:11763: kin+la&a&a&a t+haya&a&a&a yet+ya&a&a&a sam b+ha g+ha tam s+w+aa h+aa ma
NK107(tse)001:11764: l+ai ma l+ai sa tri e ka ra h+aum h+aum
NK107(tse)001:11765: phata phata s+w+aa h+aa mchod pa'i sngags ni gong gis
NK107(tse)001:11766: shes so de yang ye shes sems dapa'i thugs kha'i
NK107(tse)001:11767: 'od dang yi ge'i 'brel pa la dmigs shing bzlas
NK107(tse)001:11768: pas las la sbyar ba'i tshe na gang la yang
NK107(tse)001:11769: zla ba gcig gis nges par 'grub bo de dag
NK107(tse)001:11770: dkyus dang sbyar na de yang cho ga ni drug
NK107(tse)001:11771: tu mngon rtogs nas 'grigs pa dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK107(tse)001:11772: 'byor pas ni bskyed pa'i rim pa la mkhas shing
NK107(tse)001:11773: dmigs pa gsal ba'o rang ni gzhan ma yin pa'o
NK107(tse)001:11774: sems ni thog ma 'dus ma byas pas rgyu rkyen
NK107(tse)001:11775: la mi ltos bar du mtha' ma gang la yang
NK107(tse)001:11776: mi gnas pas ngo bo gcig tu zang thal tha
NK107(tse)001:11777: ma re dgos dang gnyis su ma mchis pas skye
NK107(tse)001:11778: ba med pa'i snying po'o dag bya'o ni blo bur
NK107(tse)001:11779: rtog pa'i dri ma bsal ba la yi dam gyi
NK107(tse)001:11780: lha mo la dmigs shing yang nas yang du yi
NK107(tse)001:11781: dam dang rang gi bla ma spyi bo gtsug nyi
NK107(tse)001:11782: zla'i gnas su bsam par bya ste gsol ba yang
NK107(tse)001:11783: nas yang du gdab bo lha mo ni zhi ba'i
NK107(tse)001:11784: bzhad yod pa gzugs kyi ni zhal gcig phyag bzhi
NK107(tse)001:11785: pa rab tu gzhon sha chags shing dkar ba'i mdangs
NK107(tse)001:11786: yod pa mdog gsum la zhes pa sgrub thabs spyi
NK107(tse)001:11787: la dgongs pa'o 'dir sku mdog dkar mo shel gyi
NK107(tse)001:11788: mdog lta bu bsgom mo yi ge h+aum bzhugs pa
NK107(tse)001:11789: ni lha mo'i snying khar sbyor ba yis ni rang
NK107(tse)001:11790: 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' bsgom par byed pa'o
NK107(tse)001:11791: mi mthun ni lha mo'i sgrub thabs gsum po kha
NK107(tse)001:11792: dog mi mthun pa'o mtshan nyid gsal ba la ni
NK107(tse)001:11793: so so'i sku mdog dang mthun pa'i 'od kyis ye
NK107(tse)001:11794: shes sems dpa' bzhugs pa'o de'i 'od las ni khro
NK107(tse)001:11795: mo so so'i khro mo dang 'dra ba'i ye shes
NK107(tse)001:11796: sems dpa' bsgom zhes pa'i tha tshig go de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11797: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i las rdzogs nas ni stong pa
NK107(tse)001:11798: nyid kyi rgyas gdab bo de ltar gsal ba las
NK107(tse)001:11799: skyon rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa ni rang gi
NK107(tse)001:11800: sems kyis snang ba'i chos thams cad skye med rang
NK107(tse)001:11801: dag tu khyer bas gnas lugs kyi rang bzhin rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:11802: pa chen po'i rang bzhin zhes bya'o de dag las
NK107(tse)001:11803: skyo na bzlas par bya ba ni a li dang
NK107(tse)001:11804: ka li dang dbyangs kyi yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK107(tse)001:11805: gnyis kyis 'khrul gyi sdebs kyis lha mo 'di rnams
NK107(tse)001:11806: gsum gyis sngags byang shes par byas la zhes pa
NK107(tse)001:11807: ste 'dir ni gcig las ma bstan no rtags dang
NK107(tse)001:11808: grub pa'i dus ni dad pa dang ldan pa gcig
NK107(tse)001:11809: gis de ltar rtag tu bsgom pa yis sku'i bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11810: pa las la sbyar ba zla ba gcig gis 'grub
NK107(tse)001:11811: bo gsung gnyis thugs gsum gyis ni so so'i 'dod
NK107(tse)001:11812: pa'i don kun 'grub pa'o zhes bzhi pa dngos grub
NK107(tse)001:11813: kun gyi mthar thug pa shes rab gtso bo'i sgrub
NK107(tse)001:11814: thabs lha mo tsan ti ka sgrub pa bstan nas
NK107(tse)001:11815: da ni lnga pa thabs gtso bor gyur pa las
NK107(tse)001:11816: thams cad kyis mthar thug pa gshin rje gshed kyi
NK107(tse)001:11817: sgrub thabs bstan pa ni thabs kyis ni yab la
NK107(tse)001:11818: dgongs pa yin la bsgrub pa ni sku dngos su
NK107(tse)001:11819: gsal ba'i tshad dang gsung nus pa rdzogs pa'i tshad
NK107(tse)001:11820: dang thugs dmigs pa gsal ba'i tshad ni bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:11821: ni zab mo nyid yin no de la yang bsam
NK107(tse)001:11822: gyis mi khyab pa gcig bzhugs kyang 'di rab tu
NK107(tse)001:11823: zab pa'i don mdor bsdus pas ni las thams cad
NK107(tse)001:11824: la zab pa gshin rje dang nus pa 'jug pa
NK107(tse)001:11825: la zab pa'i mi g.yo mgon po'i sgrub thabs bshad
NK107(tse)001:11826: par bya'o zhes bshad par zhal gyis bzhes pa'o las
NK107(tse)001:11827: ni 'khor ba'i las dang khram las kyi 'gal byed
NK107(tse)001:11828: cham la 'bebs par byed pa mthar thug pa ni
NK107(tse)001:11829: mtha' sdud gnyis po de las zag pa med pa'o
NK107(tse)001:11830: gshin 'gro ba thams cad 'chi ba las ma 'das
NK107(tse)001:11831: la de rnams kyi rje yin pas na las rab
NK107(tse)001:11832: tu myur ba srog gis bsdus pa thams cad kyi
NK107(tse)001:11833: gshed du byed pas gshin rje gshed ste 'di la
NK107(tse)001:11834: dbye na gsum yod do ye shes kyi gshin rje
NK107(tse)001:11835: gshed kyis nyon mongs pa dang 'khor ba las bsgrol
NK107(tse)001:11836: ba'i las byed la 'chi bdag gi gshin rje gshed
NK107(tse)001:11837: kyis sems can kun gyi dbugs len par byed la
NK107(tse)001:11838: las kyi gshin rje gshed kyis srid pa las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11839: 'gyur byed do 'di la bsgrub pa'i thabs 'chi bdag
NK107(tse)001:11840: de ba swa ta gsad pa las kyi khram la
NK107(tse)001:11841: brten nas bsgrub pa dang 'jam dpal ya ma khros
NK107(tse)001:11842: pa'i 'khor lo la brten nas bsgrub pa dang bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11843: pa gnyis yod pa las 'di ni 'phags pa 'jam
NK107(tse)001:11844: dpal ya ma khros pa'i sgrub thabs bshad par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:11845: 'di la gsum ste cho ga'i yan lag tshang ba
NK107(tse)001:11846: la brten nas bsnyen sgrub las kyi mtha' dbye ba
NK107(tse)001:11847: dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa la brten nas rang sems
NK107(tse)001:11848: stong pa nyid kyii go bgo ba dang las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11849: mtha' gtad pa'i rim pa la brten nas ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:11850: 'dod pa'i don bsgrub pa'o de la cho ga'i yan
NK107(tse)001:11851: lag tshang ba la brten nas bsnyen sgrub las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11852: mtha' dbye ba la dgu ste dang po gshin rje
NK107(tse)001:11853: gshed kyi rnal 'byor byas nas bsnyen pa bskyal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:11854: rim pa dang bsgrub pa chen po'i sku'i khyad par
NK107(tse)001:11855: bstan pa dang gnyis bskyed pa'i rim pa'i ting nge
NK107(tse)001:11856: 'dzin gyi rnal 'byor bya ba dang gsum gshin rje'i
NK107(tse)001:11857: 'khor lor gsal ba'i rim pa la blo gnas nas
NK107(tse)001:11858: gsol ba gdab pa dang bzhi dgug pa las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11859: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor bas bsgrub bya'i lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:11860: nyams par bya ba dang lnga 'khor lo bsgrub bya
NK107(tse)001:11861: gsod par byed pa'i sbyor bas las kyi mtha' gang
NK107(tse)001:11862: la gdeng pa dang drug gnas pa'i yi ge'i 'phreng
NK107(tse)001:11863: ba la dmigs nas bzlas pa ji ltar bya ba
NK107(tse)001:11864: dang bdun chos nyid bde ba chen po la dmigs
NK107(tse)001:11865: nas sbyor sgrol gyi khyad par bstan pa dang mchod
NK107(tse)001:11866: bstod las kyi 'khrigs kas 'phrin las kyi gzhung rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:11867: par bya'o de la gshin rje gshed kyis rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:11868: du byas te bsnyen pa bskyal ba'i rim pa ni
NK107(tse)001:11869: sngon du rang gi bla ma la tshogs bsags pa
NK107(tse)001:11870: la sogs pa byas te de nas gnas dben par
NK107(tse)001:11871: gshin rje gshed kyi dam rdzas la sogs pa tshogs
NK107(tse)001:11872: par bshams la gnas dang sbyar ba'i stegs bu mda'
NK107(tse)001:11873: gang la sogs pa gang mos pa byas la gshin
NK107(tse)001:11874: rje gshed kyi dal bzhes la gtor ma la sogs
NK107(tse)001:11875: pa mchod pa'i bye brag dpag tu med pa bshams
NK107(tse)001:11876: la bdag nyid gshin rje rgyan gcig pa'i cha lugs
NK107(tse)001:11877: su bsgoms la +amo d+h+ri stam kri ta na na
NK107(tse)001:11878: h+aum h+aum phata phata ya ma s+w+aa snying dza zhes
NK107(tse)001:11879: 'bum phrag gsum bskyar ba ni bsnyen pa'o de ltar
NK107(tse)001:11880: bsnyen pa rdzogs par byas nas bsgrub pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:11881: sku'i khyad par bstan pa ni ro ras la gshin
NK107(tse)001:11882: rje gshed kyi rab tu 'jigs shing khro bo'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:11883: nyid dang ldan pa bris la de la rab tu
NK107(tse)001:11884: gnas pa rdzogs par byas la gzhan gyis mi mthong
NK107(tse)001:11885: bar byas te mtshan mo rang gi mdun du bkram
NK107(tse)001:11886: la dur khrod kyi skud pas thugs ka nas btags
NK107(tse)001:11887: te de yang khrag chen gyis sbyar la bsgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:11888: po'i lag pa g.yon pa'i srin lag dkris la bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:11889: pa'i sngags ci nus par bzlas shing gsang ba'i mchod
NK107(tse)001:11890: pa lnga dus bzhir dbul lo 'di dag gi dus
NK107(tse)001:11891: thams cad du bskyed pa'i rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:11892: gyi rnal 'byor bya ba ni dang po +amo badz+ra
NK107(tse)001:11893: kro ta ya man ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa
NK107(tse)001:11894: tsa h+aum phata zhes bgegs bskrad de nas tshad med
NK107(tse)001:11895: pa bzhi bsgom mo de'i ngang las bdag dang dngos
NK107(tse)001:11896: po thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgom de nas
NK107(tse)001:11897: bskyed par byed pa'i yi ge h+aum mthing nag gi
NK107(tse)001:11898: 'phro 'du las 'byung ba rim brtsegs bsgom de'i steng
NK107(tse)001:11899: du gzhal yas khang tsakra rtsibs bzhi pa mu khyud
NK107(tse)001:11900: gnyis dang bcas pa dbus kyi lte ba mthing gru
NK107(tse)001:11901: gsum gyi mdangs 'phro ba sgo bzhi rta babs dang
NK107(tse)001:11902: bcas pas rdo rje rwa ba me rir bcas pa
NK107(tse)001:11903: bsgom mo 'khor lo rtsibs dang lte ba dang sgo
NK107(tse)001:11904: rnams su a las zla ba'i ma las nyi ma
NK107(tse)001:11905: pam las pad+ma'i gdan bsgom mo gdan gyi steng du
NK107(tse)001:11906: h+aum mthing nag re re 'od sna tshogs su 'phro
NK107(tse)001:11907: ba bsgom par bya'o h+aum de dag 'od du zhu
NK107(tse)001:11908: ba las 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re re bsgom
NK107(tse)001:11909: de las 'od 'phros 'dus pa las gshin rje gshed
NK107(tse)001:11910: kyi sku gsal bar bsgom pa ni lte ba la
NK107(tse)001:11911: 'jam dpal khros pa'i rgyal po zhal gsum pa phyag
NK107(tse)001:11912: bzhi pa zhabs gnyis bsgrad pa sku mdog mthing nag
NK107(tse)001:11913: sbrul dang thod rlon la sogs pas brgyan pa g.yas
NK107(tse)001:11914: dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing nag rab tu 'jigs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:11915: zhal phyag g.yas gnyis 'khor lo dang zhags pa g.yon
NK107(tse)001:11916: be con dang ral gri zhal bsgrad pa mche ba
NK107(tse)001:11917: btsigs pa khro bo'i rang bzhin shin tu 'jigs pa
NK107(tse)001:11918: yum e ka dza ti dang gnyis gnyis su med
NK107(tse)001:11919: par 'khril bar bsgom mo 'khor lo yi rtsibs rnams
NK107(tse)001:11920: la shar du mthar byed mdog nag po zhal gcig
NK107(tse)001:11921: phyag gnyis pa g.yas 'khor lo g.yon be con thogs
NK107(tse)001:11922: pa rab tu 'jigs pa bsgom mo lhor 'chi bdag
NK107(tse)001:11923: mdog mthing ka gzhan snga ma dang 'dra'o nub gsod
NK107(tse)001:11924: byed mdog dmar nag byang du bsgrol byed mdog ljang
NK107(tse)001:11925: nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas 'khor lo dang
NK107(tse)001:11926: be con kun la'o sgo ba shar nas brtsams te
NK107(tse)001:11927: khro mo dkar mo dang ser mo dang dmar mo
NK107(tse)001:11928: dang ljang khu zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma lcags kyu
NK107(tse)001:11929: dang zhags pa dang lcags sgrogs dang dril bu rnams
NK107(tse)001:11930: g.yas na thogs pa g.yon sdigs 'dzub can sha stag
NK107(tse)001:11931: go de ltar gsal ba las so so'i snying kha'i
NK107(tse)001:11932: sa bon las 'od rang gi kha dog dang mthun
NK107(tse)001:11933: pa 'phros pas ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra ba
NK107(tse)001:11934: thugs kar bzhugs so ye shes sems dapa'i thugs kar
NK107(tse)001:11935: nyi ma dang zla ba'i steng du sa bon la
NK107(tse)001:11936: a li dang ka lis bskor bar bsgom mo gtso
NK107(tse)001:11937: bo la rigs lngas dbu brgyan 'khor la rin chen
NK107(tse)001:11938: 'byung ldan gyis dbu brgyan pa'o de yang gshin rje
NK107(tse)001:11939: gshed kyi dkyil 'khor gyis 'khor lo gsal ba'i rim
NK107(tse)001:11940: pa la blo gnas par bya'o de ltar gsal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:11941: ngang las 'dod pa'i don gyi gsol ba gdab bo
NK107(tse)001:11942: 'gugs pa las kyi sbyor bas bsgrub bya'i lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:11943: nyams par bya ba ni dza h+aumhbamhhosa bsgrub bya gang
NK107(tse)001:11944: yin pa dzas bkug h+aum gis bsdams bamhgyisa bcings hos
NK107(tse)001:11945: rab tu mnyes par 'gyur ba la dmigs par bya'o
NK107(tse)001:11946: 'khor lo bsgrub bya gsod par byed pa las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11947: mtha' gang la gtad pa ni dug dang khrag gis
NK107(tse)001:11948: bris te nem pa'i du bas bdug la dur khrod
NK107(tse)001:11949: du zhag gsum bskyal la slar blangs la bsgrub bya'i
NK107(tse)001:11950: 'byung ba gshed la dbab pa'i dus na gnan pa
NK107(tse)001:11951: dang sreg pa dang 'phang ba dang sum la sbyar
NK107(tse)001:11952: na bsgrub bya bsad pa'i las dang yul dbyung ba
NK107(tse)001:11953: la sogs ji ltar byas kyang 'grub bo de yang
NK107(tse)001:11954: nyi ma bdun du 'khor lo bskor ba'i las kyi
NK107(tse)001:11955: khyad par gyis nges par 'grub bo gnas pa yi
NK107(tse)001:11956: ge'i 'phreng ba la dmigs nas bzlas pa ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:11957: bya ba ni +amo badz+ra +aa kro te ka ha
NK107(tse)001:11958: na ma tha h+aum phata ya ma ra tsa kro
NK107(tse)001:11959: ta ha na da ha sarba lo h+aum h+aum phata
NK107(tse)001:11960: phata many+dzu sh+ri ya ma s+aa tre kri pa ram
NK107(tse)001:11961: ram ma ra y+aa ma ra y+aa sa da pa
NK107(tse)001:11962: sa da pa 'dre tra ya h+aum h+aum sarba sti
NK107(tse)001:11963: sa d+ha ya h+aum h+aum ram ram de ba si
NK107(tse)001:11964: ma ra ya ri mi dza dzah b+ha ling b+hun
NK107(tse)001:11965: dza h+aum h+aum ha ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi g+han
NK107(tse)001:11966: d+ha d+hu pa push+pe a lo ke ne pe te
NK107(tse)001:11967: +amo h+aum ya ma tri ta sa ra ya ma
NK107(tse)001:11968: ri h+aum h+aum s+t+wam b+ha ya mo ha ya myags
NK107(tse)001:11969: myags khas khas song song zung zung ya ma san
NK107(tse)001:11970: du pa y+aa p+aa phatah zhes pa so so la
NK107(tse)001:11971: dmigs shing bzlas so de yang ye shes sems dapa'i
NK107(tse)001:11972: thugs ka'i sngags kyis 'phreng ba las 'od 'phros pas
NK107(tse)001:11973: ji ltar 'dod pa'i don bsam pa ni zhi rgyas
NK107(tse)001:11974: la sogs pa kha dog gis 'phro 'du bsgyur bas
NK107(tse)001:11975: nges par 'grub bo chos nyid bde ba chen po
NK107(tse)001:11976: la dmigs nas sbyor sgrol las kyi khyad par bstan
NK107(tse)001:11977: pa ni bsgral ba'i lus ram gyis bsreg pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11978: sems a la bsdu ba dang rnam shes phata kyis
NK107(tse)001:11979: 'phang ba dang rlung sems 'od kyi gong bur gzhug
NK107(tse)001:11980: rnams bya'o mchod bstod las kyi 'khrigs kas 'phrin las
NK107(tse)001:11981: kyi khrigs bstan pa ni sngon du gtor ma dang
NK107(tse)001:11982: rak+ta byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa byas nas
NK107(tse)001:11983: ya man+ta ka h+aum phatah kyis mtshams bcad yi ge
NK107(tse)001:11984: brgya pas las kyi nyes pa bshags gong gi bskyed
NK107(tse)001:11985: pa'i ting nge 'dzin tshar gcig bsgom de nas gshin
NK107(tse)001:11986: rje 'gying stabs brjid pa'i gar gyis mchod h+aum chen
NK107(tse)001:11987: bstung ba'i skad kyis gshin rje la bstod pa dang
NK107(tse)001:11988: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas mchod pa dang shin
NK107(tse)001:11989: tu 'khros pa'i brda' skad kyis bskul ba dang gtor
NK107(tse)001:11990: ma'i cho ga la sogs pa bsgrub pa'i thabs dang
NK107(tse)001:11991: sbyar ro de dag las skyo na rdzogs pa'i rim
NK107(tse)001:11992: pa ting nge 'dzin bsgom mo de dag dkyus dang
NK107(tse)001:11993: sbyar na cho ga ni gshin rje gshed bsgrub pa
NK107(tse)001:11994: la mkhas pa dgos pa ni mchog dang thun mong
NK107(tse)001:11995: gi bya ba'i don 'grub pa tshangs pa las ni
NK107(tse)001:11996: khrigs kha tshangs pa'o ji ltar mos pa'i rnal 'byor
NK107(tse)001:11997: pa gang la gang mos pa'i rnam pa gsal kyang
NK107(tse)001:11998: chog de la 'dir ni yi ge h+aum mthing nag
NK107(tse)001:11999: go bsam pa ni lha bskyed pa'i sa bon no
NK107(tse)001:12000: kha dog nges par ni so so'i sku mdog dang
NK107(tse)001:12001: mthun pa'i yi ge bsam par bya ste 'phags pa
NK107(tse)001:12002: 'jam dpal khros pa gshin rje gshed kyi bskyed rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:12003: kyi rnal 'byor du bya'o gcig ni zhes pa sgrub
NK107(tse)001:12004: thabs 'di la mos pa ste de ltar ye shes
NK107(tse)001:12005: sems dpa' dang bcas pa'i gzugs rdzogs pa la dmigs
NK107(tse)001:12006: pa gsal bar bya ba dang de la skyo na
NK107(tse)001:12007: rdzogs pa'i rim pa la blo gnas par bya'o de
NK107(tse)001:12008: ltar rnal 'byor pa'i blo gnas pas rdzogs pa'i rim
NK107(tse)001:12009: pas rang gi sems gnas par bya'o de gnyis la
NK107(tse)001:12010: skyo na bzlas pa bya ba ni a li dkar
NK107(tse)001:12011: po'i 'phreng ba ka li dmar po'i 'phreng ba la
NK107(tse)001:12012: sems mnyam par sbyor ba'o de'i sgrub thabs gnyis las
NK107(tse)001:12013: ya ma khros pa'i rgyal po'i bsnyen pa dang sgrub
NK107(tse)001:12014: pa dang las la sbyar ba'i sngags kyang shes par
NK107(tse)001:12015: bya'o las la sbyor ba'i dus na 'khor lo las
NK107(tse)001:12016: nyi ma bdun du rdzogs par bya ste gang la
NK107(tse)001:12017: dmigs pa'i las kyi mtha' btul nas nges par 'grub
NK107(tse)001:12018: bo gcig la zhes pa ni sgrub thabs gsum la
NK107(tse)001:12019: smos pa ste las kyis mtha' gsang ba la sogs
NK107(tse)001:12020: par bsgyur te rang ji ltar 'dod pa yid la
NK107(tse)001:12021: mos pas las kyi mtha' brten pas 'grub pa'o zhes
NK107(tse)001:12022: lnga pa thabs gtso bor gyur pa bsgrub pa'i thabs
NK107(tse)001:12023: las kyi mtha' thug pa dpal gshin rje gshed kyis
NK107(tse)001:12024: bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan nas da ni drug pa nus
NK107(tse)001:12025: pa 'byin par byed pa thabs gtso ba'i 'phags pa
NK107(tse)001:12026: mi g.yo ba'i bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan pa ni nus
NK107(tse)001:12027: pa ni lus kyi nus pas lha'i ting nge 'dzin
NK107(tse)001:12028: dang ldan nus pa dang ngag gis nus pas rang
NK107(tse)001:12029: dang gzhan gyis bar chad thams cad sel bar nus
NK107(tse)001:12030: pa dang sems kyi nus pas 'gugs pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:12031: pa'i nus pa'o mtha' ni mi g.yo ba la thugs
NK107(tse)001:12032: pas de yar rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa
NK107(tse)001:12033: dang bar du gcod pa gang gis mi g.yo ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12034: phyir na rab tu zab pa'o de lta bu'i khro
NK107(tse)001:12035: bo de ni sems can thams cad kyis mgon du
NK107(tse)001:12036: 'gyur ba'o mi g.yo ba 'di la sgrub pa'i thabs
NK107(tse)001:12037: sku'i sgrub pa zab mo dang gsung dang thugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:12038: sgrub thabs dang gsum yod te de la gsum ste
NK107(tse)001:12039: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs pa la brten nas rnal
NK107(tse)001:12040: 'byor du bya ba dang gang gis don la mos
NK107(tse)001:12041: pa 'od zer gyis mtha' bsdus la las dang las
NK107(tse)001:12042: kyi bye brag la mkhas pa'o cho ga'i yan lag
NK107(tse)001:12043: rdzogs pa ni sngon du bsnyen pa bya zhing rnal
NK107(tse)001:12044: 'byor gyis don bya ba bsam par bya ba dang
NK107(tse)001:12045: gnyis pa bskyed pa'i rim pa ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK107(tse)001:12046: pa'o de nas stong pa nyid kyi gnas bsam zhing
NK107(tse)001:12047: bskyed rim gyis mtha' rdzogs par bskyal zhing sems kyi
NK107(tse)001:12048: gnad bstun pa yis de la sngon du bsnyen pa
NK107(tse)001:12049: bya ba ni tsan d+ha tri sarba tsan d+ha ro
NK107(tse)001:12050: sha na h+aum zhes pa 'bum phrag lnga bskyal zhing
NK107(tse)001:12051: bla ma la tshogs bsags pa'i khyad par gyis rnam
NK107(tse)001:12052: pa rnams bya'o rnal 'byor gyi dag bya ni lus
NK107(tse)001:12053: kyi sdig pa dag par byed pa'i don du lus
NK107(tse)001:12054: kyi dge sbyor btub tshad bya ba dang ngag gi
NK107(tse)001:12055: dge sbyor yi ge brgya pa gdon pa dang sems
NK107(tse)001:12056: 'od dang kha dog la sbyang pa thun mtshams rnams
NK107(tse)001:12057: su bya'o gnyis pa bskyed pa'i rim pa'i ting nge
NK107(tse)001:12058: 'dzin bsgom pa ni sngon du bsrung ba'i 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:12059: bsgom pa badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h+aum h+aum zhes pas rdo
NK107(tse)001:12060: rje'i rwa ba dang gur dang sa gzhir bsam mo
NK107(tse)001:12061: de nas tshad med bzhi bsgom de nas bdag dang
NK107(tse)001:12062: dngos po thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgom de'i
NK107(tse)001:12063: ngang las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta
NK107(tse)001:12064: babs bzhi dang bcas pa'i dbus kyi lte ba la
NK107(tse)001:12065: nyi ma dang zla ba dang pad+ma brtsegs pa'i gdan
NK107(tse)001:12066: steng du h+aum sngon po 'od zer brgya phrag 'phro
NK107(tse)001:12067: ba bsgom de las 'od 'phro 'dus pa las mi
NK107(tse)001:12068: g.yo ba mthing ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa zhabs
NK107(tse)001:12069: gnyis brkyang bskum du bzhugs pa sbrul la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:12070: rnams kyis brgyan pa g.yas ral gri g.yon sbrul zhags
NK107(tse)001:12071: bsnams pa rab tu 'jigs pa zhal bsgrad cing ljags
NK107(tse)001:12072: 'dril ba dbu skra ser po gyen du bardzesa pa
NK107(tse)001:12073: la thod pa'i 'phreng ba dang sbrul dkar khras bcings
NK107(tse)001:12074: pa sma ra ser po me ltar 'bar ba zhabs
NK107(tse)001:12075: gnyis rgya mtsho'i gting 'khrugs par mdzad pa klu rnams
NK107(tse)001:12076: zas su za ba a la la zhes sgrogs par
NK107(tse)001:12077: mdzad pa bsgom par bya'o de'i thugs ka nas sa
NK107(tse)001:12078: bon h+aum las 'od mthing ka dpag tu med pa
NK107(tse)001:12079: 'phros pa las rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'
NK107(tse)001:12080: spyan drangs la gnyis su med par bsre ba dang
NK107(tse)001:12081: ye shes sems dapa'i thugs kar nyi ma dang zla
NK107(tse)001:12082: ba'i steng du a li dang ka li'i 'phreng ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12083: dbus su sa bon kha dog gsal bar bsgom mo
NK107(tse)001:12084: de nas dbang bskur nas don yod grub pas dbu
NK107(tse)001:12085: brgyan pa la yum lu gu rgyud mas mgul nas
NK107(tse)001:12086: 'khyud par bsgom mo de la skyo na gzugs bsdus
NK107(tse)001:12087: la bzlas brtsam par bya'o ye shes sems dapa'i thugs
NK107(tse)001:12088: la dmigs te tsan d+ha ma h+aa ro sha na
NK107(tse)001:12089: h+aum phata spo ta spo ta ya na ga ma
NK107(tse)001:12090: ra y+aa sho sha sho sha b+han d+ha b+han d+ha
NK107(tse)001:12091: na ga u tsa ta ya h+aum h+aum ma ra
NK107(tse)001:12092: ma ra sa ra sa ra du ru du ru
NK107(tse)001:12093: na ga kri nan ta ru sa de na ha
NK107(tse)001:12094: ra ya phata na ga hu ra ting nan ka
NK107(tse)001:12095: ra ya h+aum h+aum s+w+aa h+aa sarba ta th+aa ga
NK107(tse)001:12096: ta a g+ham pra ti dza ho b+han d+ha ya
NK107(tse)001:12097: ho ho h+aum h+aum phata b+ha ling ta kha kha
NK107(tse)001:12098: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi mchod pa'i sngags gong dang 'dra'o
NK107(tse)001:12099: de ltar 'od kyis 'phreng ba la dmigs shing bzlas
NK107(tse)001:12100: so de ltar dkyus dang sbyar na cho ga ni
NK107(tse)001:12101: khro bo'i sku bskyed pa la mkhas pa rnams ni
NK107(tse)001:12102: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom pa dang dal bsdu ba
NK107(tse)001:12103: la sogs pa'o de ltar bskyed pa'i rim pa la
NK107(tse)001:12104: blo gnas par byas nas rdzogs pa'i rim pa la
NK107(tse)001:12105: sems gnas par bya ba ni rnal 'byor gyis byas
NK107(tse)001:12106: pa'i 'bras bu ste khro bo gdug pa can tshar
NK107(tse)001:12107: gcod pa rgyal po ni kun las khyad par 'phags
NK107(tse)001:12108: pa'o mi g.yo ba ni bdud dang gnod sbyin rnams
NK107(tse)001:12109: las mi g.yo zhing thams cad tshar gcod par mdzad
NK107(tse)001:12110: pa bdud dang bar chad kyis nyen pa rnams bskyab
NK107(tse)001:12111: pa dang mgon byed pas na sku rab tu mthing
NK107(tse)001:12112: nag 'jigs pa mthong bas b+hud d+ha rnams kyang 'jigs
NK107(tse)001:12113: par nus te gzhan lta ci smos so dad pas
NK107(tse)001:12114: nges pa ni sku mdog ji ltar mos par rang
NK107(tse)001:12115: lus bsam 'dod pa'i don thams cad 'grub pa'o 'od
NK107(tse)001:12116: zer lcags kyu'i dbyibs dang 'dra ba'i 'od zer gyis
NK107(tse)001:12117: kha dog gang mos kyis bsgrub bya gang yin pa
NK107(tse)001:12118: 'gugs na nag por bya'o bskrad na zhes yul dbang
NK107(tse)001:12119: la sogs pa'i las byed na dmar po bcings pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12120: las byed na ljang khu de bzhin du gsad pa
NK107(tse)001:12121: la nag po zhi ba la dkar rgyas pa ser
NK107(tse)001:12122: dbang la dmar drag pa la nag po rengs pa
NK107(tse)001:12123: la dmar ser dbye ba la dmar nag klu sper
NK107(tse)001:12124: bar byed pa la dmar ser klu spa skong bar
NK107(tse)001:12125: byed pa la dkar dmar sdig pa sngon po yul
NK107(tse)001:12126: dbyung ba la ljang khu gsad pa la nag po
NK107(tse)001:12127: gnan pa la ser po rten spo na dkar pos
NK107(tse)001:12128: bya'o lhag ma rnams yang rnal 'byor pa rang gis
NK107(tse)001:12129: ji ltar 'dod pa spro'o a ni skye ba la
NK107(tse)001:12130: mi gnas pa li barjoda pa la mi gnas pa
NK107(tse)001:12131: de ltar na skye med barjoda du med pa'i don
NK107(tse)001:12132: la blo gnas par bya'o ka sku gsum lam rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:12133: pa li chos nyid bcos pa med pa de ltar
NK107(tse)001:12134: lam rdzogs dang bcos med gnyis la blo gnas par
NK107(tse)001:12135: bya'o so so'i sngags kyi 'brel btub las shes par
NK107(tse)001:12136: bya'o de rnams la ni sgrub thabs la smos pa
NK107(tse)001:12137: sngags ni bsnyen pa dang sgrub pa dang las la
NK107(tse)001:12138: sbyar ba dang mchod bstod rnam par bsgyur byed kyi
NK107(tse)001:12139: sngags la sogs pa shes par bya zhes pa'o bsrung
NK107(tse)001:12140: ba ni sgog pa dang chang dang tsh+wa dang bud
NK107(tse)001:12141: med la sogs pa rnal 'byor pa dam tshig dang
NK107(tse)001:12142: ldan pas bsrung bar bya'o de ltar sngags bzlas pa
NK107(tse)001:12143: la sogs pa rdzogs par byas la 'di ltar ci
NK107(tse)001:12144: dang ci byas pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i rim pa
NK107(tse)001:12145: bsgom pas thams cad bla na med pa byang chub
NK107(tse)001:12146: kyi don du bsngo bar bya'o zhes drug pa nus
NK107(tse)001:12147: pa 'byin par byed pa thabs gtso bo 'phags pa
NK107(tse)001:12148: mi g.yo ba'i sgrub thabs bstan nas da ni bdun
NK107(tse)001:12149: pa gshin rje dang 'phags pa mi g.yo ba'i bsnyen
NK107(tse)001:12150: pa'i grangs bstan pa ni 'di ltar sgrub pa zab
NK107(tse)001:12151: mo nyid la sogs pa gzhung gsal lo de dag
NK107(tse)001:12152: gis ni le'u dang po'i dris lan bzhi bcu zhe
NK107(tse)001:12153: drug pa bsgrub pa'i thabs zab mo khyad par gyi
NK107(tse)001:12154: sngags bstan pa la bdun du byas nas bstan no
NK107(tse)001:12155: de ni le'u dang po'i dris lan zhe bdun pa
NK107(tse)001:12156: lus rnam par bzhag pa rdzogs pa chen po'i rang
NK107(tse)001:12157: bzhin gyi gnas lugs bstan pa la yan lag gi
NK107(tse)001:12158: don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po mtha' dang bral
NK107(tse)001:12159: ba rang gi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni gnas lugs
NK107(tse)001:12160: 'dug tshul lta bu zhes pa la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:12161: te de yang gnas pa la gang yang ma grub
NK107(tse)001:12162: pas zhe 'dod med la de nyid lugs mar byung
NK107(tse)001:12163: bas spang du med pa'i chos nyid la dgag bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:12164: dang spang blang med pas bcos mi dgos pa'o 'dug
NK107(tse)001:12165: pa gzhi tshul lam de ltar na gzhi lam gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12166: su med pa'i chos nyid 'di lta bu mchog tu
NK107(tse)001:12167: zab pa 'dir thun mong du 'thad pa la blo
NK107(tse)001:12168: chung ba'i theg pa nyan dman pa nyan thos dang
NK107(tse)001:12169: dam chos la nges pa med pa'i rang rgyal rnams
NK107(tse)001:12170: kyis 'di nyid kyi don khams gsum du mi brgyud
NK107(tse)001:12171: ba'i lta ba yod zhes thos nas rab tu skrag
NK107(tse)001:12172: te 'di lta bu'i chos kyi brgyud zhes sgros dang
NK107(tse)001:12173: bskur ba 'debs pas de la brten nas sems can
NK107(tse)001:12174: dmyal bar 'gyur bas na de nyid kyis sdug basngala
NK107(tse)001:12175: mthong bas rab tu rgyal bar 'gyur ro des na
NK107(tse)001:12176: nyan thos la sogs pa la mchog tu gsang bar
NK107(tse)001:12177: bya'o de yang gzhi bcos pa med pa'i chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:12178: de ming du btags pa med pa'i phyir gang la
NK107(tse)001:12179: yang nges pa med de 'khor ba nyid 'das par
NK107(tse)001:12180: btags kyang bkag pa med 'das pa la 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12181: ming gis btags kyang bkag pa med pas de ltar
NK107(tse)001:12182: na btags pa thams cad ming yin la de ltar
NK107(tse)001:12183: na ming ming gis stong btags pa btags pas stong
NK107(tse)001:12184: ming la rgyu mtshan med pa'i phyir chos nyid la
NK107(tse)001:12185: gzhi dang rtsa ba med par rtogs pas na chos
NK107(tse)001:12186: rnams ni gang la yang rang bzhin med par rtogs
NK107(tse)001:12187: pa'o de la ming du brtags na gang nas kyang
NK107(tse)001:12188: byung sa med pa'i gzhi zhes bya'o de lta bu'i
NK107(tse)001:12189: chos nyid la dus 'di tsam du gnas zhes bya
NK107(tse)001:12190: ba'am mi gnas zhes bya ba med pa'i phyir de
NK107(tse)001:12191: la yod par snang ba'i dngos po snang rung gis
NK107(tse)001:12192: bum pa'am med pa'i dngos po lha 'dre'i bum pa'am
NK107(tse)001:12193: ri bong gi rwa lta bu la sogs pa gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12194: su yang grub pa med do de bzhin du grang
NK107(tse)001:12195: bya stong pa phyi stong pa nyid la sogs pa'am
NK107(tse)001:12196: mtha' bkag stong pa rang rgyud 'dzin pa'am rgyun chad
NK107(tse)001:12197: stong pa snga phyi mi bden pa'am yid dpyod stong
NK107(tse)001:12198: pa yin snyam dang rang bzhin stong pa sgyu ma
NK107(tse)001:12199: lta bu dang mi dmigs pa stong pa gtad med
NK107(tse)001:12200: pa dang bya bral stong pa bya byed dang med
NK107(tse)001:12201: pa la sogs pa gang la yang mi gnas so
NK107(tse)001:12202: de bzhin du mtha' yongs su rdzogs pa chen po
NK107(tse)001:12203: nyid la ma rdzogs pa gang yang med pa yis
NK107(tse)001:12204: la gang yang ma yin pa'i gnad kyis 'di ni
NK107(tse)001:12205: gsal ba yin no zhes bya ba dang mi gsal
NK107(tse)001:12206: zhes bya ba btsal du yang ma grub pa med
NK107(tse)001:12207: pa'i phyir ro de la ltos pas mun pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:12208: bya ba yang shes bya la mi srid do des
NK107(tse)001:12209: 'byung ba lnga la sogs pa'i chos la yang gnas
NK107(tse)001:12210: pa min no de ltar na rgya ma chad pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12211: ye shes phyogs lhung med pa'i lta ba 'gro 'ong
NK107(tse)001:12212: med pa'i chos nyid dus thams cad pa'i nyams myong
NK107(tse)001:12213: rtag par bzhugs pa'i b+hud d+ha de gang las byung
NK107(tse)001:12214: zhe na srid pa'i mtha' med pa rang grol ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12215: phyir ro zhes mtha' dang bral ba rang mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:12216: du gnas pa bstan nas da ni gnyis pa rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:12217: pa chen po bya bral cog bzhag la gang la
NK107(tse)001:12218: yang gol sa med par bstan pa ni snang ba
NK107(tse)001:12219: nyid snang thog tu grol las snang rkyen chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:12220: shes bya nyid 'gyus thog nas grol bas 'khor 'das
NK107(tse)001:12221: mtha' bral ba'i rig pa la 'bad cing rtsol bas
NK107(tse)001:12222: grub pa med pa'i phyir gang gis kyang ma bcings
NK107(tse)001:12223: la kun tu zang thal de nyid 'dod la med
NK107(tse)001:12224: pas zang ma'i chos nyid zhes bya'o de lta bu'i
NK107(tse)001:12225: chos nyid de gang la yang thogs pa med pas
NK107(tse)001:12226: thal 'byung ngo zhes bya'o de nyid ltar snang grags
NK107(tse)001:12227: kyis bsdus pa'i gang dang yang rgya ma chad pas
NK107(tse)001:12228: thams cad chos nyid du shar la de nyid phyogs
NK107(tse)001:12229: gang yang lhung ba med pa'i phyir ngo bo zang
NK107(tse)001:12230: thal kyang mtshan nyid la gnyis su med pa'i zhes
NK107(tse)001:12231: bya'o rtsol bral byas pa med pa'i chos nyid de
NK107(tse)001:12232: la dge bas bskyab tu med la ye nas stong
NK107(tse)001:12233: pa nyid du bzhugs la sdig pas gos pa med
NK107(tse)001:12234: pas rang ngo sgrib byed dang bral ba'i rig pa
NK107(tse)001:12235: nyid la'ng gang yang grub pa med pa'i phyir des
NK107(tse)001:12236: na rig pa rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12237: rig pa 'dis dge sdig gnyis ka rnam par sel
NK107(tse)001:12238: ba'i phyir ro des na rang shes rig gi rgyal
NK107(tse)001:12239: po dang kun tu bzang po 'di nyid ni 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12240: ba la mi gnas pas rang bzhin gang du yang
NK107(tse)001:12241: grub pa med mya ngan las 'das pa la mi
NK107(tse)001:12242: gnas pas sku gsum gyi bcings pa las grol ba'o
NK107(tse)001:12243: de cis phyir zhe na chos nyid des stong pa
NK107(tse)001:12244: nyid kun la khyab pa'i phyir ro 'o na gang
NK107(tse)001:12245: yang med dam zhe na ye shes rang gi ngo
NK107(tse)001:12246: bor gnas pa la tshig tsam du gtan la phab
NK107(tse)001:12247: na ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi tshul
NK107(tse)001:12248: du sangs rgyas sems can thams cad dbyer med do
NK107(tse)001:12249: zhes zhus don zhe bdun pa rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:12250: rang bzhin gnas lugs bstan pa la gnyis su byas
NK107(tse)001:12251: nas bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i zhus don
NK107(tse)001:12252: zhe brgyad pa lus rnam par bzhag pa 'khrul 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12253: rtsis kyi 'khor lo la brten nas sems can gyi
NK107(tse)001:12254: rgyu dang rkyen gyi rnam pa bstan pa la yan
