NK107(tse)001:12255: lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po rtsa
NK107(tse)001:12256: ba'i rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis la 'khrul pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12257: dus chos nges pa bzung ba bstan pa ni 'di
NK107(tse)001:12258: ltar gzhan du ma bshad pa'i zhes pa la sogs
NK107(tse)001:12259: pas bstan te 'di sngags kyi rgyud sde gzhan du
NK107(tse)001:12260: b+hud d+ha gzhan gyis ma bshad pa'i 'khrul pa'i gang
NK107(tse)001:12261: dang sdeb tu btub pa dang gang dang yang 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12262: du btub pa dang don gyis 'khrul zhes bya nor
NK107(tse)001:12263: zhes bya ma shes zhes bya'o rtsis ni ma rig
NK107(tse)001:12264: pa la sogs pa'i sbyor ba la brten nas rtsis
NK107(tse)001:12265: pa'i dus ci tsam nas 'khrul la ci tsam nas
NK107(tse)001:12266: ldog ston pas na ngo mtshar can zhes bya'o nga
NK107(tse)001:12267: yis ni rgyud kyi ston pa rdo rje 'chang bshad
NK107(tse)001:12268: kyis ni rang byung bcos pa med pa'i nam mkha'
NK107(tse)001:12269: las rang byung ba ste lha'i bu dga' byed dbang
NK107(tse)001:12270: phyug la lus gus pa dang ngag mos pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12271: sems gdung ba dang bcas pas legs par nyon cig
NK107(tse)001:12272: zhes gdams pa dang bcas pas legs par bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12273: yin la rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas slob
NK107(tse)001:12274: ma la gdams pa'o rtsa ba yi ni ma rig
NK107(tse)001:12275: pas gong ma'i don du rgyab tu phyogs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12276: 'du byed las kyis drug 'khor rnam shes 'dzin pas
NK107(tse)001:12277: yul 'khor ming gzugs kyis rtags pas las dang shes
NK107(tse)001:12278: pa 'khor skye mched drug gis 'gyu ba 'khor reg
NK107(tse)001:12279: gis gcod pas las 'khor tshor ba'i myong bas las
NK107(tse)001:12280: 'khor sred pa'i 'jug pas snang char 'khor srid pa
NK107(tse)001:12281: chags pas snod 'khor len pa'i rgyus dngos po 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12282: skye ba'i bskyed lus 'khor rga shi ru btung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12283: sems 'khor ba la brten nas khams gsum pa zhes
NK107(tse)001:12284: bya'o de dang 'brel ba las 'chi ba las ma
NK107(tse)001:12285: rig pa la byung bas la thug go de las
NK107(tse)001:12286: 'gro ba so so'i lus che chung gi bye brag
NK107(tse)001:12287: dpag tu med pa byung ba dang khams sum 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12288: ba'i zhes bya'o de yang brten pa lus la 'brel
NK107(tse)001:12289: ba byi ba la sogs lo bcu gnyis su 'byung
NK107(tse)001:12290: ba byer zug snyoms pa'i 'brel so yis ma rig
NK107(tse)001:12291: pa las 'khrul pa byi ba'i lor byung la 'du
NK107(tse)001:12292: byed las glang la sogs pa rnams su shes so
NK107(tse)001:12293: dus 'di tsam na 'khrul zhes pa 'khrul pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:12294: chos ngos bzung ba'i dus dang nges pa ni 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12295: gzhi gsal ba'i me long du bstan pas na der
NK107(tse)001:12296: blta'o zhes rtsa ba'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis las 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12297: pa'i dus tshod nges par bzung ba bstan nas da
NK107(tse)001:12298: ni gnyis pa 'khrul 'khor gyi gnad la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:12299: 'khrul pa'i dus dang bzlog pa'i mtshan nyid bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12300: ni rags pa ni phyi 'byung ba rags pas rdul
NK107(tse)001:12301: dang 'phra rab kyi rtsis ma zin nang shes par
NK107(tse)001:12302: rags pas gnas pa'i 'pho ba dang rlung gi tshad
NK107(tse)001:12303: ma zin gsang ba sems rags pas gnas pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:12304: ye shes dag pa'i snang bar gnas pa las rnal
NK107(tse)001:12305: 'byor pas ni nyer bar mtshon pa ste sems can
NK107(tse)001:12306: spyi la smos pa'o sems ni 'di'i dus na 'gyu
NK107(tse)001:12307: ba 'phen 'gyur gyi rlung zhes bya ba las ma
NK107(tse)001:12308: rig pa'i ye shes kyis 'phrul 'khor las chu zug
NK107(tse)001:12309: pa'i dus su 'khrul pa ni gzhi la gzhir ma
NK107(tse)001:12310: shes pa las ma gzhi yin la rig pa'i gnas
NK107(tse)001:12311: lugs su ma rig pa las 'khrul pa zhes bya'o
NK107(tse)001:12312: de yang dper na gso ba'i ma la dgra'i 'du
NK107(tse)001:12313: shes su mthong bas las kyi phung po dpag tu
NK107(tse)001:12314: med pa sogs pa lta bu'o de yang rgyu la
NK107(tse)001:12315: the tshom zos pas 'byung ba chu rkyen la sogs
NK107(tse)001:12316: pa'i byed pa'i las zug pa 'bras bu la the
NK107(tse)001:12317: tshom zos pas smin so byi byang byung ba'o de
NK107(tse)001:12318: yang chus bsdus pas 'phen pa'i rlung gi 'byed pa
NK107(tse)001:12319: la zug pas gnas pas rang gsal chos nyid kyi
NK107(tse)001:12320: mdangs ma rnyed byi bas sngar gyis snang bas ma
NK107(tse)001:12321: bzung bas mkhyen pa ye shes kyi rtsal 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:12322: la sogs su 'khrul ba'o lhag ma bcu gcig po
NK107(tse)001:12323: la yang de ltar shes par bya'o de ltar 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12324: ngos bzung na ldog pa'i dus kyang shes par nges
NK107(tse)001:12325: la de bzhin du gnas pa'i dus kyang shes so
NK107(tse)001:12326: de ltar na 'khrul dus bcu gnyis dang gnas pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12327: dus bcu gnyis 'khrul pa ldog pa'i dus bcu gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12328: te sum cu rtsa drug tu brtsis kyis zin na
NK107(tse)001:12329: 'phrul 'khor brtsis kyi yi ge pa mkhas par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:12330: ro de yang 'khor lo rtsibs sum bcu rtsa drug
NK107(tse)001:12331: pa la 'gyur byed kyi yi ge rnams btab la
NK107(tse)001:12332: de la mu khyud rim pa bcu gnyis la so
NK107(tse)001:12333: so'i 'byung ba'i 'gral bris na de nas dus brtsis
NK107(tse)001:12334: pas 'byung ba'i dus kyi bye brag su zug pa
NK107(tse)001:12335: dang byer ba dang snyams pa'o de las 'byung bzhi
NK107(tse)001:12336: las lus bcu gnyis su brtsis pas de dag re
NK107(tse)001:12337: re la yang bcu gnyis bcu gnyis su brtsis pas
NK107(tse)001:12338: sum brgya dang drug cu tham pa'i tshad kyis lo
NK107(tse)001:12339: gcig gi zhag rdzogs pa las 'khrul pa'i dus re
NK107(tse)001:12340: re ste de'i mtha' ldan pa'i dus gnyis las thong
NK107(tse)001:12341: dang khyad par gyis bye brag phye ba las drug
NK107(tse)001:12342: pa bdun brgya dang nyi shur 'gyur ro de nyid
NK107(tse)001:12343: la 'khrul pa'i dus dag gnas dang ldog pa gsum
NK107(tse)001:12344: du brtsis pas 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti
NK107(tse)001:12345: mug gsum gyi 'jug pa'i dus stong phrag gnyis dang
NK107(tse)001:12346: brgya drug cu'i tshad kyis 'phrul 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK107(tse)001:12347: la ngos zin pa yis 'khrul pa'i dus gsum nges
NK107(tse)001:12348: par shes pas tshad thams cad tshad nges par zin
NK107(tse)001:12349: pa'o des na 'khor lo re dmigs rnams ni 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12350: pa'i brtsis la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pas bzung bas
NK107(tse)001:12351: 'khrul gzhi rtsis kyi man ngag la mkhas par 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:12352: te dus tshod dang 'pho 'gyur gyi tshad zin pa
NK107(tse)001:12353: las byung bas na 'khor lo'i rtsa ba mthong bas
NK107(tse)001:12354: khams sum mi 'jug pa'o zhes gnyis pa 'phrul 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12355: gyi gnad la brten nas 'khrul pa'i dus dang ldog
NK107(tse)001:12356: pa'i mtshan nyid bstan nas da ni gsum pa skye
NK107(tse)001:12357: ba brgyud pa'i grangs kyi mtshan nyid la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:12358: 'khrul pa ldog pa'i dus bstan pa ni dus dang
NK107(tse)001:12359: zhes pa la sogs pa gzhung gis shes so zhus
NK107(tse)001:12360: don zhe brgyad pa 'khrul 'khor rtsis la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:12361: sems can gyi rgyu rkyen bstan pa la yan lag
NK107(tse)001:12362: gi don gsum du byas nas bstan no da ni
NK107(tse)001:12363: le'u dang po'i zhus don zhe dgu pa lus rnam
NK107(tse)001:12364: par bzhag pa shes bya rang gi mtshan nyid bstan
NK107(tse)001:12365: pa la yan lag gi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12366: dang po shes bya tshig barjoda kyi rim pa bstan
NK107(tse)001:12367: pa ni shes bya rang gi zhes pa yang gzhung
NK107(tse)001:12368: gis shes so gnyis pa shes bya 'jug pa'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:12369: nyid bstan pa ni de yang lugs zhes pa ste
NK107(tse)001:12370: shes bya gnas pa'i gnas lugs dang shes bya rtogs
NK107(tse)001:12371: pa'i rtogs lugs dang shes bya grol ba'i grol lugs
NK107(tse)001:12372: dang gsum mo de yang chos kyi sdebs dang gang
NK107(tse)001:12373: zag gi sdebs gnyis kyis shes bya rang gi mtshan
NK107(tse)001:12374: nyid gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'o gzhan gzhung gis
NK107(tse)001:12375: shes so zhus don zhe dgu pa shes bya rang
NK107(tse)001:12376: gi mtshan nyid dang spyi'i mtshan nyid bstan pa la
NK107(tse)001:12377: gnyis su byas nas bstan no da ni le'u dang
NK107(tse)001:12378: po'i zhus don lnga bcu pa lus rnam par bzhag
NK107(tse)001:12379: pa bla ma'i rim pa ji ltar yin pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12380: bkur bar bya ba'i rim pa bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:12381: lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po bla
NK107(tse)001:12382: ma'i mtshan nyid ji lta bu zhig la bla ma'i
NK107(tse)001:12383: bya ba'i rim pa bstan pa ni bla ma rdo
NK107(tse)001:12384: rje 'chang chen gyi bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK107(tse)001:12385: te de yang bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pas
NK107(tse)001:12386: bla ma'i rang bzhin dang bla ma ji ltar bkur
NK107(tse)001:12387: ba'i rim pa dang gsol ba ji ltar gdab pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12388: tshig dang de nyid las byin brlabs ji ltar 'byung
NK107(tse)001:12389: ba dang yid ches pa'i mtshan nyid dang bla ma'i
NK107(tse)001:12390: bye brag dang ji ltar mnyes par bya ba'i rim
NK107(tse)001:12391: pa dang bla ma la nyes par bltas pa'i nyes
NK107(tse)001:12392: dmigs dang de bshags pa'i tshad dang yon tan la
NK107(tse)001:12393: dmigs nas bsten pa'i khyad par bstan pa'o de la
NK107(tse)001:12394: bla ma'i mtshan nyid ni gnyis te rang bzhin gyi
NK107(tse)001:12395: mtshan nyid dang btags pa'i mtshan nyid do rang bzhin
NK107(tse)001:12396: ni rang bzhin gyis gzung 'dzin chung ba dang rnam
NK107(tse)001:12397: rtog chung ba dang ci la yang yangs pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12398: lus ngag la lhod yod pa'o btags pas ni bkod
NK107(tse)001:12399: pa chen po las mkhas shing bya ba bral ba
NK107(tse)001:12400: dang chos nyid don ldan tshad phab dang 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12401: don la rmongs pa med gsang sngags bla ma'i mtshan
NK107(tse)001:12402: nyid do zhes gsungs pas yang dag par btags na
NK107(tse)001:12403: mkhas shing ni yangs shing brgyud pa mkhas pa yis
NK107(tse)001:12404: gsang sngags kyi rgyud ma lus pa'i don bla ma
NK107(tse)001:12405: gong ma rnams thugs legs par sbyangs pa la slob
NK107(tse)001:12406: ma legs par 'khrul pa med par ston shes pa
NK107(tse)001:12407: dang de yang gnyis ras chod dang gzu lum la
NK107(tse)001:12408: sogs pa'i tshul ma yin par ston pa dang goms
NK107(tse)001:12409: shing sgrub thabs la mkhas pas bsnyen sgrub yan lag
NK107(tse)001:12410: bzhi don sdebs shes pa dang rtogs shing lta ba
NK107(tse)001:12411: la mkhas pa ni spyir theg pa mtha' dag gi
NK107(tse)001:12412: lta ba'i don shes pas gzhan gyi sgro 'dogs chod
NK107(tse)001:12413: pa dang bye brag tu chos nyid mngon sum gyi
NK107(tse)001:12414: lta ba la mkhas pas yid dpyod tshig gi spros
NK107(tse)001:12415: pa las grol ba'o nyams su blangs shing nyams myong
NK107(tse)001:12416: la mkhas pa ni rang gi nyams su blangs pas
NK107(tse)001:12417: shes bya nang gi sgro 'dogs chod nyams myong la
NK107(tse)001:12418: mkhas pas skal ldan gzhan gyi rgyud grol bar nus
NK107(tse)001:12419: pa'o de ltar mkhas pa bzhi dang ldan pas bla
NK107(tse)001:12420: ma phyi'i mtshan nyid nang du 'gyur ba'i mtshan nyid
NK107(tse)001:12421: do 'jig rten gyi bya ba dang bral bar byas
NK107(tse)001:12422: nas ri khrod dgon pa bsten cing 'khor mang po
NK107(tse)001:12423: dang 'du 'dzi spangs pa yin chos nyid bya ba
NK107(tse)001:12424: dang bral ba rgyud pa la brten pa'i rtags so
NK107(tse)001:12425: chos nyid kyi don dang ldan pas 'jig rten gyi
NK107(tse)001:12426: rtsis gdab las 'das pa'o chos tshig phyir ma song
NK107(tse)001:12427: bar lag tu blang rgyu'i chos 'di nyid la tshad
NK107(tse)001:12428: la phab pas nyams skyes pa dang slob ma de
NK107(tse)001:12429: gang 'dod pa'i chos rnams kyi don la rmongs pa
NK107(tse)001:12430: med par shes pa ni sngon sbyangs pa'i rtags yin
NK107(tse)001:12431: pa'am yang na gter chen po la longs spyod byed
NK107(tse)001:12432: pa'i rtags so de ltar mtshan nyid lnga dang ldan
NK107(tse)001:12433: pa ni gsang sngags kyi bla ma'i mtshan nyid do
NK107(tse)001:12434: de ltar mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bla ma'i rang
NK107(tse)001:12435: bzhin lus kyi spyod pa la dal chags pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12436: ngag gi spyod pa gsang por smra ba dang sems
NK107(tse)001:12437: kyi spyod pa sa ma ti las ma yengs pa'o
NK107(tse)001:12438: de lta bu'i rang bzhin dang ldan pa ni bla
NK107(tse)001:12439: ma rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes bya'o de ltar mtshan
NK107(tse)001:12440: nyid dang ldan zhing rang bzhin rdzogs pa'i bla ma
NK107(tse)001:12441: ji ltar bkur ba'i rim pa ni bla ma mthong
NK107(tse)001:12442: ba'i dus na mthong phyag btsal ba ni sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:12443: kyi zhing khams mngon du byed pa'i khyad par yod
NK107(tse)001:12444: do bla ma la dus rtag tu ma d+hal phul
NK107(tse)001:12445: na byang chub sems dapa'i sa la longs spyod dus
NK107(tse)001:12446: rtag tu lus gus pa dang bcas nas phyag btsal
NK107(tse)001:12447: na 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i longs spyod la
NK107(tse)001:12448: nye bar spyod dus rgyun du bskor ma byas na
NK107(tse)001:12449: 'gro ba byams shing kun gyis legs par ster bar
NK107(tse)001:12450: 'gyur ro dus rtag tu dril phyis byas na rdo
NK107(tse)001:12451: rje mig dang ldan par 'gyur dri zhim po'i thig
NK107(tse)001:12452: le byas na bde ba b+ha zhig la longs spyod
NK107(tse)001:12453: bla ma la rang gi lus nas bla ma'i bya
NK107(tse)001:12454: ba la mkhas par byas na 'gro ba thams cad
NK107(tse)001:12455: bran du 'khol bar 'gyur ro ngag gis bstod pa
NK107(tse)001:12456: sna tshogs pas bstod na dbyangs kyi snyad pa'i b+hud
NK107(tse)001:12457: d+ha'i zhing yongs su dag par skye bar 'gyur 'khor
NK107(tse)001:12458: gsum yongs su dag pa lan cig byas na 'di
NK107(tse)001:12459: la bya ba rnams legs par 'grub cing ma 'ongs
NK107(tse)001:12460: pa'i dus na 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por 'gyur
NK107(tse)001:12461: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa lan gnyis byas na
NK107(tse)001:12462: 'di la nyes pa spong zhing ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:12463: na stong pa 'dzin gyi rgyal por 'gyur ro lan
NK107(tse)001:12464: gsum byas na 'di la kun gyis snyan pa sgrogs
NK107(tse)001:12465: shing mchod pa'i gnas su 'gyur ba dang ma 'ongs
NK107(tse)001:12466: pa'i dus na mkha' spyod gyi grub pa chen por
NK107(tse)001:12467: 'gyur ro bdun byas na 'di nyid la 'dod pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12468: don ji ltar bsam pa 'grub la 'di nas shi
NK107(tse)001:12469: 'phos ma thag tu rigs kyi rgyal po chen por
NK107(tse)001:12470: 'gyur nas 'gro ba rnams kyi kha lor gyen la
NK107(tse)001:12471: bsgyur ro rang gi lo grangs tsam zhig rang gi
NK107(tse)001:12472: bla ma la yongs su bstod pa byas na 'di
NK107(tse)001:12473: nyid la tshe la dbang ba 'grub par 'gyur zhing
NK107(tse)001:12474: phyi ma dang zla ba gnas pa'i dus srid du
NK107(tse)001:12475: gnas shing sems can rnams kyi nyon mongs pa'i rtog
NK107(tse)001:12476: pa sel zhing rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs pas 'gro ba
NK107(tse)001:12477: btul nas tha ma zag bcas mi snang bar sangs
NK107(tse)001:12478: rgya ba la the tshom med do yang rang gi
NK107(tse)001:12479: bla ma la 'dun rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas
NK107(tse)001:12480: ras yug gcig tsam phul bas kyang ma 'ongs pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12481: dus na nor bu'i bang mdzod la longs spyod par
NK107(tse)001:12482: 'gyur ba bram ze'i khye'u'i lo rgyus kyang yod de
NK107(tse)001:12483: 'dir ma bris de ltar bdud rtsi 'byung ba'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:12484: nas nam mkha' gang ba'i b+hud d+ha la sna tshogs
NK107(tse)001:12485: rin chen spras pa yis stong sum gang bar phul
NK107(tse)001:12486: gyur pas bla ma'i ba spu nyag re la mar
NK107(tse)001:12487: gyi thigs pa cig blugs pa brgya phrag mang po'i
NK107(tse)001:12488: char mi phod zhes pa la sogs pa lung drangs
NK107(tse)001:12489: na dpag tu med de bla ma longs spyod spyod
NK107(tse)001:12490: lam sna tshogs pa'i sgo nas mnyes par bya ste
NK107(tse)001:12491: bla ma bzhengs pa'i dus su ldang ba dang thal
NK107(tse)001:12492: mo sbyar ba dang bzhugs pa'i dus su stan bstab
NK107(tse)001:12493: pa dang bzhengs bzhugs kyi dus na phyag sngon du
NK107(tse)001:12494: 'gro ba la sogs pa bya ba dang ma d+ha
NK107(tse)001:12495: la 'bul ba dang a la dang sprid pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12496: lud pa lu ba'i dus na lag pas kha dgab
NK107(tse)001:12497: pa dang mdor na bag ma gsar ma'i tshul gnas
NK107(tse)001:12498: par bya ba ni kun gyis mchod cing sprul pa
NK107(tse)001:12499: sku'i zhing khams su dbugs 'byin par 'gyur ro de
NK107(tse)001:12500: yang bla ma la rang la gces pa'i bu dang
NK107(tse)001:12501: nor ltar yid la 'khur bas byin brlabs 'dod 'jo'i
NK107(tse)001:12502: ba ltar 'byung ba dang dus la gted khur bas
NK107(tse)001:12503: dus kyi lto ba ltar yid la byas pas byin
NK107(tse)001:12504: brlabs bkres skom la bza' btung 'thungs pa ltar 'byung
NK107(tse)001:12505: ba dang nad pas sman pa bsten pa ltar g.yel
NK107(tse)001:12506: ba med pa lta bur khur bas byin brlabs rtag
NK107(tse)001:12507: tu bde ba la longs spyod pa'o de bzhin 'jigs
NK107(tse)001:12508: kyi lam du bskyel ma ltar mun khung gi mar
NK107(tse)001:12509: me ltar dang ji ltar rang gi yid la gces
NK107(tse)001:12510: pa'i 'dod pa bzhin dang yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK107(tse)001:12511: ltar khur ba la sogs pa'i thabs sna tshogs pas
NK107(tse)001:12512: bla ma la bsten par bya'o gsol ba ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:12513: gdab pa'i rim pa ni bkod pa yid bzhin gyis
NK107(tse)001:12514: nor bu rin po che 'byung ba'i rgyud las bla
NK107(tse)001:12515: ma rdo rje 'dzin pa ni khams gsum 'khor ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12516: gnyen cig po 'gro ba mgon med rnams kyi skyabs
NK107(tse)001:12517: thar pa'i lam skas chen po ste ma rig sel
NK107(tse)001:12518: ba'i sgron me la mun pa'i tshogs bdag skyabs su
NK107(tse)001:12519: mchi 'khor ba 'dam gyi tshogs dag tu bying ba
NK107(tse)001:12520: skyabs med bdag la skyobs dug gsum nyi mas barlana
NK107(tse)001:12521: bral ba'i sdug basngala skom la gnas pa la thugs
NK107(tse)001:12522: rje'i chu rgyun bdag la phob rtsub 'gyur dmyal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12523: me chen 'bar rang 'byung barlana gyis skems par mdzod
NK107(tse)001:12524: bla ma rdo rje 'chang ba'i lha lha yi lha
NK107(tse)001:12525: khyod phyag 'tshal bstod bdag ni bskal pa thog med
NK107(tse)001:12526: nas las kyis bcings pa'i sems can bdag 'byung ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12527: snod dang bral 'gyur nas 'od gsal dri med lus
NK107(tse)001:12528: ldan shog smra mngas ngag gi bcings pa bdag 'khrul
NK107(tse)001:12529: pa'i gtam rgyud zungs zad nas barjoda du med pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12530: don ldan shog 'gyu ba sems kyi rtog pas bcings
NK107(tse)001:12531: mi rtogs gsal ba'i snang mthong nas bsam 'das 'du
NK107(tse)001:12532: 'phro chad par shog de ltar lus ngag sems rnams
NK107(tse)001:12533: la byin gyis brlabs pas sku gsum gyi 'bras bu
NK107(tse)001:12534: tshad la phebs par mdzod ces gsol ba nyin lan
NK107(tse)001:12535: gsum mtshan lan gsum du btab pas sku gsung thugs
NK107(tse)001:12536: kyi byin brlabs barjoda kyis mi langs pa 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:12537: ni rang gi spyi bo'i gtsug tu a las zla
NK107(tse)001:12538: ba'i dal dag cing gsal ba de'i steng du nyi
NK107(tse)001:12539: ma'i dal 'gro zhing 'jam pa gnyis ga'u kha sbyar
NK107(tse)001:12540: ba lta bu'i nang nas 'od zer dpag tu med
NK107(tse)001:12541: pa 'phros pas rang gi bla ma spyi bo'i gtsug
NK107(tse)001:12542: tu spyan drangs pas bla ma gdan steng du bzhugs
NK107(tse)001:12543: te skyil krung phyed par bzhugs pa las gsol ba
NK107(tse)001:12544: btab pas bla ma yang bde ba'i ngo bor zhu
NK107(tse)001:12545: zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe bong las byang sems kyi thig
NK107(tse)001:12546: le sran ma'i rdog pa tsam mam nyungs 'bru tsam
NK107(tse)001:12547: phral phral byung ste spyi bor thim pas lus kyi
NK107(tse)001:12548: sdig pa dag nas rang gi lus bde ba'i ngo
NK107(tse)001:12549: bor zhu de nas mgrin par bsleb tsam na ngag
NK107(tse)001:12550: gi sdig pa dag nas ngag bde ba'i ngo bor
NK107(tse)001:12551: zhu de nas snying khar slebs pas sems kyi sdig
NK107(tse)001:12552: pa dag nas sems bde ba'i ngo bor zhu de
NK107(tse)001:12553: nas lte bar slebs pas lus ngag yid gsum tha
NK107(tse)001:12554: dad du 'dzin pa'i sdig pa dag nas lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:12555: yid gsum bde ba'i ngo bor zhu nas bde bar
NK107(tse)001:12556: 'gyur ba dang bde bas myos pa dang bde ba
NK107(tse)001:12557: rgyas pa dang phal cher 'phel ba la blo gnas
NK107(tse)001:12558: par bya'o 'di'i dus na bdag ji bzhin du sems
NK107(tse)001:12559: can thams cad kyang de ltar 'gyur ba la blo
NK107(tse)001:12560: gnas par bya'o de ltar nyin lan gsum mtshan lan
NK107(tse)001:12561: gsum du brtsams na bla ma'i byin rlabs 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:12562: la the tshom byar med do de yang 'jig rten
NK107(tse)001:12563: 'dir yang legs pa 'grub cing nyes pa spong bar
NK107(tse)001:12564: 'gyur la ma 'ongs pa'i dus na yang tshogs gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12565: rdzogs pa ni rdo rje bdud rtsi 'byung ba'i rgyud
NK107(tse)001:12566: las lha sku bskal ba 'bum phrag bsgom pa bas
NK107(tse)001:12567: bla ma'i sku bsgom bsod nams 'bum phrag yas des
NK107(tse)001:12568: na bla ma'i sku 'di rin thang che rdzogs rim
NK107(tse)001:12569: bsgom pa'i sngon 'gro dam pa'o zhes pas na shin
NK107(tse)001:12570: tu byin rlabs che ba'o yang bkod pa chen po
NK107(tse)001:12571: las yi dam lha sku bskal par bsgom pa las
NK107(tse)001:12572: bla ma'i sku la dmigs pa ma log na brgya
NK107(tse)001:12573: phrag stong gi char yang mi phod do bsnyen bsgrub
NK107(tse)001:12574: bzlas pa sa ya dung phyur bas bla ma'i gsol
NK107(tse)001:12575: tshig lan gsum barjoda pa ni nus pa 'bum phrag
NK107(tse)001:12576: char yang mi phod do rdzogs pa'i rim pa bskal
NK107(tse)001:12577: pa'i bar du yang 'du 'dzi yengs nas bsgom pa
NK107(tse)001:12578: bas bla ma rang sems dkyil du lan cig shar
NK107(tse)001:12579: ba tsam stong phrag nyi shur char yang mi phod
NK107(tse)001:12580: do des na bla ma bsgom dang bstod dang bsam
NK107(tse)001:12581: pas ni sangs rgyas 'bras bu cig car thob par
NK107(tse)001:12582: nges zhes pa la sogs pa lung bsgrangs na barjoda
NK107(tse)001:12583: kyis mi lang ngo de ltar bla ma rtag tu
NK107(tse)001:12584: bsten pa las byin barlaba 'byung ba yid ches pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12585: tshad ni skyes bu me'i 'obs la tshud pa sdug
NK107(tse)001:12586: basngala las grol bar 'dod pa bla ma yid la
NK107(tse)001:12587: dran pa dang de rgya mtsho gling la lus pa
NK107(tse)001:12588: dang rgyal po'i btson dong du tshud pa dang gshed
NK107(tse)001:12589: ma'i khongs su tshud pa thar bar 'dod pa bzhin
NK107(tse)001:12590: bla ma la 'dod pa skye ba yin no de'i
NK107(tse)001:12591: rtags su 'jig rten gyi zang zing ha cang ches
NK107(tse)001:12592: na rang gi mgo dang yan lag dang lus la
NK107(tse)001:12593: sogs pa rnams kyang bla ma la btang bar nus
NK107(tse)001:12594: pa dag 'byung ngo de ltar yang rgya mtsho'i gling
NK107(tse)001:12595: dang me chen 'obs rgyal po'i btson rar tshud pas
NK107(tse)001:12596: kyang bla ma'i dran pas grol bar nges zhes rdo
NK107(tse)001:12597: rje bkod pa'i rgyud las so de ltar 'gyur ba
NK107(tse)001:12598: ni byin rlabs la yid ches pa'i rtags yin no
NK107(tse)001:12599: bla ma'i bye brag bstan pa ni bla ma dang
NK107(tse)001:12600: slob dpon gnyis te slob dpon ni 'jig rten dang
NK107(tse)001:12601: 'das pa'i gnyis so 'jig rten ming du brtags shing
NK107(tse)001:12602: gang slob pa'o 'das pa'i ni spyi'i slob dpon yul
NK107(tse)001:12603: spyi'i slob dpon du khur ba yin la 'dren pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12604: slob dpon chos kyi sgor 'jug pa dam tshig dbang
NK107(tse)001:12605: gi slob dpon dbang bskur zhing sdom pa 'bogs pa
NK107(tse)001:12606: dang nyams chags skong ba'i slob dpon ni tshe'i dbang
NK107(tse)001:12607: bskur nas srog gi slob dpon no man ngag lung
NK107(tse)001:12608: gi slob dpon ni lung 'bogs pa dang man ngag
NK107(tse)001:12609: ston pa'i slob dpon no shes rgyud grol ba ni
NK107(tse)001:12610: grub pa'i mtha' rnams slob pa'o de ltar 'das pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12611: slob dpon drug po 'di rnams kyang dam tshig sa
NK107(tse)001:12612: ma ya bkod pa'i rgyud las spyi dang 'dren pa
NK107(tse)001:12613: nyams chags skong shes rgyud 'grol dang dam tshig dbang
NK107(tse)001:12614: man ngag lung gi slob dpon la khu bo pha
NK107(tse)001:12615: dang ma dang mig bu dang chung ma nor gyi
NK107(tse)001:12616: dbyig snying las lhag pa'i tshul bstan te sgo gsum
NK107(tse)001:12617: zol zogs med pa yis rab tu gces dang yid
NK107(tse)001:12618: 'thad dbul zhes pas so bla ma ni gnyis te
NK107(tse)001:12619: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang yan lag gi bla ma'o
NK107(tse)001:12620: bla ma zhes bya ba dbang bskur ba gzhir bzhag
NK107(tse)001:12621: nas yan lag gi bla ma gnyis ldan ni rgyud
NK107(tse)001:12622: bshad pa dang gsum ldan gyi de gnyis kyi steng
NK107(tse)001:12623: du man ngag bstan pa yan lag gi bla ma
NK107(tse)001:12624: gsum ldan zhes bya'o bzhi ldan ni rtsa ba'i bla
NK107(tse)001:12625: mar 'agro'o dbang bskur ba dang rgyud bshad pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12626: man ngag bstan pa dang da lta yang bla ma
NK107(tse)001:12627: de'i chos rnams nyams su len pa dang bzhi rang
NK107(tse)001:12628: la 'dzom na rtsa ba'i bla ma zhes bya bar
NK107(tse)001:12629: 'agro'o de yang slob dpon drug po de yang 'jig
NK107(tse)001:12630: rten du bzhag pas zhing las khyad par che'o de
NK107(tse)001:12631: ltar drug kyang rim gyis so 'di dag kyang dge
NK107(tse)001:12632: ba'i stobs bdun 'gyur bdun 'gyur du yod do de
NK107(tse)001:12633: dag rim gyis log pa las yan lag gi bla
NK107(tse)001:12634: ma gnyis ldan che'o de bdun pas gsum ldan khyad
NK107(tse)001:12635: par che'o de gnyis ka 'bum phrag bdun du bltabs
NK107(tse)001:12636: pa bas rtsa ba'i bla ma che bar yang he
NK107(tse)001:12637: ru ka mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud nas bshad do
NK107(tse)001:12638: yan lag bla ma 'bum phrag bdun gser ni rang
NK107(tse)001:12639: lus tsam mchod kyang rtsa ba'i bla ma srang gcig
NK107(tse)001:12640: gis legs par mchod pa'i dngos grub ni b+hud d+ha
NK107(tse)001:12641: yis kyang barjoda par dka' zhes pas so ji ltar
NK107(tse)001:12642: mnyes par bya ba ni gang zag rab kyis bla
NK107(tse)001:12643: ma mnyes par bya ba dang 'bring rnams kyis mnyes
NK107(tse)001:12644: par ji ltar bya ba dang tha ma rnams kyis
NK107(tse)001:12645: mnyes par ji ltar bya'o rab rnams kyis mnyes pa
NK107(tse)001:12646: bzhi yin te dad pas mnyes pa ni mgo mjug
NK107(tse)001:12647: thams cad du 'pho 'gyur dang skyo ngal med pa'o
NK107(tse)001:12648: de ltar yang yon tan gyi nang nas dad pa
NK107(tse)001:12649: mchog dang stong gsum gang ba'i b+hud d+ha la mchod
NK107(tse)001:12650: pas stong sum bskang mchod pas 'di nyid mnyes pa
NK107(tse)001:12651: brgya'i char mi 'phod zhes pa dang shes rab kyis
NK107(tse)001:12652: mnyes pa ni bla ma'i gsung 'gros la lhag chad
NK107(tse)001:12653: med ston shes pas te bla ma'i bstan pa'i srol
NK107(tse)001:12654: ma nyams pa'o de ltar yang dpal 'khor lo chub
NK107(tse)001:12655: par rol pa las shes rab mchog gi bla ma
NK107(tse)001:12656: la ngag gis mnyes pa byas pa ni sangs rgyas
NK107(tse)001:12657: rnams kyis gsungs pa'i chos bskal pa brgya phrag mang
NK107(tse)001:12658: por yang su yis klags shing barjoda pa las bsod
NK107(tse)001:12659: nams 'bum phrag bsam yas so brtson 'grus kyis mnyes
NK107(tse)001:12660: pa ni ji skad gsungs pa'i don nyan zhing de
NK107(tse)001:12661: nyid la brtson 'grus bton nas byed pa'o ting nge
NK107(tse)001:12662: 'dzin gyis mnyes pa ni 'jig rten bya ba spangs
NK107(tse)001:12663: nas ri khrod la sogs par bsgrub pas lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:12664: gi rtags mang po ston nas sems can gzhan 'jug
NK107(tse)001:12665: par 'gyur bas bla ma mnyes pa ni bskyed rims
NK107(tse)001:12666: bskal pa gsum du bsgoms pa las bla ma mnyes
NK107(tse)001:12667: pa'i bsod nams dpag gis dpogs pa ma yin no
NK107(tse)001:12668: 'bring po rnams kyis mnyes pa ni lus kyi bya
NK107(tse)001:12669: bas bla ma mnyes par byed pa ste bla ma'i
NK107(tse)001:12670: las dang bya bas mnyes par byed pa dang srog
NK107(tse)001:12671: gis mel tshes mnyes pa byed pa ste tshe'i bar
NK107(tse)001:12672: chad me dang chu la sogs pa dang gzhan rgyal
NK107(tse)001:12673: po'i chad pa 'byung ba'i dus na bdag gis bla
NK107(tse)001:12674: ma'i dod par 'gro bar nus pa dang mi gzhan
NK107(tse)001:12675: gyis bla ma'i srog la bar chad byed na bdag
NK107(tse)001:12676: gis de slar gsad nus pa dang don gyis bla
NK107(tse)001:12677: ma'i don du bdag gis srog gtong bar nus pa'o
NK107(tse)001:12678: de ltar yang dpal bdud rtsi bcud bsdus kyi rgyud
NK107(tse)001:12679: las gal te bla ma la gnod pa'i ma rung
NK107(tse)001:12680: sems kyis bcom pa la bdag nyid kyis ni bsad
NK107(tse)001:12681: byas na sems can 'bum gyis srog bton pas bsod
NK107(tse)001:12682: nams 'di ni char mi phod de'i phyir na bsod
NK107(tse)001:12683: nams zhes dus gsum bzhugs pa'i b+hud d+ha yis lung
NK107(tse)001:12684: du bstan pa kho na'o bla ma'i bya ba rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:12685: byas na 'di yang de dang mnyam pa'o zhes pas
NK107(tse)001:12686: so rang gi lus btsongs nas bla ma mnyes par
NK107(tse)001:12687: byed pa rnams so tha ma'i mnyes pa ni rdzas
NK107(tse)001:12688: dang longs spyod kyis mnyes par byed pa dang rgyal
NK107(tse)001:12689: srid dang 'khor rnams phul nas mnyes par byed pa
NK107(tse)001:12690: dang 'khor gsum yongs su dag par bya ste ci
NK107(tse)001:12691: yod pas bla ma mnyes par bya'o de ltar bla
NK107(tse)001:12692: ma mnyes pa'i thabs sna tshogs pas mnyes par byed
NK107(tse)001:12693: pa'o de ltar yang bkod pa chen po las che
NK107(tse)001:12694: dang chung pa'i bye brag gang bla ma mnyes par
NK107(tse)001:12695: gyur pa'o bsod nams shin tu barjoda par dka' zhes
NK107(tse)001:12696: pas na bla ma ci dang ci'i sgo nas kyang
NK107(tse)001:12697: mnyes par bya'o bla ma mtshan nyid tshang ba'i bla
NK107(tse)001:12698: ma la nyes par bltas pa'i nyes dmigs ni barjoda
NK107(tse)001:12699: kyis mi lang ngo gzhan dag lta ci smos te
NK107(tse)001:12700: rmi lam na bla ma la brnyas pa byas pa
NK107(tse)001:12701: tsam yang nyes pa 'di tsam 'byung ba ni dam
NK107(tse)001:12702: tshig sa ma ya bkod pa las gal te rdo
NK107(tse)001:12703: rje slob dpon la rmi lam dus na lus ngag
NK107(tse)001:12704: yid nyes pa phra mo tsam byas na khyi'i skye
NK107(tse)001:12705: ba brgya blangs nas rme sha can du skye bar
NK107(tse)001:12706: 'gyur de nas sems can dmyal ba yi tsha grangs
NK107(tse)001:12707: gnyis ka'i sdug basngala nyid nyams su myong ba kho
NK107(tse)001:12708: na'o zhes pas so rmi lam mi dad pa'am mi
NK107(tse)001:12709: gus pa'am mi mos pa skyes pa tsam las kyang
NK107(tse)001:12710: de tsam na dngos su byas na barjoda kyis mi
NK107(tse)001:12711: lang ngo gal te bla ma la lus kyi sgo
NK107(tse)001:12712: nas nyes pa byas na shi 'phos ma thag tu
NK107(tse)001:12713: rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'agro'o ngag gis byas na gnod
NK107(tse)001:12714: sbyin gyi lus blangs nas de nas dmyal ba'i snang
NK107(tse)001:12715: bar 'gyur ro sems kyi sgo nas byas na tshe
NK107(tse)001:12716: gsum gyi 'og tu sems kyi snang ba dmyal ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12717: sdug basngala du 'khrul nas 'gro bar nges so de
NK107(tse)001:12718: ltar nyes pa bshags pa'i tshad ni nyes pa lan
NK107(tse)001:12719: gsum dang bzhi dang bcu la sogs pa rnams la
NK107(tse)001:12720: bshags pas 'dag rang gis lo grangs tsam 'das na
NK107(tse)001:12721: ni bshags pa'i yul min no de ltar yang sa
NK107(tse)001:12722: ma ya bkod pa las gal te bla mar brnyas
NK107(tse)001:12723: pa'i mis lan ni bdun nam bcu dag las 'gyod
NK107(tse)001:12724: par byas te bshags pas 'byang rang lo 'das nas
NK107(tse)001:12725: bshags pa'i yul rdo rje sems dpas ma gnang ngo
NK107(tse)001:12726: zhes so yon tan la la dmigs nas brten pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12727: khyad par ni de yang dus thams cad du bla
NK107(tse)001:12728: ma'i skyon dor zhing yon tan ci 'dug pa la
NK107(tse)001:12729: bsam zhing bla ma bsten pas rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:12730: kyis 'dod pa'i don 'grub par nges so lhag ma
NK107(tse)001:12731: ni bla ma'i rim pa na gsal lo de dag
NK107(tse)001:12732: dkyus dang sbyar ba ni gzhung rang gsal lo da
NK107(tse)001:12733: ni gnyis pa rtsa ba dang yan lag gi bla
NK107(tse)001:12734: ma mnyes pa'i thabs ji ltar bya ba yang rtsa
NK107(tse)001:12735: ba yan lag ces pa gzhung gsal lo da ni
NK107(tse)001:12736: gsum pa dus thams cad du bla ma bsten pa
NK107(tse)001:12737: las yon tan ji ltar 'byung ba dpe dang bcas
NK107(tse)001:12738: ste bstan pa la yang bsten pa de las yon
NK107(tse)001:12739: tan ni zhes pa la sogs pa gzhung gsal lo
NK107(tse)001:12740: zhes gzhung don lnga bcu pa bla ma'i rim pa
NK107(tse)001:12741: bstan pa dang bkur bar bya ba'i rim pa ji
NK107(tse)001:12742: ltar yin pa la gsum du byas nas bstan no
NK107(tse)001:12743: da ni le'u dang po'i zhus don nga gcig pa
NK107(tse)001:12744: phyi rol gyi 'byung ba'i rtags la brten nas sems
NK107(tse)001:12745: can rnams kyi las bye brag bstan pa la yan
NK107(tse)001:12746: lag gi don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po phyi
NK107(tse)001:12747: rol gyi 'byung ba dngos kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12748: ni phyi rol 'byung ba rtags pa'i mtshan nyid sra
NK107(tse)001:12749: ba dang zhes pa gzhung gsal lo da ni gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12750: pa phyi rol gyi 'byung ba'i mtshan nyid la brtags
NK107(tse)001:12751: pas rgyal khams su las kyi legs nyes kyi bye
NK107(tse)001:12752: brag bstan pa ni 'byung ba'i bslab bya'i dum bu
NK107(tse)001:12753: yis zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te bar 'dir
NK107(tse)001:12754: bla ma 'dir lta bu gcig gsung ngo dus lnga
NK107(tse)001:12755: brgya dus kyi snyigs ma la b+hud d+ha'i bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12756: nub pa'i tshe 'gro ba rnams kyis g.yo la sogs
NK107(tse)001:12757: pa rnams kyang nag por byas nas 'ong ste de
NK107(tse)001:12758: yang gling rnams las khyad par du 'phags pa lho'i
NK107(tse)001:12759: 'dzam bu gling ste sa las khyad par can la
NK107(tse)001:12760: bsags pa'i sa zhes bya'o 'dir gang zag log sred
NK107(tse)001:12761: can zhes dam pa'i chos kyi mtshan nyid bzung nas
NK107(tse)001:12762: tshul bzhin du mi byed par b+hud d+ha'i bka' la
NK107(tse)001:12763: ras chod dang gzu lum byed pa gsang sngags khyad
NK107(tse)001:12764: par can rnams tshong dus kyi 'o ma smod pa
NK107(tse)001:12765: dang lta bsgom log pa la 'god pa dang mi
NK107(tse)001:12766: mthun pa'i lta bsgom mang po yang 'di'i dus na
NK107(tse)001:12767: 'byung ngo de lta bu byung ba'i dbang gis mi
NK107(tse)001:12768: mthun pa'i gdon mang po dang mi rnams kyang spyod
NK107(tse)001:12769: pa 'gyur nas 'ong ste lung bstan ma byung bar
NK107(tse)001:12770: byung zer ba dang dgongs pa med par yod zer
NK107(tse)001:12771: ba dang lta ba ma rtogs par rtogs zer ba
NK107(tse)001:12772: dang drod rtags med par yod zer ba dang yi
NK107(tse)001:12773: dam lha'i zhal ma mthong bar mthong zer ba dang
NK107(tse)001:12774: btsun pa kun kyang rang gis 'du khang mi bskyod
NK107(tse)001:12775: par sde pa rtsod cing mtshon gyis lus bsrung ba
NK107(tse)001:12776: dang mi mthun pa'i ltas mang po 'byung ba'o mi
NK107(tse)001:12777: 'dra ba'i ltas mang po byung ba'i dus na sum
NK107(tse)001:12778: cu rtsa gsum la sogs pa'i lha rnams ni 'dzam
NK107(tse)001:12779: bu gling pa'i mgon byed pa yin pas 'dzam bu
NK107(tse)001:12780: gling na chos tshul bzhin byed pa 'byung na ni
NK107(tse)001:12781: lha rnams kyis bsod nams 'phel lo log sred can
NK107(tse)001:12782: byung na ni lha rnams g.yul 'pham pa dang bsod
NK107(tse)001:12783: nams chung ngu 'gro bas 'dzam bu gling du lha
NK107(tse)001:12784: rnams kyis nyul le zla ba gcig tu gsum gtong
NK107(tse)001:12785: pas 'di'i dus na bdud las rgyal ba'i cho 'phrul
NK107(tse)001:12786: gtong ba ste 'das pa'i chos la mi dga' ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12787: bdud rnams kyis nyul le btang bas 'dzam bu gling
NK107(tse)001:12788: 'gro ba rnams kyi snying du zhugs nas lta spyod
NK107(tse)001:12789: phyin ci log tu btang ba la sogs pa mang
NK107(tse)001:12790: ngo de ltar song ba'i dbang gis lha rnams g.yul
NK107(tse)001:12791: 'pham ste mya ngan khang par zhugs nas smon lam
NK107(tse)001:12792: 'debs te ser chags thams cad kyis chos tshul bzhin
NK107(tse)001:12793: mi byed pas bdag cag rnams kyi bsod nams 'bribs
NK107(tse)001:12794: 'di dag gis nyes pas kyi hud 'dzam bu gling
NK107(tse)001:12795: pa'i ser chags tsam dmyal ba'i gnas su skye bar
NK107(tse)001:12796: shog cig ces smon lam btab pas lha rnams ni
NK107(tse)001:12797: smon lam mthu btsan pa yin pas dus de tsam
NK107(tse)001:12798: gyis ser chags tsam dmyal ba'i gnas su skye bar
NK107(tse)001:12799: nges so 'di'i dus na lha rnams 'dzam bu gling
NK107(tse)001:12800: skyong ba yin te bsod nams 'bri bas de'i nus
NK107(tse)001:12801: pa med pas nad dang mu ge dang gdon dang
NK107(tse)001:12802: mi mthun pa'i bye brag rnams ston pa dang dge
NK107(tse)001:12803: ba'i bye brag rnams ston par byed pa la phyogs
NK107(tse)001:12804: skyong ba rnams la lha rnams kyis bskul te khyed
NK107(tse)001:12805: rnams kyis 'dzam bu'i gling gi legs nyes ston pa
NK107(tse)001:12806: la nam makha'i cho 'phrul bcu gnyis la brten nas
NK107(tse)001:12807: legs nyes dge dang mi dge ston cig zhes bskul
NK107(tse)001:12808: bas phyogs skyong rnams kyis 'dzam bu gling pa'i 'gro
NK107(tse)001:12809: ba rnams la ltas bstan pa'i phyir sprin la brten
NK107(tse)001:12810: nas legs nyes kyi gzhi bstan pa dang rlung dang
NK107(tse)001:12811: barlangasa pa dang sgra dang 'od dang sa g.yo ba
NK107(tse)001:12812: dang nyi ma dang zla ba gzas zin dang kha
NK107(tse)001:12813: char gyi khyad par ji ltar 'babs bstan pa dang
NK107(tse)001:12814: gtam ngan dang skar mda' sa la lhung ba dang
NK107(tse)001:12815: gzugs brnyan dang nam mkha' stong sangs kyis rnam par
NK107(tse)001:12816: dag ste bcu gnyis kyis 'dzam bu'i gling du dge
NK107(tse)001:12817: ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyis khyad par ston
NK107(tse)001:12818: pa ni de yang bsgrub pa pos lo'i mgo dang
NK107(tse)001:12819: zla ba'i dang po ni lo gang byung ba'i zla
NK107(tse)001:12820: ba dang po byi ba de'i tshes gsum nas bzung
NK107(tse)001:12821: ste dus nges pa bcu gnyis dang sbyar na sprin
NK107(tse)001:12822: kha dog nag po la sogs pa'i bye brag la
NK107(tse)001:12823: brten nas dge ba dang mi dge ba bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12824: ni gsang ba'i nyi ma nas bshad de dngos po
NK107(tse)001:12825: kha bsgyur ba'i gnad kyis khams gsum gyis legs nyes
NK107(tse)001:12826: bde sdug rnams brtags pas 'gro ba gzhan la phan
NK107(tse)001:12827: thogs pa'i dgos pa yod do de yang rgyal po
NK107(tse)001:12828: dang dge sbyong dang sgom chen pa dang byis pa
NK107(tse)001:12829: dang bud med dang rgan pa dang gzhon pa rnams
NK107(tse)001:12830: la ji ltar 'gyur ba la sogs pa da ros
NK107(tse)001:12831: po kha bsgyur gyis sdong sbyar gnyis ka'i nam makha'i
NK107(tse)001:12832: yal lugs las legs par bstan no de yang dkyus
NK107(tse)001:12833: dang sbyar na 'byung ba bslab bya'i dum bu yis
NK107(tse)001:12834: ni phyi rol la bslab pa'i bye brag ston pas
NK107(tse)001:12835: phyi rol gyi 'byung rtags la brten nas sems can
NK107(tse)001:12836: gyi las kyi bye brag bstan pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:12837: gzhung du bstan no da ni gsum pa phyogs nges
NK107(tse)001:12838: pa la brten nas dge ba dang mi dge ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12839: khyad par gyi bye brag bstan pa yang 'dzam gling
NK107(tse)001:12840: rang sa'i phyogs bzung ste zhes pa la sogs pa
NK107(tse)001:12841: gzhung du rtogs zhes dris lan nga gcig pa phyi
NK107(tse)001:12842: rol gyi 'byung rtags la brten nas sems can gyi
NK107(tse)001:12843: las kyi bye brag bstan pa la gsum du byas
NK107(tse)001:12844: nas bstan no da ni le'u dang po'i dris lan
NK107(tse)001:12845: nga gnyis pa lus rnam par bzhag pa dus kyis
NK107(tse)001:12846: grol ba'i gnad la brten nas rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK107(tse)001:12847: gshis bstan pa la yan lag gis don gnyis kyis
NK107(tse)001:12848: bstan pa'i dang po 'khrul pa ldog pa'i dus nges
NK107(tse)001:12849: pa bstan pa ni de yang gnad kyis grol ba'i
NK107(tse)001:12850: dus ni sngon gyis las 'phro sad pa ni sus
NK107(tse)001:12851: ma bstan par sdom gyis song ste 'khrul ba zhig
NK107(tse)001:12852: pa yod de las 'phro sad de dper na me
NK107(tse)001:12853: dang rtsa 'phrad pa lta bu'o de yang snga ma'i
NK107(tse)001:12854: las chos nyid mngon sum la mos pa tsam la
NK107(tse)001:12855: de'i 'phro 'di nyid la las dang bag chags chos
NK107(tse)001:12856: nyid du sad pas sus kyang ma bstan par grol
NK107(tse)001:12857: ba yod de 'dis 'gro ba gzhan gyi mos pas
NK107(tse)001:12858: spyod pa tsam las b+hud d+ha'i sa la 'god nus
NK107(tse)001:12859: pa ni ma yin no yang 'byung ba las grub
NK107(tse)001:12860: pa lus kyi nges pa'i gnod pa las grol ba
NK107(tse)001:12861: ni lus 'byung ba bzhi'i rang bzhin las ma gtogs
NK107(tse)001:12862: pa gang yang med pas thog ma lus chags pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12863: dus na ma'i mngal du mas rang gi 'byung ba
NK107(tse)001:12864: dag par byed pa'i rten 'brel du spyod lam dang
NK107(tse)001:12865: zas skom la sogs pa 'byung ba dag pa'i bya
NK107(tse)001:12866: ba rnams byas pas de nas ma'i mngal nas thon
NK107(tse)001:12867: pa'i dus na lus ngag rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12868: 'byung ba bzhi rang bzhin gyis dag pas las dang
NK107(tse)001:12869: nyon mong pa rnams rang bzhin gyis 'gyur nas skad
NK107(tse)001:12870: cig la chos nyid kyi don rgyud la skyes pa
NK107(tse)001:12871: dang gcig char du grol ba yang yod de 'dis
NK107(tse)001:12872: ni sems can don dngos su byed pa ni ma
NK107(tse)001:12873: yin no gzhan 'jug par 'gyur ba'i yan lag tsam
NK107(tse)001:12874: zhig yod do yang sems can gyi gnad kyis grol
NK107(tse)001:12875: ba ni bla ma'i man ngag chos nyid mngon sum
NK107(tse)001:12876: gyi gnad la brten nas goms pa byas pas 'di
NK107(tse)001:12877: nyid la rig pa tshad la phebs nas chos nyid
NK107(tse)001:12878: zad snang las grol ba'o 'dis ni 'gro ba dpag
NK107(tse)001:12879: tu med pa b+hud d+ha'i sa la 'god nus so
NK107(tse)001:12880: gsum pa ni 'khrul pa rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12881: rtog pa rnams dag pas rnal 'byor pa rang gi
NK107(tse)001:12882: dus rnyed nas skal ldan de'i 'khrul pa ldog pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12883: dus yin no zhes 'khrul pa ldog pa'i dus nges
NK107(tse)001:12884: pa bstan nas da ni gnyis pa bstan pa rin
NK107(tse)001:12885: po che'i babs nges pas 'gro ba rnams kyi khyad
NK107(tse)001:12886: par gyi dus bstan pa ni de yang bstan pa
NK107(tse)001:12887: zhes pa dngos kyi ston pa sku gsung thugs kyi
NK107(tse)001:12888: sprul pa dngos yin la gzugs brnyan gyi mdo sde
NK107(tse)001:12889: 'dul ba mngon pa gsum mo babs zhes pa ni
NK107(tse)001:12890: 'gro ba rnams kyi bsod nams kyi bye brag las
NK107(tse)001:12891: stong pa ni gong du bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib la
NK107(tse)001:12892: dgongs te skal pa chen po gcig la drug cha'i
NK107(tse)001:12893: bar la stongs pa yin te bstan pa yod kyang
NK107(tse)001:12894: 'gro ba rnams 'di nyid la grol ba ma yin
NK107(tse)001:12895: no drug cha la stongs pa 'di lta ste bstan
NK107(tse)001:12896: pa dam pa 'di nyid kyi sgor zhugs so tsam
NK107(tse)001:12897: grol bar nges so drug cha la mthar byed gzhon
NK107(tse)001:12898: nu zhes bya ba'i dus te 'di nyid kyi lung
NK107(tse)001:12899: bstan pa tsam la brten nas kyang 'gro ba rnams
NK107(tse)001:12900: gcig char dang rim gyis grol bar nges so lhag
NK107(tse)001:12901: ma zhes bya ba ni bskal pa gcig gi phyed
NK107(tse)001:12902: la dgongs pa yin no 'di dag ni gang zag
NK107(tse)001:12903: so so'i dus te rang gi 'bad pa dang rtsol
NK107(tse)001:12904: ba la rag las pas na gcig tu nges pa
NK107(tse)001:12905: med do 'di'i dus kyi tshad ni mkha' 'gro ma
NK107(tse)001:12906: bsil sbyin gyi 'khor lo nas bshad do des na
NK107(tse)001:12907: rdzogs pa chen po kha gcig gis bstan pa'i dus
NK107(tse)001:12908: 'grol ba'i gnad la dgongs nas bshad pa la kha
NK107(tse)001:12909: cig la tshig tu 'bad pa med par grol bar
NK107(tse)001:12910: 'dod pa ni de lta ma yin te bstan pa'i
NK107(tse)001:12911: dus kyi gnad shes pas de nyid dang dus mtshungs
NK107(tse)001:12912: pas grol ba'o gong du bstan pa ni bskal pa
NK107(tse)001:12913: 'di la b+hud d+ha ba 'di tsam cig byung zhes
NK107(tse)001:12914: bya ba dang gang zag sngon gyi las 'phro sad
NK107(tse)001:12915: nas grol ba la bcu phrag stong gi cha gcig
NK107(tse)001:12916: 'gyur ba'i 'gyur gyis grol ba'i las brgya phrag lnga'i
NK107(tse)001:12917: cha sems can gyi gnad kyis grol ba ni rang
NK107(tse)001:12918: gi brtson 'grus la rag las pa nyid yin pas
NK107(tse)001:12919: na gong dang mtshungs so zhes zhus lan nga gnyis
NK107(tse)001:12920: pa dus kyis grol ba'i gnad la brten nas rdzogs
NK107(tse)001:12921: pa chen po'i gshis bstan pa la gnyis su byas
